仿宋官窑特徵的冰裂纹作地，備木雕鏤空寶珠頂蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('390', 'A Blue Ground Tea Caddy, Mid Qing Dynasty', '清中 藍釉茶罐', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_139_1.jpg', '139', '12,000 - 20,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', 'H23cm，D23cm<br />\n此罐上闊下斂，平底，通體施單色藍釉，釉不及底別有一番拙趣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('391', 'A Pair of Tin Tea Caddies', '古錫丸形茶罐一對', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_140_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_140_2.jpg', '140', '12,000 - 18,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '共箱<br />\nH9.5cm，D9cm', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('392', 'A Pair of Tin Tea Caddies, Qing Dynasty', '清 楊興漫遂 錫茶罐一對', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_141_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_141_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_141_3.jpg', '141', '6,000 - 10,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '底款：楊興漫遂<br />\nH7cm，D8.5cm', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('393', 'A Gold-Plated Yixing Teapot', '包金梨式朱泥茶壺', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_142_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_142_2.jpg', '142', '22,000 - 38,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '共箱<br />\nH7cm，D9.5cm<br />\n壺身光素無紋，泥料有皺皮，壺咀及口沿包金，造型佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('394', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot with Signature', '紫泥合菱壺', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_143_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_143_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_143_3.jpg', '143', '15,000 - 28,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '底款：江寅仙<br />\n蓋款：江、寅仙<br />\nH10cm，D19.5cm<br />\n江寅仙師承吳雲根，朱可心，裴石民及蔣蓉，其工藝集各派所長，屢有佳作；此壺是江寅仙早期作品，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('395', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '孟臣款 紫泥具輪珠茶壺', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_144_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_144_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_144_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_144_4.jpg', '144', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '底款：孟臣<br />\n箱籤：宜興窯 孟臣銘<br />\nH10cm，D10cm<br />\n壺身光素無紋，胎質厚薄適中。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('396', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot with a Bamboo Handle', '陳鳴遠  段泥繪三足提梁紫泥茶壺', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_145_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_145_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_145_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_145_4.jpg', '145', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '底款：圓印「陳」及方印「鳴遠」<br />\nH15cm，D16.5cm<br />\n此壺造型特別，壺身有段泥繪飾，為山水風景及大石，蓋有花竹紋，竹節提把。<br />\n陳鳴遠，號鶴峰，又號石霞山人，壺隱，為清朝康熙年間宜興紫砂大師。他出生於紫砂壺世家，祖籍江蘇宜興。其作品極具文化和藝術價值，被紫砂壺界視為經典。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('397', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot with Signature, Republic Period', '民初  梅花詩文提梁紫泥壺', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_146_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_146_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_146_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_146_5.jpg', '146', '30,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '器身銘刻：坐中皆士左右修竹、永隆<br />\n蓋款：江海<br />\n底款：坐中皆士左右修竹<br />\n連玻璃框<br />\nH14cm，D13cm<br />\n壺身堅挺飽滿，刻功有力，鈕摘為雌龍兩條，一大一小，造形特別。<br />\n外壁書畫「坐中皆士左右修竹」，嫻章「小山」，「石泉畫」，流下有款「永隆」。另一邊刻喜鵲登梅圖，「陸」字款。壺底款「乍浦陳永隆製」；蓋內款「江海」。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('398', 'A Set of Five Carved  Copper Chataku by Honma Takusa', '琢齋作 斑紫銅地圖紋茶托一套五客', '16', '/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_147_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a5/LOTNO_147_2.jpg', '147', '18,000 - 28,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed description, please refer to the Chinese site', '底款：琢齋<br />\nD11cm', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('399', 'A Set of Five Carved Copper Chataku', '玉真作 斑紫銅花卉茶托 一套五客', '16', '/public/pi