finder and front lens cap.', '此機連同Biogon CF 4.5/38mm鏡頭 (#7161804)、A12 (#RE3346193)、取景器及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2017', 'Xpan 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', '. 					Xpan 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_171_7.JPG', '171', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The lens here comes with box and papers, both lens caps, viewfinder, hood and center filter.', '此鏡連同包裝證書、前後蓋、取景器、遮光罩及中灰濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2018', 'Hasselblad Xpan II Set', '. 					Hasselblad Xpan II Set', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_172_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_172_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_172_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_172_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_172_5.JPG', '172', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'Two lenses are included: one is the 4/90mm (#8ZSP18506), with front cap and keeper. Another is 4/45mm (#8YSP27609) with keeper, front cap, box and certificate. Camera completes with box, papers and body cap.', '此機配有兩支鏡頭，一支是4/90mm (#8ZSP18506)連前蓋及膠盅；另一支是4/45mm (#8YSP27609)連膠盅、前蓋及包裝證書。相機則帶包裝證書及機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2019', 'Hasselblad CFi 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '. 					Hasselblad CFi 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_173_6.JPG', '173', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classic lens of Hasselblad features apochromatic correction. It comes with both lens caps.', '此拍品為哈蘇的經典鏡頭，有消色差功能，使成象質素更為銳利。配有前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2020', 'Elcan 5/117mm', '. 					Elcan 5/117mm', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_174_6.JPG', '174', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an Elcan 5/117mm lens for Hasselblad in F mount, very rare. It is probably a pre series lens because of its special serial number. The lens comes with both lens caps and filter adapter.', '這是徠卡製造的Elcan 5/117mm鏡頭，為Hasselbald F卡口，產量極少。其鏡身編號非在正常生產之列，估計為試驗版鏡頭。此鏡配有前後蓋及濾鏡接環。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2021', 'Contax IIIa', '. 					Contax IIIa', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_175_8.JPG', '175', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Contax IIIa camera produced between 1950 and 1960. It comes with Carl Zeiss Sonnar 1.5/50mm lens (#1165561) and leather case.', 'IIIa是康泰時1950至1960年生產的最後一款疊影相機，它比IIa多了一個測光錶，而且配有獨特的捲閘式快門。此機配有蔡司Sonnar 1.5/50mm鏡頭 (#1165561)及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2022', 'Nikon H Microscope', '. 					Nikon H Microscope', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_176_8.JPG', '176', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'It seems like a classic camera more than a microscope at the first glance, and actually, the Nikon Model H field microscope was a laboratory-grade diagnostic instrument which made in 1960’s. This microscope comes with a 10x objective.', '此拍品外型有如一台相機，但其實它是藝康於1960年代為醫學研究而生產的顯微鏡。此顯微鏡連有一個放大10倍的物鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2023', 'Nikkor-H.C 2/5cm Chrome', '. 					Nikkor-H.C 2/5cm Chrome', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_177_7.JPG', '177', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This kind of lens was introduced in 1946 along with Nikon’s first rangefinder camera, Nikon One. It is a very popular lens for Nikon S series camera. The lens is belonged to very early production batch. Comes with lens hood with front lens cap and metal case.', '此款鏡頭於1946年連同藝康首款旁軸相機Nikon 1一同推出，是藝康S系列中其中一款最受歡迎的鏡頭，此鏡頭屬極早期生產批次。配有遮光罩連鏡頭前蓋及金屬儲存罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2024', 'Zeiss Ikon Stereotars C 3.5/35mm Chrome', '. 					Zeiss Ikon Stereotars C 3.5/35mm Chrome', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_178_7.JPG', '178', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is launched by Zeiss Ikon in around 1952 for Contax stereo camera use. Lens was made in Germany. It comes with leather case, beam splitter, viewfinder, both lens caps, and stereo proxar 20, 30 and 50.', '這鏡頭由Zeiss Ikon於德國製造， 1952年左右推出市場，提供予康泰時立體相機所用。配有皮套、立體鏡分束器、取景器、鏡頭前後蓋及20、30和50的濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2025', 'Carl Zeiss Distagon ZF 2.8/25mm Black “Prototype”', '. 					Carl Zeiss Distagon ZF 2.8/25mm Black “Prototype”', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_179_6.JPG', '179', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'ZF 2.8/25mm is a discontinued lens for Nikon camera. This is a prototype lens, comes with hood and rear lens cap.', 'ZF 2.8/25mm是蔡司為藝康相機生產的鏡頭，已經停產。此拍品是原型鏡，連遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2026', 'Carl Zeiss Biogon ZM 2/35mm Chrome “Prototype”', '. 					Carl Zeiss Biogon ZM 2/35mm Chrome “Prototype”', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_180_6.JPG', '180', '', '15,340', null, null, null, null, 'Carl Zeiss ZM 2/35mm is made for Leica M series. This lot is a prototype lens, very rare. It comes with both lens caps and leather case.', 'ZM 2/35mm是蔡司為徠卡M系列相機生產的標準鏡頭。此拍品是原型鏡，配有前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2027', 'Le Coultre Compass Kit', '. 					Le Coultre Compass Kit', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_181_7.JPG', '181', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'LeCoultre Compass was manufactured by Jaeger-LeCoultre in 30’s, around 4,000 pieces were made. Although this exceptional camera is as small as a cigarette packet, it featured an exposure meter, range finder, EV indicator, angle viewfinder, telescope lens shape, built in filters and a device for panoramic and stereoscopic views. Extremely rare.', '此相機是由著名瑞士手錶廠家Jaeger-LeCoultre於三十年代生產。雖然Compass相機大小像一個香煙盒般，但卻集合了曝光表、測距儀、EV值指示、取景器、伸縮式遮光罩、內置濾鏡及可以搭配全景和立體取景裝置於一身；可謂麻雀雖小，五臟俱全。當時大約只生產了4,000台，但經過戰火及歲月，能保存到今天的已經為數不多。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2028', 'FOCA Camera', '. 					FOCA Camera', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_182_6.JPG', '182', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Foca camera was a French-built brand of rangefinder cameras and its production started in 1945. It comes with Oplarex 1.9/5cm lens (#11.840).', 'Foca相機是由一間法國公司製造的旁軸相機，於1945年開始投產。此機連同Oplarex 1.9/5cm鏡頭 (#11.840)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2029', 'ISO Standard Chrome', '. 					ISO Standard Chrome', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_183_7.JPG', '183', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera was manufactured by the same Italian company as ISO reporter. After being sold to German company Hensoldt, it was renamed to Henso Standard. It comes with IRIAR 2.8/5cm lens (#00237) and front lens cap.', '此機與ISO Reporter一樣，是由意大利ISO公司生產；於五十年代售于德國Hensoldt公司之後，型號改為Henso Standard。它配有IRIAR 2.8/5cm 鏡頭 (#00237)及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2030', 'ISO Reporter Chrome', '. 					ISO Reporter Chrome', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_184_9.JPG', '184', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The ISO Reporter was made by ISO company in Italy in the 50’s and was rebrand by German Hensoldt company as Henso Reporter. The standard lens IRIAR is rarely with ISO or Henso Reporter. This lot comes with IRIAR 2.8/5cm lens (#00979), front lens cap and leather case.', '此機於50年代由意大利ISO公司生產，35mm菲林格式。之後ISO公司將此型號售于德國Hensoldt公司，型號便改為Henso Reporter。在搭配ISO Reporter或者Henso Reporter的套機中，IRIAR 2.8/5cm鏡頭是最少見的。此拍品配有IRIAR 2.8/5cm鏡頭 (#00979)、鏡頭前蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2031', 'Janua San Giorgio “Leica Copy”', '. 					Janua San Giorgio “Leica Copy”', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_185_8.JPG', '185', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Janua San Giorgio camera was a Leica copy made in around 1949 by San Giorgio in Genoa, Italy for the Italian market, only small quantity produced. It comes with ESSEGI 3.5/5cm lens (#350690), front lens cap and leather case.', 'Janua相機是於1949年左右由意大利公司San Giorgio仿照徠卡相機製作，提供予當地市場，產量不多。此機配有ESSEGI 3.5/5cm鏡頭 (#350690)、鏡頭前蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2032', 'Rectaflex 30000 Rotor Outfit', '. 					Rectaflex 30000 Rotor Outfit', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_186_9.JPG', '186', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Rectaflex Rotor is a Rectaflex series 30000 with a three lens turret (Rotor). According to the record, less than 100 units of them were made. Its existence aroused much interest among photo journalists back then. This camera comes with a turret, leather case, back up body (#25331B) and three lenses; the first one is the 2nd version of Filotecnica Salmoiraghi-Milano-Beta 3.5/5cm (#39741), made in 1953 to 1955, which built like a Tessar; the second one is Angenieux Retrofocus Type R1 2.5/35mm (#197514) and Angenieux Type Y2 3.5/135mm (#371805) with front lens cap.', '這套Rectaflex Rotor是在Rectaflex 30000系列上加上三鏡頭轉台（Rotor)。根據記錄，Rotor的產量只有幾十個。它的推出引起當年新聞記者極大關注；由近攝鏡到長焦鏡只需轉動Rotor，方便快捷。此機除了鏡頭轉台連把手、皮套及後備機身（#25331B）外，還連同三支鏡頭，分別是：產於1953至1955年，外觀有如Tessar的第二代Filotecnica Salmoiraghi-Milano-Beta 3.5/5cm (#39741)、Angenieux Retrofocus Type R1 2.5/35mm (#197514)及Angenieux Type Y2 3.5/135mm (#371805)連前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2033', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', '. 					Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_187_9.JPG', '187', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original Voigtlander Bessa II 4.5/105mm APO-Lanther, in small batch of production only. It comes with leather case, with normal signs of use.', 'Voigtlander Bessa II是福倫達公司於1950年推出的顛峰之作。它有兩個取景框，分別是6x4.5及6x9，光圈景深尺為4.5至22，並配有超級名鏡APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm。此鏡由稀有鑭玻璃製成，產量少，是各收藏者追求的珍寶之一。此機配有皮套，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2034', 'Voigtlander Prominent 6x9', '. 					Voigtlander Prominent 6x9', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_188_8.JPG', '188', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'This was made in 1930’s, and was the first type of 6x9cm camera combined with split-image rangefinder and metering. It comes with Voigtlander Heliar 4.5/10.5cm lens (#787573) and strap; with some signs of use.', '此機產於1930年代，是世上第一款同時裝有裂像對焦及測距裝置的6X9cm相機。此機配有Voigtlander Heliar 4.5/10.5cm鏡頭 (#787573)及手帶，機鏡有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2035', 'Le Cent Vues de Mollier “First Model”', '. 					Le Cent Vues de Mollier “First Model”', '32', '/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a21/LOTNO_189_8.JPG', '189', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This is a very rare French early camera for 100 exposures 18x24mm on 35mm film, vertically type. It was invented by Etienne Mollier in 1909 to 1910. Only few copies have been made. It comes with Anastigmat Hermagis 3.5/40mm lens (#116225) and a pouch. Please refer to Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck “A History Illustrating every Model and Accessory – Revised Edition” for further illustration.', '此款是非常罕見的早期18x24mm格式相機，是第一代的Mollier Cent Vues，由 “Etienne Molier” 於1909至1910年間發明，生產數量極少。此機配有Anastigmat Hermagis 3.5/40mm鏡頭 (#116225)及相機布袋。有關資料可參閱Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck著作《A History Illustrating every Model and Accessory – Revised Edition》。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2036', 'TEA WARE SET', '龍文堂 龍首茶壺套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_801_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_801_2.jpg', '801', '', '27,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬13公分，高7公分<br />\r\n茶 杯｜徑6公分，高4公分<br />\r\n茶 罐｜徑8公分，高9公分<br />\r\n竹茶排｜長54公分，寬13公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n罕見「龍文堂造」款的鐵打茶壺，龍首壺是高級茶具的特徵，水蒸氣自龍口吐出，龍首有神，壺身以葉紋為題，另加上蟾蜍雕刻，寓意可跨越重重難關。配碧玉雙珠鈕摘，蓮葉枝把手。共箱，箱見「龍文堂」款。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n連同青花瓷杯三件，杯身見山水風景圖及「膽山仰賢 何去有」字句。配以竹茶排，盡顯吉祥富貴之意。另配錫茶罐一客，罐身及蓋有菊花紋，罐底有落款；組成一套惹人喜愛的藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2037', 'PAIR OF YIXING TEAPOTS, QING DYNASTY', '清 三友居款 甕式紫砂壺一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_802_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_802_2.jpg', '802', '', '25,300', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬11公分，高8公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一對甕式紫砂壺；紫泥致密質細、色深邃古雅、包漿潤澤、溜肩、鼓腹、底收，配圈把，見三彎嘴，頂為截蓋配圓摘。此器古韻盎然，小中見大。底款「三友居」，共箱，箱蓋底有款，箱面貼「三友居在銘 紫泥茗注 壹雙」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「三友居」是民間堂號，專門聘請製壺名匠作精緻紫砂器，外銷日本、東南亞等地，後因戰亂而中止生產，令產量下降，當中的好壺成稀有藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2038', 'JAPANESE GOLD PLATED TEAPOT', '日本純銀鍍金茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_803_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_803_2.jpg', '803', '', '27,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬13.5公分，高6.5公分，重157克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n鍍金壺壺身「宗」款，底款「純銀」﹔壺身光潔如鏡，菊瓣形鈕摘配象牙側把手，更添貴氣。共箱，箱款「宗浩勤製」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2039', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '尚芳堂 槌目紋日本純銀小型茶壺 連 茶托五件套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_804_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_804_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_804_3.jpg', '804', '', '27,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬11公分，高12.5公分，重116克<br />\r\n茶 托｜長9.5公分，闊7公分，高2公分，重62克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀槌目紋小型茶壺，藤編提梁，紅珊瑚鈕摘，壺底款「尚美堂造 純銀」，共箱。配五件茶托分別畫有松梅蘭竹菊，底部刻有「幹茂號造」。此套裝器形完整，古趣流露，藏用均宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2040', 'TIN TEA CONTAINER', '沈存周款 古錫雕竹詩文茶罐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_805_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_805_2.jpg', '805', '', '69,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜寬8.5公分，高9.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此古錫茶罐落款沈存周，茶罐以清風君子為題，雕有竹圖案，枝節擰折不彎，堅韌剛勁；詩文剛勁有力，是收藏家的心頭好。共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沈存周（1629-1709年），浙江嘉興人。據《耐冷談詩話》載：「康熙初，沈居嘉興春波橋，能詩，所治錫鬥，鐫以自作詩句。錢籜石詩集中載有《錫鬥歌》，頗令人稱讚。」沈存周善製各種式樣的錫茶具，所雕刻的詩句、姓氏、圖印均規整精良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2041', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '日本純銀霰紋壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_806_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_806_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_806_3.jpg', '806', '', '48,300', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺|寬22公分，高24.5公分，重996克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此器以手工逐一槌出霰紋，整齊一致，繁而不亂﹔壺形似寶珠，圓渾飽滿，鏤空銀摘更是畫龍點睛，壺底部分以槌目紋表現及有「純銀」字樣。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2042', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '芳華堂造 翠玉摘環輪線日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_807_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_807_2.jpg', '807', '', '69,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺|寬15公分，高15.5公分，重401克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n純銀湯沸，由壺身、壺蓋到壺口均搥以環輪線，於銀壺屬罕見之作﹔壺口呈砲口樣，配以三環翠玉摘，與整個環輪紋的意念連成一線，豆莢樣提梁；壺底「芳華堂　純銀」款。共箱，箱款｢芳華堂造｣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2043', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '長治齋 日本純銀翡翠鈕銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_808_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_808_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_808_3.jpg', '808', '', '161,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬15公分，高18公分，重388克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此槌目紋日本純銀銀壺，器底刻有「長治齋」款。長治齋來自大阪尚美堂，為不少收藏家支持的堂號之一。壺身呈布袋型，壺嘴挺拔，配以亮眼的三環翠玉摘，簡潔卻不失大方。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2044', 'IRON TEAPOT', '信龍堂造 浮雕隱月鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_809_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_809_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_809_3.jpg', '809', '', '19,550', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬17.5公分，高24公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n信龍堂為龍文堂的代工堂號，是頂級堂號之一。六角壺形於鐵壺類中非常少見，此器蓋內款「信龍堂造」，壺身以浮雕手法繪畫出樹林景致，一輪明亮隱藏於樹林中，另一邊見浮雕詩句，詩意盎然﹔壺身頂端飾以如意紋，銅蓋連花苞樣摘扭。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2045', 'IRON TEAPOT', '龜文堂造 浮雕葛屋老松圖鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_810_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_810_2.jpg', '810', '', '46,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺  | 寬19公分，高21.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n以龜文堂最有名的風景圖作壺身設計，壺身有「龜文堂造」小方章，壺身以浮雕方式繪畫出葛屋老松樹的圖畫，要留意此器有別於一般龜文堂作品，除了圖畫上線條寫實有力，提把亦選擇以簡約的銅提，予人清幽簡樸的感覺，此器顯示出龜文堂於浮雕風景圖設計的功力，是不可多得的收藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2046', 'IRON TEAPOT', '金龍堂 嵌金銀寶圖鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_811_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_811_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_811_3.jpg', '811', '', '52,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬17.5公分，高20公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n龍文堂的堂號很多，金龍堂是龍文堂針對高端客戶所製作的堂號。此器蓋內款「金龍堂造」，於寶袋形壺身上，以金銀鑲嵌元寶圖案，並簡約地以鐵提梁配以銀摘座作點綴。金銀鑲嵌技術在金工裡是一個十分特別的級別，能提升鐵壺的華麗感。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2047', 'IRON TEAPOT', '日本龜文堂 梅泉造 高浮雕山水家屋圖鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_812_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_812_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_812_3.jpg', '812', '', '92,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬5.5公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此鐵壺身有｢日本梅泉｣款。銅蓋、梅枝形銅提梁，圓摘上有飛鳥圖案。整體大氣撲實，屬梅泉早期的作品。釜師梅泉是著名堂口龜文堂掌門人波多野正平的大弟子。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2048', 'IRON TEAPOT', '金壽堂雨宮宗造 日本金銀鑲嵌龍鳳紋鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_813_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_813_2.jpg', '813', '', '276,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺｜寬16公分，高20公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n金壽堂強調壺體製作精美，製作鐵壺的技法獨具一格，擅長運用金、銀、銅不同的金屬材質鑲嵌或浮雕於壺身或壺把上，在當時極為珍貴華美。有不少收藏在歐洲博物館的鐵壺中，其壺身或壺蓋上也落有金壽堂的堂號﹔可看出金壽堂的歷史地位。雨宮宗為金壽堂的名釜師之一，追捧者眾。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此鐵壺出自京鐵瓶重要堂號之一的金壽堂，由名釜師雨宮宗所造﹔能做出金工的堂號寥寥無幾，金壽堂便是其一。在此長閑形鐵瓶身上，以嵌金手工勾畫出呈騰雲翩舞之龍鳳圖，龍身刻魚鱗紋，龍鬚飄動，栩栩如生；金銀花飾紋提梁，線條流暢優雅；流嘴小巧精緻，與器身相互配合，蓋內款「金壽堂造」。名堂之作存世量稀少，值得珍藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2049', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '日本皇室昭憲皇太后賜品 饕餮紋銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_814_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_814_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_814_3.jpg', '814', '', '184,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬15公分，高17.5公分，重491克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n昭憲皇太后(一八四九年至一九一四年)為明治天皇的皇后﹔大正天皇之嫡母。慶應三年(一八六七年)五月十八日成為明治天皇之女禦，同年六月二十八日女禦宣下。明治元年十二月二十八日(一九六九年二月六日)又被冊立為皇后。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺身腹深鼓圓飽滿，炮管口雕有飾紋，壺身上半部飾以饕餮紋，網底為細槌目紋，以翠玉三環為摘，是整件作品畫龍點晴之處，提把少見地包以皮革，使用起來更為舒適。共箱，箱側貼「賜 第五號」及「昭憲皇太后賜品 砡飾銀瓶」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2050', 'A PAIR OF STERLING SILVER TEAPOTS', '日本白金小茶壺一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_815_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_815_2.jpg', '815', '', '138,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬9公分，高6公分，重74克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國式的日本白金小茶壺一對，形狀似紫砂茶壺，但更為嬌小，配木圈把、截蓋及圓摘，箱蓋款「白金急須 壹雙」。同類型白金對壺極少見於近年拍賣會，屬收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2051', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '翡翠鈕日本純金壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_816_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_816_2.jpg', '816', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '金 壺 | 寬13.5公分，高15公分，重 437 克 (連翡翠環摘)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純金金壺圓潤飽滿，壺身佈滿細槌目紋，茶壺流嘴曲線完美，配有三環翡翠摘，壺底見「純金」印記，華麗堂皇，令人一見傾心。用金壺煮的水，軟中帶滑，甜而清沁，對茶性的發揮作出極為巧妙的平衡﹔為收藏家的心頭好。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2052', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '藏六二世饕餮紋鳳首金壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_817_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_817_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_817_3.jpg', '817', '', '1,150,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '金 壺 |寬16.5公分，高20.5公分，重1230克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n饕餮是古代漢族神話傳說中龍的第五子，由於饕餮是兇猛的魔獸，具有強大的力量，因此被北方很多少數民族當作護身符。把它的圖紋刻在器具、食皿上，認為這樣就可以借助饕餮強大的力量，不被其他猛獸所吞噬，成為了神獸。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n藏六二世在安正元年(1854年)生。最初的名字是秦住支祝；昭和七年(1932年)歿，享年七十八歲。其父初代藏六(秦藏六，生於1823，卒於1890)是日本史上青銅器創作非常知名的金工師，也是日本明日天皇禦璽的作者。二世藏六傳承初代風格，青出於藍,創作出戰國時代青銅器風格鐵瓶，其作品傳世量甚少，堪稱素器天王。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n金壺刻「藏六居造」底款。由器身、蓋至摘全體均雕有饕餮紋，圖案莊嚴，面目結構鮮明，雕工細膩，栩栩如生，充分展現出東方的風韻。流口設計成鳳首，配方圓角直手把；共箱，為後補木箱，經藏六後代加簽，箱款「平安 藏六造」。整壺以金而製，加上藏六二世超群的手藝，令人嘆為觀止。<br />\r\n於去年12月在台灣拍賣會中，藏六四世金壺(重775克)拍出超過一百萬港元，同期於中國拍賣會一把藏六三世金壺(僅重476克)更拍出約一百五十萬的天價，此精緻的金壺約重一千二百三十克，市場更為罕見，收藏價值極高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2053', 'A SET OF BLUE AND WHITE TEA CUPS, QING DYNASTY', '清  龍鳳青花杯五客', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_818_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_818_2.jpg', '818', '', '4,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '杯｜清代，徑5.5公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n五客青花杯身上見青花龍鳳雲紋，內沿口有連續祥雲紋，杯心見龍雲紋，青花發色雅淡；此類紋理於晚清之同治光緒年間非常流行，底款「大明萬曆年製」，應為外銷品。共箱，其墨色外表古樸，箱蓋款「古染付煎茶碗  五客」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2054', 'A SET OF BLUE AND WHITE TEA CUPS', '江戶   日本青花杯五隻', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_819_1.jpg', '819', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '杯｜江戶早期，徑6公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本燒製青花杯五客，沿口見俗稱的蟲咬痕，為日本江戶時期燒製瓷器時常見的特徵，月影門裝飾，藍色青花紋鮮艷，玉壁足，共箱，箱蓋款「南京古染附煎茶碗  五客」。帶有濃厚的日本特色。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2055', 'A PAIR OF BLUE AND WHITE TEA CUPS, QING DYNASTY', '清   青花杯一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_820_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_820_2.jpg', '820', '', '10,350', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '杯｜清代，徑6公分，高4.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n仰鐘式青花杯，底款「大明成化年製」，以造型及花式來推斷，燒製時期為清代，來自江西景德鎮， 是難得一見的小器。線條流暢，青花紋理乾淨，釉清亮，造型別緻，口沿有蔓草青花紋，發色較濃，而近足底部份則見波浪花紋，紋較雅淡﹔杯身大部份留白，此類造型之器於清代較為少見，是當時精巧器物之選。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2056', 'A SET OF TIN SAUCERS', '沈存周 刻花錫茶托', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_821_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_821_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_821_3.jpg', '821', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 托｜徑5.5公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此為出自名家沈存周之茶托五客，梅蘭菊竹雕刻巧奪天工，詩文剛勁有力，是收藏佳品，共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沈存周，精於雕鏤詩句、姓氏、圖印等。據《耐冷談詩話》載︰「康熙初，沈居嘉興春波橋，能詩，所治錫鬥，鐫以自作詩句。錢籜石（載）詩集中載有《錫鬥歌》，頗令人稱讚。元明以來，朱碧山之銀槎，張鳴岐之銅爐，黃元吉之錫壺，皆勒工名，以垂後世，而不聞其能詩。」沈存周以制錫聞名於世，後世稱為清代錫壺第一名家。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2057', 'YIXING TEA WARE SET', '宜興紫砂壺一對 茶托套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_822_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_822_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_822_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_822_4.jpg', '822', '', '9,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺 (深色)｜寬9公分，高5公分<br />\r\n茶 壺 (淺色)｜寬9公分，高5公分<br />\r\n茶 杯｜徑3.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n茶 托｜徑5.5公分，高1公分<br />\r\n木 盤｜長16公分，寬13.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此對茶壺皆有「中國宜興」底款，面微凸，直流。其一茶壺胎泥呈紫褐色，蓋底「小仙」款，另一胎泥則呈赭色。<br />\r\n配有紫砂茶杯及杯托共五對，配以木盤成為一套小巧別緻的茶具組合。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2058', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '翡翠鈕摘日本純銀茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_823_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_823_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_823_3.jpg', '823', '', '11,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬13公分，高8公分，重189克(連翡翠摘)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀製壺身刻有竹葉紋，配以翡翠鈕摘更顯高雅雍容；底款「純銀」。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2059', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET, QING DYNASTY', '清 瑪瑙半提梁日本純銀茶壺 連 蓮葉形銀製茶量', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_824_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_824_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_824_3.jpg', '824', '', '29,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬12分，高11.5公分，重169克<br />\r\n茶 量｜長12.5公分，寬5.5公分，高2公分，重57克　<br />\r\n<br />\r\n陸羽茶藝底款「純銀」的鑲瑪瑙鈕摘茶壺，配以優雅的瑪瑙半提梁，映襯在純銀製波浪紋壺身上，格外清秀動人。<br />\r\n茶量身押「正」款，此器以銀打造蓮葉形，自然彎捲，秀雅萬分。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2060', 'TEA WARE SET', '北村靜香造 南鐐蓮葉形茶量 配 銀製槌目紅木把手茶壺 茶具組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_825_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_825_2.jpg', '825', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 量｜長9.5公分，寬14公分，重27克<br />\r\n茶 壺｜寬11.5公分，高7公分，重90克<br />\r\n茶 罐｜徑8.5公分，高6.5公分<br />\r\n竹茶排｜長20公分，寬13公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此茶量出自名家北村靜香之手，底刻有「金工 北村靜香造」，共箱「北村靜香造」款。茶量為茶道六用之一，用以將茶葉從錫製茶罐中舀出，通過目視確認茶葉的份量。此器以純銀打造成南鐐蓮葉形，精細手功展現名家風采。配有錫製茶罐及銀製小槌目紋茶壺，短直流，以紅木作把手，此壺由名家所造，同類型中國式純銀茶壺在市面上難得一見。欣賞整套茶具安放於竹制茶排上也是品茗之趣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2061', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '秋田竹谷製 日本純銀雕四君子茶罐 配 前川款日本純銀茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_826_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_826_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_826_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_826_4.jpg', '826', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑8公分，高10公分，重218克<br />\r\n茶 壺｜徑10.5公分，高9.5公分，重130克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n秋田竹谷製的純銀雕四君子茶罐，形態小巧優雅，以刀代筆刻畫出梅蘭菊竹的美態，充滿生命力，底款「秋田竹谷製 純銀」。共箱。<br />\r\n日本純銀茶壺，以菊花摘配以炮口流，底款「純銀」「前川」，共箱「銀製茶容」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n竹谷金之助，秋田市人。大正四年繼承餘銀細工工廠、家業，矢志振興工藝技術，並長年致力於金工工具的開發。榮獲工藝振興功勞者，連續蟬聯五年東北北海道工藝展最高一等獎。特別將精湛的金銀細工技術移植海外，促進工藝產業的發展。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2062', 'TIN TEA WARE SET', '錫製茶罐 連 古鍚梅花茶托五件套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_827_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_827_2.jpg', '827', '', '5,750', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑10公分，高12公分<br />\r\n茶 托｜徑12.5公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n錫製茶罐，圓滿豐腴，罐身有松樹，蓋上有梅花。連古鍚五瓣梅花形茶托五客，設計精緻典雅，底款「廻龍閣陳水高老店」；共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2063', 'A SET OF JAPANESE SILVER SAUCERS', '紹美造 日本純銀梅蘭竹菊松雕刻茶托五件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_828_1.jpg', '828', '', '32,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 托｜徑10.5公分，高1公分，重58克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此日本純銀梅蘭菊竹松雕刻茶托，表現出梅花的高潔﹑蘭花的幽雅空靈﹑竹子的亭亭玉立﹑菊花的傲然開放及松樹的剛勁有力。附有紹美榮佑在大正七年(1918年)的親筆手寫收據及給客人的書信。共箱，箱款｢京都紹美造｣。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n紹美榮佑為惺惺堂之堂主，金工世家金谷五郎三郎家養子，是堪比日本金工世家中川淨益家族的金工師。紹美十八歲時到金谷家開始學習金工，並在午休時間到其他的金工工作坊學習了很多的金工手法和技巧。後因故離開金谷家獨自立業，並且聘請了兩個弟子，在資本上得到了北重先生的支持。當時用的名字仍沿用在金谷家的文次郎，後改用學習茶道時宗匠給的名字「紹美」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2064', 'IRON TEAPOT', '龍文堂 安之介造 日本浮世繪鑲嵌金銀山水家屋鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_829_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_829_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_829_3.jpg', '829', '', '517,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺|寬21公分，高24.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在日本鐵壺的歷史中，龍文堂被譽為日本第一堂號，有超過一百年鑄造鐵壺的歷史，除了有高名望外，影響更遠及歐洲。倫敦維多利亞和阿爾伯特博物館曾收藏有龍文堂金銀鑲嵌的鐵壺 。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n龍文堂創辦人龍文的傳人是二代龍文堂，名波雄，字鼎介，統稱為初代安之介。安之介在十九世紀初將京都鐵壺推上工藝的舞臺，且得到了大眾的肯定。早期安之介作品和後期作品最明顯的分別在於「花押」。花押也叫作畫押，通常會取姓名中的一至二字採用連筆速寫、交錯相疊或加入一些符號，因此形狀千奇百怪，帶有藝術性，個性化的花押優勢是較難偽造，初代安之介的鐵壺因而成為各收藏家夢寐以求的藝術收藏目標。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺身以金銀鑲嵌，以日式浮世繪的手法，一側銼以金銀山水家屋圖，另一側飾以富士山景，傳達家鄉美麗風光﹔內包銀鐵蓋，鑲嵌金銀祥雲紋提樑，響片完好，胴體陰刻「龍文堂造」。壺極新，估計未曾用過；附原箱，箱款「龍文堂 安之介造」。此壺為龍文堂掌門人安之介不可多得的早期作品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2065', 'IRON TEAPOT', '般若心經砲口鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_830_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_830_2.jpg', '830', '', '345,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺｜寬16公分，高17公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此鐵壺壺身刻有般若波羅密多心經，雕工精緻有力，釜人必須心靜、心清、手巧才能刻出如此出塵脫俗的神韻。砲形壺嘴，水流俐落順暢，銀環摘上施以細槌目，端正持重。同類心經鐵壺數年才出現一台，極為珍貴，為鐵壺收藏家不可多得的心頭好。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n《般若波羅蜜多心經》裡的「般若」為梵語音譯，指通達妙智慧；「波羅」為梵語音譯，指到彼岸(不生不滅、不垢不淨)，有解脫掛礙的意思；「蜜多」為梵語音譯，意為無極，可聯想比如蜜蜂採花釀蜜，能融合眾多不同來源成分而歸納為一。「心」：根本、核心、精髓，一方面表示內容所探討的主體重心，另一方面也表示全篇內容的重要性；「經」：字義是線、路、徑，引申為經典，代表前人走過的路途，獨特而深入的經歷或見解，借口述語言或文字記載來傳承後世，以供人們做為參考指引。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2066', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '來鳳造 般若心經日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_831_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_831_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_831_3.jpg', '831', '', '103,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬14.5公分，高14.5公分，重367克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀壺壺身刻有《般若波羅蜜多心經》，只有心神專注手穩而巧，才能完成整部經文。底款「來鳳」章﹔瓶身、環摘、提梁皆為純銀所打出﹔砲管形壺嘴，水流俐落順暢﹔斷熱把的設計讓使用時無燙手顧慮，可見作者的體貼。共箱，箱蓋「來鳳造 純銀湯沸」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2067', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '石川光一作 象牙側把百棱日本純金茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_832_1.jpg', '832', '', '207,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '金 壺｜寬12公分，高7.5公分，重398克 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n純金百棱茶壺，底款「純金 光一作」，華貴中帶有雅致之氣，不流於俗豔，搭配乳白色象牙側把，質地銜接極為靈動，讓人眼前一亮。花形鈕摘精巧，壺嘴線條流暢，靈巧美緻。金壺煮水，清心甘甜，入口順滑，令人陶醉於其中。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n純金作家石川光一是工藝家石川清太郎的長子，出生於淺草，因個人的獨特風格，得到【內閣総理大臣賞】這輝煌的實績。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2068', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEA CUP', '一鶴齋製 日本純金豬口杯', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_833_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_833_2.jpg', '833', '', '23,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶  杯｜徑5公分，高3公分，重48克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一鶴齋純金豬口杯一客，底「歸榮」，共箱，箱蓋內款「純金豬口 一鶴齋」，箱布「一鶴齋」款。杯身外壁見霧化梨紋，內壁金光耀目，富麗堂皇。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2069', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '日本純金霰紋茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_834_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_834_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_834_3.jpg', '834', '', '368,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '金 壺｜寬 13公分，高16.5公分，重490克 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n金光閃耀手感沉甸的金壺，器底落有「純金」款，手槌出井然有序的霰紋，均勻滿佈壺身，展現工藝師的功力及技巧。配以優雅的豆莢形提梁，花苞為鈕摘，更顯尊貴風範；共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n黃金擁有非常獨特的成份，以金壺煮水，使水質軟中帶滑，更添清甜，為沖沏的茶葉帶出其原有田園清香。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2070', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '日本純銀茶具套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_835_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_835_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_835_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_835_4.jpg', '835', '', '138,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶　壺｜寬13.5公分，高7公分，重204克<br />\r\n茶　罐｜徑9公分，高11公分，重284克<br />\r\n建　水｜徑10公分，高8公分，重312克<br />\r\n公平杯｜徑13.5公分，高7.5公分，重193克<br />\r\n茶　量｜徑15公分，高5.5公分，重119克<br />\r\n杯　托｜徑10.5公分，高2公分，重88克<br />\r\n木托盤｜長36公分，寬25公分，高3.4公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n純銀茶道具一套，以啞色梨紋及亮銀為每件茶器的主調，除茶量外，底款皆「純銀」。茶壺外形依照中國紫砂茶壺的設計，配有象牙把手﹔茶罐器身主要覆以啞色梨紋﹔建水蓋見如意雕刻﹔公平杯與茶壺同樣配象牙把手，質感設計與茶量一致，外啞內亮﹔雲形杯托五客。套裝連木托盤，如此整全的純銀茶具套裝令人愛不釋手。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2071', 'TIN TEAPOT WRAPPED IN A LAYER OF TIN', '詩文古錫包紫砂鑲玉茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_836_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_836_2.jpg', '836', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬14公分，高9公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n六角形紫砂壺，外包錫皮。平蓋立鈕，壺嘴、把手及摘蓋皆嵌白玉石，有三鑲玉之稱，別緻非常。壺身兩邊題詩著文，富有意境。集合紫砂、鍚及玉三道工序，用料上乘工藝精湛，文人雅士賞玩佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2072', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '日本純銀小茶壺 茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_837_1.jpg', '837', '', '29,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬12公分，高12公分，重102 克<br />\r\n茶 杯｜徑5.5公分，高4公分<br />\r\n錫茶罐｜徑5.5公分，高9公分<br />\r\n木 盤｜長44公分，寬13公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「純銀」底款小茶壺，特別之處在於壺蓋及壺身梅花間竹地施以不同的槌目，以千萬次的槌打敲擊使得皮殼閃亮，發出淡紫色的高雅效果。松毬鈕摘配以木藤枝環狀提梁，完美展現森林的靜寍，共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n拍品包括花草青花字句杯五件，沿口及杯身繪有金紋，共箱；以及錫茶罐。整組器具配以雕有蝸牛圖案的芭蕉葉形托盤，更顯茶具組的脫俗不凡，突顯與世無爭的田園樂。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2073', 'A PAIR OF BAMBOO TEAPOTS, QING DYNASTY', '清 竹根急須一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_838_1.jpg', '838', '', '32,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬9.5公分，高8公分 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺身以古竹根雕有松、竹、梅歲寒三友，以梅花枝構成提把，松樹融入摘蓋，流嘴則是仿竹節造型，外型精緻風雅。共箱，寫有「竹根急須二」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2074', 'TIN TEA WARE SET', '古錫製茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_839_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_839_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_839_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_839_4.jpg', '839', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑9.5公分，高12.5公分<br />\r\n建 水｜徑12.5公分，高9.5公分<br />\r\n茶 托｜長13公分，闊8公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n古錫製茶罐刻有松樹，傲然屹立；蓋上刻有傲雪挺立的梅花，與松樹互相輝映，底款「上鍚 半鍚」，共箱，箱蓋「錫製茶壺」底款。配錫製建水刻有梅蘭竹菊的圖案，底款「龍文堂造」。連同四件錫製八瓣花形茶托，底款「義春」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2075', 'TEA WARE SET', '紫砂壺連藤壺承 配 人物風景青花杯四客', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_840_1.jpg', '840', '', '7,475', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬15.5公分，高11公分<br />\r\n茶 杯｜徑6.5公分，高6公分<br />\r\n壺 承｜徑15公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此壺泥胎呈朱紅色，「孟臣」底款，壺體看似梨形，直流。連藤製壺承；另配人物風景青花杯四件。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2076', 'A PAIR OF YIXING TEAPOTS, QING DYNASTY', '清 刻經具輪珠紫砂壺一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_841_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_841_2.jpg', '841', '', '18,400', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬9.5公分，高7公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n紫泥焐灰，色黑微亮，壺身見空刻心經，刀功老練，為經典具輪珠壺，配圈把、短直流，壓蓋為扁平圓餅狀。共箱，箱蓋寫「唐物烏泥 壺式般若心經刻 急須一雙」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2077', 'TEA WARE SET', '「道光年制」款 朱泥茶壺茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_842_1.jpg', '842', '', '23,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬11.5公分，高7公分<br />\r\n錫茶罐｜徑6公分，高7.5公分，重271克<br />\r\n瓷 杯｜徑4.5公分，高2.5公分<br />\r\n竹 排｜長23公分，闊15公分，高1公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n朱泥梨形茶壺，造工圓滑，圓手把，少見的小巧型紫砂壺，壺底「道光年制」款﹔錫茶罐，入手沉穩，優美古樸。配有花紋瓷杯三客及個性斑紋竹排，美觀實用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2078', 'TEA WARE SET', '清 茶泥茶壺一對 連 瓷杯紅木茶道具六件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_843_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_843_2.jpg', '843', '', '17,250', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜清代，寬9.5公分，高5.5公分<br />\r\n茶 罐｜徑5公分，高11公分 <br />\r\n茶 量｜徑2.5公分，高11公分<br />\r\n瓷 杯｜徑3.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此對茶泥茶壺呈黃褐色，小巧精緻；共箱。另配紅木茶具兩件：茶罐上刻有「九莖呈瑞美　三秀擅英奇」，及蝙蝠與蓮花，寄寓福氣連連。茶量雕有白菜圖案，配以瓷杯四客，份外清新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2079', 'A SET OF BLUE AND WHITE TEA CUPS', '明治  花蝶紋青花杯五客', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_844_1.jpg', '844', '', '6,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '瓷 杯｜明治時期，徑6.5公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n五客青花杯圖紋為四季花卉，見菊花、荷花、蝴蝶等裝飾，構成四季花蝶圖，鈷料發色呈紫藍，胎白，應為外銷品，共箱，箱蓋款「花蝶模樣煮茶碗  五客」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2080', 'TEA WARE SET', '側把手紫砂壺茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_845_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_845_2.jpg', '845', '', '3,450', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '紫砂壺｜寬9公分，高7公分<br />\r\n瓷 杯｜徑4公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n紅木盒｜長16公分，闊11公分，高10公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n側把手紫砂壺刻有般若心經，刻工細緻有力。不加雕飾的紅木盒，整體造型簡樸雅致，散發著歲月洗滌的古舊美感。加上精美瓷杯三客，是賞茶的好配對。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2081', 'A PAIR OF JAPANESE SILVER TEA SCOOPS', '北村靜香 銀茶量 與 木村節三 銀茶量', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_846_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_846_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_846_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_846_4.jpg', '846', '', '14,950', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '北村靜香銀茶量｜長9.5公分，闊4公分，高1公分，重21克<br />\r\n木村節三銀茶量｜長10.5公分，闊4.5公分，高1.5公分，重33克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此對茶量分別出自兩位日本名師：北村靜香銀茶量，器底底部中央刻有北村花押「正」﹔木村節三銀茶量，底款「純銀」，共箱「木村節三作」款。這對南鐐蓮葉形茶量，手工精美，收藏或自用皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2082', 'A SET OF JAPANESE GOLD PLATED SAUCERS', '純銀鍍金繪花茶托五件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_847_1.jpg', '847', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 托｜長10公分，寬7公分，高１.5公分，重53克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此純銀鍍金茶托以木瓜形設計，表面繪以花瓣裝飾，剛柔並濟。以銀鍍金，是茶托工藝中較高的級別。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2083', 'SQUARE DISH WITH A SET OF GOLD PAINTED SAUCERS, MING DYNASTY', '明末 黒漆嵌螺鈿樓閣人物方盤 及 描金人物故事茶托', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_848_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_848_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_848_3.jpg', '848', '', '39,100', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '托 盤｜明末，徑26.5公分，高2.5公分<br />\r\n小 盤｜明末，徑11.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n黒漆嵌螺鈿托盤圖案為樓閣人物，官員在樓閣中商議，其他官員則在旁等候。柳樹的垂柳枝條柔韌，隨風起舞。雕工裁切精巧，螺鈿片剝離如紙，嵌製螺鈿閃閃生輝，光彩奪目令人讚嘆不已。共箱，寫有「青貝角盆」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n十件黑漆描金人物故事小盤的圖案各不同；山水相映、樹木繁茂、邊下棋、邊談天、策馬執鞭與家人告別、享受美麗風景的官員等等。構圖嚴謹，人物場景栩栩如生，生動傳神。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n螺鈿鑲嵌是唐代新盛的工藝，用於裝飾鏡背及奩盒。嵌螺鈿指取材於各種貝殼色澤光華最佳的部位，分層剝離和裁制後鑲嵌於木、漆器之上作為裝飾。 《髹飾錄》中描述道：「螺鈿……百般文圖，點、抹、鉤、條，總以精細密緻如畫為妙。又分截殼色，隨彩而施綴者，光華可賞。」意即按照畫面花紋的需要，採用不同色澤的螺片，裁切成各種不同的形狀，鑲嵌出各種畫面，達到近似填色的效果。宋朝工匠運用薄而軟的貝殼，鑲嵌出複雜精細的亭台樓閣、庭院人物場景，且人物面容生動逼真。至元朝螺鈿鑲嵌技術已達頂峰，更為流行。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2084', 'AGARWOOD CUP CARVING OF PLUM BLOOSOM, QING DYNASTY', '清 沉香雕梅紋杯', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_849_1.jpg', '849', '', '207,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '梅紋杯｜清代，徑7公分，高10公分，重52.7克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n明清兩代開始對沉香趨之若鶩，除擺件以外更延伸出可供把玩之香道具。此器依形而製，巧成小杯之形，雕上梅花枝，只消輕輕把玩，通體便漸發黑亮油光，散發出尤如梅花般淡淡幽香，使人心曠神怡。沉香質地堅實，造型古典優雅，為觀賞使用之沉香佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2085', 'AGARWOOD RUYI SCEPTER, QING DYNASTY', '清 沉香如意雕件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_850_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_850_2.jpg', '850', '', '126,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '如 意｜清代，長30.5公分，寬5公分，重28克<br />\r\n <br />\r\n此清朝的沉香依形而製成如意，雕工精緻考究，模仿梅枝纏繞之態，盡顯天然之美。 幽幽生香的如意放於案頭上散發沈穩的氣質，平復煩躁心情。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2086', 'WOODEN RUYI SCEPTER, QING DYNASTY', '清末 紅木根墨玉如意', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_851_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_851_2.jpg', '851', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '如 意|清代，長33公分，闊8公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n大號紅木根如意擺件，前端墨玉刻有蝴蝶正面圖案，翅膀上雕有古錢，整把柄刻上彩雲浮雕，柄部後端繫有如意繩結掛飾﹔整支如意予人生氣勃勃、吉祥連綿之感。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2087', 'STATIONERY SET', '名家精工製 文房擺件套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_852_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_852_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_852_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_852_4.jpg', '852', '', '80,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '筆 筒 | 徑7.5公分，高12.5公分<br />\r\n滴 水 | 徑10公分，高8公分<br />\r\n滴水墊| 徑7.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n座 屏 | 徑13公分，高11.5公分<br />\r\n筆 座 | 徑15公分，高4公分<br />\r\n紙 鎮 | 徑13公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一套六件小型文房擺件套組，當中四方筆筒及座屏底部「真山」款；四方筆筒四邊雕有梅、蘭、菊、竹四君子立體圖案。座屏刻有枝上對鳥圖，屏面「真山」款，背後刻有松樹山景圖。而滴水墊﹑果實形筆座及雕石上三龜紙鎮為「琢齋造」款；滴水墊見一籃果實與茶壺，寓意安樂豐收。滴水器體刻雀鳥取果圖，頂底部份刻如意紋，頂部立有麒麟，獸口把手，予人吉祥之感。均共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2088', 'A PAIR OF LONGQUAN CENSERS, MING DYNASTY', '明 龍泉窯 高瓶香爐一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_853_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_853_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_853_3.jpg', '853', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '高   瓶｜明代，徑7.5公分，高15公分<br />\r\n香   爐｜明代，徑7公分，高7.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一對珍品皆為龍泉窯出品，釉色敦厚，溫潤如玉；顯露龍泉窯簡潔典雅的風格，胎質細密；皆共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n龍泉窯懸足爐以傳統筒式設計，三足懸垂，素身無紋，造型小巧，别具特色，粉青釉瑩潤如玉，足底無釉，略帶火石紅，厚灰胎，質堅。爐頂配以銀造鳳凰爐蓋，接口位恰到好處。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n高瓶器身修長，管狀長頸，溜肩鼓腹，帶有美麗的水滴形，器身上細緻見有葉紋，器口及頸位置粗幼有緻，手工非凡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2089', 'BLUE AND WHITE TRIPOD CENSER, MING DYNASTY', '明 青花人物三足香爐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_854_1.jpg', '854', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐｜明代，徑13公分，高8.5公分 ，蓋重141克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n香爐呈圓筒形，下承三足。口沿飾連續青花回紋，器腹繪山石花木，閑坐人物，江邊行舟，儼如一幅「秋江待渡」，畫面氣韻生動，用筆寫意，佈局疏朗，景致空濛，青花勾勒渲染，發色淡和。胎體敦厚，胎白微黄，質堅厚重，見火石紅，釉帶微青，釉質滋潤。 頂配葉紋銀蓋，與青花圖互相輝映。 共箱，貼「古染付三足香爐」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2090', 'BLUE AND WHITE SQUARE CENSER, QING DYNASTY', '清 青花方形三足香爐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_855_1.jpg', '855', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香   爐｜清代，長6.5公分，高12公分 ，蓋重46克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n青花方形爐，四面有功，青花人物遊樂圖，足有十個人物，以庭園為背景，見有欄杆、梯級、海浪，畫面生動，描繪流暢，極具古韻。除了海浪紋外，特見四方青花紋，常見於明代外銷的青花瓷器，並不常見於中國瓷製品。底見如意三足，胎白。頂配鳳凰登雲紋銀蓋。 共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2091', 'LONGQUAN TRIPOD CENSER, MING DYNASTY', '明  龍泉窯刻花三足香爐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_856_1.jpg', '856', '', '20,700', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐｜明代，徑15公分，高11公分，蓋重111克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n釉色粉青三足筒式香爐， 爐身見製爐時衍生出來的葉形紋理，器形莊重，外腹飾有花紋，內外滿釉，青釉滋潤帶亮，足底無釉並帶濃重火石紅，厚灰胎，質堅，壺身外頂、底共飾鼓釘九顆，是明代龍泉窯作品的常見手法。爐頂配網形銀蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2092', 'A PAIR OF LONGQUAN BOWLS, MING DYNASTY', '明初 龍泉窯刻花紋小碟一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_857_1.jpg', '857', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 碗｜明初代，徑12.5公分，高4公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一對粉綠瓷碗，青釉滋潤帶亮，內見畫花，整器可見手工為青瓷名號龍泉窯的手法，胎質厚重，施釉均勻，燒工上承。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2093', 'A PAIR OF JAPANESE ASH SCOOPS', '北村靜香黃銅灰勻 與 清雲款日本純銀梅花灰勻', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_858_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_858_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_858_3.jpg', '858', '', '4,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '黃銅灰勻｜長23.5公分，闊6公分，高1公分，重45克<br />\r\n純銀灰勻｜長21.5公分，闊6公分，高2公分，重45克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一對共箱灰勻﹕黃銅灰勻，把手飾以波浪紋，箱蓋款「北村靜香造」。另一日本為純銀梅花鑲嵌灰勻，手工精緻，木手柄，附有清雲親筆題字木盒及收條，箱「清雲」款。<br />\r\n灰勻是香道具必要的法寶，相信這對灰勻會令香道具玩家愛不釋手。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2094', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '北村靜香  一枚打出日本純金壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_859_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_859_2.jpg', '859', '', '483,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '金 壺｜寬 13公分，高 14公分，重536克 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n出自被譽為日本金工之王名家北村靜香之手，槌目紋金壺，壺底有北村靜香的「花押」落款，蓋底「純金」款。除提梁與壺蓋外，此壺由一塊日本純金，以精湛的全手工槌打成形，輕薄精巧。壺身並無繁俗花紋，清心素面更顯高貴。豆莢形提梁，環形摘以人字釘固定，簡約的短壺嘴，皆可體會北村靜香的大師級手藝及風格。 共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n北村靜香少時已拜於傳奇金工師真鍋靜良門下，學習並發揚「槌打」及「一枚打出」的技術，當今世上持此技術之人屈指可數。以金打造的壺，傳導性快速，不易氧化，更有效將茶葉的風味展現出來，此金壺除外型貴氣逼人外，更是內外兼備。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2095', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '北村靜香 一枚打出翡翠鈕銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_860_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_860_2.jpg', '860', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬17公分，高15公分，重 320 克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此銀壺為袋形，全器一體成形，翡翠摘，豆莢形鐵提把，無論是器型、壺嘴、提把，全手工槌打成形，千變萬化，輕薄精巧，獨一無二﹔處處流露北村靜香的精巧手藝。共箱，箱蓋款「北村靜香作」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n北村靜香於二十多歲時，拜於真鍋靜良門下，開始為銀壺奉獻他的人生，將「一枚打出」技法完美呈現於人前，技巧淋漓盡致，以「銀壺的北村」之名享譽全日本。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2096', 'JAPNESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '北村靜香 槌目紋日本純銀茶罐 連 南鐐蓮葉形茶量套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_861_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_861_2.jpg', '861', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑8.5公分，高8公分，重158克<br />\r\n茶 量｜長 9.5公分，闊4 公分，高1公分，重19 克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀製茶罐連南鐐蓮葉形茶量，二器底款皆有北村靜香「押花」，皆共箱，純銀製茶罐箱款「北村靜香先生作」，箱布「北村靜香 銀」字﹔南鐐蓮葉形茶量，共箱「北村靜香作」款。器身槌目紋裝飾，設計簡潔，比例均勻和諧，散發名家沉穩氣質。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2097', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '一枚打出日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_862_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_862_2.jpg', '862', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬16.5公分，高15公分，重630克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n寶珠形日本純銀壺，壺底落有「純銀」印款。此壺由一塊銀板經反覆敲打，使其拉平延展，壺身不見接縫痕跡，壺嘴一體成形口打出，此「一枚打出」之技術於製作銀壺來說，絕對是巧奪天工之作，甚有名釜師真鍋靜良的風格。環形鐵摘，通常見於較早期銀壺，配上鐵提樑，是一把古味十足的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2098', 'IRON TEAPOT', '光玉堂 嵌金山水圖鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_863_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_863_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_863_3.jpg', '863', '', '63,250', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬18公分，高20.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此器蓋內款「光玉堂造」，壺身以鑲金手法展現寫意山水圖，技法老練﹔佐以鑲嵌銀花飾提把及花苞形銅摘，增加了鐵壺的藝術性，亦彰顯光玉堂的上乘技巧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2099', 'IRON TEAPOT', '金龍堂 大國造 山水嵌金雁紋鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_864_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_864_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_864_3.jpg', '864', '', '36,800', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬18.5公分，高23公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n高筒壺形，壺身一邊雕刻山水圓月紋，加上嵌金雁紋裝飾，另一邊見詩文及「大國造」款，沿口邊見花草紋，富有詩意。蓋內款「壽朗」，頂配鳳凰雲紋銀鈕摘，以及鑲嵌金銀花瓣紋把手，別具心思。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2100', 'IRON TEAPOT', '龍文堂 鑲嵌金銀花鳥圖鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_865_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_865_2.jpg', '865', '', '41,400', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬16公分，高22公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此壺為棗形壺身，一面鑲嵌金銀花鳥圖案，另一面呈現優美金蝶採蜜圖，配以鏤空花形鈕摘，有春暖花開之意。配以三彎提把，蓋內款「龍文堂造」花押。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n龍文堂鐵壺的世代已久，類型多達三十多種。根據記載，在龍文堂的極盛期，一年所生產的鐵壺不超過一百五十把，產量極少，而且都是應客人要求而製﹔加上每個脫蠟模具只能製作一把鐵壺，所以每一個鐵壺也是精心製造的。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2101', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '初代藏六 仿古鳳口銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_866_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_866_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_866_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_866_4.jpg', '866', '', '368,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬13.5公分，高17公分，重366克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺底款「藏六仿古」，壺嘴設計為鳳首張口形態，五官分明，雙目明亮，鳳冠飛揚，雕刻細緻栩栩如生。壺體呈葫蘆形，壺身腰線以上及至壺蓋鈕摘皆雕有饕餮紋，寓意吉祥。通體造工講究，提梁接口位見獸形連接部份，配圓角長提把，壺蓋配以花形鈕摘。連包裝箱一對，一為原箱，「藏六」款，另一個為後人再次鑑定的外箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n藏六家族已有一百多年歷史，其獸口壺作品由古至今皆受推崇，初代藏六因深受中國文物影響，對青銅器非常著迷，因此藏六家族對饕餮紋飾的雕刻非常細緻，此壺充分展示了藏六的獨特技藝。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2102', 'IRON TEAPOT', '初代藏六造 龍首鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_867_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_867_2.jpg', '867', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺| 寬18.5公分，高17公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此鐵壺為初代藏六用上最具特色的饕餮紋為題，加上逼真有力的獸口壺嘴，絕對是把難得一見，老味十足的鐵壺。另外，此器特別配有雙蓋，一個為鐵製的本蓋，另一個是備用的黃銅蓋，蓋內刻有「藏六造」，共箱，有藏六親筆題字。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n藏六家族距今已有一百多年的歷史。深受藏家喜愛的獸口壺，是藏六本人最初於龍文堂時期學過的獸口型壺技法，加上他個人風格創作改良而成。初代藏六深受中國文物影響，對中國、周漢時期的青銅器有極深厚的研究，其饕餮紋飾有一種難以言喻的美感，其鑄造法受到大家的高度評價。因此江戶時代成為皇家御用工藝大師，負責製作孝明天皇的御璽、幕府將軍德川慶喜征夷大將軍黃金印、明治六年天皇御璽、大日本國璽等等。繼承秦藏六家業的都是他的子孫，代代相傳以「藏六」為名，繼承傳統的鑄造器物技術，至今仍被推崇為金屬工藝的第一人。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2103', 'IRON TEAPOT', '藏六式 青銅紋獸首鐵壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_868_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_868_2.jpg', '868', '', '63,250', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '鐵 壺 | 寬16.5公分，高16.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n藏六作品多見中國商周青銅風格，此器獸首予人一嗚驚人之勢，壺身壺蓋刻有饕餮、龍及如意紋，整把壺見岩地紋理，器形充滿藏六的風格。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n藏六家族距今已有150年的歷史。深受藏家喜愛的獸口壺，是藏六本人最初於龍文堂時期學過的獸口型壼技法，加上他個人風格創作改良而成。初代藏六深受中國文物影響，對中國、周漢時期青銅器有極深厚的研究，其饕餮紋飾有一種難以言喻的美感，其鑄造法受到大家的高度評價。因此江戶時代成為皇家御用工藝大師，負責製作孝明天皇的禦璽、幕府將軍德川慶喜征夷大將軍黃金印、明治六年天皇禦璽、大日本國璽等等。繼承秦藏六家業的都是他的子孫，代代相傳以「藏六」為名，繼承傳統的鑄造器物技術，至今仍被推崇為金屬工藝的第一人。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2104', 'TIN TEA WARE SET', '沈存周刻　古錫茶托五客 連 藏六造 錫製詩文茶罐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_869_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_869_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_869_3.jpg', '869', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 托｜徑10.5公分，高2公分<br />\r\n茶 罐｜長5公分，闊4公分，高9公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n六瓣花形古錫茶托，底款「張星記製」，托面落款為名家沈存周﹔五客各雕有不同的景象，分明以春夏秋冬及清風君子為題，刻有詩句及沈存周名字。<br />\r\n拍品配純錫茶罐，底款「藏六居造」，左右側各刻有詩句，正背面則刻有樹木和小屋，雕工精美；共箱。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沈存周（一六二九年- 一七零九年），浙江嘉興人。沈存周善制各種式樣的錫茶具，所雕刻的詩句、姓氏、圖印均規整精良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2105', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '藏六居造 系目紋龍首日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_870_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_870_2.jpg', '870', '', '57,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬14公分，高15公分，重375克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n系目紋飾日本純銀壺，壺底刻「藏六居造」款。由著名御釜師藏六造，壺嘴見龍首設計，配以鐵製提梁及銀鈕摘。於藏六的作品中，壺嘴常見為圖騰中神鳥神獸的獸口﹔壺身常見有饕餮、如意祥雲、富貴回紋及龍鳳呈祥等浮雕工藝的圖案出現，非常美觀且別具一格。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2106', 'A SET OF JAPANESE SILVER PLATES', '藏六造 銀果碟五件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_871_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_871_2.jpg', '871', '', '17,250', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '果 碟 | 徑14.5公分，高1.5公分，重74克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一套五件藏六造銀果碟，每件均見搥目紋及底款「藏六造」，共箱。已切開的水果若以純銀裝盛，則較不易變色。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2107', 'A PAIR OF AGARWOOD PLAQUES', '觀世音菩薩沉香雕牌一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_872_1.jpg', '872', '', '41,400', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉 香｜厚1公分，闊4公分，高6.2公分，共重42克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沉香氣味可溫養正氣，於佛教中常有作敬佛聖品用，具有特殊地位。此對觀世音菩薩雕牌油線細膩、溫潤，香韻幽柔溫醇；匠人的一流雕工完美刻出菩薩「觀察世間音聲覺悟有情」的慈祥神情，工料兼美。持握雕牌以表敬神之意，亦能使精神和心靈得到慰藉和安定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2108', 'AGARWOOD PLAQUE', '汶萊 彌勒佛黑油沉香雕件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_873_1.jpg', '873', '', '55,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '雕 件｜汶萊產，寬8公分，長2.5公分，重26克，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「大肚能容，容天下難容之事。 開口便笑，笑天下可笑之人。」<br />\r\n此汶萊沉香手感沉甸，入水秒沉，包漿厚醇黑褐亮澤，雕以圓額肥耳，面容祥和之彌勒佛，面相寬容和善，線條流暢圓滑。類似這類黑油及超重的沉香雕件市面極罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2109', 'BRUNEIAN AGARWOOD BEAD NECKLACE', '汶萊 一百零八粒八毫米沉香佛珠', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_874_1.jpg', '874', '', '207,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '佛 珠｜汶萊產，珠徑0.8公分，長88公分，流蘇3.5公分，重37克(含繩)，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這款汶萊一百零八粒珠串，材質好、油分足、做工好、珠子圓潤，絲縷細密，結構緊密，整個手串隱約看到油脂順空隙外溢，猶如行雲流水之細膩。香味上等，甜中帶涼，具有獨特的風韻。同類珠正常沉水標準為29.91克，而此佛珠超重23%左右。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n汶萊面積不到六千平方公里，土壤中鉀元素豐富，出產的沉香香韻醇厚，涼意綿綿，屬於一流香韻及產區。汶萊沉香的特徵是香韻有變化，清聞甘涼，再品會有乳香味，尾韻帶一些醇厚的香味。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2110', 'AGARWOOD BRACELET', '金絲奇楠手串', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_875_1.jpg', '875', '', '299,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '手 串｜珠徑0.9公分，內徑7.2公分，長9公分，重19克(含繩))<br />\r\n<br />\r\n金絲結的奇楠被稱為金絲奇楠，質地軟，其基色為微黃色，帶有絲絲金黃。<br />\r\n放於手心輕輕搓揉，即見表面黑褐色油脂分泌物，散發甘甜幽柔，味道使人心曠神怡；配上棗紅流蘇，大方樸實。此手串整條放入水中呈半沉狀態。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2111', 'NATURAL CARVING AGARWOOD', '紫奇楠擺件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_876_1.jpg', '876', '', '529,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '擺 件｜闊8公分，高18公分，重103克，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n奇楠為沉香之中的品質最上者，據說「一萬棵沉香中只有一棵奇楠」，存世不多，一般以工藝品形式示人，如拍品般原木的狀態，極為稀罕。紫奇楠即使在不燃燒時仍能從內而發以香襲人，香味帶有豐富層次感，細細品鑒，回韻甘醇奶香，药性比沉香更加温润。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此紫奇楠紋理清晰，表面可見深色油線，質地柔中帶剛；集天地靈氣，匯日月精華，極為珍貴。通體不加修飾，渾然天成，愛香人士必愛不釋手。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2112', 'CARVING AGARWOOD OF LOTUS LEAF', '沉香荷葉擺件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_877_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_877_2.jpg', '877', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉 香｜長10公分，高3.5公分，重23.2克<br />\r\n木 台｜長10公分，高5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n難得一見的沉香擺設，以整塊沉香雕刻成一片連著蓮蓬之荷葉，油色自然，油線更顯清晰。葉莖及荷葉葉脈造工非常像真，活靈活現，可見雕刻師的手法及功力。巧配獨特海浪紋木座，尤似荷花飄盪湖面上，是上佳之沉香工藝品。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2113', 'VIETNAMESE AGARWOOD PLAQUE', '越南順化沉香 沉水無事牌', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_878_1.jpg', '878', '', '126,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉水牌｜越南產，厚1公分，闊4公分，高6公分，重27克，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n146規格，此香密度較大，於水中能沉，油脂豐富，紋線明顯；此沉香以黃金比例切割，厚度適中，手感舒適，大氣莊重。<br />\r\n整塊牌上沒有進行過雕刻，平整如鏡，是為「無事」，有「平安無事」之意，寓意平平安安。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2114', 'MALAYSIAN AGARWOOD BRACELET (WITHDRAWN)', '西馬來西亞老料沉香手串 (撤回)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_879_1.jpg', '879', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.(WITHDRAWN)', '手 串｜西馬來西亞，珠徑1.6公分，長30公分，流蘇7公分，重44克(含繩)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此串十六毫米的手串精選自上品沉香琢磨而成，珠粒渾圓飽滿，質地沉實，油線紋理優美，香味撲人，且香味中帶有冰涼味道，十分適宜長期配戴盤玩，兼有溫養正氣之功效。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n《本草求真》中載有：「沉香，辛溫，體重色黑，落水不浮。故書載能下氣墜痰：氣香入脾，故能理諸氣而調中：色黑體陽，故書載能補火、曖精、壯陽。」<br />\r\n(撤回)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2115', 'INDONESIAN CARVING AGARWOOD', '印尼春華秋實 全油沉水擺件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_880_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_880_2.jpg', '880', '', '184,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '擺 件｜印尼產，長43公分，深4.7公分，高8公分，重210克 (重量不含木座)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沉香雕件在粗碩的上好沉香上雕刻出山水人家與大自然動物融合的情景，在盡可能保留珍貴的沉香為前題下，把各種動物和山林人家仔細展現出來，彷彿聽見鹿嗚鳥啼，水流河邊及遊人的嬉笑聲，可見匠心獨具，極富巧思。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此沉香紋理細膩，質地致密，皮色溫潤，表面可見黑褐色油脂分泌物，細聞味道使人心曠神怡，有一種難以言喻的美感。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n拍品附帶兩個不同造型的木座，其中一個為紫檀木。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2116', 'AGARWOOD BRACELET', '沉香手串', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_881_1.jpg', '881', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '手　串｜珠徑1.4公分，長31公分，流蘇11公分，重33克(含繩)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此香串質地緊密，氣味在常溫下奶香濃郁明顯，奶香中帶著淡淡甘醇<br />\r\n的甜味，佩戴於腕香氣歷久圍繞。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2117', 'JAPANESE AGARWOOD BEAD NECKLACE', '日本一百零八粒八毫米沉香佛珠', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_882_1.jpg', '882', '', '41,400', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '念 珠｜珠徑 0.8 公分，長81公分，流蘇30公分，重40克(含繩)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n相對於手珠而言，此八毫米沉香珠徑較細，這需要選擇油脂線分布更密的部位才能製成，可見此拍品的珍貴價值。一百零八粒沉香製成日本佛珠的形狀，念珠的數目都有它特定的含意，而一百零八顆主要是摧破百八煩惱。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2118', 'INDONESIAN CARVING AGARWOOD OF FLUTE', '達拉干 沉香笛形雕件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_883_1.jpg', '883', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '擺 件｜達拉干產，長20.3公分，深5.5公分，高5公分，重58克，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沉香有「植物中的鑽石」的稱號，其珍貴及觀賞性為收藏家競相收藏；此香產於達拉干，通體不加雕飾，以其中心通空的筒形略加修整打磨，宛如一枚橫笛造型，並配一座。質地緊實，光澤亮麗皮色溫潤，油份甚高，時時散發出甜涼馥郁而深邃的香氣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2119', 'JAPANESE AGARWOOD BRACELET', '日本御念珠沉香手串', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_884_1.jpg', '884', '', '46,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '手 串｜徑1.4公分，長32公分，流蘇6.5公分，重24克(含繩)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本御念珠，是沉香珠之極品﹔此手串以二十二粒主珠，兩粒隔珠及一粒佛頭沉香珠組成﹔每一粒都由精選高檔沉香琢磨而成，油線飽滿，是難得的好香氣，活氣芬芳，清聞濃鬱，特殊的油脂線在珠身形成美麗花紋。連精美燙金字木盒，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2120', 'HAINAN AGARWOOD BEAD NECKLACE', '惠安一百零八粒十毫米老沉香佛珠', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_885_1.jpg', '885', '', '345,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '佛 珠｜惠安產，珠徑１公分，長111公分，流蘇11公分，重74克，沉水<br />\r\n<br />\r\n佛教中認為人間有一百零八種煩惱，稱為百八煩惱，常捻手中一百零顆念珠可消去種種煩惱事。<br />\r\n惠安系沉香有不可再生的珍貴性，此念珠由一百零八顆十毫米的惠安老沉香製成，集天地靈氣，歷歲月的積澱，香韻清雅涼甜，帶有穿透力強的果香味；年份久遠的越南老惠安沉香，油線清晰香氣更為醇厚，歷久彌香，是沉香中的上品。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n正常十毫米的一百零八粒珠重量達到五十八點一八克已沉水，此珠重量超過沉水標準迎三成左右，市面少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2121', 'VIETNAMESE NATURAL CARVING AGARWOOD', '越南沉水 富森紅土奇肉', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_886_1.jpg', '886', '', '115,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉 香｜越南產，長19公分，寬4公分，重61克<br />\r\n沉 香｜越南產，長 7.5公分，寬1 公分，重11克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n收藏沉香中有「千年沉香，萬年紅土」的說法，由於土沉香必須長時間埋於土裡醇化，每一個出土的沉根約需經百年積澱；而紅土中又以越南富森出產最優，此拍品沉水，是土沉香中的極品。<br />\r\n此二件紅土奇肉氣韻香甜甘醇，於熏燒時帶有獨特西瓜香味，回韻略帶涼甜，因奇肉外受天能內蘊地氣，香質已徹底醇化，全無木性，質地堅實。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2122', 'NATURAL CARVING AGARWOOD', '老沉香擺件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_887_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_887_2.jpg', '887', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉 香｜寬12.5公分，高22.5公分，厚5.5公分，重381克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此老沉香擺件，常溫下味道醇厚豐富，層次感強，實心料手感沉甸，燒之甘甜芳香。外形挺直沉實。受沉香收藏家歡迎。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2123', 'NATURAL CARVING AGARWOOD', '古沉香擺件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_888_1.jpg', '888', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '沉 香｜寬22公分，高41.2公分，重792克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n北宋詞人周邦彥之《蘇幕遮·燎沉香》詞中：「燎沉香，消溽暑。鳥雀呼晴，侵曉窺簷語。」記載沉香不僅味道使人心曠神怡，焚香更有達到通體舒暢的功效。此沉香擺件整料之大十分難得，一面豐盈一面內凹展現天然美感。其油線飽滿，包漿渾厚且色澤深沉。於常溫下的香氣淡雅，熏燒時散發清甜馥鬱的味道，被視為觀賞使用之沉香上品。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2124', 'INCENSE TOOL SET WITH AGARWOOD', '黑漆鎏金香具套裝 連 沉香原木', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_889_1.jpg', '889', '', '80,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '純銀香座｜徑5公分，高8公分，重90克<br />\r\n香　匙｜長14公分，重9克<br />\r\n香　夾 (一對)｜長17公分，重32克<br />\r\n香　針 (一對)｜長20公分<br />\r\n香　盤｜長18.5公分，闊11公分，高2公分<br />\r\n香　盒｜徑6公分，高8公分<br />\r\n聞香罐｜徑6.5公分，高8公分<br />\r\n沉香藏盒｜長16.5公分，闊10分分，高11公分<br />\r\n沉　香｜約重59克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日式香道具套裝配備完整，其純銀香座器身通花，見菊花圖及如意紋，配鐵製香夾一對及香匙；另外沉香藏盒、一對香針、聞香罐、香盒及香盤都配以黑漆鎏金手工，亦見日式金菊花圖，於香盤、香盒及聞香罐上更印有靈鶴印章，高貴堂皇。拍品內配有珍貴沉香散件，如此齊備的沉香連香具套組，實為難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2125', 'A SET OF AGARWOOD CHIPS FROM EIGHT COUNTRIES', '八國香木', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_890_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_890_2.jpg', '890', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '越南產 熟結棧香<br />\r\n中國 海南島產 生結棧香<br />\r\n黎巴嫩產　生結棧香<br />\r\n馬來西亞 沙巴產 生結槧香<br />\r\n柬埔寨產 生結棧香<br />\r\n緬甸產 生結棧香<br />\r\n婆羅洲產 生結水沉<br />\r\n西新幾內亞產 生結黃熟香<br />\r\n錫蓮花紋香盒<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此沉香集結了八國的獨特韻味，是供初學者學香或收藏者收藏的珍品。包括錫制蓮花紋香盒。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n越南產  熟結棧香<br />\r\n越南最典型的棧香之一。融會了土，木，大自然，歷歲月的醇厚甘香味。被日本香道愛好者稱為「真南蠻」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國海南島產  生結棧香<br />\r\n擁有傳統的香味外，尾韻還會帶一點醇厚的酸味，是飄逸輕盈的魅力沉香。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n黎巴嫩產  生結棧香<br />\r\n蘊含著油脂甘味的同時，還散發著辛辣味。不同距離去感受它，會感覺到不同韻味，是其魅力之一。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n馬來西亞沙巴產  生結槧香<br />\r\n外觀是上等的綠油伽楠香，帶有黃色的豐厚光澤。散發出辛澀味和樹木的甘味，使人心曠神怡。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n柬埔寨產  生結棧香<br />\r\n古時候柬埔寨已被稱為是優良沉香的出產地。苦澀與微酸味上，還帶出濃厚的甘味；是難以找到的稀有品。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n緬甸產  生結棧香<br />\r\n緬甸獨特的樹脂斑紋，酸味中帶有甘味，尾韻還會帶一點濃厚的腥味，是其特點之一。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n婆羅洲產  生結水沉<br />\r\n沉香中的極品，散發出濃濃的香味。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n西新畿內亞產  生結黃熟香<br />\r\n擁有辛辣的香味，遠距離也可以感覺到它的存在。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2126', 'JAPANESE CENSER WITH WOODEN STAND', '明治水晶香爐 配 木托', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_891_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_891_2.jpg', '891', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐 ｜明治時期，徑15公分，高11公分<br />\r\n香爐台｜長11公分，高5公分，闊8公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n明治三十年的水晶香爐，共箱，箱蓋寫「廣陵金城一國斎 當六十九翁之造」。手工切割研磨，線條簡潔，香爐摘和雙耳均是獅獸形；香爐足也研磨成獅子足形，附有能配合獅子足底設計的香爐台。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2127', 'SQUARE CENSER, QING DYNASTY', '晚清 藍釉方爐配紅木蓋', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_892_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_892_2.jpg', '892', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐｜晚清代，長10公分，高14 公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n海藍色爐鈞釉四方爐，四角呈窩角，下承四足，藍釉深淺不一，蓋頂為瓜形摘，配半透雲形圖案紅木蓋，造形及顏色簡潔大方；共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2128', 'JAPANESE TRIPOD CENSER', '三浦竹泉造  青花五彩四君子如意三足爐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_893_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_893_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_893_3.jpg', '893', '', '10,350', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐｜徑11公分，高10.5公分，蓋重85克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n如意三足筒式香爐，造型典雅，外折角口沿飾斷續青花雙回紋，外繪梅蘭菊竹，用筆精工秀麗，佈局疏密有致，色彩鮮明亮麗，將梅花高潔、蘭花幽芳、竹子挺拔、菊花傲霜等自然屬性表露無遺，胎細白，釉清亮，三足；爐底有款。共箱，蓋款「竹泉造」。另配有松興堂的純銀花形香爐蓋，「松興堂造」底款，更添收藏價值。共箱，箱蓋內款「松興堂造」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n三浦竹泉(1854年－1915年)，本名 渡邊政吉（駒次郎）。號「有聲居」後改號「篩月庵」。十三歲拜三代高橋道八為師，1883年出師獨立。為京都燒瓷的改良作出傑出貢獻。家族至今五代。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2129', 'JAPANESE SILVER TRIPOD CENSER', '日本純銀製雲龍刻三足香爐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_894_1.jpg', '894', '', '27,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '香 爐｜徑11.5公分，高9.5公分，重295克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此純銀香爐飽滿圓潤，底款「純銀」，爐身刻有雲龍，雙眼有神，龍鬚飄逸，龍爪遒勁，靈動張揚，在天上飛翔。爐身銀質光亮如鏡，與網編鏤空香爐蓋合為一體。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2130', 'A PAIR OF JAPANESE SILVER FLAGONS', '日本純銀松竹梅雕刻酒器一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_895_1.jpg', '895', '', '29,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀酒器| 寬10公分，高17.5公分，重248克(不含竹筒)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀酒器一對，共箱，蓋內款「藤江一喜」。此對器身身上刻有松竹梅，生機盎然，賞心悅目。盛酒柱部份配竹筒供隔熱用，壺頂口有簡單刻紋加以裝飾，壺蓋配以花形鈕摘，提把彎圓直挺。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2131', 'A PAIR OF JAPANESE SILVER FLAGONS', '「秦藏六」款　藤紋雕刻銀酒器一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_896_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_896_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_896_3.jpg', '896', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀酒器| 寬21公分，高14公分，重608克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此對酒器壺底款「秦藏六製」，共箱，「明治丙申 秦藏六造」款。壺體扁而鼓圓，壺身至壺蓋雕刻藤葉圖案，壺嘴修長，嘴口頂端開至整個壺嘴中間，方便倒酒，壺蓋配以花形鈕摘，圓角形提把。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n秦藏六（1823‐90年），江戶末到明治時期的鑄金家。因為鑄造孝明天皇的銅印、將軍德川慶喜〈征夷大將軍〉的黃金印及明治天皇的印章而名聲高企。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2132', 'JAPANESE SILVER FLAGON AND DISHES', '日本純銀「歲寒三友」酒器一對 連 鳳凰碟一套', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_897_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_897_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_897_3.jpg', '897', '', '50,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '酒 器| 寬17.5公分，高15.5公分，重376克<br />\r\n碟(大) | 徑12公分，高3公分，重149克<br />\r\n碟(中) | 徑10.5公分，高3公分，重96克<br />\r\n碟(小)| 徑9公分，高2.5公分，重68克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀酒器一對，壺身雕刻歲寒三友：竹、梅、松，酒器雕工細繳，清晰分明，蓋底款「純銀」，壺身有款；共箱。另配以純銀碟三隻，均刻有鳳凰飛翔圖案，並飾以嵌金花朵圖案，碟「純銀」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2133', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE', '一望齋造 日本純銀梅楓地紋南鐐真形釜', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_898_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_898_2.jpg', '898', '', '57,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '真形釜｜徑28公分，高21公分，重3192克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀真形釜，由名家一望齋鑄造，底款「一望齋」。器身雕有梅花楓葉圖案，頂配果實形鈕摘，兩旁有獸形環，作工精緻質感細膩。此器又名茶湯釜，有說是從香爐改良而成，與銀壺茶器一樣，能燒出上乘的水作品茶之用。共箱，箱「一望齋造」底款，箱蓋「一望齋造」底款。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2134', 'JAPANESE GOLD TEAPOT', '日本阿古陀形皇室鍍金壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_899_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_899_2.jpg', '899', '', '13,800', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬17公分，高14公分，重848克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在此鍍金的阿古陀形壺身上，刻有十六瓣八重的菊花圖案，貴重而奢華，彰顯皇家風範，共箱，寫「御金瓶」；絕對是收藏之選。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本並無法定國花，但於日本鎌倉幕府時代，當時羽天皇將菊花紋裝飾在武士刀刀柄上，並且制定為皇室紋章，十六瓣八重的菊紋就成為皇室家徽，於是菊紋就成為近千年來的皇室代表。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2135', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '岡野 槌目紋日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_900_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_900_2.jpg', '900', '', '13,800', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺| 寬10公分，高11公分，重103克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本純銀槌目紋小型湯沸，砲管式壺嘴，配以藤編提把，壺底款「岡野」，共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2136', 'PORTABLE TEA WARE SET', '竹編茶籠茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_901_1.jpg', '901', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '錫    墊｜直徑8公分<br />\r\n紫砂壺｜徑9公分，高6公分<br />\r\n錫茶罐｜徑5公分，高5公分<br />\r\n瓷茶洗｜徑12.5公分，高5公分<br />\r\n瓷茶杯｜徑4公分，高2公分<br />\r\n瓷公平杯｜徑3.5公分，高6公分<br />\r\n錫茶托｜徑5公分，高0.5公分<br />\r\n沉 香 ｜重5克<br />\r\n象牙茶量｜徑7公分，高1公分<br />\r\n竹器皿｜徑4公分，高3.5公分<br />\r\n竹    台｜徑5公分，高1.5公分<br />\r\n竹    籃｜徑9公分，高2公分<br />\r\n竹    盒｜徑8公分，高2公分<br />\r\n竹    箱｜徑22.5公分，高10.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此拍品為少見的小品茶具套組，當中以底款「端崇嘉造」的錫墊最為注目，器上有沈存周刻詩及落款，並帶有花葉紋。套組一應俱全：紫砂壺比例及手工優越，器身圓渾，泥料上乘，出自名家手筆；五客底款「是生」錫茶托，配以相同數目青花杯；茶洗配以鐵製銅錢花紋蓋；錫茶罐、瓷製公平杯﹑沉香乙件及象牙竹紋茶量，皆秀麗動人。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另配竹編茶籃、鐵三足竹台、竹盒及竹茶具箱，竹韻悠悠，方便攜帶，享茗茶之樂，值得收藏。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n沈存周為浙江嘉興人，是藝術家，亦是詩人，最為人熟悉的茶具作品為刻詩句鍚茶壺。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2137', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '名越昌晴 槌目紋三銀壺 連 茶具套裝', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_902_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_902_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_902_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_902_4.jpg', '902', '', '230,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺(大)｜徑21公分，高26公分，重1245克<br />\r\n銀 壺(小)｜徑15公分，高18.5公分，重475克<br />\r\n急 須｜徑12.5公分，高8.5公分，重204克<br />\r\n公平杯｜徑13.5公分，高6公分，重154克<br />\r\n茶托(十件)｜長12公分，寬8公分，高2.7公分，重91克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n整套名越昌晴銀壺、公平杯及茶托均以槌目紋裝飾，皆有底款「昌晴」，格調一致。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n珠寶形銀壺和急須包漿潤澤，而壺身頂部及蓋都覆以銀片，似盔甲披掛壺肩，配以環摘。大小銀壺提梁設計精美，當中急須以鳳首作壺嘴，羽冠唯肖唯妙。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n一套五件名家作品皆共箱，「名越彌五郎」款；造型高貴端莊，為名越昌晴經典作品之一，保存完整，如此齊全茶具有非常高的收藏與欣賞價值。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n名越昌晴出自江戶末期的東京地區，釜師名越彌五郎始作鐵壺，特別是十代昌晴受封大日本釜師長，是近代有名的日本名家釜師。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2138', 'TEA WARE SET', '金絲楠木托盤 茶具組合', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_903_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_903_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_903_3.jpg', '903', '', '69,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '托 盤｜長43.5公分，闊40公分，高2.5公分<br />\r\n茶 罐｜徑6.5公分，高6.5公分，重141克<br />\r\n茶 壺｜寬13公分，高6.5公分，重122克<br />\r\n茶 托｜徑10公分，高1.5公分，重56克<br />\r\n茶 杯｜徑6.5公分，高4公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此茶具組合中最令人注目的為金絲楠木托盤，盤內刻有葉紋裝飾，周邊屈曲成荷花形狀，木紋自然，見證金絲楠木的百年改變。金絲楠木為楨楠屬樹種，是中國特有的珍貴木材，但生長緩慢，一般成材要五百年。於歷史上專用於皇家宮殿、少數寺廟的建築和家具，古代一些帝王的龍椅寶座，都指定選用優質金絲楠木製作。於明清期間遭大量砍伐，國務院遂於一九八四年將楨楠木列入受保護植物之一。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n茶具組合另配有中國式紫砂壺設計的銀製茶壺，以紅木作把手，較為少見；共箱。以及絲紋日本純銀茶罐，底款「純銀 惠齋」；共箱，「一惠齋造」款。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n五客青花杯見人物景物圖，沿口及足底有橫紋裝飾。底款「大明成化年製」，共箱，箱蓋款「平安 三世 竹泉製」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n三代竹泉為第一代竹泉大師的末子。因為哥哥（二代竹泉）早逝和哥哥的兒子年幼，1921年(大正十年)繼承藝名。在1931年(昭和六年)讓位給四代竹泉，過后自號「竹軒」創作。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2139', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA WARE SET', '淨益造 菊摘側把日本純銀茶壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_904_1.jpg', '904', '', '12,650', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬17公分，高7公分，重264克<br />\r\n茶 托｜徑10.5公分，高1.5公分，重77克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n底款「淨益造」的茶壺，細霧槌目的壺身質感細滑如膚，器身呈現刀板瓣式手工，菊瓣鈕摘配以紅木側把手，典雅秀麗。配純銀茶托五客，底款「純銀」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2140', 'TIN TEA WARE SET', '日本 錫半 錫製茶具套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_905_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_905_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_905_3.jpg', '905', '', '23,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜寬15公分，高8.5公分<br />\r\n茶 罐｜徑8.5公分，高8公分<br />\r\n建 水｜徑10.5公分，高6.5公分<br />\r\n茶 量｜長9.4公分，寬4.4公分，高1.3公分<br />\r\n茶 托｜徑10公分，高2公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n來自大阪錫半的錫製茶具套組，壺底、建水底﹑茶罐底及茶托見「南錫 錫半」底款﹔每件器具風格乾淨俐落，設計統一。錫半為日本三大頂級錫器製造商之一，為最初的錫器名門。一九九六年，十代錫半夫婦與大阪錫器商議，工匠歸入大阪錫器門下，自此二人隱居，已食為樂，因此錫半的收藏品已不多見﹔共箱，「錫半造」款。整套由名釜師製作的品茶工具絕對稀有，值得愛茶之士收藏自用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n錫是緊隨白金、黃金及銀之後的稀有金屬，富有光澤、無毒，不易氧化，不變色並有很好的殺菌，淨化，保濕，保鮮效果。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2141', 'TEA WARE SET', '白泥茶壺 連 涼爐套組', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_906_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_906_2.jpg', '906', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 壺｜徑16公分，高10公分<br />\r\n涼 爐｜徑13.5公分，高18公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n少見白泥造茶壺套裝，茶壺壺身刻有字句，下方見印章，側手提把。配白泥三足涼爐，爐面左右刻畫梅枝，更刻有詩文一首，古意盎然，共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2142', 'ZITAN AND BAMBOO FOLDING SCREEN', '紫檀斑竹屏風', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_907_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_907_2.jpg', '907', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '屏 風 | 長121.3公分，高27公分，厚1.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n屏風以斑竹(又名湘妃竹)及紫檀木而製，紫檀別名「青龍木」，是一種深紫黑色的硬木，在紅木中屬高級的用材，入水即沉，適用於製作家具和雕刻藝術品。以紫檀造的器物經打蠟磨光後，不需油漆己可呈現出亮麗光澤。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此長方屏風外形簡樸，中間通空部份配上不規則排列之斑竹，秀美清雅。屏風可對摺，方便收藏，共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2143', 'XIANGFEI BAMBOO TEA TABLE, QING DYNASTY', '清  湘妃竹冰紋長方茶几', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_908_1.jpg', '908', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶  几｜清代，長61公分，闊36.5公分，高21公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n平直長方小茶几，以多根湘妃竹製成，竹色蠟黃，包漿細密，上見紅點，面板黑漆光亮如鏡 。榫卯結實，工藝孄熟，韻味十足，可供茶道之用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2144', 'ANTIQUE CUPBOARD', '紅木嵌斑竹白玉扣器局', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_909_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_909_2.jpg', '909', '', '29,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '器 局 | 高56公分，寬24.8公分，深38.8公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「器」 即茶事道具，「局」即房間；意指收存茶器具的櫃子。古色古香的紅木對開門器局為雙隔棚，設計嵌有斑竹，竹韻悠悠；白玉扣取手更添高貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2145', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '鐵平款 菊紋寶珠形日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_910_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_910_2.jpg', '910', '', '20,700', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬13.5公分，高15公分，重216克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此日本純銀壺，鐵平款，寶珠形壺身，壺蓋槌出菊花圖案﹔清雅高潔的菊花向來都是作家喜歡使用的題材，令人陶醉於其中。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2146', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '秋田竹菊造 葉紋日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_911_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_911_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_911_3.jpg', '911', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬14公分，高12公分，重347克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n長閑形銀壺，器底款「秋田力竹谷 純銀」樣，共箱。壺身至壺蓋搥打出葉紋，配以花苞式樣鈕摘，壺嘴亦較修長，整個壺予人清幽高雅之感。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2147', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '松榮堂 南瓜形日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_912_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_912_2.jpg', '912', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬14公分，高15.5公分，重474克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n松榮堂從明治時期就成為金壽堂的重要堂口，亦是京都有名的老堂號之一。此器壺呈南瓜形，壺身雕琢出天然的瓜紋，豆莢樣提梁，瓜蒂為蓋款，瓜藤為鈕摘，共箱，箱內款「松榮堂」。作品巧奪天工，生動傳神，為松榮堂之佳作。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2148', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '槌目渦紋日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_913_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_913_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_913_3.jpg', '913', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺 | 寬15公分，高14.5公分，重306克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此日本純銀壺體線圓潤，短直流，壺身槌目渦紋，藤編提樑繞上銀線作點綴，壺身風格以圓線為主，古拙而典雅，為小壺中佳品；底款「純銀」，共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2149', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '周雲亭 芋形日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_914_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_914_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_914_3.jpg', '914', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬15公分，高17公分，重470克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此日本純銀壺底款「周雲亭 製」，壺身為芋形，炮口壺嘴，寶珠形摘，交叉繩式提把，簡單大方，自用或收藏皆宜；共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2150', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEAPOT', '三環翠摘槌目紋日本純銀壺', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_915_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_915_2.jpg', '915', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '銀 壺｜寬16公分，高19公分，重377克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n丸形日本純銀壺，器身的槌目紋較常見的為疏且有金紋，三翠環摘與槌目紋互相暉映，加上古式藤編壺把，清雅脫俗。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2151', '60\'s OOLONG TEA', '六十年代紅水烏龍', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_916_1.jpg', '916', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 葉 | 重500克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n六十年代紅水烏龍，摘採心葉半開、二葉全開的茶芽為原料，發酵在25至35度之間，揉捻整型至半球型，需細心焙火精製才能完全展現應有的品質與風味。茶湯色澤金黃明亮，香氣介於花香與果香之間，入口湯質細密甘醇，無刺激性，茶韻香濃在咽喉久久不散，而且此茶相當的耐泡，可達十泡以上，茶色、香、味縱然稍減，但悶泡後仍然相當迷人。此即紅水烏龍的魅力所在。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n「紅水烏龍」即是傳統的凍頂烏龍，主產於鹿谷鄉凍頂、鳳凰以及永隆三個茶區。民國七十三年，季野前輩將凍頂烏龍茶以「紅水烏龍茶」為名，進行學術發表，始見紅水之名。因時效性以及製作工序繁雜，紅水烏龍在製造上有一定的困難度。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2152', '60\'s CHINESE TEA', '六十年代宋種單欉', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_917_1.jpg', '917', '', '23,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 葉｜重500克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n已被珍藏50餘年的六十年代宋種單欉，其樹種達三百年；富有藥韻之香，甘甜潤喉。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n單欉，如同四十歲的中年人士，有力量，有深度。沖泡單欉，要水溫高，出茶快。單欉口感清爽，層次豐富，有天然蘭花香，清新怡人。宋種單欉是香氣最清淡的一種，似有似無，若遠若近。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2153', '60\'s PUER TEA', '六十年代廣雲貢餅 (青餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_918_1.jpg', '918', '', '32,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '此六十年代的廣雲貢餅，所含的雲南大葉種原料較純、比例極高。茶菁為大葉喬木，梗條較少，茶面萌芽感覺較少，有漂亮的陳化銀毫。茶湯清澈透亮，顏色偏黃、紅艷明亮，葉底轉化均齊。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n前三泡、富有紅茶特有焦香，野樟香淡然，三泡後紅茶焦香漸失，口感轉薄為滑，潤化喉頭。第四泡後大葉種野樟香飄然，茶氣復甦、有勁，紅茶焦香盡失，野樟香醇厚濃郁，入口醇滑，膠質稠密，水性活潑，新鮮感在口中綻放，喉韻深而甜潤有勁，回甘持久，兩頰、舌面生津，頓時有「喉吻潤、破孤悶」之感！沖泡十餘泡後，甘甜不絕、回甘持久，樟香依舊、濃郁醇厚，醇滑舒順之感綿延不絕。香氣上乘及陳香味足，入口生津，回甘好。同期茶品中，性價比有絕對優勢。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2154', '70\'s PUER TEA', '七十年代宋聘青餅', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_919_1.jpg', '919', '', '34,500', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '七十年代宋聘的茶氣強，香氣純正，滋味醇厚，耐久泡，入口所呈現的是濃鬱飽滿的野樟香味，隨著層次的轉變而有不同的呈現，茶香順著兩頰流貫於口鼻間，品嘗時口感順暢且醇厚，溫潤香甜，不乾不燥。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2155', '90\'s PUER TEA', '九十年代紅印普洱青餅 (三餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_920_1.jpg', '920', '', '19,550', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '此九十年代大紅印，湯色紅亮，香氣濃郁，回甘綿長，茶湯柔細，滋味純正；受大眾歡迎。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2156', '90\'s PUER TEA (WITHDRAWN)', '九十年代黃印普洱青餅 (撤回)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_921_1.jpg', '921', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site. (WITHDRAWN)', '九十年代大黃印，綜合嫩度高，滋味的鮮爽度好。香純味而韻厚，口感細膩，回味悠遠，茶氣較足，葉底褐紅經久耐泡。<br />\r\n(撤回)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2157', '90\'s PUER TEA', '九十年代勐海茶厰7542  普洱青餅 (五餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_922_1.jpg', '922', '', '27,600', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '7542是中國茶葉領導品牌大益茶業出產量最大的青餅，以肥壯茶菁為裡，幼嫩芽葉為撒面，研配得當，面茶色澤烏潤顯芽毫，心茶肥壯。該茶品香氣純正持久，有花果香，滋味濃厚回甘好，湯色黃亮，葉底勻齊。因其研配時主要以中壯茶菁為骨架，配以細嫩芽葉撒面，結構飽滿，存放后期變化較為豐富，被市場譽為「評判普洱生茶品質的標準產品」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2158', '90\'s PUER TEA', '九十年代8582普洱青餅 (七餅加一餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_923_1.jpg', '923', '', '43,700', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '8582為選用原中茶公司自有配方拼配而成的茶葉，茶葉口感醇和甘甜，經過多年乾倉醇化，口感甘醇。此拍品有八片8582青餅，更是難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2159', '2003 PUER TEA', '二零零三年大益普洱青餅 (三餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_924_1.jpg', '924', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '由著名「大益」出品，倉存良好，有「紅大益標誌」、「易武正山 野生茶」、「勐海茶廠出品」。三片裝，市面難求。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2160', '2005 PUER TEA', '二零零五年「唐宋」青餅普洱茶 (二餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_925_1.jpg', '925', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '此茶為私人訂制產品，外包裝盒、包裝紙、收藏證、茶葉內飛等均有統一防偽認證，茶葉採用單一茶菁，古法壓制，品質一流。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2161', '2006 PUER TEA', '二零零六年斗記青餅普洱茶 (七餅加一餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_926_1.jpg', '926', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '本品採用著名普洱茶原產地勐海縣巴達山章朗鄉早春古樹茶菁精心壓制，口感豐富，香氣獨特。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2162', '70\'s PUER TEA', '七十年代文革茶磚 (青餅)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_927_1.jpg', '927', '', '16,100', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '文革磚的一大特點在於它是第一批在文化大革命期間製作的磚茶，因而得其名，具典藏價值。此七十年代文革茶磚，蔘香濃鬱，甜滑而醇厚，甜意滿溢。採用勐海新茶園大葉種灌木新樹茶菁為原料，條索細長，茶面栗紅色，水薄略有苦澀。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2163', '1989 PUER TEA', '一九八九年出口裝普洱熟茶 (五盒)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_928_1.jpg', '928', '', '23,000', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '此茶為出口法國回流品，原包裝存放倉存良好。口感綿滑，陳香醇厚。八十年代初銷法磚屬陳香型陳年普洱，在初早期由於口感好而廣受歡迎，知名度很高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2164', 'PUER TEA', '普洱方茶熟茶 (十磚)', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_929_1.jpg', '929', '', '14,950', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '普洱方茶是以晒青綠茶「滇青」為原料蒸壓而成。因此與雲南沱茶一樣屬於綠茶緊壓茶。以三至五級外滇青為原料，經蒸壓成方形，故稱「普洱方茶」。主產於雲南省的西雙版納勐海茶廠和昆明茶廠，此為勐海茶廠的出品，湯色蜜黃油光，香氣清高馥郁，滋味濃釅持久。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2165', 'TEA WARE SET', '古錫製山水茶罐 連 茶托五件', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_930_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_930_2.jpg', '930', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑8.5公分，高11公分，重341克<br />\r\n茶 托｜長9公分，闊6.5公分，高2.5公分，重52克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此古錫製茶罐是為了紀念西鹿兒島給油所開所而製造的。罐背刻有「西鹿兒島給油所開所紀念 合名會社 三角商店」。罐身和蓋上均刻有山水。可見蠢蠢欲動的火山。連五件茶托，底款「幹茂號造」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2166', 'TIN TEA CONTAINER', '古錫大茶罐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_931_1.jpg', '931', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑15.5公分，高18公分 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n古錫大茶壺，設計簡單大方，茶罐色澤古意自然，底部刻有「大阪錫新」；共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2167', 'TIN TEA CONTAINER', '古錫製小篆紋茶罐', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_932_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_932_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_932_3.jpg', '932', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 罐｜徑16.5公分，高20公分， <br />\r\n<br />\r\n此古錫製茶罐及蓋上均刻有小篆紋，底部刻有造款；共箱，「龍文堂」款。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2168', 'A PAIR OF SILVER CUPS', '銀製桃形杯一對', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_933_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_933_2.jpg', '933', '', '5,750', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '杯｜長7公分，高2公分，重23克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n匠師巧妙地把這對銀製杯設計成桃形，旁邊枝葉為把手。杯底佈滿敲打細密的槌目紋。造型別緻，製作精美。共箱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2169', 'JAPANESE SILVER TEA LADLE', '日本純銀茶杓', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_934_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_934_2.jpg', '934', '', '9,200', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '茶 杓 | 長23公分，高7公分，重61克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n茶杓底見「純銀」款，杓身見直刀板片式搥打紋，配以木手柄，予人低調雅致的感覺。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2170', 'IRON PLATE', '中尾省三造 鐵提梁葉形果盤', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_935_1.jpg', '935', '', '6,900', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '果 盤 | 長22.5公分，闊19公分，高12.5公分<br />\r\n<br />\r\n葉形鐵果盤，盤面雕有清晰葉脈紋理，樹枝作提梁，底款「省三造」。共箱，刻「中尾省三造」款。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2171', 'JAPANESE SILVER PLATE', '藏六 日本白銀菊葉盤', '33', '/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_936_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a22/LOTNO_936_2.jpg', '936', '', '14,950', null, null, null, null, 'Please refer to Chinese site.', '托 盤｜長22公分，闊13公分，高4.5公分，重213克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此白銀托盤，出自名師藏六，以菊葉為主題，盤為葉身，紋理自然細緻，巧妙地以葉柄作把手，不收口的設計更為特別，底款藏六「花押」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n秦藏六，或稱藏六；其蠟鑄法對中國青銅器發展影響深遠，除了鐵壺、銀壺等最為人所熟悉外，亦製作不少銀器用品，都是收藏家心目中的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2172', 'Oskar Barnack Design Drawing', 'Oskar Barnack Design Drawing', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_1_1.JPG', '1', '', '4,130', null, null, null, null, 'Original hand drawings by Oskar Barnack with his signature, sized 10X15cm.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOskar Barnack ( 1879 – 1936) was a German optical engineer, precision mechanic, industrial designer and the father of 35 mm photography. In 1911, Barnack was in charge of microscope research for Ernst Leitz at Wetzlar, Germany. He was an enthusiastic photographer, but the heavy equipment of the day was difficult for him to handle due to his poor health. Therefore he decided to develop a small format fine camera. In 1912, he constructed the first 35 mm camera – Ur-Leica which unleashed a revolution in photography.', 'Oskar Barnack是創製首部135格式菲林徠卡相機的設計師，於光學攝影及徠卡發展史上皆有崇高地位。此拍品是來自Oskar Barnack的設計手稿，底部附有其親筆簽名，是徠卡發展的一個重要見證﹔富有歷史意義。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOskar Barnack (1879年至1936年)是德國著名的光學工程及精密機械工程師，並且熱愛攝影﹔他最廣為人知的成就是創製首部35mm菲林徠卡相機，故被稱為35mm菲林相機之父。由於當時的攝影設備龐大笨重，身為德國徠茲技師的他萌生了要做一個小巧及高性能相機的念頭，促使他致力研究35mm菲林相機。終於在1912年，他成功研發世界首台輕巧而高質素的35mm菲林相機 – Ur-Leica，為往後的相機發展及歷史奠下一個極其重要的里程碑。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2173', '&quot;Tropen&quot; Leica', '&quot;Tropen&quot; Leica', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_2_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_2_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_2_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_2_4.jpg', '2', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'The camera has been made from a Leica III, now presenting a mixture of a Black paint “Leica Null Series” copy. An interesting part is to be noticed the brass body shell. This is a very rare “Tropen” version, used for shipments in tropical regions in the 1930th. This camera was examined by Ottmar Michaely; an authenticated certificate from Ottmar Michaely is included, with body cap.', '此機由Leica III改裝，仿照O-series所製造，結合了兩者的精髓。最特別之處是機身的銅製部份；它是1930年代徠卡為熱帶地區所製的“Tropen”版本，十分罕見。此機經過Ottmar Michaely的鑑定，連同Ottmar Michaely的鑑定信及機身蓋。機身有明顯使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2174', 'O-Series Replica', 'O-Series Replica', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_3_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_3_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_3_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_3_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_3_5.JPG', '3', '', '8,260', null, null, null, null, 'The O-Series Replica was launched in Photokina in 2000, only 2,000 pieces were made. It comes with Anastigmat 3.5/50mm lens, leather case and box.', '此款O-Series限量2,000台的復刻版相機於2000年的Photokina上推出，連Anastigmat 3.5/50mm鏡頭、皮套及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2175', 'IA Elmax 3.5/50mm (The Last Piece)', 'IA Elmax 3.5/50mm (The Last Piece)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_4_6.JPG', '4', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original Leica Model A (1926) with fixed lens Elmax 3.5/50mm. The Elmax was the second version of lens built into the 1A, after the Anastigmat and before the Elmar. Camera with Elmax occur between serial numbers 280 to 1280 approximately, this camera is the last piece produced. The camera shows original features of the second version Elmax Leica: without ratchet wind, with frame counter up to 35, 7 speed dial, lever A/R in all black and flat eyepiece, etc. The camera comes with matching front lens cap, table tripod (TOOSF) and leather case.', '此1A相機配不可更換的Elmax 3.5/50mm鏡頭。Elmax是1A套機中的第二代，是在Anastigmat及Elmar之間的產品。機身序號在280至1280之間，此機便是第二代中的最後一台; 特徵包括沒有齒輪式轉盤、菲林讀數至35、七個快門速度、但有全黑的A/R杆及平的取景框等。此機連同鏡頭蓋、坐檯腳架(TOOSF)及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2176', 'IA Elmar 3.5/5cm', 'IA Elmar 3.5/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_5_7.JPG', '5', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1930, this 1A belongs to an early production. It comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm lens, leather case, meter scale and front lens cap.', '此機產於1930年，屬於徠卡早期產品。此機配有Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭，連皮套、測距杆及鏡頭前蓋; 機頂露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2177', 'I Mod. B Dial-Set Compur', 'I Mod. B Dial-Set Compur', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_6_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_6_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_6_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_6_4.JPG', '6', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'The production of Dial-set is only 638 pieces, in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡I Mod. B Compur產量大約只有1,500台，當中分有Rim-set及Dial-set兩款，而Dial-set的產量較少，只產有638台。此相機配有鏡間快門及特別的酒窩形快門按鈕，而鏡頭上獨特的“Film Counter Lock”在Rim-set所沒有的。此機年代久遠，成色較新，屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2178', 'Non-Standard Black Paint', 'Non-Standard Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_7_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_7_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_7_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_7_4.JPG', '7', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Black painted Non-Standard comes with England cine lens Ross London Teleros 5.5/4 inch (#128042), with front lens cap. Both have light brassing and signs of normal use, in good working order.', '黑漆Non-Standard機身以黃銅及鎳金屬所製成，配以英國著名的Ross London Teleros 5.5/4 inch (#128042) 黑漆電影鏡頭，成象細膩且色調柔和。此機連鏡頭前蓋，機身及鏡頭均有正常使用痕跡及露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2179', 'IIIa with Telyt 4.8/280mm', 'IIIa with Telyt 4.8/280mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_8_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_8_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_8_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_8_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_8_5.JPG', '8', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an IIIa camera, without serial number engraved on top plate, relatively rare. It comes with a Telyt 4.8/280mm (#1850047), PEGOO 45’magnifier, Visoflex I (#19518) and front lens cap.', '本拍品為徠卡IIIa相機，快門最高為1/1000秒；此機最特別之處為機頂上沒有刻上機身號，市場較為少見。連同長焦鏡Telyt 4.8/280mm (#1850047)、PEGOO 45度取景器、Visoflex I (#19518) 及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2180', 'Hektor 2.5/12cm Prototype with Standard Black Paint', 'Hektor 2.5/12cm Prototype with Standard Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_9_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_9_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_9_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_9_4.JPG', '9', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original prototype Hektor 1:2.5/12cm lens in black. The development of the Hektor 12.5 cm Visoflex lens begun on experimentation with 12 cm Hektor projection lenses, mounted on the Visoflex. An input given by Leica pioneer Walter Benser, who found the projection lens extremely good and was excited to see results with this lens in fact used for taking pictures. The black lens here is already a complete Leica Visoflex mount lens, with helical and diaphragm. It is without serial number. It seems to be a one of a kind and is published in the Wilhelm Albert’s book ‘Geburtstage der Leitz-Foto-Konstruktionen ab 1927’ page 152 (116), reference given for the date of the design is the year of 1949. In 1950, the black lens was followed by a small pre-series in chrome, within the 7530XX serial number range, before the lens was commercially introduced as Hektor 12.5cm in 1954. Please compare Lager Vol. II (lenses), pages 92 and 93. This lens comes with a Standard in black painted (#104226), POOIM 30X swing-in magnifier showing and a mirror reflex housing Visoflex PLOOT (#7183). This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '這是一支非常罕見的原型版Hektor 2.5/12cm鏡頭。知名的徠卡攝影師Walter Benser發現把用在投影機上的12cm鏡頭用來拍照片，成象非常漂亮。於是徠茲便以此投影鏡為藍本，開發Hektor 12.5cm Visoflex鏡頭。此拍品便是Hektor 12.5cm的原型版，而且已是Visoflex卡口。此鏡沒有序號，在Wilhelm Albert的著作《Geburtstage der Leitz-Foto-Konstruktionen ab 1927》p.152(116) 中亦有對此鏡的描述，資料顯示其設計年份為1949年。隨後一年，工廠生產過少量銀色試行版推出市面(鏡頭序號在7530XX範圍)，直到1954年Hektor 12.5 cm正式量產。更多資料可參閱James Lager Vol.II p.92-93。另外，拍品包括黑漆Standard機身 (#104226)、30x放大器POOIM及直立式取景器PLOOT (#7183)。此鏡經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2181', 'Standard with Two Lenses Set', 'Standard with Two Lenses Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_10_6.JPG', '10', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica Standard comes with two lenses, which are Elmar 3.5/5cm (#730324) in chrome finished with both lens caps and a Thambar 2.2/9cm (#311309) in black painted finished with spot filter, instruction and hood with cap. A black painted meter scale (#21123) is included also.', '徠卡Standard黑漆機身配以兩支鏡頭，分別是Elmar 3.5/5cm (#730324)銀色鏡頭，配前後蓋; 另一支為徠卡著名的人像鏡皇Thambar 2.2/9cm (#311309) 黑漆鏡頭，它是徠卡唯一一款擁有柔焦效果的鏡頭，而且是早期產量較少的測距版本，帶測距杆 (#21123); 配有Leica柔焦濾鏡、說明書及遮光罩連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2182', 'Standard Black Paint with Summar 2/5cm Chrome', 'Standard Black Paint with Summar 2/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_11_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_11_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_11_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_11_4.JPG', '11', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a black painted Standard camera with repair marks on leather; it comes with Summar 2/5cm chrome lens (#267007), rapid winder and leather case.', '此黑漆Standard機身飾皮有修補痕跡；連同Summar 2/5cm銀色鏡頭 (#267007)、過片器及皮套，市面較少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2183', 'Standard Chrome with Elmar 3.5/5cm (WITHDRAWN)', 'Standard Chrome with Elmar 3.5/5cm (撤回)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_12_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_12_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_12_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_12_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_12_5.JPG', '12', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Standard in chrome finish, with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#391947) and front lens cap. (WITHDRAWN)', '銀色Standard機身配Elmar 3.5/5cm (#391947) 及鏡頭前蓋，操作正常。(撤回)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2184', 'III Black Paint with Hektor 2.5/5cm', 'III Black Paint with Hektor 2.5/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_13_8.JPG', '13', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a black paint III coupling with following equipment in nickel finsihed: Hektor 2.5/5cm (#125516), with prism housing VOSTN (#2582) and special bracket VOROD for holding; and a slow speed device HEBOO. Moreover, it also comes with leather case, FOKOS with box and VOTRA with box.', '此黑漆機身配件齊全，除了Hektor 2.5/5cm (#125516)外，更連同立體鏡裝置VOSTN (#2582)、固定托架VOROD連取景器及慢快門裝置HEBOO。此外，更配有皮套、FOKOS測距杆連盒及VOTRA立體鏡裝置連盒。整套相機配件齊備，所有金屬部分均為鎳製，市場較罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2185', 'III Black Paint with Telyt 4.5/20cm', 'III Black Paint with Telyt 4.5/20cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_14_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_14_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_14_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_14_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_14_5.JPG', '14', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black painted III body comes with Telyt 4.5/20cm (#1256508) and lens hood. With slight signs of use and in good working order.', '此黑漆機身配有長焦鏡Telyt 4.5/20cm (#1256508) 及遮光罩，成色新淨，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2186', '250GG with Elmar 3.5/5cm Dummy', '250GG with Elmar 3.5/5cm Dummy', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_15_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_15_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_15_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_15_4.JPG', '15', '', '424,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original Leica 250GG Reporter dummy in mint condition, the word “Germany” engraved on top plate. Even there is no mechanism at all inside, the pre-war Leica Dummy models are very rare and the existence of 250GG dummy is unknown. It comes with an Elmar 3.5/5cm lens and an original 250GG box.', '此機是250GG的Dummy版，成色極佳。由於戰前徠卡只生產了極少數的模型機，250GG的模型機更是鮮為人知，所以此模型機雖然缺少了內部的機械結構，但仍然是收藏家追求的珍寶。此機機頂上刻有 「Germany」 字樣；連同銀色的Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭及罕見的原裝250GG包裝盒，為收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2187', 'IIIf with Compur Summicron-M 2/50mm in Consecutive Numbers', 'IIIf with Compur Summicron-M 2/50mm in Consecutive Numbers', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_16_7.JPG', '16', '', '590,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz designer Erwin Neurath combined a between-the-lens central shutter with the fitting of a Summicron 5cm lens to enable a higher electronic flash sync speed of at 1/100 and 1/200 sec. A special release arm mounted to the camera first closed the central shutter, then opened the focal plane shutter of the Leica IIIf (set to &quot;B&quot;) and then released the exposure with the central shutter. Only 150 lenses with such usually assembly were produced. 58 of them were sold officially and the rest was sold to Leitz employees after being kept in factory for almost 20 years. Both cameras and lenses are in consecutive numbers: #1152135 and #1152136 for lenses, extremely rare. They both come with front lens caps. Please refer to James Lager Vol. II p.57-58 for illustration.', '此對IIIf相機連Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡間快門鏡頭在市場上十分罕見。為提升閃燈同步速度，徠卡設計師Erwin Neurath在此款鏡頭中加入閃光燈同步接口，並增設中央快門及特別的釋放杆，使拍攝時的閃燈同步可提升至1/100及1/200秒。這種特製的鏡間快門鏡頭只生產了150支；當時僅有58支流出市場，另外的92支鏡頭則被保存於工廠長達20年之久，隨後才出售予徠卡廠房的員工。在拍賣會上能呈現一對如此罕見的Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡間快門鏡頭 (#1152135/#1152136)，並且機鏡均是雙連號的機會微乎其微，必定讓收藏家為之驚喜。更多此拍品資料可參閱James Lager Vol. II p.57-58。此對機分別連同鏡頭前蓋，套機成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2188', 'IIIc with Summitar 2/5cm', 'IIIc with Summitar 2/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_17_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_17_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_17_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_17_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_17_5.JPG', '17', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a IIIc grey with Summitar 2/5cm (#584501) in good working order. It comes with front lens cap and leather case.', '此IIIc灰色機身配有Summitar 2/5cm鏡頭 (#584501)，操作正常。連同鏡頭前蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2189', 'IIIf Canada Midland', 'IIIf Canada Midland', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_18_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_18_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_18_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_18_4.JPG', '18', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In total 184,000 pieces of IIIf were produced between 1950 and 1957, only around 5000 units were made in Canada and this camera is one of them. “Midland Ontario” was engraved on top plate. It comes with a Summarit 1.5/5cm (#1420235), made in Canada as well, and front lens cap.', '此拍品最珍貴之處是於加拿大製造；在約十八萬台的IIIf中，只有大約五千台是由加拿大Midland生產，可見其罕有程度。此機機頂上刻有“Midland Ontario”字樣，配有同是加拿大製的Summarit 1.5/5cm鏡頭 (#1420235) 連鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2190', 'IIIf Chrome with Summarit 1.5/5cm', 'IIIf Chrome with Summarit 1.5/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_19_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_19_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_19_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_19_4.JPG', '19', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a IIIf Chrome with Summarit 1.5/5cm lens (#1357525). It comes with lens front cap, in good working order.', '此銀色IIIf 配有螺絲口Summarit 1.5/5cm (#1357525)，鏡身飾皮完好，玻璃通透，成色極新。配有鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2191', 'IIIg with Elmar 2.8/5cm Chrome', 'IIIg with Elmar 2.8/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_20_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_20_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_20_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_20_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_20_5.JPG', '20', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'IIIg was the last screw mount camera manufactured by Leica. Comes with an Elmar 2.8/5cm lens (#1453618), in mint condition.', 'IIIg為徠卡最後一款生產的螺絲口相機；本拍品連同Elmar 2.8/5cm鏡頭 (#1453618)，成色上佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2192', 'Ig with Summitar 2/5cm', 'Ig with Summitar 2/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_21_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_21_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_21_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_21_4.JPG', '21', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This Ig camera comes with a Summitar 2/5cm lens (#981008) with front lens cap.', 'Ig生產於1957-1963年間，此機連同Summitar 2/5cm鏡頭 (#981008) 及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2193', 'Hektor 6.3/2.8cm Chrome', 'Hektor 6.3/2.8cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_22_6.JPG', '22', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the very first wide angle lens of Leica. It comes with keeper, SOOHN hood, 2.8cm TUVOO viewfinder and SUOOQ viewfinder with original red box, and lens front cap; relatively rare in the market.', '這是早期的徠卡廣角鏡頭，是二戰前的版本，配件齊全，連同：SOOHN遮光罩、銀色2.8cm TUVOO取景器、銀色SUOOQ取景器連原裝紅色包裝盒、鏡頭前蓋及膠盅；越過戰爭時代保留至今，市場較為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2194', 'Summaron 5.6/2.8cm Chrome', 'Summaron 5.6/2.8cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_23_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_23_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_23_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_23_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_23_5.JPG', '23', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'This lens used a strict symmetrical design with 6 elements in 4 groups. It comes with a Leitz New York black SOOHN hood, 2.8cm TUVOO viewfinder and both lens cap.', '此款鏡頭以6片4組設計，連同紐約徠卡製的遮光罩SOOHN及銀色2.8cm取景器TUVOO；配有前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2195', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm (The First Version)', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm (The First Version)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_24_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_24_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_24_3.JPG', '24', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the first version of Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm with nine elements, made in Germany. It comes with lens hood (#12501) and rear lens cap, with signs of normal use.', '德國製的第一代Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm九枚玉經典鏡頭，是徠卡最值得收藏的廣角鏡之一。此鏡連遮光罩 (#12501)及後蓋，鏡身有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2196', 'Summaron 2.8/35mm Chrome', 'Summaron 2.8/35mm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_25_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_25_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_25_3.JPG', '25', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Early screw mount lens in 35mm, comes with both lens caps.', '早期的35mm螺絲口鏡頭，人稱「小八枚玉」；配有鏡頭前後蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2197', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_26_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_26_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_26_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_26_4.JPG', '26', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of Rigid Summar lens in nickel finished. It comes with an E. Leitz New York lens hood and both caps.', '此為第一代Summar 2/5cm Rigid鏡頭，鏡身以鎳金屬製; 配有E. Leitz New York遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2198', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_27_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_27_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_27_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_27_4.JPG', '27', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'Rigid Nickel Summar 2/5cm is the first version of Summar from 1933 to 1934, the number produced were quite small. Comes with both lens caps and original Leitz red box which is very rare.', '此款鎳鏡頭是第一代的Summar版，生產年份短，產量少。連同鏡頭前後蓋及非常罕有的原裝徠卡鏡頭盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2199', 'Summar 2/5cm Chrome Tropen Version', 'Summar 2/5cm Chrome Tropen Version', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_28_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_28_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_28_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_28_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_28_5.JPG', '28', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original TROPEN Summar 1:2/5 cm lens. In between the 400.000 serial number range of the Leica lenses, very few series of Summar lenses indicate &quot;Tropen&quot; in the factory records. It is meant that lenses are especially suitable for tropical environments. There are two key-features of the tropical Summar lenses, what concerns their technical standards: First of all, the lenses contain a compound front-element, balsamized of two elements. So in fact, the tropical Summar lenses are of a seven-element design instead of the regular six-element. Second, the tropical Summar lenses have a ball and groove design in the collapsible barrel, similar to the later Summitar lenses. Tropical Summar lenses are extremely rare. Compare VIDOM Nr. 89 (Leica Historica, Germany 2005), page 29. This lens comes with both lens caps and it has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此“TROPEN”Summar，極為罕有且不為人知，是專門為適應熱帶地區的環境而設計。此鏡頭與量產版Summar的最大分別為在鏡頭前端增加多一枚鏡片，為七組鏡片設計﹔另外鏡筒的伸縮部分有明顯的凹槽，此特徵只見於Summitar鏡頭中。有關資料可參閱VIDOM Nr. 89 (Leica Historica, Germany 2005), p 29。此鏡連同前後蓋。拍品經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2200', 'Summitar* 2/5cm Chrome Prototype (THE FIRST ONE)', 'Summitar* 2/5cm Chrome Prototype (THE FIRST ONE)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_29_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_29_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_29_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_29_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_29_5.JPG', '29', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original Summitar* lens. The Summitar* lenses can be considered as the first prototypes of what later turned into the Summicron design. Back in 1950, there were produced 88 examples of the Summitar* with serial numbers 812242-812329. The lens here is the very first one of the series. The asterisk after the lens name (not after the serial number) probably indicates the presence of a radioactive element. The general design of the optical computation was already very similar to the later Summicron. But the LaK9 (the first thorium-oxide free Lanthanium crown glass) of the 1953 Summicron was not yet available by 1950. Typically, the Summitar* lenses stop down to f/22, whereas Summitar as well as later Summicron stop down to f/16 only. This lens comes with front lens cap and keeper. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.&quot;', 'Summitar* 被視為Summicron生產前的的原型版，產於1950年，產量僅有88支，鏡頭編號由812242至812329；此鏡頭是第一支生產的Summitar*，收藏價值極高。名字後的「*」代表玻璃加入了放射性元素。Summitar*與Summicron的不同之處在於Summitar*沒有使用LaK9玻璃及其最小光圈為f/22，除此之外其光學設計光學設計已跟Summicron非常接近。James Lager Vol. II p.45-47記錄了此款鏡頭的資料。此拍品連鏡頭前蓋及膠盅，經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2201', 'Summicron 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summicron 2/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_30_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_30_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_30_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_30_4.JPG', '30', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'According to Leica Pocket Book, this lens was made two years earlier than the official commercial introduction of Summicron 2/5cm. The smallest aperture is f/16, with “meters” shown on the distance ring and gold coating on the elements. It comes with rear lens cap.', '根據Leica Pocket Book資料，此鏡比Summicron 2/5cm正式投產的年份早兩年左右生產，估計為Summitar及Summicron之間的過渡版本。此鏡光圈最小為f/16，玻璃鍍膜偏金黃色，調焦環以“米”作單位；操作正常，連鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2202', 'Summicron 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summicron 2/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_31_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_31_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_31_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_31_4.JPG', '31', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of Summicron 2/5cm lens, 7 elements in 4 groups, with 3 elements of the new LaK9 glass and a thorium glass. It comes with both lens caps.', '第一代Summicron 2/5cm鏡頭，鏡片由7片4組組成，其中三片用上當時新研發的LaK9玻璃，以改善成象質素。此鏡外觀成色上佳，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2203', 'Wollensak Velostigmat Lenses Set', 'Wollensak Velostigmat Lenses Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_32_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_32_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_32_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_32_4.JPG', '32', '', '54,280', null, null, null, null, 'This set comprises of four Wollensak Velostigmat 3.5/50mm lenses, two Wollensak Velostigmat 4.5/90mm lenses and one Wollensak Velostigmat 4.5/127mm lens. All of their optical components were supplied by Wollensak, and mounted by Leitz New York for New York Standard. “E Leitz, Inc. New York” engraved on the name rings of four 3.5/50mm lenses; and Leitz New York logo exists on 4.5/90mm lens. All lenses come with front and rear lens caps.', '此組鏡頭由四支Wollensak Velostigmat 3.5/50mm、兩支Wollensak Velostigmat 4.5/90mm及一支Wollensak Velostigmat 4.5/127mm所組成。此系列鏡頭的光學組件由Wollensak提供，經紐約徠卡組裝，供New York Standard使用。四支3.5/50mm鏡頭上皆刻有「E Leitz, Inc. New York」字樣；而4.5/90mm鏡頭上則刻有紐約徠卡的標誌。七支鏡頭均連同前後蓋。可以齊集此組同系列鏡頭實在十分難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2204', 'Summarex 1.5/8.5cm Chrome', 'Summarex 1.5/8.5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_33_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_33_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_33_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_33_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_33_5.JPG', '33', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with ORQPO hood, SGOOD 8.5cm viewfinder, both lens cap, leather case and original red box.', '此鏡頭配有ORQPO遮光罩及SGOOD 8.5cm取景器，更連同鏡頭前後蓋、皮筒及原裝紅色鏡頭盒。配件齊全，市面較為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2205', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_34_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_34_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_34_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_34_4.JPG', '34', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm was launched in the early 1930’s in small batch of production, with wider apertures for use as a portrait lens before WWII, very rare. It comes with front lens cap, keeper and L39M adapter.', '這是全黑漆的Hektor 1.9/7.3cm鏡頭，它是徠卡在二戰前首款擁有1.9大光圈的人像鏡，色彩豐富，市場較罕見。此鏡配有膠盅、鏡頭前蓋及L39M轉接環。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2206', 'Summicron 2/9cm Chrome Pre-Series', 'Summicron 2/9cm Chrome Pre-Series', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_35_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_35_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_35_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_35_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_35_5.JPG', '35', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original pre-series Summicron 1:2/9cm lens. The SOOZI Summicron 9cm lens was introduced in 1957 and produced by Leitz Canada, beginning with 1.4 Mio serial numbers. Interestingly, a quite similar design of a 9cm Summicron lens with separate lens hood was designed at Leitz Wetzlar already more than three years earlier. The Wetzlar SOOZI lenses appear between serial numbers 1119001 and 1119100 and can be considered as the prototypes of what later turned into the Canadian 9 cm Summicron design. In fact, the lenses are much more different that just the &quot;Wetzlar&quot; or &quot;Midland&quot; engravings: The Wetzlar SOOZI lenses are shorter in length and so suggest even a different optical computation. The diaphragm ring of the Wetzlar lenses has a rotating index to a fixed scale, while the Canadian version has a rotating scale to a fixed index. It is unknown, whether all of the 100 serial numbers were used in fact for produced ensues of the Wetzlar version. In any case, the lenses are extremely rare and exist in screw-mount as well as in M-mount versions. The lens here comes with both caps. Compare Lager Vol. II (lenses) pages 74 and 200. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡頭是Summicron 2/9cm (SOOZI)的原型版。在1957年發佈了由加拿大徠玆生產的2/9cm SOOZI鏡頭。但是此拍品的鏡頭卻早於1954年左右就由德國設計出來，鏡頭序號在1119001至1119100之間。此原型版鏡頭與加拿大版不同之處除了產地 “Wetzlar”及 “Midland”之外，德國原型版的鏡身較短，光學設計及調焦環設計也不同、遮光罩不是內置等。此款鏡頭數量極少，請參考James Lager Vol.II p.74及p.200。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋，已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2207', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_36_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_36_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_36_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_36_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_36_5.JPG', '36', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'Thambar is the only soft-focus lens Leica ever produced. It comes with hood, hood cap, spot filter, rear cap and original red box, in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡唯一的柔焦鏡頭，鏡頭連一塊中間鍍以銀色的反射濾鏡，作用是將中間成象造成柔焦效果。此鏡外觀成色如新，玻璃及反射濾鏡清澈乾淨，如此成色良好的Thambar在市面是絕對罕見，非常值得收藏。含原廠柔焦反射濾鏡，遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭後蓋及原廠紅色包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2208', 'Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm mount converted with 2/5cm', 'Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm mount converted with 2/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_37_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_37_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_37_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_37_4.JPG', '37', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is combined with Hugo Meyer and Leitz. The lens head is Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm and mounted on a Leitz 2/5cm lens. It comes with rear lens cap.', '此鏡由兩個品牌的鏡頭結合而成：鏡頭前端為Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm；改裝在Leitz 2/5cm的鏡筒上。此鏡連同鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2209', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_38_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_38_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_38_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_38_4.JPG', '38', '', '424,800', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare! Not often seen on the market, lens is in black/chrome finished. Original M39 mount rangefinder coupled, comes with an original lens hood, both caps and a rare leather case. Lens shows signs of use.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm鏡頭，具有極其驚人的解析力，一直都是國際市場上收藏家追捧的光學精品。加上此款鏡頭在Hugo Meyer產品系列中極為少見於市場，多年前此拍品價值已比Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm高出多一倍以上。此鏡身是銀/黑，原裝M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機。連原裝遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋及罕見的皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2210', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_39_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_39_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_39_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_39_4.jpg', '39', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare! Not often seen on the market, with original M39 mount rangefinder coupled. It comes with original scarce lens hood in brass, leather hood cap and rear lens cap.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Makro Plasmat 2.7/5cm鏡頭，一直都是國際市場上收藏家追捧的光學精品。其金屬鏡身配以高通光性玻璃及原裝M39卡口，可供徠卡螺絲機使用；加上成色上佳，市場極為難求。此鏡配有罕見的黃銅製遮光罩、皮製的遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2211', 'Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', 'Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_40_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_40_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_40_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_40_4.JPG', '40', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux Paris 2.5/35mm Type R1 Retrofocus lens, one of the most famous portrait lens of Angenieux, with Leica bayonet mount. The lens is in mint condition, with both lens caps and a rare original matching number box.', '此鏡頭可以說是Angenieux 的成名作，它是全球第一支大光圈廣角鏡頭，鏡身為全金屬製造。成像色彩豐富並富有極強立體感，充分展現浪漫的法國情調。此鏡為徠卡螺絲口，成色極佳，連鏡頭前後蓋及罕有的原裝紅色包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2212', 'Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21', 'Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_41_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_41_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_41_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_41_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_41_5.JPG', '41', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21 is one of the most famous standard lens of Angenieux, with six elements in four groups of Double Gaussian lens. This lens is in original M42 mount, very rare. It comes with L/M adapter and both lens caps.', '此為產自法國的頂級電影鏡，型號是S21。鏡頭6片4組的雙高斯設計(Double Gaussian lens)賦予超高的解象力。此鏡是原裝M42卡口，市面罕見; 配有L/M的轉接環及前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2213', 'Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', 'Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_42_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_42_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_42_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_42_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_42_5.JPG', '42', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'P.angenieux 50mm f1.8 type S1 standard lens, first version type S1 for early Alpa Prisma Reflex camera. It comes with rear lens caps and very rare S1 lens hood with cap. Some signs of use are shown.', '此為愛展能的S1系列標準鏡，散景迷人，充滿法式浪漫油畫情懷。此鏡屬於早期產量極少的Alpa Reflex S1版本，配上愛展能深藍色鍍膜﹔已是Leica M39 卡口﹔連同罕見的原裝S1用的遮光罩、遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2214', 'Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', 'Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_43_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_43_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_43_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_43_4.JPG', '43', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an Angenieux lens in Rectaflex mount, comes with both caps. The lens shows few signs of use.', '愛展能是法國的頂級電影鏡品牌，成象散景獨特，極富法國的浪漫風格。此鏡為Rectaflex卡口，連鏡頭前後蓋，有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2215', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_44_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_44_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_44_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_44_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_44_5.JPG', '44', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1 is one of the most famous portrait lens, in original M39 mount, can be used on Leica screw mount camera. It comes with both lens caps.', '本拍品為法國品牌愛展能中的名鏡之一，型號為P1大光圈鏡頭。其對焦距離為5呎，散景迷人，充份展現法國浪漫色調。此鏡是原裝M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機；帶鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2216', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_45_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_45_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_45_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_45_4.JPG', '45', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an Angenieux 1.8/90mm lens in type P1, the famous portrait lens of Angenieux. It comes with both lens caps in M42 mount.', '這是愛展能中相當著名的一支大光圈人像鏡頭，型號為P1。最近對焦距離是5呎，光圈葉數量為12片，散景迷人，有濃厚的法國浪漫色彩。此鏡頭為M42卡口，連鏡頭前後蓋；有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2217', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Chrome', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_46_6.JPG', '46', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Between 1950’s and 1960’s, several kinds of M39 screw mount lens in small batch were produced for Leica by Fujinon. Fujinon 1.2/5cm is one of the rarest one. The lens here comes with UV, both caps and leather case.', '富士在1950年代至1960年代，為徠卡製造了數款M39螺絲口的旁軸鏡頭，它們生產量不多，生產期也不長; 當中以1.2/5cm的產量最為稀少。此鏡配有前後蓋，皮套及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2218', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Black', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_47_6.JPG', '47', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Between 1950’s and 1960’s, several kinds of L39 screw mount lenses were produced by Fujinon, but only a small batch has been produced, especially Fujinon 1.2/5cm. This Fujinon 1.2/5cm in black finish comes with hood in original packing, also with both lens caps.', '富士在1950至1960年代為徠卡製造了數款L39螺絲口的旁軸鏡頭，它們產量不多，生產時期也不長; 當中以Fujinon 1.2/5cm的產量最為稀少。此黑色Fujinon 1.2/5cm鏡頭成象質素出色，配有罕見的遮光罩連原廠包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2219', 'Nikon Nikkor-NC 1.1/5cm', 'Nikon Nikkor-NC 1.1/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_48_6.JPG', '48', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Nikkor-NC 1.1/5cm lens was launched in 1956, small batch has been produced in three different versions, and this M39 mount is the rarest version, probably less than 100 units were made . This lens comes with original 62mm filter, both caps and leather case.', '此款鏡頭是於1956年面世的超大光圈鏡頭，當時分別生產了三個版本: 原裝Nikon接口、外置Nikon接口及此款最為罕見可用於徠卡的M39螺絲口; 當中M39卡口的產量估計不足100枚。此鏡配有原裝62mm濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2220', 'Nikkor-HC 2/5cm', 'Nikkor-HC 2/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_49_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_49_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_49_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_49_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_49_5.JPG', '49', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This was introduced in 1946 along with Nikon’s first rangefinder camera, Nikon 1 , which was a very popular lens for Nikon S series camera. The lens comes with lens front cap and metal case.', '此款鏡頭於1946年連同藝康首款旁軸相機Nikon 1一同推出，是藝康S系列中其中一款最受歡迎的鏡頭。配有鏡頭前蓋及儲存罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2221', 'Voigtlander Nokton 1.5/50mm Chrome', 'Voigtlander Nokton 1.5/50mm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_50_7.JPG', '50', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This was launched in the early 1950’s, only small batch was produced for Leica screw mount camera, very rare. It comes with hood, yellow filter, front lens cap and keeper.', '於1950年代初，德國福倫達生產了小批量供徠卡螺絲口相機使用的Nokton 1.5/50mm，其光學表現極為優異。鏡身為鋼製，結構穩重紮實，是其中一支非常罕有的徠卡螺口鏡頭。此鏡配有遮光罩、黃色濾鏡、鏡頭前蓋及膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2222', 'Zunow 1.1/5cm Chrome', 'Zunow 1.1/5cm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_51_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_51_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_51_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_51_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_51_5.JPG', '51', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first standard lens with aperture f/1.1 made by Zunow Japan in around 1953, approx. 200 pieces were made. The lens is in original M39 mount, comes with M mount adapter and both lens caps.', '此款鏡頭於1950年代初由日本帝國光學出品，是全世界第一支擁有超大光圈的標準鏡頭。此鏡是原裝M39卡口，產量只有200多支，市場較罕見。此鏡帶有徠卡M卡口接環及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2223', 'Fujinon 2/5cm', 'Fujinon 2/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_52_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_52_2.JPG', '52', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Fujinon 2/5cm lens with rare original M39 mount. It comes with an original hood with cap, and rear lens cap.', '這是少數擁有原裝M39卡口的Fujinon 2/5cm鏡頭，配有原裝遮光罩及遮光罩蓋; 另有鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2224', 'Konica Hexanon 1.9/50mm', 'Konica Hexanon 1.9/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_53_6.JPG', '53', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the very early Konica Konishiroku Hexanon 1.9/50mm lens in original M39 mount, only small batch were produced. It comes with lens hood in step-up ring, also the rear lens cap.', '早期的柯尼卡Konishiroku Hexanon 1.9/50mm原裝M39卡口鏡頭，產量不多。連同鏡頭後蓋、遮光罩及遮光罩接環。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2225', 'Hensoldt Wetzlar Iriar 3.5/12.5cm Prototype', 'Hensoldt Wetzlar Iriar 3.5/12.5cm Prototype', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_54_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_54_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_54_3.JPG', '54', '', '401,200', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare German Telephoto lens in RF coupled screw mount for the Hensoldt ISO Reporter camera, a Leica look like camera produced by Hensoldt, Wetzlar in the 1960s. It comes with original front lens cap and rear lens cap. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', 'Hensoldt當年與徠茲同樣位於德國Wetzlar。此公司成立於19世紀，在60年代借鑒徠卡生產了135格式相機 (Leica Copy)。此鏡頭是為Hensoldt Reporter相機生產，配有前後蓋。此拍品已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2226', 'M3 Chrome with Elmar-M 3.5/5cm', 'M3 Chrome with Elmar-M 3.5/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_55_8.JPG', '55', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early M3 with a “Corner” on the front of the top plate in chrome finished; also it has all features of early M3: Double stroke operation, short film advance lever, half-moon stopper on the hot shoe, two circular areas on the cast housing and triangular strap lugs. The camera comes with an Elmar-M 3.5/5cm (#1142793), with front lens cap and hairline scratches on top and base plate.', '這台相機擁有早期M3的特徵，最特別之處為此機機頂蓋快門位置前帶有棱角。另外，此機屬於兩次過片，過片杆相對較短，機頂熱靴位置呈半月型，後背蓋內的菲林糟內有兩個圓點，帶有三角形背帶扣等均是早期M3的特徵。此機連同Elmar-M 3.5/5cm (#1142793) 鏡頭及鏡頭前蓋，機頂及底蓋有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2227', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_56_6.JPG', '56', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a M3 chrome from early batch, with double stroke operation, shorter advance lever, triangular strap lugs and ASA is 200. It comes with body cap.', 'M3是奠定徠卡M系列的機型，此台屬於早期版本，有著早期M3的特徵如 兩次過片、過片杆較短、三角形背帶扣及ASA數字為200等﹔此機連同機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2228', 'M3 Chrome in Consecutive Numbers', 'M3 Chrome in Consecutive Numbers', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_57_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_57_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_57_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_57_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_57_5.JPG', '57', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a pair of early version M3 in consecutive numbers. For serial No. 701179 is in double stroke operation; and the other one was later changed to single stroke operation. Both come with body caps, in good working condition.', '這是市場罕見的早期相連號M3對機。其中M3 (#701179) 的過片杆較短，屬兩次過片；而另一台M3 (#701180) 則是後期改裝版本，有較長的過片杆並屬於單次過片。此對相機均帶有機身蓋，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2229', 'Telyt 3.4/180mm Prototype with M3 Chrome &amp; Visoflex II', 'Telyt 3.4/180mm Prototype with M3 Chrome &amp; Visoflex II', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_58_7.JPG', '58', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Leitz Canada 180mm f/3.4 prototype M lens head for Visoflex use. This rare prototype lens (1 of probably 5 were produced) by Leitz Canada (circa 1968) was a design for the US government. This prototype developed by Dr. Mandler (also the designer Noctilux-M 1/50mm) parallel to the 180mm Elcan R lens, which was eventually produced as 180mm f/3.4 APO-Telyt-R for Leicaflex camera. Dr Mandler also designed the 90mm /1.0 lens for the US government. It also exist a RF coupled version of the 180mm f/3.4 C47 lens with goggles similar as 135mm f/2.8. Extremely rare. This lens comes with M3 chrome (#750377), Visoflex II, OTXBO 4X magnifier and bellow. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', '此原型鏡是加拿大徠茲約於1968年應美國政府的要求而研發，估計只產5支，非常罕見。當時美國政府為此項目投放大量資金。這支原型鏡3.4/180mm是由Dr. Mandler設計，他也是Noctilux f1.0/50mm、Elcan f3.4/180mm及Elcan f1.0/90mm的設計者。此拍品另配有銀色M3機身 (#750377)、Visoflex II、皮腔及OTXBO 4倍放大器。已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2230', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_59_6.JPG', '59', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a M3 chrome in single stroke operation, with self-timer. It comes with body cap.', '這台M3銀色機身屬於單次過片並帶自拍﹔連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2231', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_60_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_60_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_60_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_60_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_60_5.JPG', '60', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a M3 chrome in double stroke operation, with self-timer. It comes with body cap.', '這台M3銀色機身屬於兩次過片，帶自拍; 成色極新，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2232', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_61_7.JPG', '61', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M3 in matte black paint was produced in 1959 and belonged to the first batch of production number 959401 to 959500, with triangular strap lugs. Matte black paint was only used in the first and second batch production of M3. This was then replaced by shiny black paint in the later M3 production. More importantly, M3 in matte black paint with serial number before 1000000 is very rare nowadays. This M3 comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1587441) and front lens cap.', '本黑漆版M3於1959年生產，屬於正式投產的首100台黑漆M3，機身編號由959401至959500，獨特之處是擁有三角形背帶扣 (俗稱佛耳)，珍貴非常。此機上的啞黑漆只供首兩批M3使用，後期版本的M3已改為亮面黑漆；而序號1000000以前的啞黑漆M3現今已極為罕見。此機是原裝啞黑漆，配有Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1587441) 及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2233', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_62_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_62_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_62_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_62_4.JPG', '62', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'This M3 in matte black paint was produced in 1960 and belonged to the second batch of production number #993501 - #993750. Matte black paint was only used in the first two batch production of M3. And the serial number before #1000000 is especially rare nowadays. This M3 is in original matte black paint with body cap and box, and in good working order.', '啞黑漆的M3只在首兩批次上使用，後期的黑漆M3已改用亮面黑漆。此拍品產於1960年，屬M3的第二批次 (#993501 - #993750)，而現存序號在#1000000之前的啞黑漆M3已極為罕見。 本拍品為原裝啞黑漆，機身有使用痕跡，操作流暢，配有機身蓋及包裝盒，是一台極具收藏價值的徠卡M3黑漆相機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2234', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_63_6.JPG', '63', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a M3 in original black paint finish, with lever rewind and self-timer; with significant signs of use and brassing. It comes with body cap.', '此為原裝黑漆M3，撥杆回片帶自拍。機身有明顯使用痕跡，機頂及頂蓋背面有露銅，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2235', 'M3 Chrome with Three Lenses Set', 'M3 Chrome with Three Lenses Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_64_9.JPG', '64', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M3 chrome is in single stroke operation with three lenses: Summicron-M 2.8/35mm goggles lens in chrome (#1947120), Elmar-M 2.8/90mm chrome lens (#2085724) and Elmar-M 4/135mm chrome lens (#1802846). It also comes with meter (#14250), lens filter, IROOA hood with cap for 2.8/35mm lens and hood (#12575N) for 2.8/90mm and 4/135mm lens. The set comes with body cap and both lens caps.', '此套機為M3銀色機身配三支鏡頭，分別是: Summicron-M 2.8/35mm銀色眼鏡版鏡頭 (#1947120)、Elmar-M 2.8/90mm銀色鏡頭 (#2085724)及Elmar-M 4/135mm鏡頭 (#1820846)。另有配件: 測光錶(#14250)、三支鏡頭通用的銀色濾鏡、供2.8/35mm鏡頭使用的IROOA遮光罩連蓋及供2.8/90mm及4/135mm鏡頭使用的遮光罩(#12575N)。套機配有鏡頭前後蓋及機身蓋，如此成色及配件齊全的套機實為罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2236', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_65_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_65_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_65_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_65_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_65_5.JPG', '65', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original M3 in black paint finished, with self-timer and lever rewind. It comes with body cap and with little brassing.', '此機是原裝黑漆M3，帶自拍及撥片回杆。操作功能正常，機身輕微露銅; 連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2237', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_66_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_66_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_66_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_66_4.JPG', '66', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a single stroke operation M3 in chrome finished, with interesting serial number containing special sequence. It comes with body cap and in good working order.', '此M3的機身號碼排列方式整齊有趣，機身屬單次過片，操作正常並連同機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2238', 'MP Chrome', 'MP Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_67_6.jpg', '67', '', '826,000', null, null, null, null, 'Only 311 pieces chrome MP were made from 1956 to 1957. Most of them were custom-made for professional photographers and reporters. The number engraved on the chassis is matching with the serial number “P 199” which is relatively rare. It comes with a Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid lens (#1581344) in same age, front lens cap and leicavit, in mint condition. The same camera was presented by Lars Netopil at the Leica Sharing in Hong Kong.', '早期銀色MP在每個徠卡收藏者的心中皆佔有重要的一席位。銀色MP於1956年開始生產，總產量只有311台，主要為專業攝影師及記者特別訂製。此機芯內刻有與機頂號碼相同的「P 199」，經過半過世紀仍保持原裝狀態，十分難得；Lars Netopil曾於本公司舉辦的徠卡分享會上介紹過此編號「P 199」的相機。配有同期的Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid (#1581344)鏡頭，帶機身蓋及過片器，整體成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2239', 'MP Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'MP Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_9.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_68_10.JPG', '68', '', '4,956,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare Leica MP camera in black paint finish. Very interesting this camera shows an M3 serial number. The top plate is a regular Leica MP top plate. There have been seen rare cases of conversions from Leica M3 into model MP. Usually, those show a patch which closes the former M3 frame counter window on those cameras. Please compare Nakamura \"Leica Collection\" page 42. The fact that here we see a regular Leica MP top plate suggests that Leitz may have prepared this camera as MP on special order, after the official Leica MP production run was finished. This camera was already published in early Leica books such as Gianni Rogliatti \"Leica, the first 70 years\", page 75. with below description: “…believed to have been made to special order, utilizing a serial number allotted to an M2, but complying with the MP specification in all respects.” It comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1587321), front lens cap and MP Leicavit, both in black paint finish. This camera and lens have been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此MP黑漆相機是市場上絕無僅有的特別訂製版：它擁有早期MP的機頂，但卻配 M3系列的機身序號。由M3轉換成MP時，原本M3的膠片讀數窗被取消，資料可參照Nakamura &quot;Leica Collection&quot; P. 4。這是工廠在MP停產後再為特別客人訂製生產的相機，相當罕見。此機曾刊登於多本書籍，包括在80年代Gianni Rogliatti出版的“Leica The First 70 Years”p.75中。拍品連同Summicron-M 2/5cm黑漆鏡頭 (#1587321)，配鏡頭前蓋及MP黑漆Leicavit。拍品經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2240', 'M2 Chrome &quot;Betriebsk&quot;', 'M2 Chrome &quot;Betriebsk&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_69_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_69_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_69_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_69_4.JPG', '69', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 chrome Betriebsk is for factory use only and has never been launched officially. “Betriebsk” engraved on top plate and the serial number is M2-2051. It comes with body cap, without self-timer, show signs of normal use.', '此為徠卡工廠內部測試用M2相機，不帶自拍功能。機頂刻有「Betriebsk」字樣，機身編號為M2-2051，連機身蓋。機身有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2241', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_70_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_70_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_70_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_70_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_70_5.JPG', '70', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 belongs to the first batch production, numbered between 948601 and 949100. It was ranked R7 - Especially Rare in the Leica International Price Guide (from R1 to R10). The camera comes with body cap, without self-timer.', '這是第一批生產的M2黑漆相機，機身編號在948601至949100之間。在徠卡國際價格指南中，黑漆M2被評為R7級，屬較稀有的收藏級別。此機不帶自拍，機身飾皮完好，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2242', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_71_6.JPG', '71', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original M2 in black paint finished with rewind lever but no self-timer, less than 300 units were produced, very rare. It comes with body cap, and shows some signs of use.', '此為原裝M2黑漆機身，產於1960年; 撥杆回片並不帶自拍，產量少於300台，實屬罕有。此機機械性能良好，機頂部分露銅，有使用痕跡; 連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2243', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_72_7.JPG', '72', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The set comes with a warranty card which shows the camera and the lens were delivered together on 1st January 1964. It is very rare to still be kept as original outfit after 50 years. Here is an original M2 in black paint finished, with self-timer and lever rewind. It comes with a black paint Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements lens (#1852193), in red scale, from Germany. This lens is different from others as its bottom ring is in black paint. The camera and the lens come with individual certificate. The set completes with box, front lens cap, paper and filter.', '此套機連原廠保用證，其證實相機和鏡頭為原廠配套，一同在1964年1月1日出廠﹔套機經過50年還能保持原廠配套可謂非常難得，市場罕見。套機包括原裝徠卡黑漆M2 (#1075065)連黑色德國製M 2/35mm八枚玉鏡頭 (#1852193)。M2帶自拍，撥杆回片﹔M 2/35mm鏡頭調焦環為紅字，卡口的外環是黑漆，與其他的黑色八枚玉不同。相機及鏡頭也帶各自的證書﹔連相機盒，鏡頭前蓋及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2244', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_73_6.JPG', '73', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an original M2 black painted with self-timer. It comes with body cap, in good working order and mint condition.', '原裝早期M2黑漆機身，帶自拍功能。操作正常連機身蓋及包裝，無磕碰痕跡，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2245', 'M2 Chrome with Telyt-M 4/200mm', 'M2 Chrome with Telyt-M 4/200mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_74_7.JPG', '74', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a M2 in chrome finished with self-timer, “Bundeseigentum” was engraved on the back. It comes with a Telyt-M 4/200mm (#1830031), 20cm viewfinder and a black painted front lens cap.', '此銀色M2帶自拍功能，機背刻有 「Bundeseigentum」 字樣，意指 “聯邦資產”；配有長焦鏡頭Telyt-M 4/200mm (#1830031)、20cm取景器及黑漆鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2246', 'M2 Chrome “Midland” with Summarit-M 1.5/5cm', 'M2 Chrome “Midland” with Summarit-M 1.5/5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_75_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_75_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_75_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_75_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_75_5.JPG', '75', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare M2 made in Canada. It was ranked R9 (almost unique) in the Leica International Price Guide; as around 1,500 units were made only. The word “M2” engraved on top plate is bigger than those made in Germany, with “Ernst Leitz Canada Limited Midland Ontario” engraved on top plate. It comes with a Summarit-M 1.5/5cm lens (#1419685), which made in Canada as well, and front lens cap.', '此機是極罕有的加拿大產M2，在徠卡國際價格指南 (Leica International Price Guide) 中，其稀有程度達至R9級 (Almost unique)，代表接近獨一無二。加拿大製的M2產量極少，估計只有1500台左右，機頂上刻有 「Ernst Leitz Canada Limited Midland Ontario」字樣；機頂上「M2」的刻字亦比德國版為大。此拍品連同同樣是加拿大生產的Summarit-M 1.5/5cm鏡頭 (#1419685) 及鏡頭前蓋；此鏡的鏡頭前端亦刻有「Midland」字樣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2247', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_76_6.JPG', '76', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is an original M2 black painted with self-timer, comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm (#2031467), front lens cap, with little brassing.', '原裝早期M2黑漆，帶自拍功能；配有Summicron-M 2/50mm (#2031467) 及鏡頭前蓋。機鏡有部分露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2248', 'M4 Black Paint', 'M4 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_77_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_77_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_77_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_77_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_77_5.JPG', '77', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 black paint was produced in 1967 with special serial number. This is from the first batch production; the sign of bulb is same as M3 type. This camera comes with body cap.', '此黑漆版M4的機身序號難得一見，只由 “1”及“8”組成，富有幸運吉祥意味。另外值得一提的是它屬於第一批生產的M4黑漆相機，其機背的閃燈圖案仍採用M3的閃燈式樣，而非後期M4的圖案，十分少有。此機連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2249', 'M4 Mot Black Paint', 'M4 Mot Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_78_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_78_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_78_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_78_4.JPG', '78', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1967 – 1970, motorized M4 was first named as M4M and later M4 Mot, all in black paint finished. It comes with body cap.', 'M4 Mot產於1967至1970年間，是M4的改良版，可加配馬達使用。早期被稱為M4M，後期易名為M4 Mot，所有機身均為黑漆。此機配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2250', 'MDa Mot Chrome', 'MDa Mot Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_79_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_79_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_79_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_79_4.JPG', '79', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a rare MDa camera with coupling for Leitz New York Motor drive, engraved “MDa Mot” on top plate. It was delivered from Leitz New York to Zeiss New York for medical use, with a Zeiss scientific instrument in early 1970’s. It comes with a New York motor drive (#02598) with fixed cord and a blue plug.', '帶有馬達的MDa相機市面非常罕見，此機有別於一般MDa相機，機頂刻有「MDa Mot」，連同於1970年代初生產的紐約徠卡馬達，一同提供予紐約蔡司作科學醫療用途。此拍品配有紐約徠卡製馬達(#02598)、連接線與藍色插頭。非常罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2251', 'M4-2 Black', 'M4-2 Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_80_6.JPG', '80', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a M4-2 in black finished, with “PETER A. MEYER 641.46.106.216” engraved on top plate. It comes with body cap.', '黑色M4-2機身，機頂刻有「PETER A. MEYER 641.46.106.216」字樣，較罕見。此機連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2252', 'M5 Black', 'M5 Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_81_7.JPG', '81', '', '4,720', null, null, null, null, 'A black M5 comes with body cap, in good working order.', '黑色M5機身，有機身蓋，操作功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2253', 'Wax Model of M Camera with M4-P Top Plate', 'Wax Model of M Camera with M4-P Top Plate', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_82_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_82_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_82_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_82_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_82_5.JPG', '82', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Wax models were often produced to assess and determine the aesthetics of a Leica camera and top plates were modelled upon them. This particular example is of a M4-P camera. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', '相機蠟製模型通常是作工廠內部，於設計初期用作評估及測量成品的外觀用﹔本拍品是M型號相機的蠟製模型連同一個M4-P機頂蓋，市場罕見。此拍品已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2254', 'M6 Cut-Away', 'M6 Cut-Away', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_83_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_83_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_83_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_83_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_83_5.JPG', '83', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'The detailed inner structure of M6 can be seen in this cutaway camera. It comes with plastic box.', '經剖切的M6機身，讓每位徠卡迷可以深入了解M6機身的內部結構。此機連同白色膠盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2255', 'MP6 0.72 Black Paint', 'MP6 0.72 Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_84_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_84_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_84_3.JPG', '84', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, '400 sets of MP6 were produced in total. This camera comes with box, papers, strap and body cap, in mint condition.', '總產量只有400台的MP6，分別有黑色及銀色版本，屬於MP量產前的版本。此機成色極佳，取景框明亮；帶包裝證書、相機帶及機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2256', 'M7 Black “Scandinavia Version”', 'M7 Black “Scandinavia Version”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_85_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_85_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_85_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_85_4.JPG', '85', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'ed in 2002 and only 30 units were made. “Camera Scandinavia” engraved on top plate with flags of four Nordic countries printed as well. It comes with body cap, in good working order.', '本拍品為特別版M7，產於2002年只生產了30台，機頂刻有 「Camera Scandinavia」字樣及印有北歐四國的國旗。此機操作正常連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2257', 'M7 and MP “A La Carte” Set', 'M7 and MP “A La Carte” Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_86_9.JPG', '86', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, '3 cameras are included in this A La Carte set: first is the M7 decorated with blue lamb leather in chrome finished, with 0.72 frame line. Second is a black painted MP with lamb leather in red and 0.72 frame line and the last one is a Chrome MP with green lamb leather and 0.58 frame line. Whole set was placed in a Leica wooden case, comes with three body caps, pen, instruction and the sample plates.', '徠卡A La Carte套裝是特別訂造的版本，市面上難以找到同款的設計，收藏價值相對較高。此套裝包括3台相機：有飾以藍色羊皮的銀色M7，配有0.85線框；黑漆MP飾有紅色羊皮，並配上0.72線框；及飾上墨綠色羊皮的銀色MP，配有0.58線框；各具獨特時尚風格。整套相機收藏於精美木盒內，連同款式和飾皮樣板、說明書、原子筆及三個機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2258', 'M8 Black', 'M8 Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_87_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_87_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_87_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_87_4.JPG', '87', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is a unique M8 camera in that it has a special finger rest on the right top hand side of top plate. Further the camera also has a landmark serial number and the speed dial is chrome. This is the only known prototype of Leica M8. The camera shows marks of wear and was used as a shown camera during Photokina. It comes with body cap, three battery cords, battery and charger. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', '此款M8原型版與其他M8 Prototype有所不同: 此機機頂上方有一指柄，以便掌握; 而且快門讀數轉盤為銀色﹔有標誌意義的機身號。此款外觀獨特的M8 Prototype是暫時唯一一台已知的M8原型機。此機曾於Photokina上陳列，有輕微使用痕跡; 帶有機身蓋、電線三條、電池及充電器。此拍品已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2259', 'M9-P Perspex Camera Model', 'M9-P Perspex Camera Model', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_88_7.JPG', '88', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'This top plate is inserted on a commemorate perspex camera shaped block with the following suspended engraving “December 2011 ACM Projektentwicklung and Blackstone entered into joint ownership of Leica Camera AG”. Reputedly 5 pieces were produced to commemorate this event and one such camera is kept in the Leica Park Museum, very rare. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', '這是以有機玻璃製造的M9-P模型，為了紀念黑石集團加入徠卡相機成為戰略投資者而製造，只生產了5只，當中更有一只被存放在徠卡博物館中。模型內刻有 「December 2011 ACM Projektentwicklung and Blackstone entered into joint ownership of Leica Camera AG」。此拍品能在拍賣會上出現機會微乎其微。此拍品已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2260', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_89_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_89_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_89_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_89_4.JPG', '89', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Approximately 350 pieces were made, comes with viewfinder, center filter, rear cap, instruction and box, in mint condition.', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm鏡頭僅生產約350支﹔此鏡連取景器、中灰鏡、說明書、鏡頭後蓋及包裝盒。成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2261', 'Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Chrome Pre-series', 'Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Chrome Pre-series', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_90_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_90_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_90_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_90_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_90_5.JPG', '90', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Only the model name is engraved on name ring, without any serial numbers. It comes with rear lens cap.', '此Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm與正常版本不處之處在於鏡頭前端只刻上型號，而沒有任何編號，較少見。此鏡連同鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2262', 'Leitz Canada rare original Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm', 'Leitz Canada rare original Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_91_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_91_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_91_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_91_4.JPG', '91', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Canada rare original Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm lens. The 21mm Elmarit were introduced at Photokina 1980, together with the Leica M4-P. The very first design had an E49 front filter thread mount, which made the lens looking very similar to the 28mm Elmarit of the time. However, the E49 lens design showed a vignetting problem when a filter was attached. Leitz immediately withdraw the E49 design and changed to E60. Most of the originally produced E49 lenses were converted to E60. We can estimate that only a few dozens of the original E49 design lenses have survived. The lens here comes with scarce original 12537 lens hood, rear lens cap and serrated focus lever. For further information on the lens, please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.15. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '這是罕有的原裝加拿大徠茲Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm鏡頭。在1980年的Photokina徠卡發表朋Elmarit-R 21mm鏡頭及M4-P。開初此鏡口徑為E49，外形與當時的28mm Elmarit相近﹔但很快徠卡就發現此設計有周邊暗角的問題，故立刻回收產品並把鏡頭的口徑改為E60。大部份原裝E49已被更換成E60，相信只有極少數還保留原裝設計。另外，此鏡配備了稀有原裝12537遮光罩，鏡頭後蓋及鋸齒紋調焦按鈕有關此鏡資料，可參閱James Lager Vol.II p.150，但書內僅有文字描述而未能提供圖片，可見此鏡在市場的罕見程度; 另外Lars Netopil亦曾於香港的徠卡分享會上介紹過此鏡頭。拍品經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2263', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_92_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_92_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_92_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_92_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_92_5.JPG', '92', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Only 500 pieces were made in chrome, very rare. It comes with box, leather case, papers and both caps.', '銀色鏡身，產量只有500支，數量稀少。此鏡連同包裝、說明書、皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2264', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_93_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_93_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_93_3.JPG', '93', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Only 500 pieces were made. It comes with both lens caps and 6 bit.', '徠卡M系列三段變焦鏡頭，產量只有500支。此鏡連同前後蓋並帶電子接點，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2265', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_94_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_94_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_94_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_94_4.JPG', '94', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'This is in E55. It comes with both lens caps, box and papers.', '此鏡是E55口徑，包裝證書全齊，連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2266', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_95_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_95_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_95_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_95_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_95_5.JPG', '95', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a steel rim Summilux-M 1.4/35mm lens in chrome, comes with box and both lens caps.', '這是當年產量較少的銀色鋼咀Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鏡頭，配有包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2267', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim &quot;Unusual Black Rim&quot;', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim &quot;Unusual Black Rim&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_96_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_96_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_96_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_96_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_96_5.JPG', '96', '', '472,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original black SR 35 mm Summilux lens of the first version. Particularly rare are the black SR lenses, which carry a black front ring. Only a very few of these lenses have ever been recorded within the 1765XXX serial number range. Black SR lenses with the black front ring are extremely rare. Compare Lager Vol. II (lenses), page 160. It comes with box, both caps and goggles for Leica M3. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '這是一支罕見原裝第一代Summilux-M 1.4/35mm黑色鋼咀鏡頭，其特別之處是通常黑或銀色鋼咀鏡頭的前鋼圈為銀色，但此鏡頭卻擁有與眾不同的黑色鋼圈；鏡身號碼在1765XXX範圍內只有極少數同款的鏡頭﹔在James Lager Vol.II p.160中也有黑色鋼咀(黑鋼圈)，鏡身號碼1765667的介紹。此鏡頭配有包裝及鏡頭前後蓋，帶眼鏡。拍品經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2268', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_97_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_97_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_97_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_97_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_97_5.JPG', '97', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm steel rim in black finished. It comes with rear lens cap and OLLUX hood.', '第一代黑色鋼咀，產量只有數十支，極為珍貴。此鏡連同鏡頭後蓋及OLLUX遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2269', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_98_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_98_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_98_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_98_4.JPG', '98', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'Nine elements in five groups and two of them are ASPH, around 2,000 units were made. It comes with box, leather case, rear lens cap, hood (#12587) with cap.', '九片五組設計，其中兩片為非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，產量2,000支左右。此鏡頭連包裝盒、皮套、鏡頭後蓋及遮光罩 (#12587) 連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2270', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_99_7.JPG', '99', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Chrome Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH lenses have already discontinued. It comes with leather case, rear lens cap, hood (#12589) with cap.', '此款銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH鏡頭已經停產；其非球面玻璃鏡頭採用黃銅製作鏡身。連同皮套、鏡頭後蓋及遮光罩 (#12589) 連蓋。玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2271', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_100_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_100_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_100_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_100_4.JPG', '99', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'This is the current version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH lens (#11663) in brand new condition, with all papers and packing.', '現行版的Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH鏡頭 (#11663)，全新未經使用，包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2272', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black Paint (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black Paint (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_101_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_101_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_101_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_101_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_101_5.JPG', '101', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an early version of Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements in red scale from Germany, only small batch was produced. The lens is in raw brass mount, the lens flange is in black paint finished. It comes with box, both caps and goggles.', '這是極早期的德國製黑色眼鏡版八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字。最特別之處是此鏡的卡口為黃銅，而卡口外圈則是黑漆；因後期的版本已改為鍍銀，黑漆版本於市場並不常見。此鏡配有包裝盒、前後蓋及帶眼鏡，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2273', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_102_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_102_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_102_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_102_4.JPG', '102', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version Summicron-M 2/35mm 8 elements lens in red scale with goggles, made in Canada, and the rear ring is brass. It comes with rear lens cap and with brassing on focusing knob.', '較早期的加拿大製黑色眼鏡版八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，鏡頭後卡口為黃銅，產量十分稀少。此鏡的調焦按鈕有輕微掉漆；連同鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2274', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_103_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_103_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_103_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_103_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_103_5.JPG', '103', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version Summicron-M 2/35mm black in 8 elements, made in Canada. It comes with both lens caps, in good working order.', '較早期的加拿大製黑色八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，調焦暢順; 配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2275', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_104_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_104_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_104_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_104_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_104_5.JPG', '104', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early Summicron-M 2/35mm 8 elements in red scale. This is a highly collectable piece from a small batch of production from Germany, with both brass focusing knob and black painted lens flange. It comes with filter and both lens caps.', '早期的黑色八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，當中德國製的產量極少。更特別的是此鏡頭的卡口外圈是黑漆，而後期版本則已經改為鍍銀。此鏡的調焦環有輕微露銅，玻璃清澈﹔配有濾鏡及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2276', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_105_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_105_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_105_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_105_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_105_5.JPG', '105', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a 8 elements lens made of high quality fluorite lens from Germany. It comes with both lens caps.', '此鏡是產於德國的八枚玉鏡頭，由高質素的螢石玻璃所製成; 連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2277', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_106_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_106_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_106_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_106_4.JPG', '106', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was produced in Germany, in small quantity only. The lens comes with both caps, in good condition.', '此鏡為德國製的Summicron-M 2/35mm黑色八枚玉鏡頭，產量較稀少。鏡頭調焦暢順，品相良好；連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2278', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH “LHSA Special Edition”', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH “LHSA Special Edition”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_107_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_107_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_107_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_107_4.JPG', '107', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH lens comes from the MP LHSA Hammertone edition. “LHSA” and year “1968-2003” were engraved on barrel, with 6 Bit. Beside the front and rear lens caps, it comes with a hood in hammertone as well. Lens is in good working order with clear glass.', '此鏡是MP LHSA Hammertone特別版所配備的Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH鏡頭，其外型為仿八枚玉造型，鏡身有「LHSA」及「1968-2003」字樣; 鏡頭帶6 Bit。除了鏡頭前後蓋外，此鏡還配有Hammertone遮光罩; 且玻璃通透，調焦暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2279', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH “Millennium” Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH “Millennium” Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_108_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_108_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_108_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_108_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_108_5.JPG', '108', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a black painted version of Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH for M6 “Millennium”, small batch was produced. It comes with leather case, hood (#12452) and both lens caps.', '這是黑漆M6千禧年版所配備的黑漆鏡頭，產量不多。此鏡配有皮套、遮光罩 (#12452) 及前後蓋，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2280', 'Summaron-M 3.5/3.5cm Chrome Set', 'Summaron-M 3.5/3.5cm Chrome Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_109_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_109_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_109_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_109_4.JPG', '109', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'The serial numbers of this set are very similar and both are end with lucky number “8”, which is very rare in the market. Both lenses come with front and rear lens caps.', '此對銀色Summaron-M 3.5/3.5cm鏡頭的編號驟眼看似是相同，當中只差一個數字; 而它們的號碼亦非常吉祥並整齊，市場罕見。兩支鏡頭均連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2281', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_110_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_110_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_110_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_110_4.JPG', '110', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This is the current version of Noctilux-M lens, comes with full packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '徠卡最新型的最大光圈Noctilux-M鏡頭，質素極佳，散景迷人。此鏡全新未經使用，包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2282', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_111_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_111_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_111_3.JPG', '111', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is the third version of Noctilux-M 1/50mm lens in E60. It comes with box, papers, both lens caps and hood (#12544).', '第三代的Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E60口徑，連包裝證書、鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩(#12544)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2283', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm Black', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_112_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_112_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_112_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_112_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_112_5.JPG', '112', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'Around 1,500 pieces were made, very rare. It comes with box, keeper, front lens cap, hood (#12503) and filter.', '此鏡為早期的Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm鏡頭，產量少，大約只有1,500支。其中兩片鏡片為手磨非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，成象質素令人一見難忘。此鏡連同包裝盒、膠盅、鏡頭前蓋、遮光罩 (#12503) 及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2284', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_113_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_113_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_113_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_113_4.JPG', '113', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in black paint finished, with raw brass mount, extremely rare. It comes with both lens caps.', '此為極度罕見的第一代Summilux-M 1.4/50mm黑漆鏡頭，鏡頭底部的接口以黃銅製造，十分稀有。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2285', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Mixed Finish', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Mixed Finish', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_114_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_114_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_114_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_114_4.JPG', '114', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original finish mix lens of the 50mm Summilux. Lens mount in mixed finish, combined from black paint and silver chrome. A mysterious field are those &quot;finish-mix&quot; lenses, which sometimes appear, but are of unknown meaning. In fact, already in the Wilhelm Albert book of 1962, finish-mix lenses appear on factory-internal photographs of the Elmarit 2.8/90 (I) and Telyt 4.5/200 prototypes.  It comes with both lens caps and hood. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此拍品是Summilux 50mm黑銀混合版鏡頭，鏡身以黑漆及銀色組成﹔這款混合版鏡頭並不常見，到現時為止其出現原因仍然不明。Wilhelm Albert在他1962年的著作中亦提及到相似混合版鏡頭Elmarit 2.8/90 (I) 及Telyt 4.5/200 prototypes曾出現於工廠內部照片。拍品經由Lars Netopil鑑定。連同鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩(#12521G)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2286', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_115_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_115_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_115_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_115_4.JPG', '115', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'The second version of Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in chrome finished, with clear glass, UV and both lens cap.', '第二代Summilux-M 1.4/50mm銀色鏡頭，玻璃通透; 連濾鏡及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2287', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_116_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_116_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_116_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_116_4.JPG', '116', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a black painted Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens with signs of use. Comes with keeper.', '較後期的黑漆鏡頭，成色優良，調焦暢順; 連同膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2288', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_117_6.jpg', '117', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'The word “Leitz-Eigentum” is engraved on the barrel which is different from the others. This lens comes with keeper, in good working order. Its rarity has greatly increased its collector’s value.', '此鏡最特別之處為鏡身上刻有「Leitz-Eigentum」字樣，表示屬徠卡所有﹔擁有此特徵的同款鏡頭，相信為數不多。此鏡連同膠盅，調焦暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2289', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_118_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_118_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_118_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_118_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_118_5.JPG', '118', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid lens in black paint finished, with raw brass mount, very rare. It comes with keeper and front lens cap. Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p. 167 for further illustration.', '此為德國製的Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid黑漆鏡頭，鏡身分別以黃銅及鎂合金製造; 鏡頭後卡口為黃銅，十分稀有。此鏡連膠盅及鏡頭前蓋，在James Lager Vol.II p.167亦有介紹同款鏡頭。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2290', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_119_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_119_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_119_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_119_4.JPG', '119', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Black Paint single scale rigid lens was made in Germany, raw brass at the rear of the lens. There is a same version lens with its serial number close to this lens illustrated in James Larger Vol.II p.167. It comes with both lens caps. Lens shows significant signs of use and brassing.', '德國製的Summicron-M 2/5cm黑漆版鏡頭，為Rigid版本，鏡身分別用上黃銅及鎂合金兩種物料所造，鏡頭後卡口為黃銅，較為稀有。在James Lager Vol. II p.167有與此鏡頭號相近的同款鏡頭介紹。此鏡連前後蓋，鏡身有明顯使用痕跡，調焦環露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2291', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Pre-Series', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Pre-Series', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_120_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_120_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_120_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_120_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_120_5.JPG', '120', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare Summicron-M 2/50mm lens with Rigid focusing ring but no knob, only small batch was produced in short period. No serial number engraved. It comes with keeper and front lens cap.', '這是Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid後的另一個版本，調焦環依然採用Rigid版本，但已取消撥杆。此外型的鏡頭生產期極短，加上此鏡不帶鏡頭編號，市面極為罕見。本拍品連同膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2292', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Dummy in Consecutive Numbers', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Dummy in Consecutive Numbers', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_121_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_121_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_121_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_121_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_121_5.JPG', '121', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the 4th version of Summicron-M 2/50mm dummy lens set with consecutive numbers, relatively rare. Both come with box.', '第四代Summicron-M 2/50mm的Dummy鏡頭，擁有相連的鏡頭號碼，而且連同包裝盒，市場上並不常見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2293', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_122_8.JPG', '122', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was launched to commemorate the 50th anniversary of Summicron, only 500 units were made. This set comes with box, all papers, leather case, presentation box, hood (#12585), hood cap and both lens caps.', '本拍品是為了紀念Summicron面世50週年而生產的紀念版鏡頭，限量500支。其外形仿照50年代的第二代Summicron Rigid鏡頭，但內裡的玻璃則採用現代Summicron鏡頭的光學設計與技術結合而成，極為獨特。此鏡頭配有包裝盒、證書、皮筒、內盒、遮光罩(#12585)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2294', 'Elmar-M 2.8/50mm Black &amp; Chrome Set', 'Elmar-M 2.8/50mm Black &amp; Chrome Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_123_7.JPG', '123', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Elmar-M 2.8/50mm lenses were discontinued in 2007. This set includes a black and a chrome one. Both lenses come with box, instruction, certificate, hood, front and rear lens caps.', '此款鏡頭已於2007年停產; 而本拍品的兩支鏡頭均連同包裝、說明書、證書、前後蓋及遮光罩，操作順滑且品相優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2295', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_124_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_124_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_124_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_124_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_124_5.JPG', '124', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/75mm lens made in Canada, with clean glass. It comes with box, certificate, hood (#12539) and both lens caps.', '加拿大生產的第一代Summilux-M 1.4/75mm鏡頭，玻璃通透。連同包裝證書、遮光罩 (#12539) 及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2296', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_125_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_125_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_125_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_125_4.JPG', '125', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version Summicron-M 2/90mm lens with built-in hood, made in Canada. Comes with both lens caps and box, with slight signs of use.', '這是第一代的Summicron-M 2/90mm鏡頭，產自加拿大，內置遮光罩。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋及包裝盒; 鏡身有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2297', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Black', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Black', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_126_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_126_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_126_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_126_4.JPG', '126', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm lens, with keeper and front lens cap. With clear glass and in good working condition.', '本拍品為第一代Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm鏡頭，玻璃通透，調焦順暢;連同膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2298', 'Elmar-M 4/9cm Chrome Set', 'Elmar-M 4/9cm Chrome Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_127_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_127_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_127_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_127_4.JPG', '127', '', '4,840', null, null, null, null, 'Here are the first version of Elmar-M 4/9cm lenses in chrome finished, with collapsible lens head. Both come with front and rear lens caps, with signs of normal use.', '此對銀色鏡頭均是第一代的Elmar-M 4/9cm鏡頭，鏡身可以伸縮。兩支鏡頭均連鏡頭前後蓋，有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2299', 'Leicina Macro-Cinegon 1.8/10mm Set', 'Leicina Macro-Cinegon 1.8/10mm Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_128_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_128_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_128_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_128_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_128_5.JPG', '128', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Leicina Macro-Cinegon 1.8/10mm lens is the M mount lens originally for Super 8 camera. The lenses were made in Germany, both come with rear caps. For #2296002 comes with hood, and the other one comes with front cap.', '此對是徠卡的電影鏡，原用於Super 8相機上。兩支鏡頭的調焦環略有不同，但均於德國製造，M卡口，配有鏡頭後蓋。編號 #2296002配有遮光罩; 而另一支則連鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2300', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_129_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_129_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_129_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_129_4.JPG', '129', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the first series of Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm lens, with some signs of use. It comes with rear lens cap and non-detachable spectacle viewfinder.', '這是早期Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm鏡頭，有使用痕跡。連同鏡頭後蓋及眼鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2301', 'IIIf Black Paint -“Swedish Military”', 'IIIf Black Paint -“Swedish Military”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_130_7.JPG', '130', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'This IIIf was specially made for the Swedish national army in 1956. It can withstand very extreme weather conditions in Sweden and only 100 units were produced, numbered 822901-823000. The camera and lens are original, complete with matching black paint Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1427142), hood and front lens cap.', '1950年IIIf正式面世，全球其中一支歷史最悠久的常備軍「瑞典國軍」(Swedish Army) 於1956年特別向德國徠卡下訂100台黑漆版IIIf，供軍隊在嚴冬環境下使用，生產批號由822901-823000。此機身及鏡頭均為原裝，連Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1427142)、遮光罩及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2302', 'M3 Olive &quot;Bundeseigentum&quot; Military Camera Set', 'M3 Olive &quot;Bundeseigentum&quot; Military Camera Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_9.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_131_10.JPG', '131', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'M3 Bundeseigentum Olive finishing produced for German military, total 144 units were made. This camera is the third one from the first batch (#910501-910600). Camera engraved “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5418” on the rear of the top plate. The set includes a Elmar 3.5/5cm chrome (#1335699) with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5419” engraved, comes with front cap and leather case; Hektor 4.5/13.5cm (#1509666) with “Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625” engraved, completes with leather case and both caps; also a Summicron 2.8/35mm (#2050540) with “6760-12-130-0901” engraved and comes with leather case and front cap. Lastly, this set comes with a meter (#97537) with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608” engraved, very rare.', '此拍品名稱中的Bundeseigentum是指「聯邦資產」。根據記錄，此款相機在1957至1968年間生產，此機第一批次僅生產100台機身號為910501至910600，此機是第一批次中的的第三台。此機機頂背刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5418」字樣，套機連同3支鏡頭，分別是銀色Elmar-M 3.5/5cm (#1335699)，鏡身刻有「Bundeseigentum12-121-5419」，帶前蓋及相機皮套；Hektor-M 4.5/13.5cm (#1509666)，鏡身刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625」，連皮套及前後蓋；Summicron-M 2.8/35mm (#2050540)，刻有「6760-12-130-0901」，配有皮套及前蓋。另配備的測光錶 (#97537) 則刻上「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2303', 'IIIcK Grey', 'IIIcK Grey', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_132_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_132_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_132_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_132_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_132_5.JPG', '132', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a IIIck made in Germany for German Air Force. The camera body and leather are both in grey, and with letter “K” engraved at the end of the serial number. It comes with body cap, and body shows some signs of use.', '此機的機身及相機飾皮均是灰色，序號後面刻有「K」 字，代表是供德國空軍使用的機型。相機機頂及底蓋有部分露銅，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2304', 'M1 Olive “Bundeseigentum” Military Camera Set', 'M1 Olive “Bundeseigentum” Military Camera Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_133_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_133_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_133_3.JPG', '133', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Only 208 units M1 Olive finishing was produced in three batches for German Army and this one came from the first batch (#950451 - #980500). “Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739” engraved on the rear of the top plate and “5+13.5” on the viewfinder frame. The top plate like MP is used on this camera and it comes with box and instruction. For this set, it also comes with a Hektor 4.5/135mm lens (#1718464); “Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625” is engraved, comes with both caps, UV and leather case. Another lens is Elmar 3.5/5cm lens (#1335761) with UV, “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5419” engraved on barrel. Moreover, meter (#97170) with case and “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608” engraved; Leica Meter MC booster cell with case and ITOOY hood with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529” engraved are included as well.', 'M1 Olive是徠卡為德國軍隊生產的相機，分三個批次，總產量僅208台，而此拍品屬於第一批次 (#950451 - #980500)。此機採用與MP相同的頂蓋，機頂背刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739」字樣，取景框刻有「5+13.5」字樣；帶包裝說明書。<br />\r\n此套機外連同以下鏡頭及配件，分別是：Hektor 4.5/135mm (#1718464) 鏡頭，鏡身刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625」，配鏡頭前後蓋、濾鏡及皮筒。另一支鏡頭為Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1335761)，刻有「Bundeseigentum12-121-5419」及連同濾鏡。配件包括一個測光錶 (#97170) 及測光增強片，兩者都帶皮套；在測光錶上刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608」字樣；最後的ITOOY遮光罩上則刻上「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529」。整套相機成色上佳，配件齊備，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2305', 'M4 Olive “Bundeswehr”', 'M4 Olive “Bundeswehr”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_134_9.JPG', '134', '', '3,304,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original Leica M4 &quot;Bundeswehr&quot; olive paint. After Leica M3 and M1 cameras, the olive Leica M4 was the last Leica camera model delivered to the German Military (Bundeswehr). It is one of the rarest Leica M versions with only 31 examples produced, serial numbers 1.266.101 to 1.266.131. The camera here is number twelve of the batch and in entirely original condition. It comes complete with matching Elmar 2.8/50 lens Nr. 2.326.845, engraved &quot;Y&quot;. The &quot;Y&quot; stands for Bundeswehr. Also included are a Leicameter MR in chrome with golden eagle sticker &quot;BWB 1482&quot; in olive green leather case, olive M4 ERV stamped &quot;BWB 1482&quot; and documents about the Leica M4, issued by the Bundeswehr. An earlier Leitz outfit case in olive is also included. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '繼M3及M1之後，M4 Olive是最後一款徠卡為西德國防軍生產的機種，是最珍貴的一款M軍機。僅有31台，機身號由1.266.101至1.266.131。本拍品是第12台，能經歷戰火洗禮後仍保存至今且擁有完全原裝且上佳成色，是極為罕見。此機於1971年1月28日付運到西德，機上刻有「Bundeswehr」字樣，相機飾皮由整塊綠色飾皮製成，有別於其他Olive是後塗綠色﹔配有銀色Elmar-M 2.8/50mm鏡頭 (#2326845)及鏡頭前蓋，鏡身刻字「Y」代表西德國防軍。相機附帶的皮套內印有「BWB 1482」及德軍徽號。整套機更連同出廠記錄、皮箱及測光錶: 測光錶刻有「Metrawatt AG Nurnberg」字樣並貼有「BWB 1482」與德軍徽號的貼紙，測光錶附有皮套及包裝盒。此機經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2306', 'KE-7A &quot;US Army&quot;', 'KE-7A &quot;US Army&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_135_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_135_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_135_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_135_4.JPG', '135', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leica KE-7A produced in 1972, only 505 units were made and 460 units for U.S. Military. The Military number &quot;FSN 6720-165-7115&quot; and contract number &quot;CONT F42600-71-C-2429US&quot; were engraved at the back of the camera. It comes with Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0395) which was specially made for the U.S. Military with ultra-high resolution. It completes with box, strap, cable release, body cap, both lens caps and hood with cap.', '徠卡的KE-7A產於1972年，產量只有505部，而屬於美國軍用版本的有460部。由於供軍方使用，此機為軍用版本。機背上分別刻有軍用編號及合約編號，號碼分別為「FSN 6720-165-7115」及「CONT F42600-71-C-2429US」。此套機配以Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0395)，此鏡是徠卡為美軍特製的，只有4枚鏡片達至超高解像度。另配有包裝盒、相機帶、快門線、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2307', 'Elcan-M 2/50mm from KE-7A Set', 'Elcan-M 2/50mm from KE-7A Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_136_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_136_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_136_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_136_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_136_5.JPG', '136', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'The Elcan-M 2/50mm lenses were specially ordered with KE-7A by US military; only 505 sets were made including the civilian version. The lens was made in Canada, with 4 elements in 4 groups. It comes with both lens caps, relatively rare.', '此Elcan-M 2/50mm是徠卡為美國軍隊所特別研發，用以配備KE-7A相機的鏡頭，連同民用版在內，產量只有505支。產於加拿大，鏡頭採用4片4組設計，擁有超高解像度。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋，市場較罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2308', 'Elcan 1.8/57mm', 'Elcan 1.8/57mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_137_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_137_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_137_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_137_4.JPG', '137', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare Elcan 1.8/57mm lens by Leica, probably for industry use and only two were made. It comes with rear lens cap in red.', '這是非常罕見的鏡頭，估計提供予工業使用，有說此款鏡頭只製造過兩支。此鏡連紅色鏡頭底蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2309', 'Elcan 2.8/6 inch', 'Elcan 2.8/6 inch', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_138_6.JPG', '138', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was launched in around 1965 for US Air Force. This was originally held in place in a complex mount which fitted it to a Vinten aerial camera KE-28B. It comes with lens board, rear mount, UV, yellow filters and front lens cap.', '此鏡於1965年左右推出，是為美國空軍所製造，適用於中畫幅的KE-28B相機上。此鏡成色上佳，屬於市面罕見的徠卡軍用鏡頭。此拍品連同接環、鏡頭底板、黃色濾鏡、透明濾鏡及前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2310', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_139_6.JPG', '139', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'In the early 1970s, Leitz of Midland Canada has specially produced 54 units of Elcan-R 3.4/180mm for the US Military during the Vietnam War. This lens has not been officially launched. It comes with both lens caps and filter carrier.', '此款鏡頭是徠茲加拿大工廠 (Leitz of Midland Canada)為美軍於1970年的越戰所生產的長焦鏡。此款鏡頭共生產五十多支，分三批交付美軍。此款鏡頭從未對外公佈，相信後期的R 3.4/180mm APO-TELYT均以此鏡為藍本，故也被稱為R 3.4/180mm APO-TELY Prototype。此鏡身上有303-0002字樣，鏡頭配有前後蓋及濾鏡接環。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2311', 'Leitz Aviodix 10x50', 'Leitz Aviodix 10x50', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_140_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_140_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_140_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_140_4.JPG', '140', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'The Aviodix 10x50 was launched in 1911 for German military. It is made of brass and adopted Porro II concept; with cast body and prism drum as well. This lot comes with a binocular booklet.', '此款望遠鏡約於1911年研發予德國軍隊使用，鏡筒以實心黃銅鑄造，採用了Porro II作設計藍本，並配上鑄模機身棱鏡股。其堅固耐用及優質的光學設計，使它可由一戰保存至今，跨越戰爭年代的百年望遠鏡，異常珍貴。此拍品連同一本徠卡出版的望遠鏡的產品小冊子。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2312', 'Leica Military Hood for Elmar 5cm', 'Leica Military Hood for Elmar 5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_141_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_141_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_141_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_141_4.JPG', '141', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an Elmar 5cm lens hood (#FISON) for military use, engraved with “6760-12-121-5529 Bundeseigentum”. Lens hood shows slight signs of use.', '此為Elmar 5cm遮光罩 (#FISON) 的軍用版本，刻有軍用編號「6760-12-121-5529 Bundeseigentum」，有輕微使用痕跡，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2313', 'Leica Military Hood for Elmar 5cm', 'Leica Military Hood for Elmar 5cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_142_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_142_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_142_3.JPG', '142', '', '4,130', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an ITOOY lens hood with early thick base for Elmar 5cm lens, with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529” engraved, relatively rare.', '此款Elmar 5cm鏡頭用的遮光罩 (#ITOOY)，刻有軍用編號「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529」，較罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2314', 'M4-P “70 Years” Chrome Outfit', 'M4-P “70 Years” Chrome Outfit', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_143_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_143_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_143_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_143_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_143_5.JPG', '143', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 70th years of the first 135mm camera produced in 1913, M4-P “70 Years” was launched. “Leica 1913 – 1983” engraved at the back of the camera and the winder. The commemorative number of this camera is I058. The winder (#15488) comes with packing, certificate and connection cable. The camera comes with packing, certificate, body cap and strap.', '此套機是為慶祝第一台135相機面世70週年而生產，紀念號為I058，相機機背刻有「Leica 1913 – 1983」字樣，配有快速過片器 (#15488) 及電源線。機身及過片器均配有原包裝證書；機身配有相機蓋及相機帶，整體成色近乎全新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2315', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_144_7.JPG', '144', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th Anniversary of the sultan’s accession to the throne on 1st October 1992, the royal family of Brunei ordered 350 sets of 24 carat gold-plated Leica M6 Sambutan Jubli Perak. The national totem of Sultan engraved on the top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak” engraved at the back. The camera comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in 24 carat gold-plated (#3653527), engraved “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92”. The commemorative number is HB-071. This set comes with wooden case and front lens cap.', '1992年10月1日，汶萊國王登基25週年，汶萊皇室為此向徠卡訂製了350台24K鍍金的M6 連Summilux-M 1.4/50mm套機作為紀念及饋贈賓客，從未對外公開發售。紀念機的紀念號碼由HB-001開始，此拍品的紀念號為HB-071。M6機頂上刻有汶萊的國徽，機背刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak」字樣，彰顯皇室尊貴地位。此套機連24K鍍金的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#3653527)，鏡頭前刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92」的字樣，連木盒及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2316', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_145_8.JPG', '145', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th Anniversary of the sultan’s accession to the throne on 1st October 1992, the royal family of Brunei ordered 350 sets of 24 carat gold-plated Leica M6 Sambutan Jubli Perak. The national totem of Sultan engraved on the top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak” engraved at the back. The camera is decorated with black leather and comes with a Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in 24 carat gold-plated (#3655761), engraved “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92”. The commemorative number is HB-303. This set comes with box and papers, wooden box, hood, body cap, lens rear cap and strap.', '為慶祝汶萊國王於1992年10月1日登基25週年，汶萊皇室為此向徠卡訂製了350台24K 鍍金的M6 連Summilux-M 1.4/50mm套機作為紀念及饋贈賓客，從未對外公開發售。紀念機的紀念號碼由 HB-001開始，M6機頂上刻有汶萊的國徽，機背刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak」字樣；機身配有黑色皮革，奢華雅緻並重，彰顯皇室尊貴地位。此拍品的紀念號為相當好意頭的HB-303。此套機連24K鍍金的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#3655761)，鏡頭前刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92」的字樣，連包裝證書、木盒、遮光罩、機身蓋、鏡頭後蓋及相機帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2317', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_146_9.JPG', '146', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th anniversary of accession the throne of Sultan of Brunei, the royal family of Brunei ordered the special limited edition in total 250 sets from Leica in 1995, which never release to market for sale. The special number of this set is HB-099, with symbol of Brunei on top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak” engraved at the back and “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92” engraved on name ring of the lens. The camera is decorated with grey lizard skin. It comes with a Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3726487), box, papers, wooden presentation box, body cap, both lens caps and strap.', '為慶祝汶萊國王登基25周年，汶萊皇室特別向德國徠卡訂製了M6鉑金紀念機：此款紀念機並不對外發行，只供汶萊國王饋贈特別貴賓用，限量250套。此機紀念號為吉祥的HB-099，機頂刻有兩個汶萊皇室徽章，分別為黑色及紅色，機背刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak」而鏡頭上則刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92」字樣，鍍上鉑金的機身飾以灰色蜥蝪皮，設計盡顯尊貴。此機連同Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鉑金鏡頭 (#3726487)，連包裝證書、木盒、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及相機帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2318', 'Leica M6 Royal Wedding Edition in Consecutive Numbers', 'Leica M6 Royal Wedding Edition in Consecutive Numbers', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_147_8.JPG', '147', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'Leica has specially launched 200 units of commemorative M6 cameras in 1995 to celebrate the wedding of Prince Joachim of Denmark. The royal crest, wedding date“18.11.1995”, serial number 082/200 and 083/200 were engraved on the top plate. They come with Summicron-M 2/35mm chrome lens (#3641196) and (#3641238); also with box and papers, wooden case, hood (#12524), body cap, both lens caps and camera strap.', '此對相連號套機是慶祝丹麥王子大婚而特別推出的，只產200台。機頂上除刻有 大婚日期 「18.11.1995」 及丹麥皇室徽章外，更各刻有「082/200」及「083/200」的相連紀念號。機身覆以駝鳥皮，彰顯尊貴。此拍品各配有Summicron-M 2/35mm鏡頭 (#3641196)及(#3641238)，兩套相機均連同包裝證書、說明書、木盒、遮光罩(#12524)、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及相機帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2319', 'M6J with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm', 'M6J with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_148_6.JPG', '148', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'Production was only 1,640 units, 40 cameras for each year of the 40 years of M production, “40 Jahre LEICA M 1954-1994” engraved on the top plate. The camera comes with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm which has the same number as the camera body. This unit comes with box, instruction, wooden case, leather case, strap and front lens cap.', '為紀念M系列推出40週年，徠卡於1994年推出1,640套M6J連Elmar-M 2.8/50mm套機。機頂刻有「40 Jahre LEICA M 1954-1994」字樣。此相機及鏡頭的紀念號均是1986-15，連包裝、說明書、木盒、皮套、相機帶及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2320', 'Leica M6 “Royal Photographic Society”', 'Leica M6 “Royal Photographic Society”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_149_7.JPG', '149', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In order to commemorate 100 years of the Royal Photographic Society of Great Britain, 100 camera sets were manufactured in 1994. The special number of this set is 095/100, with crest engraved on top plate. This set comes with a wooden presentation box and a Summicron-M 2/50mm lens, “RPS Royal; Centenary 1994” is engraved on the name ring and on the back of the camera.', '為慶祝英國皇家攝影學會成立100週年，徠卡於1994年特意推出100套特別版套機。此機紀念號為095/100，機頂上刻有徽章; 套機配有Summicron-M 2/50mm鏡頭，鏡頭及機背均刻有 “RPS Royal; Centenary 1994” 字樣，連同木盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2321', 'M6 LEICA HISTORICA e.V Deutschland edition', 'M6 LEICA HISTORICA e.V Deutschland edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_150_9.JPG', '150', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a special M6 launched in 1995 for 20th Anniversary of the establishment of LEICA HISTORICA in Wetzlar. Body decorated with turquoise blue leather; with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (#3729059) and “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-1995” engraved on top plate and barrel as well. The commemorative number of this set is 53/150. Besides, this set also included a Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm lens (#3891073) in chrome finished and with “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-2000” engraved, only 75 units were made in 2000; a Leicavit (35/40) which only 40 units were made, with “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-2005” engraved. Whole set comes with box and papers.', '這是為紀念德國徠卡歷史協會 (LEICA Historica)成立20週年而推出的特別版M6，限量150台。機身覆以海藍色飾皮，連同Summicron-M 2/50mm鏡頭 (#3729059); 機頂刻有 “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-1995” 字樣，紀念號為53/150。此外，套機亦連同2000年推出，限量75支的銀色Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm鏡頭 (#3891073); 及只有40個的銀色Leicavit (#35/40)。鏡身及過片器上分別刻有 “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-2000” 及 “LEICA HISTORICA 1975-2005” 字樣; 整套相機包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2322', 'M6 Platinum Schmidt Group 1896-1996 100 Years Edition', 'M6 Platinum Schmidt Group 1896-1996 100 Years Edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_151_8.JPG', '151', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In order to commemorate the 100th years of Schmidt group establishing as well as creating their first presence in Asia Pacific Region, 188 units of Leica M6 special edition were launched in 1996. The camera uses the M6 body with platinum plating and “Limited Edition of 188 pcs for Schmidt Group” was engraved at the back, also the logo of Schmidt Group was engraved on top. It fits with an Elmar-M 2.8/50mm lens (#3741306), with special number SC-006/188. It completes with box and papers, wooden box, body cap, both lens caps and camera strap.', '為慶祝興華集團成立100週年，188套鉑金版M6於1996年推出，機頂刻上興華集團的標誌，機背則刻有「Limited Edition of 188 pcs for Schmidt Group」字樣。此機的紀念號碼為SC 006，連同Elmar-M 2.8/50mm鏡頭(#3741306)，鏡頭前端同樣刻有紀念號碼SC-006/188。連同包裝證書、機身蓋、木盒、相機帶及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2323', 'M6 Platinum Anton Bruckner 1824 – 1896', 'M6 Platinum Anton Bruckner 1824 – 1896', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_152_8.JPG', '152', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, '200 units M6 Special Edition were produced in 1996 to commemorate the 100 years after death of Austrian Musician Anton Bruckner. The camera has an engraving of a portrait that locates at the top plate with &quot;Anton Bruckner 1824~1896&quot; engraved. The commemorative number of this set is 9-19. It comes with Elmar 2.8/50mm (#9-19), also with packing, papers, wooden box, both lens caps, body cap, strap and 12 pieces CD of Anton Bruckner.', '此套機為紀念音樂家安東 ‧ 布魯克納逝世 100 週年而發行，共生產 200 台。機身及鏡頭均鍍上鉑金，機頂刻有布魯克的肖像及 “Anton Bruckner 1824-1896” 字樣。紀念號是9-19，機身覆以稀有的藍色蜥蝪皮。套機搭配 Elmar-M 2.8/50mm 鉑金鏡頭 (#9-19)，是罕有與音樂界有關聯的紀念機，極具藝術氣息的。此紀念機帶有包裝證書、木盒、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋、相機帶及十二張布魯克納的音樂光碟。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2324', 'M6 TTL 0.72 “Millennium Edition” Black Paint', 'M6 TTL 0.72 “Millennium Edition” Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_153_7.JPG', '153', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Millennium Edition M6 Black Paint, 2000 sets were produced. The commemorative number of the set is 977/2000. With a matching Summilux-M 1.4/50mm black painted lens (#4010977); also comes with box and papers, body cap, strap, lens pouch and both lens caps.', '此台黑漆版M6為千禧紀念套機，紀念號碼為977/2000，限量推出2000台。配有後三位數字同為977的黑漆版Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#4010977)，連同包裝證書、機身蓋、相機帶、鏡頭皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2325', 'M6 TTL 0.85 Safari', 'M6 TTL 0.85 Safari', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_154_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_154_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_154_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_154_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_154_5.JPG', '154', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica has launched 300 units of M6 0.85 TTL Safari in 2000. The body was painted with military green, same as the decorate leather. The commemorative number of this set is 288, in brand new condition, with all packing and papers.', '徠卡於2000年限量推出300台M6 0.85 TTL 軍綠色版本，機身用上軍隊專用的綠色面漆，配以同色系之飾皮，更顯其獨特性。此機紀念號碼為幸運號碼 “288”，全新未經使用，包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2326', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_155_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_155_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_155_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_155_4.JPG', '155', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'Only 150 units of MP 0.72 Titanium were manufactured. Both camera body and body cap were casted with solid titanium. This set is numbered 42/150, comes with box and papers, inner box, strap and body cap.', '以純鈦製造的MP特別紀念機，全球限量150台，機身及機身蓋均以純鈦所造。此套機的特別號為42/150，配有包裝證書、內盒、相機帶及機身蓋。整套紀念機高貴經典，為收藏家追捧的焦點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2327', 'M6 TTL 0.85 “DIE LETZTEN 999”', 'M6 TTL 0.85 “DIE LETZTEN 999”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_156_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_156_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_156_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_156_4.JPG', '156', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The M6 was introduced in 1984 as the first M-camera with integrated exposure metering system and an LED. The 999 M6 camera of this special edition are the last examples of the classic model whose production ended in 2002 after run of 18 years. “LEICA M6 1984 – 2002” engraved on the top plate. Camera comes with body cap, wooden box, strap, box and papers.', '為紀念M6投產18週年，徠卡特意推出最後999台限量版銀色M6 TTL 0.85，經典的機身上刻有「LEICA M6 1984 – 2002」字樣。此套機配有機身蓋、木盒、相機帶及包裝證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2328', 'MP3 &quot;LHSA Special Edition&quot; Black Paint', 'MP3 &quot;LHSA Special Edition&quot; Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_157_6.JPG', '157', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'In 2005, Leica Black Paint LHSA Special Edition was launched, 1000 units were made. This set is numbered 602/1000. It comes with a black paint Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens (#3991050) and Leicavit (#00400), completes with all packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '發表於2005年，是徠卡與美國徠卡歷史協會共同推出的紀念機，限量1,000台。此機紀念號碼為602/1000。配有黑漆Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭 (#3991050)及過片器(#00400)。 整套套機為黑漆，甚有徠卡古典味。套機包裝配件齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2329', 'M3-P &quot;20 Jahre of Leica Shop Vienna&quot;', 'M3-P &quot;20 Jahre of Leica Shop Vienna&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_158_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_158_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_158_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_158_4.JPG', '158', '', '472,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 20th Anniversary of Leica Shop in Vienna, M3-P Special Edition was launched and only 20 units were made. Leica MP Silver chrome finish with vulcanite cladding and top cover in the typical Leica M3 style. It comes with a Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH lens in silver anodized finish (#4120596). The commemorative number is 18/20. This set completes with all packing, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝維也納Leica Shop成立20週年紀念，推出限量20台M3-P紀念機。相機以MP為藍本，相機上蓋及觀景窗的凸面邊框採用M3的經典設計。此套機紀念號為幸運數字18/20，搭配極為罕見的銀色Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm鏡頭 (#4120596)，全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2330', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_159_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_159_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_159_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_159_4.JPG', '159', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Only 100 units MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition were made. This camera features a copper and zinc-alloy body while the upper and lower lid are painted with military grey, which resembles the Leica M2 Grey film camera on the top plate. This camera is MP 100-40. The Chinese characters “ 精彩一百. 1912-2011” engraved on the top plate and a plum blossom totem engraved on the rear plate. This camera completes with box and papers, wooden presentation box and strap.', '徠卡推出的MP「建國一百週年紀念機」，限量100台。此套機以徠卡原裝木盒珍藏，配有銅鋅合金機身，機身金屬部份噴上特別的軍灰綠色，色澤如同M2 Grey底片相機。機上刻有「精彩一百. 1912-2011」字樣，機背則刻有梅花圖案。此機紀念號碼為MP100-40。配有包裝證書、精美木盒及相機帶，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2331', 'M8.2 Safari Set', 'M8.2 Safari Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_160_9.JPG', '160', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This Safari Edition was launched in 2009, only 500 sets were made. The paint is same as R3 Safari Bundeswehr, very special. This set comes with Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm ASPH lens in chrome (#4078397), strap, E39 UV/IR (#13416) and Billingham camera bag in green as well. The set completes with box and papers.', '此款Safari限量版的概念來自1960年Leitz提供德軍使用的R3 Safari Bundeswehr特製相機﹔其橄欖色的外形甚有軍用相機的風味。此款相機於2009年推出，全球限量500套。套機配有Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm ASPH銀色鏡頭(#4078397)，相機帶及E39 UV/IR (#13416)﹔另配有軍綠色的Billingham相機包﹔此機包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2332', 'M8.2 &quot;White Edition&quot;', 'M8.2 &quot;White Edition&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_161_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_161_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_161_3.jpg', '161', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This M8.2 White model (#3558790) comes with chrome Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm ASPH lens (#4087056). There were only 12 pieces produced of this camera. This camera is not be confused with the white M8 of which 275 units were produced. The set completes with packing, battery, chargers, papers, hood, body cap and both lens caps. This lot has been authenticated by Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck.', '這套是M8.2白色特別版，連同Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm ASPH鏡頭 (#4087056)。根據記錄，M8.2白色特別版只有12台，當年工廠生產了275套M8白色套機，但M8.2白色卻從未對外發佈。套機連同包裝、電池、充電器、說明書、遮光罩、機身蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。此拍品已經過Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2333', 'Leica M Monochrom und Leica M-A Edition “LEICA 100”', 'Leica M Monochrom und Leica M-A Edition “LEICA 100”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_162_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_162_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_162_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_162_4.JPG', '162', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica M Edition 100 was launched in 101 sets only and it brings together a purely mechanical rangefinder camera for film photography – the Leica M-A – with a M Monochrom in one set. The Leica M-A, with technical specifications based on the currently available Leica MP Film camera. Alternatively, M Monochrom is the contemporary variation of the theme composed a century ago by Oskar Barnack. This is the first time that stainless steel has been employed for the visible metallic elements of Leica products. The set also includes three Leica Summilux-M ASPH lenses with focal lengths of 28, 35 and 50mm. The set will be supplied in a black anodized aluminum case, and comes with box and papers.', '這套徠卡100週年限量版只生產了101套，套機包括兩款最新型號相機，分別是M-A及M Monochrom。Leica M-A是基於MP的技術規格上制作; 而M Monochrom則是為了紀念一個世紀前Oskar Barnack為徠卡研發的第一台135mm相機而推出。兩部相機均用上不銹鋼材質，也是徠卡首次在相機上用上此物料。此套機連同三支f/1.4大光圈鏡頭，分別是Summilux-M 1.4/28mm ASPH、Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH及Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH; 套機放置於黑色鋁箱內，包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2334', 'Leica M Monochrom “Ralph Gibson”', 'Leica M Monochrom “Ralph Gibson”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_163_9.JPG', '163', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a special feature in the Leica M Monochrom and Ralph Gibson, which only 35 sets were launched. The special edition is the black leather upholstery in volcanic pattern, developed by Leica, and silver-plated top. The high quality leather is not only applied to the camera body, but is also used for the corresponding shoulder strap. In addition, this camera with accessories designed in close collaboration with Ralph Gibson himself. On the chrome top of the camera is the signature of Ralph Gibson as inscription. The special number of this set is 28/35, comes with chrome Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH lens (#4237352). It also completes with box and paper, camera case, strap, the latest book “MONO” by Gibson, body cap, hood with cap and both lens caps.', '在2013年，徠卡以美國著名美術攝影師Ralph Gibson的名字命名，推出了首款銀色M Monochrom，連銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH限量版套機，只有35台。此特別版M Monochrom採用了亮銀色作機身，機身覆以高級人造皮，機頂更刻有Ralph Gibson的簽名，無疑是攝影迷涉獵的收藏品。此套機的特別號碼是幸運號28/35，配有銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH鏡頭一支 (#4237352)，並連同包裝證書、相機袋、相機帶、Gibson最新的相集 “MONO”、機身蓋、遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2335', 'R7 130th Anniversary of Nihon Siber Hegner', 'R7 130th Anniversary of Nihon Siber Hegner', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_164_7.JPG', '164', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Only 200 of these beautiful Urushi lacquer-edition cameras were produced to celebrate the 130th anniversary of Nihon Siber Hegner, the official Japanese agent for Leica. This set comes with a Summicron-R 2/50mm lens (#3667960), with front lens cap, filter and wooden presentation box, in mint condition.', '為紀念日本的經銷商Nihon Siber Hegner成立130週年，徠卡於1995年推出了200台特別版R7。機身為特別的綠色漆，並覆以駝鳥飾皮。此套機配有Summicron-R 2/50mm鏡頭(#3667960)，連同木盒、濾鏡及鏡頭前蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2336', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_165_6.JPG', '165', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'In 1997, Leica released 300 set of R6.2 limited edition plated in 18 caret gold for Hong Kong returning to China. The commemorate number is 118/300. “July 1, 1997 HONG KONG” and Hong Kong skyline were engraved on top plate. This set comes with Summicron-R 2/50mm lens (#3765186). The camera is in mint condition with box and papers, wooden box, strap, body cap and both lens caps.', '徠卡為香港回歸中國推出罕見的R6.2 18K鍍金套機，量產300套。此套機有吉祥的紀念號碼118/300，機頂刻有 「July 1, 1997 HONG KONG」 和香港著名地標，相機配有Summicron-R 2/50mm (#3765186)鏡頭。此套機連同包裝證書、木盒、相機帶、機身蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2337', 'Leica Display Stand', 'Leica Display Stand', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_166_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_166_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_166_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_166_4.JPG', '166', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'These 23 pieces of Leica camera stands were originally used in Leica Museum before they sold to private. These stands were made in much thinner plastics, not later regular thicker version supplied to other Leica dealers. Here are some of the highlights: “0 series 1923” Display stand, “Model I 1925” Display stand, “Compur Dial Set” Display stand and “Luxus 1930” Display stand etc.', '此批產品展示架原使用於徠卡博物館內，它們比後期提供予分銷商使用的展示架較為薄。此拍品共有23個展示架，其中的亮點包括有: “0 series 1923” 展示架、“Model I 1925” 展示架、 “Compur Dial Set” 展示架、 “Luxus 1930” 展示架等。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2338', 'Leica Hand Stand', 'Leica Hand Stand', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_167_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_167_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_167_3.JPG', '167', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a display hand stand for Leica screw mount camera and shaped like a hand. “Eigentum” engraved on bottom (means factory property) and this stand was made in Germany; extremely rare.', '本拍品是於德國製造的徠卡螺絲口相機用展示架，外形仿照一隻指向前方的手，底部刻有「Eigentum」字樣，是屬徠卡工廠所有，市場極為罕見，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2339', 'Leica 1A in Half Scale with Wooden Stand', 'Leica 1A in Half Scale with Wooden Stand', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_168_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_168_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_168_3.JPG', '168', '', '6,490', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Leica 1A in half scale with wooden stand, rare in the market.', '這台1A半比例模型，機身大小是正常版的一半; 連同木製展示架。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2340', 'Leica I Luxus &amp; Leica O Picture Set', 'Leica I Luxus &amp; Leica O Picture Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_169_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_169_2.JPG', '169', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Original picture set of Leica I Luxus and Leica 0 in 18x24 inch photo paper. It was originally hung in Leitz Canada, may be made from Leitz Wetzlar.', '此對是徠卡I Luxus及0機型的原裝照片，大小為18x24英吋，原展示於徠卡的加拿大分部。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2341', 'Leica Artwork', 'Leica Artwork', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_170_1.JPG', '170', '', '2,360', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Leica artwork about Oskar Barnack and Leica by famous female artist Helen Kennedy. Only 100 pieces were made and this should be the fourth one which done between 1970’s to 1980’s. Paper is in 22x28.5 inch.', '這是由藝術家Helen Kennedy於1970年代至1980年代製作，描繪Oskar Barnack及徠卡，限量100件，而此拍品應是第四件。大小為22x28.5英吋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2342', '&quot;First Group&quot; Original Photo of Ernst Leitz Canada', '&quot;First Group&quot; Original Photo of Ernst Leitz Canada', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_171_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_171_2.JPG', '171', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a real and original photo handed in Leitz Canada which shows the people who started “Ernst Leitz Canada Limited” in 1952. They are the first group of Leica employees and their families sent from Germany to Leitz Canada. A letter of all the names of the employees and families in the group is included, have very important history value.', '此照片內是首批由德國徠卡工廠到加拿大廠房工作的員工及其家屬，攝於1952年﹔照片一直展示於加拿大的廠房內，極具歷史意義。拍品連同一封列有當時員工及其家屬姓名的信件，為各位喜愛徠卡歷史的收藏家提供一件不可多得的藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2343', 'Leica Prototype Hood M886 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', 'Leica Prototype Hood M886 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_172_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_172_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_172_3.JPG', '172', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early rectangular metal prototype lens hood of early 35mm lens. It was shown in Leica Museum with museum number M886, extremely rare. For more information and pictures of this lot, please refer to Lars Netopil &quot;Prototype Leica&quot; p.49 and p.59.', '這是非常罕見的原型版金屬遮光罩，是早期為35mm鏡頭研發的矩形遮光罩。此拍品原屬徠卡博物館藏品，收藏編號為M886，市面難得一見。有關此拍品的圖片及介紹，可參閱Lars Netopil“Prototype Leica”p.49及p.59。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2344', 'Leica Prototype Hood M592 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', 'Leica Prototype Hood M592 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_173_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_173_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_173_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_173_4.JPG', '173', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a prototype lens hood for Hektor 1.9/7.3cm FGHOO, made of brass. It was shown in Leica Museum with special number M592, extremely rare in the market.', '本拍品為Hektor 1.9/7.3cm遮光罩FGHOO的原型版，以黃銅鑄造。原收藏於徠卡博物館中，收藏編號是M592，是非常罕見的徠卡配件原型版，收藏家的夢幻逸品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2345', 'Leica Prototype Hood M817 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', 'Leica Prototype Hood M817 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_174_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_174_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_174_3.JPG', '174', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens hood from Leica Museum, with museum number M817, extremely rare! And this is an early FISON prototype hood, with rectangular cut and folding version and this is a folding one. For further illustration, please refer to Lars Netopil “Prototype Leica” p.49 and p.53.', '這個原型版遮光罩原被徠卡博物館收藏，收藏編號為M817，市場罕見。根據Lars Netopil介紹，早期FISON遮光罩的原型版分別有矩型切割款及伸縮款；此拍品為伸縮款。有關詳情可參閱Lars Netopil“Prototype Leica” p.49及p.53。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2346', 'Leica Prototype Hood M543 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', 'Leica Prototype Hood M543 &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_175_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_175_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_175_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_175_4.jpg', '175', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens hood from Leica Museum, with museum number M543, it is for early Summarit lenses. For more information and photo for this lot, please refer to Lars Netopil “Prototype Leica” p.49 and p.61.', '此遮光罩原屬於徠卡博物館的收藏，藏品編號為M543。本原型版遮光罩可用於早期Summarit鏡頭上，有關此拍品的圖片及詳情，可參閱Lars Netopil“Prototype Leica”p.49及p.61。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2347', 'Leica Prototype Case &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', 'Leica Prototype Case &quot;Museum Piece&quot;', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_176_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_176_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_176_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_176_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_176_5.JPG', '176', '', '542,800', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an extremely rare prototype MBROO case with the later protection model in metal. Leica museum number is M345. This case was exactly shown in Lars Netopli “Prototype Leica” p.167-173.', '這個徠卡金屬相機盒是MBROO的原型版，市面極為罕見；原展示於徠卡博物館，收藏編號為M345。市面上MBROO的原型版已是稀有，而此拍品更是徠卡博物館中的收藏品，相信必定會成為各收藏家爭相競投的珍寶之一。Lars Netopil “Prototype Leica” p.167-173記錄了此拍品的圖片及資料。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2348', 'Leica Camera Hard Case MBROO', 'Leica Camera Hard Case MBROO', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_177_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_177_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_177_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_177_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_177_5.JPG', '177', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica camera hard case MBROO manufactured in 1955, made of metal with rubber seal which makes it impact-proof and water-resistant, designed for screw mount camera.', '徠卡於1955年生產相機套MBROO，以堅硬的金屬製成，配上經典的黑色水波紋，防撞抗水，適用於螺絲口相機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2349', 'Leica Meter Prototype', 'Leica Meter Prototype', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_178_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_178_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_178_3.JPG', '178', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Rare prototype of Leica meter with coupling to Leica-M cameras. Made by AFAB for Leitz U.S.A., as a plan to replace the Metrawatt Leicameter-MR4 for Leica M4-2 or M4-P cameras. Never reached commercial production.', '徠卡測光錶的Prototype，由AFAB製造供美國徠茲使用。此產品可用於M4-2或M4-P機身上，未曾正式生產及於市場上發佈。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2350', 'Leicavit Chrome Prototype', 'Leicavit Chrome Prototype', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_179_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_179_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_179_3.JPG', '179', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early Leicavit for screw mount cameras, especially for IIIf and IIIg in the early 1950’s. More importantly, it comes with special engraving “Ernst Leitz Wetzlar Germany” in two lines; instead of the commercial version engraved with “Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar Germany” in three lines, very special.', '此過片器的刻字與後期量產版本有所不同：量產版本中的「Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar Germany」分三行刻上，而此原型版則只分有兩行，並且沒有「GmbH」一字，可見這個早期螺口相機用的過片器十分特別。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2351', 'Leicavit MP Black Paint', 'Leicavit MP Black Paint', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_180_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_180_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_180_3.JPG', '180', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is an original Leicavit for early MP and M2 in black painted finished, which is an extremely rare piece of original accessory for MP.', '這是供早期徠卡MP及M2用的原裝黑漆過片器，產量稀少，是不可多得的收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2352', 'Leicavit Prototype Set (Black &amp; Chrome)', 'Leicavit Prototype Set (Black &amp; Chrome)', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_181_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_181_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_181_3.JPG', '181', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the prototype Leicavit set for M series, very rare. Beside the special prototype serial number, some designs are different from the official version, such as the engraving style and position. For the commercial version, “Leicavit M” was all engraved on the right hand side in capital letter; company name and origin were engraved on the bottom; which are different from this pair of prototype.', '這對拍品是M系相機過片器的原型版，除了擁有特別的機身號外，其刻字位置及設計皆與量產版本不同：量產版本上的「Leicavit M」一字以全大草刻上，並刻於過片器的右邊，而公司名稱及產地則刻於底部; 另外，其過片杆採用了原始的四方長形設計，以上特徵均與原型版有所出入。此對原型版過片器在市場上不甚常見，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2353', 'Leicavit MP “LHSA Special Edition”', 'Leicavit MP “LHSA Special Edition”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_182_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_182_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_182_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_182_4.JPG', '182', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is Leicavit in chrome finished for LHSA. It completes with box and papers, in brand new condition.', '此為美國徠卡歷史協會 (LHSA) 銀色版本快速過片器，正面刻有MP字樣。全新未經使用，包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2354', 'Leitz New York Wood Display Stand', 'Leitz New York Wood Display Stand', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_183_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_183_2.JPG', '183', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare wooden Leica display stands for Leitz New York in 1930’s. This is a decoration display for Leica products and it is hard to find one in fine condition nowadays. For the same type of display stand, please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.330.', '這是非常罕見的徠卡木製展示架，產於1930年代，提供予當時的分銷商作陳列之用。經過歲月流逝，能保存至今的陳列用配件已經所剩無幾，成色如拍品般良好的更是寥寥，絕對是收藏珍品。同款展示架可見James Lager Vol. III p.330。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2355', 'Leitz Microscope Lamp', 'Leitz Microscope Lamp', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_184_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_184_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_184_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_184_4.JPG', '184', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a microscope lamp which made in the early 1920’s. Light must be concentrated on the mirror of the microscope and will give a bright image. It comes with cord.', '此拍品於1920年代初生產，是顯微鏡用的燈具，光線會聚焦於顯微鏡的鏡上，使影像更為明亮。此拍品連同電線。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2356', 'VOTRA Stereo Viewer', 'VOTRA Stereo Viewer', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_185_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_185_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_185_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_185_4.JPG', '185', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Leica stereo viewer (VOTRA) with an opal-glass plate, also comes with red package box and VOTIV stand. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.271 for further illustration.', '此為徠卡立體鏡 (VOTRA)，可用於拍攝或配上乳白色玻璃片作觀片用。此拍品連同原包裝盒，乳白色玻璃片及支架 (VOTIV)。有關資料可參閱James Lager Vol. III p.271。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2357', 'Leitz Dealer Sign Set', 'Leitz Dealer Sign Set', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_186_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_186_2.JPG', '186', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a set of two Leica plates in 20 inch, with wording “Leica Specialist” and “Leica Full Line Dealer”respectively, made in Germany. Both with mark &quot;Eigentum: Ernst Leitz Wetzlar GmbH, Innenschild Nr.221, Made in Germany” They were originally hung in Leica Solms.', '此對20英吋大的展示牌為徠卡工廠所用，牌上印有 “Eigentum: Ernst Leitz Wetzlar GmbH. Innenschild Nr. 211.”。此拍品於德國製造，分別寫有 “Leica Specialist” 及 “Leica Full Line Dealer” 字樣; 原展示於徠卡德國廠房。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2358', 'Leica Color Glass Sign', 'Leica Color Glass Sign', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_187_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_187_2.JPG', '187', '', '8,260', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Leica color glass sign in wood frame, originally hanged in Leitz Canada.', '此為徠卡手工玻璃牌匾，原展示於徠茲加拿大。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2359', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Pioneer Metal Plaque', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Pioneer Metal Plaque', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_188_1.JPG', '188', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'This is a metal plaque commemorating Oskar Barnack who built the first Leica camera. It measures approx. 7.5” x 7.5” and depicts an image of Oskar Barnack and the first prototype Leica camera superimposed over a perforated film border.', '為紀念Oskar Barnack發明第一台徠卡135mm格式相機而特別推出的紀念牌匾，此牌匾上雕有Oskar Barnack的肖像及其發明的O-series相機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2360', 'Trinovid 8x20 “Gold Edition”', 'Trinovid 8x20 “Gold Edition”', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_189_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_189_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_189_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_189_4.JPG', '189', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'This special edition of Trinovid 8x20 “Edition” is in gold plated and decorated with calf leather with lizard pattern, only 1,999 pieces were produced. Comes with box, instruction, certificate and leather case.', '此款望遠鏡限量1,999套，鏡身以鍍金製造，並配以蜥蝪紋的小牛皮，格調尊貴。此望遠鏡連同包裝、說明書、證書及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2361', 'Leitz Microscopes', 'Leitz Microscopes', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_190_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_190_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_190_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_190_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_190_5.JPG', '190', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a brass travelling microscopes with four lenses in 3x, 6x, 8x and 1/12x, in a matching wooden container and with certificate. It shows signs of normal use.', '此為銅製的徠卡顯微鏡，配有四個放大鏡，分別是3x、6x、8x及1/12x；有使用痕跡。連同木盒及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2362', 'Leica Pradovit P150 IR Typ 623', 'Leica Pradovit P150 IR Typ 623', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_191_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_191_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_191_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_191_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_191_5.JPG', '191', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica slide projector Pradovit P150 IR was made in Germany, with projector lens Hektor-P2 2.8/85mm. It comes with box and warranty card.', '此徠卡幻燈片投影機於德國生產，配有Hektor-P2 2.8/85mm投影鏡，可使用紅外線操作。連同包裝盒及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2363', 'Voigtlander All-Metal Daguerreotype Camera Replica', 'Voigtlander All-Metal Daguerreotype Camera Replica', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_192_6.JPG', '192', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'r All-Metal Daguerreotype Camera was the first official replica by Voigtlander for their anniversary in 1939, engraved with “No. 84 Voigtlander &amp; John in Wien”. The camera was until 1945 in Voigtlander factory museum in Brunswick. This is the oldest official replica, with original brass holder and rear lens cap, very rare.', '福倫達公司於1939年起複製的全金屬相機。它以全銅製造，鏡身上刻有「No. 84 Voigtlander &amp; John in Wien」字樣。直至1945年，此相機一直存放於福倫達布倫瑞克博物館內，屬於官方早期的複製品，配以銅製支架及鏡頭後蓋，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2364', 'Super-Angulon-R 4/21mm Prototype', 'Super-Angulon-R 4/21mm Prototype', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_193_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_193_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_193_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_193_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_193_5.JPG', '193', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'The retrofocus design was created by Schneider, which would be used with the swinging mirror, allowing faster use. Moreover, a typical prototype serial number “0000000989” is engraved, relatively rare. It comes with both lens caps.', '此款原型鏡頭由施耐德公司設計，其焦點後移式的光學設計使操作更快捷。最特別之處為此鏡的序號並非在正常序列之中，市場上數量極少。此拍品連同前後蓋，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2365', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/24mm Prototype', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/24mm Prototype', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_194_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_194_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_194_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_194_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_194_5.JPG', '194', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a prototype lens of Elmarit-R 2.8/24mm; its serial number 0001344 is not in the commercial batch, very rare. It comes with front and rear lens caps.', '此鏡是Elmarit-R 2.8/24mm的原型版，鏡頭序號0001344並非在正常生產序列之中，市面罕見。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2366', 'Schneider PC Super-Angulon-R 2.8/28mm', 'Schneider PC Super-Angulon-R 2.8/28mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_195_7.JPG', '195', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both lens caps, and filter with hood (#12540), in Leica R mount.', '此款鏡頭是徠卡採用施耐德最著名的移軸鏡頭，成象質素佳，而且便於操作。此鏡是徠卡R卡口，配有鏡頭前後蓋及濾鏡連遮光罩(#12540)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2367', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_196_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_196_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_196_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_196_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_196_5.JPG', '196', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the second version of Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens with built-in hood. It comes with front lens cap and keeper, in good working order.', '此鏡為早期的第二款Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭，備有內置遮光罩。此鏡連同鏡頭前蓋及膠盅，調焦順滑。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2368', 'Leica SL Olympic Version', 'Leica SL Olympic Version', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_197_7.JPG', '197', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica released 1000 sets 5-ring “Olympic” Edition for 1972 Innsbruck Olympic Games. Olympic rings and word “72” are engraved on the prism. It comes with Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2270872), hood with cap (#12564), rear lens cap, body cap and original box with 5-ring Olympic stamped.', '為紀念奧地利茵斯布魯克舉行的奧運會，1,000台奧運版的Leicaflex SL於1972年隆重推出。機身正面刻有奧運五環及「72」字樣，極富紀念性。此機配有Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2270872)、遮光罩連蓋(#12564)、鏡頭後蓋、機身蓋及同樣印有奧運五環標記的包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2369', 'R3 Safari Outfit', 'R3 Safari Outfit', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_9.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_10.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_11.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_198_12.JPG', '198', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Between 1977 and1978, Leica produced 5000 units of R3 Safari outfit with several basic assorted lenses. This set included a R3 (#1469662) with strap, body cap and case in original green paint. Besides, it also comes with Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2922149), Summilux-R 1.4/50mm (#2900168), Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2920960) and hood(#12509). All lenses come with both caps.', '在1977至1978年間，徠卡共生產了5,000台R3軍綠色版本，並配以軍綠色鏡頭。此機連同相機帶、機身蓋及原裝軍綠色鋁箱。另外，套機還配有以下鏡頭及配件，分別是: Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2922149)、Summilux-R 1.4/50mm (#2900168)、Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2920960)及遮光罩 (#12509); 以上三支鏡頭均連同前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2370', 'Hasselblad 500CM Swedish Crystal Model', 'Hasselblad 500CM Swedish Crystal Model', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_199_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_199_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_199_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_199_4.JPG', '199', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This was usually a promotional piece for Hasselblad dealers, which is a great piece for Hasselblad collector and rare in market. It comes with an original box, with the number 03684 engraved.', '此為哈蘇提供予經銷商作推廣用的瑞典水晶擺設，市埸罕見，愛好哈蘇的收藏家不容錯過。此拍品刻有編號 「03684」，連原裝包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2371', 'Hasselblad SWA', 'Hasselblad SWA', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_200_7.JPG', '200', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Hasselblad SWA (supreme wide angle) 6x6cm camera which launched in 1954. It comes with Biogon 4.5/38mm (#1074140), magazine film back (#CI18641) and viewfinder; in good working order.', '於1954哈蘇推出的超級廣角中畫幅相機，配有Biogon 4.5/38mm鏡頭(#1074140)、菲林後背 (#CI18641) 及觀景器；操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2372', 'Hasselblad SWC/M', 'Hasselblad SWC/M', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_201_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_201_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_201_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_201_4.JPG', '201', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with Biogon 4.5/38mm (#5766771), viewfinder and rear cover.', '此機連同Biogon 4.5/38mm鏡頭 (#5766771)、取景器及後背蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2373', 'Hasselblad 903 SWC', 'Hasselblad 903 SWC', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_202_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_202_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_202_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_202_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_202_5.JPG', '202', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with CF 4.5/38mm lens (#7122481), front lens cap, rear cover and viewfinder.', '此機連同廣角CF 4.5/38mm鏡頭 (#7122481)，帶鏡頭前蓋、背蓋及取景器。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2374', 'Hasselblad C 5.6/250mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad C 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_203_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_203_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_203_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_203_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_203_5.JPG', '203', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a well-known Hasselblad lens with Superachromat. It comes with front lens cap and keeper, in mint-condition.', '此鏡頭採用特製的Superachromat超低色散鏡片，色彩銳利。此鏡連同鏡頭前蓋及膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2375', 'Hasselblad CF 5.6/250mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CF 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_204_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_204_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_204_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_204_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_204_5.JPG', '204', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a well-known Hasselblad lens with Superachromat. It comes with both lens caps, in mint-condition.', '哈蘇超級名鏡之一，為蔡司傾力之作的Superachromat 5.6/250mm鏡頭，堪稱現代光學的高峰。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2376', 'Hasselblad FE 2.8/300mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad FE 2.8/300mm Superachromat', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_205_7.JPG', '205', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Only 300 pieces made, comes with neutral filter and both lens caps.', '為滿足哈蘇 200 系列專業相機的使用者，1998年哈蘇生產了全球僅 300 支的 FE 300mm/2.8。這款鏡頭採用Superachromat優異的光學設計，是傳說中的神鏡。此鏡頭連濾鏡及前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2377', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/350mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/350mm Superachromat', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_206_6.JPG', '206', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classic lens of Hasselblad features apochromatic correction. It comes with box, certificate, leather case and both lens caps.', '此拍品為哈蘇經典鏡頭，有消色差功能，使成象質素更為銳利。配有包裝證書、皮筒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2378', 'Hasselblad Xpan with 4/45mm and 4/90mm', 'Hasselblad Xpan with 4/45mm and 4/90mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_207_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_207_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_207_3.JPG', '207', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Xpan with 4/45mm lens (#8YER12457), comes with box and papers, hood with cap, strap, body cap, front lens cap, keeper and spirit lever. It also comes with 4/90mm (8ZER10513), front lens cap and keeper.', 'Xpan連4/45mm鏡頭 (#8YER12457)，配有包裝證書、遮光罩連蓋、相機帶、機身蓋、鏡頭前蓋、膠盅及水平珠。此套機另配有4/90mm鏡頭 (#8ZER10513)，帶前蓋及膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2379', 'XPAN 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', 'XPAN 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_208_7.JPG', '208', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with center filter, viewfinder, hood, both caps and original leather box, in mint condition.', '此鏡連同中灰濾鏡、取景器、遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋及原裝皮盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2380', 'Alpa Carl Zeiss Biogon 4.5/38mm', 'Alpa Carl Zeiss Biogon 4.5/38mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_209_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_209_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_209_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_209_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_209_5.JPG', '209', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Alpa medium format system is a family of cameras with superior mechanical precision and outstanding overall quality. This makes the Alpa the ideal platform for the high performance wide angle lens Zeiss Biogon T* 4.5/38mm. Even with the aperture fully open, the Biogon T* 4.5/38mm lens produces beautifully sharp, brilliant photographs. Only 50 units were made. The lens here comes with both caps, in original ALPA mount.', '1953年，貝帖勒博士為蔡司設計的Biogon T* 4.5/38mm鏡頭是Biogon系列代表作之一，當年產量只有50支，完美的光學表現使這支鏡頭成為跨世紀的頂級鏡頭。此鏡由八片五組構成，可以提供90度視角以及完美的影像品質，即使在光圈全開的情況下，鏡頭解析度和色彩飽和度表現依然極佳，桶狀畸變和影像邊緣的失真幾乎不存在。此鏡連同前後蓋，為原裝ALPA卡口。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2381', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_210_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_210_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_210_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_210_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_210_5.JPG', '210', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm is one of the most famous cine lens, which made in France. The lens comes with focusing barrel in Leica M mount, also lens hood and rear lens cap.', '於法國生產的Kinoptik是最頂級的電影鏡品牌之一，以超高的解析度聞名; 而此鏡的濃郁色彩和油畫感散景表現更教人一見難忘。此鏡配有徠卡M系列的調焦鏡筒、遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2382', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_211_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_211_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_211_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_211_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_211_5.JPG', '211', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Kinoptik is one of the most popular cine lens. Instead of 100mm and 150mm lens, this lens is in 75mm with macro focusing tube, probably a special order in small batch production,. It can be used for macro filming in excellent quality. The lens is in ALPA mount, with both lens caps.', '產於法國的Kinoptik是最高級的電影鏡之一，以超高的解析度聞名。此鏡是少數帶有微距調焦筒的款式，有別於其他一般不能近拍的100mm及150mm鏡頭，近攝效果極佳。此款鏡頭產量極少，估計是客戶特別向廠方訂造。鏡頭為ALPA卡口，配有前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2383', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_212_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_212_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_212_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_212_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_212_5.JPG', '212', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is in ALPA mount, comes with both lens caps.', '本拍品是著名的Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm鏡頭，為ALPA卡口，配有鏡頭前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2384', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_213_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_213_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_213_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_213_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_213_5.JPG', '213', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is in ALPA mount and comes with both lens caps, clean glass.', '本拍品是著名的Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm鏡頭，為ALPA卡口，配有鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2385', 'Voigtlander Linhof 4.5/15cm APO-Lanthar', 'Voigtlander Linhof 4.5/15cm APO-Lanthar', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_214_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_214_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_214_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_214_4.JPG', '214', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Linhof 4.5/15cm APO-Lanthar was made by Voigtlander in Germany, for 4x5 large format camera used. This lens is in excellent condition.', '此鏡是由德國享負盛名的福倫達公司為林可夫製造的大畫幅相機專用鏡頭，整體成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2386', 'Voigtlander Bessa II with APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', 'Voigtlander Bessa II with APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_215_7.JPG', '215', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is an original Voigtlander Bessa II with a 4.5/105mm APO-Lanthar lens, in mint- condition.', 'Voigtlander Bessa II是福倫達公司於1950年推出的顛峰之作。Bessa II有兩個取景框，分別為6 X 4.5及6 X 9，光圈景深尺均顯示為4.5–22。此機配有超級名鏡APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm；該鏡之玻璃由稀有的鑭玻璃製成，成像優異，加上此鏡產量極少，約200-300台，是攝影愛好者追求的機鏡套裝珍寶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2387', 'Roma Gawwa with Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', 'Roma Gawwa with Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_7.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_8.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_216_9.JPG', '216', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The camera here is equipped as original. It comes with an Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1 (#160819) which in original M39 mount. Also completes with original box and lens front cap.', '這台市場少有的套機仍然維持出廠時的原裝配置，連同Angenieux 1.8/50mm Type S1鏡頭 (#160819)。鏡頭是原裝M39 mount，配有原裝包裝盒及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2388', 'Carl Zeiss Jena Protarlinse Set 29/35/41/48cm', 'Carl Zeiss Jena Protarlinse Set 29/35/41/48cm', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_217_6.JPG', '217', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a rare lens set with very good lenses; which are Protarlinse 29cm (#789396), Protarlinse VII 35cm (#874578), Protarlinse 41cm (#874703) and Protarlinse 48cm (#874754). The set comes with a wooden box.', '這是蔡司出品的套裝設計，使用方便。它配有四個前組及一個後組接環，隨時更換前組即可改變焦距; 分別配有: Protarlinse 29cm (#789396)、Protarlinse VII 35cm (#874578)、Protarlinse 41cm (#874703)及Protarlinse 48cm (#874754)。此拍品連木盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2389', 'Nikon Reflex-Nikkor 11/2000mm Mirror Lens', 'Nikon Reflex-Nikkor 11/2000mm Mirror Lens', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_218_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_218_2.jpg', '218', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'A prototype of this lens was first displayed at Photokina in 1968 and actually production was only commenced in 1970. Only 300 units were made approx. This is the longest reaching and the largest dimension Nikkor optical lens for 35mm photography. It works almost like an optical telescope which projects a compelling 40X magnification of the subject when compared with a normal 50mm standard lens. It comes with 4 types of built-in filters: ultraviolet (L37C), medium yellow (Y48), orange (056) and red (R60), also both lens caps, aluminum case, AY-1 mounting with wooden case.', '此款鏡頭最早於1968年的Photokina上展出，但正式投產則由1970年開始，共生產約300支。它是藝康為135mm格式相機所製造最長焦的鏡頭，與50mm的標準鏡相比，它可以放大40倍影像，有如望遠鏡一樣。它連同四塊內置濾鏡，分別是L37C、黃色Y48、橙色O56及紅色R60，另連同鋁箱、前後蓋及帶木盒的承托架(AY-1)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2390', 'Nikkor 2/300mm ED IF AIS', 'Nikkor 2/300mm ED IF AIS', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_219_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_219_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_219_3.JPG', '219', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was first launched in summer 1983 and it was developed in anticipation of its use covering indoor sports at the 1984 Olympics. Lens is designed as 7 elements in 3 groups, with Extra-Low Dispersion (ED) lenses to provide precise optical color correction. Including a prototype, approx. 400 pieces were made only, very rare. The lens here comes with TC-14C Ai-S Teleconverter (#283408), an attachable 1.4X focal length multiplying accessory, could do double duty as a 420mm lens and with absolutely no loss of quality. Moreover, it also completes with aluminum case, HE-1 hood, 4 filters with carries, rear lens cap and leather case.', '此款鏡頭於1983年推出，主要用於運動攝影，是為1984年洛杉磯奧運會而設。鏡頭以七片三組設計，配上ED鏡片技術以改善色散問題，使色彩更加銳利，成象質素大為提升。連同原型版在內，此款鏡頭只生產約400支左右，於1985年便停產，十分稀有。為方便用家，此鏡配有TC-14C AIS增倍鏡 (#283408)，可使焦距在質素不被影響的情況下增加至420mm。此鏡另配有鋁箱、HE-1遮光罩、濾鏡及濾鏡接環四個、鏡頭後蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2391', 'Rolleiflex 2.8GX “1929-1989” Edition', 'Rolleiflex 2.8GX “1929-1989” Edition', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_220_6.JPG', '220', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This was launched in 1989 in total 1500 sets for commemorating the 60th anniversary of Rolleiflex. It is decorated with metallic gray painted and napa alligator print leather, with a gold plated name plate. It comes with a Planar 2.8/80mm (#8104524) and Heidosmat 2.8/80mm lens. Moreover, it comes with box, instruction, certificate, two filters, strap and lens cap.', '為慶祝祿萊60週年，2.8GX特別版相機於1989年推出市場，限量1,500台。金色的名牌配以灰色機身及鱷魚紋飾皮，格調十足。此機連同兩支鏡頭，分別是Planar 2.8/80mm (#8104524) 及Heidosmat 2.8/80mm鏡頭，並配有包裝、說明書、保用證、兩片濾鏡、尼龍帶及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2392', 'Wide Rolleiflex 4.0', 'Wide Rolleiflex 4.0', '34', '/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_221_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_221_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a23/LOTNO_221_3.JPG', '221', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a Wide Rolleiflex twin reflex camera, comes with Heidomat 4/55mm (#3507886) and Distagon 4/55mm (#3506560), glass near perfect condition, still have the original flat glass for the film plane. Come with leather case and lens cover.', '罕有Rolleiflex Wideangle 4/55mm 廣角雙鏡反光相機，早期生產大約只有三千多台，是Rolleiflex系列中產量最少的相機﹔此款Distagon鏡頭變形極小，鏡片成色近乎完美，並且保留原裝的玻璃菲林壓片，連同Heidomat 4/55mm (#3507886)及Distagon 4/55mm (#3506560); 皮套及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2393', 'MP Chrome Consecutive Numbers “Jay Maisel”', 'MP Chrome Consecutive Numbers “Jay Maisel”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_82_9.jpg', '82', '', '3,422,000', null, null, null, null, 'This fully original Chrome MP (MP-222 &amp; MP-223) in consecutive numbers used by its first owner, famous photographer Jay Maisel from 1957’s. The condition of this pair of MP indicates that Jay Maisel loves and frequently used these both cameras. This lot includes two of the most familiar prints “Marilyn Monroe” and “Miles Davis” taken by Jay Maisel, and a confirmation letter written by him.<br />\r\nMP chrome produced in year 1956-1957, designed for few professional reporters and photographers, only 311 units were made, extremely rare. This model has Leicavit, up to two frames per second, so that professional users are able to capture the decisive moment. <br />\r\nAt this auction, these cameras also come with matching Summicron-M 2/5cm lens (# 1474704) and Summicron-M 2/5cm lens (# 1474914), together with the front lens cap and MP Leicavit, in good working order. The fact that these cameras owned by such famous photographer makes this precious consecutive numbers MP cameras more valuable for collection.', '這對早期的銀色MP(MP-222及MP-223)是由當代美國著名攝影師JAY MAISEL自1957年起一直所擁有，憑著對相機的外觀品相可見，JAY MAISEL對它們的喜愛及使用程度非淺。伴隨著這對MP拍品的還有兩幅JAY MAISEL最為人熟悉的攝影作品，Marilyn Monroe(瑪麗蓮·夢露）及Miles Davis(邁爾斯·戴維斯)，這兩幅相片均有JAY MAISEL的簽名，同時還連同一封由JAY MAISEL發出的確認信，證明這對相連號相機為他本人所擁有。<br />\r\nMP相機是徠卡除M3以外，另一傳奇的機型。產於1956-1957年間的MP，是當年徠卡為極少數專業記者及攝影師而製的，銀色MP只有311台，極為稀有。此機型配有快速過片器，令過片速度最高可達至每秒兩張，使專業用家輕易地於瞬間捕捉決定性的一刻。經過大半世紀的洗禮，本來已為數不多的MP被分散世界各地，並落入不同的收藏家手中，幾乎從未在拍賣會上有現身過相連號碼的MP相機；且此對連號的經典MP相機由著名美國攝影師所擁有，更具收藏價值。<br />\r\n這對連號的經典MP相機，機身號碼分別為MP-222及MP-223，分別配有供MP同時Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭(#1474704)以及Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭(#1474914)，連同鏡頭前蓋及MP Leicavit，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2394', 'MP Chrome', 'MP Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_83_8.jpg', '83', '', '1,180,000', null, null, null, null, 'only 311 pieces chrome MP were made in 1957. The serial number is matching with the number engraved on the chassis, comes with a matching Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1465842), chrome MP Leicavit and lens front cap. Moreover, a service certificate of camera provided by Leica Camera Japan Co., Ltd is included.', '此為徠卡收藏者不可缺少的的早期銀色MP。<br />\r\n銀色MP於1957年生產，當年僅生產311台，主要為專業攝影師及記者特別訂製。此機機內刻有與機頂號碼相同的「P 330」，配有同期的Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭(#1465842)，銀色MP Leicavit及鏡頭前蓋。更重要的是此機還帶有日本徠卡公司為此MP-330作檢測服務的證書(Service certificate)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2395', 'M2 Chrome with Three Lenses and OROLF Set', 'M2 Chrome with Three Lenses and OROLF Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_84_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_84_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_84_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_84_4.JPG', '84', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early M2 in chrome with self-timer and rewind button, only small numbers were produced, comes with Summaron 5.6/2.8cm lens(#1477386); Summitar 2/5cm lens(#815500) and Elmar 4/9cm lens(#1409271). All lenses complete with front caps. Also comes with a very rare Tri-Lens turret OROLF for M2/M3 (Please refer to James Lager Vol. III p. 300 for further illustration), with strap, in good working order and excellent condition.', '此稀有的快速轉台可供三支螺絲口鏡頭同時配合M3/M2相機使用，可作快速轉換鏡頭拍攝用，產量極少(可參考James Lager Vol. III p. 300中介紹)。本拍品連同一機三鏡，包括M2(#931089)、Summaron 5.6/2.8cm (#1477386)、Summitar 2/5cm (#815500)及Elmar 4/9cm (#1409271)，三支鏡頭均配有鏡頭前蓋，此轉台配有掛帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2396', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_85_7.jpg', '85', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'The first batch of M2 Black Paint with button rewind knob was produced in 1958, numbers are between 948601-949100. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.202 for further illustration). M2 Black Paint was ranked R7, “Exceptionally Rare”, in the Leica International Price Guide (R1-R10). However, for M2 with rewind button and without self-timer, less than 200 units were produced, they were indeed extremely rare and should be ranked the same as MP. This camera is in original black paint comes with box and camera body cap, well functioned, in mint condition. Very rare.', '這是首批生產的按鈕回片、不帶自拍黑漆版M2，產於1958年。首批M2黑漆的機身號在948601-949100之間 (這個版本的M2在James Lager Vol.I p.202書中也有同類型的介紹)，在徠卡國際價格指南(R1-R10)當中，M2黑漆版被評級為R7，即極為稀有(Exceptionally Rare)；而有按鈕回片、不帶自拍的M2黑漆更是罕見，產量少於200台，它的級別與MP看齊。此機原裝黑漆，運作暢順，超過半世紀，仍能尋得如此成色的黑漆M2，實屬難得。連機身蓋及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2397', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M2 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_86_8.jpg', '86', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'The first version of M2 Black Paint was produced in 1958 (batch number 948601-949100). M2 Black Paint was ranked R7, “Exceptionally Rare”, in the Leica International Price Guide (R1-R10). However, for M2 with rewind button and without self-timer, less than 200 units were produced, they were indeed extremely rare and should be ranked the same as MP. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.202 for further illustrations). This camera comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm(#1926634), in original black paint, with front lens cap and with signs of use.', '本拍品屬於第一批生產的黑漆版M2，產於1958年，機身編號在948601-949100之間。在徠卡國際價格指南(R1-R10)當中，M2黑漆版被列為R7級別，是極為稀有(Exceptionally Rare)的評級；而本拍品中帶有按鈕回片、不帶自拍的黑漆M2更是罕見，產量少於200台，其價值可媲美MP相機。同樣版本的M2在James Lager Vol.I p.202書中亦有介紹；此機連同黑漆版的Summicron-M 2/50mm(#1926634)，連鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2398', 'M2 Black Paint Consecutive Numbers', 'M2 Black Paint Consecutive Numbers', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_87_6.jpg', '87', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'A pair of original M2 Black Paint with self-timer, in consecutive numbers. One of them (#1005343) even comes with Leica service certificate. They both come with body cap and with normal signs of use and wears, in good working order, very rare.', '此對原裝連號的黑漆M2帶自拍，產於1960年，其中一台M2 (#1005343)附有徠卡原廠的維修單﹔經歷超過半世紀後能尋得兩台相連機身編號的黑漆M2，實屬難得。此對機均帶有機身蓋，露銅的機身使此對黑漆版M2更添歲月韻味。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2399', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_88_7.jpg', '88', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint with self-timer and level rewind. It comes with body cap and leather case, shows signs of use.', '原裝黑漆M2機身，產自1962年。撥杆回片，帶自拍，機械性能良好，連機身蓋及皮套，機身有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2400', 'M2 Black Paint with New York Motor Driver', 'M2 Black Paint with New York Motor Driver', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_89_8.jpg', '89', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 Black Paint was converted by Leitz New York to accept New York Motor Drive. It comes with a New York Motor Drive and body cap.', '本拍品是M2黑漆連紐約徠卡電動捲片馬達，M2機底有電子接點，配合馬達使用，令此機能夠快速上片，大大提高了M機的性能。此機為黑漆版，機頂部份有明顯露銅，令此機更具歷史韻味。同時拍品亦配有機身蓋，運作暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2401', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_90_7.jpg', '90', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint, with self-timer and level rewind. It comes with body cap, with brassing and normal signs of use and wears.', '原裝黑漆M2，產自1964年，帶自拍及撥杆回片，機身部分露銅，有使用痕跡，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2402', 'M2 Chrome with Three Lenses Set', 'M2 Chrome with Three Lenses Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_91_8.jpg', '91', '', '17,000', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 Chrome was made in 1965, comes with 3 lenses: Summicron-M 2/35mm(#2316436) in black, with front and rear caps; Summicron-M 2/50mm(#2107781) in chrome, with filter, front and rear caps, goggles with leather case; Elmar-M 4/90mm(#2089005) in chrome, with front and rear caps; Besides, it completes with two shutter release cords, lens hood(#12504), light meter(#58214), original box, leather case, camera body cap, flash cable, M couplers. With signs of use and wears, in good working order.', '本拍品為產於1965年銀色的M2相機，配有三支鏡頭，包括：有六枚玉之稱的黑色Summicron-M 2/35mm(#2316436)配有鏡頭前後蓋；銀色眼鏡版Summicron-M 2/50mm (#2107781)配有濾鏡，眼鏡連皮套及鏡頭前後蓋；銀色Elmar-M 4/90 (#2089005) 配有鏡頭前後蓋。另備有兩條快門線、適用於以上三支鏡頭使用的遮光罩(#12504)、測光錶(#58214)、原裝包裝盒及皮套、相機蓋、鏡頭連接器及閃燈同步線。機背飾皮脫落。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2403', 'M2-R Chrome', 'M2-R Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_93_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_93_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_93_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_93_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_93_5.jpg', '93', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'M2-R is basically an M2 with self-timer together with rapid film loading system of M4. It comes with body cap, well functioned.', 'M2-R是受美國陸軍委託根據M2基礎進行改良的M2相機，特別加有M4的快速裝片裝置及自拍杆，產量不多。此機配有機身蓋。成色良好，運作暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2404', 'M2-R with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M2-R with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_94_8.jpg', '94', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Rare Leica M2R outfit. During the Vietnam war about 2000 Leica M2\'s were ordered by the US government to Leica. Those cameras were regular M2\'s but with the rapid loading system of the M4\'s cameras and are known as M2 KS even though on the top plate there are no special engravings. At the end the US government didn\'t buy the all lot so the unsold cameras were given to official Leica dealers to be sold to the public. On the top plate after M2 was added an R (M2R) which means &quot;Rapid loading system&quot;. Those cameras were sold with a very late production Summicron\'s 50/2 Dual Range lens with a tall box, so that the camera, the lens and the E.R.case could fit inside. It is very rare to find an original double boxed outfit (camera+matching DR-Summicron) with the original papers and guarantee cards. It comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm (#2357590), goggles and both lens caps, body cap. The camera shows some slight sign of use while the lens is in mint condition.', 'M2-R是受美國陸軍之委託，在M2機上加上M4的快速裝片功能，M2-R的機身編號由1248201至1250200，這一機型也可以視作M2系列的最後一款。帶自拍掣，配有眼鏡版Summicron-M 2/50mm(#2357590)及鏡頭前後蓋。此套機鏡成色優良，連機身蓋，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2405', 'M1 “Sonderausfuhrung”', 'M1 “Sonderausfuhrung”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_95_6.jpg', '95', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Unusaual M1 chrome, no viewfinder and M1 engraving. According to factory record, it belonged to a batch named “Sonderausfuhrung” which means special fitting; only dozens were produced (Please refer to James Lager Vol. I p.215, the serial number of the camera in p.216 is very close to this camera’s). Extremely rare, it comes with body cap.', '此M1外觀特徵像MD，沒有取景框，此批相機在工廠的記錄是Sonderausfuhrung，即特別組合的意思(在 James Lager Vol. I p. 215中有介紹，而p.216中示範的相機機身編號更與此機非常接近)，只生產幾十台，極為稀少。連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2406', 'M1 Chrome', 'M1 Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_96_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_96_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_96_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_96_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_96_5.jpg', '96', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This is a beautiful condition M1 chrome with original factory tag, instruction manual and box.', '一部值得收藏的M1，該機成色極新。此機配有包裝盒、說明書、機身蓋及原廠標籤掛牌，取景框明亮通透，框線清晰。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2407', 'M4-M Black Paint with Leitz New York Motor', 'M4-M Black Paint with Leitz New York Motor', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_97_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_97_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_97_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_97_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_97_5.jpg', '97', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black Paint M4-M with Leitz New York Motor (#02277) in original box, comes with body cap. Show signs of use.', '為可配備Leitz New York電動馬達使用的機種，此機機底有電子接點。機身有輕微使用痕跡，連機身蓋、馬達(#02277)及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2408', 'M4 Black Paint', 'M4 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_98_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_98_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_98_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_98_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_98_5.jpg', '98', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 was produced in 1970; it comes with box, certificate, instruction manual and body cap, in mint condition and good working order.', '此拍品產於1970年，是擁有厚重感的黑漆版M4，操作功能正常，成色極新。連包裝盒，證書，說明書及機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2409', 'MDa Chrome Consecutive Numbers', 'MDa Chrome Consecutive Numbers', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_100_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_100_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_100_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_100_4.jpg', '100', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The MDa is basically an M4 without rangefinder viewfinder, self-timer and frame line selector. These two cameras are in consecutive numbers; for serial number 1379087 comes with a special slotted baseplate. Both cameras come with body caps, in good working order.', 'MDa是徠卡M機中的特別機型，設計以M4作為藍本，沒有觀景窗、自拍功能及框線變換杆。此對MDa為相連號，其中一台(#1379087)的底蓋具備撥帶，本對機連同機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2410', 'M5 Black “50 Years”', 'M5 Black “50 Years”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_102_6.jpg', '102', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'This camera is M5 in black chrome with “50 Jahre” engraved on the front plate. It comes with papers, body cap and matching number box. In mint condition and good working order.', '此機為紀念徠卡50週年的M5相機，產自1973年，機前刻有「50 Jahre」字樣。此機成色良好，操作功能正常，連同機身蓋，原廠包裝及說明書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2411', 'M4-P Three Editions Set', 'M4-P Three Editions Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_105_10.jpg', '105', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lot includes three editions M4-P: the first one is M4-P “EVEREST 82” (#1587000); the second one is M4-P Black Chrome (#1587777); and the third one is M4-P “70th Anniversary 1919-1983” (#1643150). They all come with box, papers and strap, in like new condition.', '此套裝共有三台M4-P;第一台是M4-P(#1587000)為紀念加拿大探險隊於1982年成功登上珠穆朗瑪峰而推出的紀念版，全球限量200台，機頂上刻有白色山形的標記，標記內刻有「EVEREST 82」字樣及代表加拿大的楓葉圖案，連證書﹔第二台為黑色版本M4-P(#1587777)﹔第三台是為紀念徠卡1913年第一台135格式的相機面世而生產的銀色M4-P 70週年版(#1643150)，機背後刻有C478的特別號碼，以及”Leica 1913-1983”的字樣，連證書。全部相機均連同包裝及相機帶，成色極新，收藏良品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2412', 'M4-P Chrome', 'M4-P Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_106_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_106_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_106_3.jpg', '106', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Never opened with factory seal, rarely seen.', '全新未經開封的M4-P銀色，在現今市面已是罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2413', 'M6 Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm “Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck”', 'M6 Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm “Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_107_8.jpg', '107', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica M6 Titanium (#1907319) comes with Titanium Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#3538134) and lens cap. The particular camera was made in 1992. This special version of the M6 in a grey titanium finished with a matching lens, which is very resilient to hard use, was introduced at Photokina in 1992. This exact camera is illustrated in Leica Specialist Paul Henry Van Hasbroeck’s “Leica in Color” p.94 and comes with a copy of “Leica in Color” signed by Paul Henry Van Hasbroeck. This was the particular camera used by Paul Henry Van Hasbroeck for the last 20 or so years. The camera was all taped up hence shows little marks of wears. Extremely rare.', '此套鈦版M6連Summilux-M 1.4/35mm(#3538134)由徠卡相機界享負盛名的權威Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck擁有及使用超過二十多年。在1998年，他已將此套相機刊登在他的著作“Leica in Color”中的第94頁，此套機在Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck 20多年的珍藏下，除了輕微的使用痕跡外，整體成色佳，而且也附帶了一本由Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck為此套相機親筆題字及簽名的著作“Leica in Color”，連鏡頭蓋。<br />\r\n此套鈦版相機不僅是Leica的特別版相機，而且由著名徠卡權威所使用及擁有，更被刊登在書上，為此機鏡增添收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2414', 'M6 Titanium with Titanium lenses (various)', 'M6 Titanium with Titanium lenses (various)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_108_11.jpg', '108', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'This outfit is including two M6 cameras in titanium finished and five titanium lenses as well.<br />\r\nFor the M6 (#2169005) covered with ostrich leather, with box, certificate and strap; the other M6 (#1929737) with black Leica logo and black speed dial; completes with box, papers, strap and plastic box. Five titanium lenses are: Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#3602295) with box, hood, leather case and both caps; Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#3710410) with box and papers, both caps and hood with cap; Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH (#3886634) with box and papers, leather case, hood and lens rear cap; Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#3690101) with leather case and both caps; lastly, a Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH (#3923617) with box and papers, leather case and both caps.<br />\r\nWhole set is in like new condition.', '此套鈦版機鏡包括兩部鈦版M6及五支鈦版鏡頭，如此齊全的鈦版套裝，市面極為罕見。<br />\r\n其中M6 (#2169005)機身覆以駝鳥皮，連包裝證書及頸帶﹔另一台M6鈦版(#1929737)，其機頂轉盤及正面的徠卡標誌均為黑色，連同包裝說明書、頸帶及膠盒。套機分別連同五支鈦版鏡頭，分別是: Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#3602295)，配包裝盒、遮光罩、皮套及鏡頭前後蓋﹔Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#3710410)包裝證書全齊，配遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭前後蓋﹔Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH (#3886634)連包裝證書、皮筒、遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋﹔Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#3690101)配皮套及前後蓋﹔最後Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH (#3923617)包裝證書全齊，連皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2415', 'M7 0.72 Chrome Special', 'M7 0.72 Chrome Special', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_110_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_110_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_110_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_110_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_110_5.jpg', '110', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'The M7 Special in chrome with bigger “Leica” engraved on the top plate. It comes with certificate, papers, strap, body cap and matching number box in like new condition.', '此機為特別訂製的M7，機頂刻上復古的「LEICA」刻字(此字體之前通常用於M1 – M4機頂上)，字體較大。連同機身蓋，包裝證書齊全及有相機掛帶，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2416', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint Betriebsk', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint Betriebsk', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_111_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_111_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_111_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_111_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_111_5.jpg', '111', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This MP is for Leica factory internal use or test only, “Bestriebsk” is engraved on the top plate. It comes with a matching number box which is different from the official one, no sale sticker is included. This set comes with box, papers, strap and battery, in like new condition.', '此MP機的機頂上刻有「Betriebsk」字樣，是供予徠卡工廠內部使用的相機。此機連同與機身號碼相同的包裝盒，因只供工廠內部使用，盒上並沒有貼上正式銷售時的貼紙，此類MP工廠測試用機在市面上十分罕見。連同包裝、相機帶、電池及證書，運作暢順，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2417', 'MP 0.58 Chrome', 'MP 0.58 Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_112_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_112_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_112_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_112_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_112_5.jpg', '112', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a current version of MP chrome in viewfinder magnifications of 0.58X, with full packing, body cap and papers, in like new condition.', '產量較少的現行版MP銀色機身配以0.58線框，包裝證書連機身蓋齊全，操作功能正常，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2418', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_113_6.jpg', '113', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'A current version of black paint MP with 0.72 frame line, bright viewfinder, comes with body cap. In mint condition.', '現行版黑漆MP機身配以0.72線框，取景器通透明亮，性能完好，連機身蓋。數字9在中國有長長久久的吉祥意思，而此機7位機身號中的有5個是9字，寓意非常吉祥。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2419', 'MP 0.85 Chrome with Top plate', 'MP 0.85 Chrome with Top plate', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_114_6.jpg', '114', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'It is a classic MP in a la carte version. Unlike the original design, its top plate has no engraving. It comes with body cap and the original top plate, in like new condition.', '經典的徠卡MP機身，物主費盡心機，將其原有的銀色機送回原廠換上沒有刻字的機頂蓋，使本來低調的MP更為低調，此機最特別之處是附有原裝訂有相同號碼已被更換的機頂，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2420', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_116_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_116_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_116_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_116_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_116_5.jpg', '116', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Approximately 350 pieces were made, comes with viewfinder, center filter, rear cap, instruction and box, in mint condition.', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm鏡頭約生產350支，此鏡連取景器、中灰鏡、說明書、鏡頭後蓋及包裝盒。成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2421', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_117_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_117_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_117_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_117_4.jpg', '117', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Approximately 350 pieces were made, comes with viewfinder, center filter, both caps, instruction and box. It is in mint condition.', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm鏡頭，約只生產350支。此鏡連取景器、中灰鏡、前後蓋、說明書及包裝盒，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2422', 'Super-Angulon-M 4/21mm Chrome &amp; Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Black', 'Super-Angulon-M 4/21mm Chrome &amp; Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_118_6.jpg', '118', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'These lenses are the earliest wide angle lenses of Leica, with minimum focal distance to 0.4m. The goggles were modified later, can be used directly on M Camera, very rare. The chrome M 4/21mm lens comes with both caps and the black M 3.4/21mm lens comes with both caps and goggles.', '此兩款鏡頭原是由施耐德公司代工，屬徠卡最早期的超廣角鏡頭，最短對焦距離為0.4米。眼鏡版是經後期精密加工，可直接用於M機身上，由於造工複雜且困難，仍流傳於市面上的寥寥可數。銀色M 4/21mm連鏡頭前後蓋；黑色M 3.4/21mm連鏡頭前及後蓋、眼鏡位置有輕微掉漆。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2423', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_120_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_120_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_120_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_120_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_120_5.jpg', '120', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'Chrome Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH was launched in 2008 with small batch of production, very rare. It comes with hood, hood cap and lens rear cap, with 6 bits in like new condition.', '徠卡於2008年特別生產了一少批銀色版本的Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH供應予市場，非常罕有。鏡頭帶電子接點、遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋，成色如新，屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2424', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Prototype', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_121_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_121_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_121_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_121_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_121_5.jpg', '121', '', '495,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH prototype lens made in Canada with built-in sunshade. Serial number 002 is the pieces they made under the optical formula 874. This rare Canadian prototype lens was from 1980s, which never went into commercial production. This lens comes with both caps and lens leather case in mint condition and the lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡為1980年代加拿大製的Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH的原型鏡，有內置遮光罩。鏡頭編號中首三位數字為光學技術之編號，尾三位數字的002表示本拍品是該光學技術下所生產的第二枚鏡頭，相信產量極少。而且在正式投產的28mm鏡頭中，加拿大只生產了Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm鏡頭，而非f/2光圈，故此枚加拿大製的Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH的原型鏡可謂絕無僅有。此鏡成色極佳，連鏡頭前後蓋及鏡頭皮套，並經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2425', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Black Consecutive Numbers', 'Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH Black Consecutive Numbers', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_122_6.jpg', '122', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'These are the current version of Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH lenses in consecutive numbers and in brand new condition. They complete with all packing and papers, hood, hood cap and both caps.', '此對連號現行版的Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH鏡頭，帶6-Bit電子接點，包裝證書齊全，帶遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭前後蓋，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2426', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_123_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_123_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_123_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_123_4.jpg', '123', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'Only 500 pieces made in chrome, very rare. This lens is in like new condition with 6-bit coding. Completes with both caps, papers, case and maker\'s box.', '銀色鏡身，只生產500枝，產量稀少。成色如新，帶電子接點。連原裝包裝盒、皮筒、鏡頭前後蓋及證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2427', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_124_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_124_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_124_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_124_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_124_5.jpg', '124', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'This is one of the representable lenses in the M-series. It is a zoom lens with tri focal length positions, E49. Comes with both caps, in like new condition.', '此鏡為徠卡M系列的鏡頭其中一款代表鏡頭，可以三段變焦，口徑為E49。此拍品有趣的是鏡頭編號包含1997，是香港回歸之年份。此鏡連鏡頭前及後蓋，成色優良，為使用或收藏之佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2428', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_125_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_125_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_125_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_125_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_125_5.jpg', '125', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'This Steel Rim Chrome comes with hood (#12522H), box and both caps, in mint- condition.', '銀色鋼咀Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鏡頭配有遮光罩(#12522H)、包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透明亮，由於當年產量較少，有如此包裝齊全及品相佳的鋼咀鏡頭已是十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2429', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_126_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_126_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_126_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_126_4.jpg', '126', '', '229,900', null, null, null, null, 'Black Steel Rim is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm, few dozens of pieces made. It comes with box, filter, both caps and OLLUX hood, in mint condition. Extremely rare.', '黑色鋼咀M 1.4/35mm是第一代Summilux-M鏡頭，產量稀少，約數十支，此鏡連包裝盒、濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及OLLUX 遮光罩。如此配件齊全，成色佳的黑色鋼咀，實屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2430', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_127_6.jpg', '127', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'This lens has clear glass, comes with filter, original box, both caps, in mint condition, very rare.', '銀色鋼咀Summilux-M 1.4/35mm配有濾鏡、包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋，加上玻璃通透，當年產量較少，有如此包裝齊全及品相佳的鋼咀鏡頭已是十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2431', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_128_6.jpg', '128', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Black Steel Rim is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm. Few dozens of pieces made. It comes with filter, both caps and hood (#12522), with few signs of use on barrel.', '第一代黑色鋼咀鏡頭，產量僅數十支，極為珍貴罕見。此鏡連濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩(#12522)。鏡身雖有輕微使用痕跡，但玻璃清澈。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2432', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim “Unusual Black Rim”', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim “Unusual Black Rim”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_129_6.jpg', '129', '', '826,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a very rare and unusual Leitz first type Summilux-M 1.4/35mm rangefinder lens in black, with serial number 1765637. Only a very few example of this “steel–rim” Summilux 35mm lenses were made with black steel rim. Please compare James Lager Vol.II p.160 for a black steel rim lens with serial number 1765667. The lens offered here is in fantastic and all original condition. There are only few very light marks of wear in the black paint finished of infinity lock and goggles frames. Rare early black paint lens with perfect optics in original maker box. Matching with early black paint M3 or MP cameras. Comes with OLLUX Hood, both caps and box, in mint condition. The lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '這是一支罕見且不平常的第一代Summilux-M 1.4/35mm黑色鋼咀鏡頭，鏡頭前鋼圈為黑色，通常黑或銀色鋼咀鏡頭的前鋼圈為銀色，但此鏡頭卻擁有與眾不同的黑色鋼圈；在James Lager Vol.II p.160中也有黑色鋼咀(黑鋼圈)，鏡身號碼1765667的介紹。這款第一代黑色鋼咀帶黑鋼圈的鏡頭只有數支，是為配在早期黑漆M3及黑漆MP而產的樣版。此鏡是原裝黑色，同時黑色的色澤與早期M3及MP都非常相似及匹配。此鏡頭配有OLLUX遮光罩、前後蓋及包裝盒，資料由Lars Netopil提供並經由Lars Netopil鑒證。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2433', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_130_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_130_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_130_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_130_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_130_5.jpg', '130', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is clear, in good working order and mint- condition. It comes with goggles and both caps, extremely rare.', '銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鋼咀眼鏡版，玻璃狀態良好，調焦環順暢。連眼鏡及鏡頭前後蓋，十分珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2434', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_131_6.jpg', '131', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Around 2,000 units were made. It comes with box, papers, leather case, hood (#12587), hood cap and both caps, in like new condition.', '產量約2,000支。此鏡連包裝盒、說明書、證書、皮筒、遮光罩(#12587)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。鏡身成色極佳，玻璃通透，收藏或自用皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2435', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_132_7.jpg', '132', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with a misprinted original box (Detail please refers to the pictures). It is also comes with papers, leather case, hood (#12587), hood cap and both caps, in mint condition.', '本拍品的Summilux雙非球面鏡頭貨號為11873，而其包裝盒上所標示之鏡頭名稱與正常有所出入，並沒有帶ASPHERICAL字樣，出現錯體字樣(見圖)，為此鏡有趣之處。連包裝盒、說明書、證書、皮筒、遮光罩(#12587)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。鏡身成色極佳，玻璃通透，收藏或自用皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2436', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_134_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_134_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_134_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_134_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_134_5.jpg', '134', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is early version Summicron-M 2/35mm black in 8 elements, made in Canada, in good working order. Beside the front cap and keeper, comes with unusual ITDOO lens hood with box.', '較早期的加拿大製黑色八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，調焦暢順。此鏡除了鏡頭前蓋及膠盅外，所配有遮光罩ITDOO連原裝盒是較早期罕見的。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2437', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_135_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_135_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_135_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_135_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_135_5.jpg', '135', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare black 8-elements Canada Summicron-M 2/35mm. Footage scale numerals are red, comes with keeper in mint condition.', '此款鏡頭是徠卡Summicron系列中的經典之作。鏡頭由八片六組組成，並使用當時透光度及成本極高的螢石玻璃所造，故被用家稱為「八枚玉」。此鏡為加拿大製，調焦環為紅字，產量非常少。加上品相良好，為收藏佳品。此鏡頭連膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2438', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_136_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_136_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_136_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_136_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_136_5.jpg', '136', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'This black paint lens is from the last batch of Summicron-M 2/35mm (8 Elements), made in Germany. Only small quantity was produced in Germany. It comes with lens keeper, hood with box and front cap, glass clear. Very rare.', '徠卡於1969年生產最後一批八枚玉鏡頭，此拍品正是最後一年製造的產品。德國生產的Summicron-M 2/35mm黑色八枚玉鏡頭，產量極少。配有鏡頭膠盅、鏡頭前蓋及IROOA遮光罩連蓋連盒，而且玻璃通透。如此品相優良的鏡頭在市面已經十分罕見，屬收藏家涉獵的銘鏡極品之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2439', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_137_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_137_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_137_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_137_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_137_5.jpg', '137', '', '121,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early Summicron-M 2/35mm 8 elements in red scale with goggles. This is a highly collectable piece from a rare small batch production made in Germany with both brass focusing knob and black paint lens flange! The rear cap is also included. With light signs of use.', '早期德國製的眼鏡版八枚玉鏡頭，當中黑色產量極少。此鏡調焦環為紅字，更特別的是鏡頭卡口外圈是黑漆，而後期版本則是鍍銀，玻璃通透，調焦按鈕有輕微露銅﹔連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2440', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_138_6.jpg', '138', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Very few black Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements with red scale, the lens flange is in black paint. Comes with leather case, goggles and lens front cap. Cleansing marks on glass and normal marks of use on barrel.', '較早期的加拿大製黑色八枚玉眼鏡版鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，更特別之處是此鏡卡口外圈是黑漆的，而後期的版本則為鍍銀；鏡頭品相良好，有正常使用痕跡。連鏡頭皮套及鏡頭前蓋，此鏡產量非常稀少。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2441', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome Set (8 elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome Set (8 elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_139_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_139_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_139_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_139_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_139_5.jpg', '139', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'These are Summicron-M 2/35mm 8 elements, both come with goggles, both caps and box. One was made in Germany and the other was made in Canada, both with clear glass in mint condition.', '此對銀色八枚玉均帶有眼鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及包裝。當中一支由加拿大產而另一支則由德國產，兩支鏡頭成色上佳，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2442', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_140_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_140_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_140_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_140_4.jpg', '140', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'This Summicron-M 2/35mm chrome “7 elements” lens was made in Germany, comes with box, leather case, both caps and hood (#12524), in mint condition.', '德國製銀色七枚玉鏡頭，帶包裝、皮套、鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩(#12524)，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2443', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_141_6.jpg', '141', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This is a current version of Noctilux-M, comes with full packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '徠卡最新型的最大光圈Noctilux-M鏡頭，質素極佳，散景迷人。此鏡全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2444', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_142_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_142_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_142_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_142_4.jpg', '142', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'It is the first version of Noctilux-M 1/50mm lens in E58. It comes with both caps and hood, in mint condition.', '第一代的Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E58口徑。玻璃通透明亮，調焦環順暢，品相極佳。連外置遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2445', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_143_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_143_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_143_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_143_4.jpg', '143', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is the second version of Noctilux-M1/50mm lens in E60. It comes with box, papers, hood and both caps.', '第二代的Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E60口徑。連原包裝盒及證書、外置遮光罩、鏡頭前及後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2446', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_144_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_144_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_144_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_144_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_144_5.jpg', '144', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'The 4th version of Noctilux-M 1/50mm lens made in Canada in E60, built-in lens hood, comes with leather case and both lens caps, in mint condition.', '第四代的Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E60口徑，內置遮光罩，成色極佳。連鏡頭皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2447', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_145_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_145_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_145_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_145_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_145_7.jpg', '145', '', '157,300', null, null, null, null, 'Around 1500 units were made, very rare. It completes with hood and both lens caps, with hairline scratches.', '此鏡為早期的Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm鏡頭，產量極少，大約只有1,500支。當中有兩片手磨非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，成像質素極為出色。此鏡配有鏡頭前後蓋及外置遮光罩。整體成色不錯。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2448', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_146_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_146_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_146_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_146_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_146_5.jpg', '146', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'Around 1,500 units were made. The glass is clean and completes with box, keeper, series 8 filter, front lens cap and lens hood, in mint condition, very rare.', '此鏡為早期的Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm鏡頭，產量極少，大約只有1,500支。當中有兩片手磨非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，成像質素極為出色。此鏡配有包裝盒、膠盅、series 8濾鏡、鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩， 成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2449', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_147_6.jpg', '147', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Early version made in black paint and black chrome, with clean glass and very light used marks, comes with lens hood and hood cap, also lens rear cap.', '早期生產的黑漆鏡頭，鏡身分別以黃銅及合金兩種金屬製造。鏡身有輕微露銅，玻璃十分通透。連鏡頭後蓋及遮光罩連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2450', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_148_7.jpg', '148', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'Clean glass, with very light marks of use. It comes with hood and hood cap, lens rear cap.', '黑漆鏡頭，只有極輕微使用痕跡，帶遮光罩連蓋、濾鏡及鏡頭底蓋。在市場上仍可找到如此成色的黑漆Summilux-M鏡頭，實在十分難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2451', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black and Gold Version', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black and Gold Version', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_149_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_149_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_149_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_149_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_149_5.jpg', '149', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'A gold plated Summilux-M1.4/50mm lens which has never been opened. Complete with lens hood, hood cap, rear cap, matching number box and papers in new condition. The lens sealed in unopen plastic bag.', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm的鍍金版鏡頭，有遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭後蓋及原裝包裝證書。此鏡包裝膠袋從未拆封，鏡頭全新未經使用，非常罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2452', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm 70 Years Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm 70 Years Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_150_8.jpg', '150', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 70th year of the first 135mm camera produced in 1913. No more than 500 pieces of Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens was made in year 1983. “Leica 1913-1983” is engraved on the lens barrel. This lens completes with box and certificate, lens rear cap, lens hood and hood cap in mint condition.', '為紀念首台135mm相機Ur-Leica於1913年面世，徠卡於1983年發行Summilux-M 1.4/50mm黑色70週年紀念版，產量只有500支。有遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭後蓋及原裝包裝證書，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2453', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_151_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_151_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_151_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_151_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_151_5.jpg', '151', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'Black Paint single scale rigid lens was made in Germany, raw brass at the rear of the lens. There is a same version lens with its serial number close to this lens illustrated in James Larger Vol.II p.167. It comes with front cap and keeper in mint condition. Extremely rare.', '德國製的Summicron-M 2/5cm黑漆版鏡頭，為Rigid版本，鏡身分別用上黃銅及鎂合金兩種物料所造，鏡頭後卡口為黃銅，十分稀有。加上此鏡外觀極新，是近年拍賣會上難得一見的精品。在James Larger Vol. II p.167有與此鏡頭號相近的同款鏡頭介紹。此鏡連鏡頭膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2454', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint Consecutive Numbers', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Rigid Black Paint Consecutive Numbers', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_152_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_152_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_152_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_152_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_152_5.jpg', '152', '', '365,800', null, null, null, null, 'This kind of lens was made for MP Black Paint in 1958. Rigid version. Black Paint and brass bass-mount. Rarely to find a pair of Summicron-M 2/5cm fully original Black Paint with brass bass-mount in consecutive numbers on market. These lenses come with both caps, for lens #1587388 comes with a filter as well. Show signs of use.', '在收藏市場上要找一對連號鏡頭已是不易，要找一對黑漆的連號更是極難，而能夠在黑漆裡覓得為MP黑漆配套而生產的僅極少數銅卡口的相連號鏡頭，更是比登天還難。此對相連號碼的德國製Summicron-M 2/5cm黑漆版鏡頭，均產於1958年，是Rigid版本。鏡身分別使用黃銅及鎂合金兩種物料所造，鏡頭卡口為黃銅，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2455', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_153_6.jpg', '153', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is second version of Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid in black paint, comes with both caps, with signs of use.', '此鏡為第二代Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid的黑漆版，連鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透，鏡身有使用痕跡。此款鏡頭當年主要生產銀色，在市面上能找到黑漆鏡頭實在難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2456', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_154_6.jpg', '154', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This Rigid lens was made in Germany in 1964, with both caps, in good working condition.', '德國製的Summicron-M 2/50mm黑漆版鏡頭，此拍品為Rigid版本。鏡身使用黃銅及鎂合金兩種物料所造。連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2457', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_156_6.jpg', '156', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Second version Summicron-M 2/50mm Dual Range lens with original box, goggles and cap, lens rear cap, glass clear in mint- condition.', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR鏡頭連眼鏡、包裝盒、遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋。玻璃通透，品相優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2458', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_157_7.jpg', '157', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This is the third version of Summicron-M 2/50mm lens, in mint condition with clear glass. The focusing scales are printed on the ring, which is different from the normal lenses with numbers engraved on focusing ring. This lens comes with both caps, hood and hood cap.', '此鏡為Summicron-M 2/50mm的第三代，鏡頭成色極佳，玻璃通透。最特別之處為調焦環上的數字、景深尺及產地皆為絲印，與一般版本採用刻字的方法有所不同，相信市面極為罕見。此鏡連同鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2459', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_158_6.jpg', '158', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The serial number of this lens is 3167264* stands for 3167264. It refers to the second batch production, comes with both caps and box in mint condition.', '此鏡身編號是3167264*，表示3167264的鏡頭工廠共生產過兩次，而這支帶「*」的鏡頭便是第二次生產的貨品，市面上極少見。此鏡頭連鏡頭前後蓋及包裝盒，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2460', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_159_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_159_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_159_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_159_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_159_5.jpg', '159', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 50th Anniversary of Summicron, this lens was launched and only 500 units were made, very rare. This set comes with box, all papers, leather case, presentation box, hood (#12585), hood cap and both caps, in brand new condition.', '此鏡頭是為了紀念Summicron鏡頭系列面世50週年而生產的紀念版，限量500套。其外形沿用50年代Summicron Rigid鏡頭第二代的設計，但內裡的玻璃則採用現代Summicron鏡頭的光學設計與技術結合而成，極為獨特。此鏡頭配有包裝盒、證書、皮筒、內盒、遮光罩(#12585)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2461', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_160_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_160_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_160_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_160_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_160_5.jpg', '160', '', '36,300', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of M 1.4/75mm. Made in Canada, comes with original box, certificate, lens hood and both lens caps.', '加拿大生產的第一代Summilux-M 1.4/75mm人像王鏡頭，其遮光罩是外置的，市面較少。配有原包裝盒、證書、遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋，極輕微使用痕跡，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2462', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_161_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_161_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_161_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_161_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_161_5.jpg', '161', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada with built-in hood, comes with original box, leather case and both caps. This lens is in mint condition.', '加拿大生產的Summilux-M 1.4/75mm人像王鏡頭，連內置遮光罩。配有原包裝盒、皮筒及鏡頭前後蓋，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2463', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_162_7.jpg', '162', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early black painted lens, made in Canada with built-in hood. This lens comes with both caps and filter, with normal marks of use and clear glass.', '第一代第二版的Summicron-M 2/90mm黑漆鏡頭，產於加拿大，連內置遮光罩。鏡身分別以黃銅及鎂合金製造。鏡身有使用痕跡，部份露銅，玻璃通透。此鏡連濾鏡及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2464', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_163_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_163_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_163_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_163_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_163_5.jpg', '163', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early black painted lens made in Canada with built-in hood, shows normal marks of use and clear glass. With both caps and filter.', '少見的黑漆鏡頭，產於加拿大，連內置遮光罩。鏡身分別以黃銅及鎂合金製造。鏡身有使用痕跡，部份露銅，玻璃通透，連濾鏡，鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2465', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_164_6.jpg', '164', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with a misprinted original box which shows place of origin is Germany, but this lens was produced in Canada. Also it comes with instruction, certificate, leather case and both caps, in mint- condition.', '此鏡的有趣之處是印在包裝盒上之產地與鏡頭有所出入:此鏡貨號為11884，於德國生產﹔但包裝盒上則標示此鏡於加拿大生產。出現錯體字樣的情況是較少見的。此鏡連包裝證書、說明書、皮筒及鏡頭前後蓋。成色極佳，玻璃通透，收藏或自用皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2466', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Prototype', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_165_6.jpg', '165', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm, it carries many prototype features different from the production products: 1) Aperture to f/16 instead of f/22. 2) Diameter is E43 instead of E46. 3) Name ring is horizontal instead of slanting. 4) The height of both lens and lens hood are shorter than the normal version. 5) With “15” focusing distance on the focus ring. 6) The first 3 digits of the serial number which indicates the optical formula is 321. It comes with both lens caps.', '此鏡為 Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm的原型版，它多處特徵均與正式生產的產品不同：光圈及景深尺最小為16，但正常量產版的則為f/22；拍品口徑為E43，而正式產品是E46；鏡頭前數字環為平口，正式為斜口；鏡身較短，遮光罩亦較正式產品短；調焦環數字比正式產品多出15m一檔；該鏡頭的光學技術研發編號為321。另外，此拍品的鏡頭編號並非在正常生產之列，產量甚少。連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2467', 'Hektor-M 4.5/13.5cm Prototype', 'Hektor-M 4.5/13.5cm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_166_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_166_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_166_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_166_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_166_5.jpg', '166', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'This Leitz Hektor-M 4.5/13.5cm black paint prototype lens made in 1949 with experimental A42 front mount, which is five years earlier than the first M3 that launched in 1954. This lens is quite different from the official version; firstly, this lens is covered by leather, front ring is longer than the later version and this barrel is made by brass, which is extremely rare. This lens comes with hood, hood cap and rear cap as well. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此黑漆原型版鏡頭生產於1949年，比第一台M卡口的M3早5年出現，擁有試驗性A42鏡頭前環，相信此鏡是供予M3機使用的試驗版。此原型版鏡頭有數個特徵是後期量產版所沒有的，鏡頭前部較長，鏡身以黃銅製造，覆蓋飾皮。此鏡頭配遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭前蓋及乳白色鏡頭後蓋。非常罕見。經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2468', 'MS-Optical Sonnetar 1.1/50mm Prototype', 'MS-Optical Sonnetar 1.1/50mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_171_6.jpg', '171', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'The lens is manufactured by Japan MS-Optical R&D. This is the prototype lens of MS-Optical Sonnetar 1.1/50mm, with serial number “000” engraved. The lens is in Leica-M mount, with both lens cap, hood, instruction manual and paper box.', '此鏡是日本著名的宮崎光學公司研發MS-optical Sonnetar 1.1/50mm鏡頭的原型版，鏡頭編號為「000」，配供徠卡M相機用的卡口。連同鏡頭前後蓋、遮光罩、說明書及包裝外盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2469', 'Super-Angulon 4/2.1cm Prototype', 'Super-Angulon 4/2.1cm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_31_6.jpg', '31', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early prototype lens with prototype serial number 5597436, using early gold coating. “Ernst Leitz GmbH. Wetzlar Super-Angulon” was engraved on the name ring where both capital letters and small letters were used, but the production products were changed the engraving into all capital letters to “LEITZ WETZLAR SUPER-ANGULON”. Also, there is an engraving on the rear of the lens which is absent on the production products. This lens comes with both caps.', '此原型版鏡頭在市場上非常稀少，鏡頭特徵與量產版有明顯差別：在鍍膜方面，此鏡使用極早期的偏金黃色鍍膜；其數字環上刻有以大小寫的寫法「Ernst Leitz GmbH. Wetzlar Super-Angulon」字樣，是早期用於徠卡鏡頭的刻法，而正式生產時，已改用「LEITZ WETZLAR SUPER-ANGULON」刻法，而且此拍品的後組有刻字，但在量產版並沒有此特徵，甚為罕見。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2470', 'Stemar 3.5/3.3cm Outfit Midland', 'Stemar 3.5/3.3cm Outfit Midland', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_32_7.jpg', '32', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'A very rare stereo equipment made by Leitz Canada Ltd. Midland which comes with Stemar OISBO 3.5/3.3cm (#1124334), OIEGO stereo lens hood and both lens caps, OIMPO beam splitter (#1393), 3.3cm viewfinder, everything are in original leather case. This outfit also comes with IMPUU Elmar 3.5/5cm stereo lens with box and both lens caps (Please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.287), in mint condition.', '徠茲加拿大Midland產的立體鏡OISBO 3.5/3.3cm(#1124334) 連OIEGO立體鏡遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋、OIMPO 分束器 (#1393)、3.3cm 取景器，配以原裝小皮箱。另外，此立體鏡套裝還配備IMPUU Elmar 3.5/5cm立體鏡連包裝盒及前後蓋。(可參考James Lager Vol. III p.287中介紹)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2471', 'Summicron 2/35mm Chrome 8 elements', 'Summicron 2/35mm Chrome 8 elements', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_33_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_33_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_33_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_33_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_33_5.JPG', '33', '', '29,040', null, null, null, null, 'Screw mount, 8 elements. Only 577 units made. This lens is clear, with both caps, in mint condition.', '徠卡經典鏡頭–螺絲口的八枚玉，全球僅生產577支，最短對焦距離為1米，由八片六組鏡片所組成，其中鏡片更使用透光度和成本相當高的螢石製造，故被稱為八枚玉。鏡頭外觀品相良好，玻璃通透，配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2472', 'Summarit 1.5/5cm Chrome Midland', 'Summarit 1.5/5cm Chrome Midland', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_34_6.jpg', '34', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'This is a later version of Summarit 1.5/5cm, made in Midland Canada. It comes with both caps.', '此鏡為Summarit 1.5/5cm後期版本，由加拿大Midland製造，市面少見。連同鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2473', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_35_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_35_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_35_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_35_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_35_5.jpg', '35', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'Rigid Nickel Summar 2/5cm is the first version of Summar from 1933-1934, the number produced were quite small. Comes with SOOMP hood, both lens caps, in mint- condition.', 'Rigid Summar 2/5cm鎳是第一代的Summar版，生產年份短，產量少。連SOOMP遮光罩，鏡頭前後蓋；成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2474', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_36_6.jpg', '36', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version of Rigid Nickel Summar lens, comes with clamping filter in brass, E. Leitz New York hood in black and both caps, very rare, in mint- condition.', '此鏡是第一代的Rigid Summar 2/5cm，鏡身以鎳金屬製成，配有以黃銅製造的螺絲夾環型濾鏡、E. Leitz New York遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。光圈葉順滑，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2475', 'Summar 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summar 2/5cm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_37_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_37_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_37_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_37_4.jpg', '37', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Summar rigid chrome 186481a - very rare and fully original lens in rare chrome finish. The &quot;a&quot; indicates a duplicate serial number. The name ring of the lens in chrome finished as well. The lens was later coated. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此銀色Summar 2/5cm鏡頭是非常少有及完全原裝狀態，其鏡頭編號後面帶有「a」字，表示重複的鏡頭編號。此鏡頭外觀有別於第一代的銀色Summar 2/5cm，其鏡身甚至鏡頭前環皆為銀色(通常號碼環為黑色)，而且採用後期鍍膜，配有前後蓋；經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2476', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_38_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_38_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_38_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_38_4.jpg', '38', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Rigid Nickel Summar 2/5cm is the first version of Summar from 1933-1934, the number produced were quite small. Comes with front and rear caps, original Leitz red box which is very rare, in mint- condition.', 'Rigid Summar 2/5cm鎳是第一代的Summar版，生產年份短，產量少。連鏡頭前後蓋及非常罕有的原廠徠卡鏡頭盒。鏡頭有正常使用痕跡，鏡身成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2477', 'Summar 2/5cm Nickel &amp; Chrome Set', 'Summar 2/5cm Nickel &amp; Chrome Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_2.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_39_6.jpg', '39', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'Both nickel and chrome Summar 2/5cm Rigid are the first version of Summar 2/5cm from 1933-1934. Small numbers were produced. This is a set of chrome (#193311) and nickel (#193322) collapsible Summar 2/5cm lenses with black front rim. With symmetry serial numbers, both come with front and rear caps. In excellent condition.', '鎳及鉻的Summar 2/5cm Rigid版是第一代的Summar 2/5cm，出產年份在1933-1934間，產量少。此對鏡頭分別是早期銀色的Summar 2/5cm(#193311)及鎳版Summar 2/5cm(#193322)。前者鏡身使用鎂合金所製，後者則以鎳金屬所製成，它們的共通點為黃銅製造的黑色鏡咀。此拍品最有趣之處在於經過八十年後，還能配對出編號極之相近，且數字排列對稱的鏡頭，非常難得。配有鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透，成色上佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2478', 'Summicron 2/50mm Chrome Prototype', 'Summicron 2/50mm Chrome Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_6.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_40_7.jpg', '40', '', '424,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is the prototype of Summicron 2/50mm. No name and serial number were engraved on the name ring. Shows apertures to f32 on both lens head and depth of field scale. Height of the lens is 5mm shorter than both Summitar and Summicron, the diameter is 3mm narrower than Summitar, early gold coating, the radian of the glass is different from to both Summitar and Summicron. This lens comes with both front and rear lens cap, extremely rare.', '此鏡為早期Summicron 2/50mm的原型版鏡頭，生產年期估計於Summitar及Summicron之間，其外觀與前期的Summitar及後期的Summicron有明顯差別。此鏡鏡身上並無刻有任何編號及型號，最小光圈的刻度及景深尺同時顯示為f/32，這是極罕見的原型版產品；它的鏡身比Summitar及Summicron均短5mm；玻璃直徑比Summitar窄3mm；鏡身有一條凹槽，而且此鏡的鍍膜為早期黃金鍍膜；鏡面弧度較圓。以上特徵與前/後期生產的版本不同，加上此鏡成色上佳，連鏡頭前後蓋，是極為難得的收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2479', 'Summitar 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summitar 2/5cm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_41_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_41_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_41_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_41_4.jpg', '41', '', '4,720', null, null, null, null, 'A very nice post war coated Summitar with both caps. In mint condition.', '此鏡屬於後期的Summitar鏡頭，最小光圈為f/16。鏡頭配有前後蓋，調焦暢順，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2480', 'Summicron 2/50mm Chrome', 'Summicron 2/50mm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_42_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_42_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_42_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_42_4.jpg', '42', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version of Summicron 2/50mm lens in screw mount, approx. 1,100 pieces were made, very rare. It comes with filter and both caps, in like new condition.', '根據資料顯示，螺絲口Summicron 2/50mm鏡頭的產量只有1,100支左右，十分珍貴。而此鏡更是早期版本，配有濾鏡及鏡頭前後蓋，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2481', 'Summicron 2/50mm Black Special Edition', 'Summicron 2/50mm Black Special Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_43_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_43_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_43_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_43_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_43_5.jpg', '43', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is a later model, carrying later serial number. It was introduced as special version of Summicron 2/50mm with screw mount for use with older Leicas in about 2001. It comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '這支鏡頭是採用後期設計式樣，機身編號也較後期，在2001年徠卡發佈過此款特別版的螺絲口Summicron 2/50mm給早期螺絲機用，此鏡估計是樣品之一。此鏡頭連鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2482', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_44_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_44_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_44_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_44_4.jpg', '44', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'Hektor 1.9/7.3 cm in ALL Black Paint finishing is very rare. This lens comes with lens hood and cap, lens rear cap and red paper box.', '本拍品是Hektor 1.9/7.3cm 全黑漆鏡頭，鏡身以黃銅製造；在對焦時，鏡筒會同時轉動，貨號為HEGRA。全黑的Hektor 1.9/7.3cm是極罕見的，配有遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭後蓋及原裝鏡頭紙盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2483', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint &amp; Black/Chrome Set', 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm Black Paint &amp; Black/Chrome Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_45_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_45_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_45_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_45_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_45_5.jpg', '45', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Hektor 1.9/7.3cm was launched in the early 30’s in small batch of production, with wider apertures for use as a portrait lens. This is a black paint and black/ chrome set. The black paint one is extremely rare. Both come with hood, hood cap and rear cap, with haze and normal signs of use and wears.', '此一對成色極罕見的Hektor 1.9/7.3cm鏡頭，其中一支為黑漆及銀色組成；另一支是全黑漆， 全黑漆的Hektor 1.9/7.3cm鏡頭極其罕見。此款鏡頭產於1930年代初，是首款擁有1.9大光圈的人像鏡，色彩豐富。此對鏡頭各連同遮光罩、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋，鏡片有霧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2484', 'Summicron 2/9cm Chrome', 'Summicron 2/9cm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_46_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_46_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_46_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_46_4.jpg', '46', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version of SOOZI Summicron 2/9cm lens, made in Canada, with non-removable lenshead. It comes with lens hood, lens hood cap and lens rear cap, clear glass in mint condition.', '第一代加拿大製的SOOZI Summicron 2/9cm鏡頭，鏡頭前端不能移除。此鏡成色極新，玻璃通透，帶遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2485', '2/90mm Prototype', '2/90mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_47_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_47_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_47_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_47_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_47_5.jpg', '47', '', '54,280', null, null, null, null, 'The lens is probably a prototype in early stage, with aperture scale engraved on barrel only. The optical formula B681 is engraved on the name ring, with clear glass, very rare.', '此鏡估計為極早期的光學測試原型版鏡頭。其鏡身上只有光圈的刻度，並沒有任何型號或字樣。鏡頭前端刻有光學測試編號B681，玻璃通透，市場少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2486', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint/Nickel &quot;George Eastman Museum” Piece', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint/Nickel &quot;George Eastman Museum” Piece', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_48_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_48_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_48_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_48_4.jpg', '48', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was a museum piece from George Eastman House in Rochester, USA. Its museum inventory number is 405046. George Eastman House is the oldest museum dedicated to photography and one of the oldest film archives in the world. It was built by George Eastman, the founder of Eastman Kodak company in 1905, and opened to public in 1949. This Thamber 2.2/9cm lens is in black paint/nickel finished instead of black paint/chrome, it is the 2nd lens of the production. Lens tube painted “405046” and “EASTMAN. L” with rear lens cap and spot filter.', '這支Thambar 2.2/9cm曾經是美國羅賈斯特市的George Eastman House博物館內的藏品，其藏品編號為「405046」，George Eastman House是世界上最古老的攝影器材博物館，由George Eastman (即柯達公司的創辦人)建於1905年，直到1949年才對外開放。此鏡另一特別之處是由黑漆與鎳金屬組成(通常為黑漆/銀)，而且是第二支生產的Thambar 2.2/9cm，鏡筒上印有藏品編號「405046」及「EASTMAN. L」字樣；帶有鏡頭後蓋及柔焦濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2487', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_49_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_49_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_49_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_49_4.jpg', '49', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens completely comes with spot filter, lens hood with cap, rear cap and original lens box, in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡唯一一款擁有柔焦效果的鏡頭，由三組四片玻璃組成，產量較少。配有一片柔焦濾鏡。此拍品配件齊全，連原廠遮光罩，遮光罩蓋、鏡頭後蓋及罕有的原廠鏡頭盒。成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2488', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_50_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_50_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_50_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_50_4.jpg', '50', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with spot filter, lens hood with hood cap, also the rear lens cap and red paper box, in mint condition.', '徠卡唯一一款擁有柔焦效果的鏡頭，由三片四組玻璃組成，產量非常少。鏡頭連一塊中間鍍以銀色的反射濾鏡，作用是將中間成像造成柔焦效果。此鏡連同柔焦濾鏡、遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭後蓋及原廠紅色紙盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2489', 'Elmar 4/9cm Black Paint', 'Elmar 4/9cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_51_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_51_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_51_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_51_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_51_5.jpg', '51', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'This pre war lens comes with original red box and both caps, in mint condition.', '此鏡頭產於1937年，屬較早期的4/9cm鏡頭。鏡身成色極新，配有當年原裝的紅色盒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2490', 'Elmar 6.3/10.5cm Black Paint', 'Elmar 6.3/10.5cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_52_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_52_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_52_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_52_4.jpg', '52', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is clear, comes with lens hood with cap, rear cap and original lens box, in mint condition.', '德國生產的Mountain Elmar 6.3/10.5cm螺絲口鏡頭，鏡身使用黃銅及合金所製造，鏡頭玻璃清澈，成色佳，生產至今超過70年仍保持完好成色實在難得。鏡頭配有遮光罩連蓋、鏡頭底蓋及罕有的原廠鏡頭盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2491', 'Elmarit 2.8/90mm Black &amp; Chrome Prototype', 'Elmarit 2.8/90mm Black &amp; Chrome Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_53_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_53_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_53_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_53_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_53_5.jpg', '53', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a screw mount Elmarit with typical prototype serial number 0000230. The production of Elmarit 2.8/90mm was made with the aperture to f/22, this prototype lens was made to f/16, early blue coating in black and chrome finished with leather decorated. Also a wider knurl on focusing ring. It comes with keeper and front lens cap, in excellent condition.', '此為徠卡原廠的原型鏡頭，鏡身以黑/銀金屬配以荔枝紋飾皮設計。此款鏡頭正式投產時的最小光圈為f/22，而此鏡頭則為f/16光圈。且此鏡玻璃偏藍，屬早期試驗產品；調焦環上的波浪紋也比正常為寬，是原型版，更加珍貴。此鏡配有膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2492', 'Elmarit 2.8/135mm Prototype', 'Elmarit 2.8/135mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_54_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_54_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_54_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_54_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_54_5.jpg', '54', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Leitz prototype lens of 2.8/135mm in full brass mount, without aperture ring and focusing ring. This is only aperture scale on barrel which engraved by hand. From optical bench testing, optical formula B665 and serial number 0000318 are both engraved on the front ring. This lens is extremely rare and comes with both caps. It has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡為2.8/135mm的原型鏡，鏡頭由全黃銅製造，鏡身上沒有調焦環或光圈環，只有手刻的光圈讀數，屬於極早期為光學基準測試用之初型。此鏡的鏡頭光學技術為B665，鏡頭前端亦刻有原型版編號0000318，連同鏡頭後蓋，十分罕見，經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2493', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_55_6.jpg', '55', '', '590,000', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare! Not often seen on the market, lens is in black/nickel finished. Original M39 mount rangefinder coupled, comes with an original lens hood, and both caps. Lens shows signs of use.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Makro Plasmat 2.7/3.5cm鏡頭，具有極其驚人的解析力，一直都是國際市場上收藏家追捧的光學精品。加上此款鏡頭在Hugo Meyer產品系列中極為少見於市場，多年前此拍品價值已比Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm高出過一倍以上。此鏡身是鎳/黑，原裝M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機。有使用痕跡，連原裝遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2494', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_56_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_56_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_56_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_56_4.jpg', '56', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'Kino Plasmat is one of the most favourable lens of Hugo Meyer &amp; Co- Goerlitz. “Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz” is engraved on the name ring, without coating. The lens was produced  between  1940 and 1945, made of aluminum and brass, in M39 screw mount, very rare. It comes with lens rear cap and leather pouch.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Kino Plasmat鏡頭一直都是國際市場上廣受買家追捧的光學精品之一，本拍品為寫有「Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz」的無鍍膜版本。由於它用上高通光性玻璃，而且產量十分稀有，故一直以來極受收藏家歡迎。此鏡屬於二戰時期的早期版本，鏡身使用黃銅及合金組成，做工十分優秀，質感結實沉重；已是M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機，極為罕見，連同鏡頭後蓋及鏡頭皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2495', 'Hugo Meyer & Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', 'Hugo Meyer & Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_57_7.jpg', '57', '', '542,800', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version before WWII, without coating. Lens made of nickel and in black paint, with original M39 mount, in mint condition. It comes with both caps and hood, with clear glass as well. Extremely rare.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Kino Plasmat鏡頭一直都是國際市場上廣受買家追捧的光學精品之一， 本拍品為刻有「Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz」的無鍍膜版本，屬於二戰時期的早期版本。由於它用上高通光性玻璃，而且產量十分稀有，故一直以來極受收藏家歡迎。鎳金屬及黑漆鏡身成色上佳，玻璃通透，此鏡於市場上極為難求。鏡頭為原裝M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機，連鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩。<br />\r\n此鏡與下一拍品lot 58同型號的鏡頭在外觀上多處均有不同，極少現於市面，收藏家若能集齊一系列，將能把此超級名鏡的演變過程完整演釋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2496', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_58_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_58_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_58_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_58_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_58_5.jpg', '58', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a chrome Hugo Meyer Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm. “Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz” is engraved on the name ring, without coating. Lens head is made of brass and in black paint. It is rare than the nickel one. Comes with both caps and leather pouch in M39 mount.', '這是銀色的Hugo Meyer Kino Plasmat 1.5/5cm鏡頭，Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Kino Plasmat是國際市場上備受注目的光學精品之一。它用上高通光性玻璃，是二次大戰早期寫有「Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz」的無鍍膜版本，比同一外形的鎳版更為稀少。此鏡前端為黃銅及黑漆所造，為原裝M39 mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機。連同鏡頭前後蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2497', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/7.5cm', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz Kino Plasmat 1.5/7.5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_59_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_59_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_59_3.jpg', '59', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz 1.5/7cm in M39 screw mount rangefinder coupled which can be used on Leica screw mount camera. Complete with rare and original hood, handmade cap with normal signs of use on barrel, little haze and dust on the glass.', 'Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz的Kino Plasmat鏡頭一直都是國際市場上廣受買家追捧的光學精品之一，此鏡是Hugo Meyer &amp; Co-Goerlitz出品的Kino Plasmat 1.5/7.5cm 鏡頭，此鏡已是M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機。鏡頭蓋更以人手所鑄造，矜貴非常。此鏡配有罕有的原裝遮光罩，鏡頭前及後蓋，經歷超過半世紀仍然可以保持玻璃完好，絕對是收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2498', 'Dallmeyer 2/8.5cm', 'Dallmeyer 2/8.5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_60_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_60_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_60_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_60_4.jpg', '60', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a very rare Dallmeyer 2/8.5cm lens, with 6 elements in 4 groups and “Super Six” design even without “Super Six” engraved on the name ring. The lens is in M39 mount, comes with both caps.', '此拍品為罕見的鏡頭，由英國著名廠商Dallmeyer所製造，鏡頭設計為六片四組。雖然鏡頭前端沒有刻上「Super Six」字樣，但與其他Super Six系列一樣，此鏡同樣有雙高斯設計，所以其散景十分迷人。此鏡為M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機；連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2499', 'P. Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', 'P. Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_61_6.jpg', '61', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux Paris 2.5/35mm Type R1 lens is one of the most famous portrait lenses of Angenieux, with M39 mount. The lens is in mint condition, comes with both caps.', '此鏡頭可說是Angenieux的成名作，也是當年全球較大光圈的廣角鏡頭之一，該鏡用全金屬鏡身。此鏡成像細膩，色彩豐富及有極強的立體感，可充分展現標準的法國浪漫色調。此鏡已是M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲口相機。玻璃完好，有正常使用痕跡，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2500', 'P. Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21', 'P. Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_62_6.jpg', '62', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 1.5/50mm Type S21, one of the most famous standard lens of Angenieux, with six elements in four groups of Double Gaussian lens. This lens is in Exakta ¾ mount, comes with filter, both caps and Kipon ALPA-L/M adapter, in mint- condition.', '產自法國的頂級電影鏡。此鏡的型號為S21，鏡頭以六片四組雙高斯設計 (Double Gaussian Lens)，使其擁有超高的解象力，畫面細膩。此鏡為Exakta ¾卡口，成色良好，配有濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及Kipon Alpa-L/M的轉接環，是使用和收藏兼具的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2501', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Black', 'Fujinon 1.2/5cm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_63_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_63_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_63_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_63_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_63_5.jpg', '63', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'In 1950-1960’s, some kinds of M39 screw mount lenses were produced for Leica by Fujinon, only a small batch has been produced, especially Fujinon 1.2/5cm. This black Fujinon 1.2/5cm lens comes with both lens caps and hood, with few signs of use.', '富士在1950-1960年代徠卡製造了數款M39螺絲口的旁軸鏡頭，它們產量不多，生產時期也不長；當中Fujinon 1.2/5cm的產量更為稀少。此黑色Fujinon 1.2/5cm鏡頭成像質素出色，鏡身有輕微使用痕跡。連鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2502', 'Zunow Opt. Japan 1.7/3.5cm', 'Zunow Opt. Japan 1.7/3.5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_64_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_64_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_64_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_64_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_64_5.jpg', '64', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'Wide angle lens made by Zunow Opt. Japan, in black/ chrome finished, M39mount. Comes with both lens caps, very rare.', '由日本帝國光學公司出品的廣角鏡頭，鏡身以黑色及銀色組成，為M39螺絲口，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2503', 'Zunow Opt. Japan 1.1/5cm Chrome', 'Zunow Opt. Japan 1.1/5cm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_65_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_65_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_65_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_65_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_65_5.jpg', '65', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first standard lens with aperture f/1.1, made by Zunow Opt. Japan in around 1953. Approx. 200 pieces were made. This lens is original M39 mount, very rare. Glass is clear with keeper.', '此款鏡頭於1950年代初由日本帝國光學出品，是全世界第一支擁有超大光圈的標準鏡頭。此鏡為原裝M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲相機，產量只有二百多支，非常罕見。此鏡帶有膠盅，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2504', 'Voigtlander Nokton 1.5/50mm Chrome', 'Voigtlander Nokton 1.5/50mm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_66_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_66_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_66_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_66_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_66_5.jpg', '66', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'The Nokton 1.5/50mm is a rangefinder coupled lens with two aspherical surfaces, it’s available in silver or black with 7 elements in six groups. This silver lens comes with keeper, in M39 mount and in like new condition.', '此鏡頭由福倫達公司生產及設計，有兩片非球面玻璃，是七片六組的設計，分別有黑色或銀色設計，而此鏡是銀色版本。此鏡為M39 Mount，可用於徠卡螺絲相機，連同膠盅，成色十分新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2505', 'II Mod.F Black Paint', 'II Mod.F Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_11_7.jpg', '11', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica II Mod f comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm lens (#434750), certificate and front lens cap. Certificate shows the camera and lens were delivered as a set from factory on 5th June 1940. In mint condition.', '此II Mod.f於1940年6月5日出廠，黃銅黑漆機身配以Elmar 3.5/5cm(#434750)鏡頭。證書內的機鏡編號證明此機鏡於出廠時已被配成一套，非常珍貴。機身連鏡頭前蓋及證書，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2506', 'Standard Black Paint', 'Standard Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_12_7.jpg', '12', '', '15,340', null, null, null, null, 'Black Paint Standard comes with Telyt 4.5/20cm (#768598) and hood. Shows normal marks of use and in good working order.', '黑漆Standard機身配長焦鏡Telyt 4.5/20cm (#768598)及遮光罩。機身與鏡露銅，極具歲月韻味，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2507', 'Standard Repaint Gold', 'Standard Repaint Gold', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_13_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_13_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_13_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_13_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_13_5.jpg', '13', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Repainted gold Leica Standard covered with red lizard leather and comes with Wollensak 3.5/50mm Velostigmat lens (#499522), this camera set includes gold-plated lens cap and wooden box, in mint condition.', '後期鍍金Standard機身覆以紅色蜥蜴皮，並配有較特別的Wollensak 3.5/50mm Velostigmat鏡頭(#499522)。連鍍金鏡頭蓋及木盒，做工精美，成色很新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2508', 'Standard Chrome', 'Standard Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_14_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_14_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_14_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_14_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_14_5.jpg', '14', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Leica standard comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#398171), rangefinder and front lens cap, in mint- condition and good working order.', '銀色Standard機身連Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭(#398171)，配連動測距杆及鏡頭蓋，成色優良，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2509', 'Leica II Black Paint', 'Leica II Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_15_6.jpg', '15', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Leica II Serial number 110823 (from Batch 109001 - 111550 in 1933) with feathered arrow from right to left engraved on top plate. The arrow has the double feathers as often found on the early knobs of the Leica I. This is a demonstration Leica and the arrow indicates the direction of the shutter blinds. Only very few such camera were ever produced. This particular specimen illustrated in Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck calendar 2014, January page. It comes with body cap and the calendar as well.', '本拍品產於1933年（生產批號為109001至111550間），於其機頂刻有由右至左的羽毛箭頭，此箭頭常見於早期的徠卡I的轉盤鈕上，用於指示快門位置，但只有極少數的徠卡II有此標示。本拍品亦被挑選印刷於徠卡相機界權威Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck 2014年1月份中的掛曆內。機身有使用痕跡，運作正常；拍品連同Paul-Henry Van Hasbroeck 2014年親筆簽名掛曆乙本及相機蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2510', 'III Black Paint', 'III Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_16_9.jpg', '16', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica III black paint was introduced in 1933, camera comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm lens in nickel. This set includes the stereo accessories, i.e. VOSTN (#1075), stereoly arm VOROD, VOTRA for adjusting interpupillary distance, NATRA, HEBOO and WINTU with box. This set is in excellent condition, very rare. For more illustration, please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.29, 82, 269 and 271.', '此機於1933年推出，配有由鎳金屬製造的Elmar 3.5/50mm鏡頭。此套機更連同立體鏡拍攝套裝，包括：VOSTN (#1075)、立體鏡連接杆VOROD、可調較瞳孔距離的VOTRA、NATRA觀片器連盒、慢快門控制器HEBOO連盒及WINTU取景器連盒。整套套裝成色優良，為拍攝良伴。以上配件資料可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.29、82、269及271。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2511', 'Leica III Nickel Outfit', 'Leica III Nickel Outfit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_17_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_17_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_17_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_17_4.jpg', '17', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica III comes with 3 lenses, they are Elmar 6.3/10.5cm in black paint/nickel (#136313) with hood, hood cap and rear lens cap, Elmar 3.5/50mm (#173633) in nickel, with black painted hood and Elmar 3.5/3.5cm (#225323) in nickel. This set comes with VIDOM viewfinder, WINKO viewfinder, film cassette, three color filters and leather box as well. Both are in excellent condition and in good working order, very rare.', '此黑漆徠卡III套機成色優良，配件齊全，它配備了鎳製的Elmar 3.5/3.5cm (#225323)、鎳製的Elmar 3.5/50mm (#173633) 連黑漆遮光罩及Elmar 6.3/10.5cm (#136313)配遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋，其金屬部分是鎳/黑漆。套機成色如新，操作正常，套機更配備VIDOM鎳金屬取景器、WINKO直角取景器、三塊顏色濾鏡、皮盒及菲林筒，如此配件齊全的套機實屬少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2512', '250FF Reporter Black Paint', '250FF Reporter Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_18_8.jpg', '18', '', '', null, null, null, null, '250FF was launched before WWII, approx. 246 units made. On the top-plate of the camera engraved with &quot;Brigham Bridlington&quot;, Brigham was a camera shop in Bridlington, England. The company used to own various Leica 250 Reporter cameras. All the cameras were engraved “Brigham Bridlington” because they were given to photographers who were taking pictures of the tourists in Bridlington. The photographers were walking on the street, beach, party… then people came to the shop and bought the pictures they liked.<br />\r\nThe basic-plate of the camera engraved “Open/Close” as it was sold to England, also it is the one from the last batch 150000-150125, this camera has been completely serviced by Ottmar Michaely, leather around the body has been replaced after the war, in good working condition, shows signs of use.', '250FF為二次大戰前之產物，根據記錄只生產了246台。最後一批250FF的機身號碼為150000至150125，此機正是最後一批生產的250FF。此機機頂刻有「Brigham Bridlington」，曾屬於英國一家Brigham Bridlington相機公司擁有。當時該公司借出數台250 Reporter予不同攝影師，讓他們為遊客提供景點拍攝服務，遊客可回到Brigham Bridlington購回他們心儀的照片。此機因為是出口到英國的產品，故機底的底蓋上鎖杆位置刻有「Open/Close」而不是一般的「Auf/Zu」。機身經過Ottmar Michaely鑑定，操作功能正常﹔惟機身飾皮於戰後經重新配換。此機連機身蓋，有明顯使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2513', 'Leica Optical Sketches Booklet', 'Leica Optical Sketches Booklet', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_19_8.jpg', '19', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'This is a booklet with sketches and notes by a Leitz optician, who was involved in the Saar factory during 1949, where the famous &quot;monte en Sarre&quot; cameras were assembled. It shows interesting details about lenses around 1949, including Hektor 2.8cm, Summarex, etc., authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡頭手稿是1949年左右，由一位徠茲工廠內的光學技師擁有。手稿內詳細描繪了當時的鏡頭設計，包括Hektor 2.8cm及Summarex鏡頭等，極具歷史價值。此拍品經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2514', 'IIIa Chrome', 'IIIa Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_20_7.jpg', '20', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'This IIIa chrome is original Leitz special sample for factory internal use before World War II, with a very special engraving “Leih- Kamera” on the back of the top plate, very rare. The camera comes with Summicron 2/5cm lens (#1044313) (please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.311 for illustration), with front lens cap, in mint condition.', '此款特別機型為IIIa銀色，機背刻有「Leih-Kamera」字樣；是徠茲工廠在二次大戰前提供給工廠內部測試用的相機。機身號4210並不在正常生產序號之列，非常罕有(可參閱James Lager Vol. III p.311)。此機配有Summicron 2/5cm鏡頭(#1044313)，連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2515', 'Leica 72 18x24mm Midland', 'Leica 72 18x24mm Midland', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_21_8.jpg', '21', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'Leica 72 is a 18x24mm format camera which was produced in 1954-1957 in Canada and Germany. Only 150 units of Leica 72 Midland with batch number 357301 - 357450 were produced in Canada. The top plate engraved with “18x24” and “Midland Ontario” (Please refer to James Lager Vol. I p.78). This camera comes with Summarit 1.5/5cm lens (#1246991) made by Leitz Canada. Number ring engraved with “Ernst Leitz Canada Ltd. Midland”. The Summarit 1.5/5cm was one of the first Leitz lenses to be final assembled by Leitz Canada in 1952/1953. (Please refer to James Lager Vol. II p.50). A chrome XOONS hood with clamping screw which has never seen, was included. This outfit comes with body cover, both lens caps and 4 pieces color filters as well.', '徠卡72是採用18x24mm格式的相機，於1954至1957年分別在加拿大及德國生產。而在加拿大生產的Leica 72 Midland批號由357301至357450，全球僅生產150台，本拍品便是其中一台。機頂位置刻有「18x24」及「Midland Ontario」字樣 (可參閱James Lager Vol. I p.78)。此機菲林計算器讀數可至72，取景窗口為直檔，另外此相機還配有在加拿大產的Summarit 1.5/5cm鏡頭(#1246991)；鏡頭前環刻有「Ernst Leitz Canada Ltd. Midland」字樣，這款加拿大製鏡頭是德國徠茲工廠最早在加拿大徠茲工廠裝配的鏡頭(可參考James Lager Vol. II p.50)。另外伴隨著這支鏡頭的還有XOONS銀色遮光罩(常見於市面的為黑色鍍漆)，及 4塊不同顏色的濾鏡，鏡頭前後蓋及機身保護蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2516', 'IIId Chrome', 'IIId Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_22_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_22_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_22_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_22_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_22_5.jpg', '22', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The design of IIId is based on IIIc. It was the first model of Leica supplied with a built-in time delay action. The serial number starts from 360001, around 400 pieces were made, and this is the 21st piece. It comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#545393), papers, front lens cap and leather case.', 'IIId在IIIc的基礎上加上自拍功能，是徠卡首款帶自拍的機種，機身編號由360001開始，總產量只有400多台。此機是IIId中的第21台，屬於早期版本，具收藏價值﹔配有Elmar 3.5/5cm (#545393)、說明書、鏡頭前蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2517', 'IIIf Monte en Sarre', 'IIIf Monte en Sarre', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_23_6.jpg', '23', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In the period 1949-1951, about 500 Leica cameras (number 359001-359500) were assembled in the Sarre (French zone of Germany), in order to avoid the high customs charges applied in France to import cameras. These cameras carried the engraving &quot;Monte en Sarre&quot; (assembled in Saar) on the top-plate. The camera comes with Summicron 2/5cm (#1365342) and lens cap, in mint condition. Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.82 for further illustration.', '1949至1951年，不多於500台的徠卡相機在德國境內的法屬殖民地Saar組裝，由於此批相機均於法國及其殖民地出售，選擇在Saar組裝，可避免繳付高昂的入口稅。該批相機機頂刻有「Monte en Sarre」字樣，機身號碼由359001至359500止。此機連同Summicron 2/5cm (#1365342)及其鏡頭前蓋，成色極佳。有關此款相機的介紹，可參閱James Lager Vol.I p.82。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2518', 'If with Haber and Fink', 'If with Haber and Fink', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_24_8.jpg', '24', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare tri-lens turret made by Haber &amp; Fink, New York (Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.303 for further illustration), with VIOOH viewfinder (#59840), Elmar 4/9cm (#1038389), Summaron 3.5/3.5cm (#1059281) and Summitar 2/5cm(#913948).  This set comes with 3 front lens caps, a camera strap, with normal signs of use and wears.', '此If套機連同非常罕見的三鏡頭轉台，轉台由美國著名的Haber &amp; Fink公司製造，底部刻有其公司名稱，此資料可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.303。另配有Elmar 4/9cm (#1038389)、Summaron 3.5/3.5cm (#1059281)、Summitar 2/5cm(#913948)及取景器VIOOH (#59840)。此拍品有使用痕跡，連同三個鏡頭前蓋及掛帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2519', 'IIIf Chrome with Summarit 1.5/5cm “Midland”', 'IIIf Chrome with Summarit 1.5/5cm “Midland”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_25_7.jpg', '25', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Very small number of IIIf chrome cameras were made in Canada with “Midland Ontario” engraved on the top-plate. The camera comes with a matching Summarit 1.5/5cm lens (#1053396), engraved with “Ernst Leitz Canada Limited Midland” on the name ring, a front lens cap is included.', '在18多萬台IIIf相機中，僅極少數是由加拿大生產，並於機頂刻有「Midland Ontario」字樣，同時此機配有同生產年份及同產地的Summarit 1.5/5cm鏡頭 (#1053396)，鏡環刻有「Ernst Leitz Canada Limited Midland」字樣，十分珍貴及罕有,連鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2520', 'IIIf Chrome with Red Dial', 'IIIf Chrome with Red Dial', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_26_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_26_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_26_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_26_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_26_5.jpg', '26', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This camera is the second version of IIIf (Batch numbers 615001-685000) with red synchronization scale numbers 0-20. It comes with Elmar 2.8/ 5cm (#1620023) and front lens cap, in mint- condition.', '此機為IIIf的第二版(生產編號為615001-685000)，閃燈同步的數字為紅色。連Elmar 2.8/5cm鏡頭(#1620023)及鏡頭蓋。整套成色佳，自用收藏皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2521', 'IIIf Set Chrome', 'IIIf Set Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_27_7.jpg', '27', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'This camera set owned by James. A. Sinclair, comes with four lenses: Elmar 4/9cm (#838401), Hektor 4.5/13.5cm (#1347969), Summicron 2/5cm (#1349284), and Summaron 3.5/3.5cm (#1107634) with both caps and hood. In addition, it has four different color filters and two transparent UV filters, VIOOH viewfinder (#73617), shutter release, two film cassettes and original leather suitcase, very rare.', '此套機由James. A. Sinclair公司擁有，配有4支鏡頭，分別為：Elmar 4/9cm (#838401)、Hektor 4.5/13.5cm (#1347969)、Summicron 2/5cm (#1349284)及Summaron 3.5/3.5cm (#1107634)，均連前後蓋及遮光罩。另備有四片不同顏色的濾鏡及兩塊透明濾鏡、VIOOH取景器 (#73617)、快門線、兩個菲林筒及貼有該公司資料的原裝皮箱。如此成色及配件齊全之套機，於市面上實屬少見，確為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2522', 'IIIg Chrome', 'IIIg Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_28_7.jpg', '28', '', '15,340', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with Elmar 3.5/3.5cm (#694085), leicavit and front lens cap. In good working order.', '此機連Elmar 3.5/3.5cm (#694085)鏡頭，連鏡頭前蓋及過片器，整體成色優良，機身飾皮完整，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2523', 'IIIg Re-plated Gold', 'IIIg Re-plated Gold', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_29_7.jpg', '29', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Repainted gold Leica IIIg decorated with brown lizard skin leather and comes with gold-plated Elmar 2.8/5cm lens (#1618835), this camera set includes gold-plated front lens cap, strap and box; in like new condition.', '此機可說是造工最精美的後期鍍金相機。鍍金的IIIg機身覆以棕色蜥蝪皮，連同鍍金的Elmar 2.8/5cm鏡頭(#1618835)及鍍金鏡頭前蓋﹔連同包裝盒及相機帶，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2524', 'IIIg 18x24mm Chrome Prototype', 'IIIg 18x24mm Chrome Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_30_8.jpg', '30', '', '542,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIg &quot;18X24&quot; - Canadian prototype camera with fantastic half frame brillant finder frame lines. Those cameras were never announced or officially known as projected by Leitz, but for sure made at the Canadian plant. Very rare, only about a handful known. It comes with body cap and film. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '鮮為人知的加拿大製造原型機，在IIIg的基礎上採用了Leica 72 18x24mm的半格格式及半格取景框線。此款相機是徠茲的試驗項目，從未對外公佈，甚至在工廠內的知情者亦為數不多，但肯定是在加拿大工廠製造，非常特別。此機連同機身蓋及菲林底片，以上資料由Lars Netopil提供，該機也已經Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2525', 'Ur-Leica Replica and 24 Carat Gold-plated Ur-Leica in Half Scale', 'Ur-Leica Replica and 24 Carat Gold-plated Ur-Leica in Half Scale', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_3.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_4.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_5.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_1_6.JPG', '1', '', '590,000', null, null, null, null, 'This Ur-Leica replica was together made by Leica and a celebrity, which is most likely to the original one. It comes with an Ur-Leica viewfinder, the words “Nachbildung der Ur-Leica” was engraved on top plate, and comes with a brass baseplate which was engraved the words “Ur-Leica 1913”, very rare. A 24K gold plated Ur-Leica replica in half scale (#Nr-0098) is also included, very rare.', '此台Ur-Leica複製版是由徠卡及名家製造改裝，它是目前市面上能見到的最接近原型機的複製品。它配有Ur-Leica的取景器，機頂上刻有 「Nachbildung der Ur-Leica」字樣，並配有純銅造的底座，底座上刻有「Ur-Leica 1913」字樣，甚為罕見。此機更連同一台全球量產的半比例24K鍍金Ur-Leica模型(#Nr-0098)，配有可伸縮鏡頭。整套Ur-Leica複製版極具收藏價值，是不可忽視的收藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2526', 'O-Series Replica', 'O-Series Replica', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_2_6.jpg', '2', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is the 26th of the 31 replicas made by Italian Alberico Arces, with serial number and model name engraved on the chassis, very rare. It comes with Anastigmat 3.5/50mm lens, in mint condition.', '此機與其他Leica O-Series的複製品有所不同，它是由意大利Alberico Arces公司重新製造，只產有31台，此機是第26台﹔機身號碼刻於底盤內。此機連同Anastigmat 3.5/50mm鏡頭，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2527', 'O-Series Replica the FIRST piece', 'O-Series Replica the FIRST piece', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_3_8.jpg', '3', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This was launched in Photokina in 2000, only 2000 pieces were made, number starts from 2676501, and this is the <b>FIRST</b> piece. It comes with Anastigmat 3.5/50mm lens and leather case.', '此款O-Series限量複製品相機於2000年的Photokina上推出，機身號碼由2676501開始，此拍品是該限量版中生產的<b>第一台</b>，別具收藏價值。此機連Anastigmat 3.5/50mm鏡頭及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2528', '1A Elmax', '1A Elmax', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_4_8.jpg', '4', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Authentic early Elmax camera with ratchet wind and early features. The counter-dial with &quot;40 and 0&quot; is a replica, the finder re-painted, the lens tube re-nickeled (no datum line visible anymore). Still very collectible and rare. Camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此1A相機配不可更換的Elmax 3.5/50mm鏡頭。Elmax是1A套機中的第二代，是在Anastigmat及Elmar鏡之間的產品。沿用了Anastigmat五片玻璃設計的Elmax鏡頭，機身序號在280至1280之間，僅生產約700多台。根據徠卡專家Ottmar Michaely的專業知識，機身編號在625以內的1A相機均屬於Anastigmat系列。該機除菲林計數盤、取景器及鏡筒有後塗及更換外，大部份均保留原廠狀態，如齒輪式轉盤、全黑及較短A/R杆、平的取景框、原廠六速速度盤及蘑菇狀按鈕等。<br />\r\n收藏價值極高。此機連同鏡頭前蓋，已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2529', '1A Elmax 3.5/50mm', '1A Elmax 3.5/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_5_9.jpg', '5', '', '424,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leica model 1A with Elmax 3.5/50mm is the second version of 1A, but this camera retains the original features of 1A Anastigmat: short lever rewind in black paint, ratchet winding mechanism, base plate without two screws and without arrows indicating “Auf-Zu”, frame counter up to 40 and dome shape bottom, coarse vulcanite, flat eye piece viewfinder, etc. According to Ottmar Michaely\'s professional knowledge, Elmax cameras up to serial #625 in reality are Anastigmat cameras. He states this 1A Elmax was sent to Leitz Company for upgrading in 1930, speed dial upgraded from 6 to 7, the rest of camera is in the condition like when it was delivered. This camera is in fine original condition. Complete with Ottmar Michaely\'s signed authentication letter, box, leather case, matching original lens cap, container with two cassettes and FODIS rangefinder (#5712), very rare.', '1A相機配Elmax 3.5/50mm鏡頭，是1A套機中的第二代，此機身擁有第一代1A Anastigmat的特徵，包括:較短身的A/R杆、有齒輪式轉盤、機底沒有螺絲、底蓋上鎖杆沒有箭頭指「Auf-Zu」、菲林讀數至40及蘑菇形按鈕，粗糙的硬膠飾皮，取景器後部扁平，鏡身亦有明顯的基準線等等。根據徠卡專家Ottmar Michaely的專業知識，如果機身編號在#625以內的1A相機都應屬於Anastigmat系列。他指出此機曾於1930年送返原廠升級，把快門速度由6級增至7級；此機經過Ottmar Michaely鑑定並確認為百分百真品。此機配有Ottmar Michaely親筆簽署的鑑定信，連同包裝、皮套、原裝鏡頭蓋、2個菲林盒、FODIS連動測距杆(#5712)。如此成色及配件齊全的原廠1A Elmax絕對是拍賣會上難得一見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2530', '1 Mod.B Dial-Set Compur', '1 Mod.B Dial-Set Compur', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_6_6.jpg', '6', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, early dial-set Compur shutter, only 638 units were made. It has film counter lock as special feature, shows normal marks of use.', '帶有鏡間快門的徠卡1 Mod B Compur有兩款，一種是靠鏡頭中間上面的外環來設定快門速度(Rim-set)；另一種是靠鏡頭前面的撥盤來設置快門速度 (Dial-set)。Dial-set的產量較少，只生產約638台。此相機是較稀少的Dial-set，配有特別的酒窩形快門按鈕，而鏡頭上更有獨特的Film Counter Lock。機身露銅，因產量稀少且超過八十年歷史，具極高收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2531', '1c with Compur Elmar 3.5/5cm', '1c with Compur Elmar 3.5/5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_7_7.jpg', '7', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, '1c with standard mount and Elmar 3.5/5cm lens (#105506) with rim-set compur shutter, very rare. Camera and lens show signs of use.', '帶標準接環的1c機身配上Rim-set鏡間快門的Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭(#105506)，非常罕見(可參考James Lager Vol II p.125介紹)。有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2532', '1A Hektor 2.5/50mm', '1A Hektor 2.5/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_8_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_8_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_8_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_8_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_8_5.jpg', '8', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Black and nickel finished Leica 1A comes with Hektor 2.5/50mm lens and lens cap, with normal marks of use.', '此徠卡1A套機，以黑色及鎳金屬組合而成，連鎳製Hektor 2.5/50mm鏡頭，有正常使用痕跡，連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2533', 'I Mifilmca 1/3x', 'I Mifilmca 1/3x', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_9_7.jpg', '9', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Mifilmca 1/3x produced for scientific commute photo micrographic use. It comes with 8x magnifier, very rare. Please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.332 for further illustration.', '徠茲於1931年推出Mifilmca 1/3x系統，此款顯微鏡相機配有可拆除的專用鏡箱，用於加裝徠卡顯微鏡及科學顯微攝鏡等特別設備，此相機連8倍放大鏡。這款產品非常珍貴，可參閱James Larger Vol. III p. 332。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2534', 'Non-Standard with Three Lenses Set', 'Non-Standard with Three Lenses Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_10_8.jpg', '10', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica 1A original updated by Leica to Non Standard, only very short time Leica made this service for upgrade from Leica 1A to Non-Standard, camera in original condition with 3 pieces of lenses with same serial number 101. Including Elmar 3.5/35mm in nickel, Elmar 3.5/50mm and Elmar 4.5/135mm in brass and nickel. This set comes with rangefinder in brass and nickel (#15814), viewfinder (VISOR), early right angle viewfinder (WINKO), three color filters and three close up lens (1x, 2X, 3X), double cassette holders in box, leather case. All lenses with front cap.', '此套機產於1929年，當時徠卡為1A機身提供升級至Non-Standard型號的服務，但為期非常短暫，約只有半年；所以在現今收藏市場上能見到的數量遠比正式生產的Non-Standard為少。此套機配有三支同為101編號的鏡頭，分別是: 鎳製的Elmar 3.5/35mm、Elmar 3.5/50mm及以由黃銅與鎳合金製造的Elmar 4.5/135mm，以上三支鏡頭均配有前蓋。另外，此套機配有黃銅及鎳製的測距器(#15814)、魚雷形狀的取景器(VISOR)、早期的角度取景器(WINKO)、兩個菲林筒及其包裝盒﹔三塊顏色濾鏡及近攝鏡(1x,2x,3x)，配有原廠皮套。此拍品有正常使用痕跡，但如此久遠又配件齊備的Non-Standard套機於市場上甚少見到，是收藏的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2535', 'M3 Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm', 'M3 Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_71_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_71_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_71_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_71_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_71_5.jpg', '71', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early M3 Chrome with double stroke operation and short film advance lever. It comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1351963), also completely with leather case, original factory tag, instruction, front lens cap and a matching number red box.', '早期銀色M3連Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭 (#1351963)。相機為兩次過片、過片杆較短。此機布幕完好。配有原裝相機皮套、原廠吊牌、說明書、鏡頭前蓋及與相機同號的原廠紅色包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2536', 'M3 with Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', 'M3 with Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_77_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_77_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_77_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_77_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_77_5.jpg', '77', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This outfit is a black paint M3 with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (#1836418), in mint condition. It is from the batch of 300 cameras made in 1963, serial number 1078501-1078800. Comes with leather case, lens front cap.', '此套M3黑漆連Summicron-M 2/50mm黑漆(#1836418)，套機的品相可說是在眾多M3黑漆相機中屬上品。此M3是1963年生產的300部黑漆相機之一(序號1078501-1078800)，連皮套及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2537', 'MP Black Paint “Eric Schaal”', 'MP Black Paint “Eric Schaal”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_80_11.jpg', '80', '', '4,956,000', null, null, null, null, 'This fully original Black Paint MP (MP-141) with matching Leicavit used by the famous photographer Eric Schaal. According to factory delivery record, this camera was delivered to Koln, Germany in 25th October, 1957. The chassis of the camera engraved “P 141” which matching to the serial number on the top-plate. The camera MP-141 also comes with a matching Summicron-M2/50mm (#1468980) in black paint finished with raw brass mount. A portraits photobook “ERIC SCHAAL PHOTOGRAPH” is also included. In the book, a Eric Schaal’s relative wrote a confirmation letter and mentioned Eric still used this camera to take photographs of his loved ones a year before his death. This lot has been reviewed by James Lager.', '本拍品是僅生產138台MP黑漆版的其中一台，機身號碼為141，並且由Eric Schaal所擁有。當年只有此般出色的專業攝影師及極少數的記者才能擁有徠卡MP相機，相機所配有的LEICAVIT(快速過片器)最多可以每秒過片兩張，這功能可滿足專業攝影師的不同要求。而Eric Schaal擁有的還是更罕見的黑漆版本。此乃早期的原裝MP黑漆相機, 機底同樣刻有與機身相同的“P 141”，相機保留原廠原裝狀態。配有供MP使用的同期黑漆銅卡口鏡頭Summicron-M 2/50mm(#1468980)連前蓋。根據相關資料，此台相機於1957年10月25日付運德國科隆。拍品連同的Eric Schaal人像攝影集《ERIC SCHAAL PHOTOGRAPH》，在書中，其親人親筆證明Eric Schaal直至去世前一年依然用此台MP為他的至親拍攝，足見此機在Eric Schaal心目中是何等重要。<br />\r\n大部份僅餘的黑漆MP都較為殘舊，此套MP連LEICAVIT及鏡頭成色可算為上上之選。經由James Lager檢閱。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2538', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_92_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_92_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_92_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_92_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_92_5.jpg', '92', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera belongs to the last 50 units of production of Leica M2, carrying some features of M4, such as rapid film loading system, with self-timer, very rare. It comes with body cap and leather case.', '此機是徠卡最後五十部生產的銀色M2相機之一，機身有部份M4設計，如菲林上片裝置及自拍等，十分罕有。此機帶機身蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2539', 'M4 Black 50th Anniversary in Three Consecutive Numbers', 'M4 Black 50th Anniversary in Three Consecutive Numbers', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_99_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_99_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_99_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_99_4.jpg', '99', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here are three units M4 50th Anniversary in consecutive numbers, made in Leitz Canada. <br />\r\nIn 1975, 1750 units were launched for celebrating Leica 50th anniversary, but only 350 units made in Canada. The special numbers of these three cameras are #1412698/098-E, #1412699/099-E, #1412700/100-E respectively, they come with boxes, papers and body caps, in like new condition.', '本拍品是三台相連號及由加拿大徠茲生產的M4徠卡50周年紀念機。在1975年為慶祝徠卡50週年，推出了1750套M4的50周年紀念機，當中只有350台由加拿大工廠製造。此三台連號紀念機的特別號分別是#1412698/098-E，#1412699/099-E及#1412700/100-E；三台相機均配有包裝證書及機身蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2540', 'MD-2 Black', 'MD-2 Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_103_1.jpg', '103', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This MD-2 in black, lacking serial number engraving, with body cap.', '徠卡MD-2相機，機身並沒有刻有機身編號；帶相機蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2541', 'MD-2 Chrome Prototype', 'MD-2 Chrome Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_104_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_104_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_104_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_104_4.jpg', '104', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a rare Leica MD-2 prototype in silver chome finished, lacking &quot;MD-2&quot; and serial number engraving, with M4 type advance level, using rapid loading system of M4, it comes with body cap. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '本拍品為徠卡MD-2的原廠原型機，機身頂蓋正面並未刻上「MD-2」的字樣及正式編號，只在機頂刻有「Leitz」字樣。機頂背部沒有刻上「M」「X」字及產地。回片杆帶有M4回片特徵，膠捲上片裝置為M4的快速上片裝置，同時帶有MDa的條碼凹糟，極為罕見，成色佳，帶機身蓋。此機已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2542', 'M6 0.72 Chrome with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH', 'M6 0.72 Chrome with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_109_7.jpg', '109', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'This set is M6 0.72 TTL Silver with a same serial number Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH lens in chrome (#2593000*), fantastic. It comes with wooden box, front lens cap and hood with cap.', '此套機為M6 0.72銀色機身(#2593000)，配有相同序號的Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH銀色鏡頭 (#2593000*)。此套機配搭特別及奇妙，十分少見；套機配有木盒、鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩連蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2543', 'Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/180mm', 'Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/180mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_168_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_168_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_168_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_168_4.jpg', '168', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'The production of this type of lens was below 275 pieces, only supplied to US market. The serial number of this lens is 2082796* stands for 2082796. It refers to the second batch production, comes with built-in hood and both caps.', '據資料顯示此款鏡產量少於275支，當時只供應予美國紐約市場發售，並沒有於歐洲地區發售及推廣過，其產量之少及特別的銷售渠道令此鏡更添收藏價值。<br />\r\n此鏡身編號是2082796*，表示序號2082796的鏡頭，工廠共生產過兩次，而這支帶*的鏡頭便是第二次生產的貨品。此鏡頭連內置遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2544', 'Telyt 4.8/280mm', 'Telyt 4.8/280mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_169_6.jpg', '169', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare first version of the Telyt 280/4.8.This very early production still retain the back of the lens of the Telyt 400.Only few hundreds pieces were made.Then a new back was designed for this lens and was used in the rest of the production.It comes with both caps , the original box and is in mint- condition.', '此鏡是早期螺絲卡口的版本，它用了Telyt 5/400mm的調焦環，其生產期極短，估計只有數百支，直到1961年後才改為較輕巧的調焦環，所以此拍品在市場上並不常見。它更可用於Visoflex 上，連同包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2545', 'Telyt 5/400mm Prototype', 'Telyt 5/400mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_170_6.jpg', '170', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is the prototype of Leica Telyt 5/400mm Visoflex lens and has early features of the early version. No serial number was found on lens. Please refer to http://www.mir.com.my for further illustrations. This lens comes with rear lens cap and Visoflex viewfinder, with signs of use and wears. The lens has been authenticated by James Lager and he was amazed by the rarity of this lens.', '此鏡頭並沒有鏡身序號，是研發初期的Telyt 5/400mm原型版，鏡頭有著早期的設計特徵。此款鏡頭於http://www.mir.com.my有照片介紹；James Lager也親自鑑定過本鏡頭，對其罕有程度大為讚賞。連鏡頭後蓋及Visoflex取景器，有明顯使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2546', 'Standard with Leica Sabre Gun Stock', 'Standard with Leica Sabre Gun Stock', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_174_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_174_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_174_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_174_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_174_5.jpg', '174', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Sabre Gun Stock for Leica photography, made by Sabre Photographic Supply Company (Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.188 for further illustration), comes with a Leica Standard in chrome (#329290), Telyt 5/40cm (#804092) with front cap, Visoflex I (#12360), PLOOT mirror reflex housing (#3820) and double cable release. Whole set is in excellent condition, very rare.', '軍刀型槍托手柄是其中一款為配合徠卡早期相機及長焦鏡的罕見配件（可參閱James Lager Vol.II p.188)，主要配合以20cm及40cm的長焦鏡上使用，機上帶有雙快門線連接槍扳機位，方便拍攝及有助提升穩定性。此槍托是由Sabre Photographic Supply Company製造，連同徠卡Standard相機 (#329290)、Telyt 5/40cm (#804092)連鏡頭前蓋、Visoflex I (#12360)、PLOOT取景器(#3820)及雙快門線。成色優良，絕對是收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2547', '250GG with ” Kugellager” Consecutive Number', '250GG with ” Kugellager” Consecutive Number', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_176_10.jpg', '176', '', '1,062,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica 250 was officially introduced in 1934, approximately 130 units of 250’s equipped with ball bearing shutters were prepared for the German military in 1942-1943 (Please refer to James Lager Vol. I p.50 & 55 for further information). These two cameras are painted with white K on the shutter curtain. According to factory record, they were stolen from the factory during the war. For camera #352423 comes with a Summar 2/5cm (#442081), leather case and front lens cap; for the other one #352424, it comes with a Summar 2/5cm (#468684) and front lens cap. Both are still in excellent condition, extremely rare. Besides, this set includes a long load (with two special cups) NAKUL which used to inspect film shot in the 250 exposure reporter, in nickel finished, with 5X magnifier. The NAKUL is in a grey wooden box with white lettering “Betrachtungslupe fuer Kleinbild-Aufnahme”. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '根據James Lager Vol.I p.50和p.55敘述，徠卡於1942-1943年間專門為德國軍隊生產了大約130台的250GG相機，它們獨有的特徵包括快門布簾印有「K」字及帶滾珠軸承(Kugellager)，而且機底配有馬達介面，可提高在戰場上的拍攝速度。根據徠卡工廠紀錄，此對250GG在二次大戰期間被盜，之後這對相機輾轉流散於世界各地，成為了不同收藏者的手中掌珍，超過半世紀，竟能再度成雙出現於本拍賣會，堪稱奇蹟。本相連號帶K字布簾的250GG相機中，編號#352423的相機配有Summar 2/5cm(#442081)連皮套、四個菲林匣及鏡頭前蓋﹔而編號#352424則配有Summar 2/5cm (#468684)、四個菲林片匣及其鏡頭前蓋。另外此拍品更包括一件估計是1940年德軍向徠卡訂造的，可用在250 Reporter的負片放大觀片配件“NAKUL”，此觀片器帶有手柄，兩端各有一個承托長膠片的金屬筒，觀片器有5倍放大效果，用刻有「Betrachtungslupe fuer Kleinbild-Aufnahme」的灰色木盒承裝(詳細可參考James Lager Vol.III p.234-235)。本拍品經James Lager及Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2548', 'IIIc Chrome “Luftwaffen-Eigentum”', 'IIIc Chrome “Luftwaffen-Eigentum”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_177_7.jpg', '177', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a IIIc chrome for German Air Force (Luftwaffen), it comes with an Elmar 3.5/5cm (#536297). Both camera and lens barrel engraved with “Luftwaffen Eigentum”. The camera and lens were shipped on 10th Jan 1941 and 20th Jan 1941, with shipping code 19785 and 19787 respectively. This set comes with a front lens cap.', '德國空軍銀色IIIc連Elmar 3.5/5cm(#536297)，機鏡均刻有「Luftwaffen Eigentum」字樣，證明為空軍財產，而機頂刻有特別編號「FL. NO. 38079」。此機鏡的運送編號分別為19785及19787，運送日期分別是1941年1月10日及1941年1月20日。此套機經過二次大戰的洗禮仍可保留至今，實在難得。套機配有鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2549', 'IIIc Chrome “Luftwaffen-Eigentum”', 'IIIc Chrome “Luftwaffen-Eigentum”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_178_6.jpg', '178', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is produced for German Air Force, engraved “FL. No_38079” on the top plate and “Luftwaffen- Eigentum” at the back of the camera. Delivered to Luftwaffen Berlin on 1st October 1941, shipping number is 25912. It comes with camera body cap.', '供德國空軍使用的IIIc銀色軍用機。機頂刻有「Fl. No_38079」字樣;而機背則刻有「Luftwaffen-Eigentum」。此機於1941年10月1日付運予德國柏林空軍，交貨編號為25912。此機操作正常，成色良好，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2550', 'IIIcK with Summitar 2/5cm Grey', 'IIIcK with Summitar 2/5cm Grey', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_179_6.jpg', '179', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This Military IIIcK grey is in mint condition. The “K” letter is engraved at the serial number on top plate and “K” stamped on shutter curtain in dark red. According to Lars Netopil’s Leica expertise, only one camera is with dark red “K” in every 30 sets IIIcK. Red “K” is less common than the white one, please refer to 《Leica Collector’s Guide》 p.77 written by Dennis Laney. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. This camera comes with Summitar 2/5cm (#578707) and front lens cap.', '此機為非常罕有原裝灰色的德國軍用IIIcK相機。除機身序號後刻有「K」字外，相機快門簾上的「K」字呈暗紅色，根據Lars Netopil描述，大約每三十台IIIcK中，只有一台擁有紅色「K」字，可見此相機的稀少罕有程度。由 Dennis Laney著作的《Leica Collector\'s Guide》77頁中也有關於IIIc灰帶紅K布簾的描述。此拍品配有Summitar 2/5cm鏡頭(#578707)及鏡頭蓋。由二次大戰至今，機身仍保存較新，實為難得。經由Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2551', 'IIIcK Grey “WEHRMACHT HEER”', 'IIIcK Grey “WEHRMACHT HEER”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_180_10.jpg', '180', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Original gray K-type IIIC “Wehrmacht Heer” with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#584189) were designed for German Armed Forces Army, camera body covered gray wartime paint, “W.H.” engraved on top-plate of the camera and lens. The camera is fitted with two “fiducial points” visible when the shutter is held open, these points bisect the long dimension of the Leica format. According to factory record, both camera and lens were delivery to Berlin on 3rd February 1944, shipment no. 9773 (please refer to James Lager Vol. I p.90 for further illustration).This camera comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#584189), case, original Leica tag, extremely rare. The camera and lens have been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '原裝罕有的灰漆IIIcK WEHRMACHT HEER連Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭(#584189)是特別為德國國防軍設計，機身為灰色飾皮，相機機頂及鏡身都刻有「W.H.」字樣。當打開快門，相機的膠卷門分別有上下兩個三角形的膠片長度平分點，同時快門簾亦印有「K」字。根據工廠的記錄，這套相機及鏡頭是同時於1944年2月3日運往柏林，運送編號9773。關於此款相機的資料，可參考James Lager Vol. I第90頁。此拍品附有徠卡標籤吊牌及皮套。跨越戰爭時代至今半個世紀，機身成色仍然良好，為見證歷史的收藏品。本拍品經Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2552', 'Summarex 1.5/8.5cm Black Paint', 'Summarex 1.5/8.5cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_181_9.jpg', '181', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'This Summarex was delivered as SOOCX on 12th August 1943 to Berlin with delivery number 29777. There are only 2 lenses delivered to Berlin of these BLACK SUMMAREX. The lens hood is a special with early black clamp-screw, cut out for use in aeroplanes. This lens comes with both lens caps and original red box.   <br />\r\n*The chrome hood is not included in this lot.', '此拍品為非常早期的Summarex 1.5/8.5cm鏡頭，此鏡於1934年8月12日交付柏林，交貨編號為29777; 此款鏡頭只有兩支付運到柏林。連同此鏡還有一個黑色給空軍用的遮光罩，可用螺絲固定在鏡頭上，而且遮光罩的取景孔位與後期銀色版本不同 (請參考圖片)。此拍品配有鏡頭前後蓋及紅色包裝盒。<br />\r\n*此拍品並不包括銀色遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2553', 'Leather Case for IIIF Swedish Army', 'Leather Case for IIIF Swedish Army', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_182_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_182_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_182_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_182_4.jpg', '182', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This leather case is made for IIIF Swedish Army. In order to have a better protection under the extreme weather, a special material is added inside of the case, extremely rare.', '此皮套是徠卡特別為IIIf瑞典軍機製造的皮套，為方便於嚴寒天氣下使用並達到更佳的保暖效果，此皮套內特別加入厚布料，市場上罕見，是與IIIf瑞士軍機配套的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2554', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_183_7.jpg', '183', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'M3 Bundeseigentum Olive finishing produced for German military, total 144 units were made. This camera is from the first batch (#910501-910600). Camera with double stroke, and engraved “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5418” on the rear of the top plate. Small part of covering leather was off. The set includes a Hektor 4.5/13.5cm (#1509781) with “Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625” engraved, completes with both caps; also an Elmar 2.8/50mm (#1934707) with a IROOA hood and numbers “12-130-0927” engraved on it. Moreover, this set completes with a film container, cassettes, two color filters, one plastic case for filer, shutter release with box (14076N), light meter with case (#39916) and “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5710” engraved on case. Lastly, this set comes with a leather storage case with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5829” engraved, very rare.', '此拍品名稱中的Bundeseigentum是指“聯邦資產”。根據記錄，此款相機在1957年至1968年間生產，第一批機身號為910501至910600，生產100台。此軍用版M3為兩次過片，機背刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5418」字樣，機身皮革經歷戰爭的洗禮後有部份剝落，及有明顯使用痕跡，部份油漆有經後期修補。此套機包括以下鏡頭及配件: Hektor 4.5/13.5cm(#1509781)，上面刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625」字樣，連前後蓋﹔而Elmar 2.8/50mm(#1934707)則連同IROOA遮光罩，遮光罩上刻有數字“12-130-0927”。此外，套機連同菲林盒、菲林匣、兩塊顏色濾鏡、濾鏡盒、快門線連盒(10476N)、測光錶連套(#39916)，套上更刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5710」字樣。整套套機放於軍綠色皮箱內，皮箱背面刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5829」，十分稀有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2555', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_184_10.jpg', '184', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'M3 olive 927695 - serial numbers of the 927XXX olive not listed in shipping records, but cameras are genuine. There are olive M3 between 927671 and 927734. However, those cameras usually have a quite shiny paint, as well as &quot;Bundeseigentum&quot; AND the contract number engraving on the rear top plate. The camera to me looks fine, but seems to have been repaired at the Leitz factory somewhen around 1960 or so: There are top- and bottom plate mounted on the camera, of a more matte paint, such as usually it occurs on olive M3 cameras with 11xxxxx. serial numbers. This top plate does not show the contract number. The bottom plate with a golden eagle sticker even. The camera body shell still carries the original coarse grain vulcanite. Authentic olive M3 with top-, bottom plate and rear door replaced in the 1960s, with nice patina. Camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此機927695雖然不是在工廠交貨紀錄上，但是此機絕對是真品，在機身號碼927671-927734之間，工廠也有出產M3 Olive，是極罕有的原裝Olive，擁有二次過片及選用了適合用於戰場用的荔枝飾皮。這兩個特徵並不常見於後期的M3 Olive，十分特別。此機底蓋貼有金色的鷹標，機頂與底蓋的漆較啞，這通常會發生在機身號#11xxxxx的相機中；機身後背僅刻有「Bundeseigentum」字樣。<br />\r\n此機配有Hektor 4.5/135mm鏡頭(#1509619)，鏡身上刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625」的字樣，連前後蓋；同時連同Trinovid 7x42 BA望遠鏡(#874404)。整套套機連同皮箱、相機帶及布袋。除此以外，此套機更配有E39黃色濾鏡(#13086H)、快門線及測光錶(#87998)連套，測光錶上更刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608」。此機在1960年送往徠卡工廠維修並有更換過部份配件；此套機經Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2556', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_185_9.jpg', '185', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Only 208 units M1 Olive finishing in three batches were produced for Germany Army. Number 980451-980500; 1035926-1036000 and 1098101-1098183. The three cameras of this lot were from the three different production batches. The camera #980470 and #1035952 use the top plate like MP, “Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739” was engraved on the rear of the top plate and “5+13.5” on the viewfinder frame; For #1098178, only “Bundeseigentum” was engraved. This set comes with a Hektor 4.5/135mm lens (#1718738) with engraving “Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625” and two Elmar 2.8/50mm lenses (#1723544 &amp; #1934818); All lenses come with front caps. This set also comes with a hood with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529” engraved, which is suitable for these three lenses.', 'M1 Olive是徠卡為德軍生產的相機，總產量只有208台，共有三個批次，分別為：1960年生產50台(編號980451-980500)，1961年生產75台(編號1035926-1036000)及1964年生產83台(編號1098101-1098183)。此套相機分別來自這三個不同的批次。當中機身編號980470及1035952的機背上，刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739」字樣，相機採用與MP相同的機頂蓋，並刻有「5+13.5」取景框字樣﹔而機號1098175的機背上則刻有「Bundeseigentum」字樣。此套機分別連同一支Hektor 4.5/135mm鏡頭 (#1718738)，刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-120-1625」及兩支Elmar 2.8/50mm鏡頭(#1723544及#1934818)，另搭配三個鏡頭前蓋，同時連同刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529」字樣的遮光罩，均適用於以上三支鏡頭。經半世紀，並以三個批次中各保留一台至今半世紀，非常難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2557', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_186_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_186_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_186_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_186_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_186_5.jpg', '186', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is one of the M1 Olive finishing camera for Bundeseiggentum military from the second batch (1035926 – 1036000), engraved with “Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739” on the back. Using the top plate like MP, also engraved “5+13.5” on the top plate. It comes with an Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1334992) with the words “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5419” engraved. Whole set completes with Olive leather case engraved with “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5423” and Leica Meter MC Booster Cell.', '此機是第二批西德軍用的M1 Olive相機之一，生產編號為1035926至1036000。此機機頂背後上刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739」字樣，機頂採用與MP相同的機頂蓋，並刻有「5+13.5」取景框字樣。配搭銀色的Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭(#1334992)，鏡頭上同樣刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5419」字樣﹔連同軍綠色的皮套，刻有「Bundeseigentum 12-121-5423」及徠卡測光增強片。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2558', 'Elcan-M 2/66mm with KE-7A “U.S. Army” Set', 'Elcan-M 2/66mm with KE-7A “U.S. Army” Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_187_10.jpg', '187', '', '1,416,000', null, null, null, null, 'A total of 505 units of Leica KE-7A were produced and in which about 460 units were assigned to the U.S. Military while the rest were civilian version. The military version engraved with serial number, military force number \"FSN 6720-165-7115\" and contract number \"CONT F42600-71-C-2429US\" were engraved on the rear of the top plate of the camera. <br />\r\nThis camera set comes with Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0131) and extremely rare Elcan-M 2/66mm lens (#286-0003). This Elcan-M 2/66mm engraved with its serial number and military contract number “VH6760-168-3240” on the name ring. It is specially made for the U.S. Navy with ultra-high resolution. The lens comprises with 9 glass elements and is extremely rare in the market. According to some literature, it used by North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) during the Cold War. <br />\r\nThis set comes with instructions, packing, cable release, strap and a matching leather case; for Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0131) comes with hood and cap, Elcan-M 2/66mm comes with both caps as well. Whole set is in mint condition, extremely rare.<br />\r\n(*The pistol in this lot is a model only.)', '此套機包括了一支極罕見的Elcan-M 2/66mm鏡頭，此Elcan-M 2/66mm鏡頭除刻上機身序號「283-0003」外，另刻有軍用編號「VH6760-168-3240」。根據資料顯示，此鏡是Elcan設計予美國海軍(US Navy)的超高解像力鏡頭，也有一些文獻指於冷戰時期給北大西洋公約組織(NATO，North Atlantic Treaty Organization)的軍隊使用，鏡頭以9枚鏡片設計，產量稀少；近幾年的拍賣市場上其跡罕見。<br />\r\n屬同一拍品的KE-7A，總產量為505部，約460部是屬於美國軍方的採購合約，其他的則是民用版本。軍用版除刻有機身序號外，還包括軍用編號與合約編號，民用版本則只刻有機身序號。而此套機的機背上分別刻有軍用編號及合約編號，號碼分別是「FSN 6720-165-7115」及「CONT F42600-71-C-2429US」。<br />\r\n此套機同時還配有Elcan–M 2/50mm (#276-0131)，遮光罩連蓋。而Elcan-M 2/66mm配有鏡頭前後蓋﹔套機連同Trinovid 10X40望遠鏡(#679814)及其皮套、說明書、外包裝盒、快門線、掛帶及與相機相同號碼的相機皮套。此套機產量稀少，成色極佳的軍用版本更是寥寥無幾，所以此套機可說是收藏珍品。<br />\r\n(註:拍品中的手槍為模型槍)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2559', 'KE-7A “US Army”', 'KE-7A “US Army”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_188_8.jpg', '188', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'A total of 505 units of Leica KE-7A were produced and in which about 460 units were assigned to the U.S. Military. This camera engraved the serial number “1294713”, Military Force number &quot;FSN 6720-165-7115&quot; and contract number &quot;CONT F42600-71-C-2429US&quot; were engraved on the rear of the top plate. This camera set comes with Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0296) and hood with cap.', 'KE-7A總產量為505部，約460部是屬於美國軍方的採購合約，其餘的則是民用版本。軍用版除刻有機身序號外，還包括軍用編號與合約編號，民用版本則只刻有機身序號。而此套機的機背上分別刻有軍用編號及合約編號，號碼分別是「FSN 6720-165-7115」及「CONT F42600-71-C-2429US」。<br />\r\n此套機連同Elcan-M 2/50mm(#276-0296)及遮光罩連蓋；成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2560', 'KE-7A', 'KE-7A', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_189_9.jpg', '189', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'A total of 505 units of Leica KE-7A were produced and in which the majority was assigned to the U.S. Military while only 45 units were civilian version. This set is civilian version with only serial number engraved on the back. It comes with Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0434) and front lens cap.', 'KE-7A總產量為505部，大部份是美國軍方的採購合約用機，其中僅有45台為民用版本。此拍品應為民用版，機背上只刻有機身序號，沒有合約編號。成色極新，是KE-7A系列收藏者必不可少的版本。連Elcan-M 2/50mm(#276-0434)及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2561', 'M4 “Sweden Military” Set', 'M4 “Sweden Military” Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_190_11.jpg', '190', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This set is a special order from Swedish Army, with three lenses. It comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm (#2394730) with both caps, Summicron-M 2/50mm (#2350991) and Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm (#2343876) with both caps. Moreover, it comes with light meter (#35552), mini ball head (#14121), hood (#12585) with cap, strap, batch record, instruction manual and leather case.', '應瑞典軍方要求少量訂製，官方訂單貨號為94400-85-000-000-000-01。一機三鏡套裝，套機包括M4銀色機身(#1251014)、Summicron-M 2/35mm(#2394730)連鏡頭前後蓋、Summicron-M 2/50mm(#2350991)及Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm(#2343876)均連鏡頭前後蓋。另配有測光錶(#35552)、迷你雲台(#14121)、遮光罩(#12585)連蓋、相機帶、說明書、批次清單及存放套機的黑色皮箱。成色極新，操作完好。配件如此齊備實在是非常罕有，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2562', 'R3 Safari The LAST Piece', 'R3 Safari The LAST Piece', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_191_11.jpg', '191', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'The camera is the last piece of 5,000 units of R3 Safari which produced in 1977-1978. It comes with box, certificate, guarantee card, instruction, body cap and strap. It also comes with an unopened Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2920703) with hood (#12509) and both caps; Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2891909) with box, certificate and both caps; Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2882393) with box, guarantee card, both caps and Trinovid 10x22C binocular (#940456) with box.', '這是徠卡軍綠色版R3的最後一台，在1977-1978年間，徠卡共生產了5,000台軍綠色版本R3。此相機機身號碼為1485000，特別編號是L960。連包裝盒、證書、保證卡、說明書、機身蓋及相機帶。另外，此套機亦配有全新未開封的Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2920703)，連包裝、遮光罩(#12509)及鏡頭前後蓋;其次是Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2891909)及Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2882393)均連同包裝證書及前後蓋，最後Trinovid 10x22C望遠鏡(#940456)備有包裝。整套相機成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2563', 'Reid', 'Reid', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_192_7.jpg', '192', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Reid camera was made by Reid & Sigrist Ltd, which was a manufacturer of aircraft parts and precision instruments, located in Leicester, England. Most of the Reid cameras were produced for British military. This camera is remodel version without the viewfinder for the special use such as the Submarine, with “Reid & Sigrist Ltd” and “LEICESTER. Eng.” engraved on the top plate, and the British military number “AP8886” on the leather of the back.', '英國軍用飛機零件和精密儀器製造商Reid & Sigrist Ltd，在德國徠卡取得設計藍圖，在二次大戰後仿製出媲美徠卡的相機Reid，相機主要供應給英國軍方。Reid的製造技術非常精準，是英國當時最優秀的相機。此機沒有取景器，是特別供潛水艇使用的改裝款。此機機頂刻有「Reid & Sigrist Ltd」及「LEICESTER. Eng.」字樣，機背飾皮刻有「AP8886」，為軍用機專用的編號。帶有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2564', 'Kardon Military Leica Copy', 'Kardon Military Leica Copy', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_193_8.jpg', '193', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a military camera produced by Kardon USA during the World War II, approximately 750 pieces were made. All military version and civilian version were discontinued in 1948. The most significant character can be identified by a metal plate on the back, containing the military designation and serial number. Military cameras are lack of the serial number on the top plate that the civilian models have. This camera comes with Kodak Ektar 2/47mm lens and leather case, with some signs of use.', '此相機為二次大戰期間，由美國Kardon公司仿徠卡相機而製，並於大約1948年停產。此拍品為軍用版本，共生產約750台；軍用版本的相機背後，會附有一片金屬片，上面會刻有軍用號碼及機身號，而民用版只有機頂位置刻有機身號。此相機連同Kodak Ektar 2/47mm鏡頭及皮套，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2565', 'M6 Chrome with the Sultan of Brunei Signature', 'M6 Chrome with the Sultan of Brunei Signature', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_194_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_194_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_194_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_194_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_194_5.jpg', '194', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'This is a special camera with engraving the full name of the Sultan of Brunei and his signature on top plate, extremely rare. It comes with body cap, strap, packing and papers.', '此M6相機機頂刻有汶萊國王的全名及其簽名。經典的銀色M6機身上，配上汶萊國王的簽名，相信只此一台，絕對是收藏佳品。套機連機身蓋、相機帶及包裝證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2566', 'M6 Gold-plated with Diamond for 50th Birthday of the Sultan of Brunei', 'M6 Gold-plated with Diamond for 50th Birthday of the Sultan of Brunei', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_195_9.jpg', '195', '', '1,003,000', null, null, null, null, 'In 1996, in order to commemorate the 50th birthday of His Majesty Sultan of Brunei on 15th Jul 1996, Brunei ordered the special limited edition from Leica in 1996. It was a special gift to prestige guests of honore, and never release to market for sale. The special number of this set is HB-039, with one fine cut diamond and the royal emblem engraving at the top plate. ”15th July 1996” and ”In Commemoration of The 50th Birthday of His Majesty Sultan” are engraved at the back. The camera covered in red lizard leather and plated in 24 carat gold. The set comes with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH lens (#3751039) in 24 carat gold, with ”HB039-125“ imprinted at the front lens deterring; also with gold lens front cap with the royal emblem, extremely rare! The camera comes with body cap, strap, lens cloth, lens rear cap, wooden box, certificate of diamond and all packing.', '本拍品在外觀上已使人望之儼然，在機身及鏡頭上均鍍以24K黃金，黃金機身上鑲嵌了一枚珍奇奪目的美鑽，根據拍品中附有的EGL證書，此鑽石淨度達VVS1的F級。<br />\r\n源於1996年為慶祝汶萊國王50歲壽辰，汶萊皇室向徠卡訂製125套的24K黃金鑽石套機。在24K鍍金機身上覆以高貴的紅色蜥蝪皮，機頂上刻有專屬號碼「HB039」；機背則刻有國 王50壽辰的日期–「15th July 1996」及「In Commemoration of The 50th Birthday of His Majesty Sultan」字樣，完美演繹出皇室尊貴的氣魄。<br />\r\n此機連同24K鍍金Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#3751039)，鏡頭上亦刻有專屬號碼「HB039-125」，並配有精緻的鍍金鏡頭前蓋。附設機身蓋、鏡頭後蓋、背帶、鏡頭布、精美木盒、鑽石證書及包裝證書齊全。<br />\r\n此款相機產量稀少，只為慶祝汶萊國王生日饋贈國賓而生產，未曾公開發售，讓收藏家專屬尊榮﹔配上極致璀璨的黃金鑽石造型，是珍貴的收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2567', 'O-series Oskar Barnack 1879-2004 Edition', 'O-series Oskar Barnack 1879-2004 Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_196_7.jpg', '196', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica special edition Oskar Barnack 1879-2004 Jubilee Edition Set marks the 125th birthday of Oskar Barnack (1879-1936), the designer of the first 35mm Leica camera. In homage to the inventor of the 35mm system, the set comprises the true-to-detail new edition of a historic camera type, the LEICA O series “Prototype 2”, which Oskar Barnack developed as a second camera after the “Ur Leica” and tested in practice. The LEICA 0 series “Prototype 2” is in full working order and demands intensive study of all photographic parameters and concentration on each step of exposure. This set comes with all packing, papers, CD &amp; leather case.', '為紀念Oskar Barnack 125歲誕辰，徠卡特別推出了1,000 套Leica O-Series“Prototype 2”原型復刻機。Oskar Barnack是創製首部35mm 菲林徠卡相機的設計師， 於光學攝影及徠卡發展史上皆有崇高地位。早期繼Ur-Leica與Leica O-Series的製造與試用經驗後，Oskar Barnack在1923年又加以改良，製造出他心目中最理想的相機”Prototype 2”，成為徠卡富有傳奇色彩的35mm相機之先驅之一，也是現代化金屬加工量產相機的始祖。此復刻機連同包裝證書，光碟及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2568', 'M4-2 Gold O.Barnack with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', 'M4-2 Gold O.Barnack with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_197_10.jpg', '197', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'In 1979, 1,000 Gold M4-2 cameras with matching Summilux 1.4/50mm lens (#2848124) were made to commemorate the centenary of Oskar Barnack, creator and pioneer of the most famous Leica camera. The camera plated with 24 carat gold and covered with precious lizard skin, engraved with facsimile Oskar Barnack‘s signature at the back, as well as “1879-1979”. It comes with wooden box, outer box, papers, both lens caps, body cap, hood, strap and a golden Leica lapel pin. Hot shoe shows very light oxidation. In mint- condition.', '此套相機是為紀念徠卡相機之父 Oskar Barnack誕生100年而推出的，配有Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#2848124)。相機及鏡頭部分組件均以24K鍍金製成，機身覆以珍貴蜥蝪皮，共生產1,000台。此機紀念號碼為100-0941。機背刻有Oskar Barnack簽名及「1879-1979」字樣。此套機連同包裝盒、精美木盒、證書、鏡頭前後蓋、機身蓋、背帶、遮光罩連蓋及同樣是限量的相機造型襟針。相機熱靴位置有輕微氧化，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2569', 'Leica M6 150 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Leica Photographie with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', 'Leica M6 150 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Leica Photographie with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_198_8.jpg', '198', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'In 1989, Leica M6 150 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Leica Photographie was launched to commemorate the 150th Anniversary of the invention of photography and the 75th Anniversary of Leica, 1,250 units were made. The camera body is decorated with snake leather and platinum-plated. This set is numbered A098. It comes with platinum Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3482112) and completes with certificate, hood, hood cap and filter, in like new condition.', '在1989年，徠卡為慶祝底片發明150年及徠卡成立75週年，特別推出1,250台鍍鉑金紀念機。機身覆以蛇皮，特顯尊貴。同時配有鉑金版的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#3482112)。此套機的特別號碼為A098，連證書、遮光罩連蓋及濾鏡，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2570', 'M6 Colombo 1992 Special 500th Anniversary Edition', 'M6 Colombo 1992 Special 500th Anniversary Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_199_7.jpg', '199', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, '200 M6 Colombo were made to commemorate the quincentenary of Christopher Columbus’s voyage to America. The top plate and front lens cap are engraved with &quot;500 Colombo 92” and “1492~1992 500\' SCOPERTA DELL \'AMERICA, ITALIA”. The camera body decorated with green leather. The set comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (#3623783) and completes with certificate and packing.', '為紀念哥倫布發現美洲新大陸500週年，徠卡於1992年特別推出200台紀念機。機頂及鏡頭前蓋刻有「500 Colombo 92 」及「1492~1992 500\' SCOPERTA DELL \'AMERICA, ITALIA」字樣，機身覆以綠色飾皮，造型獨特，並配有Summicron-M 2/50mm鏡頭(#3623783)。整套套機包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2571', 'M6 “LHSA 25th Anniversary” Camera Set', 'M6 “LHSA 25th Anniversary” Camera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_200_7.jpg', '200', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 25th Anniversary of American Leica Historical Society (LHSA), Leica launched the LHSA 25th Anniversary camera set in 1996, it comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome, Summicron-M 2/50mm and Summicron-M 2/90mm. Only 151 units were produced. The top plate engraved the logo of LHSA and &quot;1968-1993&quot;, while the rear of the top plate engraved &quot;Special Edition of 151 Cameras for LHSA 25th Anniversary&quot;. Also, the body is decorated with ostrich leather. This camera set was available to LHSA members only, extremely valuable. The commemorative number of this camera set is 25-111 and the front ring of the lens engraved “LHSA 25th ANNIVERSARY 25-111”. It comes with wooden box, carton box, body caps, front and rear lens caps, in brand new condition.', '1996年，為紀念美國徠卡歷史協會(LHSA)成立25周年，徠卡發行了151套LHSA 25周年紀念一機三鏡套機，包括銀色Summicron-M 2/35mm、Summicron-M 2/50mm及Summicron-M 2/90mm鏡頭。機頂刻有 LHSA 標誌及「1968-1993」字樣，而機背則刻有「Special Edition of 151 Cameras for LHSA 25th Anniversary」字樣，銀色機身更飾以駝鳥皮。此機紀念號碼為25-111，而鏡頭亦刻有「LHSA 25th ANNIVERSARY 25-111」字樣。此套機當時僅向會員發售，並沒有在市場公開出售，因而特別珍貴。整套拍品配有木盒、包裝盒，機身蓋及三支鏡頭的前後蓋，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2572', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', 'M6 Gold Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_201_6.jpg', '201', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th Anniversary of the sultan’s accession to the throne on 1st October 1992, the royal family of Brunei ordered 350 sets of 24 carat gold-plated Leica M6 Sambutan Jubli Perak. The national totem of Sultan engraved on the top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak” engraved at the back. The camera is decorated with red lizard skin embossed ornamentation. The camera comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in 24 carat gold-plated (#3653542), engraved “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92”. The commemorative number is the lucky number HB-018. This set comes with wooden box and certificate, in like new condition.', '1992年10月1日，汶萊國王登基25週年，汶萊皇室為此向徠卡訂製了350台24K 鍍金的M6 連Summilux-M 1.4/50mm套機作為紀念及饋贈賓客，從未對外公開發售。紀念機的紀念號碼由 HB-001開始，M6機頂上刻有汶萊的國徽，機背刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak」字樣；機身罕見地配有紅色蜥蝪皮，奢華雅緻並重，彰顯皇室尊貴地位。 幸運的是此拍品的紀念號為HB-018。<br />\r\n此套機連24K鍍金的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#3653542)，鏡頭前刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92」的字樣，連木盒及證書，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2573', 'M6 Gold Dragon', 'M6 Gold Dragon', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_202_9.jpg', '202', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'M6 Gold Dragon Edition comes with a matching Summicron-M 2/50mm, only 300 units were made. The camera body is decorated with red snake leather and has a dragon engraved on the top plate and the wooden box. The commemorate number is 213/300, lens number is 3700213, with full packing, in brand new condition.', '此M6金龍機連Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭(#3700213)，限量300台，此套相機的紀念號碼為213/300。機身配有紅色蛇皮，機頂及木盒均刻有傳統中國龍圖案。包裝證書齊全，全新未經使用，極有收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2574', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_203_9.jpg', '203', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th anniversary of accession the throne of Sultan of Brunei on 5th Oct 1992, the royal family of Brunei ordered the special limited edition in 250 sets of M6 platinum Sambutan Jubli Perak, which never release to market for sale. With symbol of Brunei on top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92” engraved at the back and name ring of the lens. The camera is decorated with grey lizard skin. The commemorative numbers of these two sets are lucky number <b>HB-088</b> and <b>HB-188</b>, both with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3726394 / #3726353). Two sets are complete with box, wooden box, instruction and certificate.', '擁有極為吉祥的號碼，也是此款紀念機中最多8字的一對汶萊紀念機。為慶祝汶萊國王登基25週年，汶萊皇室特別向德國徠卡訂製的M6鉑金紀念機﹔對於此款紀念機，徠卡公司沒有對外發行，只供汶萊國皇饋贈特別貴賓用，限量250台。兩台紀念機的特別號碼分別為<b>HB-088</b>及<b>HB-188</b>，同樣配有Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#3726394 / #3726353)。機頂刻有兩個黑及紅色的汶萊皇室徽章，機背及鏡頭上刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92」字樣，而鏡頭及機身均以鉑金製成，機身覆以灰色蜥蝪皮，盡顯尊貴。此套紀念機均連同包裝、木盒、說明書及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2575', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei Silver Jubilee Edition 1992', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_204_9.jpg', '204', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th anniversary of accession the throne of Sultan of Brunei , the royal family of Brunei ordered the special limited edition in total 250 sets from Leica in 1995, which never release to market for sale. The special number of this set is HB-168, with symbol of Brunei on top plate and “Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92” engraved at the back and name ring of the lens. The camera is decorated with grey lizard skin. It comes with a Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3726380), both caps, body cap, wooden box, packing and papers.', '為慶祝汶萊國王登基25周年，汶萊皇室特別向德國徠卡訂製了M6鉑金紀念機﹔此款紀念機徠卡公司沒有對外發行，只供汶萊國王饋贈特別貴賓用，限量250台。此機紀念號為HB-168，機頂刻有兩個黑及紅色的汶萊皇室徽章，機背及鏡頭上刻有「Sambutan Jubli Perak 5 OCT. 92」字樣，十分獨特。此機連同Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鉑金鏡頭(#3726380)，機身覆以灰色蜥蝪皮，盡顯尊貴。連鏡頭前後蓋、機身蓋、木盒及包裝證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2576', 'M6 Platinum Schmidt Group 1896-1996 100 Years Edition', 'M6 Platinum Schmidt Group 1896-1996 100 Years Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_205_8.jpg', '205', '', '54,280', null, null, null, null, 'In 1996, in order to commemorate the 100th years of Schmidt group establishing as well as creating their first presence in Asia Pacific Region, 188 units of Leica M6 special edition were launched. The camera uses the M6 body with platinum plating and the word “Limited Edition of 188 pcs for Schmidt Group” was engraved at the back, also the logo of Schmidt Group was engraved on top. It fits with an Elmar-M 2.8/50mm lens (#3741328), with special number SC-028/188. It completes with both lens caps, body cap, strap, cleansing cloth, packing and papers.', '為慶祝興華集團成立100週年，188鉑金版M6於1996年推出，機頂刻上興華集團的徽章，機背則刻有「Limited Edition of 188 pcs for Schmidt Group」字樣。此機擁有特別吉祥的紀念號碼<b>SC 028</b>，連同Elmar-M 2.8/50mm鏡頭(#3741328)，鏡頭前端同樣刻有特別號碼SC-028/188。連同鏡頭前後蓋、機身蓋、手帶、鏡頭布及包裝證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2577', 'M6 Thai Gold with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M6 Thai Gold with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_206_7.jpg', '206', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'In 1996, to celebrate the 50th Anniversary of the Thai King’s accession to the throne, limited edition of 700 units were made. Top engraved with their King\'s exclusive printed emblem, 24K gold-plated and lizard leather body with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (#3695641-HM 641), this camera is one of the perfect camera for collectors. Come with wooden box, outer box, strap, cleaning cloth, both caps, papers and body cap. In new condition.', '1996 年，為慶祝泰國國王登基 50 週年而特別訂製，限量700 台，此機紀念號碼為 HM-641。機身為 24K 鍍金，配Summicron-M 2/50mm鏡頭(#3695641-HM 641)，機身貼上棕紅色蜥蝪皮。機頂刻有泰王專屬印徽，是收藏家心目中完美的紀念機之一。連精美木盒、包裝紙盒、尼龍帶、 Leica鏡頭布、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋、證書。全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2578', 'M6 TTL 0.72 Black Paint Millennium Edition “Hanns-Peter Cohn”', 'M6 TTL 0.72 Black Paint Millennium Edition “Hanns-Peter Cohn”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_207_9.jpg', '207', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This Millennium Edition camera set is owned by previous Leica CEO – Mr. Hanns-Peter Cohn with his initial “H-P. COHN” engraved on the top plate. Two black paint lenses are included, which are Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#4010044) and Summicron-M 2/35mm (#400044). The serial numbers of these items are ended with number <b>44</b>. Both lenses come with front lens cap. This set comes with a certificate and a letter from Hanns-Peter Cohn in which he mentioned he brought this camera with him during several vacations in 2000-2004. Besides this set also include a photograph which he took on 11st October, 2001 at Ground Zero, New York.', '此套機是德國徠卡上一任行政總裁Hanns-Peter Cohn所擁有的千禧年紀念機，是此紀念機中的第44台，機頂上原廠特別刻有其名字簡寫「H-P. COHN」，甚有紀念價值。此套機連同兩支黑漆鏡頭，分別是Summicron-M 2/35mm(#400044)及Summilux-M 1.4/50mm(#4010044)；此一機兩鏡的後四位編號<b>0044均相同</b>，可謂十分獨特。此拍品連同證書及由Hanns-Peter Cohn親筆信件及作品乙張，證明此機為他所擁有，信中更提及於2000-2004年間他曾多次攜同此機出遊外地；拍品所連同的作品為他於2001年10月11日在紐約世貿大廈遺址拍下的一幅照片。整套拍品代表性高，甚有收藏價值。此拍品連同兩個鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2579', 'MP Hermes', 'MP Hermes', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_1.JPG,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_208_7.jpg', '208', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'The ”Edition Hermes” is a special edition of 500 silver-chrome LEICA MP cameras covered with exquisite Barenia calfskin supplied by the famed Parisian high-fashion house Hermes. The naturally brown leather harmonizes particularly well with the silver chrome finish of the camera. In addition to Summicron-M 2/3mm ASPH lens (#101/500) that is also finished in silver chrome with hood, this special edition includes a camera carrying strap that is handcrafted by Hermes, using the same exquisite Barenia leather. The lens hood, the camera body cover as well as the both caps of the lens are made of solid brass and they are finished in silver chrome too. Whole set comes with box and papers, Leica pouch, filter, in like new condition.', '自2000年法國時尚品牌Hermes入股徠卡後，於2003年徠卡結合Hermes Barenia小牛皮推出第一款聯名相機MP，全球限量500台。此機機身覆以Hermes的棕色小牛皮，加上銀色機身，並搭配銀色的Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH(#101/500)鏡頭連遮光罩。套機還包括Hermès手工製小牛皮的相機帶、徠卡布袋及濾鏡、包裝證書全齊﹔配以純銅製造，呈銀色的機身蓋及鏡頭前後蓋，盡顯兩大百年品牌氣派。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2580', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_209_10.jpg', '209', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 35th Anniversary of American Leica Historical Society (LHSA), MP LHSA was launched with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH and Leicavit. This lens is numbered 3966546, with Leicavit (#00167) and a special Hammertone lens hood, only 1000 units were made. This set comes with all packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '為紀念美國徠卡歷史協會成立35週年所發行的MP Hammerton連Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH鏡頭。鏡頭是仿八枚玉造型，編號為3966546，並配有快速過片器Leicavit(#00167)及特別的Hammertone遮光罩。限量生產1,000台。此套機包裝配件齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2581', 'MP Classic with Summicron-M2/50mm Black Paint', 'MP Classic with Summicron-M2/50mm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_210_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_210_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_210_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_210_4.jpg', '210', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'MP classic was made following early MP design, only 500 units were made. It does not have any electronics, as would be necessary to use along with an exposure meter for example. The commemorate number of the camera set is 438. It comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm (#3983672), box, papers, body cap, hood, hood cap, both lens caps and strap, in brand new condition.', '此黑漆MP套機是徠卡特別仿照早期MP機而生產，機身不帶電子測光系統，限量500套。此套機紀念號碼為438，連Summicron-M 2/50mm黑漆鏡頭(#3983672) ，配有包裝證書、機身蓋、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及相機帶。全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2582', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Black Paint', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_211_10.jpg', '211', '', '115,000', null, null, null, null, 'In 2005, Leica and LHSA together launched MP3 Black Paint LHSA Special Edition, 1000 units in black painted or chrome were made. This set is in black painted and numbered 575/1000. It comes with a black painted Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens (#3990902) and Leicavit (#00167), completes with all packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '發表於2005年，是徠卡與美國徠卡歷史協會共同推出的紀念機，限量1,000台；分別有黑漆版及銀色版，此拍品為經典黑漆版，紀念號碼為575/1000。配有黑漆Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭 (#3990902)、快速過片器Leicavit (#00167)及遮光罩連蓋。整套套機類似MP的復刻機種，甚有徠卡古典味。套機包裝配件齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2583', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Chrome', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_212_8.jpg', '212', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 2005, Leica together with LHSA launched MP3 LHSA Special Edition and only 375 sets in chrome were made. This set comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens (#3990113) and Leicavit (#00115) and completes with all packing, papers, body cap, hood, hood cap, both caps, lens case, battery cover and camera strap, in brand new condition.', '發表於2005年，是徠卡與美國徠卡歷史協會共同推出的紀念機，限量1,000台；分別有黑漆版及銀色版，當中銀色套機限量375套；此套套機為銀色套裝，紀念號碼為143/1000。配有Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH 鏡頭(#3990113)、快速過片器Leicavit(#00115)及遮光罩連蓋。整套套機類似MP的復刻機種，甚有徠卡古典味。套機包裝證書齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2584', 'M3J Black Paint', 'M3J Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_213_6.jpg', '213', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'M3J in black paint finished comes with box and papers, in mint condition.', '徠卡以經典的M3早期版相機為藍本，加以優化而推出的M3J黑漆相機，全球只生產200台。此機機身與經典M3一樣，相機背帶扣有著早期M3的設計，荔枝紋飾皮，極具收藏價值，是收藏家追棒的對象。包裝證書齊全，背帶扣有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2585', 'M7 100th Anniversary of the 1911 China Revolution with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', 'M7 100th Anniversary of the 1911 China Revolution with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_214_11.jpg', '214', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'On 10th October 2011, Leica launched in China a limited edition M7 to commemorate the 100th Anniversary of the Xinhai Revolution. Clad in green leather, this edition is limited to 101 pieces. The top plate is also inscribed with the Chinese words &quot;天下為公 孫文&quot;, and over at the back has the Chinese words &quot;辛亥革命一百周年纪念，1911 - 2011”. A matching Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens (#4102718) comes with the camera. This set also comes with all packing and papers in brand new condition.', '為紀念辛亥革命100週年，徠卡特別於2011年10月10日推出了101套M7辛亥革命紀念套機。黑漆機身配以綠色駝鳥皮，頂蓋刻有「天下為公 孫文」字樣﹔機身背面則刻有「辛亥革命一百周年纪念，1911 - 2011」。連同Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭(#4102718)，包裝證書齊全，成色如新，未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2586', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_215_6.jpg', '215', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Only 100 units MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition were made. This camera features a copper and zinc-alloy body while the upper and lower lid are painted with military grey, which resembles the Leica M2 Grey film camera on the top plate. This camera is MP 100-52. The Chinese characters “ 精彩一百. 1912-2011” engraved on the top plate and a plum blossom totem engraved on the rear plate. This camera completes with packing, papers, body cap, batteries, strap and presentation box, in brand new condition.', '徠卡推出的MP「建國一百週年紀念機」，限量100台。此套機以徠卡原裝木盒珍藏，配有銅鋅合金機身，機身金屬部份噴上特別的軍灰綠色，色澤如同M2 Grey底片相機。機上刻有「精彩一百. 1912-2011」字樣，機背則刻有梅花圖案。此機紀念號碼為MP100-052。配有包裝證書、木盒、機身蓋、電池及相機帶，全新未經使用，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2587', 'M9-P Hermes Pre-Production', 'M9-P Hermes Pre-Production', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_216_8.jpg', '216', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'In 2012, Leica teamed up with luxury label Hermes to create a special edition of Leica M9-P set. This set is the pre-production version with a special engraving “N13/20” on top plate. A Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#4128064) is included, very rare. The camera is designed by Audi designer - Walter de Silva, various features of the camera body have been designed, i.e., top plate, the shutter speed dial, the multi-function wheel and shutter release covered with Hermes Vean Swift calfskin; also the shape of Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens has been redesigned. <br />\r\nThis set comes with inner presentation box, certificate, instruction, both caps, leather strap, cotton gloves, cleaning cloth, battery and charger.', '徠卡與Hermes於2012年合作推出由Audi汽車設計總監Walter de Silva設計的M9-P套機，全球限量300套，而此套機更是正式投產前首20套的試行版，為徠卡進入時尚圈作熱身用。機頂上刻有試行版編號「N13/20」。此機的頂蓋、快門鈕、功能轉盤及快門釋放鍵，甚至連配備的銀色Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭(#4128064)，其外觀及刻字也是重新設計。而銀色機身上覆以Hermes高級手製小牛皮，盡顯奢華。<br />\r\n此套機配有展示盒、證書、說明書、鏡頭前後蓋、相機帶、棉質手套、相機抹布、電池及充電器。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2588', 'The Hong Kong Jockey Club Leica X2 &amp; Leica Silverline 8 x 42 Special Edition', 'The Hong Kong Jockey Club Leica X2 &amp; Leica Silverline 8 x 42 Special Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_217_10.jpg', '217', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This special edition comes with Leica X2 (#4673236) digital camera and Silverline Ultravid 8 x 42 binoculars (#1621438). In 2012, 100 units were launched exclusively available for The Hong Kong Jockey Club members. The camera and binoculars covered with blue leather, and printed with &quot;The Hong Kong Jockey Club\'\' words and Jockey Club logo on the body and binoculars. This set with camera leather case and binoculars case, leather strap, wipe lens cloth, manual, certificates and black piano paint surface wooden box.', '此套X2數碼相機(#4673236)連徠卡Silverline Ultravid 8 x 42望遠鏡(#1621438)，是2012年香港賽馬會特別向徠卡定制的限量版套機，僅向賽馬會會員內部訂購，全球限量100套，而本拍品的紀念編號為兩位相同的22/100，非常吉祥。銀色的機身及望遠鏡均配以藍色飾皮，並且均印有「The Hong Kong Jockey Club」字樣及馬會標誌，亮麗優雅。此套裝連藍色相機皮套、望遠鏡套、皮質掛帶、抹鏡布、說明書、證書、電池、充電器及黑色鋼琴面木盒包裝，盡顯尊貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2589', 'Leicaflex SL Olympic Version with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'Leicaflex SL Olympic Version with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_218_6.jpg', '218', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 1972, 1,000 sets of 5-ring &quot;Olympic&quot; edition for 1972 Innsbruck Olympic Games were launched by Leica, 1000 sets were made. Olympic rings and word “72” are engraved on the prism. It comes with a rare black Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens (#2901418), show some signs of use.', '為紀念奧地利茵斯布魯克舉行的奧運會，1000台奧運版的Leicaflex SL於1972年隆重推出。機身正面刻有奧運五環及「72」字樣，甚有紀念性。此銀色機身配有極罕見的黑色Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#2901418)；本拍品有輕度使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2590', 'R3 100 Jahre Oskar Barnack Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'R3 100 Jahre Oskar Barnack Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_219_7.jpg', '219', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'In 1979, 1000 set of R3 gold-plated were made to commemorate the 100th Birthday of Oskar Barnack. The body covering is black lizard skin, with Oskar Barnack\'s signature on the top plate. Special number of this set is 100-462. This set comes with a matching gold-plated Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens (#2932102). This set also comes with papers, box, body cap, both lens caps and strap. In mint condition with light use and wears.', '為紀念徠卡相機之父Oskar Barnack誕生100週年，徠卡特別於1979年推出一批R3金色紀念套機。此套機機身覆以黑色蜥蝪皮，機頂上有Oskar Barnack簽名。此機之特別號碼為100-462，連同金色的Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#2932102)，配有包裝證書、機身蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及相機帶，有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2591', 'R4 Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'R4 Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_220_7.jpg', '220', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'In 1984, limited edition Gold R4\'s with brown snake skin were launched. The special number of this set is E022, comes with a matching Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens (#3295529), box and papers, presentation box, strap and front lens cap, in like new condition.', '1984年，徠卡特別推出了一批R4金色特別版。機身鍍上24K金，並覆以棕色的蛇皮。此機之特別號碼為E022。套機連同金色的Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#3295529)，並配有包裝證書、木盒、相機帶及鏡頭前蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2592', 'R4 Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'R4 Gold Plated with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_221_6.jpg', '221', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 1984, limited edition Gold R4\'s with brown snake skin were launched. The special number of this set is I146. The set comes with a matching Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens (#3295465) and front lens cap, in mint condition.', '1984年，徠卡特別推出了一批R4金色特別版。機身鍍上24K金，並覆以棕色的蛇皮。此機之特別號碼為I146。套機連同金色的Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#3295465)，鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2593', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_222_8.jpg', '222', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'In 1997, Leica released 300 rare limited edition kits for Hong Kong returning to China. The commemorate number is 175/300. “July 1, 1997” and Hong Kong skyline were engraved on top plate. This set comes with Summicron-R 2/50mm lens (#3736135). The camera is in new condition with original papers and packing.', '徠卡為香港回歸中國推出罕見的R6.2 18K鍍金套機，僅限量生產300套。此套機紀念號碼為175／300，機頂刻有 “July 1, 1997” 和香港著名地標，相機配有Summicron-R 2/50mm (#3765135)鏡頭。此套機全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2594', 'R6.2 Singapore\'s 30th Anniversary of Independence Gold Plated Set', 'R6.2 Singapore\'s 30th Anniversary of Independence Gold Plated Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_223_8.jpg', '223', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica R6.2 Singapore\'s 30th Anniversary of Independence gold plated camera was specially made to celebrate Singapore\'s independence (1965-1995). It comes with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens (#3702597-S045/150) and only 150 units were produced. The whole camera set was plated with 24 carat yellow gold. The top plate engraved “30, My Singapore, My Home” and the serial number is S045/150; the back engraved with “Republic of Singapore 1965-1995” and the national totem of Singapore. The camera body is decorated with red snake skin leather, with box, both lens caps, papers, body cap, strap and cleaning cloth in new condition.', '徠卡R6.2新加坡獨立30週年鍍金紀念套機，是為了慶祝新加坡獨立(1965-1995) 所發表，以經典的R6.2相機搭配Summilux-R 1.4/50mm超大光圈鏡頭(#3702597-S045/150)，全球限量150台。整套機以24K黃澄色鍍金製造，璀璨奪目。機頂刻有「30, My Singapore, My Home」的字樣，及其限量號碼「S045/150」；背面則有「Republic of Singapore 1965 –1995」的刻字以及代表新加坡的國徽圖騰。機身飾有紅色蛇皮，奢華感與復古味兼俱。整套相機配有包裝證書、說明書、鏡頭前後蓋、機身蓋、相機帶及鏡頭布，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2595', 'Phase One IQ280 “20 Years Anniversary” Limited Edition', 'Phase One IQ280 “20 Years Anniversary” Limited Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_224_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_224_2.jpg', '224', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Phase One A/S, the world leader in professional digital imaging solutions, was founded in 1993. In order to commemorate the 20th anniversary of Phase One, total 99 sets of IQ280 special edition was launched in 2013. Signature of Phase One CEO Henrik Håkonsson was engraved on the back. The limited number of this set is <b>PO000008</b>. Comes with a Rimowa suitcase, 645DF+, 80mm standard lens; Capture One software and a booklet of Phase One, very rare.', '飛思成立於1993年，是專業數碼中畫幅相機品牌。為慶祝成立20週年，飛思於2013年推出全球限量99套紀念版相機套裝，此套紀念機的限量編號是吉祥的<b>PO000008</b>，連同一個銀色的Rimowa鋁金屬旅行箱，箱內收藏了IQ280的數碼後背，後背上有飛思行政總裁Henrik Håkonsson的金色簽名﹔此外連同一個645DF+機身、一支80mm的標準鏡頭、飛思發展歷程的紀念冊及Capture One軟件一套﹔絕對是時尚感與實用兼備的紀念機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2596', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_74_6.jpg', '74', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Original Leica M3 black paint with single stroke, leather has been repaired. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '相對於銀色機身的M3，黑漆產量則較少。此機為原裝黑漆，飾皮有修補過的痕跡，外觀成色上佳，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2597', 'M3 Chrome with Summarit-M 1.5/5cm “Midland”', 'M3 Chrome with Summarit-M 1.5/5cm “Midland”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_78_6.jpg', '78', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'This M3 with Summarit-M 1.5/5cm outfit was made in Leitz Canada Midland. Camera is in single stroke with “Midland Ontario” engraved on the top plate, the lens (#1420257) engraved with “Ernst Leitz Canada Ltd. Midland” on the name ring. This lot comes with front cap.', '此機為加拿大製造的M3，機頂上刻有「Midland Ontario」字樣，市場極為罕見。此機是單次過片，連同首款於加拿大製造的Summarit-M 1.5/5cm鏡頭(#1420257)，鏡頭前端刻有「Ernst Leitz Canada Ltd. Midland」。拍品連同鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2598', 'M2, M3, M4 Cut-away', 'M2, M3, M4 Cut-away', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_79_1.jpg', '79', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'The cut-away model set includes early M2 with button rewind and no self-timer, M3 with double stroke, and a M4. All come with body caps.', '本拍品是徠卡用早期按鈕不帶自拍的M2機身、早期二次過片的M3機身及M4機身，分別以不同的剖切面去呈現，讓每位鍾情徠卡M機的徠卡迷可以更了解開創徠卡M機型先河的M3、M2及M4機內的每個構造及細節﹔從而比較三大機型的不同機械結構。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2599', 'MP Black Paint', 'MP Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_81_8.jpg', '81', '', '1,062,000', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the MP-31 camera within serial number MP-13 to MP-150. This camera was sold in an auction several years ago, with below description:<br />\r\n“Leica MP-31 with rare black enamel 50mm Summicron f2 (#1944043). Original finish: not re-painted – just beautiful! The 20th black Leica MP manufactured! This camera was originally owned by the famed Leica collector, Dr. Wayne Hull, of St. Petersburg, Florida, a founder of the designer of special Leica ophthalmic laboratory equipment for E. Leitz, Wetzlar.” <br />\r\nThe camera comes with Leicavit only, in beautiful condition.', 'MP-31是黑漆MP從MP-13至MP-150生產編號內的號碼，該機曾於數年前在歐美拍賣會拍賣過，當年的描述如下：<br />\r\n「徠卡MP-31連同罕有的黑漆Summicron 50mm鏡頭(#1944043)，它是原裝黑漆，沒有後塗，成色漂亮。此機是第20台製造的MP，它由徠卡美國歷史協會(LHSA)創辦人兼徠茲視光實驗設備的設計師– Dr. Wayne Hull所擁有。」<br />\r\n此拍品僅連機身及快速過片器，成色良好，運作暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2600', '24x27mm Postcamera Set', '24x27mm Postcamera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_101_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_101_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_101_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_101_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_101_5.jpg', '101', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Postcamera was produced between 1963 and 1972, for German Post Office and Telephone Authorities, about 200 pieces with 24x27mm format. Postcamera (#1206942) comes with a Summaron 2.8/35mm lens (#2311637); and the other one (#1286718) comes with a rare Summaron 5.6/2.8cm lens. Both lenses come with front lens caps.', '徠卡Postcamera於1963至1972年間生產，以MD、MDa及MD-2為藍本，是為當時德國郵政局及通訊機構生產，用作記錄早期的電話讀錶(telephone meter reading)。當時分別推出24x26mm及24x27mm格式﹔當中以24x27mm格式較為罕有，只生產了二百多台。本拍品正是由兩台24x27mm的Postcamera組成，其中一台Postcamera(#1206942) 配有Summaron 2.8/35mm鏡頭(#2311637)﹔另一台(#1286718)則配有多用於科學微距拍攝且較少見的Summaron 5.6/2.8cm鏡頭﹔此款鏡頭與Postcamera配搭並不常見。兩支鏡頭均連同鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2601', 'M Monochrom Chrome', 'M Monochrom Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_115_6.jpg', '115', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'This Monochrom camera with chrome top-plate assembled, black hot shoe, top-plate without brand name engraving and covered by protection sticker. It comes with inner box, body cap, battery, charger, cord, strap and instruction.', '徠卡於2012年的Photokina上推出黑白機(Monochrom)，只有黑色機身投入生產。此台Monochrom相機機頂是銀色，而熱靴位置則是黑色﹔機頂大部分位置均以白色膠紙覆蓋，估計未經使用。此外，機頂亦沒有品牌刻字，十分少有。此機連同內盒、電池、電線、充電器、掛帶、說明書及機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2602', 'Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Pre-Series', 'Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm Pre-Series', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_119_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_119_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_119_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_119_4.jpg', '119', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a pre series Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm lens probably, relatively rare. The model name is engraved on name ring, without any serial numbers. The lens comes with both caps.', '此鏡估計為Super-Angulon-M 3.4/21mm鏡頭量產前的試行版或測試版，相信為數不多。此鏡與正常版本不同，鏡頭前端只刻上型號，沒有任何編號。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2603', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_133_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_133_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_133_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_133_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_133_5.jpg', '133', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is an early version of Summicron-M 2/35mm 8 elements lens made in Canada . It comes with both caps and red focusing scale, in mint- condition.', '較早期的加拿大製Summicron-M 2/35mm黑色八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，玻璃明亮﹔配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2604', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint Dummy', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint Dummy', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_155_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_155_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_155_3.jpg', '155', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Dummy version of early Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid lens in black paint finished, without engraving of serial number, relatively rare. It comes with both caps.', '早期的Summicron-M 2/50mm的Rigid Dummy黑漆鏡頭，鏡頭上沒有編號，市場上較罕見。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2605', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm with Pre-Series Tube', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm with Pre-Series Tube', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_167_9.jpg', '167', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm lens probably is pre-series. The serial number from the first batch is 1957001 – 2656666, with knurled focusing ring and early lens hood style. However, this lens has no goggles, very rare, focusing tube with goggles. It comes with filter and both caps.', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/135mm共生產過有兩款鏡頭，這兩款鏡頭都帶有眼鏡。這是一支擁有早期特徵的Elmarit：波浪紋的調焦環及二段式的遮光罩，但沒有帶眼鏡，序號2656348也是屬於第一代產物，估計是試行版。此拍品配有濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及額外一個調焦環後組。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2606', 'P. Angenieux 1.8/75mm Type Y31', 'P. Angenieux 1.8/75mm Type Y31', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_172_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_172_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_172_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_172_4.jpg', '172', '', '21,780', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the P. Angenieux 1.8/75mm Type Y31. Lens has been modified to Leica M mount by MS-Optical R&amp;D. It comes with a certificate of modification and lens rear cap.', '法國著名光學公司愛展能生產的1.8/75mm鏡頭，鏡頭經日本宮崎光學改為徠卡M卡口，附有宮崎原廠證明書及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2607', 'P. Angeniuex 1.8/80mm Type Y31', 'P. Angeniuex 1.8/80mm Type Y31', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_173_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_173_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_173_3.jpg', '173', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here is the P. Angenieux 1.8/80mm Type Y31. Lens has been modified to Leica M mount by MS-Optical R&amp;D. It comes with a certificate of modification and both lens caps.', '由法國著名光學公司，愛展能生產的1.8/80mm鏡頭，鏡頭由四片四組組成，成像佳。鏡頭經日本宮崎光學改為徠卡M卡口，附有宮崎原廠證明書及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2608', 'Leitz Military Aeronautic Stuka Lens Hood with IIIc', 'Leitz Military Aeronautic Stuka Lens Hood with IIIc', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_175_8.jpg', '175', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'The unique combination lens hood and camera holder was made for German Stukas (Air Force) for aerial photography. Only one completely finished, plus around five examples of unfinished metal, which were acquired by Gianni Rogliatte about 30 years ago.<br />\r\nThis lot is one of these unfinished examples, with green painted like M1 and M3 Olive, also with the original template engraved with “Sonnenblende fur Luftaufnahmen Objetiv Summitar f 5cm 1:2”.<br />\r\nIt is in like new condition, with certificate by Gianni Rogliatti. The set includes a IIIc (#360580), SNOOC baseplate and a Summitar 2/5cm lens (#865834). For further illustration, please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.83 and Gianni Rogliatti “Leica The First 70 Years” p.123.', '此徠卡軍用航攝遮光罩現存於世上的數量約六件，在市場上難得一見。它是1940年代徠卡專門為德國空軍的Stukas轟炸機所開發，結合了遮光罩及相機固定器的功能，二為一體的設計方便用於航空拍攝。此款遮光罩當時僅有一件完成品，另外的五件僅為半成品，並於30年前被徠卡書籍作家Gianni Rogliatte納為珍藏。本拍品為五件半製成品的其中一件，遮光罩塗上M1及M3 Olive般的軍綠色，刻有 「Sonnenblende fur Luftaufnahmen Objetiv Summitar f 5cm 1:2」字樣，成色如新。此拍品除附有Gianni Rogliatte的簽名證書外，同時配有IIIc相機 (#360580)、Summitar 2/5cm 鏡頭 (#865834) 及SNOOC過片底蓋，是罕見及最有收藏價值的軍用拍品之一。(有關遮光罩的詳細資料，可參閱James Lager Vol. III p.83及Gianni Rogliatti “Leica The First 70 Years” p.123)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2609', 'Hasselblad 2000FC/M 100th Anniversary in Photography 1885-1985', 'Hasselblad 2000FC/M 100th Anniversary in Photography 1885-1985', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_260_10.jpg', '260', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera was made in 1985 and was the very first gold plated Hasselblad commemorating their 100th Anniversary with a total production of 700 units. The special number of this set is 532. It comes with Planar 2.8/80mm (#5872687) and A12 magazine (#RI3264724), also with box, wooden presentation box, instructions and front cap.', '1985年，哈蘇為紀念公司成立100週年，首次推出鍍金紀念機。此機的特別編號為532，配有Planar 2.8/80mm鏡頭(#5872687)及A12後背(#RI3264724)，連同包裝外盒、木盒、說明書及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2610', 'Hasselblad 503CX Golden Blue 50th Anniversary', 'Hasselblad 503CX Golden Blue 50th Anniversary', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_261_7.jpg', '261', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'The 50th Anniversary Edition in 24K gold plated, decorated with blue leather. The commemorative number is 214. It comes with CF 2.8/80mm (#7144942) and A12 magazine (#03EV10472), leather presentation box, outer box, papers, front lens cap and strap, in like new condition.', '這是為慶祝第一台哈蘇503CX相機面世50週年而生產的紀念機。此機紀念號碼為214。配有CF 2.8/80mm鏡頭(#7144942)，A12後背(#03EV10472)，精美包裝盒連皮箱、鏡頭蓋、藍色鍍金相機手帶、證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2611', 'Hasselblad 503CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', 'Hasselblad 503CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_262_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_262_2.jpg', '262', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 50th Anniversary of the first Hasselblad camera introduced in October 6, 1948, Hasselblad launched a special jubilee model - The Hasselblad Gold Supreme. It is a complete 503CW with all visible chromed details plated in 24 carat gold. It comes with CF 2.8/80mm (#8148398), A12 magazine (#30ER11414), maker\'s box, leather presentation box, leather strap and all papers.  *The camera is for reference only, the packing of this lot is unopened.', '此503CW紅皮24K鍍金紀念機是為慶祝哈蘇相機面世50週年而推出，機身刻有「The System 1948-1998」字樣，全球限量500套。連CF 2.8/80mm鏡頭(#8148398)及A12後背(#30ER11414)，全新未經使用。附有精美皮箱(皮箱亦刻有「1948-1998」字樣)、紅色鍍金相機手帶，證書齊全，極具收藏價值。*此圖相機僅供參考，拍品實物未拆封。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2612', 'Apollo 11-CM Hasselblad 500EL', 'Apollo 11-CM Hasselblad 500EL', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_263_8.jpg', '263', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 1969, American astronauts landed on surface of the moon by Apollo 11 and this successful Lunar Mission impacted the human history significantly. The 500EL Camera was designed and produced for this particular lunar mission. Since the camera was designed for astronauts, some changes were made. One of the biggest changes is the absence of mirror and waist-level finder in order to reduce weight. Besides the control knobs and the handle on the dark slide were enlarged for use with space gloves . The camera comes with a Carl Zeiss Planar Compur 2.8/80mm (#4591811), as well as Carl Zeiss Sonar 5.6/250mm lens (#4382139) with “SEB33100032” and “S/N 1022” engraved, and A200 Magazine  (#33100082) with “TE 400433” engraved. It also comes with a Lunar mission booklets that were made by Hasselblad. This set is very rare and limited on the market now.', '稱霸全幅畫面相機的哈蘇，是美國太空總署挑選為執行太空任務的相機品牌。1969年，美國航太員乘坐阿波羅11號成功登上月球，揭開人類太空研究歷史的新一頁。為了讓航太員可以拍下眼前所見的事物，紀錄人類登陸月球的創舉，哈蘇因應美國太空總署的嚴格要求而製造了500EL登月相機。在設計方面，500EL機身上的按鈕比較大顆，以便航太員在穿上厚身的太空保護衣時，依然可以輕易調較各項功能；而加大了的保護菲林刀片手亦便於掌握。相機內不設鏡片及腰平觀景器，以減輕重量。這些設計確保500EL可勝任於太空中拍攝時所遇到的極端環境挑戰。此套機配有登陸月球時採用的同款Carl Zeiss Planar Compur 2.8/80mm(#4591811)和Carl Zeiss Sonar 5.6/250mm(#4382139)，鏡頭下面刻有「SEB33100032」及「S/N 1022」字樣；A200後背(#33100082)刻有「S/N 829」及「LUNAR MISSION」，背後亦刻有「TE 400433」字樣；底片匣連同哈蘇特別為登月相機製作的小冊子，是極具紀念性的拍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2613', 'Hasselblad 500C/M Kit', 'Hasselblad 500C/M Kit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_264_1.jpg', '264', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This 500CM is still in very good condition after 30 years since it’s launched in 1975. This set comes with Distagon 3.5/60mm (#5735299), S-Planar 5.6/120mm (#6226769), Sonnar 4/150mm (#5638931), Distagon 4/50mm (#5776061), both of them come with both caps in mint condition. Moreover, this set as well as with a Planar 2.8/80mm T* lens in Chrome (#5515641) which is very rare in the market. This lens comes with both caps and HZ filter too.<br />\r\nThe set completes with two A12 (#UP417383and #UP422899), A16 (#RP328152), viewfinder (#RH414599), 45’ Prism, two hoods, two flash shoes, rewind knobs, quick focus handle and aluminum case.', '此套機的配備完善整齊，鏡頭包括Distagon 3.5/60mm(#5735299)、S-Planar 5.6/120mm (#6226769)、Sonnar 4/150mm(#5638931)、Distagon 4/50mm(#5776061)，以上鏡頭均連同前後蓋，成色極佳。此套機的最珍貴之處為銀色Planar 2.8/80mm T*鏡頭(#5515641)、其前後蓋及HZ濾鏡，產量極少，在市面難得一見。<br />\r\n另配有兩個A12(#UP417383及#UP422899)、A16(#RP328152)、取景器(#RH414599)、45度角取景器、兩個遮光罩、兩個閃燈座、過片轉鈕、快速對焦環及鋁箱。此套機面世至今已有30多年，配件齊全，成色佳，市場罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2614', 'Hasselblad 501CM Kit', 'Hasselblad 501CM Kit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_265_8.jpg', '265', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classic 501CM with CFE Planar 2.8/80mm lens (#8805090) and A12 magazine (#30EU12683), in mint- condition, with front lens cap.', '經典的哈蘇501CM機身配CFE Planar 2.8/80mm鏡頭(#8805090)及A12後背(#30EU12683)，連同鏡頭前蓋，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2615', 'Hasselblad 903SWC*', 'Hasselblad 903SWC*', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_266_9.jpg', '266', '', '29,040', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with CF 4.5/38mm lens (#7265636), A12 magazine (#30EP56525), viewfinder, hood and front lens cap. Whole set is in mint condition.', '此套機成色極佳，配有CF 4.5/38mm鏡頭(#7265636)、A12後背(#30EP56525)、取景器、遮光罩及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2616', 'Hasselblad Arcbody Kit', 'Hasselblad Arcbody Kit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_267_9.jpg', '267', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This set comes with APO-Grandagon 4.5/45mm (#8TER10242), body cover, rear lens cap and plastic box. This set also comes with five correction slide, focusing screen, three extension tubes, center filter, cable release, hoods and instruction, in mint condition.', '此Arcbody套機包括機身，APO-Grandagon 4.5/45mm鏡頭(#8TER10242)，機身前後蓋，鏡頭後蓋及包裝膠箱。另外，此拍品連同五塊矯視片、對焦屏、接環三個、中灰、快門線、兩個遮光罩及說明書，此套機運作正常，調焦暢順，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2617', 'Hasselblad CF 5.6/250mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CF 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_268_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_268_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_268_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_268_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_268_5.jpg', '268', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a well-known Hasselblad lens with Superachromat in very good quality. It comes with both caps in mint condition.', '哈蘇超級名鏡之一，為蔡司傾力之作的Superachromat 5.6/250mm鏡頭，堪稱現代光學高峰。此鏡玻璃通透，外觀成色極佳，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2618', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/250mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_269_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_269_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_269_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_269_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_269_5.jpg', '269', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classic lens of Hasselblad features Apochromatic correction. It comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '此拍品為哈蘇的經典鏡頭，有消色差功能，使成象質素更為銳利。配有鏡頭前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2619', 'Nikon I with Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm Chrome', 'Nikon I with Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_270_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_270_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_270_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_270_4.jpg', '270', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'The first Nikon camera featured a focal plane shutter with rangefinder focusing and a smaller picture format of 24mm X 32mm. Comes with Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm lens (#50050214), front lens cap and hood, with normal signs of use and wears, quite rare.', '這是第一台有焦平面快門的藝康旁軸相機，格式是24mm X 32mm。此機連同Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm鏡頭(#50050214)、鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩，機身有使用痕跡，市面少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2620', 'Nikon S2 with Nikkor-S 1.4/ 5cm Black Paint', 'Nikon S2 with Nikkor-S 1.4/ 5cm Black Paint', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_271_6.jpg', '271', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'The S2 was the first Nikon camera to use a standard 24x36mm film format. The Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm was a popular standard lens for Nikon\'s rangefinder cameras of the 1950s and it was the first f/1.4 lenses for any 35mm camera in the world. The serial number of this Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm is #377475. This set is in black paint, comes with hood and filter, with some signs of use.', '藝康S2黑漆，是藝康當年第一台針對專業市場定制的相機，僅接受專業攝影者訂單生產，並沒有量產，故產量非常稀少，一直都是藝康愛好者及收藏家追逐的珍品。S2黑漆分為前期和後期，本拍品是後期版本，機身有使用痕跡及露銅。所配的Nikkor-S 1.4/5cm鏡頭(#377475)連同遮光罩及濾鏡，為本拍品錦上添花。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2621', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', 'Alpa Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_272_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_272_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_272_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_272_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_272_5.jpg', '272', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is in Alpa mount, comes with box which is often missing, lens hood (#72306) and both caps, in excellent condition.', '產於法國的Kinoptik是最頂級電影鏡頭品牌之一，以超高的解析度聞名。此拍品為著名的Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm鏡頭配ALPA卡口，少有的連同包裝盒、遮光罩(#72306)及鏡頭前後蓋；成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2622', 'ALPA 12 SWA with Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/38mm', 'ALPA 12 SWA with Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/38mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_273_9.jpg', '273', '', '96,800', null, null, null, null, 'The ALPA 12 SWA (Shift Wide Angle) was the first model in the ALPA 12 medium format camera series. First only with roll film backs and later with digital backs also. Vertical movements +25 mm are possible (−25 mm with a special adapter or by rotation of the camera). This set comes with Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/38mm lens (#14764597), back, viewfinder, film cassette and straps, in mint condition.', '機身使用航太鋁合金打造，拍品名稱中的S代表移軸，WA代表廣角，適用於中片幅底片、數位機背或拍立得片盒。與ALPA 12 WA不同，此款相機可最多上移+25mm，若配合ALPA 多功能附加裝置或三腳架使用，同樣也可下移-25mm。此機連同Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/38mm超級廣角鏡頭 (#14764597)，連同後背、取景器、膠片筒、遮光罩連蓋、手帶及掛帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2623', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_274_6.jpg', '274', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Original Voigtlander Bessa II 4.5/105mm APO-Lanthar, comes with leather case. In mint- condition.', 'Voigtlander Bessa II是福倫達公司於1950年推出的顛峰之作。Bessa II有兩個取景框，分別為6 X 4.5及6 X 9，光圈景深尺均顯示為4.5 – 22。並配有超級名鏡APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm；該鏡之玻璃由稀有的鑭玻璃製成，成像優異，加上此鏡產量極少，約200-300台。如此機鏡套裝一直都是攝影愛好者追求的珍寶。此機配有皮套，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2624', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_275_6.jpg', '275', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Voigtlander Bessa II was modified, with a 4.5/105mm APO-Lanthar lens, in mint condition.', 'Voigtlander Bessa II是福倫達公司於1950年推出的顛峰之作。Bessa II有兩個取景框，分別為6 X 4.5及6 X 9，雖然此機經過後期改裝；但由於配備了稀有的鑭玻璃的超級名鏡APO-Lanthar 4.5/105mm，成像優異，成色佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2625', 'APO-Lanthar 4.5/10.5cm', 'APO-Lanthar 4.5/10.5cm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_276_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_276_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_276_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_276_4.jpg', '276', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'This APO Lanthar 4.5/105mm lens is the most popular APO Lanthar for 4 x 5 formats. It is made of Lantharnum glass, and achieved full Apochromatic correction. The lens is in mint condition; optics are clean, comes with both caps and box.', 'APO Lanthar鏡頭一共有4款不同規格的設計，光圈都是4.5，視角劃一為56度。本拍品為4.5/150mm規格，主要搭配給4 x 5畫幅使用。此款鏡頭採用了高級鑭玻璃製造，擁有高折射率並且只有極低的色散，完美達到消色差的矯正，是第一款真正的APO攝影鏡頭。此鏡的不銹鋼外表刻有紅綠藍三色環，標誌其獨一無二的地位，同時配有包裝及鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃通透且成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2626', 'APO-Lanthar 4.5/21mm', 'APO-Lanthar 4.5/21mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_277_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_277_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_277_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_277_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_277_5.jpg', '277', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This multi-coated Voigtlander lens has a near legendary reputation for quality. It is made of Lantharnum glass, and achieved full Apochromatic correction. The lens is in mint condition; clean barrel showing normal wears. Optics is clean and bright with little dust. Comes with both caps and cam.', 'APO Lanthar除與同廠6 x 9 Bessa II相機配搭使用外，亦常用於林可夫相機。鏡頭的多層鍍膜設計，配上稀有的鑭玻璃，使成像質素極為出色。此鏡配有前後蓋及對焦刀，玻璃有微塵但通透，鏡身有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2627', 'Apochromat Kinoptik 2.5/150mm', 'Apochromat Kinoptik 2.5/150mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_278_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_278_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_278_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_278_4.jpg', '278', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is the famous cins lens from France. It comes with Helicoid Extension Tube for Pantax 6x7 and adapter ring for Nikon, also the lens rear cap, with clear glass.', '產於法國的Kinoptik是最頂級的電影鏡頭品牌之一，以超高解析度聞名。這款Apochromat Kinopik 2.5/150mm電影鏡頭的旋形散景及油畫般的色彩令人一見難忘。此鏡配有Helicoid 6x7延伸管、Asahi Pentax for Nikon轉接環及鏡頭後蓋﹔玻璃非常通透明亮。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2628', 'Compass II Kit', 'Compass II Kit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_279_6.jpg', '279', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'LeCoultre Compass camera was designed by Mr. Pemberton-Billing in 1930’s. It is a pocket size of 35mm film rangefinder camera. After World War II, Compass camera has been discontinued. Serial number of Compass camera is started from 1000, the last number is 4638. It is estimated that less than 4000 pieces were made. This one comes with back, tripod, instruction manual and box, extremely rare.', '罕有的全套配件，未被使用的菲林及包裝齊全的拍品，此LeCoultre Compass相機是由英國人Pemberton-Billing於1930年設計，它是一種使用35mm底片的袖珍型旁軸相機。Compass相機的序號是從1000開始，自1939年開始劇減，二戰結束後Compass已經停產；文獻記載的最高序號為4638，因此估計總產量低於4,000台。此相機另配有後背、小型腳架、原裝菲林、說明書及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2629', 'Carl Zeiss Mirotar 4.5/500mm', 'Carl Zeiss Mirotar 4.5/500mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_280_6.jpg', '280', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Only approximately 200 pieces were produced, extremely rare. Can be used for Contarex, comes with rear lens cap.', '本拍品的產量極少，大約只生產200支，十分罕見。此鏡成像質素極佳，是遠攝鏡的代表作。此鏡是Contarex卡口，有使用痕跡，連同鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2630', 'Linhof 617SV Prototype', 'Linhof 617SV Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_281_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_281_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_281_3.jpg', '281', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a rare prototype of Linhof 617SV. The model “SV” is engraved on the camera, instead of the existing model “SIII”. The top plate and flash synchronized of the prototype comes with a platform; with bigger size and the engraving on top plate are bolded. This prototype camera comes with a viewfinder in chrome finished, which has never launched in the market, very rare.', '此機是林可夫617SV的原型版。林可夫617至今只有SIII出售，但此機卻刻上S V，估計此拍品是在SIII基礎上研發的SV原型版，極為罕見。此機外形與現行版SIII有若干不同：此原型版的機頂及閃光燈位置有台階，而現行的SIII則沒有。另外，此機的過片器及體積較大，機身上的字形亦較現行版本為粗，機身前端的鏡頭接合位是黑色，而非現行SIII的銀色。此原型機更連同一個銀色取景器，甚為特別，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2631', 'Plasmat Roland Camera Set', 'Plasmat Roland Camera Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_282_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_282_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_282_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_282_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_282_5.jpg', '282', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Plasmat Roland 6x4.5 was introduced in 1933 by Plasmat (renamed as Rudolph &amp; Co. Kamerabau in 1936) located in Berlin, Germany. Roland is a 120mm film rangefinder camera which film sized 6x4.5cm and 16 photos can be shot per film roll. They are equipped with two Plasmat 2.7/70mm lenses (#572222 and #38051), with six elements in five groups. Both come with front lens cap, with normal signs of use.', '德國品牌Roland 6 x 4.5相機於1933年發明，是一款120mm菲林格式的旁軸相機，每次可拍16張照片。此對機是初期及後期產品，分別連同兩支較盛名的Plasmat 2.7/70mm銅色鏡頭#572222及Plasmat 2.7/7cm黑漆鏡頭#38051，均是六片五組的設計。此套機較接近原廠狀態，市面較少見，相機均連同鏡頭前蓋，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2632', 'Voigtlander Bessamatic Kit', 'Voigtlander Bessamatic Kit', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_283_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_283_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_283_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_283_4.jpg', '283', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Manufactured around 1958-1963, it’s a popular 35mm SLR camera with its fully interchangeable lenses and match-needle metering. This set comes with two lenses; the first one is Zoomar 2.8/36-82mm lens (#4962998) which is a first zoom lens for 35mm camera and manufactured by Voigtlander, with front lens cap, adapter, filter and leather case; and the other is Super Dynarex 4/135mm (#5701647) with both caps and leather case.', '此拍品生產年份大約由1958至1963年，有內置測光錶，是熱門的35mm單鏡反光相機，成色優良。分別配有Zoomar 2.8/36-82mm(#4962998)連鏡頭前蓋、轉接環、濾鏡及皮套，此款鏡頭更是35mm相機中的第一款變焦鏡頭。另外更有Super Dynarex 4/135mm(#5701647)連前後蓋及皮套。整套相機成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2633', 'Voigtlander Prominent Set', 'Voigtlander Prominent Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_284_7.jpg', '284', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Manufactured around 1951, this interchangeable-lens 35mm rangefinder camera is fitted with an Ultron 2/50mm lens (#3644567) in a Synchro-Compur shutter with front lens cap. Also, this set comes with Telomar 5.5/100mm lens (#3644964) with a reflex housing (#2668) and leather case as well. Whole set is in good condition, very rare.', '此機身是福倫達的Prominent系列，是可換鏡的35mm旁軸相機。此機連同標準鏡頭Ultron 2/50mm(#3644567)及其鏡頭前蓋。另外更配有罕見的Telomar 5.5/100mm(#3466964)鏡頭、俯視取景器(#2668)及其皮套。此款鏡頭是一款俯視式的微距鏡頭，鏡頭及俯視取景器皆可拆下分開。整套相機成色優良，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2634', 'Tele-Apotessar 8/500mm HFT PQS', 'Tele-Apotessar 8/500mm HFT PQS', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_285_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_285_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_285_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_285_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_285_5.jpg', '285', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Here is a prototype lens made by Zeiss and Rollei, with shutter speed 1/1000 second and HFT coating from Rollei. The prototype lens comes with a matt-chrome lens hood, instead of the black one; with two rubber rings on focusing ring; neither Zeiss nor Rollei was marked on barrel; scale on aperture ring and focusing ring are different from the official lenses. This prototype lens is very rare, comes with both caps.', '本拍品是蔡司與祿萊合力研發的中幅長焦距鏡頭之原型版，此款鏡頭快門速度可達1/1000秒，快門葉片以特殊材料製造，鏡片鍍膜使用祿萊的HFT鍍膜技術。原型版的啞銀色遮光罩於正式投產時改為傳統黑色，黑色鏡筒沒有品牌標誌﹔調焦環防滑膠由兩個變成一個，而光圈刻度及焦距顯示數字亦有顯著差別。此款鏡頭在正式投產時產量不多，而此原型鏡在市場上亦甚為罕見。此鏡配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2635', 'Carl Zeiss T* ZV Limited Special Edition for V system', 'Carl Zeiss T* ZV Limited Special Edition for V system', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_286_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_286_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_286_3.jpg', '286', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 2007, Carl Zeiss announced a limited special edition of lenses in three different focal lengths for Hasselblad V system: Distagon T* 4/50mm ZV, Makro-Planar T* 4/120mm ZV and Sonnar T* 4/180mm ZV. Each lens comes with edition number.<br />\r\nThis lot are: The <b>1st</b> of Makro-Planar T* 4/120mm (#15645651); The <b>321st</b> of classic wide-angle Distagon T* 4/50mm ZV (#15645321); The <b>40th</b> of Tele lens Sonnar T* 4/180mm ZV (#15646340), all completely with papers and box, in brand new condition.', '蔡司於2007年為哈蘇V系列相機推出了三款經典鏡頭，分別為ZV Makro-Planar T* 4/120mm、ZV Distagon T* 4/50mm及ZV Sonnar T* 4/180mm，各限量1,000支。鏡身鍍銀，外形設計仿似早期哈蘇銀色經典鏡，並包裝在精美的禮盒中，每支鏡頭都有限量編號：拍品中的當中最大亮點非ZV Makro-Planar T* 4/120mm(#15645651)莫屬，<b>其限量編號為“1”</b>，是此款限量版的<b>首支</b>鏡頭，附有證書；其餘兩支鏡頭分別為限量編號<b>“321”</b>的ZV Distagon T* 4/50mm(#15645321)附有證書；及限量編號<b>“40”</b>的ZV Sonnar T* 4/180mm(#15646340)。三支銀色的金屬鏡身配搭經典外型設計，加上超高的解像力，使此套拍品更具收藏價值。三支鏡頭均連同遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋、鏡頭皮袋及高貴的灰色絲絨鏡頭儲存盒，連同包裝。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2636', 'Nikon FA with Nikkor 1.4/50mm Gold Set', 'Nikon FA with Nikkor 1.4/50mm Gold Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_287_6.jpg', '287', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Nikon FA is the most advanced manual-focus camera ever designed by Nikon. It can give Program auto exposure along with Matrix metering with all AI and AI-s manual-focus lenses. This set comes with Nikkor 1.4/50mm lens (#5509840), box, presentation box, papers and front lens cap, in mint condition.', '鍍金色的Nikon FA限量相機，容許手動對焦鏡頭，並且可以自動曝光的進階相機。此機連同Nikkor 1.4/50mm鏡頭(#5509840)，配有包裝盒、木盒、證書及鏡頭前蓋，成色上好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2637', 'Rolleiflex 2.8F AURUM', 'Rolleiflex 2.8F AURUM', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_288_7.jpg', '288', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Special edition gold plated with brown lizard surfaces, comes with Helidosmat 2.8/80mm (#948355) and Xenotar 2.8/80mm (#13964508). Completes with dark wood box, packing, strap and lens cap.', '此機是祿萊2.8F的特別版，部分機身鍍上金色，並飾以咖啡色的蜥蝪皮。連同Helidosmat 2.8/80mm(#948355)及Xenotar 2.8/80mm鏡頭(#13964508)，附有精美木盒、包裝、鏡頭蓋、及掛帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2638', 'R5 Set', 'R5 Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_225_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_225_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_225_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_225_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_225_5.jpg', '225', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This set includes two R5 cameras, one is in black (#1714540), another one is in chrome (#1720242). Both were produced in 1987. They come with box and body cap. For the chrome one, it also comes with instruction; strap for the black one.', '此對拍品分別由黑色機身的R5(#1714540)及銀色機身的R5(#1720242)組成，兩機同產於1987年，連機身蓋及包裝盒。銀色機身另帶說明書﹔黑色機身則有相機背帶。兩部相機成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2639', 'R6 Chrome', 'R6 Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_226_6.jpg', '226', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica R6 in chrome and with black leather. It comes with box, instruction, strap and body cap, in mint condition and good working order.', '此機為徠卡R6，銀色機身，黑色飾皮，連機身蓋、相機背帶、包裝盒以及說明書，成色如新，市面少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2640', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_227_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_227_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_227_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_227_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_227_5.jpg', '227', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 2003, this lens belongs to the last model of zoom lens in the R-series. It comes with built-in hood, ROM and both caps, in mint condition.', '此拍品為徠卡於R系列中最後一款變焦鏡王，帶ASPH，產於2003年，配有鏡頭前後蓋、內置遮光罩及ROM，玻璃通透，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2641', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Black', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Black', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_228_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_228_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_228_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_228_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_228_5.jpg', '228', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Germany with built-in hood and ROM in E60. It comes with packing, instructions, leather case and both caps, in mint condition.', '此鏡為德國製的Summilux-R 1.4/50mm最新款鏡頭，內置遮光罩。此鏡頭口徑為E60，帶ROM，玻璃通透，成色極佳。連包裝盒、說明書、皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2642', 'R Lens Set in Chrome', 'R Lens Set in Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_229_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_229_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_229_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_229_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_229_5.jpg', '229', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Here are the R series lenses in Chrome finished; both were made in Germany in 1960’s, only small number produced. For the Elmarit-R 2.8/35mm lens (#1972094) comes with lens rear cap and hood with hood cap; and the Summicron-R 2/50mm lens (#1999074) comes with lens rear cap, hood with hood cap and filter adapter (#14160U).', '此對銀色版本的R系列鏡頭，均在1960年代由德國製造產，產量極少。當中Elmarit-R 2.8/35mm鏡頭(#1972094)連鏡頭後蓋及遮光罩連蓋﹔而Summicron-R 2/50mm鏡頭(#1999074)則帶鏡頭後蓋、遮光罩連蓋及濾鏡轉接環(#14160U)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2643', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_230_7.jpg', '230', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with ROM, leather case, both caps and built-in hood, in mint condition.', '此款鏡頭為恆定光圈的變焦鏡王，質素可媲美定焦鏡，為R系列中的名鏡之一。鏡頭帶ROM，連內置遮光罩、皮筒及前後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2644', 'Vario-Elmar-R 4.2/105-280mm', 'Vario-Elmar-R 4.2/105-280mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_231_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_231_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_231_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_231_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_231_5.jpg', '231', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens has ROM contacts on the mount for electronic coupling with the Leica R8 cameras, with small production batch, approximately 1,500 units were made only. This lens comes with box, papers, both caps and built-in hood, in like new condition.', '此款鏡頭為第一款帶ROM的鏡頭，產量只有大約1,500支，最早可用於R8之上。此鏡成色如新，玻璃通透，連包裝證書、皮筒、鏡頭前後蓋及內置遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2645', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/135mm', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/135mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_232_6.jpg', '232', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada in 1978. It comes with both caps and built-in hood, in excellent condition.', '此鏡為加拿大製的Elmarit-R 2.8/135mm，產於1978年，調焦順暢，內置遮光罩，連鏡頭前後蓋，有輕微使用痕跡，吉祥號碼2886868。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2646', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/180mm', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/180mm', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_233_6.jpg', '233', '', '54,280', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with both caps, built-in hood, leather case and box in mint condition.', '本拍品是徠卡 R 中，長焦鏡頭系列的最大光圈代表作，帶APO消色差的鏡頭，成像獨特，散景迷人。此鏡頭有內置遮光罩，連同鏡頭前後蓋、包裝盒及皮筒，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2647', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_234_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_234_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_234_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_234_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_234_5.jpg', '234', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of the first version of Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm. The depth of field scale is different from the original one; also the serial number of this lens is not within the original production batch. It comes with both caps and built-in hood. With normal marks of use and clear glass.', '第一代徠卡Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm的原型鏡，其景深呎與現行版的有明顯不同。鏡頭編號亦不在正常生產之列，極為罕見。此鏡頭有內置遮光罩，連同鏡頭前後蓋及掛帶，玻璃通透，鏡頭有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2648', 'APO-Telyt-R 2.8/400mm Prototype', 'APO-Telyt-R 2.8/400mm Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_235_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_235_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_235_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_235_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_235_5.jpg', '235', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'The prototype lens was in action at the Olympic Games in 1988, only six pieces were made. With substantial changes between it went into production in 1992. The rear part of the prototype lens is shorter, without built-in carrying handle. Also, the engravings of model names are different; and the closer focusing distance of the prototype lens is 15 feet, instead of 25 feet for the official one. This set comes with lens hood, aluminum case, separate carrying handle, instruction manual, Series 5.5 filter and quick release plate. Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.289 &amp; p.299 for further illustration.', '此款原型鏡最早出現於1988年漢城奧運，第一批試產五支，之後再追加一支，共六支。為迎合市場，1992年正式投產時，與原型版比較有明顯差別：此原型鏡的後組較短、手柄設計及鏡身上的刻字與正式量產版本完全不同、最短對焦由25呎改為後期的15呎。此拍品連同遮光罩、鋁箱、獨立手柄、Series 5.5濾鏡、快裝片及說明書﹔極為罕有。同款鏡頭可參閱James Lager Vol.II p.298及p.299。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2649', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Award Medal', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Award Medal', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_236_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_236_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_236_3.jpg', '236', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The Oskar Barnack Award honors great photographers. The practice of awarding a solid silver medal started in the early 1980’s until 1991. Mr. Hans-Guenther Von Zydowitz of Leitz was in charge of this program in the 1980’s. The medal comes in a beautiful presentation case in around 250 grams. The silver content alone makes it valuable.', '此獎牌由純銀鑄造，重量約250克，為Oskar Barnack Award中所頒發的獎牌。Oskar Barnack獎項是80年代至90年代初，徠卡公司為表揚傑出攝影師而設，當時由徠茨公司的Hans-Guenther Von Zydowitz先生主理。此獎牌附有精美禮盒，市場上難得一見，相信不少攝影愛好者均是首次目睹，收藏價值極高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2650', 'Leica VIOOH Round Body Universal Viewfinder Prototype', 'Leica VIOOH Round Body Universal Viewfinder Prototype', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_237_6.jpg', '237', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This is a round body VIOOH. It ranks R9 (Almost Unique) in the Leica International Price Guide (8th Edition), and this is a prototype one with \"E.LEITZ WETZLAR\" engraved at the back. The prototype model without number engraved, made in matte black and nickel, and comes with a red paper box. Extremely rare. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.22-p.24 for further illustration.', 'VIOOH圓筒形取景器(Round Body)在徠卡國際價格指南中被列為R9，代表其級別屬於“接近獨一無二”(Almost Unique)。此拍品以啞黑漆的黃銅及鎳合金製造，而且更是原型版，鏡身背面刻有\"E.LEITZ WETZLAR\"，鏡身上亦沒有刻上產品編號，相信數量極為稀少，此拍品連同紅色包裝，是市場上難得一見之物。有關詳情可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.22-p.24。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2651', 'Leica Finder AYOOC', 'Leica Finder AYOOC', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_238_6.jpg', '238', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This viewfinder was launched in 1930 - 1932; an extra front lens could be swung in to convert the field of view to 3.5cm. This one comes with original red box, in like new condition. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.16 for further elaboration.', '此取景器於1930至1932年間推出，可將取景視野轉換為3.5cm。此取景器連同原廠紅色包裝盒，成色極佳。同類拍品可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.16。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2652', 'Leica 3.5cm Viewfinder Chrome SBLOO', 'Leica 3.5cm Viewfinder Chrome SBLOO', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_239_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_239_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_239_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_239_4.jpg', '239', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'Metal viewfinder from 1951, for Summicron 3.5cm, in mint condition, comes with original red box.', '由1951年起發行的金屬取景器，用於Summicron 3.5cm鏡頭上，成色極新，連同紅色包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2653', '7.3cm/9cm/13.5cm Folding Finder Set', '7.3cm/9cm/13.5cm Folding Finder Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_240_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_240_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_240_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_240_4.jpg', '240', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'These thee folding optical sports viewfinders produced in 1935; focal length 7.3cm (SAIOO), comes with factory red box, 9cm (SEROO) and 13.5cm (SYEOO), only small batch was produced. Glass and frame line are clean, parallax correction lever is smooth, whole set is in mint condition. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.35 for further illustration.', '此一套三件的取景器產於1935年，分別有7.3cm(SAIOO)、9cm(SEROO)及13.5cm(SYEOO)。當年只生產了小批量後便停產，於市面並不常見，此拍品般成色及玻璃完好。三個觀景器框線清晰，撥桿順滑，其中7.3cm的觀景器更配有原廠的包裝盒。同類貨品可在James Lager Vol.III p.35中找到。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2654', 'Leica Diopter Checker DIOOY', 'Leica Diopter Checker DIOOY', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_241_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_241_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_241_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_241_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_241_5.jpg', '241', '', '5,310', null, null, null, null, 'This is a correction lens mounted to universal viewfinders, cameras and magnifiers. Only delivered to dealers. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.50.', '這是屈光度檢視器，產於1955年，度數由-5至+4度。當年生產此檢視器，只供徠卡經銷商使用，沒有正式推出於市面上發售，非常罕有。可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.50。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2655', 'Leicavit Chrome Set', 'Leicavit Chrome Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_242_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_242_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_242_3.jpg', '242', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'One of the Leicavit is pre-production, with different engravings of the normal one. For the pre-production, “Ernst Leitz Wetzlar Germany” is engraved on the left hand side while “Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar Germany” is engraved on the normal one (please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.56), with some signs of use.', '此對過片器由原型版及量產版組成，原型版過片器上的刻字排位及內容均與量產版有別。在原型版過片器上，「Ernst Leitz Wetzlar Germany」刻字分開上下兩行，只有「Germany」一字置於下排。而量產版過片器則刻有「Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar Germany」，並分三行排列(可參考James Lager Vol.III p.56)；此拍品見證產品生產前後分別，別有收藏意義。此對過片器有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2656', 'Special Base Plate modified by Haber &amp; Fink N.Y', 'Special Base Plate modified by Haber &amp; Fink N.Y', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_243_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_243_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_243_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_243_4.jpg', '243', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'This is a unique base plate for M cameras modified adding a SCNOO mechanism (which is a pre war trigger used on screw mount cameras).The modification was done in the 50\'s by Haber & Fink  New York , which made the famous tri lens turret to be used on Leica screw mount cameras. This base plate can also be used either on Leica M2\'s or MP\'s cameras. It works perfectly and smooth as a regular Leicavit MP. Unique, interesting and clever modification which might have been done before the start of the regular production of the Leicavit MP.', '這是一個特別的徠卡M相機底蓋，由美國的Haber & Fink N.Y改裝(此公司為著名的螺絲口三鏡頭快速轉台的生產商)，此底蓋改裝後就像LEITZ為螺絲口相機生產作過片用的SCNOO一樣，可快速過片，此底蓋可用在MP相機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2657', 'MP Leicavit Chrome', 'MP Leicavit Chrome', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_244_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_244_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_244_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_244_4.jpg', '244', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This is early MP Leicavit in chrome, with signs of use and wears, very rare.', '早期的徠卡MP過片器，較為罕有，有嗑碰痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2658', 'MP Leicavit Chrome &quot;Dagnes Nyheter”', 'MP Leicavit Chrome &quot;Dagnes Nyheter”', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_245_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_245_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_245_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_245_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_245_5.jpg', '245', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Dagens Nyheter (means &quot;Today\'s News&quot;) is a daily newspaper in Sweden which has the largest circulation of Swedish morning newspapers. The name &quot;Dangens Nyheter&quot; is engraved on the back of this Leicavit, very rare.', '此過片器背面刻有「Dagens Nyheter」字樣，Dagens Nyheter是瑞典其中一家最大型的報社，中文譯名“每日新聞”。此過片器是「Dagens Nyheter」的記者用來抓拍新聞，所以有明顯使用痕跡，但由於市場上少見，故收藏價值依然甚高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2659', 'MQUOO Mouth Release', 'MQUOO Mouth Release', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_246_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_246_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_246_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_246_4.jpg', '246', '', '2,124', null, null, null, null, 'This is an unusual MQUOO mouth release for screw mount camera, designed for handicapped, engraved “Leitz” on the clip. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.79 for further illustration.', '這是用於徠卡螺絲口相機上的快門裝置，作用為以口代替手操控快門來使用，以照顧不同用者的需要，特別是殘疾人士；十分罕有。可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.79。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2660', 'Leica Left Hand Release', 'Leica Left Hand Release', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_247_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_247_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_247_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_247_4.jpg', '247', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This accessory began available in the mid-late 1930\'s. This was built for left handed people. Three versions are known, and this is for Leica screw mount cameras. For further illustration, please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.79.', '為照顧使用左手的拍攝者的需要，徠卡於1930年代，特別推出少量此配件。此配件可安裝於熱靴位置，令那些不方便用右手的拍攝者可同樣盡情享受拍攝的樂趣。此配件適用於徠卡螺絲機上，可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.79。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2661', 'NAKUL Negative film viewer', 'NAKUL Negative film viewer', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_248_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_248_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_248_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_248_4.jpg', '248', '', '4,248', null, null, null, null, 'This film viewer can be used on slide or negative film. It comes with bakelite handle and milk glass (NAMAS). This set is in excellent condition with code NAKUL. For further illustration, please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.234.', '此戰前菲林觀片器可用於檢視正片或負片膠卷，鏡身以鎳金屬製成，另配有手柄及磨砂玻璃片(NAMAS)，整套配件名為NAKUL，可完整保留至今是非常罕見，成色優良。有關拍品可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.234中的介紹。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2662', 'Leica OOFRC', 'Leica OOFRC', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_249_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_249_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_249_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_249_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_249_5.jpg', '249', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This is a remote release and shutter winder device. This is one of the most specialized early Leica accessories during 1935 - 1939. It comes with original box and instruction, very rare.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n＊The camera is not included in the lot.', '本拍品為非常罕有的手動快門調控器，產於1935至1939年間，可直接安裝在機身上使用。附有的兩條操控繩，分別用於操控快門按鈕及操控快速過片之用，可提高拍攝速度與方便性。此配件連同原裝包裝盒及說明書，成色極佳。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n＊此拍品並不包括相機。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2663', 'New York Motor Battery Pack Prototype Set', 'New York Motor Battery Pack Prototype Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_250_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_250_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_250_3.jpg', '250', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'In 1964, Norman Goldberg re-designed the motor drive for Leica and called Technical Photomation Instruments (TPI) to produce. These models were designed, produced and sale of about 12 units. They were completed in 1965 with company name “TPI” engraved. However, Leica purchased all parts and patents and continued to make the “New York Motor” from 1966 to 1971. From this period, the TPI logo are milling out.<br />\r\nMore important thing is two prototypes are probably from the early stage, logo “TPI” were engraved. And the word “TPI” is milling out for the last piece which is probably a prototype of late version.<br />\r\nThe lot comes with a certificate sign by Don Goldberg, son of Norman Goldberg, very rare.', '此拍品由三件特別的原型版組成，其中兩件更刻有「TPI」字樣。在1960年代初期，Norman Goldberg為徠卡M系列設計電池組，並在1965年由美國Technical Photomation Instrument(TPI)公司製造，而最重要的是此款刻有「TPI」字樣的電池只完成了12件；直到1973年TPI公司重新製造的同款電池組上已經沒有刻「TPI」字樣。而此三件原型版中，其中兩件刻有「TPI」字樣，估計為早期的原型版本﹔另外一件機頂的「TPI」字樣則被刻意磨走，而且特別地覆上飾皮，估計為較後期的原型版本。由此拍品中可更了解整個電池組的演變過程。<br />\r\n此拍品連同一份由Norman Goldberg兒子親筆簽署證明信件的複本。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2664', 'Leica OLIGO Set', 'Leica OLIGO Set', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_251_6.jpg', '251', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Leica accessory for single exposure, first introduced in 1934. It accepts a ground glass screen or a film holder in the back and Leica lens in the front. This set is combined with five lenses, which are Summitar 2/5cm (#488872), Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1343936), Summaron 3.5/3.5cm (#975465), Hektor 2.5/5cm and Elmar 3.5/50mm with box, with some signs of use.', '此套徠卡的照片單拍器是收藏者瀝盡心血，於市面收集五款不同的單拍器，各款式的造型及刻字各有不同。附有以黃銅鑄造的菲林匣及快門控制器。此套裝更連同五支鏡頭，分別為Summitar 2/5cm(#488872)、Elmar 3.5/5cm(#1343936)、Summaron 3.5/3.5cm(#975465)、Hektor 2.5/5cm及 Elmar 3.5/50mm連盒，套裝有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2665', 'Leica Green Bundeseigentum Ever Ready Case', 'Leica Green Bundeseigentum Ever Ready Case', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_252_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_252_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_252_3.jpg', '252', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Original olive green ever ready case for M3, “Bundeseigentum” is marked at the back, with small batch of production only. It comes with the original strap, in excellent condition, very rare.', '此軍綠色的皮套為徠卡M3軍用機之皮套，皮套後面印有「Bundeseigentum」字樣，為當年限量生產，數量極少，成色優良，配有原裝相機背帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2666', 'Leica Case M Model', 'Leica Case M Model', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_253_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_253_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_253_3.jpg', '253', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is an exceptionally rare leather case in that it is fitted for a Leica M model, but without any space for MC/MR Leica meter. Very few such cases were ever produced as most M cameras were used with meters. Further this case is in like new condition. This is the rarest of all Leica M cases.', '這是一個極為罕見的早期M皮套，當年大部分Leica M機的皮套於生產時，已預留一定的空間，讓測光錶可安裝於相機上，並一同置於皮套內；但如本拍品一樣，並沒有預留測光錶位置的M機皮套，產量卻非常稀少，十分獨特。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2667', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Cut-Away', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Cut-Away', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_254_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_254_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_254_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_254_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_254_5.jpg', '254', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This is the cut-away of the legendary Summicron 50mm lens and shows the interesting design of this lens.', 'Summicron 50mm是徠卡的傳奇鏡頭，通過此剖切版本可讓徠卡迷一睹其巧妙的內部結構。如同時完整收藏各鏡頭剖切版本，必更為珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2668', 'S2 with Summarit-S 2.5/35mm Lens Cut-Away', 'S2 with Summarit-S 2.5/35mm Lens Cut-Away', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_255_6.jpg', '255', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The S2 was the most expensive camera ever produced and Leica’s first middle format digital reflex. Only one such cutaway was ever produced completes with the 35mm lens. This must be considered as the ultimate cut-away camera, extremely rare.', 'S2是徠卡第一台的中畫幅數碼單鏡反光相機，亦是徠卡生產以來最昂貴的數碼相機。為了讓徠卡迷更清楚其內部精密的結構，廠方特別將一台套約20萬港元的S2套機剖切公諸於眾，堪稱剖切機中的極品。此拍品連同經剖切的Summarit-S 2.5/35mm鏡頭及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2669', 'Trinovid Cut-Away', 'Trinovid Cut-Away', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_256_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_256_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_256_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_256_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_256_5.jpg', '256', '', '8,260', null, null, null, null, 'This is an unusual cut-away of a Leica binocular, showing the intricacies of the construction, very rare.', '此拍品為非常特殊的望遠鏡剖切版本，徠卡迷可藉此了解其獨特而複雜的內部結構，十分難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2670', 'Summitar front cap with Swastika', 'Summitar front cap with Swastika', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_257_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_257_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_257_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_257_4.jpg', '257', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'Unique, interesting custom made Summitar front cap with swastika made for the Luftwaffen (the German air force).Inside of the cap is possible to see the Leica logo stamped on the front of the cap. Normal sign of use.', '此鏡頭蓋為二次大戰期間，徠卡原裝生產予德國納粹空軍使用。鏡頭前蓋刻有納粹空軍徽號及納粹黨的黨徽。此拍品適用於Summitar鏡頭，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2671', 'Leitz Micrometer', 'Leitz Micrometer', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_258_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_258_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_258_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_258_4.jpg', '258', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a rare micrometer used to calculate the tolerance. This item was not built by Leitz but supplied to Leitz employee hence the Leitz logo. This was an instrument of a very high precision and hence very expensive when new.', '此測微計是徠茲工廠當年提供予職員，對生產的相機產品作測量及計算公差使用，因此亦印有徠茲商標。此測微計在當時售價極高，十分珍貴，而且市面罕見，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2672', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Pioneer Metal Plaque with Belt Buckle', 'Leica Oskar Barnack Pioneer Metal Plaque with Belt Buckle', '35', '/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_259_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_259_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a24/LOTNO_259_3.jpg', '259', '', '14,520', null, null, null, null, 'This is a metal plaque commemorating Oskar Barnack who built the first Leica camera. It measures approximately 7.5” x 7.5” and depicts an image of Oskar Barnack and the first prototype Leica camera superimposed over a perforated film border. Moreover, it comes with three different sizes of belt buckles. Three buckles are made in bronze, the biggest one is 3.8” and the others are 2.2” and 2.3”.', '為紀念Oskar Barnack發明第一台徠卡135mm格式相機而特別推出的紀念牌匾；此紀念牌匾上刻有Oskar Barnack的肖像及其發明的O-Series相機，尺寸為7.5”X7.5”。此拍品亦連同三個徠卡製造的皮帶扣，尺寸分別為3.8”、2.3”及2.2”，均以銅製，十分獨特，別具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2673', 'Leica Special Edition Pocket Watch 1913-1993', 'Leica Special Edition Pocket Watch 1913-1993', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_1_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_1_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_1_3.jpg', '1', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate Leica\'s 80th Anniversary (1913-1993), Leica Special Edition Pocket Watch was made. It was recorded HKD 21,250 at auction in 2010. It comes with original box and guarantee card, in brand new condition, very rare.', '此精緻非常的鍍金陀錶是於1993年為慶祝徠卡80週年(1913-1993)所鑄造，當時僅供限量發售，市場上非常罕見。此款陀錶曾出現於2010年的拍賣會上，並以港元21,250成交，升價潛力極高。連原包裝盒並配有鍍金錶鏈及保養卡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2674', 'Ur-Leica Dummy', 'Ur-Leica Dummy', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_2_6.jpg', '2', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'Dummy Camera of Ur-Leica, engraved “Nachbildung der Ur- Leica” on the top plate, comes with box, in like new condition.', '徠卡第一台135格式相機於1913年問世，此機正是它的模型版。機頂刻有“Nachbildung der Ur-Leica”。連包裝，成色接近全新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2675', 'O-Series Replica', 'O-Series Replica', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_3_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_3_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_3_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_3_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_3_5.jpg', '3', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Launched in Photokina in 2000, only 2,000 units were made. It comes with Anastigmat 3.5/50mm lens, in mint condition.', '於2000年的Photokina推出，限量2000台。此機身連Anastigmat 3.5/50mm鏡頭，並用上現代鍍膜技術，可以正常使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2676', 'IA with Elmax 3.5/5cm', 'IA with Elmax 3.5/5cm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_4_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_4_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_4_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_4_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_4_5.jpg', '4', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica model A (1925) with fixed Elmax 3.5/50 lens. The Elmax was the second version of lens built into the Leica IA, after the Anastigmat and before the Elmar. The Elmax still is the 5-element design of the Anastigmat. Cameras with Elmax occur between serial numbers 280 and 1280 approximately. The camera here shows all original features of the a second version Elmax Leica, without ratched wind, with frame counter up to 35, aluminum knobs, long but all black &quot;R/A&quot; lever, flat eyepiece, etc., in very fine original condition. Later baseplate. Complete with matching original cap, FODIS rangefinder and container with two cassettes, in rare original &quot;EPI&quot;-style ETRIN case. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此IA相機配不可更換的Elmax 3.5/50mm鏡頭。Elmax是IA套機中的第二代，是在Anstigmat及Elmar鏡之間的產品。沿用了Angstigmat五片玻璃設計的Elmax鏡頭，機身序號在280至1280之間，僅生產約700多台。此機身符合所有第二代配Elmax鏡頭的特徵，包括: 沒有齒輪式轉盤，菲林讀數至35，鋁的轉盤，但有全黑的“A/R”杆及平的取景框等等。除後期底蓋外，此機均為原裝，成色優良。此機另配有原裝機身蓋、FODIS連動測距杆、兩個菲林盒及十分罕見的ETRIN套。此套機經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2677', 'IA Convert to IID Black Paint', 'IA Convert to IID Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_5_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_5_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_5_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_5_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_5_5.jpg', '5', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'Leica II (lavatory seat) in black and nickel finish, factory-converted from early Leica model A with Elmax No.1206. The lens on the camera still is the original 5-element Elmax lens of 1925 with original fronting, converted into a &quot;7 o', '當年由於II型號推出，部分IA使用者可將IA送返原廠升級，此機由IA升級至IID，以黑色及鎳組合而成。機身保留原來#1206的編號，鏡頭也保留了原有原裝極罕見的5片玻璃的Elmax， 並將它改進成7點鐘位耦合可更換鏡頭卡口。此套機鏡成色極佳，已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2678', 'IA with Elmar', 'IA with Elmar', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_6_6.jpg', '6', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1926-1927, this IA with Elmar belongs to an early production. It comes with Elmar 3.5/50mm lens, the leather was changed, normal used marks and in good working order.', '產於1926至27年，屬徠卡早期產品，機身覆以黑色皮。此相機配以Elmar 3.5/50mm鏡頭，經過翻新及換皮，有使用痕跡，但操作功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2679', 'III Convert from I mod A', 'III Convert from I mod A', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_7_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_7_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_7_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_7_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_7_5.jpg', '7', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This I mod A body was upgraded to III. It comes with Elmar 3.5/50mm lens, lens cap and leather case, with slight repaired part and some signs of use.', '此機為I mod A的機身升級至III，機身有輕微露銅，露銅位置有輕微修補痕跡。此機配有Elmar 3.5/50mm鏡頭，連鏡頭蓋及皮套，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2680', 'I Mod.A Re-plated Gold', 'I Mod.A Re-plated Gold', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_8_6.jpg', '8', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1930 with repainted gold, decorated with lizard skin leather. It comes with Elmar 3.5/50mm repainted gold lens, rangefinder, front lens cap, with some normal signs of use.', '徠卡I Mod A機身產於1930年，此機為後期鍍上金色，機身覆以蜥蝪皮，配有Elmar 3.5/50mm鍍金鏡頭連測距器及鏡頭蓋。機身有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2681', 'I Mod.B Dial Set Compur Black Paint', 'I Mod.B Dial Set Compur Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_9_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_9_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_9_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_9_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_9_5.jpg', '9', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, early first model with dial-set Compur shutter, only 638 units were made. It has original features, comes with clean lens, meter scale, in good working order.', '徠卡I Mod B Compur分別有Rim-set及Dial-set兩款，當中以Dial-set的產量最少，共生產只有約638台。此相機配有鏡間快門及特別的酒窩型快門按鈕，及鏡頭上獨特的“Film Counter Lock”。此機生產編號較早，並配有測距器(#33669)，整體成色良好，屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2682', 'I Mod.B Rim Set Compur Black Paint', 'I Mod.B Rim Set Compur Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_10_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_10_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_10_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_10_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_10_5.jpg', '10', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Only 1072 units were made in 1928-1941, comes with Elmar-SM 3.5/50mm(#218633) lens, in good condition.', '於1928-1941年生產，共生產1072台，連Elmar-SM 3.5/50mm鏡頭 (#2186633)。機身長久經使用下的露銅，更令其增添歷史味道，是古董收藏和徠卡迷必納之佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2683', 'I Mifilmca 1/3x with 10x Lens Dial Set Black Paint', 'I Mifilmca 1/3x with 10x Lens Dial Set Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_11_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_11_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_11_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_11_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_11_5.jpg', '11', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Mifilmca (#5384), Photo micrographic Leica produced in 1932 Leitz, Wetzlar. Second type of Mifilmca 1/3x, utilizing a Compur Leica housing with removable Leica thread adapter (standardized lens mount). Removable microscope adapter with 10x lens. Very rare.', '1932年，徠茲威茲勒推出的第二款Mifilmca 1/3x系統，該機以徠卡B Compur相機為藍本，增加了附帶徠卡螺口接環、可以拆除的專用鏡箱，配有10倍放大器，用於加裝徠卡顯微鏡等特種設備。這款產品屬於非常珍罕的收藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2684', 'Ic Re-plated Gold', 'Ic Re-plated Gold', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_12_7.jpg', '12', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Re-plated Leica Luxus with Elmar 3.5/5cm lens (#434509). Gold plated body decorated with red leather.', '後期鍍金的徠卡Luxus連Elmar 3.5/5cm鏡頭 (#434509)。金色機身配以紅色飾皮。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2685', '250FF Convert to 250GG Black Paint', '250FF Convert to 250GG Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_13_6.jpg', '13', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Authentic Leica 250 &quot;Reporter&quot; No. 150085, which was originally delivered as FF model. Postwar factory upgrade to a GG version, small top plate with &quot;ERNST LEITZ GMBH WETZLAR&quot; in capital letters with white filling. Body cover is IIIf type vulcanite. A rare postwar conversion without &quot;f&quot; type flash synchronization. The camera in very nice condition. It has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. It comes with Xenon 1.5/5cm (#490251) and lens cap.', '此機原是250FF，在戰後升級為GG。此機有較小的頂蓋，刻上大楷“ERNST LEITZ GMBH WETZLAR”字樣，機身用上IIIf的飾皮。此機於戰後升級，但沒有f型閃燈同步數字盤。此機成色極佳，已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。同時擁有FF 及GG 特徵的250 Reporter 十分罕有。此機外觀漂亮，配有Xenon 1.5/5cm鏡頭(#490251)，連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2686', 'II Black Paint', 'II Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_14_6.jpg', '14', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black painted body with chrome rewind knobs and shutter release button, comes with body cap, in good working order.', '黑漆黃銅機身配以銀色過片鈕及快門按鈕。機身有輕微露銅，更顯其古典味道。此機配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2687', 'II Mod. D Black Paint', 'II Mod. D Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_15_6.jpg', '15', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica II Mod. D was produced in 1932. It comes with Hektor 3.5/5cm lens (#156296) and front lens cap, with normal used marks, in good working order.', '徠卡IId於1932年間生產，黃銅黑漆機身配以Hektor 2.5/5cm鏡頭 (#156296)及鏡頭前蓋。機身有輕微露銅，操作完好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2688', 'II with wood showcase camera holder', 'II with wood showcase camera holder', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_16_7.jpg', '16', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica wooden stand for camera was printed on the back cover of James Lager’s book and has not been seen by many. This was actually made in 1930, illustrating a portrait of the body of a woman, with the camera body of II and Elmar 3.5/50mm Lens(#99486) (Please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.330 for further illustrations), extremely rare.', '此徠卡木製陳列架僅在James Lager書中的封底見過，相信眾多徠卡收藏者均未見過實物。這是1930年代生產的木製展示架，以一女性人像為主體，搭配上II型機身及Elmar 3.5/50mm鏡頭(#99486)，絕對是徠卡迷不可錯過的拍品(可參閱James Lager Vol.III p.330中展示的圖片)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2689', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_17_6.jpg', '17', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica III Mod.f Black Paint was produced in 1932, “Germany” engraved on the hot shoe, very rare. This camera has some signs of normal use, comes with body cover.', '徠卡III Mod.f黑漆機，產於1932年，觀景窗帶有活動性的1.5x矯視片，於機頂位熱靴位置刻有”Germany”字樣，於同類型機款中甚為罕見。相機操作功能完好，有正常使用痕跡。相機配有機身保護蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2690', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_18_6.jpg', '18', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This model was introduced in 1933, serial number starts from #107601. This is the 60th Leica III in the batch. Very similar to Leica II but with the additional slow shutter speed from 1 to 1/20 added and the word “Germany” engraved on the hot-shoe, very rare. It comes with body cap, has some normal signs of use.', '徠卡III於1933年開始投產，基本上與徠卡II型機大致相同，新增了1至1/20秒慢快門及相機掛繩扣，機頂熱靴位置刻有“Germany”字樣，同類型相機款中極為少見。此款相機生產序號由#107601開始，此機是早期生產的第60台。相機操作功能良好，有正常使用痕跡，相機配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2691', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', 'III Mod.f Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_19_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_19_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_19_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_19_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_19_5.jpg', '19', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leica III Mod.f Black Paint with Elmar 3.5/50mm Nickle lens(#142635) and OOFRC remote release and shutter winder device. The glass is clear, sperture is smooth, comes with lens cap and leather case, in good working order.', '此拍品的亮點是非常罕有的手動快門調控系統(OOFRC)，可直接安裝在機身上使用，此調控系統產於1935-1939年，主要使用兩條操控繩，分別用於操控快門按鈕，另一條則用於快速過片，大大提高了拍攝速度與方便性，這是徠卡早期產物中最具標誌性的配件。徠卡III Mod.f黑漆機身配有Elmar 3.5/50mm鏡頭(#142635)。相機操作正常，鏡頭玻璃完好，調焦暢順。配有鏡頭蓋及相機皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2692', 'III Black Paint', 'III Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_20_6.jpg', '20', '', '6,490', null, null, null, null, 'Leica III was introduced in 1933, serial number starts from #107601. Slow shutter speed is 1-1/20 and the shutter speed is 1/500 second. It comes with front lens cap and normal used marks.', '徠卡III於1933年推出，機身號由#107601起。此機慢快門功能可達1-1/20秒，而快門最快速度為1/500秒。此機為黑漆機身，配有機身蓋，輕微露銅，更有古典味。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2693', 'III Mod.f Chrome Visoflex I with PEGOO Magnifier', 'III Mod.f Chrome Visoflex I with PEGOO Magnifier', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_21_6.jpg', '21', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This IIIf Chrome with Visioflex I (#22657), PEGOO 45 ° magnifier, double cable release and Elmar 4/135mm lens (#1768621). It comes with front lens cap, excellent condition.', '此IIIf相機配有Elmar 4/135mm鏡頭(#1768621)，另配有Visoflex I (#22657)、45度放大器(PEGOO)及雙頭快門線。這款快門線可同時操作機身和Visoflex反光鏡。相機操作良好，帶鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2694', 'IIIa Chrome', 'IIIa Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_22_7.jpg', '22', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'In 1935, IIIa was produced with 1/1000 shutter speed added. It comes with flash unit VIII (SELSY) and flash reflictor (Please refer to James Lager Vol. III p.248 for further illustrations). It comes with body cap, in good working order.', '徠卡IIIa相機於1935年投產，新增1/1000秒快門速度。相機配有由紐約徠卡製造的閃光燈VIII (SELSY)及反射罩(可參閱James Lager Vol. III p.248)。此機操作正常，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2695', 'IIIa Chrome', 'IIIa Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_23_7.jpg', '23', '', '2,360', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIa was introduced in 1935. This model is identical to Leica III except the shutter speed of 1/1000 was added, which is more suitable for sports photography. It comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm lens (#392902), with normal used marks.', '徠卡IIIa於1935年推出，其設計與III系統相機大致相同，但快門則增加至1/1000秒，更適合用於運動攝影上。此機連Elmar 3.5/5cm(#392902)，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2696', 'IIIb Chrome', 'IIIb Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_24_7.jpg', '24', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIb was introduced in 1938, the rangefinder – viewfinder eyepieces are placed adjacent to one another; the diopter adjustment lever is coaxial with the rewind knob. It comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm(#612854) and body cap, with slight used marks.', '徠卡IIIb於1938年推出，特別之處為取景框與連動測距對焦合併於同一位置上，屈光矯視器則設在回片鈕旁邊。此機連同Elmar 3.5/5cm (#612854)及鏡頭蓋，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2697', 'IIIb Chrome', 'IIIb Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_3jpg.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_25_7.jpg', '25', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIb was introduced in 1938, the rangefinder – viewfinder eyepieces are placed adjacent to one another; the diopter adjustment lever is coaxial with the rewind knob. It comes with body cap and slight used marks.', '徠卡IIIb於1938年推出，特別之處為取景框與連動測距對焦合併於同一位置上，屈光矯視器則設在回片鈕旁邊。此機連機身蓋，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2698', 'IIIc Chrome', 'IIIc Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_26_6.jpg', '26', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is an early version IIIc, comes with body cap and normal used marks.', '此為早期IIIc，機身有輕微使用痕跡，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2699', 'Leica 72  18 X 24mm Midland', 'Leica 72  18 X 24mm Midland', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_27_6.jpg', '27', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leica 72 is a 18mm X 24mm format camera and was produced in 1954-1957 in Canada and Germany. Only 150 units of Leica 72 Midland with batch No.357301-357450 were produced in Canada. The top plate engraved with &quot;18 X 24&quot; and &quot;Midland Ontario”. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.78 for further illustrations). It comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm (# 464161) and lens cap.', '徠卡72是採用18mm X 24mm格式的相機，於1954-1957年分別在加拿大及德國生產。而加拿大生產的Leica 72 Midland批號由357301-357450， 全球僅有150台，機頂位置刻有“18 X 24” 及“Midland Ontario“字樣(可參考James Lager Vol.I p.78 介紹同款機型)。此機身的菲林計算器可數至72，取景器窗口為直擋，配有Elmar 3.5/5cm (#464161)及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2700', 'IF Siemens', 'IF Siemens', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_28_6.jpg', '28', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This IF special is not listed in Leica guilds. According to the factory record, there’s only 20 units were made in year 1956 for Siemens Germany. This is the last 18th pieces of IF, even less the IG Seimens. Comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '此相機只生產二十部，是Leica guides中也沒有出現過的型號。製造年份為1956年，也是IF系列中最後的第十八台。此機與IG Seimens一樣是特別訂製，但數量卻比IG版本的64台更為罕有。此機連機身蓋，成色極佳，為收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2701', 'IIIf Chrome', 'IIIf Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_29_6.jpg', '29', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIf was introduced in 1950. It has similar design as IIIc while flash synchronization is added and film type rewinder built into the film advance knob. It comes with Summitar 2/5m (#977535), with lens cap, camera box and certificate.', '徠卡IIIf於1950年開始投產，外型大致與IIIc相同，新增了閃光燈接口及膠卷顯示於過片杆上。此機配有Summitar 2/5cm 鏡頭 (#977535)，光圈葉呈六角型設計，玻璃明亮，配有鏡頭蓋、相機盒及原廠證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2702', 'IIIf Chrome', 'IIIf Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_30_7.jpg', '30', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIf with &quot;Property of E. Leitz Inc New York&quot; engraved at the back, comes with Elmar-3.5/5cm lens (#1046659) engraved the same letter as the camera body. The glass is clear, with front lens cap, with some signs of normal use, in good working order.', '此機機背刻有“Property of E. Leitz Inc New York”，配有鏡頭Elmar- 3.5/5cm (#1046659)，鏡頭同樣刻有“Property of E. Leitz Inc New York”字樣。這樣一套完整的紐約徠卡資產在現今徠卡收藏品中可謂非常罕有，是絕佳收藏品。鏡頭玻璃通透連鏡頭蓋，機身操作完好，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2703', 'IIIf Chrome Set', 'IIIf Chrome Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_31_8.jpg', '31', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'This IIIf camera set comes with four lenses, Summaron 3.5/3.5cm(# 714779) with front cap, Elmar 4/9cm(# 1182114) with both caps, Hektor 4.5/135mm(# 1717355) with rear cap and Summarit 1.5 / 5cm(# 953991) with both caps. Accessories include hood, light meter(# 10866 and # 13689), five different colors filters, belt, cable release and two film cassettes. This set is in excellent condition and good working order, very rare.', '此IIIf套機連四支鏡頭，分別是Summaron 3.5/3.5cm(#714779)連前蓋，Elmar 4/9cm (#1182114)連前後蓋，Hektor 4.5/135mm(#1717355)連後蓋及Summarit 1.5/5cm(#953991)連前後蓋。配件則包括遮光罩、測光錶(#10866及#13689)、五片不同顏色的濾鏡、皮帶及兩個菲林匣。以上貨品均放置於一個啡色徠卡皮盒內。套機成色優秀，操作正常。如此配件齊全的套機實屬少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2704', 'If Chrome', 'If Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_32_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_32_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_32_3.jpg', '32', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'If Chrome with Elmar 4/9cm lens (#879067), bellow, Visoflex I(#14730), 45 ° maganifier, OZXVO cable release with box. All in good working order.', '銀色If 機身配以極少見的Elmar 4/9cm 鏡頭(#879067)，鏡身連接著皮腔、Visoflex I (#14730)、45 度放大器、OZXVO 快門線及其原裝盒。此機配件齊全，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2705', 'Ig Chrome', 'Ig Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_33_7.jpg', '33', '', '6,490', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with Summicron 2/5cm lens (#1155046) and body cap, with some normal used marks, in good working order.', 'Visoflex I (#14730)、45度放大器、OZXVO快門線及其原裝盒。此機配件齊全，成色優良，為收藏或自用的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2706', 'Ig Chrome', 'Ig Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_34_6.jpg', '34', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'The first Leica Ig with “Leica” engraved at the front. Similar to IIIg but comes with flash synchronization outlet. The rewind knob is built into the camera top plate. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '徠卡Ig是首台在機身前幅上刻上“Leica”品牌字樣的相機。製作大致與IIIg相同，早期生產，有閃光燈接口，但此機取消了二個閃燈熱靴，回片杆以嵌入式設計。機身成色良好，有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2707', 'IIIg Chrome', 'IIIg Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_35_7.jpg', '35', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica IIIg was first introduced in 1956 and was the last screw mount camera of Leica. It comes with body cap, in mint condition, extremely rare.', '一組難得一見的完美吉祥數字。IIIg的機身編號為888880。這樣完整而幸運的組合極為罕見，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2708', 'IIIg Chrome', 'IIIg Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_36_6.jpg', '36', '', '8,850', null, null, null, null, 'IIIg is the last model of Leica screw mount camera, with a bigger viewfinder. It comes with Leicavit and body cap, with insignificant signs of use and in good working order.', 'IIIg是最後一款螺絲口相機，跟其他螺絲口型號比較，其觀景窗較一般大，配有快速過片器，操作完好。有輕微使用痕跡，連相機蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2709', 'Summicron-SM 2/50mm Prototype', 'Summicron-SM 2/50mm Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_37_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_37_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_37_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_37_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_37_5.jpg', '37', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare and original Leitz Wetzlar prototype version of the later Summicron 2/50 lens. Leica screw mount. The lens head in unfinished brass. The fronting without name or serial number engraved. The diaphragm index from f/2 to f/16, additionally bears two index markings for f/22 and f/32 even (without figures engraved). Only the &quot;Summitar *&quot; forerunners of the Summicron do have a diaphragm index down to f/22. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡是後期Summicron 2/50mm的原型鏡，十分罕有。鏡頭為螺絲卡口，鏡頭前端是黃銅，而且沒有型號及編號的刻字。此鏡的光圈環只顯示2到16的光圈值，但此光圈16旁邊有兩道刻度線，雖然沒有顯示數值，但指的是22及32光圈，這是Summitar* (Summicron鏡頭生產前的試行版)才有的光圈值，十分特別及罕見。此鏡頭已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2710', 'Summicron-SM 2/50mm Rigid Prototype', 'Summicron-SM 2/50mm Rigid Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_38_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_38_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_38_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_38_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_38_5.jpg', '38', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'This Leitz Wetzlar 2/50 lens in collapsible LTM mount is a genuine and all original factory prototype of the later Summicron. Without type or serial number engraving, it remembers to the “Summitar*” design. The aperture ring does carry an additional index for f/22. The front ring bears the engraving “E” only. It has been reported one similar engraving “D” on another early Summicron prototype with “SummiKron” engraving. Probably there was a series of such experimental lenses by the time, names “A, B, C, D, E”.', '此鏡頭是Summicron-SM 2/50mm Rigid的原型版鏡頭，十分罕見。鏡頭的前端並無刻上任何型號及工廠名稱，而且光圈值最大至22，有如Summitar*的設計。鏡頭上只刻一個 “E”字。而且此鏡頭亦無任何編號。根據資料顯示，另一支Summicron 的原型鏡亦只刻有一個英文字母 “D”及”SummiKron”字樣，估計徠卡有可能生產過數支實驗性鏡頭，編號分別A、B、C、D、E。此鏡頭已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此鏡頭保守估計已有50多年歷史，但成色極新，連膠盅及M卡口接環，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2711', 'Super Angulon-SM 4/21mm Chrome', 'Super Angulon-SM 4/21mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_39_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_39_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_39_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_39_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_39_5.jpg', '39', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'Super Angulon-SM 4/21mm was made by Schneider. It comes with keeper, front lens cap, hood, hood cap and 21mm metal viewfinder, in excellent condition.', '此鏡是較少見的螺絲口鏡頭，並由施耐德公司代工，該鏡是4組9片玻璃的設計，最近對焦距離為0.4M。 連膠盅、鏡頭前蓋、遮光罩(IWKOO)、遮光罩蓋及21mm金屬取景器，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2712', 'Summicron-SM 2/35mm Chrome', 'Summicron-SM 2/35mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_40_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_40_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_40_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_40_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_40_5.jpg', '40', '', '26,620', null, null, null, null, 'Only 577 units of this lens were made. This lens is clear with keeper, front lens cap, in good condition.', '徠卡經典鏡頭 – 螺絲口德產的八枚玉，全球僅生產577支，最近對焦距離為1米，由八片六組鏡片所組成，其中鏡片更使用透光度和成本相當高的螢石製造，故被稱為八枚玉。鏡頭外觀品相良好，玻璃通透，配有膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2713', 'Hektor-SM 6.3/2.8cm Nickel', 'Hektor-SM 6.3/2.8cm Nickel', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_41_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_41_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_41_3.jpg', '41', '', '11,210', null, null, null, null, 'This lens in nickel is the 120th in the early batch, with clear lens, keeper and both caps, in mint condition.', 'Hektor名鏡，於1935年開始投產，是徠卡第一批研發的廣角鏡頭，編號由#250001開始。這支是很早期的第120支，鏡身以金屬鎳所鑄造。鏡頭玻璃清澈明亮，帶鏡頭膠盅及前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2714', 'Summaron-SM 5.6/2.8cm Chrome', 'Summaron-SM 5.6/2.8cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_42_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_42_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_42_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_42_4.jpg', '42', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with keeper, black painted hood cap and both caps, in good condition.', '此款鏡頭由1955年開始投產，以小巧，成像優越而深受用家歡迎。玻璃清澈明亮，光圈及對焦環順滑，配以膠盅、黑漆遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2715', 'Xenon-SM 1.5/5cm Chrome', 'Xenon-SM 1.5/5cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_43_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_43_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_43_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_43_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_43_5.jpg', '43', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'The Leitz Xenon 1.5/5cm is a pre-war lens, designed by Schneider, with seven elements in five groups and three rings design. This lens is in mint condition, comes with both caps.', '此款鏡頭是二戰前產物，由施耐德公司設計，鏡頭為五片七組，三環式設計。鏡頭有正常使用痕跡，配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2716', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Nickel', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Nickel', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_44_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_44_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_44_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_44_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_44_5.jpg', '44', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is of excellent fineness and clearness, with no scratch and haze, very rare. It comes with both caps and lens hood.', '此款是Summar螺絲口鏡頭，鏡身以鎳金屬所製成，鏡口以黑色黃銅製造。鏡頭玻璃清澈，沒有花痕或灰霧，非常罕有。此鏡頭非常適合用於人像及風光攝影，彩色照片效果柔和美麗，配有鏡頭前後蓋及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2717', 'Hektor-SM 2.5/5cm Nickel', 'Hektor-SM 2.5/5cm Nickel', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_45_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_45_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_45_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_45_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_45_5.jpg', '45', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Early version of nickel lens, comes with both caps.', '此鏡是非常早期的Hektor鎳版，配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2718', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Nickel', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Nickel', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_46_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_46_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_46_3.jpg', '46', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Early Rigid Summar in nickel, with front lens cap &amp; keeper, in good condition.', '早期 Rigid Summar 鎳鏡頭。鏡身前端金屬部份後期開有兩個小槽(詳見實物)，前組鏡片有輕微清潔痕跡，連鏡頭膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2719', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', 'Summar-SM 2/5cm Rigid Nickel', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_47_6.jpg', '47', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'This early version Rigid Summar lens comes with rear cap and lens hood, in mint condition.', '早期Rigid Summar的名鏡頭，連鏡頭後蓋及遮光罩。成色十分良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2720', 'Summitar-SM 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summitar-SM 2/5cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_48_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_48_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_48_3.jpg', '48', '<span class=\"font11\">開拍價格:</span> HK$ 4,000  &nbsp; | &nbsp;  \n										\n					<span class=\"font11\">估計價格:</span> HK$ 6,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'Late version Summitar lens, it comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '後期Summitar鏡頭，特別之處為光圈至F16，較少見。而光圈葉更呈六角形，能拍出特殊的散景效果。鏡頭配有前後蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2721', 'Summicron-SM 2/5cm Compur Chrome', 'Summicron-SM 2/5cm Compur Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_49_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_49_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_49_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_49_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_49_6.jpg', '49', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is with haze and some cleansing marks, with both caps, very rare.', '非常罕有的Summicron鏡間快門螺絲口鏡頭，此款鏡頭特點是增加了兩個鏡間快門（1/100，1/200）及閃光燈同步接口供拍攝時使用，生產量極少，非常罕見。玻璃有霧及清潔痕跡，配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2722', 'Summarex-SM 1.5/8.5cm Chrome', 'Summarex-SM 1.5/8.5cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_50_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_50_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_50_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_50_4.jpg', '50', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with early ORQPO lens hood (lens hood showing four slots), both caps , in  mint condition.', 'Summarex SM 1.5/8.5cm螺絲口鏡頭，生產年份由1943-1960年左右，共生產約4300支，是徠卡其中一支著名的人像鏡皇，也是當時第一支有鍍膜的徠卡鏡頭。鏡身外觀良好，連遮光罩、非原裝鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2723', 'Thambar-SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar-SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_51_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_51_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_51_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_51_4.jpg', '51', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with spot filter, lens hood with cap and rear cap, in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡唯一的柔焦效果鏡頭，由三組四片玻璃組成，鏡頭連一片中間鍍以銀色的濾鏡，作用是將中間成象造成柔焦效果，附件完整，連原廠柔焦反射濾鏡，遮光罩，遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋。此鏡頭產量非常少，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2724', 'Thambar-SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar-SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_52_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_52_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_52_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_52_4.jpg', '52', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with hood, hood cap, spot filter and rear cap, in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡唯一的柔焦效果鏡頭，由三組四片組成，鏡頭連一塊中間鍍以銀色的反射濾鏡，作用是將中間成象造成柔焦效果，此鏡外觀成色如新，玻璃及反射濾鏡清澈乾淨，如此成色良好的Thambar在市面是絕對罕見，非常值得收藏。含原廠柔焦反射濾鏡，遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2725', 'Summicron-SM 2/9cm Chrome Pre-Series', 'Summicron-SM 2/9cm Chrome Pre-Series', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_53_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_53_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_53_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_53_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_53_5.jpg', '53', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'The lens barrel engraved “Germany”, approximately 100 units were made, serial no. starts from 1119001-1119100. Its production year is four years before SOOZI was officially introduced. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.72&amp;200 for further illustrations). It comes with both caps, in good condition.', '此鏡鏡身刻有“Germany”字樣，產於德國，鏡身編號顯示出產年份為1953年，比“SOOZI”正式投入生產早四年，約生產100支，鏡頭碼由1119001-1119100 (請参考James Lager Vol.II p.72 &amp; 200)。此鏡和正式生產的鏡頭分別在於鏡身較短，調焦環較窄，光圈讀數刻於鏡身，而非刻於調焦環，非常珍貴。配有鏡頭前後蓋。同類鏡在我司上屆拍賣會上錄得五萬多(含佣金)的成交價。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2726', 'Elmarit-SM 2.8/90mm Chrome', 'Elmarit-SM 2.8/90mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_54_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_54_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_54_3.jpg', '54', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both caps, matching serial no. of lens and lens body, very rare', '較少見的螺絲口鏡頭，此款鏡頭可卸下鏡頭前組並用於Visoflex系統，成像銳利，解析度高，鏡頭調焦順滑，鏡片晶瑩通透。配有鏡頭前後蓋。鏡頭與鏡身號碼相同。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2727', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Black Paint', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_55_6.jpg', '55', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'This lens with little haze and comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '這款徠卡鏡頭約於1931-32年生產，編號非常特別，在正常生產編號後帶有“a”字，黑漆鏡筒配以特製的對焦環，卡口則以銀色合金製造。鏡頭玻璃有輕微起霧，外觀品相良好。連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2728', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Black Paint', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_56_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_56_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_56_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_56_4.jpg', '56', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with box and both caps, in mint condition.', '此款鏡頭產於1938年，屬較前期的4/9cm鏡頭，鏡身分別使用黃銅及合金兩種金屬物料所造。鏡頭成色很新，配有當年原裝紅色盒及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2729', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Chrome', 'Elmar-SM 4/9cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_57_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_57_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_57_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_57_4.jpg', '57', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'The body engraved “Eigentum der Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar”, only 50 units were made. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.126 for further illustrations) This lens comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '非常稀有的Elmar 4/9cm，鏡身刻有“Eigentum der Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar”（徠茲工廠資產）字樣，大約生產50支。同類鏡頭在James Lager Vol.II p.126中有介紹。此鏡品相極好，連前後蓋，鏡頭號碼完整。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2730', 'Elmar-SM 6.3/10.5cm Black Paint', 'Elmar-SM 6.3/10.5cm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_58_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_58_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_58_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_58_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_58_5.jpg', '58', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is clear, comes with lens hood and rear cap, in mint condition.', '德國生產的Mountain Elmar 6.3/10.5cm螺絲口，鏡身使用黃銅及合金所製造，鏡頭玻璃清澈，成色完美，超過70年仍保持這完好成色實在難得。鏡頭配有遮光罩連蓋及鏡頭底蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2731', 'M3 Betriebsk “UR-M5” Prototype', 'M3 Betriebsk “UR-M5” Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_59_8.jpg', '59', '', '1,770,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original factory prototype M-camera with built-in TTL light meter. This camera represents one of the first units of prototyping of a built-in meter arm into Leica-M. Around 1965. Please compare van Hasbroeck \"Leica, an illustrated history, second revised edition\" on plated XXXIII and XXXII of the colour plates for similar units numbers 1206 and 1208. Only a handful of those experimental units were completed, before the project turned into the M4/M5 development. As a set, complete with external display instrument built on basis of a Leicameter-MR, which connects to the camera with a plug and shows the value given from the camera´s built-in meter. The camera is in nice conditions. This camera set has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.<br />\r\nThis comes with a meter (MR) and body cap, in excellent condition. Extremely rare.', '非常稀有的原裝工廠內部測試機，連內置TTL測光系統。這是其中一部內置meter-arm的原型機，大約在1965年生產。在Van Hasbroeck &quot;Leica, an illustrated history, second revised edition&quot; 一書中，有此款相機的圖片及介紹，書中的相機序號為1206及1208。此機與市面的M3 Betriebsk機完全不同，是為後期M4及M5的設計及製造的試驗機，通過內置的測光系統將數據傳到外置的Leicameter-MR上顯示，這樣的一台Betriebsk，是極少數由設計概念到較成熟完整功能的工廠測試機，它的收藏價值絕不亞於M4，M5的Prototype機。此機經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此機連測光錶及機身蓋，極為罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2732', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_60_7.jpg', '60', '', '377,600', null, null, null, null, 'First batch M3, The 147th Leica M3 made! With double stroke operation, short film advance level, sharp and liner non-rounded contour, these are special features found in part of earliest M3 cameras (700000-700200). It has half-moon stopper on the hot shoe, ASA is 200, frame counter with black triangular indicator, rewind knob with red “-” , triangular strap lug; A field-selector has been added later, the Shutter crated engraved “700147” , this camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. This camera comes with body cap, extremely rare.', '本機是第147 台生產的M3相機，二次過片，過片杆較短，其快門按鈕一側的前額轉角處有棱角，這只是在首批生產約700部M3中少部分才能有此特徵；此機的測距框亦有明顯突出的棱角，熱靴最上面的掣動是半月型，後背蓋內的菲林槽內有兩個圓點，ASA數字為200，回片鈕為紅色 “-” 字，三角形背帶扣，機芯同樣刻有 “700147”，以上均是第一批M3的設計特徵，它與部分早期M3 (如#700019等機)一樣，原廠加有取景框變換桿，此機已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此機機身飾皮完好無損，有使用痕跡，配有機身蓋，是市面難求的收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2733', 'M3 Chrome Consecutive Numbers', 'M3 Chrome Consecutive Numbers', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_61_8.jpg', '61', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare M3 Chrome in consecutive numbers. With double stroke operation, short film advance level, sharp and liner non-rounded contour, half-moon stopper on the hot shoe, ASA is 200, frame counter with black triangular indicator, rewind knob with red “-” triangular strap lug. #700352 also comes with a viewfinder lever. Both cameras come with box (with no numbers), instruction and leather case. Extremely rare.', '罕見的兩台相連號碼M3。此對機均有早期M3的特徵，包括: 兩次過片、過片杆較短、測距框邊的斜度較大、熱靴最上面的制動是半月型、後背蓋的菲林蓋內有兩個圓點、ASA數字為200、回片鈕為紅色 “-“字、三角型背帶扣，而機芯內的號碼亦與機頂相同。而#700352更帶有取景框撥杆。此套機連包裝盒(無碼)、證書及皮套。可以在早期800台中找到兩台相連號的M3實在十分難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2734', 'M3 Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm Double Stroke', 'M3 Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm Double Stroke', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_62_6.jpg', '62', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'This camera belongs to the first batch M3 production. With some normal signs of use, comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm lens (#1118139) and meter (#01140).', '此機為徠卡生產的第一批M3，有早期M3的特徵。除有兩次過片的特性外，過片杆較短，而回片鈕亦只有一個圓點，相機背帶扣呈三角型。此機機身雖有使用痕跡，但取景框明亮通透。配以Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭 (#1118139)及測光錶 (#01140)，為當時徠卡的專業配置。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2735', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_63_7.jpg', '63', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early M3 Chrome with double stroke operation, no frame line sector. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '較早期的M3相機，有兩次過片的功能特性，過片杆較短，不帶線框撥杆。連機身蓋。超過半世紀仍保持如此成色，較為罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2736', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_64_7.jpg', '64', '', '7,260', null, null, null, null, 'Early M3 Chrome with double stroke and self-timer, it comes with body cap, in good condition.', '早期的M3相機，有兩次過片功能特性，帶自拍。機身有輕微使用痕跡，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2737', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_65_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_65_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_65_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_65_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_65_5.jpg', '65', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Early version M3 with double stroke. It comes with body cap, in good condition.', '早期的M3相機，有兩次過片的特性，過片杆較短，連同機身蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2738', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke with Summicron-M 2/5cm', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke with Summicron-M 2/5cm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_66_6.jpg', '66', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'A classic M3 camera comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm Chrome (#1533275) and front lens cap, in good working order and mint condition.', '經典的M3銀色機身，兩次過片，配以銀色Summicron-M 2/5cm鏡頭 (#1533275)及鏡頭蓋。操作功能正常，成色上佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2739', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_67_6.jpg', '67', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Classical M3 Chrome was produced in 1958, with single film advance. It comes with box, certificate, body cap and leather case, in like new condition.', '經典的銀色M3機身，產於1958年，屬單次過片。此機連包裝盒、證書、機身蓋及皮套，運作暢順，成色接近全新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2740', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_68_7.jpg', '68', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M3 in matte black paint was produced in 1960 and belongs to the second batch production no.993501-993750. Matte black paint was only used in the first and second batch production of M3, early button rewind M2 and MP original Black Paint. This was then replaced by shiny black paint in the later M3 production. What is more, M3 in matte black paint with serial number before #1000000 is exceptionally rare nowadays. This M3 is in original matte black paint, well functioned and in excellent condition.', '此徠卡M3啞黑漆於1960年生產，是第二批次生產相機 (#993501-993750)。獨特的地方是，用在M3上的啞黑漆只在最早的第一批、第二批及MP黑漆上用，後期版本的M3已經改為亮面黑漆，更值得留意的是在序號1000000以前的啞黑漆M3現今極為罕見，十分珍貴。本M3為原裝啞黑漆，未經翻新，外觀成色良好，取景明亮，操作順暢，功能正常，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2741', 'M3 Black Repainted', 'M3 Black Repainted', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_69_7.jpg', '69', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'Early M3 with repainted, single stoke operation. This camera comes with body cap, with insignificant sign of use and good working order.', '後塗的黑漆M3機身，屬單次過片，帶自拍。機頂上後刻的字體較大。而且機身只有輕微使用痕跡，操作功能正常，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2742', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_70_6.jpg', '70', '<span class=\"font11\">開拍價格:</span> HK$ 18,000  &nbsp; | &nbsp;  \n										\n					<span class=\"font11\">估計價格:</span> HK$ 28,000 - 38,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'M3 repainted by Leica, with single stroke, it comes with body cap and original Leica invoice for Leica factory repaint, in mint condition.', 'M3黑漆機身，單次過片。機身黑漆為後期送往徠卡工廠加工，附有原廠單據。連機身蓋，外觀成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2743', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_71_6.jpg', '71', '', '181,500', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar Leica M3 in black paint finish Nr. 1078750 from batch of 300 cameras Nr. 1078500-1078800 made in 1963. Please compare Leica Historica magazine VIDOM Nr. 105 (June 2013). The camera in entirely original, and very beautiful condition. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.<br />\r\nThis camera comes with body cap, in good working order and mint condition.', '此M3黑漆機身號碼為1078750，產於1963年。是當年在序號由1078550 – 1078800中生產的300台黑漆相機之一，可參閱2013年6月的Leica Historica magazine VIDOM P.105。此相機是完全原裝，成色極佳，配機身蓋，並經過Lars Netopil鑑定。屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2744', 'M3 Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_72_6.jpg', '72', '', '181,500', null, null, null, null, 'Original Leica M3 Black Paint with single stroke. It comes with body cap, in good working order and mint condition.', '相對銀色機身，黑漆的產量相對較少。此機為原裝黑漆，未經翻新，外觀成色良好，操作正常，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2745', 'M3 Gold', 'M3 Gold', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_73_6.jpg', '73', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'A re-plated M3 Gold, comes with a re-plated gold Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#1883394), in mint condition.', '後期鍍金的經典M3機身，配以同為金色的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#1883394)，外觀成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2746', 'MP Black Paint', 'MP Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_74_8.jpg', '74', '', '5,428,000', null, null, null, null, 'Initially, Leica early MP was custom-made for a very few professional photographers and reporters in 1957. With Leicavit, the user can quickly shoot up to two frames per second without taking the camera away from eyes so that the decisive moment can be quickly recorded. Around 138 units of it were produced. The serial number starts from MP-013 to MP-150. (Please refer to James Lager Vol. I p.193 for further illustrations). This camera is made in original black paint. The serial number engraved at the bottom matches that of the body. It comes with Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1474804) Black Paint for MP and front lens cap, extremely rare.', 'MP初期是徠卡為極少數專業攝影師及記者而訂製，配有過片器，最多可以每秒過片兩張，使決定性瞬間(DECISIVE MOMENT)都得以快速記錄下來。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此乃早期的MP黑漆相機，產於1956-1957年。當時黑漆相機產量極少，MP黑漆只有138台左右。而當時黑漆相機為油質漆，後期黑漆相機則改為水質漆，所以早期的黑漆相機更為罕見珍貴。黑漆的機身號碼由MP-013至MP-150止(可參閱James Lager Vol.I p.193)。此機機底號碼與機身相同，配有供MP同期使用的黒漆鏡頭Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1474804)、鏡頭蓋及MP Leicavit，機身露銅，有久遠的歷史韻味。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2747', 'MP Leather Case', 'MP Leather Case', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_75_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_75_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_75_3.jpg', '75', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare early leather case for MP. The most valuable is the leather case was stamped the Japanese imported customs seal in 1957. This reveals that the case was made in 1957 or years earlier, specially for MP cameras.', '極為罕見之早期MP專用皮套。最珍貴之處是皮套內蓋有1957年日本當年海關入口的印鑑。顯示是1957年或之前已生產，是專供MP機用。另外，皮套底部有特別的位置，預留予MP Leicavit過片時使用，甚為特別。皮套成色極佳，為收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2748', 'M2 Chrome Betriebsk', 'M2 Chrome Betriebsk', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_76_7.jpg', '76', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 Chrome Betriebsk is factory-used only and has never been launched officially. “Betriebsk” engraved on top plate and the serial number is M2-2007. It comes with body cap, without self-timer, in mint condition.', '此機為徠卡工廠內部測試用的M2機身，沒有自拍功能。機頂刻有 “Betriebsk” 字樣，機身號碼為M2-2007，連機身蓋，成色極佳，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2749', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_77_6.jpg', '77', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early M2 in chrome, without self-timer, bottom rewind, only small number produced, comes with body caps, in good working order and excellent condition.', '早期的M2銀色，不帶自拍，按鈕回片，產量較少。外觀成色良好，連機身蓋，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2750', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_78_7.jpg', '78', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 Chrome was produced in 1963, with body cap and normal used marks.', '此銀色M2產於1963年，不帶自拍，功能正常，有正常使用痕跡，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2751', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_79_7.jpg', '79', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M2 Chrome made in 1965, comes with body cap, in good working order.', '此銀色機身於1965年生產，機身外觀成色良好。此機功能正常，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2752', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_80_7.jpg', '80', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'The first version of M2 Black Paint was produced in 1958, numbered 948601-949100. It was ranked R7, Exceptionally Rare, in the Leica International Price Guide (R1-R10). However, for M2 with rewind button and without self-timer, less than 200 units of them were produced. They were indeed extremely rare and should be ranked the same as MP (Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.202 for further illustrations). This camera comes with body cap, in original black paint with used marks, well functioned. It has been authenticated by Mr. James Lager.', '第一代的M2黑漆版，產於1958年，批號在948601-949100之間，雖然在徠卡國際價格指南(R1-R10)當中，M2黑漆版被列為R7，是極為稀有(Exceptionally Rare)的評級，但是按鈕回片、不帶自拍的M2黑漆更是罕見，產量少於200台，它的級別應是與MP同級。這個版本的M2在James Lager Vol.I p.202書中也有同類型的介紹，此機有使用痕跡，運作暢順，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2753', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_81_7.jpg', '81', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'This camera belongs to the first batch production, numbered 948601 - 949100. It was ranked R7, Exceptionally Rare in the Leica International Price Guide (R1-R10). Without self-timer, decorated with leather, it comes with body cap and leather case, in good working order.', '此機是第一批生產的M2黑漆相機，生產編號在#948601至#949100之間。在徠卡國際價格指南(R1-R10)當中，M2被列為R7級別，是較為稀有的收藏級別。該機不帶自拍，機背飾皮為後貼。此機連機身蓋及皮套，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2754', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_82_7.jpg', '82', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint with self-timer. It comes with body cap, and normal used marks, in good working order.', '原裝黑漆M2，有自拍功能，運作良好連機身蓋。機身有使用痕跡，部份露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2755', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_83_6.jpg', '83', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint, with self-timer, level rewind. It comes with body cap with normal used marks.', '原裝徠卡黑漆M2，帶自拍，撥杆回片。機身有輕微露銅，連機身蓋，操作功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2756', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_84_6.jpg', '84', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint, with self-timer, comes with body cap, and normal used marks, in good working order.', '原裝早期M2黑漆機身，帶自拍功能，運作良好連機身蓋，有明顯使用痕跡，機身部分露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2757', 'M2-M Chrome', 'M2-M Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_85_6.jpg', '85', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'M2-M Chrome, only 275 units were produced, serial number starts from 1163771 to 1164046. It comes with body cap, in good working order.', 'M2-M作為配備Leitz New York電動馬達使用的機種，於機底位置有電子觸點。生產序號為1163771-1164046，共275台。機身有正常使用痕跡，連機身蓋及馬達，十分罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2758', 'M2-R Chrome', 'M2-R Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_86_6.jpg', '86', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'M2-R is basically an M2 with self-timer together with rapid film loading system of M4. Serial number starts from 1248401 to 1250200. It comes with certificate, papers, strap, body cap and matching number box, extremely rare.', 'M2-R是以M2相機加上M4的快速裝片功能，機身編號由1248001至1250200。此機與機身號碼相同的包裝盒、證書、說明書、相機帶及機身蓋。成色像新，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2759', 'M4 Chrome Dummy', 'M4 Chrome Dummy', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_87_7.jpg', '87', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'The Leica M4 was launched in between 1967- 1975, serial number starts from 1175001 to 1443170. This is the M4 dummy comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '徠卡M4原於1967年至1975年間分階段生產，機身編號由1175001至1443170。此機是M4的模型機，當時只提供予經銷商作展示之用，並無流出市面。此機連機身蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2760', 'M4 Chrome', 'M4 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_88_7.jpg', '88', '', '7,260', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 Chrome was produced in 1969, comes with body cap, with normal used marks and in good working order.', '此台銀色的M4產於1969年，連機身蓋，操作正常，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2761', 'M4 Black Chrome', 'M4 Black Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_89_6.jpg', '89', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 produced in 1974, comes with body cap, in mint condition and good working order.', '此台黑色的M4產於1974年，外觀成色良好，取景框明亮，操作功能正常，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2762', 'M4 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm', 'M4 Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_90_8.jpg', '90', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 Black Paint was produced in 1963, engraved “MDW 062461508” on top plate, barrel and meter. It comes with a Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome lens (#2010236) and meter, in good working condition.', '黑漆版的M4產於1963年，機頂上刻有“MDW 062461508”，配有銀色Summicron-M 2/35mm八枚玉鏡頭 (#2010236)，連測光錶。而鏡身與測光錶上亦同樣刻有 “MDW 062461508” 字樣，機頂有輕微露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2763', 'M4 Black Paint', 'M4 Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_91_6.jpg', '91', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 Black Paint was produced in 1970, with body cap, insignificant sign of use and good working order.', '此台黑漆版的M4產於1970年，連機身蓋，運作良好，有輕微使用痕跡，回片杆位置有輕微露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2764', 'M4 Mot Black Paint', 'M4 Mot Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_92_7.jpg', '92', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1967-1970, motorized M4 was first named M4M and later M4 Mot. They are all in black paint finish, comes with body cap and plastic box, in mint condition.', 'M4 Mot產於1967-1970年間，是M4的改良版，可加馬達使用，早期稱為M4M，後期則名為M4 Mot，所有機身均為黑漆。此機配有機身蓋及相機盒，成色極新，功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2765', 'M4-2 Chrome', 'M4-2 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_93_6.jpg', '93', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare M4-2, it was launched in 1977 since the production of M4 was suspended in 1975. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '極為罕見的M4-2銀色機身。當M4於1975年停產後，M4-2於1977年推出市場。M4-2可安裝馬達，框線與M4一樣，但機頂省卻了複雜的刻字，而原有的自拍器亦取消了。此機成色極新，連機身蓋，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2766', '24x27mm Postcamera – The LAST Postcamera', '24x27mm Postcamera – The LAST Postcamera', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_94_6.jpg', '94', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Postcamera is a 24x27mm format camera, which built on the MD, MDa and MD-2 housings. This was launched in 1963-1972 and approximately around 700 units were produced. This camera comes with Summaron-M 2.8/35mm lens (#2311877), “DBPIII 100” engraved on barrel refers to “Deutsches Bundes Post”, it comes with front lens cap, in mint condition.', '此台相機最珍貴之處是Postcamera中最後一台生產的相機。Postcamera是24X27mm的格式，依MD、MDa及MD-2的式樣為藍本。第一台產於1958年，機身號碼為928997，而最後一台生產的機身編號為1294000。由1963至1972年間共生產700台左右。機身配有固定的Summaron-M 2.8/35mm鏡頭 (#2311877)，鏡上刻有 “DBP III 100”，是指 “Deutsches Bundes Post”。另外亦配有鏡頭前蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2767', 'M4-P Chrome Set', 'M4-P Chrome Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_95_7.jpg', '95', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 70th Anniversary of the first 135mm format camera, M4-P was launched. The back of the top plate engraved “Leica 1913-1983”, comes with body cap, in mint condition. Another M4-P in Chrome was made in 1982, with body cap, well functioned, in mint condition.', '此M4-P套裝其中一部為M4-P 70週年版。徠卡為紀念1913年第一台135格式的相機面世70週年而生產的M4-P，此機的特別號碼為C410，機背上刻有 “Leica 1913-1983” 字樣，連機身蓋，成色優良。另一台銀色普通版M4-P產於1982年，連機身蓋，操作暢順，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2768', 'M4-P Black', 'M4-P Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_96_6.jpg', '96', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'The serial no. of this M4-P is *1552623 stands for #1552623. It refers to the second batch production, comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '此M4-P的機身編號是*1552623，表示序號1552623的相機，工廠共生產過兩次，而此台帶*的相機便是第二次生產的貨品。此相機連機身蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2769', 'Leica M5 Wooden Model (From Leica Museum)', 'Leica M5 Wooden Model (From Leica Museum)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_97_6.jpg', '97', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'These two M5 models were original design specially made pre the production of M5. One of them was painted with light gray paint, its shape is the same as the original M5 but without any engraved marks. Another model is a more developed version, the camera body is decorated with black leather, some other parts of the camera were made of metal, e.g. film advance level and self-timer and the strap lug was made of plastic. This wooden cast model is relatively more alike to the original M5. This pair of M5 wooden model is exactly the one from Leica Museum, which illustrated in &lt;&lt;Prototype Leica&gt;&gt; written by Lars Netopil.', '這兩台為生產M5而設計的原裝M5木製模型機。其中的一部掃上淺灰色油漆，外型特別。此機雕刻出M5的輪廓，屬於M5的設計雛型，木製機身上沒有任何數字刻度。而另外一台是比較完善的設計版本，機身位置飾有黒色皮，部份位置亦以金屬製造，如過片杆及自拍按鈕等；兩邊的相機扣則以膠製，與正式生產機型較相近。這對M5木製模型機就正是Lars Netopil的《Prototype Leica》書中展示的那兩部。<br />\r\n此對徠卡原裝木制M5模型機及M5的第一台相機 (#1287001)，均為收藏佳品。如收藏家能同時擁有這三部珍品，則M5的設計及生產歷程能淋漓盡致地表現出來。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2770', 'M5 - The FIRST Leica M5', 'M5 - The FIRST Leica M5', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_98_7.jpg', '98', '', '472,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar Leica M5 from the first 50 units, batch numbers 1287001 - 1287050, indicated as M5 &quot;Null-series&quot; in the factory records. The camera here, the very first one of this series, is the very first officially produced and serial-numbered M5. With a number of small differences in finish and engraving, compared to later series. (Please refer to James Lager Vol. I p. 243 for #1287002.) This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. This camera comes with body cap and box.', '第一部徠卡正式出廠的M5相機，也是屬於50部留在工廠內作測試系列的M5 (1287001- 1287050)的第一部，此機身的外型與後期的M5亦稍有不同，例如部分配件的顏色、ASA轉盤上的條紋較細及機身編號刻字較大等，在James Lager Vol. I p.243中亦有介紹此款M5，其機身號為#1287002。此機已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n此機配有機身蓋及包裝盒，屬收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2771', 'M6 Cut Away', 'M6 Cut Away', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_99_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_99_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_99_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_99_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_99_5.jpg', '99', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'The detailed inner structure of M6 can be seen in this camera, it comes with body cap.', 'M6機身以剖切面的形式呈現，讓每位徠卡迷可更清楚了解M6機身的內部結構。此機連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2772', 'M6 0.72 Black', 'M6 0.72 Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_100_6.jpg', '100', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera in black comes with body cap, in mint condition.  The top plate engraved with \"Ernst Leitz Wetzlar Gmbh\".', '經典的M6黑色機身配以徠卡的紅色標誌，是徠卡的暢銷機之一。此機外觀成色良好，配機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2773', 'M6 Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Titanium', 'M6 Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Titanium', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_101_8.jpg', '101', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'M6 Titanium decorated with ostrich leather, comes with packaging, certificate. Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Titanium (#3661128), comes with both caps and certificate, with normal used marks, in mint condition.', '鈦金屬版M6，機身覆以駝鳥皮，連包裝證書，機身有輕微使用痕跡。配有鈦版Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#3661128)，連鏡頭前後蓋及包裝證書，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2774', 'M6A 0.72 Chrome', 'M6A 0.72 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_102_6.jpg', '102', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The serial number of this camera is 0000014, “Leica M6A” and the special number 0000014 engraved on hot shoe. There are electrical contacts at the back and chassis, very rare. It comes with presentation box and body cap, in mint condition.', 'M6A屬於M7的Prototype。此機的熱靴上刻有 “Leica M6A” 及 “0000014” 的字樣和編號，產量極少。機頂快門轉盤上有光圈優先模式，機內有電子接點。本機配有內包裝盒及機身蓋，品相接近完美，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2775', 'M7 0.72 Chrome with Leicavit', 'M7 0.72 Chrome with Leicavit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_103_8.jpg', '103', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'M7 Chrome body comes with Leicavit (#00152) and body cap, in mint condition.', '此機成色優良，運作暢順，連Leicavit (#00152)及機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2776', 'MP 0.58 Chrome', 'MP 0.58 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_104_7.jpg', '104', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'MP Chrome with 0.58 frame line, comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '現行版的MP銀色配以0.58線框，連機身蓋，操作功能正常，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2777', 'MP 0.58 Chrome A la cart', 'MP 0.58 Chrome A la cart', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_105_6.jpg', '105', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'A la cart MP 0.58 Chrome decorated with red leather, with 0.58 frame line. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '經典的徠卡銀色MP機身，配以0.58的取景線框。機身覆蓋大紅色的飾皮，經典得來不失個人風格。此機配有機身