, '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'This lens has clear glass, comes with OLLUX hood, filter, box, both caps, in like new condition, very rare.', '銀色鋼咀Summilux-M 1.4/35mm配有OLLUX遮光罩、濾鏡、包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋，加上玻璃通透，當年產量較少，有如此包裝齊全及品相佳的鋼咀鏡頭已是十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2789', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_117_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_117_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_117_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_117_4.jpg', '117', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada in 1960, comes with goggles, OLLUX hood, leather case, box, in good working condition.', '產於1960年的Summilux-M 1.4/35mm銀色鋼咀，由加拿大製造。連眼鏡、OLLUX遮光罩、皮套及原裝紙盒。操作正常，調焦暢順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2790', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_118_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_118_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_118_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_118_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_118_5.jpg', '118', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is clear, in good working order and mint condition. It completes with goggles, both caps and filter, extremely rare.', '銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鋼咀眼鏡版，成色極新，玻璃通透，調焦順暢。連眼鏡、鏡頭前後蓋及濾鏡，十分珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2791', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_119_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_119_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_119_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_119_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_119_5.jpg', '119', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim, less than 100 pieces were made, extremely rare. It comes with filter, rear lens cap and OLLUX hood, with normal used marks, in good working order.', '第一代黑色鋼咀，產量約數十支，極為珍貴罕見。此鏡連濾鏡、鏡頭後蓋及OLLUX 遮光罩。鏡身雖有輕微使用痕跡，但玻璃清澈，為收藏者必納入的囊中之物。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2792', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_120_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_120_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_120_3.jpg', '120', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The first version Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim, comes with both caps, goggles, filter and OLLUX hood, in mint condition, extremely rare.', '第一代黑色鋼咀眼鏡版，產量只有數十支，極為珍貴。此鏡頭連鏡頭前後蓋、眼鏡、濾鏡及遮光罩(OLLUX)，成色極佳，市面絕對難尋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2793', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black Steel Rim', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_121_6.jpg', '121', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a Summilux-M 1.4/35mm lens with steel rim but black barrel. It completes with black chrome goggles, filter, silver cap, rear cap and box, in mint condition with clear glass.', '這是早期的Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鋼咀眼鏡版鏡頭，鏡身為黑色，但鏡頭頂端則是鋼金屬接環，產量僅數十支，加上成色特佳，配原裝包裝盒，極為珍貴。此鏡頭配濾鏡、銀色鏡頭前蓋、鏡頭後蓋及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2794', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_122_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_122_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_122_3.jpg', '122', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is clear, with both caps, in excellent condition.', '連鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃清澈，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2795', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_123_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_123_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_123_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_123_4.jpg', '123', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with hood, both caps, box and certificate, with fungus in glass.', '此鏡頭配有遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋、包裝盒及證書。玻璃有霉。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2796', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_124_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_124_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_124_3.jpg', '124', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'A Summilux-M 1.4/35mm lens with leather case, lens front cap and goggles, in mint condition.', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鏡頭連皮套、鏡頭前蓋及眼鏡。鏡身雖有輕微使用痕跡，但整體成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2797', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_125_7.jpg', '125', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, '1st Production Version, three small bright marks on lens body, bright marks at filter mount from screw-mount custom hood ring. Comes with Non-original Contax cap, original hood, hood cover and leather case and matching serial box.', '九片五組玻璃設計，其中兩片為非球面玻璃，產量只有2000支左右。此鏡連包裝盒、皮筒、遮光罩 (#12587)、遮光罩蓋及非原廠鏡頭前蓋，後蓋。玻璃清澈，唯鏡頭前端有輕微掉漆。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2798', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_126_6.jpg', '126', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Nine Elements in five groups and two elements are ASPH, around 2000 units were made. It comes with box, all papers, leather case, hood (#12587), hood cap, both caps, in like new condition.', '九片五組設計，其中兩片為非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，產量約在2000支左右。此鏡頭連包裝盒、說明書、證書、皮筒、遮光罩 (#12587)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋。鏡身成色極佳，玻璃通透，收藏或自用皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2799', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_127_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_127_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_127_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_127_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_127_5.jpg', '127', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome in mint condition, discontinued, comes with hood and rear lens cap.', '銀色Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH非球面玻璃鏡頭是採用黃銅製作鏡身。此鏡玻璃通透，成色新淨。連遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。此款鏡頭已經停產。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2800', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_128_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_128_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_128_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_128_4.jpg', '128', '', '31,860', null, null, null, null, 'The latest version Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#11663) comes with hood, hood cap, leather case, both caps, all papers and box, in brand new condition.', '為最新款的Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH鏡頭 (#11663)，此鏡連遮光罩及遮光罩蓋、皮筒、鏡頭前後蓋及包裝證書。全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2801', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_129_7.jpg', '129', '', '19,360', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classical Summicron-M 2/35mm lens with eight elements, made in Germany. It completes with keeper and hood (#12585H), with normal used marks, clear lens.', '德國生產的 “八枚玉” 鏡頭為徠卡Summicron系列中的經典之作。此鏡頭配有膠盅及遮光罩 (#12585H)。鏡身有正常使用痕跡，但玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2802', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_130_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_130_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_130_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_130_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_130_5.jpg', '130', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is a classical Summicron-M 2/35mm lens with eight elements, made in Germany. It comes with both caps and some haze found in lens.', '德國生產的 “八枚玉” 鏡頭為徠卡Summicron系列中的經典之作。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃內有輕微霧，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2803', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron M2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_131_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_131_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_131_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_131_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_131_5.jpg', '131', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made of high quality fluorite glass, produced in Germany, comes with filters and packaging box, in like new condition.', '此鏡產於德國，是由高質素的螢石玻璃所製成，故被用家稱為 “八枚玉”。所產生的影像自然，色調豐富油潤，偏古典韻味，在黑白照片上的表現尤其出色。此鏡連濾鏡及包裝盒，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2804', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_132_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_132_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_132_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_132_4.jpg', '132', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'Early version Summicron-M 2/35mm lens in chrome, with both caps, goggles and fungus in glass.', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm早期版本。連鏡頭前後蓋及眼鏡，玻璃有霉。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2805', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_133_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_133_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_133_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_133_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_133_5.jpg', '133', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Germany, some parts were repaired, has normal used marks, with both caps.', '德國製的黑色八枚玉鏡頭，有正常使用痕跡，玻璃良好，有後期維修及更換過零件，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2806', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_134_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_134_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_134_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_134_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_134_5.jpg', '134', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Germany, some parts were repaired, has normal used marks, with rear cap.', '德國製的黑色八枚玉鏡頭，有明顯使用痕跡，玻璃良好，有後期維修及更換過零件，連鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2807', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_135_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_135_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_135_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_135_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_135_5.jpg', '135', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is early version Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements), made in Canada, with both caps, no scratches, in mint condition.', '較早期的加拿大製黑色八枚玉鏡頭，調焦環為紅字，品相良好，玻璃沒有劃痕。連鏡頭前後蓋，該鏡產量稀少，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2808', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black Paint (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black Paint (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_136_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_136_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_136_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_136_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_136_5.jpg', '136', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens consists of eight elements in six groups made of the precious polished fluorite glass. It was produced in 1965, comes with both caps, the black painted ones are extremely rare.', '八枚玉鏡頭為徠卡Summicron系列中最為傳奇和經典的鏡頭。它由八片六組組成，鏡片是由成本高昂的螢石玻璃打磨而成。由於其設計及用料出色所以其成象質素極為出眾。此鏡頭於1965年生產，連鏡頭前後蓋。當中只有極少數為黑漆，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2809', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_137_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_137_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_137_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_137_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_137_5.jpg', '137', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada, some screws mounted on the depth of field scale were changed, has normal used marks, with both caps.', '加拿大製的黑色八枚玉鏡頭，產量稀少，有使用痕跡，景深尺環螺絲非原裝。連鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2810', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_138_6.jpg', '138', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very few black Summicron-M 2/35mm (8 Elements) was made in Germany, it is the last batch, comes with both caps and clear glass, in mint condition. Very rare.', '德國生產的Summicron-M 2/35mm黑色八枚玉鏡頭，此鏡更是八枚玉中最後一年生產的產品，產量極少。配有鏡頭前後蓋，而且玻璃通透。如此品相優良的鏡頭在市面已經十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2811', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_139_6.jpg', '139', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Very few black Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements with brass mount, goggles and both caps. Cleansing marks on glass and normal used marks on barrel.', '此鏡由德國生產，為徠卡Summicron系列中的傳奇之作。鏡頭由八片六組玻璃組成，並使用當時透光度及成本極高的螢石玻璃所造，故被用家稱為 “八枚玉” 。此鏡身是黑色，鏡頭卡口為黃銅，產量十分稀少，極為珍貴。鏡頭配有眼鏡及前後蓋，玻璃有清潔痕跡，眼鏡玻璃稍有損傷，鏡身亦有掉漆，為鏡頭添上歲月痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2812', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_140_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_140_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_140_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_140_4.jpg', '140', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was produced in 1963, with 8 Elements in 6 groups, very rare. It comes with filter and goggles, with normal used marks on focusing knobs, in like new condition.', '黑色版的德產Summicron-M 2/35mm鏡頭，產於1963年，由八片六組鏡片組成，故稱為八枚玉。當中黑色產量極少，此鏡按鈕位置僅有輕微露銅，鏡身品相良好，玻璃通透。此鏡連眼鏡及濾鏡，成色極新，市面罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2813', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 Elements )', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 Elements )', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_141_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_141_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_141_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_141_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_141_5.jpg', '141', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'This Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 Elements) was made in Germany. It comes with rear lens cap, hood (#12526) and hood cap, in mint condition.', '德國製銀色七枚玉鏡頭，帶鏡頭後蓋、遮光罩 (#12526)及遮光罩蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2814', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (7 Elements )', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (7 Elements )', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_142_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_142_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_142_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_142_4.jpg', '142', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada, in good working order with normal used marks. It comes with hood and rear lens cap, in mint condition.', '鏡頭產自加拿大，有正常使用痕跡，操作正常。連遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2815', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_143_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_143_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_143_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_143_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_143_5.jpg', '143', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'It completes with rear lens cap, hood and hood cap, in mint condition.', '此鏡頭有非球面玻璃，備有鏡頭後蓋、遮光罩及遮光罩蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2816', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Titanium', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Titanium', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_144_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_144_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_144_3.jpg', '144', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lens completes with box, instruction, certificate, leather case, hood, both caps in titanium, in mint condition and good working order.', '鈦版非球面玻璃鏡頭，成色新淨，調焦暢順。配有包裝盒、證書、說明書、皮筒、遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2817', 'Elmarit-C 2.8/40mm Black', 'Elmarit-C 2.8/40mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_145_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_145_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_145_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_145_4.jpg', '145', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was produced for Leica CL series, very rare and not even launched officially. It comes with both caps, in mint condition.', 'Elmarit-C鏡頭適用於徠卡CL機，產量極少，不曾正式推出，十分稀有。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2818', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH Chrome', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_146_6.jpg', '146', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'This Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH lens is not in the Leica production list, which is a set of M9-P white edition launched in 2012 specially for Japanese market. Only 50 pieces produced. It completes with both caps, instruction manual, certificate and inner box, in brand new condition.', '極為珍貴的銀色Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH鏡頭。此鏡頭為2012年M9-P白色套機中所配備的銀色Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH鏡頭，全球僅生產50支，並只在日本市場公開發售。此銀色鏡頭只為紀念機而生產，並非在正常生產列表中的產品。此鏡頭配有前後蓋、說明書、證書及內盒，玻璃通透，全新未經使用，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2819', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_147_6.jpg', '147', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'The current version Noctilux-M, comes with all packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '徠卡最新型最大光圈的Noctilux-M鏡頭，質素極佳。此鏡全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2820', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_148_6.jpg', '148', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Third version Noctilux-M 1/50mm lens in E60. It comes with hood, box and certificate in matching number and both caps, in brand new condition.', '第三代的Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E60口徑，連外置遮光罩、相同號碼的包裝盒及證書與鏡頭前後蓋，全新未經使用。如此成色及包裝齊全的鏡頭在市面已是難得一見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2821', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_149_6.jpg', '149', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This lens belongs to the testing batch production. It was launched approximately five years earlier than the original batch, comes with both caps, very rare.', '這一代內置遮光罩型號的生產編號正常為36字頭開始。但此鏡頭編號為34開頭，比正式批量生產的時間早五年左右，十分珍貴，為收藏極品。此鏡配有鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2822', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_150_6.jpg', '150', '', '43,560', null, null, null, null, 'The 4th version of Noctilux-M 1/50mm lens made in Canada in E60, comes with both lens caps, in mint condition.', '加拿大產第4代Noctilux-M 1/50mm鏡頭，E60口徑，連鏡頭前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2823', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm (One of the last 100 pieces)', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm (One of the last 100 pieces)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_151_7.jpg', '151', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is from the last batch of 100 pieces lenses, very rare. It comes with wooden presentation box, instruction manual, certificate, both caps, key and gloves, lens is clear and with 6 bit.', '此鏡為徠卡經典鏡頭Noctilux-M 1/50mm最後一百支珍藏版，配有精美木盒、說明書、證書、鏡頭前後蓋及手套，木盒更配有鑰匙，更見精緻及尊貴。木盒雖有輕微碰撞痕跡，但此鏡品相極佳，玻璃通透潔淨，帶電子接點，是市面難求的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2824', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_152_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_152_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_152_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_152_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_152_5.jpg', '152', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'This lens belongs to the first batch production, approximately 100 pieces were made. This lens comes with keeper and both caps, in mint condition.', '通常市面上常見的Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm鏡頭編號均為22或25開頭。此鏡編號為217開頭，是第一批生產100多支的其中一支。且鏡頭前端上的UV之處與後期略為不同，十分珍貴，收藏者不可或缺。此鏡配有膠盅及鏡頭前蓋，成色極佳 。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2825', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_153_6.jpg', '153', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is early version Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm lens, around 1500 units were made. The glass is clean and clear, with normal used marks on the lens barrel, very rare. It completes with both caps, in very good condition.', '此鏡為早期的Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm鏡頭，產量極少，大約只有1500支。當中有兩片手磨非球面玻璃，製作工序繁複，成象質素極為出色。此鏡配有鏡頭前後蓋，鏡身有輕微使用痕跡，但玻璃清澈，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2826', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Prototype Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Prototype Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_154_7.jpg', '154', '', '519,200', null, null, null, null, 'This lens head is of an early experimental state, with diaphragm-index hand-engraved. It was probably from optical bench testing, Optical formula B679. Leica produced three such lens heads with serial numbers 0000459 - 0000461 between November 1960 and February 1961.The lens head here mounted in a later serial production helicoid from Summilux 50mm. Please refer to L&amp;H Auction 1 catalogue, p.31 for more details, the lens illustrated inside is 0000460 and is in sequence with the number of this lens (#0000459).', '徠卡於1960年11月至1961年2月期間，共生產三枚測試用的鏡頭，鏡頭光學技術為B679，編號由0000459 - 0000461。<br />\r\n此鏡頭為原型版鏡頭，屬於早期測驗版，光圈數字為手工雕刻，收藏價值極高，為市面難求的稀有珍品，可參閱我司首屆拍賣會拍賣圖錄第31頁，其號碼為0000460，與此鏡 (#0000459)為相連號碼。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2827', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_155_6.jpg', '155', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'The first version Summilux 50mm lens. It completes with XOOIM hood, hood cap, leather case and lens rear cap, in mint condition.', '第一代Summilux 50mm鏡頭。連遮光罩XOOIM、遮光罩蓋、皮筒及鏡頭後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2828', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black &amp; Chrome Set', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black &amp; Chrome Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_156_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_156_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_156_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_156_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_156_5.jpg', '156', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'These two lenses come with rear lens caps, have some normal used marks, in good working condition.', '兩支Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭均配有鏡頭後蓋，另分別配有遮光罩(XOOIM及12586)。兩支鏡頭外觀有輕微使用痕跡，但操作功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2829', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_157_6.jpg', '157', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is the first version Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint lens with brass mount. This completes with keeper and front cap, in mint condition. James Lager talked about this lens during the Leica Seminar held in September 2013, Beijing.', '極為罕見的第一代Summilux-M 1.4/50mm黑漆鏡頭，鏡頭底部的接口為黃銅製造，產量十分稀少。此鏡頭連膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。玻璃通透，調焦暢順，此鏡頭鏡身極新。產於半世紀以前的鏡頭仍能保持如此上佳的成色，實在十分罕有，是不可多得的收藏佳品。於本年度北京舉行的徠卡研討會上，James Lager曾特別介紹此鏡頭。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2830', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_158_6.jpg', '158', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens completes with box, certificate, instruction, leather case and both caps, in like new condition.', '此鏡頭連包裝盒、證書、說明書、皮套及鏡頭前後蓋，玻璃清澈通透，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2831', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_159_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_159_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_159_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_159_4.jpg', '159', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'A black painted lens comes with both lens caps, leather case, box and all papers, in brand new condition.', '千禧年生產的黑漆鏡頭，配有鏡頭前後蓋、皮筒、包裝證書齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2832', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_160_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_160_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_160_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_160_4.jpg', '160', '', '2,360', null, null, null, null, 'This lens with signs of use, fungus in glass, comes with both caps.', '鏡頭有使用痕跡，玻璃有霉。連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2833', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black &amp; Chrome and Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Black &amp; Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black &amp; Chrome and Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Black &amp; Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_161_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_161_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_161_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_161_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_161_5.jpg', '161', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'Set of two Leitz factory-internal Leica M lenses Leitz Wetzlar Summicron 2/50 (II) Nr. 1885111 and Leitz Canada Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90 (II) Nr. 3003249. Lens mounts in mixed finish, combined from black and silver. A mysterious field are those &quot;finish-mix&quot; lenses, which sometimes appear, but are of unknown meaning. In fact, already in the Wilhelm Albert book of 1962, finish-mix lenses appear on factory-internal photographs of the Elmarit 2.8/90 (I) and Telyt 4.5/200 prototypes. These lenses have been authenticated by Lars Netopil. Summicron-M2/50mm(#1885111) comes with keeper and front cap, in mint condition. Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm(#3003249) comes with keeper, in mint condition.', '兩支鏡頭都是徠茲工廠的內部使用鏡，鏡身分別由黑色及銀色組成，當中具體目的及用途暫時仍未清楚。在1962年Wilhelm Albert出版的書中亦有介紹過兩款此類鏡頭：第一代Elmarit 2.8/90mm及Telyt 4.5/200mm的原型鏡是由工廠內部拍攝的相片。兩支鏡頭都已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\nSummicron-M 2/50mm(#1885111) 配有膠盅及鏡頭前蓋，品相極佳。<br />\r\nElmarit-M 2.8/90mm(#3003249) 配有膠盅, 兩支鏡頭品相極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2834', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_162_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_162_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_162_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_162_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_162_5.jpg', '162', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Germany in 1958, with cleansing marks on the glass, both caps, in good working condition.', '德國製的Summicron-M 2/50mm黑漆版鏡頭，產於1958年，為Rigid版本，鏡身分別用上黃銅及鎂合金兩種物料所造，鏡頭後卡口為黃銅，十分稀有。玻璃有清潔痕跡，調焦暢順，連鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2835', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_163_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_163_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_163_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_163_4.jpg', '163', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'This lens is second version Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Black Paint, comes with keeper, in mint condition.', '此鏡為第二代Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid的黑漆版，連膠盅。玻璃通透，調焦暢順，成色極佳。當年此款鏡頭主要只生產銀色，在市面上能找到如此成色的鏡頭實在難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2836', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_164_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_164_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_164_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_164_4.jpg', '164', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both caps, keeper and box, in mint condition.', '此鏡頭產於1963年，操作功能正常。有前後蓋、膠盅及鏡頭盒，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2837', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_165_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_165_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_165_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_165_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_165_5.jpg', '165', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This lens completes with lens rear cap and filter, with normal used marks and clear glass.', 'Summicron Rigid 2/50mm後的另一個版本，調焦環依然採用Rigid版本，但已取消撥杆。此形狀的鏡頭生產年期極短，現在市面十分罕見。鏡身有輕微使用痕跡，玻璃通透。連鏡頭後蓋及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2838', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome Prototype', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_166_7.jpg', '166', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'This Leitz Wetzlar Summicron-M 2/50mm lens with number 0000011 is a genuine and all original factory prototype. 14 lenses of Summicron 50mm prototypes were made with number 0000009 to 0000022 between July 1954 and April 1955. The lens #0000011 was completed on 30thAugust 1954.  This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡是Summicron-M 2/50mm DR的原型鏡，鏡身編號為0000011。由1954年7月至1955年4月，此款鏡頭徠卡只生產了14支。鏡身編號由0000009至0000022，此鏡頭則在1954年8月30日製造。<br />\r\n此原型鏡的鏡身多處地方均與後期版本有所不同。首先，其光圈環位置較長，與早期Rigid版本相似。其次，此鏡調焦環上的數字與眾多版本不一，而且調焦尺上只有“米”為單位，沒有“尺”。此鏡所配備的眼鏡同樣是原型版，取景鏡片較薄，甚為罕有及特別。<br />\r\n此鏡成色極佳，配鏡頭前蓋及罕有的透明後蓋，已經過Lars Netopil 鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2839', 'Summicron M 2/5cm DR Chrome', 'Summicron M 2/5cm DR Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_167_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_167_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_167_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_167_4.jpg', '167', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Rigid bayonet mount with near-focusing range, comes with goggles leather case, in mint condition.', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm帶微距功能，附有近攝用眼鏡。連同皮筒，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2840', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_168_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_168_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_168_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_168_4.jpg', '168', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'Second version Summicron-M 2/50mm lens with guarantee card, box, goggles and both caps, with some signs of use on barrel, hairline scratches and haze in the glass.', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm DR 鏡頭連眼鏡、保證卡、包裝盒、鏡頭前後蓋。鏡身有使用痕跡，玻璃內亦有輕微劃痕及有霧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2841', 'Elmar-M 2.8/50mm Chrome', 'Elmar-M 2.8/50mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_169_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_169_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_169_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_169_4.jpg', '169', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with box, keeper and front lens cap, with some fungus in glass.', '此鏡連包裝盒、鏡頭前蓋及膠盅。玻璃內有霉。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2842', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm 50 Jahre Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_170_6.jpg', '170', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 50thAnniversary of Summicron, this lens was launched and only 500 units were made, very rare. This set comes with box, all papers, leather case, presentation box, hood (#12585), hood cap and rear lens cap, in like new condition.', '此鏡頭是為了紀念Summicron面世50週年而生產的紀念版，限量500套，十分稀有。其外型為50年代第二代的Summicron Rigid鏡頭，但內裡的玻璃則採用現代Summicron鏡頭的光學設計與技術結合而成，極為獨特。此鏡頭配有包裝盒、證書、皮筒、內盒、遮光罩(#12585)、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2843', 'Elmar-M 3.5/65mm Black', 'Elmar-M 3.5/65mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_171_6.jpg', '171', '', '10,030', null, null, null, null, 'This lens has clear glass, it completes with box, both caps, focusing mount (#16464K), certificate, in mint condition.', '鏡頭外觀品相極佳，玻璃通透，連包裝盒、鏡頭前後蓋、對焦環 (#16464K)及證書，較為稀有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2844', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_172_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_172_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_172_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_172_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_172_5.jpg', '172', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Canada, comes with box, both lens caps, in mint condition.', '加拿大生產的Summilux-M 1.4/75mm人像王鏡頭。配有包裝盒及鏡頭前後蓋，外觀新淨，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2845', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_173_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_173_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_173_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_173_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_173_5.jpg', '173', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'The first version Midland SOOZI, comes with hood and rear cap, with normal used marks and clear glass.', '第一代Midland SOOZI鏡頭，連遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。鏡身有正常使用痕跡，但玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2846', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_174_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_174_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_174_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_174_4.jpg', '174', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Midland, Canada, comes with box, hood and both caps, in mint condition.', '鏡頭於加拿大Midland生產，配有包裝盒、遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。品相極佳，玻璃潔淨，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2847', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_175_6.jpg', '175', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Early black painted lens with brass mount, normal used marks, clear glass. Comes with both caps.', '少見的黑色鏡頭，加拿大產。鏡身分別以黃銅及鎂合金製造。鏡身有使用痕跡，玻璃通透，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2848', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_176_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_176_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_176_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_176_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_176_5.jpg', '176', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'The 3rd version Summicron-M 2/90mm lens, launched in 1993. It comes with both caps, with normal signs of use and clean glass.', '第三代Summicron-M 2/90mm鏡頭，於1993年推出銀色版本，鏡身編號由3643276開始。此鏡頭連前後蓋，鏡身有輕微使用痕跡，玻璃通透。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2849', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black Prototype', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_177_7.jpg', '177', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Canada rare pre-series version of the APO-Summicron-M 2/90 ASPH. &quot;Designed by Leica Camera, Manufactured in Canada&quot; engraved on the lens and with no serial number, very rare. It comes with both caps, in like new condition. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此鏡頭應為Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH的Pre-series版。在正式投產時，此款鏡頭全部在德國生產。但此鏡頭是屬於少部分由加拿大製造的Pre-Series鏡頭，鏡頭上沒有任何鏡身編號，鏡身上刻有 “Designed by Leica Camera, Manufactured in Canada&quot;，極為罕見。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋，成色如新，極為珍貴。此鏡經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2850', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_178_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_178_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_178_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_178_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_178_5.jpg', '178', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'The lens is clear, with both caps, in mint condition.', '同時擁有消色差(APO)及非球面玻璃的中長焦鏡頭，玻璃清澈，外觀如新，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2851', 'Elmar-M 4/135mm Black Pre-Series', 'Elmar-M 4/135mm Black Pre-Series', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_179_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_179_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_179_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_179_4.jpg', '179', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'The serial number of this lens starts from 2007700 and “Elmar” instead of “Tel-Elmar” engraved on the lens. This is taken as the pre-series, in good working order and mint condition. (Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.212 for further illustrations).', 'Tele-Elmar-M 4/135mm的鏡頭序號是由2007700開始，此鏡頭編號略早，加上鏡頭前端刻有 “Elmar” 字樣，而非正式生產刻上的 “Tel-Elmar” 字樣，光圈環及鏡身也略有不同。故此鏡頭可能是試驗品或Pre-Series。以上部分特徵均與Tele-Elmar-M 4/135mm鏡頭不一樣。此鏡成色極佳，調焦暢順，絕對是收藏家追求的珍品。(請參閱James Lager Vol.II p.212)', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2852', 'Visoflex III Set Black', 'Visoflex III Set Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_180_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_180_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_180_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_180_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_180_5.jpg', '180', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'This Visoflex III set completes with Leica 5.6/400mm (#2307767), Leica Telyt-M 5.6/560mm (#2228203), adapter (#14137), Televit-R rapid focusing mount (#14136), viewfinder and Televit-R shoulder support, with normal used marks, in good working order.', 'Visoflex III 套機連Leica Telyt-M 5.6/400mm (#2307767)，Leica Telyt-M 5.6/560mm (#2228203)，轉接環 (#14137)，Televit-R 快速對焦環 (#14136)，取景器及Televit-R肩膊支撐架，可用於M系列相機上。有正常使用痕跡，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2853', 'Hektor 4.5/13.5cm HEFAR “W.H.” lllck Grey', 'Hektor 4.5/13.5cm HEFAR “W.H.” lllck Grey', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_181_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_181_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_181_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_181_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_181_5.jpg', '181', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare Leitz Wetzlar and all original gray HEFAR 13.5cm lens No. 558827 from WWII in very nice condition. Shipped to Berlin on September 20th 1944 with shipment number #13096. Matching to &quot;Rundbildkamera&quot; outfit &quot;E2&quot; in combination with gray Leica lllck &quot;W.H.&quot;. (Please refer to James Lager Vol. II p.102 &amp; Vol. III p.182 for further illustrations). This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '原裝徠卡Hektor 4.5/13.5cm灰漆鏡頭是在二戰期間提供給德國國防軍，配lllck: W.H.用的鏡頭，此鏡頭是在1944年9月20日運送到柏林，貨運編號為13096， 鏡身塗以德國國防軍用灰色，產量極少。(請參閱James Lager Vol.II p.102&amp; Vol.III p.182關於此鏡介紹) 此鏡頭已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2854', 'IIIc Convert to IIIf Chrome', 'IIIc Convert to IIIf Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_182_7.jpg', '182', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIc wartime in chrome finish, No. 369315. Camera original delivered as &quot;Luftw.&quot;-Leica, shipped to Luftwaffe Berlin on January 16th 1941 with shipment number 19787. After World War II, Leitz provided the upgrade service to customers. For this camera, a new top plate was used after the war to very elegantly civilize the camera, a step for shutter speed dial, &quot;f&quot;-type flash synchronization added later. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. This camera comes with Elmar 2.8/5cm lens (#1626547) and front lens cap in mint condition.', '此機為戰時的IIIc銀色機身，編號為369315。此機原本於1941年1月16日以“軍用”名稱運送至德國柏林Luftwaffe（空軍），運送編號為19787。在二戰後徠茲公司提供新的升級服務，讓客人把原有的相機更新至新款相機，此台相機正是由二戰時的IIIc升級為IIIf的功能，機頂用於民用相機頂蓋，並加上F型號的閃光燈介面。整套相機除了揉合IIIc及IIIf的設計外，亦結合了戰時及戰後的產品，見證了時代的進步及徠卡的演變過程。此機經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n此相機配有Elmar 2.8/5cm (#1626547)，鏡頭蓋，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2855', 'IIIc Heer', 'IIIc Heer', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_183_7.jpg', '183', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'Rare Leica IIIc from WWII, with original &quot;Heer&quot; engraving on top plate, No. 369824. 20 pieces were shipped to Berlin on February 10th 1941 with shipment number 19995. 19995 is one of the shipments which has turned out to contain originally &quot;Heer&quot; engraved items. The camera in very nice and original chrome condition, with a later body-cover, red curtain. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '罕有的IIIC二次世界大戰軍用機，機頂上刻有 “HEER” 軍隊字樣，編號為369824。1941年2月10日運送了二十台IIIc Heer到柏林，運送編號為19995。此機為原裝銀色機身帶紅色布廉。成色極佳，配印有 “Heer” 字的皮套及非原裝的機身蓋，此機經Lars Netopil鑑定為真品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2856', 'IIIf Black Paint “Swedish Military”', 'IIIf Black Paint “Swedish Military”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_184_7.jpg', '184', '', '1,180,000', null, null, null, null, 'This IIIf was specially made for the Swedish national army in 1956. It can withstand very extreme weather conditions in Sweden and only 100 units were produced, numbered 822901-823000. The camera and lens are original, complete with matching black paint Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1427190) and early A36 Black Paint lens cap (Please refer to James Lager Vol.I p.98), in like new condition, very rare. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '1950年IIIf正式面世，全球其中一支歷史最悠久的常備軍「瑞典國軍」(Swedish Army)，在1956年特別向德國徠卡下訂單，訂造100台IIIf予軍隊使用。能夠在嚴冬環境使用的IIIf黑漆版， 生產批號由822901- 823000，遺留至今仍然保存如此完美成色的，相信不多於20台。<br />\r\n此機身及鏡頭均為原裝，連Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1427190)及早期黑漆A36鏡頭蓋(可參閱James Lager Vol.I p.98)，成色極新，為不可多得之珍品。此機已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2857', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M3 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_185_8.jpg', '185', '', '708,000', null, null, null, null, 'Bundeseigentum refers to &quot;Property of Federal German Government&quot; in English. In the record, this model was produced in 1957-1968 with batch No.1100401-1100450. Since only 50 units were produced, it becomes extremely rare. The rear of top plate engraved &quot;Bundeseigentum&quot;, it comes with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm Chrome (#1727638) engraved &quot;Bundeseigentum 12-121-5971&quot;, with goggles and olive leather lens case. ITOOY hood (engraved &quot;Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529&quot;) for Summaron-M 2.8/35mm Chrome (#2050525) engraved &quot;6760-12-130-0901&quot;; Tele-Elmar-M 4/135mm in Black (#2046215) engraved &quot;6760-12-140-9090&quot;, it comes with olive ever-ready leather case and light meter engraved &quot;Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608&quot;. This camera set comes with filter, hood (12575N) and green leather case. Extremely rare.', 'Bundeseigentum英文是指 “Property of Federal German Government”，中文是指“聯邦資產”。根據記錄，此款相機在1957年至1968年間生產，該批次的產量更只有50台，序號由1100401至1100450止，數量十分稀少。<br />\r\n此套機機身後背刻有Bundeseigentum字樣，連同銀色Elmar-M 2.8/50mm (#1727638)：刻有 “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5971” 的字樣，銀色Summaron-M 2.8/35mm (#2050525)：刻有 “6760-12-130-0901” 的字樣，黑色Tele-Elmar-M 4/135mm (#2046215)：刻有 “6760-12-140-9090” 的字樣，並連同皮套及測光錶，測光錶上更刻有 “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5608”。除此以外，此套機更配有黃色濾鏡、ITOOY遮光罩 (遮光罩上刻有 “Bundeseigentum 12-121-5529” )、12575N遮光罩及遮光罩蓋。Tele-Elmar-M 4/135mm鏡頭則連同鏡頭後蓋、遮光罩及遮光罩蓋；而Summaron-M 2.8/35mm鏡頭眼鏡版則備有眼鏡及綠色皮套。經過年月的流逝及戰火的洗禮，如此配件齊全及成色優良的軍用套機在市面上已是難得一見，實為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2858', 'M2 Chrome KS15-4', 'M2 Chrome KS15-4', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_186_6.jpg', '186', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Only 875 units of M2 Chrome KS15-4 were produced for the U.S. Military during Vietnam War and later M2-R was developed and launched in the market. The serial number starts from 1163150 - 1163770 and 1164046 - 1164300. It comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '此機在越南戰爭時供應予美軍使用，只生產875台，後來更演變為M2-R 推出市場。其機身編號由1163150 - 1163770 及1164046 - 1164300 止。此機配有機身蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2859', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_187_7.jpg', '187', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'M2 Chrome engraved with “KS15-4B 6720-163-4875 US” and “FSN 4875”, comes with body cap, in mint condition.', '銀色M2，機背刻有 “KS15-4B 6720-163-4875 US”，機底刻有“FSN 4875”字樣，配有機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2860', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M1 Olive Bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_188_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_188_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_188_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_188_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_188_5.jpg', '188', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M1 for Bundeseigentum Military, engraved “Bundeseigentum” on the back of top plate. It comes with an Elmar 2.8/50mm (#1934734) also engraved “Bundeseigentum” on barrel. A total of 208 units were made and which only 82 sets made in this batch (1098101 - 1098183) and this camera is the second last piece. It comes with front lens cap, in mint condition.', '西德軍用相機，機背上刻有“Bundeseigentum”字樣，<br />\r\n此機配搭銀色Elmar-M 2.8/50mm鏡頭 (#1934734)，<br />\r\n鏡身上同樣刻有 “Bundeseigentum” 字樣。<br />\r\n此機產於1964年，本批次共生產82台，序號為1098101 – 1098183，<br />\r\nM1 Olive僅生產208台，此機是最後第二台，十分珍貴。<br />\r\n此套機連鏡頭前蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2861', 'KE-7A “U.S. Army”', 'KE-7A “U.S. Army”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_189_6.jpg', '189', '', '145,200', null, null, null, null, 'Leica KE-7A produced in 1972, only 505 units were made and 460 units for U.S. Military. Its durability is much higher than other M Cameras. The Military no. “FSN 6720-165-7115” and contract no. &quot;CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US&quot; engraved at the back of the camera. It comes with “Elcan-M 2/50mm, specially made for the U.S. Military with ultra-high resolution, comes with hood engraved “C42-LS.39F” and hood cap. This set comes with leather case, manual, extremely rare.', '徠卡的KE-7A產於1972年，產量只有505部，而屬於美國軍用版本的有460部。由於供軍方使用，所以其耐用度遠高於其他M型機。此機為軍用版本。機背上分別刻有軍用編號及合約編號，號碼分別為 “FSN 6720-165-7115”及 “CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US”。此套機配以Elcan-M 2/50mm，此鏡是徠卡為美軍特製的，只有4枚鏡片達至超高解像度，配有遮光罩，其刻上 “C42-LS.39F” 字樣及遮光罩蓋。套機連原裝皮套及操作說明書，如此配件齊備的KE-7A，實屬極之罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2862', 'KE-7A “U.S. Army”', 'KE-7A “U.S. Army”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_190_7.jpg', '190', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'A total of 505 units of Leica KE-7A were produced and in which about 460 units were assigned to the U.S. Military while the rest were civilian version. The Military version engraved with serial no, Military force no and contract no. While the civilian version only engraved with serial no. For this camera, &quot;FSN 6720-165-7115&quot; and &quot;CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US&quot; were engraved on the rear of the top plate. This camera completely comes with Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0293), hood, hood cap, filter, manual, matching serial number leather case and packing in brand new condition.', 'KE-7A總產量為505部，其中約460部是屬於美國軍方的採購合約外，其餘的則是民用版本。軍用版除刻有機身序號外，還包括軍用編號與合約編號，民用版本則只刻有機身序號。而此套機的機背上分別刻有軍用編號及合約編號，號碼分別是: “FSN 6720-165-7115”及“CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US”。此套機連同Elcan-M 2/50mm (#276-0293)，配有遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、濾鏡、合約及與相機相同號碼的相機皮套。此套機產量稀少，民用版本已是一機難求，成色極佳的軍用版本更是寥寥無幾，所以此套機可說是收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2863', 'R3 Safari outfit', 'R3 Safari outfit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_191_8.jpg', '191', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 1977-78, Leica produced 5000 units of R3 Safari outfit with several basic assorted lenses and khaki-finished Trinovid binoculars for the set. This set includes R3 camera (#1484093) with box, certificate, guarantee card, instruction, body cap and strap; Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2876089) comes with box, guarantee card, hood and both caps; Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2878649) comes with box, certificate and both caps; Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2882393) comes with box, guarantee card, both caps and Trinovid 10x22C binocular (#941519) comes with box, instruction and strap.', '在1977-78年，徠卡共生產了5000台R3軍綠色版本，配有軍綠色的鏡頭及軍綠色望遠鏡。此套機機身號碼為1484093，連包裝盒、證書、保證卡、說明書、機身蓋及相機帶。另外，此套機同時配有以下鏡頭及望遠鏡: 首先是Elmarit-R 2.8/28mm (#2876089)，連包裝、保證書、遮光罩 (#12509)及前後蓋; 其次是Summicron-R 2/50mm (#2878649)連包裝、證書及前後蓋; 另外Elmar-R 4/180mm (#2882393)則配有包裝、保證卡及鏡頭前後蓋。最後Trinovid 10x22C望遠鏡 (#941519)備有包裝、說明書及頸帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2864', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_192_6.jpg', '192', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'In the early 1970s, Leitz of Midland Canada has specially produced 54 units of Elcan-R 3.4/180mm for the US Military during the Vietnam War. This lens has not been officially launched. The serial number of this lens is 303-0058, comes with both caps, in like new condition, extremely rare.', '此款鏡頭是徠茲加拿大工廠 (Leitz of Midland Canada)為美軍於1970年的越戰所生產的長焦鏡。此款鏡頭共生產五十多支，第一批供美軍使用20支，第二批20支，其餘於第三批交付，鏡身上有303-0058字樣。此款鏡頭從未對外公佈，相信後期的R 3.4/180mm APO-TELYT均以此鏡為藍本生產，故也稱為R 3.4/180mm APO-TELY Prototype。經過戰火洗禮，現存量十分稀少，成色極佳，連前後蓋，極為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2865', 'M4 50 Years Black', 'M4 50 Years Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_193_6.jpg', '193', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'This M4 50 Jahre version was made in Germany, special numbered 235-E. It comes with box, certificate and body cap, with normal used marks.', '此機為徠卡M4 50週年版，產於德國，特別號碼為235-E，連包裝盒、證書及機身蓋，有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2866', 'M4-P 70 Years Chrome Outfit', 'M4-P 70 Years Chrome Outfit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_194_7.jpg', '194', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 70th year of the first 135mm camera produced in 1913, M4-P70 was launched.“Leica 1913-1983”engraved on the top plate and barrel. The commemorative number of this camera is E588. It comes with Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm (#3200946), Summicron-M 2/50mm (#3261950), meter (#81400) and winder (#10810), also with box, certificate, camera strap, body cap, lens caps. For Summicron-M 2/50mm lens, it comes with hood and hood cap, both in like new condition.', '此套機是為慶祝1913年第一台135相機面世70週年而生產，紀念號為E588，相機機頂及鏡身刻有 “Leica 1913-1983” 字樣，成色像新。連Tele-Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm (#3200946)、Summicron-M 2/50mm (#3261950)、測光錶 (#81400)及快速過片器 (#10810)，配有機身蓋、鏡頭蓋、相機帶及包裝證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2867', 'Leica M6 50 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Fotografie with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', 'Leica M6 50 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Fotografie with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_195_7.jpg', '195', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'In 1989, Leica 50 Jahre Photographie, 75 Jahre Fotografie was launched to commemorate the 150th years of photography and 75th years of Leica, only 250 units were made. The camera body decorated with snake leather and platinum-plated. This set is numbered A051. It comes with platinum Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3481948) and completes with box, certificate, papers, hood, hood cap, body cap, wooden box, batteries, rear cap and strap, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝底片發明150年及徠卡成立75週年，在1989年，徠卡特意推出250台底片發明150週年紀念機。機身覆以鉑金及蛇皮，特顯尊貴。同時配有鉑金版的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#3481948)鏡頭。此套機的特別號為A051，連包裝、證書、機身蓋、遮光罩及遮光罩蓋、木盒、電池、相機帶及鏡頭後蓋，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2868', 'M6 Rooster with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M6 Rooster with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_196_8.jpg', '196', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M6 Rooster is the first commemorative camera made for Asian market in 1993. It was also the first time Chinese characters were engraved on the camera. Top plate engraved“徠卡吉祥” ,rear plate engraved “SPECIAL EDITION OF 300 PCS FOR SCHMIDT GROUP”, body decorated with ostrich leather. The commemorative number of this set is 85/300. It comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm (#085/300), hood, hood cap and wooden box.', '金雞吉祥紀念機是徠卡為華人地區特別製作的第一台紀念機，也是第一次在產品刻上中文。此套機於1993年推出，全球300套。機身飾以駝鳥飾皮，機頂刻有精美圖案與 “徠卡吉祥” 字樣，機背則刻有“SPECIAL EDITION OF 300 PCS FOR SCHMIDT GROUP”字樣，特別號碼為085/300。此機配有Summicron-M 2/50mm (#085/300) 鏡頭，連木盒、遮光罩及遮光罩蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2869', 'M6 with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Titanium Camera Set', 'M6 with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Titanium Camera Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_197_7.jpg', '197', '', '885,000', null, null, null, null, 'A round numbers of M6 Titanium (#1900000) with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Titanium lens(#3600000) have never been seen among the special Edition cameras. These special editions are usually commemorative sets made for special clients. For example, Leica IIIf (#500000) dedicated to Ernst Leitz II; M3 (#700000) was produced one year after M3 (#700001) and dedicated to Austrian Prof. Stefan Krukenhauser in 1955; M3 (#800000) dedicated to the World War II West German Chancellor, Konrad Adenauer in 1956. In addition, these round numbers were assigned to particular camera models as well. For example, (#3000000) was assigned to M7 Titanium Camera set to celebrate the 50th Anniversary of the Leica M series. This set comes with wooden box, titanium hood, front cap, camera body decorated with lizard skin leather, in brand new condition.', '一套完整號碼的鈦版M6 (#1900000)連Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鈦金屬鏡頭 (#3600000)套機在特別版紀念機中從未有過如此搭配，工廠通常會將這類完整號碼留起來送給特別的客人。如徠卡IIIf (#500000)送予Ernst Leitz II ; M3 (#700000)是在M3 (#700001)生產後的一年，於1955年生產送予奧地利的Prof. Stefan Krukenhauser。而M3 (#800000)是於1956年送予二戰時期的西德總理康拉德•阿丹拿 (Chancellor Konrad Adenauer)。另外，這類完整號碼亦會分配給特別相機型號用，如#3000000 號則分配給慶祝徠卡M系列50週年推出的M7鈦版一機三鏡的第一部號碼用，足見珍貴。此機鏡連木盒、鈦遮光罩、鏡頭前蓋，機身更飾以蜥蝪皮，貴氣十足。此套機全新未經使用，為收藏的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2870', 'M6 Gold Sambutan Jubli Perak', 'M6 Gold Sambutan Jubli Perak', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_198_7.jpg', '198', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 25th Anniversary of accession to the throne of Sultan of Brunei on 1st October 1992, the royal family ordered 350 sets of gold plated Leica M6 Sambutan Jubli Perak. The national totem of Sultan engraved on the top plate and “Sambuton Jubli Perak” engraved at the back. The camera is decorated with black leather embossed ornamentation. The camera comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in gold (#3653690), engraved &quot;Sambuton Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92&quot;. The commemorative number is HB-230. This set comes with packing, wooden box, hood and hood cap, body cap, lens rear cap, cleansing cloth, strap, in brand new condition.', '1992年10月1日，汶萊蘇丹登基25週年，汶萊皇室為此向徠卡訂製了350台M6套機作為紀念。此套機是以M6為基礎，鍍上24K黃金，機頂上刻有汶萊的國徵，機背後亦有 “Sambuton Jubli Perak” 字樣。機身配有黑色壓花紋飾皮，盡顯高貴。此套機連一支金色的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#3653690)，鏡頭前刻有 “Sambuton Jubli Perak 5 Oct 92” 的字樣，特別號碼為HB-230。此套機連包裝、精美木盒、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、機身蓋、鏡頭後蓋、相機抹布及相機帶，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2871', 'M6 Gold Dragon', 'M6 Gold Dragon', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_199_6.jpg', '199', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'M6 Gold Dragon Edition comes with a matching Summicron-M 2/50mm, only 300 units were made, the commemorate number is 238/300, lens number is 3700238, with full packing, in brand new condition.', '此機連Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭，限量300台。此套的紀念號碼為238/300，鏡頭編號為3700238，包裝證書齊全，全新未經使用，極有收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2872', 'M6 Royal Wedding with Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome', 'M6 Royal Wedding with Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_200_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_200_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_200_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_200_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_200_5.jpg', '200', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Leica has specially launched 200 units of commemorative M6 cameras in 1995 to celebrate the wedding of Prince Joachim of Denmark. The royal crest, wedding date“18.11.1995”and serial number 020/200 engraved on the top plate. It comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm chrome lens (#3640821), box and wooden presentation box, in like new condition.', '此為丹麥王子大婚而特別推出的200台紀念套機。機頂上除刻有 “18.11.1995” 的大婚日期及丹麥皇室的標誌外，更刻有020/200的紀念號。機身覆以駝鳥皮，彰顯尊貴。此機配有Summicron-M 2/35mm鏡頭 (#3640821)，連包裝及木盒，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2873', 'M6 “LHSA 25th Anniversary” Camera Set', 'M6 “LHSA 25th Anniversary” Camera Set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_201_8.jpg', '201', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 25th Anniversary of American Leica Historical Society (LHSA), Leica launched the LHSA 25th Anniversary camera set in 1996, it comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome, Summicron-M 2/50mm and Summicron-M 2/90mm. Only 151 units were produced. The top plate engraved the logo of &quot;LHSA&quot; and &quot;1968-1993&quot;, while the rear of the top plate engraved &quot;Special Edition of 151 Cameras for LHSA 25th Anniversary&quot;. Also, the body is decorated with ostrich leather. This camera set was available to LHSA members only, extremely valuable. The commemorative number of this camera set is 25-108 and the front ring of the lens engraved “LHSA 25th ANNIVERSARY 25-108”. It comes with wooden box, carton box, body cap, front and rear lens caps, in brand new condition.', '1996年，為了紀念美國徠卡歷史協會(LHSA)成立25周年，徠卡發行了151套LHSA 25周年紀念套機，連銀色Summicron-M 2/35mm、Summicron-M 2/50mm及Summicron-M 2/90mm，一機三鏡。機身和鏡頭都是銀色。機頂刻有 “LHSA” 標誌及 “1968-1993” 字樣，而機背則刻有 “Special Edition of 151 Cameras for LHSA 25th Anniversary” 字樣，機身更飾以駝鳥皮。此套機當時僅向會員發售，並無在市場公開出售，因而特別珍貴。<br />\r\n此機紀念號為25-108，而鏡頭亦刻有 “LHSA 25th ANNIVERSARY 25-108” 字樣。此機配有木盒、紙盒，機身蓋及三支鏡頭的前後蓋，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2874', 'M6 “Ausrustung Benelux” Chrome', 'M6 “Ausrustung Benelux” Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_202_8.jpg', '202', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'In 1996, 70 units of M6 engraved “Leica DEMO Ausrustung Benelux 96” were made, with an engraved map of Benelux region of Europe, which covers portions of the Netherlands, Belgium, and Luxembourg. It comes with box, body cap, strap and papers in mint condition.', '1996年，徠卡推出了70台M6銀色相機，機頂上刻有 “Leica Demo Ausrustung Benelux 96” 字樣，同時機頂上有荷蘭、比利時及盧森堡的地圖及歐盟旗幟，以紀念“比荷盧經濟聯盟”。此機配有包裝證書、機身蓋及相機帶，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2875', 'M6 Platinum 150 Jahre Optik with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M6 Platinum 150 Jahre Optik with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_203_7.jpg', '203', '', '519,200', null, null, null, null, 'Only 150 sets produced , this camera commemorative number is 1856. Comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (150 Jahre Optik 1905). Complete with all packing, wooden box, box, Leica cleansing cloth, lens rear cap, body cap, commemorative coin and certificate.', '1999 年為紀念徠卡光學技術發明 150 週年 (1850~1999)，特別推出150套極其罕有的M6光學紀念鉑金機。每部相機均刻有不同年份，分別配以五款不同鏡頭，每款鏡頭套機僅生產30套，比M7鈦金版一機三鏡的數量還少。此機的紀念年份是1905配Summicron-M 2/50mm鏡頭 (150 Jahre Optik 1905)，機身用蜥蜴皮包覆。全新包裝，精美木盒、包裝紙盒、Leica鏡頭布、紀念幣(銀色)、鏡頭後蓋、機身蓋、紀念證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2876', 'M6 TTL 0.85 \'Dragon 2000\' Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', 'M6 TTL 0.85 \'Dragon 2000\' Black Paint with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_204_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_204_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_204_6.jpg', '204', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the Chinese Dragon year, 500 units of M6 TTL0.85 “Dragon 2000” were made. The back of the camera engraved “龍2000” . This camera set is numbered 83/500. It comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH (#4000083), box, papers, strap, body cap, lens hood and both caps, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝千禧年正值中國傳統龍年而發行的M6 0.85龍年套機，黑漆機身背面刻有 “龍2000” 字樣，限量500台。此機紀念號為83/500，連Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH鏡頭(#4000083)，配以機身蓋、遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋、包裝證書及相機帶，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2877', 'M6 TTL 0.72 “Millennium Edition” Black Paint', 'M6 TTL 0.72 “Millennium Edition” Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_205_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_205_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_205_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_205_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_205_5.jpg', '205', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Millennium Edition M6 Black Paint, 2000 sets were produced. It comes with packing, papers and body cap, in brand new condition.', '此台黑漆版M6為千禧紀念套機，紀念號碼為781/2000，限量推出2000台。配有包裝、說明書及機身蓋，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2878', 'M6 TTL 0.85 LHSA Black Paint', 'M6 TTL 0.85 LHSA Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_206_8.jpg', '206', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'In 2000, 1000 units of Leica M6 0.85 Black Paint were produced. The Leica logo in black is used instead of the red one. Without M6 engraved marks found on camera body, it comes with box, all papers, strap and body cap, in brand new condition.', '此機生產年份為2000年，限量1000台。機身採用黑色烤漆，以黑色徠卡商標取代了原有的紅色徠卡商標設計，機身上亦沒有M6字樣，連包裝證書、機身蓋及相機帶，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2879', 'M6 0.85 TTL Safari Consecutive Numbers', 'M6 0.85 TTL Safari Consecutive Numbers', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_207_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_207_2.jpg', '207', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'Leica has launched 300 units of M6 0.85 TTL Safari in 2000. The camera body was painted with military green, same as the decorated leather. The consecutive numbers of the set make it exceptionally valuable and rare. It comes with packing and all accessories, in brand new condition.', '徠卡於2000年限量推出300台M6 0.85 TTL軍綠色版本，機身用上軍隊專用的綠色面漆，配以同色系之飾皮，更顯其獨特性，此對機的紀念號碼分別為246-300及247-300。時至今日，徠卡Safari一直都是徠卡收藏者追捧之物，能於300台限量生產的號碼中可找到相連號碼的絕無僅有。此套機全新未經使用，包裝配件全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2880', 'MP Anthracite Kit', 'MP Anthracite Kit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_208_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_208_2.jpg', '208', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 50th Anniversary of the M Series, Leica MP Anthracite was made especially for the Japanese market in 2001, only 600 units were made. This camera is numbered 444/600, it comes with Leicavit, full packing, in brand new condition.', '為紀念徠卡M系列生產50週年，徠卡於2001年為日本市場特別推出MP Anthracite套機，連Leicavit紀念套裝，共有600套。此機的特別號碼為444/600，連包裝證書，配件齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2881', 'M7 0.72 Black', 'M7 0.72 Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_209_7.jpg', '209', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'M7 Black Paint with 0.72 frame line, engraved “Test the best” and the map on top plate, specially made for Switzerland. It comes with box, all papers, strap and body cap in mint condition.', '黑漆機身配以0.72線框，性能良好。機頂上刻有 “Test the Best” 字樣及地圖，是徠卡特別為瑞士而製。配有包裝證書、相機帶及機身蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2882', 'M7 &quot;Handmade titanium camera&quot; Prototype', 'M7 &quot;Handmade titanium camera&quot; Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_210_8.jpg', '210', '', '2,124,000', null, null, null, null, 'Original factory prototype from the project &quot;handmade titanium camera&quot;, which was made as a one of a kind model for Sheikh Saud Al-Thani of Qatar in the year of 2002. While the outer parts of the final version of this camera were in all-titanium, including the body cover (refer to LFI magazine No.06/2003), the unit here has a black leather body cover, some black knobs and levers, which let it look a bit like a &quot;Titanium Panda&quot; version. The set finally delivered contained five different lenses, all with solid titanium mounts. The camera here comes complete with a later solid titanium mount version of the Summilux-M 1.4/50 ASPH of 2004 (from &quot;50 years of Leica M edition&quot;). This camera and lens have been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '2002年卡塔爾皇室成員Sheikh Saud Al-Thani向徠卡訂製了一套獨一無二的全鈦版M7連5支全鈦版鏡頭，機頂上刻有Sheikh Saud Al-Thani的簽名，這個項目稱為 “Handmade titanium camera”。 Sheikh Saud Al-Thani不但是卡塔爾皇室成員，也是卡塔爾國家文化藝術遺產協會的主席，他熱愛藝術及攝影，也收藏了很多徠卡產品。此套相機的設計及生產比徠卡在2004年推出的 “M系列50周年M7 鈦版一機三鏡紀念機” 還早兩年 (請參考徠卡6/2003 的LFI介紹)。<br />\r\n在此次拍賣會中的這部M7是 “Handmade titanium camera” 的 Prototype (原型機)，與正式交給Sheikh Saud Al-Thani的M7鈦版略有不同，此台原型機機頂上刻有Sheikh Saud Al-Thani的親筆簽名。回片鈕、過片杆及快門轉盤均以黑色材料所造，有如是 “鈦版熊貓機” 一樣，機身飾以黑色真皮，機背與正式版本一樣，覆以鈦金屬，甚為特別。此套機能在本屆拍賣會上出現，堪稱奇蹟。此套機已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。<br />\r\n連此機身所配的鏡頭是後期2004年推出徠卡50週年版中的Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭 (#3985299)，連鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2883', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_211_7.jpg', '211', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 35th Anniversary of LHSA, MP LHSA was launched with Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH and Leicavit. This lens is numbered 3963203, with Leicavit (#00517) and a special Hammertone lens hood, only 1000 units were made. This set comes with big presentation box, in brand new condition.', '為紀念美國徠卡歷史協會成立35週年所發行的MP連Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH及Leicavit。鏡頭是仿八枚玉造型。此套機鏡頭編號為3963203，並配有Leicavit (#00517)及特別的Hammertone遮光罩。限量生產1000台。此套機以一個大禮盒包裝，較罕見。此套機包裝配件齊全，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2884', 'M7 Titanium &quot;50 Jahre&quot; with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', 'M7 Titanium &quot;50 Jahre&quot; with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_212_8.jpg', '212', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 50th Anniversary of M Series, M7 Titanium “50 Jahre” was launched with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#3982070), only 500 units were made. The top plate engraved “1954-2004 50 Jahre M-system” . The whole camera set was made in solid Titanium, comes with full packaging, certificate, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝徠卡M系列50週年而推出的M7鈦版連Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#3982070)。機頂刻有\"1954-2004 50 Jahre M-system\"字樣。整套機鏡以鈦金屬製造，全球限量500 套。此套機包裝證書及配件齊全，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2885', 'MP3 LHSA Special Edition with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Chrome', 'MP3 LHSA Special Edition with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_213_7.jpg', '213', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'In 2005, MP3 LHSA Special Edition was launched and only 375 sets in Chrome were made. This set comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens (#3990212) and Leicavit (#00100), all packings, papers, body cap, hood, hood cap, both caps, lens case, battery cover and camera strap, in brand new condition.', '發表於2005年，是徠卡與美國徠卡歷史協會共同推出類似MP的復刻版機種，當中銀色套機限量375套。此套機為銀色套裝組配有Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#3990212)及過片器 (#00100)，包裝證書及其他配件，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2886', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Black Paint', 'MP3 “LHSA Special Edition” Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_214_7.jpg', '214', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'In 2005, MP3 Black Paint LHSA Special Edition was launched, 1000 units were made. This set is numbered 947/1000. It comes with a black painted Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens (#3990474) and Leicavit (#00426), completes with all packing and papers, in brand new condition.', '發表於2005年，是徠卡為美國徠卡歷史協會推出的紀念機，限量1000台。此機紀念號碼為947/1000，配有Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH鏡頭 (#3990474)及過片器(#00426)。整套套機為黑漆，甚有徠卡古典味。套機包裝配件齊全，全新未經使', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2887', 'MP Classic with Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', 'MP Classic with Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_215_6.jpg', '215', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'MP classic was made following early MP design, only 500 units were made. The camera set is numbered 317. It comes with Summicron-M 2/50mm (#3983551), box, papers, body cap, hood, hood cap, both caps and strap, in brand new condition.', '此黑漆MP套機是徠卡特別仿照早期MP機而生產，機身不帶測光，限量500套。此套機紀念號碼為317，連Summicron-M 2/50mm黑漆鏡頭 (#3983551)，配有包裝證書、機身蓋、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及相機帶。全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2888', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_216_6.jpg', '216', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'Only 150 units of MP 0.72 Titanium were manufactured. Both camera body and body cap were casted with solid titanium. This set is numbered 79/150, comes with full packing and certificate.', '以純鈦製造的MP特別紀念機，全球限量150台，機身及機身蓋均以純鈦所造。此套機的特別號為79/150，包裝證書全齊。整套紀念機高貴經典，為收藏家追捧的焦點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2889', 'M3J Black Paint', 'M3J Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_217_8.jpg', '217', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'In order to celebrate the opening of first Leica Store in Ginza, Japan, 200 units of M3J were launched in 2006. The letter “J” stands for “Japan” . It has the classical design of M3, comes with body cap, in good working order and like new condition.', '徠卡以經典的M3相機為藍本，加以優化而推出的M3J黑漆相機，全球只生產200台。此機機身與經典M3一樣，相機背帶扣有著早期M3的設計，荔枝紋飾皮，極具收藏價值，是收藏家追棒的對象。連機身蓋，成色近全新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2890', 'M3-P “20 Jahre Leica Shop Vienna”', 'M3-P “20 Jahre Leica Shop Vienna”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_218_7.jpg', '218', '', '542,800', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 20th Anniversary of Leica Shop in Vienna, M3-P Special Edition was launched and only 20 units were made. Leica MP Silver chrome finish with vulcanite cladding and top cover in the typical Leica M3 style, “Classic Leica Script” engraved on the top plate. It comes with a Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH lens in silver anodized finish (#4120542). The commemorative number is 10/20. This set completes with all packing, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝維也納Leica Shop成立20週年紀念，推出限量20台M3-P紀念機。相機以MP為藍本，相機上蓋採用經典的M3設計，觀景窗使用M3經典的凸面邊框，並於機頂刻有<br />\r\n“Classic Leica Script” 字樣。此套機紀念號為10/20，搭配極為罕見的銀色Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm鏡頭 (#4120542)，全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2891', 'MP Edition 60 Years PRC with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Gold Plated', 'MP Edition 60 Years PRC with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Gold Plated', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_219_6.jpg', '219', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 60th Anniversary of People’s Republic of China, Leica produced 24 carat gold-plated MP with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH lens. Body covered with red calf skin, only 61 sets made, each bears a mark between 1949-2009, engraved “中華人民共和國萬歲” on the top plate. This commemorate number is 2001, completes with full packing, in brand new condition, extremely rare.', '為慶祝中華人民共和國建國60年，徠卡特別推出61套鍍金MP連Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH紀念機。鍍金機身搭配紅色飾皮，機頂刻有天安門圖案及 “中華人民共和國萬歲” 字樣，而且取景框的右上位置更印有 “中華人民共和國成立60週年1949 – 2009” 字樣。紀念機限量編號由1949至2009，每個年份只生產一套，此機限量編號為2001，鏡頭號碼是4073580。配有全新包裝，證書全齊，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2892', 'M9-P Edition Hermes with Three Lenses Kit (Misprinted Version)', 'M9-P Edition Hermes with Three Lenses Kit (Misprinted Version)', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_220_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_220_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_220_3.jpg', '220', '', '708,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M9-P Edition Hermes comes with Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH (#4161665), Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH (#4138358) and Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH lens (#4174623). Only 100 units were produced. The color of the aperture figures filled on Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH is different from the other two lenses. The commemorative number of this camera set is 89/100, completes with Hermes camera bag, strap, hood, full packing, in brand new condition.', 'M9-P愛瑪仕連Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH (#4161665)、Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH (#4138358)及Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH (#4174623)，一機三鏡的套裝全球只有100套。其中Summicron-M 2/90mm APO ASPH該鏡光圈上數字的顏色與其它兩支不同，它被塗上橙色而非其他鏡頭所採用的黑色。本套機的紀念號碼為89/100。連愛瑪仕相機背包、包裝證書，配件齊全，全新未經使用。此套機是德國相機的最高工藝與法國國寶級皮革品牌的完美結合，絕對是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2893', 'M8 Gold Colored Finish Prototype', 'M8 Gold Colored Finish Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_221_6.jpg', '221', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'Original factory prototype of a Leica M8 body in gold colored finish, Serial no. 3329318. Leicameter with coupling to Leica-M cameras. Never reached commercial production. This camera is the only specimen known of this kind and has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '此台M8是採用啞金色面漆，是徠卡數碼機中已知的唯一一台採用金色面漆所造的原型機，也是當年徠卡的概念機。此版本內置測光錶，從未在市場上出現過，十分罕見。已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2894', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', 'MP Republic of China Centennial Limited Edition', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_222_7.jpg', '222', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'Only 100 units were made. This camera features a copper and zinc-alloy body while the upper and lower lid are painted with military grey, which resembles the Leica M2 Grey film camera on the top plate. This camera is MP 100-081. The Chinese character “ 精彩一百. 1912-2011 ” engraved on the top plate and a plum blossom totem engraved on the rear plate. This camera completes with packing, papers, body cap, batteries, strap and presentation box, in brand new condition.', '徠卡推出的MP“建國一百週年紀念機”，限量100台。此套機以徠卡原裝木盒珍藏，配有銅鋅合金機身，機身金屬部份噴上特別的軍灰綠色。機上刻有 “精彩一百. 1912-2011”字樣，機背則刻有梅花圖案。此機紀念號碼為MP100-081。配有包裝證書、機身蓋、電池、相機帶及木盒，全新未經使用，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2895', 'R3 “100 Jahre Oskar Barnack Golden Set” with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'R3 “100 Jahre Oskar Barnack Golden Set” with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_223_8.jpg', '223', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'To commemorate the 100th birthday of Oskar Barnack, R3 100 Jahre Oskar Barnack was made. The camera decorated with the lizard skin leather and Oskar’s facsimile signature engraved on top. This set comes with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm (#2932387), front lens cap and wooden presentation box, in mint condition.', '此套機是為紀念徠卡相機之父Oskar Barnack誕生100週年而推出的。配有Summilux-R 1.4/50mm鏡頭 (#2932387)。相機及鏡頭部分組件均鍍以24K金，機身覆以名貴蜥蝪皮，共生產1000台。此機紀念號為100-614，連木盒及鏡頭蓋，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2896', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', 'R6.2 Gold “July 1, 1997 Hong Kong”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_224_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_224_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_224_3.jpg', '224', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'In year 1997, Leica released 300 special edition rare limited kits for Hong Kongreturn to China. The commemorate number is 12/300. “July 1, 1997” and Hong Kong skyline is engraved on top plate. This set comes with Summicron-R 2/50mm lens (#3736392). The camera is in new condition with original papers and packing.', '徠卡為香港回歸中國推出罕見的R6.2 18K鍍金套機，僅限量生產300套。此套機紀念號為12／300，機頂刻有 “July 1, 1997” 和香港著名地標，相機配有Summicron-R 2/50mm (#3736392)鏡頭。此套機全新未經使用，包裝證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2897', 'R6.2 Singapore\'s 30thAnniversary of Independence gold plated set', 'R6.2 Singapore\'s 30thAnniversary of Independence gold plated set', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_225_8.jpg', '225', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leica R6.2 Singapore\'s 30th Anniversary of Independence gold plated camera was specially made to celebrate Singapore\'s independence (1965-1995). It comes with Summilux-R 1.4/50mm lens and only 150 units were produced. The whole camera set was casted with 24K yellow gold. The top plate engraved“30, My Singapore, My Home”and the serial no. 140; the back engraved “Republic of Singapore 1965-1995” and the national totem of Singapore. The camera body was decorated with red snakeskin, in completely new condition.', '徠卡R6.2新加坡獨立30週年鍍金相機，是為了慶祝新加坡獨立 (1965-1995)所發表，以經典的R6.2搭配Summilux-R 1.4/50mm超大光圈鏡頭，全球限量150台。<br />\r\n整套機組以24K黃澄色鍍金製造，貴氣十足。機頂刻有「30, My Singapore, My Home」的字樣，以及限量號碼140的序號；背面則有「Republic of Singapore 1965 - 1995」的刻字以及代表新加坡的國家圖案；機身則飾有紅色蛇皮，奢華感與復古味兼具。整套相機配有包裝盒、證書、鏡頭蓋，全新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2898', 'Leicaflex SL2 50 Jahre Chrome', 'Leicaflex SL2 50 Jahre Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_226_6.jpg', '226', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'This camera is numbered 025-L. It comes with box, certificate and body cap, has some normal used marks.', '此機是Leicaflex 50週年紀念機，特別號碼為025-L，連包裝證書及機身蓋，有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2899', 'Super-Elmarit R 2.8/15mm ASPH', 'Super-Elmarit R 2.8/15mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_227_6.jpg', '227', '', '54,280', null, null, null, null, 'Super wide angle lens of R series, with ROM. It comes with both caps, leather case, all papers in mint condition.', 'R系列的超級廣角鏡，帶非球面玻璃，故在變形方面的控制十分優良。鏡身帶ROM，玻璃完美，連鏡頭前後蓋、皮套、證書及紙盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2900', 'Fish Eye-Elmarit-R 2.8/16mm', 'Fish Eye-Elmarit-R 2.8/16mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_228_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_228_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_228_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_228_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_228_5.jpg', '228', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with four built-in filters, including 80B, orange 56, yellow 48, UV filter and both caps, in mint condition.', '徠卡唯一一支魚眼鏡，不能加上濾鏡，內置有UV濾鏡及有色濾鏡，分別為黃色48、橙色56及80B濾鏡，設計特別。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋，調焦暢順，成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2901', 'Vario-Elmar-R 3.5-4.5/28-70mm', 'Vario-Elmar-R 3.5-4.5/28-70mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_229_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_229_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_229_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_229_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_229_5.jpg', '229', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with ROM, hood, hood cap and lens rear cap, has clear glass, in mint condition.', '此鏡帶ROM，連遮光罩、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋，鏡身及玻璃如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2902', 'Vario-Elmait-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', 'Vario-Elmait-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_230_6.jpg', '230', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 2005, this lens belongs to the last zoom lens model in the R-series. It comes with built-in hood, ROM and both caps, in mint condition.', '此為徠卡於R系列中最後一款變焦鏡王，帶ASPH，產於2005年，配有一鏡頭前後蓋、內置遮光罩及ROM，玻璃通透，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2903', 'Summilux-R 1.4/35mm Prototype', 'Summilux-R 1.4/35mm Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_231_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_231_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_231_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_231_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_231_5.jpg', '231', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of Summilux-R 1.4/35mm. The serial number of this lens is 5175314, which is not within the original production serial no., very rare. It comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '此鏡是Summilux-R 1.4/35mm的原型鏡。正常生產的鏡身編號由3271401開始，但此鏡號碼是5175314，並不是在正常生產編號之中，十分罕見。此鏡連鏡頭前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('2904', 'Summicron- R 2/35mm Prototype Consecutive Numbers', 'Summicron- R 2/35mm Prototype Consecutive Numbers', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_232_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_232_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_232_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_232_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_232_5.jpg', '232', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Set of two original Leitz prototype lenses of the Summicron-R 2/35 (2nd Version), Consecutive serial numbers 0001387 and 0001388. Only four of such prototype lenses have been produced with numbers 0001385 till 0001388 Leitz Wetzlar on 2nd April 1976. These lenses have been authenticated by Lars Netopil. #0001387 comes with keeper and #0001388 comes with front and rear lens caps, clean and clear lenses, smooth focusing, extremely rare.', '這兩支鏡頭是第二代Summicron-R 2/35mm的原型鏡，只生產4支，序號由0001385至0001388，十分珍貴罕有。兩支鏡頭的光圈環、內置遮光罩、對焦環及鏡身都以金屬製造，造工精良。#0001387連同膠盅，＃0001388則連鏡頭前後蓋。兩支鏡頭分別經過Lars Netopil鑑定為真品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2905', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8/35-70mm ASPH', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8/35-70mm ASPH', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_233_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_233_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_233_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_233_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/g', '233', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'It is one of the rarest R lens. It comes with built-in hood, ROM and both caps, in like new condition.', '徠卡R鏡頭系列的超級名鏡，帶有非球面玻璃，成像可媲美定焦鏡頭。 由於生產成本太高，故產量十份稀少。此鏡連內置遮光罩、有ROM、鏡頭前後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2906', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Black', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Black', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_234_6.jpg', '234', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Germany with built-in hood and ROM in E60. It comes with packing, all papers, leather case and both caps, in like new condition.', '德國製的Summilux-R 1.4/50mm最新款鏡頭，內置遮光罩。此鏡頭玻璃通透，口徑為E60，帶ROM，成色近乎全新。連原裝包裝、證書、說明書、皮套及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2907', 'Summicron-R 2/50mm', 'Summicron-R 2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_235_6.jpg', '235', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens has clear glass and normal used marks, it completes with box, certificate and both caps, in excellent condition.', '此鏡玻璃通透，鏡身有輕微使用痕跡。連包裝證書及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2908', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_236_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_236_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_236_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_236_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_236_5.jpg', '236', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with ROM, filter, leather case, both caps and built-in hood, in mint condition.', '此款鏡頭可媲美定焦鏡的變焦鏡頭，為R系列中的名鏡之一。鏡頭帶ROM，連內置遮光罩、濾鏡、皮筒及前後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2909', 'Vario-Elmar-R 4/70-210mm', 'Vario-Elmar-R 4/70-210mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_237_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_237_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_237_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_237_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_237_5.jpg', '237', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was made in Japan with signature of the famous sport player, Jesse Owens. It comes with built-in hood and both caps, in mint condition.', '此鏡於日本生產，鏡身有著名運動員Jesse Owens的簽名，有輕微使用痕跡，玻璃透亮。連內置遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2910', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_238_7.jpg', '238', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of first version Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm, with three cams design. The serial number of this lens is 0000808, which is not within the original production serial numbers. It comes with lens rear cap and built-in hood, with normal used marks.', '徠卡Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm第一代的原型鏡。鏡頭有使用痕跡，連內置遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。其三刀設計可支援Leicaflex, SL, SL2及R系列。鏡頭編號為0000808，並不是正常生產內的序號，極為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2911', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_239_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_239_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_239_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_239_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_239_5.jpg', '239', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of second version Elamrit-R 2.8/180mm, E67, without any serial number engraved on the barrel. It comes with built-in hood and rear cap in good condition.', '此鏡為Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm第二代的原型鏡，口徑為E67，連內置遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。此鏡鏡身上沒有任何編號，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2912', 'APO Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm', 'APO Elmarit-R 2.8/180mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_240_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_240_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_240_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_240_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_240_5.jpg', '240', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with built-in lens hood, with ROM, leather case and both caps, in mint condition.', '徠卡一支帶APO消色差的長焦鏡。此鏡有ROM，連內置遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋及皮套，玻璃通透，成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2913', 'Telyt-R 4.8/350mm Prototype', 'Telyt-R 4.8/350mm Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_241_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_241_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_241_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_241_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_241_5.jpg', '241', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'This is a prototype lens of Telyt-R 4.8/350mm. Only model no. &amp; serial no.5175561 engraved on the barrel but not the focusing scales and aperture scales. The focusing ring is shorter than the normal one and the front of lens is longer. It comes with rear cap and has normal used marks.', '此鏡為Telyt-R 4.8/350mm的原型鏡。鏡身只刻有其型號及鏡身編號 (#5175561)，此鏡身編號並非正常生產序號之列。此鏡並沒有刻上焦距尺及光圈的刻度，調焦環較正常版為短，鏡身前段則較長，是比較原始的Prototype，市面從未見過同款之鏡頭，十分罕有。此鏡有使用痕跡，玻璃通透，連鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2914', 'APO Extender-R 2X', 'APO Extender-R 2X', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_242_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_242_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_242_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_242_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_242_5.jpg', '242', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '德國製的R系列兩倍增倍鏡，帶ROM，有前後蓋，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2915', 'Leica Diopter Checker DIOOY', 'Leica Diopter Checker DIOOY', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_243_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_243_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_243_3.jpg', '243', '', '4,720', null, null, null, null, 'This is a correction lens mounted to universal viewfinders, cameras and magnifiers. Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.50 for further illustrations.', '此款是屈光度檢視器，產於1955年，度數由-5度至+4度，當年此檢視器只提供徠卡經銷商使用，並沒有正式推出市場 (可参閱James Lager Vol.III p.50)，非常罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2916', 'Leica 3.5cm Viewfinder SBLOO Prototype', 'Leica 3.5cm Viewfinder SBLOO Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_244_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_244_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_244_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_244_4.jpg', '244', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare and all original Leitz SBLOO 35mm bright line finder (1950’s), in black paint finish. Never commercially advertised, a very small number of those scarce black paint SBLOO finders were originally made by Leitz. It is known that Henry Cartier Bresson and others got black paint Leica IIIg cameras on special order. Also, very early and original special order black paint versions of the Leica M3 do exist with serial numbers from 746571. Both cameras the IIIg as well as the M3 only had a 50mm finder as built-in and 35mm &quot;RF&quot; lenses with goggles for M3 were only made from 1956.  So the black SBLOO could have been made for those early black versions. Beautiful, very clean condition with some tiny bubbles in the black paint. Perfect glass. This finder has been authenticated by Lars Netopil. This viewfinder is clear and bright, there are signs of normal use and it comes with original box. Please refer to James Lager Vol.II p.25 and Vol.III p.42 for further illustrations.', '這是非常罕見的SBLOO 3.5cm黑漆取景器訂製版，以黃銅鑄造而成。當年正式生產時只推出過銀色版本。原裝黑漆從未正式推出市場，產量特少，十分罕見。只知道徠卡曾經幫法國著名記實攝影師Henry Cartier Bresson和擁有IIIG黑漆特別定製版以及M3黑漆特別定製版 (#746571)特別生產過這個SBLOO取景器。此取景器上的黑漆有小氣泡，玻璃通透，配有盒子，成色極佳。已經過Lars Netopil鑑定。在James Lager Vol.II p.25及Vol.III p.42中亦有提及此取景器。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2917', 'OROLF Tri-lens', 'OROLF Tri-lens', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_245_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_245_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_245_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_245_4.jpg', '245', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare Tri-Lens turret OROLF for M2 and M3 (Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.300 for further illustrations).', '供M2或M3使用的三支螺絲口鏡快速轉台 (可参考James Lager Vol.III p.300)，非常稀有，配有掛帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2918', 'Leica Hood OLLUX for Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', 'Leica Hood OLLUX for Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_246_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_246_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_246_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_246_4.jpg', '246', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'Lens hood OLLUX for early Summilux 1.4/35mm Steel Rim. Extremely rare.', '早期的OLLUX遮光罩，用於Summilux-M 1.4/35mm鋼咀鏡頭2/35mm、2/50mm、2.8/35mm、2.8/50mm、3.5/35mm或3.5/50mm鏡頭。成色十分完好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2919', 'Leica Hood IROOA', 'Leica Hood IROOA', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_247_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_247_2.jpg', '247', '', '1,770', null, null, null, null, 'The early version lens hood (#12571J) is used for 8 Elements, comes with original box.', '早期的遮光罩 (#12571J)，主要用於八枚玉鏡頭上。連原包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2920', 'Leica Hood for Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Leica Hood for Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_248_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_248_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_248_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_248_4.jpg', '248', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Leica lens hood for Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm, in like new condition, extremely rare.', '徠卡Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm (#12503)遮光罩，近乎全新，非常罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2921', 'KE-7A Technical Manual', 'KE-7A Technical Manual', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_249_1.jpg', '249', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'This instruction manual is for KE-7A and KE-7A is made for U.S. military in 1972, only 505 pieces were made. Very rare.', '此說明書是KE-7A所用。而KE-7A是1972年左右由徠卡提供予美軍使用。每台軍用機均配有操作說明書一本，十分珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2922', 'Leica OLIGO', 'Leica OLIGO', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_250_6.jpg', '250', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica OLIGO is a miniature view camera for single exposure (Please refer to James Lager Vol.III p.293 for further illustrations). It completes with original packing, in good working order, very rare.', '徠卡照片單拍器連鏡頭接環及玻璃屏，附有以黃銅鑄造的菲林夾及快門控制器 (可参閱James Lager Vol.III p.293)。套件操作正常，連原包裝盒，市場少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2923', 'MP and MP2 Top Plate', 'MP and MP2 Top Plate', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_251_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_251_2.jpg', '251', '', '1,003,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is MP and MP2 top plate with original black paint, in brand new condition, extremely rare.', '此對相機頂蓋為百分百徠卡原廠出品的MP及MP2黑漆頂蓋，全新未經使用。MP頂蓋沒有刻上機身序號，而MP-2的頂蓋則只刻有MP2-字樣，同樣沒有機身序號，甚為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2924', 'Leica Motor Drive', 'Leica Motor Drive', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_252_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_252_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_252_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_252_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_252_5.jpg', '252', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Leica black painted motor drive with normal used marks. It completes with box &amp; instruction manual, in good working order.', '徠卡NEW YORK黑漆電動捲片馬達，操作正常，成色極新，連包裝盒及說明書，十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2925', 'Leica Winder M Prototype', 'Leica Winder M Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_253_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_253_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_253_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_253_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_253_5.jpg', '253', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica winder M Prototype was made in Canada, with insignificant sign of use, comes with box, very rare.', '此捲片器於加拿大生產，正常生產是黑色，此銀色版本是原型版，未曾正式推出過市場，市面非常罕見，貨品只有輕微使用痕跡，連包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2926', 'Leicavit MP', 'Leicavit MP', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_254_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_254_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_254_3.jpg', '254', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Early MP Leicavit, very rare.', '早期的徠卡MP銀色過片器，較為罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2927', 'Leicavit MP LHSA Special Edition', 'Leicavit MP LHSA Special Edition', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_255_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_255_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_255_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_255_4.jpg', '255', '', '7,670', null, null, null, null, 'Leicavit Chrome for LHSA, it completes with box &amp; papers, in brand new condition.', '美國徠卡歷史協會 (LHSA) 銀色版本快速過片器，正面刻有MP字樣。全新未經使用，包裝證書齊備。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2928', 'Leica Camera Hard Case MOORB', 'Leica Camera Hard Case MOORB', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_256_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_256_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_256_3.jpg', '256', '', '3,776', null, null, null, null, 'Leica Camera Hard Case MOORB manufactured in 1955, made of hard metal and designed for screw mount cameras, very rare.', '徠卡於1955年生產的相機套MOORB，以堅硬的金屬製成，配以經典的徠卡黑色水波紋，防撞防水，用於螺絲口機上，市場頗為罕見，屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2929', 'Leica Universal-Lupe 5X', 'Leica Universal-Lupe 5X', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_257_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_257_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_257_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_257_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_257_5.jpg', '257', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica Universal-Lupe 5X first appeared in Photo Kina, Germany in 1988, in mint condition.', '此款底片觀片器首次出現於1988年德國的Photokina展覽會上，屈光調節由-2至+2，帶5倍放大比率，接目處可調整焦距，實為底片愛好者必備之物。外觀成色如新，放大器附有一個135膠片的滑動片夾。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2930', 'Leica Magnus 1.5-10x42', 'Leica Magnus 1.5-10x42', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_258_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_258_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_258_3.jpg', '258', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica Magnus 1.5-10x42 is in like new condition, good working order, clear glass, comes with original box, both caps, batteries, cleaning cloth, manuals and certificates.', '由徠卡製造的瞄準器，可將目標影像放大至10倍 (口俓為42mm)鏡片上有刻度線，使瞄準變得容易及精準。成色如新，操作正常，鏡片通透明亮，配以原裝盒，鏡頭前後蓋，電池，清潔布，說明書及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2931', 'Leica Magnus 2.4-16x56', 'Leica Magnus 2.4-16x56', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_259_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_259_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_259_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_259_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_259_5.jpg', '259', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This Leica Magnus 2.4-16x56 is in like new condition, good working order, clear glass, comes with original box, both caps, batteries, cleaning cloth, manuals and certificates.', '由徠卡製造的瞄準器，可將目標影像放大至16倍 (口俓為56mm)鏡片上有刻度線，使瞄準變得容易及精準。弱光下均可發揮理想的影像效果。成色如新，操作正常，鏡片明亮通透。配有原裝盒，鏡頭前後蓋，電池，清潔布，說明書及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2932', 'Hasselblad 503CX “Golden Blue” 50th Anniversary', 'Hasselblad 503CX “Golden Blue” 50th Anniversary', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_260_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_260_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_260_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_260_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_260_5.jpg', '260', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'The 50thAnniversary Edition in 24K gold plated, decorated with blue leather. The commemorative number is 412. It comes with CF 2.8/80mm (#7212998) and A12 (#03EV10575), leather presentation box, outer box, papers, front lens cap and strap, in like new condition.', '為慶祝1941年第一台哈蘇503CX相機面世50年而產，配有CF 2.8/80mm鏡頭 (#7212998)，A12菲林後背 (#03EV10575)。此機紀念號碼412，附有精美包裝皮箱、鏡頭蓋、藍色鍍金相機手帶、證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2933', 'Hasselblad 503 CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', 'Hasselblad 503 CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_261_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_261_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_261_3.jpg', '261', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 50 th Anniversary of the first Hasselblad camera introduced in October 6, 1948, Hasselblad launched a special jubilee model - The Hasselblad<br />\r\nGold Supreme. It is a complete 503CW with all visible chromed details plated in 24 carat gold. It comes with CF 2.8/80mm (#8149297), A12 (#30ER12077), maker\'s box, leather presentation box, leather strap and all papers.', '此503CW紅皮24K鍍金紀念機是為慶祝哈蘇相機面世50週年而推出全球限量500套503CW連CF 2.8/80mm及 A12 菲林後背。機身刻有 “The System 1948-1998” 字樣。此套機限量號碼為266/500，鏡頭編號為8149297，A12後背編號為30ER12077，全新未經使用。附有精美皮箱 (皮箱亦刻有 “1948-1998” 字樣、紅色鍍金相機手帶，證書齊全，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2934', 'Hasselblad 503CW Millennium Kit', 'Hasselblad 503CW Millennium Kit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_262_6.jpg', '262', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'This Hasselblad 503CW Millennium chrome camera comes with special gold colored darkslide and magazine slide on the filmback. This set comes with CFE 2.8/80mm (#8882408), A12 (#30SS17634), matching box, body cap, leather strap and papers, the lens with box, instruction manual and both caps.', '哈蘇於2000年推出503CW千禧年紀念套機，機身側面及刀片均有24K鍍金 “Millennium” 字樣。此套機配有CFE 2.8/80mm鏡頭 (#8882408)及A12菲林後背(#30SS17634)，連機身蓋，皮帶及包裝證書；鏡頭帶有包裝，說明書及前後蓋，十分珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2935', 'Hasselblad 503CW &quot;60th Birthday of the PRC&quot; Limited Edition', 'Hasselblad 503CW &quot;60th Birthday of the PRC&quot; Limited Edition', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_263_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_263_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_263_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_263_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_263_5.jpg', '263', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 60th Anniversary of People’s Republic of China, Hasselblad released only 61 units of 503CW 18K gold-plated camera, each camera between with a year between 1949 to 2009. The number “1949” was donated to the department of Xinhua News Agency. It complete with a Distagon CFi 3.5/60mm (#8925091) and A12 magazine (#30SE16932). The special number of this set is 1994. This set complete with all packing in brand new condition.', '哈蘇公司為慶祝中華人民共和國成立60年推出了一款限量版503CW紅皮金機。此機紀念號是1994號，所有金屬部件均飾以18K鍍金，其機身側面名牌上更刻有 “慶祝中華人民共和國成立60週年1949 – 2009” 字樣。此款鍍金限量版共生產61台，其中首台1949年編號己送予新華社作珍藏。套機配有經典的Distagon CFi 3.5/60mm (#8925091)鏡頭，菲林後背 (#30SE16932)。此套機全新未經使用，包裝證書全齊，非常珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2936', 'Hasselblad 503CW “60 Years Victor Red Edition”', 'Hasselblad 503CW “60 Years Victor Red Edition”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_264_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_264_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_264_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_264_4.jpg', '264', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'This is a commemorative 503CW to celebrate 60 years of cooperation between Carl Zeiss and Victor Hasselblad. Only 60 sets made and this is the first set, with the special commemorative number 01/60.<br />\r\nThis set comes with A12 (#30SR16475), body cap, strap, box & certificate, in brand new condition.', '為慶祝哈蘇與蔡司合作60週年而發行的503CW紀念套機，全球限量發行僅60套。此套機限量號碼為01/60，是第一套發行的套機，非常珍貴。套機配有A12菲林後背(#30SR16475)，連機身蓋，皮帶及包裝證書，全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2937', 'Hasselblad 905 SWC', 'Hasselblad 905 SWC', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_265_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_265_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_265_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_265_4.jpg', '265', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This camera set comes with Biogon CFI 4.5/38mm (#8899801), viewfinder, box, front lens cap, strap and instruction manual, in like new condition.', '哈蘇905 SWC超廣角頂級機王，配備Biogon CFI 4.5/38mm (#8899801)彪鋼鏡頭。此套相機連取景器、鏡頭前蓋、相機帶、說明書及包裝，成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2938', 'Hasselblad Distagon CFE 4/40mm', 'Hasselblad Distagon CFE 4/40mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_266_6.jpg', '266', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens completes with box, instruction, certificate &amp; both caps with clear glass, in like new condition.', '此鏡頭連包裝證書、鏡頭前後蓋。玻璃通透，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2939', 'Hasselblad CFI Distagon 4/50mm', 'Hasselblad CFI Distagon 4/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_267_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_267_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_267_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_267_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_267_5.jpg', '267', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with hood and both caps, in like new condition.', '此鏡頭連遮光罩及鏡頭前後蓋，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2940', 'Hasselblad Makro-Planar CFE T* 4/120mm', 'Hasselblad Makro-Planar CFE T* 4/120mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_268_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_268_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_268_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_268_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_268_5.jpg', '268', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '此鏡頭可用作近攝用，成象質素甚佳，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2941', 'Hasselblad CF Sonnar 5.6/250mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CF Sonnar 5.6/250mm Superachromat', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_269_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_269_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_269_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_269_4.jpg', '269', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with box, keeper and front lens cap, in mint condition.', '哈蘇超級名鏡之一，Superachromat。此鏡玻璃通透，外觀成色極佳，連包裝盒、膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2942', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/350mm Superachromat', 'Hasselblad CFE 5.6/350mm Superachromat', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_270_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_270_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_270_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_270_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_270_5.jpg', '270', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with matching serial number box, lens hood, hood cap, rear lens cap and leather case, in like new condition.', '哈蘇長焦名鏡，Superachromat。此鏡玻璃清澈，功能正常，配有與機身號碼相同的包裝盒、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、鏡頭後蓋及皮筒，成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2943', 'Carl Zeiss 2.8/300mm Tele-Superachromat Prototype', 'Carl Zeiss 2.8/300mm Tele-Superachromat Prototype', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_271_8.jpg', '271', '', '377,600', null, null, null, null, 'This prototype lens was designed for Hasselblad FE 2.8/300mm Tele-Superachromat. The design of it is different from the original ones, its lens hood is shorter, without the brand name “Hasselblad” engraved on both lens and 1.7XE APO converter. The lens cap is helicoid design. Also, the serial number of the official batch starts from 9300xxx but this prototype is numbered 8801907. This prototype comes with UV filter, CPL filter, both caps and aluminium box with keys, also with prototype 1.7 XE Apo-Mutar converter (#8801948).', '此原型鏡是為生產哈蘇FE 2.8/300mm Tele-Superachromat而設計的原型版。其特徵亦有別於一般哈蘇FE 2.8/300mm鏡頭。遮光罩比正式生產的版本較短，機身及增倍鏡亦沒有刻有 “Hasselblad” 字樣。鏡頭蓋是螺絲帽型。正式生產批次編號由9300xxx 開始，此鏡頭編號則為8801907。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2944', 'Hasselblad Xpan with 4/45mm', 'Hasselblad Xpan with 4/45mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_272_7.jpg', '272', '', '15,340', null, null, null, null, 'This Xpan comes with 4/45mm lens (#8YER10137), front lens cap and hood quick mounting plate, in mint condition.', 'Xpan連4/45mm鏡頭 (#8YER10137)，連鏡頭前蓋、遮光罩及快裝板，外觀成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2945', 'Hasselblad Xpan 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', 'Hasselblad Xpan 5.6/30mm ASPHERICAL', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_273_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_273_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_273_3.jpg', '273', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with center filter, viewfinder, spirit level, both caps, hood and original leather box, in mint condition.', '此鏡連同中灰、取景器、水平珠、遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋及原裝皮盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2946', 'Hasselblad Teleconverter APO 1.4XE', 'Hasselblad Teleconverter APO 1.4XE', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_274_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_274_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_274_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_274_4.jpg', '274', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'This teleconverter APO 1.4XE comes with both caps, in mint condition.', '此增倍鏡成色極新，玻璃通透，適用於哈蘇的長焦鏡上，配鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2947', 'Hasselblad PME45 Prism', 'Hasselblad PME45 Prism', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_275_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_275_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_275_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_275_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_275_5.jpg', '275', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'It comes with the back cover, in mint condition and good working order.', '45度角取景器，帶測光功能，操作正常連底蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2948', 'ALPA 11si Gold with Kern-Macro-Switar 1.9/50mm AR', 'ALPA 11si Gold with Kern-Macro-Switar 1.9/50mm AR', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_276_6.jpg', '276', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'Gold plated edition, decorated with brown lizard skin, comes with Kern-Macro-Switar 1.9/50mm (#1114565), presentation box, papers, certificate and lens front cap.', 'ALPA 11si機身鍍以黃金並覆以咖啡色的蜥蝪皮，配有Kern-Macro-Switar 1.9/50mm (#1114565)鏡頭。套機配有包裝盒、相機展示盒、說明書、證書及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2949', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar', 'Voigtlander Bessa II APO-Lanthar', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_277_7.jpg', '277', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'Original Voigtlander Bessa II 4.5/105mm APO-Lanthar, comes with leather case. In mint condition, extremely rare.', 'Voigtlander Bessa II是福倫達公司於1950年推出的顛峰之作。Bessa II配有三款鏡頭，分别是Color-Skopar、Color-Heliar和APO-Lanthar，此Bessa II 有兩個取景框，分別為6 X 4.5及6 X 9，光圈景深尺均顯示為4.5 – 22，並配有超級名鏡APO-Lanthar。由於配備了稀有的鑭玻璃鏡頭，成像優異， 加上此鏡產量極少（有說法在200 ﹣300台)， 故此機鏡一直都是攝影愛好者追求的珍寶。此機配有皮套，成色極佳，甚為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2950', 'Angenieux 3.5/28mm Type R11', 'Angenieux 3.5/28mm Type R11', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_278_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_278_2.jpg', '278', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 3.5/28mm Type R11, with Retrofocus. This lens comes with both caps, in Leica bayonet mount, with normal using wears.', 'Angenieux (愛展能)是產於法國的名鏡，型號為R11，這是愛展能中有Retrofocus的鏡頭 (焦點後移式或反轉遠攝鏡式光學設計)。此鏡層次分明，色彩豐富，充滿古典色彩的韻味。此鏡頭為徠卡螺絲口，連前後蓋，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2951', 'Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', 'Angenieux 2.5/35mm Type R1', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_279_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_279_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_279_3.jpg', '279', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux Paris 2.5/35 Type R1 Retrofocus lens, one of the famous portrait lens of Angenieux, with original Leica bayonet mount. The lens is in mint condition, comes with both caps and 52mm filter.', '此鏡頭可說是Angenieux的成名作，它是全球第一支大光圈廣角鏡頭，全金屬鏡身。此鏡成像細膩，色彩豐富及有極強的立體感，可充分展現標準的法國浪漫色調。此鏡頭是原裝徠卡螺絲口用，鏡頭成色良好，有正常使用痕跡，連鏡頭前後蓋及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2952', 'Angenieux Paris 1.5/50mm Ltm', 'Angenieux Paris 1.5/50mm Ltm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_280_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_280_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_280_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_280_4.jpg', '280', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'With small batch of production, has been modified to Leica bayonet mount. It comes with lens rear cap in mint conition.', '愛展能為法國頂級的電影鏡頭牌，其成像散景獨特，極富法國的浪漫風格。而此鏡頭為愛展能的名鏡之一，產量僅數十支，鏡頭卡口為徠卡螺絲口，極為罕有，此鏡連同後蓋，成色優良，運作暢順，收藏價值極高。配有鏡頭底蓋、鏡片有輕微清潔痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2953', 'Angenieux 1.8/65mm Type Y31', 'Angenieux 1.8/65mm Type Y31', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_281_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_281_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_281_3.jpg', '281', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This lens was modified to Canon mount, with cleaning marks on the lens.', '此款鏡頭是法國愛展能的投影鏡，後期改為佳能卡口，鏡頭外觀良好，玻璃有清潔痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2954', 'Angenieux 1.8/65mm Type Y31', 'Angenieux 1.8/65mm Type Y31', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_282_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_282_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_282_3.jpg', '282', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both caps, has been modified to Leica M bayonet.', '此款鏡頭是愛展能的鏡頭，後期改為徠卡M卡口，鏡頭成色優良，運作暢順。配有購買單據及鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2955', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm Type P1', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_283_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_283_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_283_3.jpg', '283', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 1.8/90mm, Type P1, the famous portrait lens of Angenieux. This lens has been modified to Leica bayonet mount, comes with both caps in mint condition.', 'Angenieux (愛展能)是產於法國的名鏡，型號為P1，這是愛展能中相當著名的一支大光圈人像鏡。最近對焦距離為5尺，光圈葉數目為12片，所形成的散景十分迷人。而且影像反差較少，較有古典色彩的韻味，令人難忘。此鏡頭為原裝徠卡螺絲口，連前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2956', 'Angenieux 3.5/135mm Type Y2', 'Angenieux 3.5/135mm Type Y2', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_284_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_284_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_284_3.jpg', '284', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Angenieux 3.5/135mm Type Y2, made in France. This lens has been modified to Leica bayonet mount, comes with both caps, in mint condition.', 'Angenieux (愛展能)由Pierre Angenieux於1933年在法國巴黎創立，以135單反相機及電影鏡聞名於世。此鏡頭為3.5/135mm Type Y2，最近對焦距離為1.5米，光圈葉數量為12片，由最大至最小光圈時皆呈現圓形，解象度極高，相片層次感豐富。此鏡頭為徠卡螺絲口，連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2957', 'Contax Zeiss Plannar T* 85mm f1.2 “60 Years Limited Edition”', 'Contax Zeiss Plannar T* 85mm f1.2 “60 Years Limited Edition”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_285_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_285_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_285_3.jpg', '285', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with packing, instruction manual, certificate, filter, both caps, hood and leather case, in mint condition.', 'Contax為慶祝60週年而生產的大光圈鏡頭，產於德國，鏡身同樣刻有 “60 Years”字樣。連同包裝、證書、說明書、濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋、遮光罩及皮套，成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2958', 'Contax RTS Gold Edition', 'Contax RTS Gold Edition', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_286_6.jpg', '286', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Only 100 units made, with Planar 1.4/50mm (#6053077), box, certificate, instruction, lens cleaning cloth, wooden presentation box and lens front cap in good working order.', 'Contax黃金紀念套機，限量100台。RTS機身連同Planar 1.4/50mm (#6053077)，配有包裝盒、證書、說明書、抹鏡布、木盒及鏡頭前蓋，操作功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2959', 'Zeiss Ikon Hologon Ultrawide with 8/15mm', 'Zeiss Ikon Hologon Ultrawide with 8/15mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_287_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_287_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_287_3.jpg', '287', '', '45,980', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with Hologon 8/15mm (#4581319), hand grip, two cable releases, leather case, strap, center filter (S574).', '由西德製的Zeiss Ikon超廣角相機配以著名廣角鏡頭Hologon 8/15mm (#4581319)，此機配有手柄、兩條快門線、皮盒、相機帶及中灰濾鏡(S574)。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2960', 'Carl Zeiss Anastigmat 6.3/170mm', 'Carl Zeiss Anastigmat 6.3/170mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_288_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_288_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_288_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_288_4.jpg', '288', '<span class=\"font11\">開拍價格:</span> HK$ 60,000  &nbsp; | &nbsp;  \n										\n					<span class=\"font11\">估計價格:</span> HK$ 90,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, no serial number, but engraved “Carl Zeiss Anastigmat 6.3/170mm” and “DRP56109” on the lens barrel by hand. With normal signs of used.', '這是最早期蔡司生產的，採用了著名的Potar結構，此鏡鏡身保留黃銅顏色，使其更顯古典韻味。鏡身有人手雕刻上 “Carl Zeiss Anastigmat 6.3/170mm” 及“DRP56109” 字樣，但沒有鏡身編號，十分罕有。鏡頭為L41口徑，有正常使用痕跡 。此鏡頭在市面上有如鳳毛麟角，十年難得一見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2961', 'Cooke Deep Field Panchro 2.5/100mm', 'Cooke Deep Field Panchro 2.5/100mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_289_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_289_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_289_3.jpg', '289', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'Deep blue, purple and copper-colored lens coatings. M42 rear mount fitted to custom extension, mount for Canon FD and metal rear lens cap. Lens fits to Canon M15-25 helical. Lens optics, coatings, body, filter adapter, hood and original slip-on Taylor-Hobson hood all as new.', '由英國製的電影鏡頭Cooke，在大型相機與電影機中有舉足輕重的地位。二十世紀的前五十年間的荷里活，幾乎所有的電影都是以Cooke之鏡頭拍攝，是一個極富歷史色彩及代表性的電影鏡頭。此鏡為佳能FD口徑，連遮光罩，遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋。鏡身上刻有 “Lens Made in England By Rank Taylor Hobson”。有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2962', 'Dallmeyer Super-Six Anastigmat 2” 1.9/50mm', 'Dallmeyer Super-Six Anastigmat 2” 1.9/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_290_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_290_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_290_3.jpg', '290', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Made in original Leica bayonet mount, with small batch of approx. 250 pieces only, very rare. This lens comes with both lens cap, in excellent condition.', '此鏡為英國著名製造商Dallmeyer製造，鏡身為罕有的原裝徠卡螺絲卡口。早期產量極少，只生產約250支，現存數量極少。此鏡頭連鏡頭前後蓋，成色上佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2963', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/50mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/50mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_291_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_291_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_291_3.jpg', '291', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with hood, hood cap, rear lens cap, cleaning marks on the lens, has been modified to Leica M bayonet.', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/50mm電影鏡頭。此鏡配有遮光罩，遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋，鏡片有輕微清潔痕跡，成色良好，後期已改裝為徠卡M卡口。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2964', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_292_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_292_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_292_3.jpg', '292', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Red-Green Coating, original front cap, box, mfr’s inspection paper, Angenieux rear cap (not original). Lens as new (never mounted), box un-torn but lid creased.', '產於法國的Kinoptik是最頂級電影鏡頭品牌之一，以超高的解析度聞名，這支Kinoptik Apochromat 2/75mm電影鏡頭，其濃郁的色彩和油畫感散景表現讓人一見難忘。此鏡配有包裝盒、證書及鏡頭前後蓋. 玻璃內有輕微塵霧.', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2965', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_293_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_293_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_293_3.jpg', '293', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with hood, hood cap and lens rear cap. Has been modified to Hasselblad mount, in excellent condition.', '產於法國的Kinoptik是最頂級電影鏡頭品牌之一，以超高的解析度聞名，此為著名的Kinoptik Apochromat 2/100mm鏡頭，配有遮光罩連蓋，鏡頭底蓋。已轉哈蘇卡口。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2966', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2.5/150mm', 'Kinoptik Apochromat 2.5/150mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_294_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_294_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_294_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_294_4.jpg', '294', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Red-Green coating, custom filter ring and 67mm front cap. Hasselblad-mount Pentax helicoid with rear extension and cap. Optics, lens body, helicoid and custom hardware.', '這一支Kinoptik Apochromat 2.5/150mm電影鏡頭。此鏡頭連同鏡頭前後蓋及Asahi Pentax 6x7微距延伸管，哈蘇卡口，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2967', 'Kodar Ektor 2/47mm Chrome', 'Kodar Ektor 2/47mm Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_295_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_295_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_295_3.jpg', '295', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Kodar Ektor 2/47mm made in America. This lens comes with hood and both caps, in 35 Leica bayonet mount.', '這支Kodar Ektor 2/47mm是由美國製造。由於老鏡頭的二線散景比較明顯，所以成像散景呈螺旋狀，極具特色。此鏡影像色彩濃郁鮮明，富有濃濃的老鏡味道，喜歡老鏡頭的用家可不能錯過。鏡頭為L35口徑的徠卡螺絲口，帶有遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2968', 'Shanghai 58II', 'Shanghai 58II', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_296_7.jpg', '296', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Copy of Leica IIIb, engraved with “中國上海照相機厂” on the top plate, comes with Shanghai 3.5/50mm lens, leather case, lens cap.', '上海58II仿徠卡相機，機頂刻有 “中國上海照相機厂” 字樣，是中國上海照相機廠以徠卡相機IIIb為藍本而生產的相機。此機配以3.5/50mm鏡頭、皮套及相機前蓋，有正常使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2969', 'Minox 50 Jahre AX Gold II', 'Minox 50 Jahre AX Gold II', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_297_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_297_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_297_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_297_4.jpg', '297', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'Minox AX Gold II 50TH Anniversary Edition of Minox Gmbh, 250 sets were made, comes with burgundy leather case, presentation box and papers.', '美樂時為德國著名微型攝影機牌子，如現時打火機般大小的微型相機於七十多年前面世，其封閉式的設計，微型的機身可握於掌中，可謂微型攝影機的先驅。此相機是MINOX微型相機面世50週年的紀念版，全球限量250套，以24K鍍金機身，配有專用皮套、收藏木盒及包裝證書，是收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2970', 'Nikon M Rangefinder Chrome', 'Nikon M Rangefinder Chrome', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_298_8.jpg', '298', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Nikon M comes with Nikkor-SC 1.4/50cm (#50051722), lens cap.', 'Nikon M在1949年推出, 此機為24×24mm規格。它的影像畫幅處於徠卡的24×36mm及Nikon I型24×32mm規格之間，而被稱為M型。由於生產年期極短， 此機型於1950年就停產了，產量極少，極富有收藏價值。此機配有Nikkor-S.C 1.4/5cm (#50051722)鏡頭及鏡頭前蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2971', 'Nikon S3 Olympic Black Paint', 'Nikon S3 Olympic Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_299_7.jpg', '299', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'Nikon made a last series of S3 Black Paint camera set for Japan Olympics in 1964. Total 2,000 units were made. They came with a new improved version of Nikkor-S 1.4/50mm (#140190) lens, outer box, leather case, front cap and lens hood.', '此套機是為迎接1964年日本奧林匹克運會而生產，限量2000台。此機配有Nikkor-S 1.4/50mm (#140190)鏡頭、包裝盒、皮套、鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2972', 'Nikon S3 Olympic Black Paint', 'Nikon S3 Olympic Black Paint', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_300_7.jpg', '300', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'Nikon made a last series of S3 Black Paint camera set for Japan Olympics in 1964. Total 2,000 units were made. They came with a new improved version of Nikkor-S 1.4/50mm (#206681) lens, filter, lens front cap and lens hood.', '此套機是為迎接1964年日本奧林匹克運會而生產，限量2000台。S系列產量稀少，因而更具收藏價值。此機配有Nikkor-S 1.4/50mm (#206681)鏡頭、濾鏡、鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2973', 'Nikon S3 Rangefinder Black with Nikkor-S.C 1.4/5cm', 'Nikon S3 Rangefinder Black with Nikkor-S.C 1.4/5cm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_301_8.jpg', '301', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with Nikkor-S.C 1.4/5cm (#382530) lens, lens front cap and hood.', '此機配有Nikkor-S.C 1.4/5cm (#382530)鏡頭，配有鏡頭前蓋及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2974', 'Nikon F301', 'Nikon F301', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_302_8.jpg', '302', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'This is the test camera for Swedish Army. It comes with 4/200mm lens (#940020), with plastic case, instruction, and battery holder, filter and lens front cap, in good condition.', 'F301是1985年上市的相機，是第一台內置卷片馬達的相機，此機更是藝康提供予瑞典軍隊用的測試機。連同 4/200mm鏡頭 (#940020)，配有膠箱、說明書、電池匣、濾鏡及鏡頭前蓋，整體成色良好，有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2975', 'Nikkor-S.C 1.5/8.5cm', 'Nikkor-S.C 1.5/8.5cm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_303_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_303_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_303_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_303_4.jpg', '303', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'This is a telephoto lens for Nikon S-series rangefinder cameras. According to the History of Nikon rangefinder camera, from serial number 264345 - 266046 from 1951-1961, there were approx. 2,000 units being produced with approx. 500 units made in other mounts. This lens completes with both caps, in mint condition, glass with very minor dust.', '這是尼康為S系列旁軸相機製作的鏡頭。根據官方記錄，由1951年至1961年期間共生產2000支SC 1.5/8.5cm鏡頭，編號由264345到266046，其中少於500支為其他品牌型號的接口，如徠卡螺絲口及康泰時(Contax)卡口, 其中康泰時卡口的產量非常少，鏡筒上刻有 “C” 字樣作識別為可用於康泰時機身上，如此產量稀少而又保存如新的，更顯其珍貴。此鏡頭連同鏡頭前後蓋，成色極新，玻璃有少量微塵。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2976', 'Zunow Ronetgen 1.4/65mm', 'Zunow Ronetgen 1.4/65mm', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_304_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_304_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_304_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_304_4.jpg', '304', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'This lens comes with both lens caps, has been modified to Leica M bayonet.', 'Zunow Ronetgen 1.4/65mm為日本製鏡頭，除製作頂級電影鏡，軍用及醫療光學設備外，也生產適用於相機用的鏡頭。由於其產量稀少，所以成為國際市場上熱門的收藏品。此鏡配有鏡頭前後蓋，由日本改裝徠卡M卡口的證書。鏡片有輕微清潔痕跡.', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2977', 'Rolleiflex 2.8F “Platin Edition”', 'Rolleiflex 2.8F “Platin Edition”', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_305_6.jpg', '305', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'Manufactured from 1984 to 1985, this is the last model of the Rolleiflex 2.8F was the special edition &quot;Platin&quot; in 500 pieces only. Special Edition Platinum plated with black African Lizard surfaces. Comes with dark wooden box, paper box, warranty, front lens cap with taking lens: Carl Zeiss Planar HFT 2.8/80mm (#6887024) and viewing lens: Triotar 2.8/80mm (#6990567), in like new condition.', '此機產於1984-1985年，為Rolleiflex 2.8F的鉑金版，產量只有500台。此特別版相機除鍍以鉑金外，更以蜥蝪皮覆蓋機身表面，更為珍貴。此套機連同黑色木盒、包裝外盒、證書及鏡頭蓋，配以Carl Zeiss Planar HFT 2.8/80mm (#6887024)及Triotar 2.8/80mm (#6990567)鏡頭，成色極新，為收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2978', 'Linhof 617SIII with Three Lenses Kit', 'Linhof 617SIII with Three Lenses Kit', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_306_1.jpg', '306', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'This camera comes with three lenses - Schneider 5.6/72mm XL (#14622544 with N.D. filter viewfinder and papers, Super Angulon 5.6/90mm (#14597678) with N.D. filter, viewfinder, Schneider 5.6/180mm (#14652410) with filter. Three lenses come with viewfinder, strap and front cap, in mint condition.', '此617套機配有三支鏡頭，分別為Schneider 5.6/72mm XL (#14622544)連減光鏡及證書，Super Angulon 5.6/90mm (#14597678)連減光鏡，Schneider 5.6/180mm (#14652410)連濾鏡。三支鏡頭均有特備的取景器及鏡頭前蓋，配有機身帶，整體成色優良，操作順暢。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2979', 'Linhof Technorama 617 Jubilee SIII', 'Linhof Technorama 617 Jubilee SIII', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_307_6.jpg', '307', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'In 2007, 120 cameras were manufactured to commemorate 120 years of Linhof Company. This camera decorated with red leather, engraved “1887 – 2007 120 Years Linhof Germany” on the back and the commemorative number is 57/120. Complete with a Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/90mm XL lens (#15030270), viewfinder and front lens cap, in mint condition.', '此款相機是為慶祝林可夫公司成立120年，特別於2007年推出120台紅皮紀念套機。此套機紀念號為57/120，連同Schneider Super-Angulon 5.6/90mm XL (#15030270)鏡頭、取景器及鏡頭前蓋，成色極新，機背印有 “1887-2007 120 Years Linhof Germany” 字樣，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2980', 'Linhof Master 45 Gold Edition 100 Jahre 1887-1987', 'Linhof Master 45 Gold Edition 100 Jahre 1887-1987', '36', '/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a25/LOTNO_308_7.jpg', '308', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'In commemoration of Linhof 100th anniversary, 100 sets Limited edition of Linhof Master 45 Gold edition was produced, the commemorative number is 009. Camera  in excellent condition, very rare!', '由德國製造的林可夫相機，是屬於大畫幅相機中全球第一大品牌。為紀念林可夫公司 100 週年而推出的林可夫Master 45镀金紀念機, 限量100台。此機紀念號是009。 此款是林可夫相機中的經典款式，機身鍍以24K镀金更令本來精確的工藝品更見罕貴。機身成色良好，操作正常，屬收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2981', 'Replica in Half Scale in 24 Carat Plate Finish Outfit', 'Replica in Half Scale in 24 Carat Plate Finish Outfit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_1a.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/1_6.jpg', '1', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Half scale Ur-Leica (#NR-0111), Leica I (#NR-1111), Leica IIIf (#NR-2111), Leica 250GG (#NR-3111) and Leica M3 (# NR-4111) in new condition.', '徠卡製造史上最經典機型的半比例模型，包括徠卡原型機Ur-Leica (#NR-0111) ﹑ Leica I (#NR-1111) ﹑ Leica IIIf (#NR- 2111) ﹑ Leica 250GG (#NR-3111) 及 Leica M3 (# NR-4111)。 機身鍍以24K 黃金，配置可伸縮鏡頭及配件；全球發行999 套，極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2982', 'Ur-Leica Dummy', 'Ur-Leica Dummy', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/2_1.jpg', '2', '', '4,956', null, null, null, null, 'Dummy Camera of Ur-Leica, engraved “Nachbildung der Ur- Leica” on the top. Like new with box.', '徠卡第一台135 格式相機於1913 年問世，此機正是它的複 製品。 機頂刻有“Nachbildung der Ur-Leica”。 成色接近全新， 有包裝。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2983', 'O-Series Replica, Serial no. 2677565', 'O-Series Replica, Serial no. 2677565', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/3_1.jpg', '3', '', '11,210', null, null, null, null, 'Only 2000 units made. Comes with Anastigmat 3.5/50mm, with leather case, papers, box, in brand new condition.', '於2000 年Photokina 推出， 限量2000 台。此機身連同 Anastigmat 3.5/50mm 鏡頭，並用上現代鍍膜技術，可以正 常使用。此套機連同包裝盒﹑皮套及證書，品相極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2984', 'I Mod. A(Copy)', 'I Mod. A(Copy)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/4_1.jpg', '4', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'With Anastigmat 3.5/50mm, 2x close-up lens, viewfinder, lens cap, film holder and case. With used marks.', '配 Anastigmat 3.5/50mm ﹑ 2x 近攝鏡﹑取景器﹑鏡頭蓋﹑菲 林匣及皮套。有明顯使用的痕跡，機身露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2985', 'I Mod. A Elmar', 'I Mod. A Elmar', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/5_1.jpg', '5', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Rare dimple shutter release, base-plate (open-close), with black painted cap. Well-functioning.', '少有的酒窩型快門按鈕，連 Elmar 3.5/50mm 伸縮鏡頭。連 原裝黑漆鏡頭蓋，非常值得收藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2986', 'I Mod. B Dial-Set Compur', 'I Mod. B Dial-Set Compur', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/6_1.jpg', '6', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'The production of Dial-set is only 637 pieces with used marks, in mint- condition.', '徠卡I Mod B Compur 產量只有約1500 台，當中分有Rim-set 及Dial-set，當中以Dial-set 產量最少，只有約637 台。 該機外型雖與Leica I 相似，但此相機配有鏡間快門及特別的酒窩型快門按鈕。而在鏡頭上獨特“Film Counter Lock”，在 Rim-set 上並沒有配備。此機歷史久遠，成色良好，屬收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2987', 'I Mod. B Rim Set Compur', 'I Mod. B Rim Set Compur', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/7_1.jpg', '7', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1928-1941, total 1072 pieces. In excellent condition.', '於1928-1941 年，共生產1072 台，此機成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2988', 'I Mod. C Standard Black', 'I Mod. C Standard Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/8_1.jpg', '8', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'I Mod. C Standard Black with three unnumbered lenses, matching with 11 o’clock nickel Elmar 3.5/50mm with front cap, black paint Elmar 4/9cm with case and both caps, black paint Elmar 4.5/135mm with maker’s box and both caps. All items are in mint- condition. Very rare.', '徠卡 Ic Standard 連三枚沒有鏡身序號的鏡頭，分別是鎳 Elmar 3.5/50mm 連前蓋﹑黑漆 Elmar 4/9cm 連皮筒與前後 蓋﹑黑漆 Elmar 4.5/135mm 連原廠紅色包裝盒與前後蓋。品 相極好，非常罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2989', 'Standard \'New York\'', '', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/9_1.jpg', '9', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Rare Standard ‘New York’ with Velostigmat 3.5/50mm (#488250), engraved “E. Leitz, Inc. New York” on front ring. Comes with cap, maker’s box. In mint- condition.', '罕有二戰後生產的 Standard ‘New York’, 有極輕微使用痕跡。此機連同 Velostigmat 3.5/50mm 鏡頭 (#488250), 鏡前刻有 “E. Leitz, Inc. New York” 字樣，連鏡頭蓋及紅色膠盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2990', 'I Mod. C Non-Standard', 'I Mod. C Non-Standard', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/10_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/10_2.jpg', '10', '', '377,600', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare original Non-Standard outfit. Includes Elmar 3.5/35mm with front cap, Elmar 4.5/135mm with rear cap and Hektor 2.5/50mm lenes (this Hektor lens is very few and rare, please refer to James Lager V. II P.34). All lens engraved “043” on the barrel, matching camera serial number, camera bottom plate engraved “auf-zu”, swing mask for 135mm; with FOFER rangefinder, VISOR torpedo finder and WINKO right angle finder and film container, everything in matching original outfit case. In excellent condition.', '十分珍貴的 I Mod. C Non-Standard 連 Elmar 3.5/35mm 與前蓋﹑ Elmar 4.5/135mm 與後蓋及Hektor 2.5/50mm 鏡頭( 這 枚Hektor 鏡頭最為罕見，詳情可參閱James Lager V. II p.34)。所有鏡身都刻有 “043” 機身號, 與機身相對應，相機底盤 刻有“auf-zu” 字樣。取景框前附有135mm 的變換框，連FOFER 測距﹑ VISOR ﹑ WINKO 取景器﹑菲林匣及原裝配套小 皮箱。此相機飾皮完好，如此配件齊全及成色良好的Non-Standard 是非常罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2991', 'Standard Chrome', 'Standard Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/11_1.jpg', '11', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with Summar 2/5cm (#484763), lens front cap. In mint condition.', '銀色Standard 機身配 Summar 2/5cm (#484763) 及鏡頭蓋， 成色優良，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2992', '250 GG', '250 GG', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/12_1.jpg', '12', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Introduced in 1939, before the WWII. For military and industrial used. This camera comes with Summar 2/5cm (#268523) and two film holders. With normal wear marks in good working condition.', '徠卡Reporter 250 GG 產於1939 年二次大戰前，當時為軍用及工業用相機；配 Summar 2/5cm (#268523)，及兩個膠卷匣。 正常磨損痕跡，功能良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2993', 'IIIa Chrome Summar', 'IIIa Chrome Summar', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/13_1.jpg', '13', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIa chrome body show signs of used, with Summar 2/5cm (#324532) in good working order. Comes with case and front lens cap.', '機身有正常磨損痕跡。配 Summar 2/5cm (#324532)，鏡頭 操作正常。連鏡頭前蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2994', 'IIIa with Hektor 2.5/5cm Repaint Gold', 'IIIa with Hektor 2.5/5cm Repaint Gold', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/14_1.jpg', '14', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Repainted gold with Hektor 2.5/5cm and lens cap, covered with red leather.', '後期鍍金的 IIIa 連 Hektor 2.5/5cm， 紅色飾皮，連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2995', 'III Mod. F Black Paint', 'III Mod. F Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/15_1.jpg', '15', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIf in black paint with Elmar 3.5/5cm (#461107) and Hektor 6.3/2.8cm (#495744) in mint condition, with both caps.', '黑漆Leica IIIf 配 Elmar 3.5/5cm (#461107) 連鏡頭前蓋及 Hektor 6.3/2.8cm (#495744) 連鏡頭前後蓋。成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2996', 'Leica 72 18 X 24mm Midland', 'Leica 72 18 X 24mm Midland', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/16_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/16_2.jpg', '16', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'In 18x24mm format, engraved “18 X 24” & “Midland Ontario” on top plate (please refer to James Lager V. I p. 78 for same model). Batch number from 357301 – 357450, only 150 pieces made in Midland Canada. This comes with front body cap, in mint- condition.', '徠卡72 是採用18 亳米x 24 毫米格式的相機，機頂位置刻有“18 X 24” 及 “Midland Ontario” 字樣 ( 可參考James Lager V. I p.78 介紹同款機型)。此機是加拿大 Midland 製造，而加拿大產的Leica72 批號由357301-357450，只有150 台。此機 連機身蓋，機身有輕微使用痕跡，如此良好成色在市面上極為罕見，屬收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2997', 'IIIf Betriebsk', 'IIIf Betriebsk', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/17_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/17_2.jpg', '17', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare camera for factory internal use. Engraved “Betriebsk. Nr.174” on top plate, with Summitar 2/5cm (#754825) and lens cap, in good working order.', '此機為稀有的徠卡工廠內部測試機，機頂刻有 “Betriebsk. Nr.174” 字樣，操作正常, 機械性能良好，有使用痕跡。連 Summitar 2/5cm (#754825) 及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2998', 'IIIf Chrome Prototype', 'IIIf Chrome Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/18_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/18_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/18_2_2_copy_672.jpg', '18', '', '2,832,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIf Red Dial experimental camera, early prototype design to what turned into the IIIg. showing F-type, synchronization and built-in bright line viewfinder, rear view showing combined rangefinder viewfinder eyepiece, and synchronization outlet in traditional location to the right side. This particular camera is pictured in James Lager V. I p.135.', '徠卡為生產 IIIg 而準備的Prototype 機身，具有獨特設計，紅色刻度，閃燈同步及明亮的加大取景框。其機身背後的測距 及取景結合成為同一個目鏡，且比正常較大，而閃燈同步插口則移到右邊。該機可能僅生產一台，並是本次拍賣會的焦點 之一。於 James Lager V. I 第135 頁中刊登出的正是同一台相機；成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('2999', 'IIIg Betriebsk', 'IIIg Betriebsk', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/19_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/19_1_2_copy_672.jpg', '19', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Leica IIIg chrome engraved “Betriebsk. Nr.256” on the top plate, with Summitar 2/5cm (#981379) and engraved “Leitz-Eigentum” on barrels, in mint condition and good working order.', '比較稀有的徠卡工廠內部測試機， 機頂刻有 “Betriebsk. Nr.256” 字樣。機內膠片背部鋼板有條紋狀，屬試驗用品。 配 Summitar 2/5cm (#981379) 及鏡頭蓋；鏡頭刻有 “Leitz- Eigentum” 字樣，成色優良，功能運作正常，收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3000', 'IIIg with Summicron 2/5cm', 'IIIg with Summicron 2/5cm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/20_1.jpg', '20', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'With Summicron 2/5cm (#1350409) lens, almost new condition in perfect working order with front lens cap and box.', '銀色 IIIg 連 Summicron 2/5cm (#1350409) 鏡頭，套機成色 完美，功能正常，飾皮完好，帶鏡頭蓋及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3001', 'Screw Mount Camera and lens (various)', 'Screw Mount Camera and lens (various)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/21_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/21＿1_copy_672.jpg', '21', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'If, chrome, serial no. 575899 with Leicavit and body cap. IIIg, chrome, serial no. 878826 with body cap. Summilux 1.4/50mm, serial no. 1691509, with hood, front cap, keeper, filter. Summicron 2/35mm, serial no. 1671863, with filter, lens cap, keeper. Super Angulon 4/21mm, serial no. 1604667, with filter(yellow), front cap, keeper, hood. 21mm chrome viewfinder in maker’s box. 3.5cm viewfinder in maker’s box. Leicavit for screw mount camera. Leicatime camera protector.', 'If, 銀色, 機身號 575899 連過片器及機身蓋。 IIIg, 銀色, 機身號 878826 連機身蓋。 Summilux 1.4/50mm, 機身號 1691509, 連遮光罩, 前蓋, 膠 盅及濾鏡。 Summicron 2/35mm, 機身號 1671863, 連前蓋, 膠盅及濾鏡 Super Angulon 4/21mm, 機身號1604667, 連遮光罩, 前蓋, 膠盅及黃色濾鏡。 21mm 銀色取景器連包裝外盒。 3.5cm 取景器連包裝外盒。 螺絲口相機用的過片器。 Leicatime 相機保護套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3002', 'Summaron SM 2.8/35mm', 'Summaron SM 2.8/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/22_1.jpg', '22', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare screw mount lens in early version. Engraved “W6/WF/0943 ↑”on barrel. The close-up focusing range is one meter. Complete with both caps in mint condition.', '早期的螺絲口鏡頭，鏡上刻有 “W6/WF/0943↑” 軍用字樣；最 近對焦距離為一米。連鏡頭前後蓋，成色良好，十分罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3003', 'Summilux Screw Mount and M Mount 1.4/50mm Chrome Set', 'Summilux Screw Mount and M Mount 1.4/50mm Chrome Set', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/23_1.jpg', '23', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'A pair of first type Chrome Summilux 1.4/50mm Screw Mount and M Mount lenses, serial numbers are #1641879 and #1546056 respectively, both with caps and keepers, in mint condition.', '一對第一代銀色 Summilux 1.4/50mm 螺絲口鏡頭(#1641879) 及 M 卡口鏡頭(#1546056) ，成色極新，連膠盅及鏡頭蓋， 十分稀有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3004', 'Summitar SM 2/5cm', 'Summitar SM 2/5cm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/24_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/24_2.jpg', '24', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Normally the serial number should be “Nr. 662448”, but it only engraved “N 662448”. Very rare, with perfect glasses, well working order.', '此鏡頭正常的編號應為“Nr. 662448”， 但此鏡僅刻有“N 662448”， 非常珍貴及罕有，鏡面完好，操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3005', 'Summar SM 2/5cm Nickel', 'Summar SM 2/5cm Nickel', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/25_1.jpg', '25', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Early Rigid Summar in nickel, in excellent condition, with both caps.', '早期 Rigid Summar 鎳鏡頭。連鏡頭前後蓋，成色良好， 較 為少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3006', 'Leitz Velostigmat SM 3.5/50mm', 'Leitz Velostigmat SM 3.5/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/26_1.jpg', '26', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced by E. Leitz Inc, New York with “E. Leitz, Inc. New York” engraved on barrel,in mint condition with both caps.', '由徠茲紐約工廠生產，操作良好，外觀品相完美，鏡頭上刻 有 “E. Leitz, Inc. New York” 字樣。連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3007', 'Stemar 3.5/3.3cm with Elmar 3.5/5cm Outfit', 'Stemar 3.5/3.3cm with Elmar 3.5/5cm Outfit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/27_1.jpg', '27', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare stereo equipment. Comes with Stemar OISBO 3.5/3.3cm (#1124360) and caps. OIMPO beam splitter (#1376), 3.3cm viewfinder, everything are in original leather case; this outfit also comes with IMPUU Elmar 3.5/5cm projection lens, OIDYO Stereo finder in maker’s box and adapter. (Please refer to James Lager V. III p.285, 288 and 289.). In mint condition.', '立體鏡3.5/3.3cm (#1124360) 連遮光罩及鏡頭前蓋﹑ OIMPO 分束器 (#1376) ﹑ 3.3cm 取景器 ，配以原裝小皮箱。另外， 此立體鏡套裝還配備 Elmar 3.5/5cm 幻燈機用鏡頭﹑ OIDYO 立體取景器及轉接環。( 可參考James Lager V. III p.285 ﹑ 288 及289 中介紹)。如此配備齊全的立體鏡套裝相當罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3008', 'Hektor SM 1.9/7.3cm Black/Chrome', 'Hektor SM 1.9/7.3cm Black/Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/28_1.jpg', '28', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'Black/Chrome, with hood and both caps, used marks in excellent condition.', '黑漆及銀色組合。有使用痕跡，運作良好。 連鏡頭前後蓋﹑ 遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3009', 'Summicron SM 2/9cm SOOZI (Pre-series)', 'Summicron SM 2/9cm SOOZI (Pre-series)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/29_1.jpg', '29', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, barrel engraved “Germany”. The serial number indicates the production of 1953, four years before the SOOZI was officially introduced and the out look is different from the official one. (Refer to James Lager V.II p.72). In mint condition, with both caps.', '非常珍貴，鏡身刻有“Germany” 字樣，產於德國，鏡身編號 顯示出產年份為1953 年，比“SOOZI” 正式投入生產早四年 ( 請參考James Lager V. II p.72) 。此鏡頭比正式生產的鏡頭， 鏡身較短，調焦環較窄，光圈讀數刻於鏡身， 而非刻于調焦 環，品相極好，配鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3010', 'Elmar SM 4/9cm Prototype', 'Elmar SM 4/9cm Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/30_1.jpg', '30', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Rare Elmar 4/9cm, prototype of the 3-element Elmar, engraved “Eigentum der Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar”, from a small batch of approx. 50 lenses, (a similar lens is illustrated in James Lager V. II p.126), in mint condition.', '非常稀有的 Elmar 4/9cm，鏡身刻有“Eigentum der Ernst Leitz GmbH Wetzlar”( 徠茲工廠資產) 字樣 ，大約只生產50 支，類似 鏡頭在 James Lager V. II p.126 中有介紹)。此鏡品相極好，連前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3011', 'Thambar SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', 'Thambar SM 2.2/9cm Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/31_1.jpg', '31', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with hood, hood cap, spot filter and rear cap in mint condition, very rare.', '徠卡唯一的人像柔焦效果鏡頭，附件完整( 含原廠柔焦反射 濾鏡﹑遮光罩﹑遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋)。該鏡頭產量非常少， 成色極好，如此成色在市面罕見，為收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3012', 'Elmar 4.5/10.5cm Compur', 'Elmar 4.5/10.5cm Compur', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/32_1.jpg', '32', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare Elmar 4.5/10.5cm Compur, please refer to James Lager V.II p128.', '較為少有的鏡間快門鏡頭， 在James Lager V.II 的 Atypical Screw Mount Lenses 部分第 128 頁中有介紹。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('3013', 'Elmar SM 6.3/10.5cm Black/Nickel', 'Elmar SM 6.3/10.5cm Black/Nickel', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/33_1.jpg', '33', '', '10,030', null, null, null, null, 'This black/nickel Elmar in good condition, a minor scratch on the first element. Comes with both caps and original hood.', '由黑漆與鎳組成 Elmar 鏡頭，歷史久遠，在第一片玻璃位置 有輕微劃痕。連鏡頭前後蓋及原裝遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3014', 'Hektor SM 2.5/12.5cm, Serial no. 1760153', 'Hektor SM 2.5/12.5cm, Serial no. 1760153', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/34_1.jpg', '34', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, '“feet” and “meter” were shown on depth of field scale. In mint condition with clean lens, both caps and hood.', '徠茲後期生產的 Hektor 鏡，鏡身罕有地同時以“ 尺” 及“ 米” 顯示，十分少見。此鏡品相極好，玻璃乾淨，連遮光罩及前 後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3015', 'M3 \"Chrome Muster 1\"', 'M3 \"Chrome Muster 1\"', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/35_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/35_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/35_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/35_4.jpg', '35', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M3 camera with top and bottom plate from a series of finish plating samples, circa 1955/56. When a change in chrome finish plating for Leica M3 was discussed among a relevant board of officers at Leitz Wetzlar in about 1955/56, several sets of parts for two different versions of chrome plating were produced. Those were marked “Chrom Muster 1” and “Chrom Muster 2”. The camera for sale here equipped with parts engraved “Chrom Muster 1”, the bottom plate engraved internally. The shutter crate with a cartouche for the place of the internal serial number. A similar unit is pictured in Shinichi Nakamura “Leica Collection” on page 36, this camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '於1955/56 年其間, 徠卡生產了一批M3 供內部使用, 該批M3 刻有“Chrom Muster 1” 或 “Chrom Muster 2”, 分別指兩種不 同的銀色。而此機的機頂及底蓋內都同樣刻有 “Chrom Muster 1” 字樣; 而快門附近則有內部使用的機身號碼, 十分罕有。 類似此機照片可參閱 Shinichi Nakamura “ Leica Collection” 書中第36 頁; 此相機已經由Lars Netopil 驗證為真品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3016', 'M3 Black Paint with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'M3 Black Paint with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/36_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/36_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/36_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/36_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/36_5.jpg', '36', '', '519,200', null, null, null, null, 'Original M3 Black Paint, with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#1897227), in mint condition. Comes with box and lens cap.', '經典的M3 黑漆機身，單次過片；配黑漆Summilux-M 1.4/50mm (#1897227)。整套相機外觀成色幾乎全新，如此完美成 色的M3 黑漆套機極少出現於拍賣會上；連包裝及鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3017', 'M3 Black Paint Single Stroke', 'M3 Black Paint Single Stroke', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/37_1.jpg', '37', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1963, single stroke with body cap and normal used marks.', '此M3 產於1963 年，屬單次過片，原裝黑漆。帶機身蓋；有明顯 使用痕跡，局部露銅，更顯經典。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3018', 'M3 Black Paint, Serial no. 1157597', 'M3 Black Paint, Serial no. 1157597', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/38_1.jpg', '38', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'Rare, classic black painted M3, single stroke with body cap, used marks in good condition.', '經典的M3 原裝黑漆機身，屬單次過片，甚為罕有。帶機身蓋； 機身部分露銅，是絕佳收藏品之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3019', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/39_1.jpg', '39', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'Early double stroke M3 from the second year of production with all original features in perfect working order, clean and clear finder, shutter accurate. Complete with original leather case, body cap, matching serial number red maker’s box and papers.', '早期的M3 相機，有兩次過片的功能特性，過片杆較短。 快門速度準確，布幕完好，玻璃壓片，取景框明亮通透， 機身飾皮完好無損；成色如新。如此完美成色實為罕見， 屬收藏珍品。配原裝相機皮套﹑機身蓋﹑與機身號相同的 原廠紅色包裝盒及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3020', 'M3 Chrome', 'M3 Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/40_1.jpg', '40', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Single stroke with box, body cap and papers. In like new condition.', 'M3銀色機身，屬單次過片。連包裝盒﹑機身蓋及證書；成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3021', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', 'M3 Chrome Double Stroke', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/41_1.jpg', '41', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Early double stroke with all original features in perfect working order, clean and clear finder, shutter accurate. Complete with original leather case, body cap and box.', '早期的M3 相機，兩次過片。快門速度準確，布幕完好， 取景框明亮通透，機身飾皮完好無損；成色如新。如此完 美成色實為罕見，屬收藏珍品。配原裝相機皮套﹑機身蓋 及包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3022', 'MP Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm and Leicavit', 'MP Chrome with Summicron-M 2/5cm and Leicavit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/42_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/42_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/42_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/42＿3_copy_672.jpg', '42', '', '826,000', null, null, null, null, 'Early MP Chrome, only 449 pieces were made in 1957, out of 311 pieces are in chrome. The serial number is matching with the number inside of the body. This camera comes with matching Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1466063) and MP Leicavit. In mint condition, extremely rare.', '早期的MP 銀色，於1957 年生產，當年僅生產449 台，其中311 台為銀色。此機機內的號碼與機身號相同，連同期的 Summicron-M 2/5cm (#1466063)，MP Leicavit，該機成色優良，是徠卡收藏者不可缺少的收藏機種。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3023', 'M2 Chrome Consecutive Number', 'M2 Chrome Consecutive Number', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/43_1.jpg', '43', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'A pair of M2 Chrome consecutive numbers. Both come with Elmar 3.5/3.5cm (#1596786 and #1563747) and lens front caps, in mint condition. Very rare.', '十分罕有的相連序號M2 對機，各帶有 Elmar 3.5/3.5cm 鏡頭 (#1596786 及#1563747) 及鏡頭前蓋。操作正常，成色極好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3024', 'M2 Chrome', 'M2 Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/44_1.jpg', '44', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Early version M2 Chrome with button rewind and self-timer. Made in Canada, with big “M2” which is very rare. Comes with body cap. In good working order. With used marks.', '早期大字M2 銀色，按鈕回片並有自拍，加拿大產， 此機市面較少。功能正常，有使用痕跡，帶機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3025', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/45_1.jpg', '45', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Early model M2 black paint with lever rewind, without selftimer, normal used marks. In good operation condition with body cap.', '早期M2黑漆，不帶自拍，撥杆回片，極為罕見。有使用痕跡， 運作暢順，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3026', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/46_1.jpg', '46', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Original black painted M2 with self-timer, good working condition, with cap.With used marks.', '原裝黑漆M2，帶自拍功能，運作良好連機身蓋。有使用痕跡， 機身部份露銅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3027', 'M2 Black Paint', 'M2 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/47_1.jpg', '47', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'Original M2 Black Paint with self-timer. “Chuck Sleeper” is engraved on top plate. Mint- condition with body cap, all packing, papers, well functioning.', '原裝黑漆M2，機身刻有“Chuck Sleeper” 字。帶自拍功能， 操作順暢，連機身蓋﹑包裝﹑證書及說明書，成色很好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3028', 'M2-M', 'M2-M', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/48_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/48_3.jpg', '48', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'Can work with Leitz New York motor, batch number are from 1163771 – 1164046, 275 pieces made. In like new condition, Very rare.', 'M2-M 作為能搭配Leitz New York 電動馬達使用的機種，於 機底位置有四個電子觸點。生產序號為1163771 - 1164046， 共275 台；此機成色極新，功能正常，如此優異成色在市場 上比較稀有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3029', 'M2A, M3A, M4A, M5A', 'M2A, M3A, M4A, M5A', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/49_1.jpg', '49', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'Serial no. 13029A,12627A ,209A, A512, N/A, Dummy set, M2A (#13029A) with cap, M3A (#12627A) with cap, M4A (#209A), M5A (#A512) with cap, in good condition.', '徠卡的Dummy 機，該收藏者依次序集齊M2A (#13029A) 連 蓋,M3A (#12627A) 連蓋, M4A (#209A),M5A (#A512) 連蓋； 共四件，較為少有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3030', 'M1 “Sonderausfuhrung” Consecutive numbers', 'M1 “Sonderausfuhrung” Consecutive numbers', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/50_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/50_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/50_3.jpg', '50', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare pair of unusual M1 Chrome in consecutive numbers, the cameras lack the viewfinder, in factory records indicate “Sonderausfuhrung” (special fitting), (please refer to James Lager V. I P215, 216), only dozens pieces made. Body # 979744 comes with body cap; the other one #979745 comes with body cap and maker’s box. Both in mintcondition.', '此對相連號的M1 對機極為罕見和特別， 外觀特徵像MD，沒 有取景框，此批相機在工廠的記錄是“Sonderausfuhrung”( 特 別組合）（在 James Lager V.I P215,216 有介紹), 只產幾十 部，能在僅有的幾十部中找到一對相連號的機會更是絕無僅 有。兩部相機有使用痕跡，機身編號#979744 配有機身蓋； 而機身編號#979745 則配有機身蓋及原廠包裝盒。極為稀 少。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3031', 'Leica M4 (M5) Prototype', 'Leica M4 (M5) Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/51_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/51_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/51_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/51_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/51_5.jpg', '51', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original factory prototype M-camera with built-in TTL light meter. This camera was projected around 1965 as M4. However, research and development took another six years, until the camera was finally launched as M5. Already giving the idea of the later M5 design, the camera shows many differences in individual technical details, such as the rewind-crank operated from the camera body side, instead from the top plate, through-the-lens metering.This particular camera is published in Paul Henry van Hasbroeck \"Leica, an illustrated history, revised and updated edition\", on plate XXXIV of the colour plates. Complete with Leitz Wetzlar prototype lens 1:2/50 Nr. 0000460. The lens head is of an early experimental state, with diaphragmindex hand-engraved. Most probably from optical bench testing. Optical formula B679. Leitz produced three such lens heads with serial numbers 0000459-0000461 between November 1960 and February 1961. The lens head here mounted in a later serial production helicoil from Summilux 50mm. This camera and lens have been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '十分稀有的徠茲M 系列的Prototype 連同內置測光功能。1965 年工廠計畫將此台機器設計為M4， 但由於研製和開發的時 間很長，在M4(1967 年) 正式投入生產前還未完成設計。直到1971 年才把這部Protorype 的一些概念加到M5 的生產中， 整個過程整整花了6 年，此Prototpye 的產量比M3 Prototype 稀少。此機器與其他M 機的設計有所分別，捲片器由頂部 改為在機身側面, 通過鏡頭測光。此相機的介紹及圖片亦刊於 Paul Henry van Hasbroeck 的“Leica, an illustrated history, 更新版” 一書彩色圖頁XXXIV 中。此相機配有徠卡1:2/50 原型版鏡頭, 編號為Nr. 0000460。此鏡頭是屬早期測驗版，光 圈數字是手工雕刻。徠卡於1960 年11 月到1961 年2 月期間, 共生產三枚測試用的鏡頭, 鏡頭光學技術為B679, 編號由 0000459-0000461. 此相機及鏡頭已經過 Lars Netopil 鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3032', 'M4 Black Paint', 'M4 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/52_1.jpg', '52', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'This black paint camera in good working order and normal used marks, with body cap.', '此台黑漆的M4 產於1968-1969 年間。有明顯使用痕跡，操 作正常，連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3033', 'M4-M Black Paint with Motor', 'M4-M Black Paint with Motor', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/53_1.jpg', '53', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'This Black Paint M4 with motor (#02258). In good working order, with body cap and normal used marks.', '此台黑漆M4 連馬達 (#02258) 產於1969 年，距今已有40 多 年歷史。表面有輕度使用痕跡，操作正常連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3034', 'M4-P Chrome \'70 Years\' with Summicron-M 2/35mm Black', '', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/54_1.jpg', '54', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'In 1983 Leica issued chrome M4-P‘s to commemorate 70 years of Leica dating from Oscar Barnack’s first prototype in 1913. The back of the top plate and barrel of the lens were engraved “Leica 1913-1983”, special number A284, with Summicron-M 2/35mm (#3182198), complete with filter, hood, hood cap, body cap, all papers in maker’s box。', '為慶祝 1913 年第一台 135 相機誕生 70 週年而生產,此套相 機紀念號為 A284。連 Summicron-M 2/35mm (#3182198)。 相機頂蓋上和鏡頭鏡身刻有 “Leica 1913-1983”。連包裝盒、 濾鏡、遮光罩與遮光罩蓋、機身蓋、證書;成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3035', 'M4-P Black', 'M4-P Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/55_1.jpg', '55', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Produced in 1982, complete with body cap, strap, all packing and papers in new condition.', '此機產於 1982 年,連機身蓋及相機尼龍帶,包裝證書全齊, 全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3036', 'M6 Classic Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Titanium, Serial no. 1918211', 'M6 Classic Titanium with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Titanium, Serial no. 1918211', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/56_1.jpg', '56', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'M6 Titanium covered with ostrich leather on body with all packaging, papers and normal used marks. Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#3795335) in titanium. Complete with filter, hood, hood cap, front cap, boxes and papers in mint condition.', 'M6 鈦金版, 機身覆蓋鴕鳥皮飾皮, 連包裝證書, 機身有輕 微 使 用 痕 跡。Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#3795335) 鈦 金版,連濾鏡,遮光罩,遮光罩蓋,鏡頭蓋,包裝證書, 成 色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3037', 'M6 Classic Black', 'M6 Classic Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/57_1.jpg', '57', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'Early M6 Classic, comes with packing and strap. In mint condition.', '早期的 M6 Classic;帶包裝及背帶,成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3038', 'MP 6 Chrome', 'MP 6 Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/58_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/58_2.jpg', '58', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare MP 6 Chrome was produced less than 20 pieces, with body cap and box. Mint condition.', '十分罕見的 MP6 銀色,估計生產不超過二十台,極為罕有;連機身蓋及內盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3039', 'MP 6 Black Paint', 'MP 6 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/59_1.jpg', '59', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Only 380 pieces were produced, very rare. With body cap in good condition and well-functioning.', '此機為 MP6 黑漆版,僅生產了 380 台。品相極佳,性能完好,連機身蓋。使用和收藏皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3040', 'M6A Black', 'M6A Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/60_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/60_1_copy_672(1).jpg', '60', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'This camera is M7 prototype. Engraved “LEICA M6 A” on the hot shoe, very rare and with body cap, in perfect condition.', 'M6 A 為 M7 的 Prototype,在快門速度轉盤上有光圈優先模式。於機頂熱靴上刻有 “LEICA M6 A” 字樣,屬罕有機種。機內菲林匣有電子接點,機身品相接近完美,極具收藏價值;連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3041', 'M7 0.72 Chrome', 'M7 0.72 Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/61_1.jpg', '61', '', '16,520', null, null, null, null, 'Chrome body in mint- condition and well-functioning. With packing, papers and strap.', '成色優良,運作順暢。連包裝、證書及尼龍帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3042', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint', 'MP 0.72 Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/62_1.jpg', '62', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Black paint MP with 0.72 frame line, comes with body cap, in mint- condition.', '現行版黑漆 MP 機身配以 0.72 線框,性能完好,連機身蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3043', 'M Monochrome Silver Prototype', 'M Monochrome Silver Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/63_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/63_2.jpg', '63', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare, chrome Monochrome body should be prototype, only few pieces were made. There are no any engraving on top plate and hot-shoe. Complete with battery, charger, body cap and inner box.', '徠卡於 2012 年 Photokina 上推出黑白機 (Monochrome),只有黑色機身投入生產,此台銀色機身應該是 Prototype,產量 估計只有數台,機頂及熱靴位置均沒有刻上 “Monochrome” 字樣或任何編號,極度稀有。連電池、充電器、機身蓋及包裝 內盒,收藏價值非常高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3044', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm, Serial no. 5736109', 'Hologon-M 8/15mm, Serial no. 5736109', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/64_1.jpg', '64', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'Rare like new lens from a small batch of approx. 350 pieces only. Comes with viewfinder, center filter, both caps, certificate and matching serial number box.', '總共生產 350 枝,極其稀有,此鏡頭成色如新。連取景器及中灰,包裝盒編號與鏡頭號對應。鏡頭前後蓋及證書齊全。如 此配備齊全,成色優良的鏡頭實為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3045', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm ASPH Chrome', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/65_1.jpg', '65', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Mint condition with hood, hood caps, both lens caps, leather case and original maker’s box, discontinued.', '銀色 Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm 非球面玻璃鏡頭,鏡身由黃銅製 成,品相極好。連原裝包裝盒、皮套、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋、 鏡頭後蓋,此款鏡頭現已停產。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3046', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm ASPH Black', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/21mm ASPH Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/66_1.jpg', '66', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'In like new condition, with 21mm viewfinder (#12008), hood, hood cap and both caps, case, papers and box.', '幾 乎 全 新 的 黑 色 非 球 面 玻 璃 鏡 頭, 連 21mm 取 景 器 (#12008) 、遮光罩、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭前後蓋、皮筒、證書, 包裝齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3047', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/24mm ASPH Chrome', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/24mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/67_1.jpg', '67', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'In like new condition with hood, hood cap, both caps, leather case and maker’s box. Discontinued.', '銀色 Elmarit-M 2.8/24mm 非球面玻璃鏡頭,鏡身由黃銅製 成,品相極好,現已停產。連原裝包裝盒、皮套、遮光罩與 遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3048', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/68_1.jpg', '68', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'First version of Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm, nine elements, made in Germany. Normal used marks, with hood (#12501M) and rear cap.', '第一代 Elmarit-M 2.8/28mm,九枚玉經典名鏡,德國製造。 是徠卡最值得收藏的廣角鏡頭之一。鏡身有使用痕跡。連遮 光罩 (#12501M) 及後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3049', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/69_1.jpg', '69', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'Only 500 pieces made in chrome, very rare. Complete with both caps, papers, case and maker\'s box in like new condition.', '銀色鏡身,只生產 500 枝,產量稀少。成色接近全新。連原 裝包裝盒、皮筒、鏡頭前後蓋及證書全齊。屬收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3050', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Prototype', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/70_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/70_2.jpg', '70', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'The prototype of M28-35-50/4 E49, the diametr is difference to the current version E49 and early version, the front of the barrel made by special materials, with both lens caps, case, very rare.', '此鏡頭是 Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm E49 的試驗版;此鏡頭內的玻璃口徑均比產品編號 #11625 (E49) 或 #11890 (E55) 大, 鏡頭前部份是黑啞色特殊材質,十分罕有。連前後蓋及皮套。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3051', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm ASPH Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/71_1.jpg', '71', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'E49, like new condition, comes with original box, case, both caps and all papers.', 'E49 口徑,品相極好,連原裝包裝盒、皮套、鏡頭前後蓋及 證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3052', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Chrome Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Chrome Steel Rim', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/72_1.jpg', '72', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'The first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm chrome Steel Rim. With original filter, OLLUX hood and rear cap in mint- condition.', '第一代銀色 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm 鋼咀,產量甚少,長久 以來為收藏家一直追捧的目標。外觀品相完美,連原裝濾鏡、 OLLUX 遮光罩及後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3053', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Chrome Steel Rim', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Chrome Steel Rim', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/73_1.jpg', '73', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'The first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm chrome steel rim. Comes with OLLUX hood, both caps and box, in like new condition, extremely rare.', '第一代 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm 銀色鋼咀,產量甚少,長久 以來為收藏家一直追捧的目標。配 OLLUX 遮光罩,前後蓋, 包裝盒。外觀品相極新,非常珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3054', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Black', '37', '', '74', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'The first version of Summilux-M 1.4/35mm steel rim in black, used wear marks, with caps, box. Extremely rare.', '第一代黑色鋼咀,產量約數十支,異常珍貴。連前後蓋及包裝盒。在市面是非常罕見的珍藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3055', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm Steel Rim Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/75_1.jpg', '75', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Like new condition with goggles, OLLUX hood, both cap and box, extremely rare.', '銀色 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm 鋼咀眼鏡版,玻璃及外觀如新, 沒有劃痕,連眼鏡、 OLLUX 遮光罩,前後蓋及包裝盒,非常 珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3056', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/76_1.jpg', '76', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'With keeper, in mint- condition.', '黑色, 連膠盅, 有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3057', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/77_1.jpg', '77', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'Nine elements in five groups and two elements are ASPH, with a small batch of approx. 2000 units. This comes with box, leather case, both caps, hood (#12587), hood cap and papers, in mint condition.', '九片五組設計,其中兩片為非球面球玻璃,製作工序繁複, 產量只有約 2000 支,此鏡玻璃通透,鏡身有輕微使用痕跡, 配有包裝盒、皮筒、遮光罩 (#12587)、遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後 蓋及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3058', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPHERICAL', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/78_1.jpg', '78', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'Approx. 2000 pieces made. Comes with hood (#12587), hood cap, lens rear cap in mint- condition.', '九片五組的設計,其中有兩片為手磨非球面玻璃,製作工序 繁複,產量少,約有 2000 枝。此鏡頭玻璃通透,外觀品相良 好。配遮光罩 (#12587) 、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3059', 'Summilux-M 35/1.4 ASPH Black', 'Summilux-M 35/1.4 ASPH Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/79_1.jpg', '79', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with hood (#12588), hood cap, leather case, both caps, papers and packing. In mint- condition.', '此鏡頭連遮光罩 (#12588) 與遮光罩蓋、皮筒、鏡頭前後蓋、 包裝及證書;成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3060', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/80_1.jpg', '80', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Product code 11883,Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH chrome in like new condition, discontinued. With hood, hood cap, both caps, case, papers and box.', '銀色的 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm 非球面玻璃鏡頭是採用黃銅製 造。此鏡頭成色如新,已停產。帶皮套、鏡頭前後蓋、遮光 罩與遮光罩蓋、包裝、證書全齊。屬收藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3061', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH', 'Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/81_1.jpg', '81', '', '35,400', null, null, null, null, 'Latest version Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#11663). Clean glass in mint condition. With hood, hood cap and rear cap.', '最新版 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#11663) 非球面玻璃廣角鏡, 帶 6 bit。玻璃清澈,成色極新。連遮光罩、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭 後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3062', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements), Serial no. 1998772', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements), Serial no. 1998772', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/82_1.jpg', '82', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'The classic Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements , made in Germany. Cleaning marks on glass, in mint- condition with both caps and leather case.', '此鏡為徠卡 Summicron 系列中最傳奇的經典,德國生產,由 八片六組鏡頭組成,使用當時透光度和成本都相當高的螢石 鏡片製造,被用家稱為 “ 八枚玉 ”。玻璃有輕微的清潔痕跡, 外觀成色極佳,配鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3063', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/83_1.jpg', '83', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'The classic eight elements Summicron-M 2/35mm. Signs of used with both caps.', '“ 八枚玉 ” 為 Summicron 系列中最傳奇的經典作品;此鏡為 第一年生產的鏡頭,數量稀少,收藏價值極高。連鏡頭前後 蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3064', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (8 Elements)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/84_1.jpg', '84', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Classic Summicron lens of Leica. This Lens complete with keeper, lens cap & outer box in mint condition.', '徠卡 Summicron 中的經典鏡頭 “ 八枚玉 ”,此鏡連膠盅,鏡 頭前蓋及包裝盒,成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3065', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/85_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/85_2.jpg', '85', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Very few black Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements with infinity knob, in mint- condition, comes with IROOA hood, Hoya filter and both caps, very rare.', '德國生產的 Summicron-M 2/35mm 黑色八枚玉,產量極少。玻璃通透,無限遠鎖定鈕輕微露銅,外觀品相佳,市面已是 極為罕見。連 IROOA 遮光罩、 Hoya 濾鏡和鏡頭前後蓋,是收藏的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3066', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Black (8 Elements)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/86_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/86_2.jpg', '86', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Very few black Summicron-M 2/35mm eight elements in mint- condition, focus knob has used marks, with lens front cap and keeper. Very rare.', '德國生產的 Summicron-M 2/35mm 黑色八枚玉,產量極少。玻璃通透,無限遠鎖定鈕輕微露銅,外觀品相佳,市面已是 極為罕見。連同鏡頭前蓋及膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3067', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 Elements)', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm Chrome (7 Elements)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/87_1.jpg', '87', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Chrome Summicron-M 2/35mm seven elements in mint condition, with hood (#12526) and rear cap.', '銀色七枚玉,帶遮光罩 (#12526) 及鏡頭後蓋 , 成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3068', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/88_1.jpg', '88', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'In mint condition and good working order. Complete with box, hood, hood cap, both caps and leather case.', '非球面玻璃鏡頭,成色接近完美,調焦順滑。連包裝外盒、 遮光罩與遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3069', 'Elmarit-C 2.8/40mm Black', 'Elmarit-C 2.8/40mm Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/89_1.jpg', '89', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'Produced for Leica CL series, very rare and not even launched officially. Comes with front cap, keeper in mint condition.', 'Elmarit-C 鏡頭適用於徠卡 CL 機,產量極少甚至沒有被正式 推出,十分罕見。此鏡成色近乎完美;有鏡頭前蓋及保護膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3070', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/90_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/90_2.jpg', '90', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, with a small batch of approx. 1500 units only. Complete with original matching number box, paper, keeper and lens front cap in mint condition.', '產量稀少,只有 1500 支左右。當中有兩片手磨非球面玻璃,製作過程繁複。此鏡頭調焦流暢,沒有離膠,外觀成色完美。 配與鏡頭號碼相同的原廠包裝盒、證書、膠盅及鏡頭前蓋。如此品相及配件齊全,在市面上已經愈見稀有,是收藏家必納 入囊中之物。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3071', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/91_1.jpg', '91', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare, with a small batch of approx. 1500 units made only. Scratches on the rear glass, comes with cap, keeper in mint- condition.', '此鏡為早期的徠卡 Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm,鏡頭產量稀少,約只生產 1500 枚。兩片手磨非球面玻璃,製作工序繁複。後組 玻璃有清潔痕跡,連同鏡頭前蓋及保護膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3072', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/92_1.jpg', '92', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'Built-in hood (E60) Noctilux-M 1/50mm, complete with box, leather case, both caps and papers, in new condition.', '第四代的 Noctilux-M 1/50mm 鏡頭,內置遮光罩,玻璃通透,調焦順暢,品相完美。配鏡頭前後蓋、皮筒、包裝及證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3073', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', 'Noctilux-M 1/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/93_1.jpg', '93', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'E60, third version Noctilux-M 1/50mm, comes with hood, filter and both caps, like new.', '第三代的 Noctilux-M 1/50mm 鏡頭,E60 口徑,連外置遮光罩、濾鏡、鏡頭前後蓋,成色完美。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3074', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', 'Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/94_2.jpg', '94', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'The current version Noctilux-M, brand new, never be opened.', '徠卡最新型最大光圈的 Noctilux-M 鏡頭,質素極佳。此鏡全新未經使用,包裝、證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3075', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/95_1.jpg', '95', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'Early version made in black paint and black chrome, with clean glass and very light used marks, comes with hood and keeper.', '早期生產的黑漆鏡頭;鏡身分別以黃銅及合金兩種金屬製造。鏡頭號碼與鏡身內號碼相同。有輕度使用痕跡。連遮光罩及 保護膠盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3076', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/96_1.jpg', '96', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'With Hood, hood cap and rear cap, in mint condition.', '連遮光罩與遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋,成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3077', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Gold Plated', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Gold Plated', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/97_1.jpg', '97', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'A rare gold plated version of Summilux M-1.4/50mm lens. Complete with lens hood, hood cap, rear cap, matching number box and papers in new condition.', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm 的鍍金版,有遮光罩、鏡頭後蓋及包 裝證書。全新未經使用,十分罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3078', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', 'Summilux-M 1.4/50mm Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/98_1.jpg', '98', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'The second version of Leica Summilux-M 1.4/50mm lens in chrome. Comes with hood (#12586), hood cap, lens rear cap, in mint condition.', '此鏡為徠卡第二代 Summilux-M 1.4/50mm 鏡頭,銀色鏡頭以 黃銅製造,採用兩組複合黏合鏡片,光學質素佳。鏡頭連同 遮光罩 (#12586) 、遮光罩蓋及鏡頭後蓋,成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3079', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Prototype', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/99_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/99_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/99_3.jpg', '99', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar rare original factory prototype lens Summicron-M 2/50mm, Nr. 0000909. Black anodized mount, the lens front element holding ring of different from the serial production finish. Six-element design \"C155\". Between July 1966 and May 1967 Leitz produced six of such prototype lenses, numbers 0000909-0000914, before the lens was commercially introduced in 1969. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '非常稀有的徠茲 Summicron-M 2/50mm 原型鏡, 編號為 0000909, 此鏡卡口為電鍍黑色, 而鏡頭前玻璃固定環亦與後期 版 “C155” 有所不同的六片設計, 於 1969 年 Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭正式發佈前, 徠卡在 1966 年 7 月至 1967 年 5 月期間, 共生產了 6 枚類似此鏡的原型鏡 , 編號為 0000909-0000914。此鏡頭是經過 Lars Netopil 鑑定。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3080', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/100_1.jpg', '100', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Early Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid in black paint, made in Germany, in mint- condition. Comes with both caps and filter, matching serial number with inside of the lens.', '早期的 Summicron-M 2/50mm Rigid 黑漆鏡頭,由德國製造。 鏡身以黃銅及合金製成,成色良好,非常罕見。鏡身內的號 碼與鏡頭號相同,連鏡頭前後蓋及濾鏡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3081', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Black Paint, Serial no. 1587441', 'Summicron-M 2/5cm Black Paint, Serial no. 1587441', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/101_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/101_2.jpg', '101', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'Early black paint lens with brass mount, lens number on barrel is matching with the serial number inside of the lens, with both caps and haze in lens.', '為黑漆的早期產品,鏡頭後卡口為黃銅色,產量稀少,鏡身內的號碼和鏡頭號碼相同。鏡身分別以黃銅及鎂合金兩種金屬 物料所造,並連同鏡頭前後蓋,十分稀有,玻璃內有霧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3082', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black, Serial no. 2439145', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black, Serial no. 2439145', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/102_1.jpg', '102', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'The focusing ring and focusing scale is in black paint and its engraving on focusing ring and aperture scale is bigger than usual . With used marks, hood, hood cap and keeper.', '調焦環及刻度尺為黑漆,而調焦環及光圈數位字體比正常大, 十分罕見。外觀有輕微使用痕跡,連遮光罩、遮光罩蓋及膠 盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3083', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint Dummy', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Black Paint Dummy', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/103_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/103_2.jpg', '103', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare early version Summicron 2/50mm black paint rigid dummy lens, chrome focus knob. Unnumbered, in like new condition .', '早期 Summicron-M 2/50mm 的 Rigid Dummy 黑漆鏡頭,調焦按扭是特別的銀色設計 ; 鏡頭上沒有編號。是市面上極為罕 見的黑漆 Dummy 鏡頭 , 成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3084', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Chrome', 'Summicron-M 2/50mm Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/104_1.jpg', '104', '', '10,620', null, null, null, null, 'Built-in hood with lens both caps, leather case in mint condition.', '銀色 M 系列標準鏡頭,內置遮光罩連皮筒,帶前後蓋,玻璃 通透,成色完美。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3085', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/105_1.jpg', '105', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Second version of Summilux-M 1.4/75mm, made in Canada with built-in hood. Comes with both caps and matching number outer box, in mint condition, good working order.', '第二代鏡頭 Summilux-M1.4/75mm 於加拿大生產,連內置遮 光罩。外觀及玻璃近乎完美,連同鏡頭前後蓋及與機身編號 相同包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3086', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', 'Summilux-M 1.4/75mm Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/106_1.jpg', '106', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Second version of Summilux-M 1.4/75mm, made in Canada with built-in hood. Comes with both caps and matching number outer box in mint condition, good working order.', '第二代 Summilux-M 1.4/75mm 鏡頭於加拿大生產,連內置遮 光罩。此鏡調焦暢順,功能正常,外觀及玻璃近乎完美,連 同鏡頭前後蓋及與機身編號相同原裝包裝盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3087', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome SOOZI', 'Summicron-M 2/9cm Chrome SOOZI', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/107_1.jpg', '107', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'A rare Midland SOOZI with both caps in chrome, hood and the matching serial number box, in mint condition.', 'Midland SOOZI,連遮光罩。鏡身成色極好,調焦順暢,連 銀色鏡頭前後蓋及相同號碼的包裝盒,市面罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3088', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black', 'Summicron-M 2/90mm Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/108_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/108_2.jpg', '108', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'Second version of Summicron-M 2/90mm lens (E55), made in Canada. Built-in hood, cones with both caps, matching serial no. box and papers, in new condition.', '加拿大製的第二代後期鏡頭,口徑為 E55,有內置遮光罩。此鏡頭 連同前後蓋、與機身編號相同包裝及證書全齊,成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3089', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Chrome', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/109_1.jpg', '109', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'The chrome version was discontinued and very rare in the market. This lens comes with both caps and leather case, in mint condition.', '銀色的鏡身由黃銅製造,擁有消色差 (APO) 及非球面玻璃 (ASPH)。銀色已停產,市面較為罕見。此鏡成色極好,調焦 操作順暢。連鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3090', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/110_1.jpg', '110', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Like new condition with original box, case, both caps and all papers.', '此鏡頭擁有消除色差 (APO) 及非球面鏡片的中長焦鏡頭。成 色接近完美,連原裝盒、皮套、鏡頭前後蓋及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3091', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black', 'APO-Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/111_1.jpg', '111', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, '6 bit , In mint condition with case and both caps.', '同時擁有消除色差 (APO) 及非球面玻璃的中長焦鏡頭,帶 6 bit;鏡片清澈,外觀極新;連鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3092', 'Elmar-M 4/90mm (Pre-Series)', 'Elmar-M 4/90mm (Pre-Series)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/112_1.jpg', '112', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'Pre-series lens, a bit yellow on glass coating, slope angle of the lens front number ring (it should be flat in usual), Engraved \"LENS MADE IN GERMANY\" on lens body. All of these features are different from the normal products. Comes with hood, hood cap and keeper.', '此鏡頭為正式生產前的小批量試產鏡頭,玻璃鍍膜較黃,鏡 頭前數字號碼環為斜角度 ( 正常的應為平面 ),鏡身前面的光 圈數字環較凹入,鏡身刻上 \"LENS MADE IN GERMANY\" ; 以上特徵均有別於後期正式投產產品,是收藏佳品。連遮光 罩、遮光罩蓋及保護盅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3093', 'Elmar-M 4/90mm Chrome', 'Elmar-M 4/90mm Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/113_1.jpg', '113', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'One of the famous lens in 90mm focus length, composed by three glasses. Very light used marks, comes with both caps.', '此鏡是 90mm 焦段名鏡之一,由三片玻璃組成。鏡頭有輕微 使用痕跡,連鏡頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3094', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Prototype, Serial no. 321-145', 'Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Prototype, Serial no. 321-145', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/114_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/114_2.jpg', '114', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Canada are original factory prototype lens Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm Nr. 321-145. With built-in sunshade. Most probably a four element design, late 1970s/early 1980s. Two other specimens of this lens have been recorded, numbers 321-006 and 321-027. This lens has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '徠茲加拿大廠生產的黑色原型鏡 Elmarit-M 2.8/90mm,鏡頭號碼為 321-145,內置遮光罩。於 1970 年後期及 1980 年前期 生產,大多為四片玻璃組合設計,此款的另外兩枚鏡頭亦被紀錄,編號為 321-006 和 321-027。此鏡頭已由 Lars Netopil 鑒認。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3095', 'Telyt-M 8/400mm Prototype', 'Telyt-M 8/400mm Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/115_1.jpg', '115', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Experimental 8/400mm with tube focusing. This was eventually developed into 6.8/400mm Telyt lens. Another consecutive number (#0000684) to this lens illustrated in Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck P.178. It comes with both caps. Very rare.', '管狀對焦的 8/400mm 原型鏡是後期 6.8/400mm 的試驗版。 與此鏡相連號 (#0000684) 在 Paul-Henry van Hasbroeck 書 中第 178 頁中有介紹。此鏡外觀完美,連鏡頭前後蓋,較為 少見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3096', 'Leica III (Kripo Chemnitz)', 'Leica III (Kripo Chemnitz)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/116_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/116_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/116_3.jpg', '116', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'This model is made for Germany Criminal Police, comes with Summar 2/5cm(#208758), the back of top plate and lens barrel engraved “Kripo Chemnitz”, without serial number, with original lens cap and keeper. This item has been bided in Nineties in Christie’s auction.', '黑漆機身 , 此機是徠卡提供給德國刑事警員使用的相機,機頂沒有編號。在機背面刻有 “Kripo Chemnitz” 字樣。配 Summar 2/5cm (#208758)。鏡頭亦同樣刻有 “Kripo Chemnitz” 字樣。連原裝鏡頭蓋及膠盒,極為罕有。此機曾在九十年代 於佳士得拍賣會中被拍賣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3097', 'IIIc Chrome \"Luftwaffen-Eigentum\"', 'IIIc Chrome \"Luftwaffen-Eigentum\"', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/117_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/117_2.jpg', '117', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Produced for German Air Force, comes with Elmar 3.5/5cm, engraved “FL. No_38079” on the top plate, and “Luftwaffen- Eigentum” on the back of the camera, comes with ever- ready case, and lens cap in grey.', '供德國空軍使用的銀色 IIIc 連 Elmar 3.5/5cm 鏡頭。機頂刻有 “FL. No_38079” 字樣;而機背則刻有 “Luftwaffen-Eigentum”。 此相機有原裝啡色皮套;皮套上亦壓有 “Luftwaffen-Eigentum” 字樣。此機操作正常,成色良好,配灰色鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3098', 'IIIc Grey', 'IIIc Grey', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/118_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/118_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/118_3.jpg', '118', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'Original IIIc grey with Elmar 3.5/5cm, engraved with “Artl.” and Reichsadler on the back of the camera and lens, comes with lens cap and ever-ready case in grey, mint condition, extremely rare.', '原裝 IIIc 灰色機身連 Elmar 3.5/5cm 鏡頭,機頂背部及鏡身刻有 “Artl.” 字樣及納粹德國國旗圖案,屬德國炮軍所用。操作正常, 連鏡頭蓋及灰色皮套;成色極新,為收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3099', 'IIIcK with Summitar 2/5cm Grey', 'IIIcK with Summitar 2/5cm Grey', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/119_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/119_2.jpg', '119', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'The camera and leather both in grey, made in Germany, for German Air Force used. Engraved “K” follow the serial number; the engraved wording “Luftwaffen-Eigentum” had been removed from top plate and lens. Comes with Summitar 2/5cm (#564808) , lens cap and original camera case, cracks of body leather.', '相機和飾皮均是灰色,由德國製造,供德國空軍使用。序號後面刻有 “K” 字樣;而機頂、機背及鏡頭應刻有的 “Luftwaffen- Eigentum” 空軍字樣,已被後期移除。配有 Summitar 2/5cm 鏡頭 (#564808) 、鏡頭蓋及原裝相機套,機身飾皮有裂痕。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3100', 'IIIcK Grey \"Luftwaffen-Eightum\"', 'IIIcK Grey \"Luftwaffen-Eightum\"', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/120_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/120_2.jpg', '120', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'Military IIIc grey in mint condition. Engraved “FL. No. 38079 “ on top plate, and “Luftwaffen-Eigentum” on the back of camera and lens barrel, comes with Summitar 2/5cm (#586553), “K” stamped on shutter curtain, with lens cap and ever- ready-case.', '非常罕有的原裝灰色 IIIcK,機身及飾皮為灰色皮,機身序號後刻有 “K” 字, 機頂刻有 “FL. No. 38079”,而機頂背部及鏡 身則刻有 “Luftwaffen-Eigentum” 字樣, 顯示為德國空軍所有。鏡頭為 Summitar 2/5cm (#586553),快門簾印有 “K” 字, 成色上佳,操作正常,連灰色鏡頭蓋及皮套。由二次大戰至今,機身仍保存極新,實為難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3101', 'IIId Chrome', 'IIId Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/121_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/121_2.jpg', '121', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'Early IIId in near mint condition, the IIId was the first Leica camera with self-timer, only 427 cameras were produced between 1940-1945, only few pieces with the red shutter curtain, extremely rare.', 'Leica IIId 是首部配有自拍計時器的型號,在 1940-1945 年間生產,產量只有 427 台,其中只有極少數的相機快門廉為紅色。 此機身成色近乎完美,連鏡頭蓋,實為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3102', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Safari & Elmar-R 4/180mm safari', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm Safari & Elmar-R 4/180mm safari', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/122_1.jpg', '122', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Build-in lens hood, with both caps, in mint condition.', 'R 系列軍用狩獵版鏡頭,外觀成色完美,連內置遮光罩及鏡 頭前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3103', 'IIIf Black Paint Swedish Military', 'IIIf Black Paint Swedish Military', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/123_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/123_2.jpg', '123', '', '1,003,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leitz Wetzlar Leica IIIf in black paint finish Nr. 822933 from small batch of 100 cameras Nr. 822901-823000 made for the Swedish Army in 1956. The camera in entirely original, close to like new condition. Complete with matching original black paint Elmar 3.5/5cm lens Nr. 1427174. A black paint Leitz lens cap in A36 size included (cap earlier). In like new condition. This camera has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '非常稀有,在 1956 年只製作 100 部予瑞典軍隊,生產批號 822901-823000,整部機身和鏡頭均是原裝,連原裝黑漆的 Elmar 3.5/5cm (#1427174) 及原裝早期黑漆 A36 鏡頭蓋,( 在 James Lager V. I p98 中有介紹),成色極新。Lars Netopil 證明此套相機是原裝的。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3104', 'IIIg Black Paint \"Swedish Army\"', 'IIIg Black Paint \"Swedish Army\"', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/124_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/124_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/124_3.jpg', '124', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare military camera for Swedish Army, engraved with 3 crowns on the back of top-plate and lens Elmar 2.8/5cm (#1635392) , only 125 sets made.', '1960 年瑞典皇家軍隊向徠卡訂製了 125 台 IIIg 連 Elmar 2.8/5cm 供皇家軍隊使用。生產批號由 987901-988025,軍用版的徠卡 IIIg 在機頂後方及鏡身上均刻有瑞典皇家三皇冠標誌,因此這一版本的 IIIg 又被稱為三皇冠版 (3 CROWNS)。此套機連同 Elmar 2.8/5cm (#1635392);雖然外觀留有歲月痕跡,但功能依然正常,飾皮經後期修補,極為珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3105', 'M1 Olive bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', 'M1 Olive bundeseigentum Military Camera Set', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/125_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/125_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/125_3.jpg', '125', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Camera for Bundeseigentum military, engraved “Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739”on the back of camera top plate. The shape of finder frame is bulge like M3\'s; also engraved “5+13.5” on top plate. Elmar 4/135mm (#1025185) covered with olive leather . Total 208 sets made; only 50 sets made in the first batch, batch number are within 980451-980500. Comes with hood, front cap, yellow filter, meter with leather case, incident light, shutter release, a black bag for changing film. All of these accessories and boxes are engraved/printed the force number. And it also comes with the olive leather outfit case. Extremely rare.', '西德軍用相機,機身上刻有 “Bundeseigentum 12-133-4870”,而機頂背後則刻有 “Bundeseigentum 12-129-7739” 字樣, 機身正面取景框外型設計與 M3 一樣凸出,機頂刻有 “5+13.5” 取景框的字樣。配搭銀色軍綠色飾皮的 Elmar 4/135mm 鏡 頭 (#1025185),總產量只有 208 台,第一批僅生產 50 台,批號為 980451-980500。連遮光罩 (#12-121-5529) 、鏡頭前蓋、 黃色濾鏡、測光錶、測光錶皮套、 INCIDENT LIGHT 、快門線及換菲林黑袋;以上配件及包裝紙盒上均刻有 ( 印有 ) 部隊 編號。另外更配有存放上述套機的軍綠色皮箱,屬極罕有的收藏品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3106', 'KE-7A \"US Army\"', 'KE-7A \"US Army\"', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/126_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/126_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/126_3.jpg', '126', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare KE-7A “US Army”, engraved “CAMERA STILL PICTURE KE-7A” on the top plate, and back of the camera engraved “Serial N 1294577 FSN 6720-165-7115 CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US”, in mint- condition, comes with Elcan 2/50mm (#276-0504) with lens cap, and a purchased invoice in 1989 as well.', '此機為極之罕有的黑色 M4 美國陸軍用機,產於 1972 年。機頂刻有 “CAMERA STILL PICTURE KE-7A” 字樣。而機頂 背部則刻有 “Serial N 1294577 FSN 6720-165-7115 CONT F42600-71-C-2429 US” 字樣,並配有 Elcan 2/50mm 鏡頭 (#276-0504),連鏡頭蓋,附帶 1989 年購入的證書。品相佳,極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3107', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', 'Elcan-R 3.4/180mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/127_1.jpg', '127', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'In the early 1970s the US military in response to special photographic needs created for Vietnam Conflict. Commission Leitz of Midland Canada designed and produced this lens. The first batch 20 pieces was delivered in 1972. the second and third batch totally in 34 pieces was delivered before 1974, the lens carried serial number sequence 303-00XX, total 54 lenses. The serial number of this lens is 303-0053 with both caps, in perfect condition. Extremely rare.', '此款鏡頭是徠茲加拿大工廠 (Leitz of Midland Canada) 為美軍於 1970 年的越南戰爭設計的長焦鏡。該款鏡頭共生產 54 枝, 第一批供美軍使用 20 枝,第二批 20 枝, 第三批 14 枝,鏡身上有 “303-0053” 字樣。此款鏡頭至今從未對外發佈,相信後 期的 R 3.4/180mm APO-TELYT 是以此鏡為藍本設計生產, 故此也稱之為 R 3.4/180mm APO-TELYT 的 Prototype。鏡頭 經歷戰爭洗禮,現存世上的可能不足一半,成色良好,連前後蓋, 極為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3108', 'M4-2 Gold O.Barnack with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', 'M4-2 Gold O.Barnack with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/128_1.jpg', '128', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'In 1979, 1000 Gold M4-2‘s with matching Summilux 1.4/50mm lens (#2822093) were made to commemorate Oskar Barnack’s birth in 1879, engraved with copy Oskar‘s signature on the top plate, as well as “1879-1979”, comes with wooden box, outer box, and lens cap. In mint- condition.', '此套相機是為紀念徠卡相機之父 Oskar Barnack 誕生 100 年 而推出的,配 Summilux-M 1.4/50mm 鏡頭 (#2822093),相 機及鏡頭部分組件均以 24K 鍍金製成,共生產 1000 台,此 機紀念號為 100-0468。此套機連同包裝木盒、包裝紙盒及鏡 頭蓋;成色良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3109', 'M6J with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm', 'M6J with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/129_1.jpg', '129', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'Production was only 1640 units, 40 cameras for each year of the 40 years of M production, Engraved “40 Jahre LEICA M 1954-1994” on the top plate, the special number is indicates a year of M production (a range from 1954-1994), a number range of 1 to 40 for that year, the camera comes with Elmar-M 2.8/50mm which has the same number as the camera body. This unit comes with wooden box, outer box, leather case, hood, both caps and papers. In new condition.', '1994 年為紀念 M 系列推出 40 週年,徠卡推出 1640 套 M6J 連 Elmar-M 2.8/50mm 套機 ( 由 1954-1994,40 套 / 每年計算 ) 機頂刻有 “40 Jahre LEICA M 1954-1994” 的字樣,每套相機 及鏡頭的機身號是以該年年份,再加上 1 至 40 數字範圍。此 套機的紀念號是 1973-12,連精美木盒、包裝盒、皮套、遮 光罩、鏡頭前後蓋,包裝證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3110', 'M6 Platinum Anton Bruckner 1824 - 1896', 'M6 Platinum Anton Bruckner 1824 - 1896', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/130_1.jpg', '130', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, '200 units Special Edition produced, with Elmar 2.8/50mm (#9-00), commemorative number is 0-01, comes with wooden box, outer box, strap and papers in new condition.', '為紀念音樂家安東 ‧ 布魯克納逝世 100 週年而發行,共生產 200 台。機身及鏡頭均鍍上鉑金,機頂刻有布魯克的肖像及 “1824-1896” 字樣。紀念號是 0-01,機身覆以稀有的藍色蜥 蝪皮。套機搭配 Elmar-M 2.8/50mm 鉑金鏡頭 (#9-00),極具 藝術氣息的紀念機。此紀念機帶有包裝、木盒、尼龍帶、紀 念證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3111', 'M6 ‘Ein Stück Leica’ with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', 'M6 ‘Ein Stück Leica’ with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/131-1.jpg', '131', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, '996 units produced, with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH, the commemorative number is 350/996, also comes with box, lens cap, hood (#12589), strap, certificate and Leica cleansing cloth; in brand new condition.', '為慶祝德國徠卡公司 1996 年股票上市而發行,全球限量生 產 996 套。此套機連同 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH 鏡頭 (#3758350),紀念號是 350/996,是值得收藏的紀念機。連 精美木盒、包裝盒、鏡頭前後蓋、遮光罩 (#12589) 、尼龍 帶、 Leica 鏡頭布、股票證及證書,全新未被使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3112', 'M6 Royal Photographic Society with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M6 Royal Photographic Society with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/132_1.jpg', '132', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'Limited edition in 100 sets with Summicron-M 2/50mm,The commemorative number is 069/100, with full packing and papers in new condition.', 'M6 英國皇家歷史學會紀念套機,限量 100 套。此套機連同 Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭 ,紀念編號為 069/100。有包裝 及證書,未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3113', 'M6 Thai Gold with Summicron-M 2/50mm', 'M6 Thai Gold with Summicron-M 2/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/133_1.jpg', '133', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'In 1996, to celebrate ascended the throne 50 years of Thai King, limited edition of 700 units were made. 24K gold-plated and lizard leather body with Summicron-M 2/50mm lens (# 3695493-MH). Top engraved with their King\'s exclusive printed emblem, is one of a perfect camera for collectors. Come with wooden box, outer box, strap, cleaning cloth, both caps and papers. In new condition.', '1996 年,為慶祝泰國國王登基 50 週年而特別訂製, 限 量 700 台,此機紀念號為 HM-493。機身為 24K 鍍金,配 Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭 (#3695493-HM) ,機身貼上棕 色蜥蝪皮。機頂刻有泰王專屬印徽,是收藏家心目中完美的 紀念機之一。連精美木盒、包裝紙盒、尼龍帶、 Leica 鏡頭 布、鏡頭蓋、證書。全新未被使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3114', 'M6 Platinum 150 Jahre Optik with Elmar 2.8/50mm', 'M6 Platinum 150 Jahre Optik with Elmar 2.8/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/134_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/134_2.jpg', '134', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Only 150 sets produced , this camera commemorative number is 1856. Comes with Elmar 2.8/50mm lens (#150 Jahre Optik 1856). Complete with all packing, wooden box, box, Leica cleansing cloth, commemorative coin and certificate.', '1999 年為紀念徠卡光學技術發明 150 週年 (1850~1999),特別推出 150 套極其罕有的 M6 光學紀念鉑金機。每部相機均 刻有不同年份,分別配以五款不同鏡頭,每款鏡頭套機僅生產 30 套 , 比 M7 鈦金版一機三鏡的數量還少。此機的紀念年份 是 1856 配 Elmar 2.8/50mm 鏡頭 (#150 Jahre Optik 1856),機身用蜥蜴皮包覆。全新包裝,精美木盒、包裝紙盒、 Leica 鏡頭布、紀念幣 ( 銀色 ) 、紀念證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3115', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei 50th Birthday Edition with Diamond', 'M6 Platinum Sultan of Brunei 50th Birthday Edition with Diamond', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/135_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/135_2 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/135_3 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/135_4 copy.jpg', '135', '', '4,484,000', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate 50th birthday of his majesty, Sultan Brunei ordered the special limited edition from Leica in 1995. There were 150 pieces made with diamond on the top plate and come with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm, special number started with HB001. But more particularly, the camera in this auction carried with serial no. HB-000 which is the first unit of this batch, and the lens is Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#375200, #HB000-125). This camera was property of the Leica Museum in Solms, leave in Leica museum up to 2003. Extremely rare, comes with lens cap.', '1995 年為慶祝汶萊國王 50 歲生日,特別向徠卡訂制 150 台的 M6 鉑金帶鑽石紀念機,此款紀念機徠卡公司沒有對外發行, 是由汶徠國王送給特別貴賓,機身特別號是由 “HB001” 開始,配 Summilux-M 1.4/50mm。但更特別之處是在這次拍賣會 中的此套紀念機的特別號是 “HB000” 連 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#375200, #HB000-125),是徠卡公司只供給汶萊 國王看的樣機,屬徠卡的財產,之後一直存放在徠卡博物館,直到 2003 年才流出市面。此套紀念機是史上最為高貴華麗 的紀念機,獨一無二。此套機連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3116', 'M6 TTL Dragon Black Paint, Serial no. 2688278 (278/500)', 'M6 TTL Dragon Black Paint, Serial no. 2688278 (278/500)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/136_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/136_2 copy.jpg', '136', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, '500 cameras produced for Chinese Dragon year, engraved “ 龍 2000”, with full packing, included box, strap and papers. In new condition.', '為慶祝千禧年正值中國傳統龍年而發行的 M6 0.85 龍年套機, 黑漆機身背面刻有 ” 龍 2000” 字樣,限量 500 台,此機紀念 編號為 278/500。包裝硬盒、尼龍帶、證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3117', 'M6 Gold Dragon Edition with Summicron-M 2/50mm Chrome', 'M6 Gold Dragon Edition with Summicron-M 2/50mm Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/137_1 copy.jpg', '137', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, '300 units M6 Gold Dragon Edition with a matching Summicron-M 2/50mm (#3700009), the commemorative number is lucky number 009, with full packing in brand new condition.', '限量 300 台連同 Summicron-M 2/50mm 鏡頭 (#3700009),極具中國傳統味道。每枝鏡頭編號後面都會有限量生產編號 (009/300),此紀念機的紀念號為中國吉祥數字 009,象徵九龍吐珠。而在中國傳統中,九條龍也具有特殊象徵意義。此紀 念機包裝證書齊全。極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3118', 'M7 Hermès (Orange) with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', 'M7 Hermès (Orange) with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/138_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/138_2 copy.jpg', '138', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'M7 Hermès “Orange” (39/200) with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (# 4083483) and Leicavit (#01307), 100 units produced, with full packing, in brand new condition.', '徠卡 M7 愛馬仕套機包含 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#4083483) 及 Leicavit (#01307),結合了徠卡與愛馬仕兩個高貴且時尚 的品牌,限量推出分別以 “Etoupe” 及 “Orange” 兩個顏色為飾皮的套機,每款各生產 100 套。此套相機為愛馬仕的經典顏 色 “Orange” ( 橙色 ),編號為 39/200。全新未經使用,包裝證書配件全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3119', 'M7 Hermès (Etoupe) with Summilux-M with M 1.4/35mm, Serial no. 3009750 (117/200)', 'M7 Hermès (Etoupe) with Summilux-M with M 1.4/35mm, Serial no. 3009750 (117/200)', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/139_1 copy.jpg', '139', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'M7 Hermès “Etoupe” (117/200) with Summilux-M 1.4/35mm (#4083409) and Leicavit (#01332), 100 units produced, with full packing, in brand new condition.', '只生產 100 套的徠卡 M7 愛馬仕 “Etoupe” 套機 包含 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm ASPH (#4083409) 及 Leicavit (#01332),編 號為 117/200。全新未經使用,包裝證書配件全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3120', 'M7 Titanium \"50 Years\" with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', 'M7 Titanium \"50 Years\" with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/140_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/140_2 copy.jpg', '140', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Limited edition made available in 2004 to commemorate the 50th anniversary of Leica M system, 500 units produced, made by titanium, engraved \"1954-2004 50 Jahre Leica M System” on the top-plate. Comes with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH(#3982119), full packing in new condition.', '為慶祝徠卡 M 系列 50 週年推出的 M7 鈦版連 Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#3982119),整套相機是由鈦金屬製成,全 球限量 500 套。此套紀念機包裝、證書全齊,收藏價值極高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3121', 'MP Anthracite Kit', 'MP Anthracite Kit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/141_1 copy.jpg', '141', '', '40,120', null, null, null, null, 'In 2001, Leica MP Anthracite special-edition model was designed especially for Japan market. The camera is available as a set in a limited edition of 600 units, this commemorate number is 474/600. With full packing and in brand new condition.', '為紀念徠卡 M 50 週年,Leica 為日本市場特別推出 MP 相機 連 Leicavit (#0000269) 的紀念套裝,共推出 600 套,此機限 量號為 474/600,包裝證書、配件全齊,全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3122', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm', 'MP LHSA 1968-2003 Grey Hammertone with Summicron-M 2/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/142_1.jpg', '142', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'MP Hammertone comes with Summicron-M 2/35mm (#3967085), Hammertone hood, in brand new condition, with box, hood and papers.', '為紀念美國徠卡歷史協會成立 35 週年所發行的 MP 相機連 Summicron-M 2/35mm ASPH (#3967085) ( 仿八枚玉外型 ), 並配有特別的 Hammerton 遮光罩。限量生產 1,000 套。包裝證書全齊,全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3123', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', 'MP 0.72 Titanium', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/143_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/143_2 copy.jpg', '143', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, '150 units was produced to commemorate the first anniversary opening of Leica Store in Ginza, Tokyo. The commemorative number is 42/150, with full packing in brand new condition.', '為慶祝日本銀座店開業一週年而於 2007 年 4 月特別推出的紀念機,限量 150 台,機身及機身蓋為純鈦金製造。此套機為 42/150 號,包裝證書全齊。整套紀念機高貴經典,是收藏家追捧的焦點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3124', 'M9-P “White” Limited Edition with Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH, Serial no. 4420882', 'M9-P “White” Limited Edition with Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH, Serial no. 4420882', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/145_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/145_2 copy.jpg', '145', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'M9-P White limited edition with chrome Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm was announced for Japanese market. Only 50 units produced, especially the Chrome Noctilux which is never in Leica production list. The commemorative number is 24/50, lens number is 4170673, with white leather strap, full packing in brand new condition.', '為慶祝日本大丸店開幕而推出的 M9-P 白色配銀色 Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH 鏡頭,全球限量 50 套,僅於日本公開發售。 此紀念機特別之處是搭配銀色的 M 0.95/50mm ASPH 鏡頭;此款鏡頭除專為紀念機生產過銀色版本外,並不是正常生產列 表中的產品。此套紀念機號是 24/50, 鏡頭 (#4170673)。包裝證書、配件全齊。全新未被使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3125', 'MP Edition《60 Years PRC》with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Gold Plated', 'MP Edition《60 Years PRC》with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH Gold Plated', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/146_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/146_2 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/146_3 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/146_4 copy.jpg', '146', '', '590,000', null, null, null, null, 'In commemoration the 60th Anniversary of the People\'s Republic of China Leica has produced 24 carat gold-plated MP with Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH #4073525, body covered with red calf skin, only 61 units made, each bears a mark between 1949 and 2009, engraved “ 中 華 人 民 共 和 國 萬 歲 ” on the top. This commemorative number is 1987, complete with full packing in brand new condition. Extremely rare.', '為慶祝中華人民共和國建國 60 年,Leica 特別推出 61 套鍍金 MP 連 Summilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH (#4073525) 紀念機。鍍金機 身配搭紅色飾皮,機頂刻有天安門圖案及 “ 中華人民共和國萬歲 ” 字樣,而於取景框的右上位置更印有 “ 中華人民共和國成立六十 週年 1949-2009” 字樣。紀念機限量編號由 1949 起至 2009,每個年份只生產一套,此機限量編號為 1987,鏡頭號為 #4073525 。 配有精美木盒,全新包裝、證書齊全,極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3126', 'M9-P Edition Hermès with Three Lenses Kit', 'M9-P Edition Hermès with Three Lenses Kit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/147_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/147_2 copy.jpg', '147', '', '590,000', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M9-P Edition Hermès comes with Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH, Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH and Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH; only 100 units produced. The commemorative number is 52/100 , comes with Hermès camera bag and strap, hood, full packing and brand new condition.', 'M9-P 愛馬仕連同 Summicron-M 2/28mm ASPH, Noctilux-M 0.95/50mm ASPH 及 Summicron-M 2/90mm ASPH 鏡頭 , 一機三鏡的套裝全球只限量 100 套,本套機編號為 52/100 。連愛馬仕相機背包、包裝證書、配件全齊。全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3127', 'M9-P “Edition Hermès– Série Limitée Jean-Louis Dumas” with Summuilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', 'M9-P “Edition Hermès– Série Limitée Jean-Louis Dumas” with Summuilux-M 1.4/50mm ASPH', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/148_1 copy.jpg', '148', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'Leica M9-P “Edition Hermès– Série Limitée Jean-Louis Dumas” is a celebration of the friendship and collaboration between Jean-Louis Dumas, the former president of Hermès, who died in May 2010. M9-P Hermès (093/300) comes with Summuilux-M1.4/50mm, full packing in brand new condition.', 'M9-P 愛馬仕特別版套機連 Summuilux-M 1.4/50mm,共推出 300 套,此套機結合徠卡及愛馬仕兩個高貴且時尚品牌氣質。 本機限量編號為 93/300。包裝證書、配件全齊;全新未經使 用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3128', 'X2 White with Elmarit 2.8/24mm', 'X2 White with Elmarit 2.8/24mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/149_1 copy.jpg', '149', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, '100 pieces produce for celebration of opening a new store in Osaka, Japan. With Elmarit 2.8/24mm (#4675598). It completes with a white leather strap, full packing in brand new condition.', '為慶祝日本大阪專賣店開幕,徠卡於 2013 年 3 月特別推出 100 部白色 X2 特別版。連 Elmarit 2.8/24mm (#4675598); 包裝證書及配件全齊,全新未經使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3129', 'X2 “Edition Paul Smith” Prototype with Elmarit 2.8/24mm', 'X2 “Edition Paul Smith” Prototype with Elmarit 2.8/24mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/150_1 copy.jpg', '150', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'It is Leica X2 “Edition Paul Smith” Prototype , unnumbered. Comes with Elmarit 2.8/24mm, battery, lens cap and all packing.', '此部相機為 Leica X2 “Edition Paul Smith” 的 Prototype( 工廠 原型機 ),機身沒有刻上機身編號。連 Elmarit 2.8/24mm 鏡頭; 配有包裝盒、電池及鏡頭蓋,有相當的收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3130', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/19mm', 'Elmarit-R 2.8/19mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/151_1 copy.jpg', '151', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with hood (12546), hood cap, both caps and box, in mint condition.', '此鏡內藏三色濾鏡,連包裝盒、遮光罩 (#12546) 與遮光罩蓋、鏡頭前後蓋、 成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3131', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', 'Vario-Elmarit-R 2.8-4.5/28-90mm ASPH', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/152_(672).jpg', '152', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'With Rom, build-in hood, both caps, Kenko filter. In mint condition.', '此鏡為徠卡 R 系列最後一支變焦的鏡頭,產於 2003 年,帶 有內置遮光罩及電子接點。成色優良,連 Kenko 濾鏡及鏡頭 前後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3132', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', 'Summilux-R 1.4/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/153_1 copy.jpg', '153', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'E60, with ROM, built-in hood with both caps in mint condition.', '此鏡為 E60 口徑,帶 ROM,連內置遮光罩。配有前後蓋 ,, 成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3133', 'Macro-Elmarit-R 2.8/60mm Prototype', 'Macro-Elmarit-R 2.8/60mm Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/154_1 copy.jpg', '154', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'Second version prototype of Macro-Elmarit-R 2.8/60mm, with both caps.', '徠卡 Macro-Elmarit-R 2.8/60mm 第二代的 Prototype,連鏡頭前後蓋;市面罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3134', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', 'Vario-APO-Elmarit-R 2.8/70-180mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/155_2 copy.jpg', '155', '', '51,920', null, null, null, null, 'With Rom, clean glass, filter (#13337), both caps and strap. In mint condition.', '徠卡 R 名鏡之一,是一枝可媲美定焦的變焦鏡。此鏡帶 ROM, 成色優良,連鏡頭前後蓋 , 內置遮光罩 , 原裝濾鏡 (13337) 及背帶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3135', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/90mm ASPH', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/90mm ASPH', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/156_1 copy.jpg', '156', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'With Rom, both caps and case, fungus inside, in mint- condition.', '鏡頭帶有電子接點,消色差及非球面玻璃,連鏡頭前後蓋及 皮筒。鏡身成色優良,惟鏡筒內啞黑部份帶有白點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3136', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/180mm', 'APO-Summicron-R 2/180mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/157_1 copy.jpg', '157', '', '42,480', null, null, null, null, 'Built-in hood, with both caps, in mint condition.', '徠卡 R 中長焦鏡頭中的最大光圈代表作,成像獨特。此鏡頭 內置遮光罩,連同鏡頭前後蓋,成色極佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3137', 'APO-Telyt-R with Focus Module Set', 'APO-Telyt-R with Focus Module Set', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/158_1 copy.jpg', '158', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'Full set Focus Telyt Module with caps, aluminum case, in mint- condition. Very rare.', '此 套 鏡 由 兩 個 前 組 (#11841, #11842) 及 三 個 後 組 (#11843, #11844, #11845) 組 成, 可 作 2.8/280mm, 2.8/400mm, 4/400mm, 4/560mm, 5.6/560mm 及 5.6/800 的焦距使用。有輕微使用痕跡,是不可多得的遠攝套裝,連鏡頭前後蓋、鋁箱。 如此完整配套,在市面上實為罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3138', 'AQOOT', 'AQOOT', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/159_1 copy.jpg', '159', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'Designed for screw mount cameras, provides more convenient hand hold for film advance.', '此配件為螺絲卡口相機設計,方便快速過照片使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3139', '5cm \"Saddle\" Viewfinder', '5cm \"Saddle\" Viewfinder', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/160_1 copy.jpg', '160', '', '10,030', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare “Saddle” Viewfinder in mint condition (please refer James Lager V.III p.28).', '徠卡 Saddle 5cm 取景器,產量稀少 ( 可參考 James Lager V. III p.28),此取景器成色優良,十分罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3140', 'OROLF Tri-lens Turret', 'OROLF Tri-lens Turret', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/161_1 copy.jpg', '161', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare Tri-lens turret OROLF for M2/M3 (please refer to James Lager V. III p.300).', '供 M2/M3 使用的快速三枝螺絲口鏡頭轉台 ( 可參考 James Lager V III p.300 中介紹 ),非常稀有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3141', 'Leicavit MP Black Paint', 'Leicavit MP Black Paint', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/162_1 copy.jpg', '162', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'Extremely rare early MP Leicavit in black paint, used marks.', '早期的徠卡 MP 黑漆過片器,產量稀少。有輕微使用痕跡及 露銅,成色良好,屬收藏極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('3142', 'Leicavit MP Chrome', 'Leicavit MP Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/163_1 copy.jpg', '163', '', '20,060', null, null, null, null, 'Very rare early MP Leicavit in very average condition.', '早期的徠卡 MP 銀色過片器,十分罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3143', 'Cut-away Tri-Elmar M', 'Cut-away Tri-Elmar M', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/164_1 copy.jpg', '164', '', '11,210', null, null, null, null, 'Cut-away version of Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm E49 (#96201) with outer box.', 'Tri-Elmar-M 4/28-35-50mm E49 的切割解剖鏡頭 (#96201)。 帶包裝盒', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3144', 'Leica meterD Prototype', 'Leica meterD Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/165_1 copy.jpg', '165', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'Rare prototype Leicameter with coupling to Leica-M cameras. Made by AFAB for Leitz U.S.A., as a planned succeeded to the Metrawatt Leicameter-MR4 for Leica M4-2 / M4-P cameras. Never reached commercial production. This light meter has been authenticated by Lars Netopil.', '徠卡測光錶的 Prototype,由 AFAB 製造供美國徠茲使用。此 產品可用於 M4-2 / M4-P 上,未曾於市場上正式發佈及生產。 此產品已經由 Lars Netopil 鑑定為真品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3145', 'Super Angulon 3.4/21mm Hood', 'Super Angulon 3.4/21mm Hood', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/166_1 copy.jpg', '166', '', '1,298', null, null, null, null, 'The hood suitable for Super Angulon-M 3.4/21mm lens.', '使用於 Super Angulon-M 3.4/21mm 鏡頭的遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3146', 'Noctilux 1.2/50mm Hood', 'Noctilux 1.2/50mm Hood', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/167_1 copy.jpg', '167', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'Brand new lens hood for Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm, with original box. Extremely rare.', '全新 Noctilux-M 1.2/50mm 遮光罩,未經使用,連原裝包裝盒,十分罕有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3147', 'Lens Hood OLLUX for Summilux 1.4/35mm', 'Lens Hood OLLUX for Summilux 1.4/35mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/168_1 copy.jpg', '168', '', '6,490', null, null, null, null, 'Lens hood OLLUX for early Summilux 1.4/35mm Steel Rim, in new condition, extremely rare.', '早期的 OLLUX 遮光罩,用於 Summilux-M 1.4/35mm 鋼咀鏡 頭上;成色優良。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3148', 'VOTRA Stereo Viewer', 'VOTRA Stereo Viewer', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/169_1 copy.jpg', '169', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Stereo viewfinder in mint- condition.', '徠卡的立體觀景器,有輕微使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3149', '10X22 C Trinovid Safari', '10X22 C Trinovid Safari', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/170_1 copy.jpg', '170', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'Trinovid in mint condition.', '狩獵版 10X22 C 雙筒望遠鏡,外觀品相良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3150', 'Leitz Microscope', 'Leitz Microscope', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/171_1 copy.jpg', '171', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'The Microscope with two eyepieces (2x and 4x), in wooden box, average condition.', '此顯微鏡連兩個目鏡 (2x 及 4x) 及其他配件 ( 如圖所示 )。由 黑漆及銅組合而成,配以原裝木盒。此顯微鏡成色良好,附 帶證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3151', 'MOOLY-C Black', 'MOOLY-C Black', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/172_1 copy.jpg', '172', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'MOOLY-C Motor for IIIc and IIId, with engraving “5589”, only 800 pieces made, in mint- condition. Very rare.', 'Mooly-C 為早期生產用於螺絲機 IIIc 及 IIId 上的馬達,馬達上 刻有 “5589” 字樣。 產量極少,只生產了 800 件。此馬達成色 優良,實屬難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3152', 'M4-2 Winder Prototype', 'M4-2 Winder Prototype', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/173_1 copy.jpg', '173', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'Prototype of the M4-2 Winder, produced 30 pieces only, very rare.', 'Leica M4-2 銀色過片器的 Prototype,產量僅 30 件,十分稀 有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3153', 'HASSELBLAD *503CX 35th Anniversary', 'HASSELBLAD *503CX 35th Anniversary', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/174_1 copy.jpg', '174', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Special edition of 503CX, body and focusing ring covered with brown lizard leather, the commemorative no. is 050, comes with CF 80mm/2.8 (#7135507), A12 (#RE3338443) in wooden box and outer box, papers, in brand new condition.', '特別版的 503CX,機身為棕色蜥蝪皮,鏡頭特別之處在於 其調焦環上貼有同款蜥蝪皮。此相機紀念號碼為 050 號,連 A12 後背 (#RE3338443) 及 CF 80mm/2.8 鏡頭 (#7135507)。 外觀全新,配精美木盒、紙盒、配件齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3154', 'HASSELBLAD 503CX “Golden Blue” 50th Anniversary', 'HASSELBLAD 503CX “Golden Blue” 50th Anniversary', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/175_1 copy.jpg', '175', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'The 50th Anniversary edition plated in 24K gold, covering with blue leather. The commemorative number is 464. Comes with CF 80mm/2.8 (#7174546) and A12 (#03EV10148), leather presentation box, box, papers and strap, in like new condition.', '為慶祝 1941 年第一台哈蘇 503CX 相機面世 50 年而產,配有 CF 80mm/2.8 鏡頭 (#7174546) 及 A12 後背 (#03EV10148)。 此機紀念號碼為 464 號,附有精美包裝皮箱、藍色鍍金相機 手帶、證書全齊。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3155', 'HASSELBLAD 501CM Green Kit', 'HASSELBLAD 501CM Green Kit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/176_1 copy.jpg', '176', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Special edition covered with green leather, comes with CFE 80mm/2.8 (#8884236), A12 (#30SV17971), front lens cap, strap and papers in maker\'s box.', '特別版的 501CM 綠色飾皮,連最新款 A12 後背 (#30SV17971),配備 CFE 80mm/2.8 鏡頭 (#8884236)。帶 鏡頭前蓋、背帶、說明書及證書齊全。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3156', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW Gold Supreme Red Gold Edition', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/177_1 copy.jpg', '177', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'To celebrate the 50th anniversary of the introduction of the first Hasselblad camera in October 6, 1948. Hasselblad are presenting a special jubilee model - The Hasselblad Gold Supreme. It is a complete 503 CW with all visible chromed details plated in 24 carat gold. It complete with a CF 80mm/2.8 lens (#752058), A12 magazine (#30EU14835), with leather presentation box, all papers and maker’s box.', '為慶祝哈蘇相機面世 50 週年而生產的 503 CW 連 CF 80mm/2.8 (#752058) 及 A12 後背 (#30EU14835) 的紅皮鍍金紀念版。 機身刻有 “The System 1984-1998”,並有 24K 鍍金。全球限量 500 套,此套機限量編號為 045/500。全新未經使用,附 有精美皮箱、紅色鍍金相機手帶,證書齊全,極具收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3157', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/178_1 copy.jpg', '178', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with CFE 80mm/2.8 (#8875758), A12 magazine (#30SS16281), lens cap, in mint- condition.', '此機身配有新款 A12 後背 (#30SS16281) 及 CFE 80mm/2.8 (#8875758) 鏡頭,成色良好,連鏡頭蓋,操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3158', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW Ruby Red', 'HASSELBLAD 503 CW Ruby Red', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/179_1 copy.jpg', '179', '', '28,320', null, null, null, null, 'Special edition 503 CW, body covered with Ruby Red leather, comes with CFE 80mm/2.8 (#8851044), A12 (#30EE17214), good working order and mint condition.', '特別版的503CW 配紅色飾皮,連新款A12後背 (#30EE17214) 及 CFE 80mm/2.8 鏡頭 (#8851044)。品相優 良,操作正常,連鏡頭蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3159', 'HASSELBLAD 903 SWC Chrome', 'HASSELBLAD 903 SWC Chrome', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/180_1 copy.jpg', '180', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with CF 38mm/4.5 len (#8855066) viewfinder, lens caps, strap, all papers and box, in mint condition.', '配 CF 38mm/4.5 鏡頭 (#8855066),此機帶有包裝盒、鏡頭 前後蓋、取景器、背帶、證書及說明書;品相極好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3160', 'HASSELBLAD 905 SWC', 'HASSELBLAD 905 SWC', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/181_1 copy.jpg', '181', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with Biogon Cfi 38mm/4.5 (#8910976), viewfinder, box , cap, in mint condition.', '哈蘇 905 SWC 超廣角頂級機王,配備 Biogon Cfi 38mm/4.5 (#8910976) 彪鋼鏡頭。此套相機帶取景器、鏡頭蓋及包裝, 成色極新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3161', 'Hasselblad F-Distagon CFi 30mm/3.5', 'Hasselblad F-Distagon CFi 30mm/3.5', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/182_1 copy.jpg', '182', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'With both lens caps, lens clean and clear, in like new condition.', '哈蘇超廣角的魚眼鏡頭, 連前後蓋 , 玻璃通透,外觀成色如新。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3162', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 40mm/4', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 40mm/4', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/183_1 copy.jpg', '183', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with both caps, all papers, filter and box in mint condition.', '此鏡頭包括包裝盒,鏡頭前後蓋及 95mm 濾鏡,成色完好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3163', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 250mm/5.6 Superachromatic', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 250mm/5.6 Superachromatic', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/184_1 copy.jpg', '184', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with both caps and papers, in mint condition.', '哈蘇的名鏡之一, Superachromatic;玻璃通透,外觀完美。 連同鏡頭前後蓋及證書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3164', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 350mm/ 5.6 Superachromatic', 'HASSELBLAD CFE 350mm/ 5.6 Superachromatic', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/185_1 copy.jpg', '185', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with hood, both lens caps and leather case, in mint condition.', '哈蘇長焦名鏡, Superachromatic。玻璃清澈,功能正常;連遮光罩,鏡頭前後蓋及皮筒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3165', 'HASSELBLAD Xpan with 45mm/4', 'HASSELBLAD Xpan with 45mm/4', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/186_1 copy.jpg', '186', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with 45mm/4 (#8YSH24042), center filter, hood, front cap, in mint- condition.', 'Xpan 連 45mm/4 (#8YSH24042) 鏡頭。膠片讀數 130; 成色 良好,連鏡頭蓋,中灰及遮光罩。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3166', 'HASSELBLAD FE 300mm/2.8 Superachromatic', 'HASSELBLAD FE 300mm/2.8 Superachromatic', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/187_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/187_2 copy.jpg', '187', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'Only 300 pieces made, comes with 1.7x APO, UV filter, CPL, both caps, aluminum case, in new condition. Very rare.', '為滿足哈蘇 200 系列專業相機的使用者,1998 年哈蘇生產了全球僅 300 支的 FE 300mm/2.8。這款鏡頭採用 Superachromatic 優異的光學設計,是傳說中的神鏡。此鏡頭連 1.7x APO 增倍鏡 ( 可變為 510mm 焦距使用 ) 、 UV 濾鏡、 CPL 濾鏡、前後蓋、鋁箱,全新。異常珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3167', 'HASSELBLAD Xpan 30mm/5.6 ASPHERICAL', 'HASSELBLAD Xpan 30mm/5.6 ASPHERICAL', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/188_1 copy.jpg', '188', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with center filter, viewfinder, both caps, hood, and leather box. In mint condition.', '此鏡連同中灰、取景器、遮光罩、鏡頭前後蓋及原裝皮盒。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3168', 'HASSELBLAD Arcbody Kit', 'HASSELBLAD Arcbody Kit', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/189_1 copy.jpg', '189', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with APO-Grandagon 45mm/4.5 (#8TER10459), Grandagon-N 75mm/4.5 (#8UEE13735) and APO- Grandagon 35mm/4.5 (#8SEE13436). Comes with filter adapter, caps, plastic case, papers and other accessories, in mint condition.', '此機身連同三枝鏡頭,分別是 APO-Grandagon 45mm/4.5 (#8TER10459), Grandagon-N 75mm/4.5 (#8UEE13735) 及 APO-Grandagon 35mm/4.5 (#8SEE13436)。此套機功能正 常,調焦暢順。帶有原裝膠箱、鏡頭前後蓋,濾鏡接環及其 他配件;成色完美。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3169', 'Canon 7S with 0.95/50mm', 'Canon 7S with 0.95/50mm', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/190_1 copy.jpg', '190', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'Canon 7S with 0.95/50mm (#27651), comes with filter, hood, lens cap and ever-ready case, in mint condition.', '7S 為 CANON 於 1965 年生產的連動測距相機;此機配有 Canon 超大光圈 0.95/50mm 鏡頭 (#27651)。連同鏡頭蓋、 濾鏡、遮光罩及黑色原裝皮套;品相優良,是佳能收藏者的 最佳選擇。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3170', 'Contax 1', 'Contax 1', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/191_1_2_copy_672.jpg', '191', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black paint body with Sonnar 2/5cm (#1606271), and lens cap, with used marks.', 'Contax 1 黑漆機身連 Sonnar 2/5cm 鏡頭 (#1606271) ,機背 刻有中文 “ 德國製 ” 字樣。連銀色鏡頭蓋,有使用痕跡,操作 正常;極罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3171', 'Contax 1B', 'Contax 1B', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/192_1_copy_672.jpg', '192', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black paint body with Sonnar 2/5cm (#1454724), with used marks.', 'Contax 1B 連 Sonnar 2/5cm (#1454724),黑漆機身,操作正 常,有使用痕跡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3172', 'Contax 1E', 'Contax 1E', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/193_1_copy.jpg', '193', '', '4,720', null, null, null, null, 'Black paint body with Sonnar 2/5cm (#1548417), used marks.', 'Contax 1E 連 Sonnar 2/5cm (#1548417) 鏡頭。黑漆機身, 有使用痕跡,操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3173', 'Contax 1', 'Contax 1', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/194_1 copy.jpg', '194', '', '', null, null, null, null, 'Black paint body with Tessar 3.5/5cm (#1377443), with used marks.', 'Contax 1 連 Tessar 3.5/5cm 伸縮鏡頭 (#1377443) ,黑漆機 身,有使用痕跡,操作正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3174', 'Contax RTS Gold', 'Contax RTS Gold', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/195_1 copy.jpg', '195', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'Only 100 units made, with Planar 1.4/50mm (#6059180), commemorative number is E-10, comes with golden cap, in wooden presentation box, mint condition.', 'Contax RTS 黃金紀念套機,限量 100 台。RTS 機身搭配 Planar 1.4/50mm (#6059180),連金色金屬鏡頭前蓋,機底 刻有 “E-10” 編號。連木盒,功能正常。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3175', 'Contax Zeiss Planar T*85mm f1.2 60 YEAR', 'Contax Zeiss Planar T*85mm f1.2 60 YEAR', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/196_1 copy.jpg', '196', '', '30,680', null, null, null, null, 'Comes with box, UV Filter, hood, papers and rear cap, in mint condition.', 'Contax 為慶祝 60 週年而生產的大光圈鏡頭,全部在德國生 產,連包裝、證書、濾鏡、遮光罩及鏡頭後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3176', 'PME45 Prism', 'PME45 Prism', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/197_1 copy.jpg', '197', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'With cover and case, in mint condition.', '45 度角取景器,操作正常連皮套及後蓋。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3177', 'Linhof Master 45 Gold Edition 100 Jahre 1887-1987', 'Linhof Master 45 Gold Edition 100 Jahre 1887-1987', '37', '/public/pic_content/img/a26/198_1 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/198_2 copy.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a26/198_3e.jpg', '198', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'In commemoration of Linhof 100th anniversary, 100 sets Limited edition of Linhof Master 45 Gold edition with Symmer-S 5.6/150mm produced, the commemorative number is 072, lens no. is 14074074 with leather case and key. This camera also comes with another special edition of 125th Anniversary of Founder Jos. Schneider, a pair of gold plating Super- Angulon 5.6/90mm (#92), Symmar-S 5.6/210mm (#002), both with wooden box, caps, and papers. In mint condition, very rare.', '為紀念林可夫公司 100 週年而推出的林可夫 Master 45 黃金紀念機,連 Symmar-S 5.6/150mm (#14074074) , 配皮箱及鑰 匙, 該機紀念號是 072。 另外此套機還配有為紀念施耐德公司成立 125 週年而推出的鍍金鏡頭, Super-Angulon 5.6/90mm (#92) 及 Symmar-S 5.6/210mm (#002),均配以精緻木盒,連前後蓋及證書,是收藏及陳列極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3178', '3 Tongs Of Purple ‘Dayi’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1996', '96 紫大益青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_201_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_201_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_201_3.jpg', '201', '', '1,062,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品屬於首次將7542常規茶印成玫瑰紫色外包裝的紫大益青餅，口感獨特。市場上的96紫大益青餅中只有少部份是乾倉，使其價格更見高昂。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第294頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3179', '2 Tongs Of Aquatic Pu-er Tea Cake, 1997', '九十年代 97水藍印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_202_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_202_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_202_3.jpg', '202', '', '495,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '水藍印是勐海系九十年代比較出名的一款茶，亦可以說是88青的接班人。一組兩筒的拍品為乾倉存儲。隨著時間的流逝，除了保存普洱茶的自身價值外，亦提升了品茗的價值，使其變得彌足珍貴起來。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第270頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3180', 'A Piece Of Expo 2010 Shanghai China Pu-er Tea Cake', '中茶牌世博紀念茶餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_203_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_203_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_203_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_203_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_203_5.jpg', '203', '', '49,560', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '為紀念2010年上海世博會順利舉行而推出的中茶牌紀念青餅，餅面巨大，全球僅發行999片，本拍品紀念號為357，全新未曾拆封，附包裝證書；精良工藝加上意義特殊，收藏價值非凡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3181', '2 Tongs Of Water Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1996', '九十年代 水藍印普洱青餅（8582）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_204_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_204_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_204_3.jpg', '204', '', '542,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '96水藍印是採用8582配方制作，選擇枝葉粗大的茶葉，使茶的口感更舒適。20年的陳化表現非常好，其陳香正而濃烈，滋味醇厚，表現出7542剛柔兼具的特點，是市場熱門的收藏明星茶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3182', 'A Tong Of 88 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980s', '88青普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_205_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_205_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_205_3.jpg', '205', '', '495,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此組聞名中外的88青乾倉倉儲，竹箬包裝完整，品相上佳。作為七十年代雲南七子餅茶出產的一款標杆茶，在1988至1992年間以經典生茶7542配方製作，用中壯葉為主體，嫩芽鋪面，間以少量粗老葉製成，一直深受藏家追捧，升值潛力與日俱增。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3183', 'A Tong Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cake, Early 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 7542普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_206_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_206_2.jpg', '206', '', '472,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為陳期約30年的乾倉7542，是第一批的中厚紙小內票版本，乾倉陳香味明顯，並保持完整竹箬狀態，為一眾普洱茶愛好者趨之若鶩。此茶以少量的茶芽灑面，餅底為4至 5級粗壯茶葉，粗幼有序，堪稱勐海茶廠的長青產品。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第205頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3184', 'A Tong Of 8592 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 8592厚紙普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_207_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_207_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_207_3.jpg', '207', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是與8582同期的厚紙8592普洱茶餅，是8582的同系茶品，採用9級粗茶原料，由勐海茶廠渥堆發酵而成的早期熟餅，更被稱為八十年代中最乾倉的熟餅。拍品餅面較大，品相較完整，倉儲良好，連竹箬包裝，此等高質茶品為一眾茶客之佳音。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3185', 'A Tong Of Little Green Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970’s', '七十至八十年代 73普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_208_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_208_2.jpg', '208', '', '684,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為大口中73青餅（又名小綠印），一直為藏家所珍藏，竹箬及包裝較完好。<br />\n73青餅為早年的7542普洱茶餅，被譽為八十年代勐海青餅的「三大名牌」。經近四十年的陳化，滿口甜醇餘韻豐滿，被普洱茶收藏界視為珍品；由於需求者眾，故近年價格也愈見高昂。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3186', '4 Pieces Of Yellow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970&#039;s', '七十年代 大黃印圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_209_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_209_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_209_3.jpg', '209', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是產於70年代初的標準版七子大黃印，黃印七子餅是現代拼配普洱茶工藝的始祖，因為茶質優良，是公認的好茶，近年更因達到四十年陳化轉變，使之成為受歡迎的收藏品。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第121頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3187', '3 Pieces Of Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970s', '七十年代 大藍印圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_210_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_210_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_210_3.jpg', '210', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此組大藍印圓茶品相上佳，餅身比一般七子餅寛厚，而得名「大藍印」，其使用的茶葉亦較粗大，撥開餅身甚至可以在葉底中找到完整的大葉，這在其它的七子餅中難得一見。此拍品在茶韻上樟香與甜香交錯，為品飲及收藏者帶來驚喜。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第180及181頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3188', '3 Pieces Of Chung Cha Brand Pu-er Tea Cake with Simplified Chinese Character, 1960’s', '六十年代 簡體昆鐵普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_211_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_211_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_211_3.jpg', '211', '', '413,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品倉儲良好，整茶緊實，烏亮有光，氣韻足。由於壓制成鐵餅，茶膠豐富，口感表現強勁，十足耐泡。中茶牌雲南七子餅茶，緊壓程度堅實如鐵，故得「七子鐵餅」之名。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3189', 'A Tong Of 8653 Pu-er Tea Cake In Traditional Chinese Charaters, 1980\'s', '八十年代 首批下關8653中茶繁體字青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_212_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_212_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_212_3.jpg', '212', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品是首批8653繁體字版，餅型較寬，以5級茶菁為主要拼配原料。由於當時生產管理的原因，部分首批繁體8653茶菁是用簡體版本，而包裝是用了後期的繁體字版本，所以部分首批繁體8653實際上卻是70至80年代的簡體鐵。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第373頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3190', '14 Pieces Of 8653 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1990&#039;s', '九十年代 下關8653中茶青餅（將軍餅）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_213_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_213_2.jpg', '213', '', '295,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組14片無紙包裝的8653下關茶，又稱中茶繁體8653將軍餅，餅面見布痕，而且餅形完整份量十足，為中期陳茶的佳品。此茶以5級茶菁為主要拼配原料，由下關茶廠用雲南大葉種曬青毛茶生產壓制的普洱茶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3191', '2 Tongs Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 8582厚紙普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_214_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_214_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_214_3.jpg', '214', '', '802,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此為80年代中期的8582，茶餅外形圓厚端正，撤面條索肥壯，鬆緊適中，茶質極佳，是中期茶中的精品。此茶包裝為「長撇雲」版本；採用五至八級粗壯新老茶菁拼配緊壓，當中三、四級為面；五至八級為裡茶尤以七、八級為主，是收藏市場的搶手貨。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3192', '5 Pieces Of Yellow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1960’s', '六十年代 八中黃印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_215_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_215_2.jpg', '215', '', '885,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '八中黃印乃早期印級茶過渡七子餅茶交替期的產物，其特別之處於使用純八中款式內飛，下半部份沒有勐海公司字樣，屬於與無紙紅印及藍印鐵餅同款的內飛，亦沒有後期七子茶之內票。<br />\n有關「七子八中黃印」資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第120頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3193', '2 Tongs Of Snow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代初 雪印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_216_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_216_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_216_3.jpg', '216', '', '1,160,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '7532配方的雪印青餅是勐海茶廠出品中最為細嫩的茶品，產量不多，因茶質陳化優秀，帶有油樟香，有些更帶奶香及杏仁香，特別的口感使其受到市場歡迎，是普洱茶收藏界精品。 <br />\n此拍品連同原廠紙筒包裝，小內票。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3194', 'A Tong And 3 Pieces Of 8592 (Purple Sky) Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 8592（紫天）普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_217_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_217_2.jpg', '217', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '貴為勐海茶廠的常規熟茶，香港南天貿易公司曾於90年代初特別訂製一批8592，為了區分市場其它8592熟茶，便在包裝印了紅紫色「天」字，因而被稱「紫天8592」。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3195', '2 Pieces Of Green Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 大字綠印青餅（藍印）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_218_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_218_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_218_3.jpg', '218', '', '979,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '綠印青餅是紅印之後廣泛流通的茶品，綠印圓茶乃取材自勐海地區上好茶菁製成，茶品非常出色。包裝紙上的中文標示與紅印相同，而八中標誌則改為綠色，口感香氣則與藍印十分相似。<br />\n此組拍品一片為早期的桃紅版，另一片為常見的硃紅版，包裝品相上好；加上經過近60年的陳化，表現出絕佳的口感與喉韻，深受市場歡迎。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第73及74頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3196', '3 Piece Of Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 藍印鐵餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_219_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_219_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_219_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_219_4.jpg', '219', '', '1,121,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '傳奇的藍印鐵餅餅型較厚，採用易武喬木茶菁為原料，餅面金芽毫多，茶芽較為粗壯，屬「印級茶」中茶氣偏強之作，是上世紀五十年代經典代表茶品；由於餅型堅實，故陳化時間相對需時，至今經過六十多年的時日陳化。 <br />\n此藏品品相完好，雖然外層包裝紙稍有殘缺，但「八中一茶」的商標仍清晰可見；餅面烏亮潤澤，條索粗壯緊實。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3197', 'A Tong Of &#039;Gam San Lau&#039; Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake without wrapping, 1950’s', '五十年代 金山樓舊藏 無紙紅印', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_221_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_221_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_221_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_221_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_221_5.jpg', '221', '', '2,900,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '普洱貴在越陳越香，此無紙紅印經過六十年漫長的陳化，散發著迷人陳韻。茶餅面較紅，並採用軟竹筒作包裝，兼承金山樓一貫的良好倉儲。<br />\n於九十年代初期經營普洱茶的香港「金山樓」，在清理茶樓倉庫時出倉了此無紙紅印；作為愛茶之人，無不嚮往這酒樓的倉庫所儲藏的老茶。此茶茶氣乾淨而足，品相及質量極佳。至今陳化逾六十年歷史，葉底依舊具活性，散發出的陳韻一樣迷人，生聞已感覺其韻氣醇而樟香味濃烈，令人回味無窮。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3198', 'A Tong Of Green Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 大字綠印青餅（藍印）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_222_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_222_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_222_3.jpg', '222', '', '3,248,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品是與紅印藍印等同列印級茶之列的大字綠印青餅，系出名門，是普洱市場中品飲高級普洱茶的優先選擇。陳期達六十多年，倉儲良好乾淨，竹箬包裝。<br />\n大字綠印青餅是勐海茶廠在上世紀五十年代以後，延續無紙綠印的茶品，採用了藍印青餅的包紙，惟沒有印上「甲、乙級」字樣及沒有藍色手工蓋印。在這段時期，大字綠印圓茶是勐海茶廠普洱茶生產的重點茶品之一；其所用茶菁來源範圍廣，使其品質多樣化，分別有蘭香、樟香、清香等，變化豐富。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3199', 'A Piece Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950&#039;s', '五十年代 紅印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_223_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_223_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_223_3.jpg', '223', '', '767,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為五十年代生產的紅印青餅，歷經六十多年，仍保存良好，倉儲較佳，品相完整。拍品屬於早期粗體版本，因其陳化品質卓越，傳世稀少，被普洱藏家譽為印級茶之首。<br />\n由於早期紅印在生產時取得了原料的主導權，品質極具穩定性，甚至遠超當時同期的私人商號產品。加上採用勐海產區頂級茶菁精製，加重萌芽的用量，科學嚴謹的芽葉配比、壓製、發酵方法，保證了印級古董茶餅擁有豐富細膩的口感；半世紀後，整片紅印依舊呈現驚人的生命力，所以「紅印」之名不脛而走，簇擁者無數。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3200', 'A Piece Of ‘Jiang Cheng Hao’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1940\'s', '百年 江城號普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_224_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_224_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_224_3.jpg', '224', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '這片陳期十足的江城圓普洱圓茶餅身結實，條索偏長，色澤栗黃餅面見油光，手感強，有著大葉種普洱茶的外觀特色。江城號圓茶與普慶圓茶一樣，只有內票而沒有內飛；內票為米黃底黑色手工油印字樣，有五星標誌。此拍品當年產量不多，現存市面流通極少，多屬私人收藏，更顯其格外珍貴。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第240至241頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3201', 'A Piece Of ‘Tong Chang Hao Huang Wen Xing’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1930’s', '百年 同昌號․黃文興圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_225_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_225_2.jpg', '225', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為30年代的同昌號黃文興普洱圓茶，陳期高達80多年之久；餅身中可見黃文興普洱早期版本的白底藍色圖字內飛，落款為「主人黃文興謹白」。此茶餅厚實呈金栗色，條索扁長粗碩，十分自然美觀。<br />\r\n同昌號，亦為易武大茶莊，創設於同治七年，曾經在清末民初停廠歇業。至1930年，同昌號茶莊由商人黃文興接手主持業務運作。茶莊易主的初期，仍然是以同昌號的商標發行茶品，只是在茶品內飛的落款，改為「主人黃文興謹白」。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《號級古典茶事典》第206頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3202', 'A Piece Of ‘Tong Chang Hao Huang Jin Tang’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1930’s', '百年 同昌號․黃錦堂圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_226_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_226_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_226_3.jpg', '226', '', '1,624,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為30年代的同昌號黃錦堂普洱圓茶，陳期高達80多年之久；其倉儲良好，重量十足。於餅身中可見早期版本的白底藍色圖字內飛，落款為「主人黃文興謹白」。此茶餅厚實呈金栗色，條索扁長粗碩，自然美觀。<br />\n同昌號，亦為易武大茶莊，創設於同治七年，曾經在清末民初停廠歇業。至1930年，同昌號茶莊由商人黃文興接手主持業務運作。茶莊易主的初期，仍然是以同昌號的商標發行茶品，只是在茶品內飛的落款，改為「主人黃文興謹白」。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《號級古典茶事典》第204頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3203', 'A Tong Of &#039;Pu Qing Hao&#039; Pu-er Tea Cake, 1910&#039;s', '百年 普慶號普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_227_7.jpg', '227', '', '2,320,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '作為民初時期生產的百年普慶號圓茶，陳期越一個世紀，能在拍賣市場上找到一筒七片，原裝竹箬包裹可謂難得可貴。圓茶附有內票一張，淡土黃色底，紅色圓字，配以龍鳳花草，畫面顯得文雅且古意盎然。由於年代久遠，茶邊緣已略見鬆散，但精緻的品相與精良製作工藝，可演繹出清代普洱茶最為輝煌的篇章，能被流傳至今的「號級茶」格外的珍貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3204', 'A Pack Of Vintage Pu-er Tuocha In Original Packing, 1930&#039;s', '百年 末代緊茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_228_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_228_2.jpg', '228', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為原包裝一條七粒，經歷近一世紀仍有此完整包裝，加上停產多年而且產量不多，能保存至今特別罕見。<br />\n末代緊茶又有「香菇頭」之俗稱，包裝為每七個首尾相連，用糯筍葉包成長條，減少其在運輸過程中發霉的情況。末代緊茶主要分「猛景緊茶」及「鼎興緊茶」兩種，緊茶芽毫較多，味甜滑帶甘和清香鮮爽。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3205', 'A Tong Of Yellow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1960&#039;s', '六十年代 八中黃印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_229_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_229_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_229_3.jpg', '229', '', '1,160,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此組「八中黃印」採用原裝牛皮紙包裝紙筒，倉儲良好。<br />\n八中黃印乃早期印級茶過渡七子餅茶交替期的產物，其特別之處於使用純八中款式內飛，下半部份沒有勐海公司字樣，屬於與無紙紅印及藍印鐵餅同款的內飛，亦沒有後期七子茶之內票。<br />\n有關「七子八中黃印」資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第120頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3206', 'A Tong Of Snow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代初 雪印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_230_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_230_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_230_3.jpg', '230', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為原廠牛皮紙的「紙仝」包裝，它以「小口中」厚棉紙包裝，「茶」字為粉綠色手工蓋印，品相良好。<br />\n雪印青餅是勐海茶廠7532配方的出品，以「3級」幼葉為主要原料，是勐海茶廠最為細嫩的茶品，產量不多。以豐富口感及細膩而聞名，其聲名與73青餅及8582不遑多讓。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3207', 'A Tong Of 73 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970-1980&#039;s', '七十年代 73普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_231_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_231_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_231_3.jpg', '231', '', '708,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組八片的大口中73青餅（又名七子小綠印），一直為藏家所珍藏，竹箬完好，倉儲佳。<br />\n73青餅為早年的7542普洱茶餅，被譽為八十年代勐海青餅的「三大名牌」。經近四十年的陳化，滿口甜醇餘韻豐滿，被普洱茶收藏界視為珍品；由於需求者眾，故近年價格也愈見高昂。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第197至203頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3208', '2 Tongs Of 88 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980s', '88青普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_232_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_232_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_232_3.jpg', '232', '', '531,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '經近三十年的陳化，擁有優質茶底的八八青茶質愈見成熟。此青餅茶氣足，茶湯質感強勁厚重，野香誘人，散發一縷縷甜香味，生津回甘快，茶韻變化無窮，具有普洱茶的天然真味，即使經過多次沖泡，仍然不減其明快悠揚口感，深受藏家追捧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3209', '7 Pieces Of Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970&#039;s', '七十年代 大藍印圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_233_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_233_2.jpg', '233', '', '472,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組七片的大藍印餅面較大，包裝極少見，為大口中的白紙版本，屬於七十年代的包裝風格。此茶茶韻帶樟香與甜香，略帶藥香，富印級味道；逾四十年陳期，是值得推薦的品飲七子茶品。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第180及181頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3210', '6 Tongs Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 8582薄紙普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_234_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_234_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_234_3.jpg', '234', '', '5,130,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此組藏品是市面罕見的純乾倉薄紙8582，茶餅外形圓厚端正，撤面條索肥壯，鬆緊適中，品相良好，打開包裝已聞到極香茶氣；該茶採用五至八級粗壯新老茶菁拼配緊壓，當中三、四級為面，五至八級為裡茶尤以七、八級為主，優良品質使之成為市場上流通性甚廣的中期七子茶產品，更為市場所追逐。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3211', 'A Tong Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 8582厚紙普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_235_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_235_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_235_3.jpg', '235', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '80年代中期的厚紙8582，包裝較完整，倉儲良好，茶餅外形圓厚端正，撤面條索肥壯，鬆緊適中，茶質極佳，是中期茶中的精品。此茶採用五至八級粗壯新老茶菁拼配緊壓，當中三、四級為面；五至八級為裡茶尤以七、八級為主，是收藏市場的搶手貨。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第243至245頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3212', 'A Tong Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cake in Think Wrapping, 1980’s', '八十年代 7542厚紙普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_236_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_236_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_236_3.jpg', '236', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品為八十年代初的7542普洱青餅，是中國茶葉領導品牌大益茶業出產量最高的青餅，以肥壯茶菁為裡，幼嫩芽葉撒面，研配得當，面茶色澤烏潤顯芽毫，心茶肥壯。該茶品香氣純正持久，有荷花香，滋味濃厚回甘好，湯色黃亮，葉底勻齊；相當討喜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3213', 'A Tong Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 商檢8582普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_237_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_237_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_237_3.jpg', '237', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為80年代中的商檢版8582，指在竹箬上貼有「中國商檢」的綠色欖圓形貼紙。最初是香港南天公司向進出口公司訂制茶品向勐海茶廠訂製；此茶包裝品相良好，堪稱中期茶中的精品。此茶採用五至八級粗壯新老茶菁拼配緊壓，當中三、四級為面；五至八級為裡茶尤以七、八級為主，是陳茶史上知名度最廣的茶品之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3214', 'A Tong Of Pu-er Tea Cake, late 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 88大葉青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_238_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_238_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_238_3.jpg', '238', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '茶餅以自然倉儲存，口感強勁而豐富，包裝較完好。經近三十年的陳化，擁有優質茶底的青茶愈見成熟，具有普洱茶的天然真味，深受藏家鍾愛。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3215', 'A Tong Of Yellow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1970’s', '七十年代 小黃印普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_239_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_239_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_239_3.jpg', '239', '', '1,062,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品保存良好，為原筒包裝，條索中級偏粗，茶面茶芽已醇化為深金黃色。餅面條索級數高，偶有一些茶芽與茶骨拼入，皆粗壯肥美，豐富了茶味層次，是為印級入門茶收藏首選。 <br />\n七十年代七子小黃印之名源自外包紙上面的「八中茶商標」綠色茶字，因積年累月油墨氧化，綠字漸漸變成了黃字,因此被市場稱呼為黃印；因其餅模比傳統的印級茶為小，遂以小黃印相稱；另外，市場為了區分其與六十年代黃印茶，特意加上「七子」二字，是為七子小黃印。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第130及131頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3216', 'Two Pieces Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake without wrapping, 1950’s', '五十年代 無紙紅印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_240_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_240_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_240_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_240_4.jpg', '240', '', '767,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '戰火過後第一年春所採的茶芽頭小而內含物豐富，原料採用勐海茶區野放茶菁壯葉，茶菁條索粗壯飽滿；至今陳化逾六十年歷史，倉儲優良的無紙紅印品質絕對不輸甲級紅印。<br />\n本拍品餅面較紅，條索肥大金黃，二餅皆可見內飛，品相甚佳。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3217', 'A Piece Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake,1950s', '五十年代 紅印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_241_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_241_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_241_3.jpg', '241', '', '826,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為早期大字紅印青餅，茶餅倉儲良好，餅形完整，重量達331克，經歷六十多年仍保存完好，是為難得。茶菁條索粗壯飽滿，經歷近一甲子的陳期，散發著豐富的陳韻；其茶葉品質和人文歷史意義，使它成為了普洱茶中的曠世珍寶。<br />\r\n經典的紅印青餅，產於新中國成立的年代，普洱茶界中印級茶始祖——「紅印圓茶」，被譽為「可以喝的古董」。因其陳化品質卓越，傳世稀少，被普洱藏家視為印級茶之首。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3218', 'A Tong Of Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake In Fluorescent Green, 1950’s', '五十年代 藍印鐵餅（螢光綠版）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_242_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_242_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_242_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_242_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_242_5.jpg', '242', '', '2,668,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品作為上世紀五十年代的經典茶品，傳奇的藍印鐵餅陳期越半世紀，而且更是藍印鐵餅中產量最少的版本之一，其八中一茶商標的「茶」為螢光綠色，現存市面上所見之藍鐵，多數為綠字版，瑩光綠版較為罕見。歷經六十多年，一筒七片仍保持竹箬包裝，品相及倉儲良好，其包裝紙只有輕微耗損痕跡，堪稱普洱界彌珍。<br />\n由於鐵餅緊壓，茶膠更易提早釋放出來，使豐富的茶膠勻齊地分佈在茶葉表層；同時因茶餅緊實，後續發酵轉變會比較緩慢，茶湯的口感較傳統餅形就更加濃烈紮實，氣韻更足而充滿活性，為上乘佳品。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3219', '3 Pieces Of Blue Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950s', '五十年代 藍印青餅大三元 (甲級藍印﹑乙級藍印及大字綠印)', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_243_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_243_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_243_3.jpg', '243', '', '1,508,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此一套三片的藏品是五十年代與紅印並駕齊名的印級皇者：甲級藍印﹑乙級藍印及大字綠印青餅。三片茶餅的重量十足，平均重達337克，倉存狀態良好，「甲級」及「乙級」字樣清晰可見，狀態出色，深受茶界好評。<br />\n藍印普洱茶是勐海茶廠五十年代生產普洱茶餅，屬經典的印級茶，餅茶質優秀，經過半世紀的陳化，散發出無與倫比的陳年老韻。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3220', 'A Tong Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake without wrapping, 1950’s', '五十年代 無紙紅印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_244_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_244_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_244_3.jpg', '244', '', '2,668,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '兩筒無紙紅印以軟竹箬包裹，乾倉儲存，品相上好。在烏亮金黃的餅面與粗壯條索之中。至今陳化逾六十年，葉底活性依舊，散發出的陳韻一樣迷人，生聞已感覺其韻氣醇而樟香味濃烈。<br />\n無紙紅印，如雷貫耳的名字，無人不識；在市場上不僅有「殿堂級」普洱茶的美譽，而且是號級茶的承接者，成為普洱彌珍。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3221', 'A Tong Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 紅印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_245_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_245_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_245_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_245_4.jpg', '245', '', '5,358,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為五十年代紅印青餅，是新中國成立後的第一批普洱青茶餅，選取勐海最好的茶菁，數量不多；如今整筒上拍，其品相較完好，倉儲乾淨，更覺珍貴非常。<br />\n經過近一甲子的陳期，其口感較強烈，葉底依舊具活性，生聞已覺其韻氣醇而樟香味濃烈。沖泡後，茶湯明亮栗紅，清澈見底；茶水醇厚馥郁，富層次，生津極致、喉韻持久，濃郁芳香而不霸道，令人舌底鳴泉，回味無窮。此藏品二十泡後依舊有頂級印級茶之餘韻，厚度依舊，非常罕見。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3222', 'A Piece Og Qun Ji Hao Pu-er Tea Cake, 1930’s', '百年 群記號圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_246_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_246_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_246_3.jpg', '246', '', '944,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品陳期近一世紀，條索粗壯，餅形完整，白底紅字內飛陷埋餅身之內，品相上佳，倉儲良好，是為難得。<br />\n群記茶莊由張季皋創辦，由於創辦人與永茂昌茶莊的老闆有親屬關係，使其生意如魚得水，青雲直上，分支代銷機構迅猛發展；至1920年代後更開始生產圓茶，分銷至香港與東南亞等地。據有關資料記載，群記號圓茶有白底紅字「盧仝品茶商標」內票，票上印有「督造人張季皋，監製人張蔭培……主人張季皋謹識」等字。有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第234頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3223', 'A Piece Of ‘Fu Yuan Chang Hao’ Purple Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1920’s', '百年 福元昌號紫標圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_248_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_248_2.jpg', '248', '', '3,534,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '「福元昌圓茶」與「宋聘紅標」合稱「茶后」與「茶皇」；福元昌圓茶的內飛共有三種色紙，為紅紫、淺藍、白三色，本拍品屬陽剛型茶品的紫標，茶餅上紫底紅字的內飛清晰可見，條索金黃，附有少見之筒票。<br />\r\n福元昌號創於光緒初年，在倚邦和易武兩大茶山設制茶廠，專門採用有別於倚邦小葉茶種的易武山大葉種普洱茶葉，製造精選茶品，演繹出清代普洱茶最為輝煌的篇章；能被流傳至今的「號級茶」格外的珍貴。此茶採用最優良的大葉種普洱茶菁斤製，茶葉厚大，條索寬扁，油光淡薄但茶氣濃。經過時代醇化，底蘊極其沉穩，入口自然融化的香韻，屬多層次而有爆發力。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第196頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3224', 'A Piece Of ‘Jiang Cheng Hao’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1940&#039;s', '江城號普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_249_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_249_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_249_3.jpg', '249', '', '944,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '江城號茶品在1994年被發現時，其陳期已達50多年，為市面上非常珍貴之上乘陳年老茶，也被喻為古董茶中的明星。此茶在質量和技術上都名列前茅，具有典型的大葉種普洱茶的外觀特色，其條索扁長粗壯，色澤金黃，餅面泛油光；而且茶餅只有內票而無內飛，各內票的圖案及文字內容雖然一樣，但卻風格各異，這在古董茶中極為少見。江城號圓茶有一股濃厚的老茶清香，為見證普洱茶輝煌歷史的最佳佐證之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3225', '12 Pieces Of Sun Yishun Liu An Tea, 1950&#039;s', '五十年代 三票孫義順老六安', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_250_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_250_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_250_3.jpg', '250', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '根據藏家所述此品為戰前六安，出自香港一所1943年正式成立的茶行，為三票版本。<br />\n兩條六安均是竹箬原包，竹箬上題「孫義順 嫩葉芽蕊六安茶」；在超過半世紀後仍能找到如此佳品實在可遇不可求。此品以頭芽製造，加上條索壯實勻齊，色澤黑褐油潤，「香飄十里外、味釅一杯中」。 <br />\n安徽六安州產之六安茶，在清嘉慶年間的《六安州志》記載被列為貢茶：「天下<br />\n六安籃茶選料精緻，做工講究，成品色澤烏黑，常年內銷兩廣香港，外銷東南亞諸國；不僅為上乘飲料，且被視為良藥，嶺南中醫診方常用此茶作引，因而被尊為聖茶。<br />\n大票資料可參閱《號級古典茶事典》第54頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3226', '6 Pieces Of Sun Yishun Liu An Tea, 1920&#039;s -  1930’&#039;s', '二十至三十年代 五票孫義順老六安', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_251_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_251_2.jpg', '251', '', '885,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為20年代尾至30年代早期，保存原好的原條孫義順老六安。此茶已有蟲屎，包裝未有拆封，竹箬上蓋印「上上貢尖 揀選雨前芽蕊 正地道六安 孫義順字號 新雨春前」。陳期80多年的原條六安茶實在彌足珍貴。如此精品甚少於拍賣市場上亮相，其茶葉品質和人文歷史意義，使它成為了茶界中的曠世珍寶。<br />\n安徽六安州產之六安茶，在清嘉慶年間的《六安州志》記載被列為貢茶：「天下產茶州縣數十，惟六安茶為官廷常進之品」。六安籃茶選料精緻，做工講究，成品色澤烏黑，不僅為上乘飲料，且被視為良藥，嶺南中醫診方常用此茶作引，因而被尊為聖茶。大票資料可參閱《號級古典茶事典》第54頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3227', 'A Tong Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980\'s', '八十年代 厚紙7542普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_252_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_252_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_252_3.jpg', '252', '', '295,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品為80年代的厚紙包裝7542普洱青餅，完整竹箬，雖然不含內票，但偏乾倉儲存，狀況良好，依然相當討喜。7542是普洱茶市場的指標產品，也是勐海茶廠最受歡迎的產品，至今有超過30年以上陳期。該茶品香氣純正持久，滋味濃厚，被稱為普洱茶收藏市場的明星茶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3228', 'A Tong Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 大葉青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_253_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_253_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_253_3.jpg', '253', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '大葉青餅配方為8582，約在八十年代出現，常稱8582大葉青餅。早期的8582大多為厚紙包裝，茶質極佳，是收藏市場的搶手貨。這款茶的特色為表面茶用三、四級茶菁，裡面用七、八級茶，因用的茶料粗枝大葉，又被稱大葉青餅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3229', '2 Tongs Of 88 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '88青普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_254_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_254_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_254_3.jpg', '254', '', '1,508,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品純乾倉儲存，配上竹箬包裹，餅形完整，透過竹箬已聞到陣陣茶香，約為八十年代末出品。<br />\r\n陳期恰巧及茶菁乾淨優質的88青，來源於勐海純正野生大葉種，是七十年代雲南七子餅茶出產至今無法超越的一款標杆茶。早在1992年此茶被引進香港時，成本價只為港幣7.8元一片；及至去年市場價格一路猛進達至港幣10萬元一片，升值潛力與日俱增。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3230', 'A Tong Of Pu-er Tea Cake, late 1980’s', '八十年代 88大葉青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_255_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_255_2.jpg', '255', '', '1,624,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組六筒的拍品竹箬原筒，為自然偏乾倉。經近三十年的陳化，出色的茶質愈見成熟，野香誘人，具有普洱茶的天然真味，即使經過多次沖泡，仍然不減其明快悠揚口感，深受藏家追捧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3231', 'A Tong Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 大葉青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_256_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_256_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_256_3.jpg', '256', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品竹箬原包，包裝完好，倉儲乾淨，茶品見內票；經過30年陳化及在優良倉存之下，已經轉化至富有印級茶的韻味。<br />\r\n大葉青餅配方為8582，約在八十年代出現，常稱8582大葉青餅。早期的8582大多為厚紙包裝，茶質極佳，是收藏市場的搶手貨。這款茶的特色為表面茶用三、四級茶菁，裡面用七、八級茶，因用的茶料粗枝大葉，又被稱大葉青餅，餅身也較大較厚。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3232', 'A Piece Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 紅印鐵餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_257_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_257_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_257_3.jpg', '257', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '餅身緊實堅硬，茶膠豐富，茶氣強勁，包裝與紅印青餅相似，配茶上與甲級紅印相口感相近的紅印鐵餅。當年生產量極為稀少，現市場罕見。此拍品倉儲良好，加上其茶氣在紅印中獨樹一幟，別具風韻，深得愛茶之人的歡心。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3233', '7 Pieces Of Iron Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s to 1990’s', '五十年代至九十年代 鐵餅一條龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_258_7.jpg', '258', '680,000 - 900,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組七片的鐵餅一條龍為50至90年代勐海茶廠出品的鐵餅系列，當中包括紅印鐵餅及藍印鐵餅等大名鼎鼎的茶品；另配60年代與70年代下關簡體字鐵餅、70年代至90年代昆鐵三片。整組拍品完整收集為「鐵餅一條龍」，把普洱茶的演變進程同時收納囊中。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3234', 'A Tong Of \'Gam San Lau\' Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake without wrapping, 1950’s', '五十年代 金山樓舊藏 無紙紅印', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_259_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_259_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_259_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_259_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_259_5.jpg', '259', '', '3,016,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '普洱貴在越陳越香，此無紙紅印經過六十年漫長的陳化，散發著迷人陳韻。茶餅面較紅，並採用軟竹筒作包裝，兼承金山樓一貫的良好倉儲。<br />\r\n於九十年代初期經營普洱茶的香港「金山樓」，在清理茶樓倉庫時出倉了此無紙紅印；數十年來茶倉都存放陳年普洱茶，其牆面﹑地下都瀰漫著陳舊的普洱茶茶氣，形成一個理想存放普洱茶的陳化環境。作為愛茶之人，無不嚮往這酒樓的倉庫所儲藏的老茶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3235', 'A Tong Of Red Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 紅印鐵餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_260_8.jpg', '260', '', '5,586,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '紅印鐵餅當年生產量極為稀少，現市場罕見程度被稱為「傳說中存在的茶」，如此拍品般帶有原筒軟竹箬更是可遇不可求也。紅印鐵餅的製作時間比「圓茶」稍遲，質量及香氣與紅印同出一徹，包裝八中茶字為紅色、採用鐵餅緊壓製作而被定名為「紅印鐵餅」。<br />\n本拍品包裝完整，經過六十年陳化，品相極佳，現今市場上已極為罕見，在一眾舊普洱中更顯珍貴。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3236', 'A Tong Of Green Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950’s', '五十年代 大字綠印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_261_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_261_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_261_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_261_4.jpg', '261', '', '3,132,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '對於普洱茶歷史來講，大字綠印圓茶具有從「印級」到「七子餅」承先啟後意義。本拍品一筒七片以竹箬原包，品相上佳，陳期越半世紀，於收藏或品飲皆炙手可熱，值得世代流傳。<br />\n以茶香而論，大字綠印圓茶幾乎包納了所有普洱茶香型，其茶味、茶韻、茶氣的變化也十分豐富並各有千秋，且整體品質一流。隨著陳期越久，其各種表現漸入佳境，在現今老茶一片難求的局面下，大字綠印圓茶成為優質潛力股，是許多茶饕的心頭好。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第73及74頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3237', '2 Pieces of Chung Cha Brand Tea Cake in Simplified Chinese, 1970\'s', '七十年代 中茶牌簡體字鐵餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_262_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_262_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_262_3.jpg', '262', '', '200,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '中茶牌簡體字鐡餅是八十年代之前的產品，是下關茶廠中具代表性的茶品，餅型扁平堅實，展現濃厚質感及強勁氣韻，被譽為50年代監印鐵餅的沿擊。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第369及371頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3238', 'A Tong Of Snow Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, early 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 雪印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_263_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_263_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_263_3.jpg', '263', '', '1,276,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此茶連同原廠牛皮紙的「紙仝」包裝，「茶」字為粉綠色手工蓋印，小內票，紙筒包。雪印是勐海茶廠出產包裝承襲了七子黃印的七子餅茶，以三至六級茶菁原料混拼，是其出品中最為細嫩的茶品，面裡一致，產量不多，深具收藏價值。餅面細芽多且芽白如雪，故有名「雪印」，也是50年代印級茶品後繼者，極受市場歡迎。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3239', 'A Tong Of ‘Song Pin Hao’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1960&#039;s', '六十年代 宋聘號圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_264_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_264_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_264_3.jpg', '264', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '珍藏五十多年的宋聘號圓茶，為泰廠白紙版。百年茶莊宋聘號的出品，陳放多年已自然陳化為藥蔘香氣韻。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第257頁。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3240', 'A Tong Of  &#039;Yong Mao Chang’Pu-er Tea Cake, 1960&#039;s', '永茂昌普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_265_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_265_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_265_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_265_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_265_5.jpg', '265', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '據《江城縣誌》載，永茂昌茶莊為三十年代左右著名的普洱商號；和眾多邊境普洱茶一樣，原料取自雲南正山優質茶菁。上好的茶菁配合精湛的加工工藝，與幾十年的自然陳化，賦予了永茂昌圓茶醇厚柔順、潤喉回甘的特徵。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第274頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3241', '7 Pieces Of &#039;Guang Yun&#039; Pu-er Tea Cake, 1950&#039;s', '58廣雲貢餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_266_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_266_2.jpg', '266', '', '295,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為五十年代的廣雲貢餅，倉儲條件佳。內飛沿用印級茶的「方形八中」設計，但較細小。是廣雲系列中最特別、目前所剩最少的產品之一。餅形比其他年代的茶餅大，但反面的凹洞卻是最小，且茶餅邊形呈角狀。<br />\n當時中央規定雲南茶葉公司每年需固定提撥茶菁讓廣東茶葉公司做為拼配原料，所以早期之廣雲貢餅大都摻有印級茶之茶菁。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第430頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3242', 'A Piece Of &#039;Guang Yun&#039; Pu-er Tea Cake, 1960&#039;s', '六十年代 廣雲貢餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_267_1.jpg', '267', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本收藏品一直以乾倉存放，條索金黃：餅面見小方形中茶標誌內飛。<br />\n廣雲貢餅和中茶公司印級茶為同期茶，也被視為印級茶的一員。其製作方式沿用中茶印級茶；雖然製程相近，但由於氣候、茶菁來源不同，廣雲貢餅比其它印級茶更為細膩油潤。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第425至427頁。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3243', '7 Pieces Of 7432 Pu-er Tea Cake, Manufactured in Menghai', '八十年代 7432普洱圓茶 (勐海廠)', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_268_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_268_2.jpg', '268', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品為勐海茶廠七子系列中的高檔茶品，用料講究，質屬大葉種喬木春尖，茶味醇厚。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3244', '6 Tongs Of 8592 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980’s', '八十年代 8592厚紙普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_269_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_269_2.jpg', '269', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是與8582同期的8592普洱茶餅，被稱為八十年代中最乾倉的熟餅，是香港南天公司於八十年代向勐海茶廠訂製的茶品。六筒拍品均是竹箬原包，見大票；此等高質茶品為一眾茶客之佳音。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3245', '7 Pieces Of 8653 Pu-er Tea Cake With Traditional Chinese Charaters, 1980s', '八十年代 下關8653繁體字中茶青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_270_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_270_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_270_3.jpg', '270', '', '188,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組七片的茶餅均是八十年代中期薄絲紋紙版本的繁體字中茶牌鐵餅，倉儲良好，品相完整，附中英文版內票一張。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3246', '15 Pieces Of 83 Disus Pu-er Tea Cakes, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 姑娘餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_271_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_271_2.jpg', '271', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品為80年代中末期由香港茶商特意訂造的青餅，選料結構合理，精心配製緊壓，又稱「姑娘餅」。包裝品相完好如初，餅面油光結實，近聞茶香沉穩內斂，條索緊結。經三十年左右陳化，效果完美呈現。<br />\n根據藏家所描述，此茶湯呈現琥珀般的色澤，紅亮誘人，茶香四溢。口感茶滋飽滿圓潤，樟香強烈。葉底鮮活富有彈性，茶滋釋出持久，可媲美83鐵餅。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3247', '3 Tongs Of Purple ‘Dayi’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1996', '96 紫大益青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_272_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_272_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LTONO_272_3.jpg', '272', '', '826,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品屬於首次將7542常規茶印成玫瑰紫色外包裝的紫大益青餅，內飛為紅大益無R，其乾倉儲存更凸顯拼配配方比例堪稱完美，經廿多年的陳化之後，茶質厚重，帶輕樟香，更顯出陳年茶韻，令人心生嚮往。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第294頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3248', 'A Pack Of 7572 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 7572普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_273_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_273_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_273_3.jpg', '273', '', '413,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一支十二筒的7572保持原包裝，有大票與內飛。採用勐海茶區青壯茶菁為心茶，金毫細茶作撒尖和蓋茶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3249', 'A Pack Of 8592 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 薄紙8592普洱圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_274_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_274_2.jpg', '274', '', '1,062,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是與8582同期的8592普洱茶餅，被稱為八十年代中最乾倉的熟餅，拍品為薄棉紙版本，包裝品相上佳，見大票及竹箬原包，倉儲良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3250', 'A Tong Of Orange Mark Pu-er Tea Cake, 1996', '九十年代 橙印青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_275_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_275_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_275_3.jpg', '275', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為後期的「橙色茶字」的版本、其外包紙及內票均為「橙色茶字」的「橙中橙」，實為可存可飲之佳茗。<br />\r\n橙印青餅是南天貿易公司向勐海茶廠訂製的著名茶品，採用1993至1994年茶青製成，編號「7532」。南天所訂製之茶品一直都較優質，直至1996年完成這批7532後便光榮引退，所以「橙印7532」可算是南天公司的最後代表作。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第262頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3251', '12 Tongs Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1992', '九十年代 92普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_276_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_276_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LTONO_276_3.jpg', '276', '', '1,740,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為92青餅中的無飛版本，是辨別1992年產的一大特色。此茶以勐海7542為配方，薄紙包裝，印刷顏色為硃砂紅，中央「茶」字為青草綠色；拍品連竹箬包裝。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深遂的七子世界》第254頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3252', 'A Tong And A Piece Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1993', '九十年代 93青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_277_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_277_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_277_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_277_4.jpg', '277', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本組拍品為1993年勐海茶廠生產的「大七」版本，包裝完好，倉儲乾淨，至今也有25年陳期，是繼88青後最具收藏價值的普洱茶之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3253', '6 Tongs Of 8582 Pu-er Tea Cake, 1998', '九十年代 8582配方訂製青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_278_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_278_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_278_3.jpg', '278', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品由有「普洱茶教父」之稱的白水清先生特別以8582配方訂製，8582是與7542齊名的普洱茶配方，採用3至8級粗壯新老茶菁拼配。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3254', '2 Tongs Of Yunnan Wild Tea Cake with Red Ribbon, 1998', '紅大益 雲南野生餅茶（紅帶）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_279_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_279_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_279_3.jpg', '279', '', '377,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '陳期已接近廿年的紅大益青餅，拍品竹箬保存完整，品相上佳，茶餅見內飛與紅絲帶。而此茶主要以芽頭為料，茶氣帶班章味，湯色黃潤透亮，回甘十足，為中生代的明星茶品。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深遂的七子世界》第299頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3255', '7 Pieces Of 99 Pu-er Tea Cakes With Purple Marks, 2000', '綠大樹紫紅票青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_280_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_280_2.jpg', '280', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此茶味韻勻長，呈現出一股原野高香，包裝品相良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3256', 'A Tong Of ‘Yi Chang Hao’ Pu-er Tea Cake (Sung Edition), 1999', '99易昌號精品（宋體版）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_281_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_281_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_281_3.jpg', '281', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '99易昌號是昌泰茶行的經典作品，本拍品為宋體版，附竹箬原包，品相優良，附內飛；竹箬上題「易武正山野山青餅」。經過10年陳化的99易昌號，口感圓潤不苦澀、茶味強，被認為是同期普洱茶中最出色的作品之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3257', '2 Tongs Of 7062 ‘Dayi’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 2000', '無R紅大益 7062紅帶青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_282_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_282_2.jpg', '282', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為2000年左右由勐海茶廠研制的新茶品，配方為7062，並未大規模量產。拍品連竹箬包裝，品相上佳，包裝原好；經近廿年陳化，漸成為市場精品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3258', 'A Piece Of Fengching Pu-er Tea Cake, 2003', '鳳慶號圓茶  限量版', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_283_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_283_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_283_3.jpg', '283', '', '141,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為大名鼎鼎的八八青乾倉始創人，陳國義先生於2003年委託鳳慶茶廠以3200年的茶王之母茶王樹所製的第一批頂級樣品茶，彌足珍貴。由於當地政府於2007年起對古茶樹實施保育的關係，致使其停產至今，價格高居不下；此茶樹王於2006年所產的最後一批30片茶王青餅，曾經以一片高達40萬元人民幣成交。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3259', '2 Tongs Of 7542 Pu-er Tea Cakes, 2001', '01繁體雲普洱青餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_284_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_284_2.jpg', '284', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '經典7542配方茶，與01簡體雲為同年產品，是勐海茶廠最常規的標杆茶之一。此組拍品為竹箬原包，品相上好，十多年的陳化使其茶氣漸足。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3260', '24 Pieces Of Liu An Tea, 1980’s', '八十年代  六安茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_285_1.jpg', '285', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '四條共廿四粒的六安茶以竹簍與粽葉組合包裝，品相上好。明代聞龍在《茶箋》中稱，六安茶入藥最有功效，不僅可消暑生津解渴，而且還有可幫忙消化，保健作用不容置疑，被視為養生品飲的珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3261', '7 Pieces Of Kunmiung Red Seal Raw Tea Iron Cake, 2000', '昆明紅印鐵餅', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_286_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_286_2.jpg', '286', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '由昆明茶廠產於2000年的紅印鐵餅，配方8668，約廿年的轉化使其陳韻漸足，茶味回甘，絲絲滲甜；加上拍品倉儲良好，品相上佳，使其漸漸成為收藏市場上的搶手貨。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《新生普洱年鑑1998至2003》第300頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3262', '8 Pieces Of 79 Jing Gu Pu-er Tea Brick, 1970’s', '七十年代 79景谷磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_287_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_287_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_287_3.jpg', '287', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '79景谷磚是文革磚類中特別的產品，是唯一有資料證明由景谷茶廠出品的熟磚，也是於七十年代赫赫有名的景谷茶廠最後一批產品。部分拍品依然保留着30多年前以國貨公司購入的價格標籤 (6.5元港幣)。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第413頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3263', '5 Pieces Of 7562 Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1970’s', '七十年代 7562茶磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_288_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_288_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_288_3.jpg', '288', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本組茶磚一組五片，連原包裝，品相良好，重量亦足。此茶產於文革前後，被視為文革磚的延續，惟此茶採用後發酵工藝製作，也是第一批在外包装上印製编號的普洱茶。它以3至6級茶菁混拼，採用勐海茶區出產的大葉種灌木茶樹所產幼嫩茶菁，因此老茶茶面呈金黄色，價格不菲。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第412頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3264', '8 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks Produced During Cultural Revolution, 1973', '七十年代 文革厚磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_289_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_289_2.jpg', '289', '', '212,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是文化大革命期間製作的磚茶，因其特殊的文化和歷史背景而得名，存世的數量不多。<br />\n文革磚的茶箐原料選用雲南喬木型大葉種曬青毛茶，品質優越，壓製緊結密實。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第408頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3265', 'A Pack Of 73 Jujube Tea Bricks, 1960&#039;s', '六十年代 73棗香磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_290_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_290_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_290_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_290_4.jpg', '290', '', '295,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為市面罕見連同原包裝紙的73棗香磚，光聞茶體時就能自然散發出淡雅的棗香味，當年於台灣舉行第一屆國際普洱茶嘉年華大展時每片茶價就已高過了當時非常紅火的73青餅及雪印青餅。本藏品包裝頗為完整，是為難得。<br />\n同款茶磚曾刊登於《深邃的七子世界》第409頁中。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3266', '2 Packs Of 73 Tea Bricks With Jujube Aroma, 1960’s', '六十年代 73棗香特厚磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_291_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_291_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_291_3.jpg', '291', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為兩組共八塊的73棗香特厚磚，附包裝，內票為「八中一茶」商標，票上題「雲南普洱茶磚」，品相頗為完整，十分難得。<br />\n棗香磚主要是用西雙版納勐海喬木曬青毛茶，調配出特別的爽朗棗香味與韻味，在口感上有古董茶風韻的表現。另外，由於其發酵過程充足，藥用價值相對較大，對心血管、胃部都有很好的養護作用，品嚐及收藏價值尤佳。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第409頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3267', 'A Piece Of ‘Keyixing’ Tea Bricks, 1930’s', '百年 可以興茶磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_292_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_292_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_292_3.jpg', '292', '', '885,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '可以興磚茶被稱為「磚中之王」，其茶之香氣優越甚少古董茶能與之比擬。1927年後的可以興茶磚存量甚少，此拍品內飛陷埋於茶磚之內。據資料顯示，15年前其留存量僅3件，每件160片即480片而已，經15年的消耗，目前全球可能存留不到幾十片 。<br />\n<br />\n可以興茶磚具備以下四個特點，也創造了普洱茶歷史上很多唯一：<br />\n一． 可以興磚茶是普洱茶歷史上唯一的「十兩磚」，與當時及目前流行的250公克（六兩半）磚茶不同。<br />\n二． 可以興磚茶是生茶磚的傑出代表，也是唯一存留下來的生茶磚。<br />\n三． 勐海茶聞名於世，以黑色為上佳。可以興磚茶就是以細黑條索、上好的勐海普洱茶菁制造的，堪稱黑色普洱茶的標本。<br />\n四． 可以興磚茶改寫了普洱磚茶史，是最早的磚形茶。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3268', '12 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks from 1960’s to 1980’s', '六十至八十年代 茶磚一條龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_11.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_293_12.jpg', '293', '180,000 - 300,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1967年前的藏銷茶多以牛心型制，因為此形狀有利通風及儲存。至後期為了減低勞動力及便於機械化製造，於1960年代中起便改以磚形製作，當中景谷磚便應運而生。本藏品正由60年代景谷磚開始，同時包括文革磚及其他青磚，整個普洱茶磚的發展歷史同時呈獻，使大眾了解茶界傳奇的發展，更顯彌足珍貴，為普洱茶愛好者帶來妙不可言的心神體會。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3269', '4 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks Produced During Cultural Revolution, 1973 (Vermilion)', '七十年代 文革厚磚（朱砂紅版）', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_294_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_294_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_294_3.jpg', '294', '', '271,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此組拍品為四十多年前的文革磚朱紅版本，以黃紙包裝，品相完整良好。此磚的條索粗壯，大約是七八級粗老葉壓成，以文革磚而言，是口碑較好的早期熟磚，所以價錢相對較高。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第406頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3270', '9 Pieces Of Wide 73 Camphor Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1970’s', '七十年代 73寬版樟香磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_295_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_295_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_295_3.jpg', '295', '', '224,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組九片的73樟香磚均為寬版，倉儲良好。此茶品樟香味醇厚，口感順滑，茶氣強烈，為一眾茶人所追捧。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深遂的七子世界》第411頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3271', '8 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks Produced During Cultural Revolution, 1973', '七十年代 文革厚磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_296_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_296_2.jpg', '296', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品是第一批在文化大革命期間製作的磚茶，因其特殊的文化和歷史背景而得名，存世的數量不多。<br />\n文革磚的茶箐原料選用雲南喬木型大葉種曬青毛茶，品質優越，壓製緊結密實。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第408頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3272', '4 Pieces Pu-er Tea Bricks Before Cultural Revolution, 1970’s', '七十年代 普洱厚磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_297_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_297_2.jpg', '297', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為最早期的文革磚，雖然欠缺外包裝，但可見其條索粗壯緊實，味道醇厚，香氣濃郁；更難得的是此茶屬於73文革磚前的產物，市面罕見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3273', '2 Packs Of 73 Jujube Tea Bricks, 1960\'s', '六十年代 73棗香磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_298_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_298_2.jpg', '298', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本藏品為市面罕見連同原包裝紙的73棗香磚。當年五行圖書在編輯世界權威普洱茶書《深邃的七子世界》時，遍尋連包裝的73棗香磚不果，可見本拍品之珍貴。此藏品部分茶磚見內飛，品相頗為完整，十分難得。<br />\r\n由於使用了大葉為材料，故其轉化過程較佳，帶顯著陳香。在發酵過程中更產生接近紅棗的香甜味道，故稱為棗香普洱茶。<br />\r\n同款茶磚曾刊登於《深邃的七子世界》第409頁中。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3274', '6 Pieces Of Wide 73 Tea Brick, 1970’s', '七十年代 寬版73磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_299_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_299_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_299_3.jpg', '299', '', '106,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '「文革磚」製成於上世紀七十年代，由勐海茶廠生產出品，茶菁原料均選用雲南大葉種曬青毛茶，品質優越；部分拍品包裝上有當時購入的價格標籤。<br />\r\n有關資料可參閱《深遂的七子世界》第409頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3275', '30 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1992', '92普洱方磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_300_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_300_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_300_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_300_4.jpg', '300', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '九二方磚於1991及1992年間共產四批，本拍品倉儲良好，包裝背後見製作日期為1992年1月或2月，而盒身可見有引人注目的錯體「淨重100公分」。<br />\n九二方磚由勐海茶廠所制，中茶商標，陳期已達二十五年，品質受到市場及茶客的認可。曾被「普洱茶王」鄧時海先生形容為「末代茶王」，其收藏潛力不容忽視。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3276', '20 Packs Of 92 Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1990’s', '92普洱方磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_301_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_301_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_301_3.jpg', '301', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組三十片的92方磚以自然倉儲存，包裝品相原好，盒身有錯體的「淨重100公分」。<br />\r\n2000年後，這批茶展現出極佳的轉化，早年的苦澀轉化成醇厚；轉化完成的92方磚被評為：「金毫顯露」、「茶厚質醇」及「回甘強烈」等。市場給予正面的評價，甚至有「末代茶王」之美譽，因而受到茶界追捧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3277', '12 Pieces Of Kunming Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1980’s', '八十年代 昆明普洱茶磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_302_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_302_2.jpg', '302', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組十二片的昆明普洱茶磚，品相包裝完好，色香味美兼具，為收藏佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('3278', '30 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1980\'s', '八十年代 油光紙磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_303_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_303_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_303_3.jpg', '303', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組20片的普洱熟磚為油光紙包裝，外包裝貼有中茶標誌。其色澤黑亮，條索緊實分明，品相完好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3279', '20 Packs Of 92 Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1990’s', '92普洱方磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_304_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_304_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_304_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_304_4.jpg', '304', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此批茶磚色澤黑亮，芽毫顯露，條索緊實分明，乾倉儲貯。<br />\r\n九二方磚於1991及1992年間共產四批，由於西雙版納勐海縣的電話由1992年5月起已改為五位數，而本藏品背後的日期小票上顯示「1992年12月」電話號碼亦已改為5位數；而盒身亦有引人注目的錯版「淨重100公分」，更為本拍品增添收藏價值。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3280', '80 Packs Of 92 Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1990’s', '92普洱方磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_305_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_305_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_305_3.jpg', '305', '', '283,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '92普洱方磚由勐海茶廠所制，中茶商標，陳期越四分一世紀，品質受到市場及茶客的認可，曾被「普洱茶王」鄧時海先生形容為「末代茶王」，有機會重演普洱茶另外一個神話的茶品，其收藏潛能不容忽視。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3281', '100 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks, 1980’s – 1990’s', '八十至九十年代 黃雞皮紙普洱茶磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_306_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_306_2.jpg', '306', '', '295,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本組拍品多達100片，均以黃雞皮紙包裝未曾開封，包裝品相良好，倉存佳，深受世界各地茶友所愛戴，為收藏品飲的最佳選擇。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3282', '22 Pieces Of Pu-er Tea Bricks, from 1980’s to 1990’s', '八十年代及九十年代茶磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_307_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_307_2.jpg', '307', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此拍品為一組十三片的油光厚黃紙熟磚與一組九片下關茶廠淨含量磚，品相俱佳，存儲得宜。當中油光厚黃紙熟磚包裝紙上的「洱」字與其他版本有輕微差別；有關資料可參閱《深邃的七子世界》第415及417頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3283', '6 Packs Of Pu-er Tea Bricks With Glossy Paper, 1990’s', '九十年代 油光紙普洱青磚', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_308_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_308_2.jpg', '308', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '六組青磚為竹箬包裝，包裝品相上好，陳期十足，為中期茶磚的入門首選。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3284', 'A Pack Of Fulu Shouxi Tea Bricks, late 1990’s', '九十年代 「福祿壽禧」雲南貢茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_309_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_309_2.jpg', '309', '8,000 - 12,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品以雲南大葉種曬青毛茶一、二級為原料，選料嚴格，嫩度較高，精工篩選。整盒茶磚共一公斤，分別由壓有福、祿、壽、喜四字的4塊250克茶磚組成，是壓制茶中的高檔產品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3285', '2 Pieces Of Anhua Tea Brick, 1960’s', '六十年代 花磚茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_310_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_310_2.jpg', '310', '100,000 - 150,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此茶磚面四邊有花紋，加上一磚為淨合老秤1000兩，故又稱花磚茶或千兩茶。此茶陳期約五十年，品相極佳，其中磚連同原包裝紙；加上磚面色澤黑褐，內質香氣純正，葉底老嫩均稱，為品飲佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3286', '2 Pieces Of Anhua Tea Brick, 1960’s', '六十年代 黑磚茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_311_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_311_2.jpg', '311', '100,000 - 150,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品其中一片附原包，題「安化黑磚茶」。其磚面平整光滑，棱角分明；茶葉加以磚身緊實，不易受潮黴變，收藏越半世紀仍不變味，越陳越好，適於烹煮飲用，起保健養生之效。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3287', '4 Bags Of Chongcha From &#039;Tong On Hong&#039;, 1970&#039;s', '七十年代 同安茶行蟲茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_312_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_312_2.jpg', '312', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '自乾隆年間起，蟲茶就奉為貢品，據說它有清熱祛暑、解毒健胃、助消化等功效，因而聞名海內外。此批蟲茶的藏期達四十多年，就養生及品飲而言，甚有質素保證。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3288', 'A Piece Of Pumpkin Tribute Tea', '金瓜貢茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_313_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_313_2.jpg', '313', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '早年的金瓜茶是專為上貢朝廷而制，故名「金瓜貢茶」；形制如此碩大的更是市場少有，為當時吉幸茶廠出品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3289', '3 Rolls Of Chung Cha Brand Tuocha, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 中茶餅沱茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_314_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_314_2.jpg', '314', '', '82,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '80年代中茶綠印沱以竹箬包裝，布紋手工薄紙包裝見八中手工印章蓋上綠色茶字，上方印上雲南緊茶。此茶年代及口感有若88青餅，致使近年價格飛升。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3290', 'A Set Of ‘Yichanghao’ Pu-er Tea, from 1999 to 2002', '易昌號普洱系列', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_315_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_315_2.jpg', '315', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組四套的易昌號茶品，均秉承傳統方法，嚴選西雙版納易武茶區野生喬木茶精製而成，具古樹茶的深厚底藴，經久耐泡。隨著時間的流逝，陳化後的易昌號，其口感豐富而茶韻十足。四組藏品以竹箬包裹，品相上好，送禮收藏皆宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3291', 'A Pack Of ‘Yi Chang Hao’ Yi-Wu Tuocha, 2006', '易昌號 蜀沱生沱茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_316_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_316_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_316_3.jpg', '316', '', '53,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此藏品為2006年時，易昌茶廠使用易武茶區野生老茶料而製的沱茶；拍品原支上拍，雖然茶品外包裝及竹殼呈些微陳化現象，但茶品條索清晰，香氣顯，附橫票，依然是品飲收藏的上佳之選。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3292', 'Liu Bao Tea With A Pair Of Yixing Tea Caddies, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 珍藏六堡連紫砂茶葉罐及紫砂加彩蓋碗', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_317_1.jpg', '317', '', '8,260', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此早期紫砂罐為原礦燒製，泥料純正，並火氣已退，以此藏茶有利陳化，蘊藏滋味；加彩蓋碗亦為紫砂經典。連同兩份珍藏六堡，茶齡真確，湯色紅濃明亮，滋味醇厚，略帶藥香，不可多得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3293', 'Liu Bao Tea With A Pair Of Silver And Crystal Tea Caddies, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 珍藏六堡連鍍銀及水晶茶葉罐', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_318_1.jpg', '318', '6,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '此六堡茶條索緊結黑褐，湯色紅濃明亮，滋味醇厚帶陳香。以洋味十足的鍍銀及水晶茶葉罐盛載，盡顯華麗典雅。以此藏茶，實洋為中用，可謂名茶配美器。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3294', '7 Pieces Of Liu An Tea, 1980&#039;s', '八十年代 八中六安茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_319_1.jpg', '319', '70,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組七粒的六安茶為80年代末特別訂製，於80年代末生產過少批量而已，當時主要為外銷用。此茶連同當時鴻昌泰茶行的包裝紙，品相上佳。<br />\n六安茶屬於黑茶中的貴族茶，此藏品陳期30多年不黴不爛，茶味越陳越醇。因六安籃茶的諸多保健功能，使它從古至今廣贏中外青睞。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3295', '12 Pieces Of Liu An Tea From Ying Kee Tea House, 2001 - 2002', '英記家藏舊六安', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_320_1.jpg', '320', '30,000 - 55,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '明代屠隆在《茶笺》中記：「六安，品亦精，入药最效」。六安茶甘醇濃和，以保健功效見稱；而且由始創於1881年的英記茶莊經嚴格挑選及加工配製而成，品質有所保證。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3296', '2 Pieces Of Sun Yishun Liu An Tea', '六十至七十年代 龍福記 三票孫義順六安茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_321_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_321_2.jpg', '321', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '龍福記瑞春源茶莊為六安茶香港總代理，60年代時遠銷加拿大及美國。此茶以竹簍包裝，附孫義順內票三張，連當時香港龍福記瑞春源茶莊包裝；包裝紙上印有60至70年代時使用的6位數的電話號碼：430747，內票也印有香港總代理龍福記瑞春源茶莊等字樣，品相上佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3297', 'A Piece Of Liu An Pu-er Tea', '孫義順六安茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_322_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_322_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_322_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_322_4.jpg', '322', '15,000 - 22,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品為六安三票版本，三張票皆保存完整；茶品為竹簍與粽葉組合包裝，以頭芽製造，而且條索壯實勻齊，色澤黑褐油潤。大票資料可參閱《號級古典茶事典》第54頁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3298', '4 Boxes Of Taiwan Alishan High Mountain Tea, 2009 &amp; 2012', '阿里山農會特等獎 阿里山金萱茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_323_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_323_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_323_3.jpg', '323', '12,000 - 18,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組四盒的阿里山高山茶分別為2012年春季及2009年冬季金萱組特等獎的得獎之作。金萱茶帶天然的牛奶香，製成的茶葉香氣獨特，風味絕佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3299', '4 Boxes Of Taiwan Alishan High Mountain Tea, 2012', '2012年 梅山鄉農會特等獎 青心烏龍配金萱茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_324_1.jpg', '324', '12,000 - 18,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '烏龍茶與金萱茶同屬半發酵的高山茶；金萱茶帶淡淡天然奶香，烏龍茶則溫醇口感回甘，一組拍品帶來兩種不同口感，頗值收藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3300', '4 Boxes Of Taiwan Alishan High Mountain Tea, 2009 &amp; 2012', '阿里山農會特等獎 阿里山青心烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_325_1.jpg', '325', '18,000 - 28,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組四盒的阿里山高山茶分別為2012年春季及2009年冬季的特等獎得獎之作。阿里山高山茶區被稱為臺灣高山茶最頂級的茶品，在市場上相當搶手，獲獎作品為甚。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3301', '2 Boxes Of Oolong Tea, 2006', '2006年 和平農鄉會特等獎 梨山茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_326_1.jpg', '326', '20,000 - 30,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '梨山茶是產自台灣高海拔地區的烏龍茶，其芽葉柔軟，香氣淡雅，茶水色蜜綠顯黃，滋味甘醇，滑軟耐沖泡，茶湯冷後更能凝聚香甜，愛茶之人不可錯過。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3302', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2006', '2006年 北埔鄉農會特獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_327_1.jpg', '327', '28,000 - 40,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '新竹縣東方美人茶的茶價年年攀升，在2006年時市價已達台幣48萬元1斤；本組拍品更獲得北埔鄉農會評審的特獎，就品飲及收藏而言，如此出色的茶品相信是別具雅趣的選擇。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3303', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2005', '2005年 全國特等獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_328_1.jpg', '328', '30,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '本拍品榮獲2005年全台灣東方美人茶比賽的最高榮譽特等獎，是台灣最知名的茶品之一。此款茶是半發酵茶之中發酵程度最重的茶品，其茶湯不苦不澀，湯色溫潤透明，帶淡淡蜜味與果香，教人陶醉。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3304', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2006', '2006年 新竹縣政府特等獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_329_1.jpg', '329', '30,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '這一組兩罐的拍品曾獲得2006年新竹縣政府東方美人茶比賽最高等級特等獎，質素之佳不容置疑。它是台灣最知名的茶品之一，它具有採收量少、有機天然的特色；而且帶甘甜蜜香、花香、果香，深受世界各地茶友所愛戴，為收藏品飲的最佳選擇。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3305', '2 Boxes Of Oolong Tea With Champion, 2005', '2005年 台灣農委會冠軍 青心烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_330_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_330_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_330_3.jpg', '330', '80,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '一組兩盒的青心烏龍榮獲2005年全台灣冬季優質茶競賽冠軍，被譽為「台灣第一好茶」。在涼冷的自然環境中製作出半球型翠綠色的烏龍茶，可沖泡出蜜綠色茶湯，口味甘醇並芬多精幽香；這種獨特風味為茶人所鍾愛。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3306', '2 Boxes Of Oolong Tea With Golden Award, 2005', '2009年 海峽兩岸金獎 春季青心鳥龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_331_1.jpg', '331', '50,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '青心烏龍是台灣傳統茶樹品種之一，用半球形烏龍茶製程，發酵程度比較輕，輕烘焙，保留原味。本拍品原封未開，並曾於2009年獲得海峽兩岸烏龍茶展銷會的金獎，實力無容置疑，廣受歡迎。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3307', '2 Boxes Of Dongding Oolong Tea, 2009', '2009年 鹿谷農鄉會特等獎 青心烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_332_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_332_2.jpg', '332', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '凍頂烏龍乃烏龍茶中的最高級別，製作過程講求緊結均整，外形曲卷成半球體，白毫顯露，色澤墨綠烏亮；香氣似桂花，茶味微甜，回甘快又耐泡。本拍品更為得獎之作，實乃箇中精品，廣受歡迎。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3308', '4 Boxes Of Oolong Tea, 2010', '2010年 仁愛農鄉會特等獎 青心烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_333_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_333_2.jpg', '333', '38,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '憑藉專業的製茶技術與嚴苛的茶葉精製控管二者緊密配合，本拍品喜獲2010年冬季及春季合歡山高冷茶競賽特等獎，原封未開，為品飲佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3309', '2 Boxes Of Oolong Tea, 2008', '2008年 永隆鳳凰特等獎 凍頂烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_334_1.jpg', '334', '20,000 - 30,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '永隆鳳凰社區是凍頂茶的發源地，也是全台灣最早推廣凍頂烏龍茶的社區，舉辦比賽茶越20多年。比賽茶數量稀有，並強調凍頂烏龍茶富喉韻，入口生津的風味，能獲獎的寥寥可數，必為上佳之作。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3310', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2014', '2014年 新竹縣政府特等獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_335_1.jpg', '335', '20,000 - 30,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '這一組兩罐的拍品曾獲得2014年新竹東方美人茶比賽最高等級特等獎，質素之佳不容置疑。東方美人茶是台灣特有的茶品，這種茶最特別之處在於必須經由小綠葉蟬刺吸而生成，侵害愈嚴重茶品質侵害愈嚴重品質愈好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3311', '2 Boxes Of Dong Din Oolong Tea, 2015', '2015年 凍頂合作社特等獎 青心烏龍', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_336_1.jpg', '336', '8,000 - 12,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3312', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2005', '2005年 全國頭等獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_337_1.jpg', '337', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3313', '2 Cans Of Oriental Beauty Tea, 2011', '2011年 新竹縣政府特等獎 東方美人茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_338_1.jpg', '338', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3314', 'A Piece Of Extremely Rare’ Jingchanghao’ Pu-er Tea Cake, 1940&#039;s', '百年 敬昌號圓茶', '38', '/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_247_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_247_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a27/LOTNO_247_3.jpg', '247', '', '649,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '這片敬昌號圓茶倉儲良好，餅面完整，餅身表現均稱豐滿，外觀圓順。茶葉內仍能見白底紅字的內飛，一直珍藏於少數藏家手裡。茶餅的壓制技術非常精細而規矩，採用普洱正山最上好的大葉種茶樹製成，其條索肥碩，葉子寬大，茶菁有如泡過茶油，油亮充足，帶金黃色碩大的毫頭。 <br />\n1921年時敬昌號茶莊是江城地方最大最有名的普洱茶莊之一，在所有先期私人茶莊的茶品中，首推敬昌和同慶圓茶；而敬昌號是當中製造技術最優良，其茶餅壓制技術、筒包技術、竹箬篾條材料、內飛內票的設計和印刷，以及貯存陳放方法等都是數一數二。直至現在，普洱茶界仍以此茶作為普洱茶品質的標杆，可見此茶地位之高。<br />\n有關資料可參閱《號級古董茶事典》第236至237頁。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3315', 'A sterling Silver Kettle With Heart Sutra Inscription', '隆真作 般若心經純銀茶壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_101_6.jpg', '101', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：隆真<br />\n箱蓋題：盤若心經銀瓶 隆真作 <br />\n共箱<br />\nH15cm，D15cm，重367g<br />\n<br />\n此藏品體形飽滿渾厚，皮色亮澤，壺身虔刻《般若波羅蜜多心經》，刀筆流暢富神韻；砲管形直流出水順暢，配寶珠形摘鈕，珠圓玉潤。圓中帶方之提梁與壺肩鑄成一體，提梁近兩耳處鑲斷熱環方便使用，為收藏家不可多得的心頭好。&quot;', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3316', 'A Carved Iron Tetsubin by Kibundo, First Generation', '初代龜文堂 鎏金銀菖蒲戲蟹鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_102_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_102_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_102_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_102_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_102_5.jpg', '102', '80,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器款：日本龜文、湖巖堂印款<br />\r\n箱蓋題：龜文堂造<br />\r\n共箱<br />\r\nH22cm，D17.5cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此器壺肚廣圓，浮雕立體菖蒲從壺底向上延伸，流線滿佈壺身，以鎏金點綴作花，螃蟹遊戲於其間，畫面活潑中有動，配以靈芝造型嵌銀點綴銅提把，寓意吉祥。<br />\r\n壺身銀嵌印章日本龜文，壺底款模糊，隱約可判斷為湖巖堂印款。&quot;', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3317', 'A Sterling Silver Kettle With An Iron Handle BY Somi Sawada', '澤田宗味造 大槌目紋鐵把純銀壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_103_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_103_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_103_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_103_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_103_5.jpg', '103', '26,000 - 38,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器底款：純銀<br />\r\n共箱，箱蓋內款：澤田宗味造<br />\r\nH15.5cm，D17cm， W454g<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺身飾有形態不一的大搥目紋，使銀器的折射及光澤提升至更高層次，為難得佳作。鐵打壺把上以金銀嵌出代表日本皇室的菊花圖紋，更添高雅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3318', 'A Sterling Silver Kettle With Arare Embossment', '尚美堂 霧霰紋銀壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_104_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_104_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_104_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_104_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_104_5.jpg', '104', '18,000 - 28,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '箱面題：銀製霰打湯沸<br />\r\n蓋面款：尚美堂造<br />\r\n共箱<br />\r\nH17cm，D15cm，W519g', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3319', 'A Maru-Gata Silver Kettle With A Short And Round Spout', '砲口丸型銀壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_105_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_105_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_105_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_105_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_105_5.jpg', '105', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n共箱<br />\nH13.5cm，D13.5cm，W260g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丸型器身端莊沉穩，銅圈鈕摘環環緊扣，為整器增添跳脫靈動的色彩，感覺簡潔大器。整器包漿瑩潤富光澤，流光溢彩。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3320', 'A Carved Tin Tea Caddy with Shen Cunzhuo Mark', '沈存周刻 古錫雕詩文茶罐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_106_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_106_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_106_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_106_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_106_5.jpg', '106', '', '53,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n器底款：竹居主人刻<br />\n共箱<br />\n箱面：「沈存周 茶壺」及「楊基之詩」<br />\nH7.5 cm，D8.5cm<br />\n<br />\n此罐直口短頸，圓鼓腹而腹下略收；一面刻上明代詩人楊基寫的《立夏前一日有賦》；另一面刻挫以山水家屋圖，遠近山巒，兀立隱現，是收藏珍品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3321', 'A Sterling Silver Kyusu With Jade Handle By Ikoma', '生駒造 玉把純銀急須', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_107_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_107_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_107_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_107_4.jpg', '107', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：純、生駒<br />\nH5.5cm，D13.5cm，W171g<br />\n<br />\n此急須為純銀所造，壺身扁圓，銀製器身上滿佈凹凸有致的荒地岩肌紋，立體漸變，材質貴氣而不流俗艷；玉雕瑞獸為點晴之筆，溫潤高貴，古樸雅致。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3322', 'A Carved Gold-and-Silver-Inlaid Iron Tetsubin by Kougyokudo', '光玉堂 嵌金銀山水家屋圖鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_108_9.jpg', '108', '90,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n蓋內款：光玉堂<br />\n箱蓋內款：平安光玉堂<br />\n共箱<br />\nH20cm，D17cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此壺鐵提梁直立，銅蓋包漿光潤；壺身兩面近景金雕山水家屋，樹木蔥蘢，碧波蕩漾，有舟徐行於其中；遠景山川錦繡，楊柳飄飄，水天一色，一派生機盎然。此藏品渾圓敦實，在鐵瓶素肌上飾嵌金圖樣，拙雅中見奢華。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3323', 'A Carved Gold And Silver-Inlaid Iron Tetsubin With A Silver Handle', '鐵紫堂造 金銀象嵌花草紋銀把鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_109_7.jpg', '109', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n蓋內款：鐵紫堂造<br />\n共箱，箱蓋有款<br />\nH16cm，D11cm<br />\n<br />\n鐵紫堂是江戶時期京都的特殊堂號，其技法別樹一幟。此壺雙面均以嵌金技法，浮雕花草紋樣，在寂靜的美景裡增添一抹律動感，靜中有動，動中漸靜；配上銀製槌目紋刀把，饒富趣味。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3324', 'A Sterling Silver Teapot with Arare Embossment', '純銀　霧霰紋茶壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_110_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_110_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_110_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_110_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_110_5.jpg', '110', '22,000 - 38,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：純銀<br />\n箱面題：純銀製湯沸<br />\n共箱<br />\nH25cm，D19.5cm，W1415g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重逾1400克的純銀壺敦厚穩重，整器滿佈勻稱漸變的霧霰紋飾，工法嚴謹；配菊花形金鈕摘與花瓣形摘座，巧添貴氣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3325', 'A Golden Carved Kettle With A Phoenix Spout By Zoroku', '藏六造 純金 饕餮紋鳳口茶壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_111_9.jpg', '111', '', '566,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器底款：藏六造 、純金<br />\n共箱<br />\n箱蓋內海野忠行識，題「五代秦藏六造無紛者也」<br />\nH16cm，D17.5cm， W992g<br />\n<br />\n此品以純金鑄造而成，奢華大氣，尊貴耀眼，保養得宜。流口巧妙依形打造成引頸長鳴的鳳凰，柳葉細目，出神入化，盡顯百鳥之王的靈動尊貴；更寓意鳳鳴朝陽，盛世榮華太平。<br />\n壺腹及壺蓋同飾半浮雕青銅器式饕餮紋，是藏六製壺的經典造型；莊嚴大氣，象徵王權的威嚴；雙環摘鈕精工細膩，在純金器的奢華中點綴了優雅韻致；提梁飾藤把起斷熱之用，構思巧妙，匠心獨運。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3326', 'A Carved Gold-and-Silver-Inlaid Iron Tetsubin by Ryubundo', '龍文堂 嵌金雲龍盛上鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_112_11.jpg', '112', '', '377,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n蓋內款：龍文堂造<br />\nH19cm，D14cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n釜師在粗獷的荒地肌紋上展現非凡刻功，壺身巧雕神龍盤飛祥雲之中，龍身金鱗片片，龍鬚威武雄壯；蒼龍騰躍，氣勢雄偉，英姿凜然，無拘無束。銅蓋上圈圈弦紋，上飾花苞形摘，倍添嬌美；三彎提梁有如浮雲，與壺腹飛龍呼應，造形一氣呵成。此藏器構圖縝密巧妙，精湛工藝不言於表。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3327', 'A Golden Teapot With Signature', '大淵武則 刀板瓣式藤把金壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_113_8.jpg', '113', '', '767,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：純金、光則<br />\n共箱<br />\n箱面題：純金製湯沸、光則<br />\nH22cm，D17 cm，1006G<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此金壺由日本當代金工大師大淵武則所製，整器純金所打，華美尊貴，氣質高雅。其刀板瓣式設計的槌打法使金的質感內收而沉穩，清心素面更顯高貴。提梁以藤覆蓋，整器在質感與色澤上比對強烈，予人無上的視覺享受。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3328', 'A Gold Kyusus with Signature', '純金 石黑光南 立筋紋急須', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_114_7.jpg', '114', '250,000 - 350,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器底款：純金 光南<br />\n箱蓋題：純金 立筋急須<br />\n共箱<br />\nL16.5cm，H8.5cm，W396g<br />\n<br />\n此藏品純金鍛造，小巧壺身為啞光立筋紋，低調中見奢華，華貴時尚。配素三彎流，出水順暢；乳白色牙側把則有助斷熱，尊貴中又添雅趣。金壺煮水，清心甘甜，入口順滑。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3329', 'A Carved Gold Kettle With Signature', '純金 水波紋松摘壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_115_7.jpg', '115', '220,000 - 350,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：純金<br />\n共箱，箱面題字<br />\nH11cm，D14cm，W519g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品純金鍛造，壺身不假雕飾，只見點點水波紋，營造流水淙淙之效，紋理疏密有致，宛若餘波蕩漾的湖面，開合有度，線條簡潔流暢。配松果摘與花形摘座，提梁接駁位置巧雕花瓣相互呼應，頗見巧思，尊貴中又添雅趣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3330', 'A Carved Bronze Teapot', '銀銅鎏金菖蒲壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_116_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_116_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_116_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_116_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_116_5.jpg', '116', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	 	<br />\n共箱<br />\nH18cm，D12.5cm，W457g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此器採用罕見銅和銀合製。壺身及壺蓋均立體雕塑鎏金菖蒲，其枝葉仰俯自如，出枝延至壺蓋，使紋飾構圖更顯生趣盎然；吐露飽滿的銀花苞象徵繁盛昌榮，呈現極緻工藝。配以盛放的花苞摘紐、竹節樣高身提把，令整器造型顯得修長雅致，別具氣韻。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3331', 'A Carved Tin Tea Caddy With Shen Cunzhou Mark', '沈存周款 漢詩梅花圖茶罐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_117_6.jpg', '117', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器底款：洋換<br />\n器身款：沈存周<br />\n蓋面題：清香喫茶<br />\nH6.5cm，D9cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n茶罐一面刻寒梅傲霜圖，另一面篆刻盧梅坡《雪梅》其二：「有梅無雪不精神，有雪無詩俗了人。日暮詩成天又雪，與梅並作十分春。」，運刀如筆又見冬日意境，值得收藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3332', 'A Tin Caddy With Signature', '家人居造 錫製大茶罐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_118_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_118_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_118_3.jpg', '118', '8,000 - 12,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：家人居造<br />\nH17cm，D14cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直口短頸錫茶罐造形內斂樸素，錫皮色澤古雅亮麗，質感極佳。整器簡約大氣，甚有茶道主張寂靜清和之氣韻。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3333', 'A Set Of Five Carved Bronze Chataku With Signature', '琢齋作 斑紫銅花草紋茶托 一套五件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_119_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_119_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_119_3.jpg', '119', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器身款：琢齋<br />\n共箱<br />\n蓋內有款：琢齋造<br />\nD11.4cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此套藏品由斑紫銅所鑄，其質感厚重，銅色紫中帶紅，使器物色調多變，呈現一種神秘的吸引力。器身以梅、蘭、竹、菊、松為題，迎風搖曳，線條優美。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3334', 'A Set OF Five Carved Mother-Of-Pearl-Inlaid Black Lacqure Basin', '黑漆嵌螺鈿人物圖盤 一套五件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_120_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_120_2.jpg', '120', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n共箱，蓋內題字<br />\nD12cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品以螺鈿工藝細嵌出五幅栩栩欲活的人物圖，人物在山內樓閣之間，談笑風生，甚具古韻。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3335', 'A Carved Cannibar Lacquer Plate With Gold Inlaid', '明 剔紅如意紋描金小碟', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_121_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_121_2.jpg', '121', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', 'H1.5cm，D14cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n器身巧雕如意祥紋，中央描金繪蓮花紋樣，祥雲紋向外延伸，立體感強。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3336', 'A Song Jian Tea Bowl', '宋 建窯 兔毛茶盞', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_122_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_122_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_122_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_122_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_122_5.jpg', '122', '', '29,500', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nH5.5cm，D13cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品為建窯茶盞，在窯內高溫焙燒的過程中，通過火煉，使釉面產生各種自然奇特的斑紋，形成的各種變幻莫測的釉色，予人感覺有若宇宙星空，精美絕倫。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3337', 'An Iron Carved Tetsubin With Animal Spout By Zoroku', '藏六造 荒地肌紋獸口鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_123_6.jpg', '123', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：藏六造<br />\n共箱<br />\nH13.5cm，D15cm <br />\n<br />\n此藏品為荒地紋肌，壺身及壺蓋皆以嵌銀絲的如意祥雲紋繞緣一圈，靈動秀氣。此壺流咀乃藏六經典獸口狀，雙目靈動，不怒而威。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3338', 'A Carved Gold-and-Silver-Inlaid Iron Tetsubin by Ryubundo', '龍文堂 嵌金銀葡萄藤蔓鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_124_6.jpg', '124', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n蓋內款：龍文堂造<br />\n共箱<br />\n蓋內款：龍文堂安之介造<br />\nH13cm，D17cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壺身呈荒地肌紋，壺腹兩面以嵌金銀勾勒出葡萄藤蔓圖樣，有碩果累累，豐收圓滿之美意。提梁同飾葡萄串串，點點銀光，頗見匠心。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3339', 'A Set Of Two Sterling Silver Kettles With Arare Embossment', '純銀 霧霰紋壺一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_125_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_125_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_125_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_125_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_125_5.jpg', '125', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器底款：純銀<br />\r\n共箱<br />\r\n銀壺一｜H12.5cm，D10.5cm，W228g<br />\r\n銀壺二｜H12.5cm，D10.5cm，W222g', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3340', 'Five Pieces Of Sterling Silver Tumbler Set With Signature', '純銀 回紋六角酒杯一套五件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_126_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_126_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_126_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_126_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_126_5.jpg', '126', '', '5,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：純銀製<br />\n箱面題：純銀製 御盃<br />\n蓋內有款<br />\nH3cm，D4.5cm，W25g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一組五件的小酒杯六角形制，六邊切面為磨砂面，杯緣飾如意回紋，寓意吉祥之外六見匠心巧思。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3341', 'A Set Of Glaze Water Drop', '海鼠釉水滴套組', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_127_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_127_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_127_3.jpg', '127', '18,000 - 30,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n箱面題：翰墨因緣<br />\n共箱<br />\nH3cm，W7cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海鼠釉本名海曙釉，是稀有瓷器之一，古人以「雨過天晴雲破處」形容其窯變效果。此水滴胎質細膩光滑，雅致可人，是為臻品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3342', 'An Iron Tetsuibin With Silver And Gold Inlay By Zoroku', '藏六造 金銀象嵌獸口鐵壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_128_6.jpg', '128', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n箱面題：藏六造<br />\n共箱<br />\nH16.5cm，D17cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藏六家族距今已有150年的歷史。深受藏家喜愛的獸口壺，是藏六本人最初於龍文堂時期學過的獸口型壺技法。 此壺腹金銀嵌一圈纏枝紋緣飾，倍添華貴；銅蓋飾金嵌花草和紙扇，詩情雅致。箱體見「藏六造」字樣。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3343', 'A Carved Iron Tetsubin by Nihonbaisen', '日本梅泉造 古韻山水图鐵壶', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_129_6.jpg', '129', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n壺身款：日本梅泉<br />\n壺底方章款：家拙日本琵琶湖之東<br />\nH19.8cm，D18cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藏品壺身採用鐵浮雕生動細膩表現出遠近山勢綿延，碧波閣榭隱於中，一派靜謐恬然之景，又用銀鑲嵌雀鳥環飛，銀之光潔對比生鐵的古拙，一明一暗，一動一靜，匠心獨運，可見一斑。原配銅蓋摘鈕上亦鑲嵌銀飛鳥與提把上秀竹互相呼應，寓意長壽吉祥。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3344', 'A Tin Caddy With Signature', '古錫花鳥紋茶罐一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_130_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_130_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_130_3.jpg', '130', '6,000 - 10,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	 	<br />\n共箱<br />\n箱蓋題：「瑞花文 合子」<br />\nH11.5cm，D5.5cm<br />\n<br />\n此藏品為一對圓筒高身錫茶罐，罐身雕有荼蘼盛放山茶花，雲鴿遊戲花間；蓋頂刻太極兩儀，包漿色澤古雅樸素，喻品茗者常存茶意道心，隨喜自在。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3345', 'A Set Of Two Carved Iron Tea Caddies By Shoyeido', '松榮堂造　古錫刻花鳥紋茶罐 一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_131_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_131_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_131_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_131_4.jpg', '131', '', '8,850', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：淨足、松榮堂造<br />\r\n茶罐一 | H11cm，D7.5cm<br />\r\n茶罐二 | H9.5cm，D9cm', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3346', 'A Hammered Iron Tea Caddy', '一如造 鐵打出花鳥紋茶罐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_132_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_132_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_132_3.jpg', '132', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器身款：一如<br />\nH13.5cm，D6.5cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3347', 'A Carved Water Drop In Sterling Silver With Signature', '瓜形銀水滴', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_133_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_133_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_133_3.jpg', '133', '3,000 - 5,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器底有款<br />\r\n共箱<br />\r\nH5.5cm，D5.5cm，W55g', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3348', 'A Carved Bronze Vase With Gold And Silver Inlaid', '金銀嵌山水家屋圖花瓶', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_134_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_134_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_134_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_134_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_134_5.jpg', '134', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	<br />\n共箱<br />\nH24cm，D13cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瓶身兩面開光鑲嵌樓閣山水圖，家屋樓閣佇立於遠近山巒之中，小橋流水，描繪出傳說中的蓬萊仙景，氣勢恢宏。瓶頸以金銀鑲嵌豐瓜碩果，瓶口處飾如意回紋，整器設計拙雅中見奢華，寓意安定富貴。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3349', 'A Carved Sterling Silver Vase With Signature', '金光堂 雲龍紋銀花瓶', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_8.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_9.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_10.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_11.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_12.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_135_13.jpg', '135', '250,000 - 380,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器身題：金光堂守親堂並雕刻<br />\n落款：東台子美彥補作<br />\n箱蓋內題：銀象嵌雕刻花瓶 美彥補作 <br />\n共箱<br />\nH59cm，D39cm，W18225g<br />\n<br />\n匠師在素面銀瓶上打造出氣度恢弘、壯麗華貴的藝術品。瓶身正中心以精細手工勾畫出呈騰雲翩舞之飛龍圖，龍身刻魚鱗紋，龍鬚飄動，栩栩如生，仿若神光華普照大地。飛龍外則細膩如繡地勾勒如意雲紋，一金一銀，一虛一實，璀璨中又見雅致，富麗中又見生機。整器層次生動，爐火純青，嘆為觀止。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3350', 'A Bamboo Flower Vase With Signature', '元之齋 竹編花器', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_136_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_136_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_136_3.jpg', '136', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：元之齋<br />\n共箱<br />\nH45.5cm，D20cm<br />\n<br />\n細密的網狀織紋相互纏繞，配古意十足的提把，整體色澤古樸清麗；乃實用性與藝術性兼具的創作。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3351', 'A Bamboo Vase in Round Shape', '竹編圓工環耳花器', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_137_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_137_2.jpg', '137', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n共箱<br />\nH20.5cm，D24cm<br />\n<br />\n圓潤器身上巧妙結合兩種不同編織手法；上半網密，下半則以簡單縱向線條修飾，營造縷空效果，簡潔大氣。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3352', 'A Bamboo Flower Vase With Signature', '修荺齋作 竹編花器', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_138_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_138_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_138_3.jpg', '138', '6,000 - 10,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：修筠齋<br />\nH22cm，D41cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3353', 'A Bamboo Flower Vase With Signature', '巧竹齋款 竹編花器', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_139_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_139_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_139_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_139_4.jpg', '139', '3,000 - 5,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：巧竹齋<br />\n箱面題：白竹製華籃、銘　雙月<br />\n蓋內款：巧竹齋造<br />\n共箱<br />\nH31.5cm，D28cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3354', 'A Pair of Wooden Ornament in Gourd Shape', '葫蘆擺件一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_140_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_140_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_140_3.jpg', '140', '', '7,080', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n共箱，蓋內有款<br />\nH12.5cm，W7cm<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3355', 'A Set Of Carved Bronze Paperweights', '銅卧馬 配 福蛙紙鎮', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_141_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_141_2.jpg', '141', '5,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n卧 馬｜H4cm，D5cm<br />\n青 蛙｜H2.5cm，D4.5cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3356', 'A Bronzed Plate With Gold Inlay By Zouroku', '藏六造 青銅鎏金瑞鳥飾皿', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_142_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_142_2.jpg', '142', '12,000 - 18,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：藏六<br />\nH8.5cm，D15cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以藏六家族最經典的塗金工藝於古拙青銅上鑲造象徵吉祥之鳥羽翼花紋，鎏金鳥頭，突顯生機與氣勢。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3357', 'A Carved Bronze Double-Ground Censer', '瓜瓞綿綿葫蘆形香爐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_143_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_143_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_143_3.jpg', '143', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	<br />\nH29cm，D25cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此爐通體雕葫蘆藤葉及花卉紋樣；葫蘆諧音「福祿」，代表了多子多福，家族興旺繁盛。可見此藏品既可如意進福，亦可成為文房精緻雅玩，是為難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3358', 'A Carved Sterling Silver Hanging Censer', '平安金美造 純銀 鳳凰紋吊香爐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_144_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_144_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_144_3.jpg', '144', '', '29,500', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	 	<br />\n共箱<br />\n蓋面題：桐鳳凰透 純銀釣香爐<br />\n蓋內款：平安 金美造<br />\nH9cm，D8.5cm，W239g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「蕭韶九成，鳳凰來儀」；千百年來鳳凰被視作祥瑞的象徵，在純銀的雕香爐上縷雕鳳凰于飛，更寓意夫妻間和睦遂順。香爐雕工簡練大氣，雲霧繚繞下，裊裊悠悠，令人心馳神往。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3359', 'A Mother-Of-Pearl-Inlaid Box And Cover, Ming Dynasty', '明 黑漆嵌螺鈿 鳳凰紋香盒', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_145_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_145_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_145_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_145_4.jpg', '145', '', '14,160', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n箱面題：唐物青貝香盒<br />\n共箱<br />\nH2.8cm，D7.8cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品螺鈿片剝離如紙，螺鈿嵌製百鳥之皇，鳳凰閃閃生輝，有鳳來義，象徵吉祥和諧。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3360', 'A Carved Gold-Inlaid Bronze Box', '金銀象嵌菊紋卷物形鐵香盒', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_146_6.jpg', '146', '', '23,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '共箱，箱面題字<br />\r\nL9cm，D3cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此盒長圓筒形仿如書畫捲軸，向外拉出則可作儲物用，獨具匠心。鐵盒上以金嵌菊紋，乃日本皇室象徵，富貴逼人。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3361', 'Green Qinan Powder', '綠油奇楠粉', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_147_1.jpg', '147', '', '88,500', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n	<br />\n重40.7g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此香粉選自上等綠油奇楠，酒脂豐富，輕扭香韻醇厚一流，其奶香與甜味直入鼻腔久久不散，為上爐品香之選。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3362', 'A 10mm Vietnamese Nha Trang Agarwood Malas', '越南芽莊 八毫米沉香佛珠', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_148_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_148_2.jpg', '148', '60,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：越南芽莊<br />\n108顆，珠徑8mm，約重28g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此香香氣清涼雅致，散發著清爽的熟果氣息，甘冽宜人，適合輕撫手中或佩戴身上，氣味通透聞後使人清新舒心。由於芽莊沉香香材稀少難尋，珍貴非常，是藏家夢寐以求的上品沉香', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3363', '3 Pieces Of Hainan Agarwood in Sinking Grade', '沉水 海南沉香三件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_149_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_149_2.jpg', '149', '120,000 - 200,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：海南<br />\n尺寸不一，共重約37.5g，沉水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明代名醫李時珍在《本草綱目》中曾記載到：「海南沉香，一片萬金，冠絕天下」，可見海南沉香一直珍貴難得。<br />\n本藏品凝練光鮮，大氣古樸，結油飽滿，包漿瑩潤富光澤，入水能沉。天然海南沉香一直都冠絕百香，其味香甜醇美，渾厚深沉，歷百年而不衰，反而更加醇厚，收藏價值極高。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3364', 'A Piece of Carved Qinan', '李鳳榮雕 黃奇楠 琴瑟和鳴山形雕件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_150_6.jpg', '150', '300,000 - 500,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nH15.3cm，L11.6cm，重約173.5g<br />\n附香粉，約9g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此山子雕件出自中國著名工藝雕刻家李鳳榮，以珍貴的黃奇楠為材，隨形巧妙雕琢峰巒迭嶂之態。山間松樹叢生，山巒雲繞，偶有一亭，老人與知音於山林間奏樂琴瑟合鳴，盡顯山林之樂。<br />\n此黃奇楠表面見油，皮色深棕，包漿古樸雅致，香味清新具穿透力。家中供賞，古意盎然，妙不可言，為工料皆美之作。<br />\n雕件背金漆刻有「李鳳榮 作」款，附同料香粉。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3365', 'A Piece of Yellow Qinan Plaque', '黃奇楠無事牌', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_151_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_151_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_151_3.jpg', '151', '50,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nL60mm，W40mm，D10mm，重20g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品香氣甚佳，穿透力非常，急沁入喉，氣味層次豐富；尾調帶青草的芬芳清爽，甘涼如蜜，細膩溫婉卻又明麗雅致，餘香恬然持久。佛說：無即是有，無事牌也祝福吉祥多福，應有盡有。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3366', 'A 10mm Agarwood Malas', '七毫米沉香佛珠', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_152_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_152_2.jpg', '152', '', '11,210', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n108顆，珠徑7mm，重17.9g<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3367', 'A 10mm Yellow Qinan Malas', '黃奇楠十毫米佛珠', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_153_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_153_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_153_3.jpg', '153', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n108顆，珠徑10mm，重54.9g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本藏品以溫潤有體的黃奇楠設計，色澤金黃，深棕色香脂射腺密致，禪意清雅。<br />\n此佛珠氣息悠遠，富於變化，香型甜涼純淨，實為奇楠中的逸品。<br />\n奇楠是沉香中極少現世的特殊品種，不少奇楠愛好者都會把所喜愛的奇楠香品隨身攜帶，望在潛移默化之間諦聽純淨心靈的禪意與簡樸。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3368', 'A Vietnamese Nha Trang Qinan 16 Beads Bracelet', '越南 黃奇楠十六子手串', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_154_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_154_2.jpg', '154', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：越南<br />\n共16顆，珠徑10及12毫米，重12.48g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此款手串產自越南，味道醇厚上乘，具奇楠特有的爆發力，甘甜馥郁中透著絲絲涼意，涼意直沖上丹田，在鼻腔，咽喉處化開，久久縈繞沁人心脾。整條手串形製小巧，顆珠大小相隔別出心裁，而且粒粒皆烏黑油亮，是難得佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3369', 'A 10mm Yellow Qinan 17 Beads Bracelet', '越南黃奇楠十毫米17子手串', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_155_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_155_2.jpg', '155', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：越南<br />\n17顆，珠徑10mm，重9.64g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此黃奇楠手串色澤黑潤，深棕色香脂射腺密致，禪意清雅。戴於手上時甜涼純正的香韻久久縈繞沁人心脾，叫人暢快愉悅。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3370', 'A Piece Of Carved Vietnamese Black Qinan', '李鳳榮作 越南 黑奇楠雕件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_156_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_156_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_156_3.jpg', '156', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：越南<br />\nH7cm，D8cm，重63g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此黑奇楠雕件皮色呈琥珀，體斑之間見油線紋理非常細膩，油份十足，散發幽玄的藥香味。作者取其天然質地與紋理，巧雕兀立山巒，底部有如波濤萬丈，捲起風雲暗動，如橫峰又如蒼雲，與世無爭又凜乎不可侵的氣質，彌足珍貴。不論從取材，還是雕刻工藝，均是精益求精，造就出令人尊崇的作品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3371', '3 Pieces Of Green Qinan', '綠奇楠三塊', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_157_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_157_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_157_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_157_4.jpg', '157', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n尺寸不一，重量約70.5g<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品表面泛出黑油，皮色深棕，如蒼山覆苔，豐澤映入。香味清新具穿透力，鮮靈而具穿透力，引人入勝。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3372', 'A Piece Of Carved Vietnamese Agarwood', '越南荷塘錦鯉紅土雕件', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_158_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_158_2.jpg', '158', '30,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：越南<br />\nH6.5cm，D6.4cm，重19.2g<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3373', 'A Carved White Porcelain Censer', '「大明宣德年製款」德化窯白瓷象耳香爐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_159_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_159_2.jpg', '159', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n底款：大明宣德年製款<br />\n共箱<br />\nH12.5cm，D12.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此爐釉質瑩厚細膩，潤如油脂，胎白質堅，胎釉結合緊密渾為一體，是為難得佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3374', 'A Carved Bronze Censer In Lion Shape', '銅製瑞獅香爐', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_160_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_160_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_160_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_160_4.jpg', '160', '6,000 - 10,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n共箱<br />\n箱面：獅子香爐<br />\nH19cm，D13.5cm<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3375', 'A Carved Incense Tube With Signature', '二代義山 紅斑竹雕漢詩紋香筒', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_161_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_161_2.jpg', '161', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n器身款：義山<br />\n箱面題：香筒<br />\n蓋內款：二代義山作<br />\n共箱<br />\nL37cm<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3376', 'A Carved Bamboo Incense tube With Signature', '珍賢款 竹雕山水人物紋香筒', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_162_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_162_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_162_3.jpg', '162', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器身款：珍賢<br />\nL37cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3377', 'A Gilt-Inlaid Black Lacquer Maki-E Box', '蒔繪金楓銀樺煙草漆盒', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_163_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_163_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_163_3.jpg', '163', '5,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nH16cm，D29cm<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3378', 'An Inscribed Yixing Teapot', '烏泥心經茶壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_164_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_164_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_164_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_164_4.jpg', '164', '', '9,440', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nH5.5cm，D9.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品由烏泥所製，發色烏亮，壺身刻般若心經經文，字體蒼勁。整器小巧盈握，下腹略收；配環把及砲口壺流，罕見的平頭壺蓋，大器古樸。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3379', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot, Mid-Qing Dynasty', '清中　「森峰雅樂」款紫泥茶壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_165_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_165_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_165_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_165_4.jpg', '165', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：森峰雅樂<br />\nH8cm，D12.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此古春壺年代久遠，造型大器，氣韻古穆，鼓腹，直嘴，圈把。壺身色厚，包漿溫潤，沉靜溫存；胎體則輕薄古雅，反映泥料陳腐充份，火候恰到好處。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3380', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot In late Qing Dynasty', '清末  紫泥扁圓壺一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_166_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_166_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_166_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_166_4.jpg', '166', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：閉門即是深山<br />\n共箱<br />\nH7cm，D11cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圓渾小巧的扁圓壺以詩詞為款，詩以壺傳，壺以詩貴，如此做法常見於清代；壺咀與壺蓋的接泥痕跡於清末年間亦頗為流行，全器勻整秀雅，飽滿有神，較為少見。其中一壺有損耗痕跡。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3381', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature, Republic Period', '民初 藝古齋 壽珍款 段泥矮足古壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_167_6.jpg', '167', '', '29,500', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n銘刻：傳世富貴<br />\n底款：藝古齋<br />\n蓋內款：壽珍<br />\n共箱<br />\nH8cm，D17cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是民初年間以老段泥所造，泥色熟；鈕摘接橋以竹為形，壺咀及壺把相當有力，線條大器流暢。器身雕刻蘭花紋樣，造形生動，刀工流麗，師傅功力深厚。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3382', 'A Pair Of Yixing Teapot With Signature, late Qing Dynasty', '清末民初 吳德盛款 朱泥具輪珠一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_6.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_7.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_168_8.jpg', '168', '', '92,040', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：吳德盛製<br />\n蓋面題：朱泥急須一對<br />\n共箱<br />\nH7cm，D10cm<br />\n<br />\n此對壺選料上乘，朱泥砂質細膩溫潤，火侯十足，色澤紅潤，口線嚴密，保香一流。器底見早期單框大字款，加上壺內三孔，造功精良可謂非常罕有，對壺堪稱文物級藏品，是為難得。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3383', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '朱泥古春壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_169_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_169_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_169_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_169_4.jpg', '169', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：乾隆年製<br />\n蓋內款：水平<br />\n共箱<br />\nH6cm，D8.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古春壺渾圓別緻，三彎流，蓋大而平，器身輪廓分明，線條流暢。蓋緣銜接嚴密，間不容髮，茶香不易散渙；壺身有輕微耗損。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3384', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '清德堂款 朱泥蓮子壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_170_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_170_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_170_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_170_4.jpg', '170', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：清德堂<br />\nH9.5cm，D13cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此壺狀如蓮子，珠摘截蓋，圈把配砲嘴。形制小巧，線條優美，胎薄輕盈，是泡飲上好茶品佳器。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3385', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature', '孟臣款 留佩刻詩文朱泥壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_171_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_171_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_171_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_171_4.jpg', '171', '', '12,980', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n蓋內款：留佩<br />\n底款：孟臣製<br />\nH8.5cm，D12.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此品泥色細潤，為朱泥胎質，器身鼓圓，蕈菇形壺蓋弧度自然，砲口壺流，線條舒展優美。器型比例協調，結構嚴謹，底刻詩文，技藝精湛。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3386', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature', '孟臣款 朱泥宮燈壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_172_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_172_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_172_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_172_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_172_5.jpg', '172', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：孟臣製<br />\r\n銘刻：明月一天涼似水<br />\r\nH8.5cm，D11.5cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此藏品為朱泥製，壺身圓潤討喜，柔潤幼細；配圈把、劍嘴及圓鈕，底刻詩文，實為惹人寶愛之伴茶佳侶。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3387', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot, Early Years of the Republic of China', '民初 詩文花卉芝麻紋壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_173_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_173_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_173_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_173_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_173_5.jpg', '173', '8,000 - 16,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：振華出品<br />\nH10cm，D17.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此壺鼓腹上斂下收，圈把，鈕摘作瓜蒂狀。腹面一面刻有詩文，另一面巧雕花卉紋樣。此器素淨，以簡練流暢的造型，雅致明快的色澤，反映文士的意趣和審美觀。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3388', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature', '邵景南款 留佩刻詩文朱泥壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_174_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_174_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_174_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_174_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_174_5.jpg', '174', '', '37,760', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n器底款：邵景南<br />\n壺腹款：留佩<br />\nH7.5cm，D11.5cm<br />\n<br />\nA Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature<br />\n<br />\n此壺壺腹飽滿豐腴，寶珠壺鈕，截蓋，圈把。全器勻整秀雅，泥色油潤帶光澤，氣韻古穆，刻有唐陸羽《茶經·事》撮句：「香分花上露，水汲石中泉」，簡樸中見雅致。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3389', '4 Pair Of Yixing Teapot', '朱泥壺一組四對 (共八隻)', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_175_6.jpg', '175', '', '25,960', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n朱泥壺一：H7.5cm，D11cm<br />\n朱泥壺二：H8cm，D11cm<br />\n朱泥壺三：H7cm，D10cm<br />\n朱泥壺四：H6cm，D9.5cm<br />\n落款：貢局、龍印、清德堂及真自履源<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一組四對朱泥壺分別為具輪珠、小圓珠、蓮子及梨式；此四式朱泥壺形態俏妙，紅而鮮潤，做工精巧, 更難得成對, 堪稱極品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3390', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot', '柏原刻 朱泥榴皮小壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_176_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_176_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_176_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_176_4.jpg', '176', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：柏原<br />\n銘刻：一枝香吐味<br />\nH9cm，D11.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此壺從壺鈕及壺腹均呈寶珠的圓潤型態，團結藴蓄，壺蓋若蕈菇，配三彎流，幼耳把，圈足。胎質潤澤，入手紮實沉穩；底刻「一枝香吐味」，字體工整有勁，頗值收藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3391', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '陳增元款 朱泥水平壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_177_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_177_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_177_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_177_4.jpg', '177', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：陳增元<br />\nH9.5cm，D13cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此品為朱泥胎質，泥色細潤，寶珠鈕，鼓腹收足，肩部與腹下弧度自然，線條舒展優美。壺流與壺口高度持平，出湯順暢；圓形圈把，把持舒適。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3392', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature', '周寧華 紫泥花卉紋壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_178_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_178_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_178_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_178_4.jpg', '178', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n壺底款：周寧華<br />\n壺身有款<br />\n蓋內款：寧華<br />\nH14cm，D14cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此藏品為花貨中的大型紫泥壺，泥色沉穩、細緻，以櫻花形態示人，清麗脫俗。此壺手工精湛，壺把、壺蓋與一彎咀均以花枝為形，線條生動，形態挺秀；壺腹則巧雕櫻花紋樣，雍和秀麗，為不可多得之作。壺腹見方園牌標貼。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3393', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '紫泥 太極暖鼓壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_179_6.jpg', '179', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '紫泥 太極暖鼓壺<br />\n<br />\n壺底款：蔣坤仙製<br />\n手柄款：坤仙<br />\n蓋內款：坤仙<br />\n壺身刻字<br />\nH7cm，D8cm<br />\n<br />\nA Signed Yixing Teapot<br />\n<br />\n圓潤壺身一邊行書銘刻詩文，落款「雲春刻」，字體蒼勁有力；另一邊刻拆枝梅花圖，率性灑脫的詩文與梅花清雅的姿態相輔相承，散發著充滿禪意的典雅，深受文人雅士的鍾愛。壺身見方園牌標貼。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3394', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '朱泥玉笠壺一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_180_6.jpg', '180', '', '21,240', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：吳小華製<br />\r\n壺柄款：小華<br />\r\n蓋內款：小華<br />\r\nH9cm，D10cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此壺身圓潤討喜，一彎嘴曲懷有度，仿佛漁翁撒竿，壺體線條舒展流暢，勻稱柔和；壺把設計頗見巧思，風格清和恬淡，乃品茗良伴。壺身見有方園牌標貼。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3395', 'Yixing Teapot', '紫泥仿鼓壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_181_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_181_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_181_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_181_4.jpg', '181', '', '3,540', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nH10cm，D10.5cm<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3396', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '顧景舟款 紫泥仿鼓壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_182_6.jpg', '182', '', '4,720', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '器底款：顧景舟<br />\r\n器內款：珍品<br />\r\nH6.5cm，D14cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n器形圓潤的紫泥壺，鼓腹、底收，配圈把乳鈕，工藝細膩精巧。泥色純正乾淨，為收藏自用佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3397', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '萬豐順記 紫泥圓珠壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_183_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_183_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_183_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_183_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_183_5.jpg', '183', '', '10,030', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：萬豐順記<br />\n共箱<br />\nH6cm，D11cm<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3398', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '西施朱泥壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_184_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_184_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_184_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_184_4.jpg', '184', '5,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n底款：荊溪<br />\nH6cm，D10.5cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壺身圓潤，截蓋、短嘴、倒把，憨態可掬；以梨皮為表，呈凹凸感，並以黃砂鋪面，實為品茗把玩的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3399', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot', '紫泥魚化龍紫砂壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_185_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_185_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_185_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_185_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_185_5.jpg', '185', '6,000 - 10,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\nH8cm，D18cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此器完好乾淨，造功利落，以魚化龍為題；魚化龍是中國傳統寓意紋樣，魚化為龍，古喻金榜題名。整器工藝細膩精巧，龍鬚飄動，躍躍欲活。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3400', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot', '顧順仙 小周盤提梁壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_186_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_186_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_186_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_186_4.jpg', '186', '5,000 - 8,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '底款：顧順仙<br />\r\nH10cm，D10.5cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n壺身以拼紫泥為原料，六方咀，配扁提梁，造工精準有力，線條利落。由於扁提梁燒製時要更精準，所以難度會較高；加上壺蓋與口縫緊密順暢，整器相當討好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3401', 'A Signed Yixing Teapot With Flat Handle', '楊新義富 扁提梁紫泥壺', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_187_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_187_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_187_3.jpg', '187', '4,000 - 6,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n底款：楊新義富<br />\nH11cm，D16cm<br />\n<br />\n此紫泥藏品形制較大，拼紫泥製，配扁提梁，一彎咀；壺肩一圈凸起，與壺身組合如兩圓環套，線條優美，功力非凡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3402', 'A Carved Yixing Teapot With Signature', '韋洪英 紫泥矮足提梁壺一對', '39', '/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_5.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a28/LOTNO_188_6.jpg', '188', '25,000 - 40,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n壺底款：韋洪英<br />\n蓋內款：洪英<br />\nH10cm，D10cm<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壺形方圓制，下斂平底，壺腹飾線紋一圈，圓蓋凸起，與鈕摘相互呼應。高架提梁相交於壺體上方，曲中有直，直中有彎，勾勒婉轉。此壺提梁的造型與壺身渾然一體，使作品具有平衡性而又不失活潑。壺身見方園牌標貼。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3403', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED OVER 60 YEARS', '約六十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_501_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_501_2.jpg', '501', '', '84,960', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：新會<br />\n數量：三袋<br />\n重量(連袋)：每袋各重約633克、630克、632克<br />\n           共重約3斤<br />\n<br />\n超過60年的新會老陳皮，陳化時間足久，乾曬透徹，皮身乾脆，外皮棕黑，內皮油室密集，紋路明顯，質素上好。年代久遠，加之曬制功夫較足，倉儲良好，此老陳皮散發著一股乾燥、微苦的藥香味，輕輕一敲，還可聽到清脆響聲，乾燥的粉末也會隨之飄落，此乃上好陳皮的一大特色。<br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3404', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED OVER 40 YEARS', '約四十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_502_1.jpg', '502', '<span class=\"font11\">開拍價格:</span> HK$ 3,000  &nbsp; | &nbsp;  \n										\n					<span class=\"font11\">估計價格:</span> HK$ 60,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：新會<br />\n重量(連袋)：5袋共重約3000克(約5斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為陳化40多年的老陳皮，外皮呈深紅色，內皮油室密集且紋路清晰。由於倉儲良好，該陳皮較乾倉，散發陣陣藥香味。陳化時間足夠，且分量有足5斤之多，質、量雙佳，值得納入囊中。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3405', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED OVER 50 YEARS', '約五十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_503_1.jpg', '503', '8,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：新會<br />\n重量：淨重約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為新會老陳皮，收藏約50年，陳化時間足久，水分蒸發較為透徹，皮身乾脆，外表呈現棕黑色澤。年代久遠，加之曬制功夫較足，此老陳皮散發著一股乾燥、陳年的陳皮香味，輕輕搖晃外袋會有細屑粉末飛出，可見其乾身程度較高。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3406', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED AROUND 60 YEARS', '約六十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_504_1.jpg', '504', '', '11,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：新會<br />\n重量：淨重約300克(約8両)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳皮當屬越老越好，此拍品有近60年的陳化時間，乾曬透徹，皮身乾脆，輕輕一敲，還可聽到清脆響聲，乾燥的粉末也會隨之飄落。外皮棕黑，內皮油室密集，紋路明顯，質素上好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null);
INSERT INTO `curio_pic_content` VALUES ('3407', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED AROUND 70 YEARS', '約七十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_505_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_505_2.jpg', '505', '', '22,420', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：新會<br />\n重量：淨重約300克(約8両)<br />\n<br />\n經過70年的沉澱，此拍品得到充分的陳化，皮身較乾，雖有歲月的痕跡，但形狀尚算完整，顏色深湛，油室較密集，外富紋路細坑，質素上好。蘊涵數十年正火的老陳皮，泡水入饌，口感絕佳，還是保健、治病的絕佳良品，有祛痰濕、平喘咳的功效。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3408', 'DRIED TANGERINE PEEL AGED AROUND 80 YEARS', '約八十年陳齡 新會 老陳皮', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_506_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_506_2.jpg', '506', '', '17,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：新會<br />\n重量：淨重約150克(約4両)<br />\n<br />\n古代早有典籍記載「橘皮以色紅、日久者為佳，故曰陳皮。」<br />\n此拍品為陳化約80年的老陳皮，外皮呈深邃的紅褐色，內皮油室密集且紋路清晰。輕輕搖晃袋子會有細屑粉末飛出，倉儲乾燥。香氣十足，隔著袋子能聞到陣陣藥香味。如此陳年的老陳皮極為罕見，此拍品為藏家多年珍藏之物，所以量較少，但是零售市場上是幾乎購買不到的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3409', 'NO.2 WILD AMERICAN GINSENG', '美國野生 二號泡 花旗蔘王', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_507_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_507_2.jpg', '507', '', '123,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：美國紐約北省<br />\n重量：2盒共重約1000克(每盒約500克)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花旗蔘：味甘性寒，入心、肺、腎經，功能補氣養陰，清熱生津(俗稱“下火”、“清虛火”)。 適用於治療陰虛火旺，喘咳痰血，熱病氣陰兩傷，煩倦口渴，津液不足，口乾舌燥，腸熱便血等屬氣陰兩虛症狀。<br />\n花旗蔘獨特之處在於補氣而甘涼，中藥裏有補氣功效的大都偏於溫熱，能“補而不燥”、補氣又甘涼的，就只有花旗蔘。所以花旗蔘適用於“虛火”、氣陰兩虛而有火的症候。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3410', 'NO.2 WILD AMERICAN GINSENG', '美國野山 二號泡 花旗蔘王', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_508_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_508_2.jpg', '508', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：美國俄亥俄州紅番區<br />\n數量：1盒<br />\n重量：淨重約300克<br />\n<br />\n此蔘產自美國俄亥俄州紅番區，該區所產的均為野生蔘，約有20年天然生長期，蔘體保存完好，條紋清晰，品相較佳。泡蔘則是花旗蔘中的一種，統指花旗蔘主根，也常用作指野生花旗蔘的主根，相比其他花旗蔘更高級一些。<br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3411', 'EXTRA LARGE WILD AMERICAN GINSENG', '美國野生 上身泡 花旗蔘王', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_509_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_509_2.jpg', '509', '220,000 - 320,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：美國紐約北省<br />\n數量：3盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約1500克(每盒約500克)<br />\n<br />\n野生花旗蔘是受美國特殊稀有物種法律保護，因此進出口及買賣均受到嚴格管制。但其藥用功效和價值絕佳，所以市場需求一直居高不下。<br />\n此拍品為花旗蔘王上身泡，等級最高，蔘體最大，且紋路清晰、品相良好。此種質素均屬上乘，且為最大號的花旗蔘，實在難能一見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3412', 'NO.3 WILD AMERICAN GINSENG', '美國野生 三號泡 花旗蔘王', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_510_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_510_2.jpg', '510', '80,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：美國紐約北省<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約1000克(每盒約500克)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為美國紐約北省出產的野生花旗蔘，等級為3號泡蔘，每個約有3g重，蔘體完整、蘆頭細長而多節，蔘身橫紋密而深色，品相為佳。現時，野生花旗蔘的來源已經極稀少，市場上售賣的多數屬人工種植品，價格會因生產地、質量優劣等因素而有很大差距。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3413', 'NO.1 WILD AMERICAN GINSENG', '美國野生 一號泡 花旗蔘王', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_511_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_511_2.jpg', '511', '', '129,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：美國紐約北省<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約1000克(每盒約500克)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n野生蔘以大粒、蘆頭蔘鬚完整為貴。此拍品1號泡花旗蔘王，屬人蔘業界中級數頂尖的，且蔘體均形狀完整，表相良好，無論送禮或自用，皆為優品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3414', '1974/1975/1976 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 20)', '正官庄 1974年/1975年/1976年產\n天字 高麗蔘20支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_512_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_512_2.jpg', '512', '130,000 - 180,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n產地：韓國<br />\n數量：3罐<br />\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\n共淨重約1800克<br />\n<br />\n此3罐為正官庄天字20支高麗蔘，分別為1974年、1975年和1976年入罐，陳年40多年，年代久遠，零售市場上少之又少，為藏家多年收藏之物。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3415', '1977 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 20)', '正官庄 1977年產 天字 高麗蔘20支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_513_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_513_2.jpg', '513', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\r\n數量：2罐<br />\r\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\r\n      共淨重約1200克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此天字號根高麗蔘，每罐20隻，品質上乘，產自1977年，入罐後有40多年的陳齡，陳期使罐內人蔘濁氣消除，正氣越純，補而不燥，有生津安神、補氣養身的功效。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3416', '1987 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 15)', '正官庄 1987年產 地字 高麗蔘15支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_514_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_514_2.jpg', '514', '50,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\r\n數量：4罐<br />\r\n重量：每罐淨重約600克  <br />\r\n      共淨重約2400克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此拍品為地字10支高麗蔘，陳化30年左右。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3417', '1987 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 20)', '正官庄 1987年產 天字 高麗蔘20支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_515_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_515_2.jpg', '515', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\r\n數量：2罐<br />\r\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\r\n      共淨重約1200克 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n高麗蔘有大補元氣、生津安神等作用，適用於驚悸失眠者，體虛者，心力衰竭、心源性休克等。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3418', '1988 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 10)', '正官庄 1988年產 \n天字 高麗蔘10支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_516_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_516_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_516_3.jpg', '516', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '<br />\n<br />\n產地：韓國<br />\n數量：2罐<br />\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\n      共淨重約1200克<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此天字號根高麗蔘，品質上乘，產自1988年，入罐後有接近30年的陳齡，陳期使罐內人蔘濁氣消除，正氣越純，補而不燥，有生津安神、補氣養身的功效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3419', '1988 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 10)', '正官庄 1988年產 \n地字 高麗蔘10支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_517_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_517_2.jpg', '517', '', '27,140', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\n數量：1罐<br />\n重量：淨重約600克<br />\n<br />\n作為韓國最具象徵意義的保健食品，高麗蔘是贈予國賓和重要人物的國家禮品。此拍品為地字10支高麗蔘，陳化30年左右。<br />\n    <br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3420', '1989 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 10)', '正官庄 1989年產 天字 高麗蔘10支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_518_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_518_2.jpg', '518', '160,000 - 220,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\r\n數量：3罐<br />\r\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\r\n共淨重約1800克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此天字號根高麗蔘，每罐10隻，品質上乘，產自1989年，入罐後有接近30年的陳齡。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3421', '1988/1989/1990 CKJ KOREAN RED GINSENG ROOTS (HEAVEN GRADE 20)', '正官庄 1988年/1989年/1990年產天字 高麗蔘20支(一斤裝)', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_519_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_519_2.jpg', '519', '', '100,300', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：韓國<br />\r\n數量：3罐<br />\r\n重量：每罐淨重約600克<br />\r\n共淨重約1800克<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此3罐為正官庄天字20支高麗蔘，分別為1988年、1989年和1990年入罐，陳年近30年，陳齡足夠，療效顯著，在預防糖尿病，動脈硬化，高血壓等方面有明顯效果。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3422', 'TIBET NAGQU CORDYCEPS SINENSIS', '西藏那曲 野生冬蟲夏草', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_520_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_520_2.jpg', '520', '', '70,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：西藏那曲<br />\r\n重量：約300克<br />\r\n條數：每斤約2510條<br />\r\n<br />\r\n冬蟲夏草為上乘補品，具有補腎助陽、護肺定喘、止血化痰等功效，並為滋陰補虛良品，且補而不燥，四季皆宜，長期服用冬蟲夏草有助增強人體免疫能力。<br />\r\n此拍品品相優良，蟲體完好，色澤棕黃，值得收藏。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3423', 'COLLOCALIA CUBILOSE FROM INDONESIA', '印尼 金絲燕窩', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_521_1.jpg', '521', '', '33,040', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：印尼<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約1200克(約2斤)<br />\n<br />\n印尼為全世界生產燕窩最多的地方，當地行家採集燕窩的經驗豐富，盡可能保持了燕窩的完整自然，出產的燕窩大多質量較佳。<br />\n此款燕窩產自印尼，形狀完整，紋理清晰，底座輕薄，盞身通透。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3424', 'QINGHAI YUSHU CORDYCEPS SINENSIS', '青海玉樹 野生冬蟲夏草', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_522_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_522_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_522_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_522_4.jpg', '522', '50,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：青海玉樹<br />\n重量：凈重約500克<br />\n條數：約1500條(1條約0.33克)<br />\n<br />\n冬蟲夏草外形可分為「蟲」與「草」兩部份：<br />\n「蟲」體似蠶，表面深棕色，有環紋20至30個，足8對，中間4對最為明顯。蟲體質脆易斷，帶有微腥氣，微香味； <br />\n「草」為子座，從蟲體的頭部長出，表面黑褐色，有細縱紋，質輕柔韌。<br />\n<br />\n冬蟲夏草主要以蟲體豐滿肥壯，外皮色黃，內肉色白，乾身完整者為上品。此品蟲體較肥，蟲身較乾，紋路清晰，色澤黃亮，質素較佳。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3425', 'PREMIUM READ IRON OXIDE CUBILOSE', '二十年陳齡 頂級 血燕', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_523_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_523_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_523_3.jpg', '523', '', '59,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：泰國  <br />\n重量：約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n血燕屬於洞燕的一種，是金絲燕築巢於山洞的岩壁上，岩壁內部的礦物質透過燕窩與岩壁的接觸面或經岩壁的滴水，慢慢地滲透到燕窩內，其中鐵元素占多數的時候便會呈現出部分不規則的、暈染狀的鐵銹紅色，我們將此稱之為血燕。<br />\n血燕以顏色鮮紅、營養豐富、產量稀少被追捧為燕窩中的珍品。其主要功效就是滋陰、潤肺、補虛、美容養顏、調節內臟經脈紊亂、緩解壓力、補充體力等等。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3426', 'CUBILOSE FROM HOI AN VIETNAM', '頂級 越南 官燕', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_524_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_524_2.jpg', '524', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：越南<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：淨重約1000克(約1斤10両)<br />\n<br />\n全世界燕窩80%都來自印尼產區，其他由馬來西亞、泰國及越南出產。而越南燕窩只佔了全世界產量的1%，每年產量只有3000公斤，鳳毛麟角。即使越南燕窩價格高於印尼產區很多，依然供不應求。<br />\n官燕是眾多屋燕當中的一個品種，指品質較優，盞形完整的白色燕窩，因此官燕是燕窩中的極品。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3427', 'TIBET NAGQU CORDYCEPS SINENSIS', '2017年 西藏那曲 野生冬蟲夏草', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_525_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_525_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_525_3.jpg', '525', '', '165,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：西藏那曲<br />\n重量：淨重約500克<br />\n條數：約1100條(1條約有0.45克)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為西藏那曲野生冬蟲夏草，2017年採摘，十分新鮮。蟲身較肥，身色深黃，有淡淡的腥香味。 <br />\n冬蟲夏草由於其神奇的一物兼動植的特徵，讓其含有多種微量元素，目前科學上公認的四大神奇元素是蟲草素、蟲草酸、蟲草多醣、超氧化岐化本酶，具有抗腫瘤，保護呼吸系統及肝腎，提高免疫力，降血糖、血壓、血脂等顯著作用。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3428', 'COLLOCALIA CUBILOSE FROM THAILAND', '泰國 金絲燕窩', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_526_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_526_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_526_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_526_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LTONO_526_5.jpg', '526', '55,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：泰國<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約1200克(約2斤)<br />\n<br />\n燕窩的主要產地分佈於東南亞地區，主要在印尼、泰國、越南、馬來西亞一帶。泰國燕窩產量較少，價格也就相對較高。此款金絲燕窩，產自泰國，外形完整，寬度大，顏色天然無漂白跡象，紋理清晰，縫隙自然，品相尚佳。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3429', 'TIBET NAGQU CORDYCEPS SINENSIS', '西藏那曲 野生冬蟲夏草', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_527_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_527_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_527_3.jpg', '527', '80,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：西藏那曲<br />\r\n重量：約300克<br />\r\n條數：每斤約2100條 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n此拍品呈現金黃色，蟲身較肥，透過外表紋路隱約可見內裡呈奶白色。極乾，味香氣足，色、香、味之品質皆屬上乘。均經過金屬探測器檢測，不存在人為注水或插金屬條絲入蟲身以增加重量，為純天然野生上品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3430', 'DRIED AMIDORI ABALONE (4-HEAD)', '四頭 溏心 乾網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_528_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_528_2.jpg', '528', '', '64,900', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '數量：8隻<br />\n重量：共重約1200克(約2斤)<br />\n<br />\n此8隻四頭鮑魚為藏家精挑細選出來的精品，收藏已經超過15年，年代久遠。肉厚肥美的溏心網鮑蘊藏大量維他命和礦物質，益腎滋補，是四季皆宜的養生補品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3431', 'JAPANESE AMIDORI ABALONE (4-HEAD)', '四頭 日本 大網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_529_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_529_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_529_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_529_4.jpg', '529', '55,000 - 90,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：日本<br />\n數量：4隻<br />\n重量：共重約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n此四頭網鮑產自日本，是香港海味店多年珍藏之物，保存得宜，外形完整無劃痕，品相良好。<br />\n日本出品的乾鮑是世界公認第一，鮑魚體型較大，鮑身肉厚而堅硬，裙邊闊而粗糙，吸盆尾部較尖，枕底呈清晰珠粒之狀，呈深棕色，香味濃郁。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3432', 'JAPANESE AMIDORI ABALONE (AROUND 6-HEAD)', '六頭 日本 舊水網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_530_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_530_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_530_3.jpg', '530', '', '53,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：日本<br />\n數量：12隻<br />\n重量：共重約1200克(約2斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品出產於鮑魚盛產之地日本，外形呈橢圓狀呈深咖啡色，鮑身肥厚，鮑邊細小，鮑枕呈珠粒狀，底邊廣闊平坦，尾部較尖，肉質大而肥厚，用刀切後，其截面有網狀紋路，故名網鮑。由香港資深海味藏家提供，收藏時間久，但保存得宜，品相上佳。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3433', 'SOUTH AFRICAN ABALONE', '南非 大網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_531_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_531_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_531_3.jpg', '531', '28,000 - 40,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：南非<br />\n數量：6隻<br />\n重量：共重約1055克(約1斤11両)<br />\n<br />\n“南非鮑”顧名思義，產於南非，邊緣毛刺非常多。南非鮑因為個頭大、品質高，一直在國際市場上頗受青睞。<br />\n此拍品為6隻產自南非的鮑魚，個頭較大，外形完整，價格合理，實屬質價雙佳。<br />\n<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3434', 'DRIED AMIDORI ABALONE (NEARLY 2-HEAD)', '近二頭 溏心 大網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_532_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_532_2.jpg', '532', '60,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '數量：1隻<br />\n重量：重約245克(約6.5両)<br />\n<br />\n此溏心大網鮑，體型巨大，接近二頭。顏色深邃，裙邊珠粒粗壯分明，鮑枕肥厚，品相良好。近年來二頭鮑魚已十分罕見，此拍品收藏約15年，形狀仍十分完整，且重量十足，因保存良好打開盒子時，還能聞到濃郁乾鮑鮮味。<br />', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3435', 'DRIED AMIDORI ABALONE (10-HEAD)', '十頭 溏心 乾網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_533_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_533_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_533_3.jpg', '533', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '數量：40隻<br />\n重量：共重約2400克(約4斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品是香港某行家收藏了約15年的存貨，陳期十足。4盒鮑魚個個鮑身厚實飽滿，形狀對稱，色澤深邃，裙邊珠粒分明，且一組共有40隻，分量十足。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3436', 'JAPANESE AMIDORI ABALONE (5-HEAD)', '五頭 日本 大網鮑', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_534_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_534_2.jpg', '534', '50,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：日本<br />\n數量：5隻<br />\n重量：共重約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n鮑魚具有滋補養顏、平衡血壓、養肝明目、滋陰清熱等作用，並且含豐富蛋白質，尤以滋陰明目、滋補強身功效甚大，適合肝腎虛弱、視物昏暗等人士食用。<br />\n此5頭網鮑產自日本，保存得宜，外形完整無劃痕，品相良好。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3437', 'PAKISTAN MALE CODFISH MAW OVER 20 YEARS', '約二十年陳齡 巴基斯坦 鰵魚公肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_535_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_535_2.jpg', '535', '38,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：巴基斯坦<br />\n數量：1隻<br />\n重量：128克<br />\n<br />\n此拍品產自巴基斯坦。花膠產地，除中國東、南海外，屬印度和巴基斯坦較為出眾。<br />\n花膠有公母之分，花膠公營養價值及口感優於花膠母，而鰵魚公魚鰾曬成的花膠屬頂級貨。公肚形如馬鞍，肚身中部較厚，而兩邊較薄，以質地結實、厚身、乾淡，呈半透明狀為上品。<br />\n此拍品為鰵魚公肚，收藏近20年，陳化時間長，又保存得宜，質素尚佳。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3438', 'PAKISTAN POLLOCK MAW (2-HEAD)', '巴基斯坦 兩頭 鰵魚肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_536_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_536_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_536_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_536_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_536_5.jpg', '536', '110,000 - 150,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：巴基斯坦 <br />\n數量：2隻<br />\n重量：每隻各重約300克(約8両)、305克(約8両)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為2隻巴基斯坦出產的鰵魚魚肚，色澤均勻，呈深棕色，紋路清晰。最難得的是，這2隻花膠個頭偏大，足兩頭，重量十足。所謂“十斤魚一両膠”，可見要幾十斤的魚才有這麼大的魚肚。而鰵魚大部分是生活在深水中，不能養殖，所以要獲取像此拍品這樣優質的鰵魚肚可謂是越來越難。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3439', 'FISH MAW AGED OVER 60 YEARS', '六十年陳齡 極品大花膠', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_537_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_537_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_537_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_537_4.jpg', '537', '15,000 - 28,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '數量：2隻<br />\n重量：各重約530克(14兩)、590克(15兩6)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為50年代極品花膠，至今已有60年陳齡，1組2個，厚身乾爽，形狀完整，外表呈現黃褐色，顏色越深，年份越久。少處破損，為捕魚時魚鉤勾破所致，但不足以影響其價值，反而更顯天然。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3440', 'MALAYSIAN FISH MAW', '馬來西亞 蜘蛛膠', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_538_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_538_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_538_3.jpg', '538', '', '236,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：馬來西亞<br />\n數量：4隻<br />\n重量：共重約240克(約6両3)<br />\n<br />\n蜘蛛膠對於治療支氣管炎、咳嗽、哮喘等效果顯著，有滋陰補腎、養胃潤肺、益精健脾、補血理氣等功效，同時也是美容養顏、強身健體之佳選。<br />\n此拍品為兩對蜘蛛膠，據藏家敘述，市面上很難找到體型相近的蜘蛛膠可以配對，且4隻膠均有膠須，實在難能一見。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3441', 'MALAYSIA MALE POLLOCK MAW', '馬來西亞  鰵魚公肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_539_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_539_2.jpg', '539', '40,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：馬來西亞<br />\n數量：14隻<br />\n重量：共重約570克<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為鰵魚公魚鰾曬成的花膠，產自馬來西亞，為優質花膠盛產之地。收藏多年，陳化足久，保存較好，膠身乾燥，體型較小，送禮自用雙宜。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3442', 'PREMINUM FISH MAW', '陳年 極品花膠', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_540_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_540_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_540_3.jpg', '540', '60,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '數量：1隻<br />\n重量： 848克(約1斤6両4)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品雖具體年份未知，但且看花膠表面呈現濃郁的茶色，膠身厚實且體積大，外表有如樹皮一般的紋路，顏色深且線條清晰，不經過幾十年，是無法陳化為此等品相，可見此膠年代久遠，且此上土花膠，形狀完整，膠身較大較厚，足有1斤6両4，原生魚體積必然夠大，才能提取出這種龐大的魚鰾，故此膠乃市面稀有的佳品。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3443', 'PAKISTAN POLLOCK  MAW (2-HEAD)', '巴基斯坦 兩頭 鰵魚肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_541_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_541_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_541_3.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_541_4.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_541_5.jpg', '541', '120,000 - 160,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：巴基斯坦 <br />\n數量：2隻<br />\n重量：每隻各重約288克(約7.6両)、293克(約7.8両)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為鰵魚魚鰾曬成的花膠，產自巴基斯坦，為優質花膠盛產之地。其形如馬鞍，中部較厚，顏色呈深褐色，兩邊較薄，顏色呈金黃色。2隻花膠膠身乾燥，表面帶油潤感，呈半透明狀，聞著香而不腥，且足兩頭大，重量十足。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3444', 'PAKISTAN MALE CODFISH MAW OVER 20 YEARS', '約二十年陳齡 巴基斯坦 鰵魚公肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_542_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_542_2.jpg', '542', '38,000 - 50,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：巴基斯坦<br />\n數量：1隻<br />\n重量：156克<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為鰵魚公魚鰾曬成的頂級花膠，收藏近20年，陳化足久，保存得較完整，重量較足。產自優質花膠盛產之地的巴基斯坦，膠身乾燥，呈半透明狀，聞著香而不腥。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3445', 'SOUTHERN CHINA SEA CODFISH MAW', '南中國海 黃鰵魚公肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_543_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_543_2.jpg', '543', '130,000 - 180,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地:南中國海<br />\n數量：2隻<br />\n重量：每隻各重約230克(約6両)、270克(約7両1)<br />\n      共重約13両1<br />\n此拍品為南中國海產鰵魚膠一對，膠身厚實，呈深黃褐色，燈光下通透可見清晰紋路，保存良好，乾燥完整。<br />\n鰵魚體形龐大，肚頭數大，膠質特別豐富。鰵魚膠的膠質細膩，肚身爽口，燉後湯水清，無腥味，乃花膠中之上上品，對改善皮膚組織健康和加速傷口之康復有顯著功效。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3446', 'SOUTH AFRICAN DEEP SEA BASS MAW', '南非 深海鱸魚膠', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_544_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_544_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_544_3.jpg', '544', '70,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：南非<br />\n數量：1隻<br />\n重量：約620克(約1斤4両)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為深海鱸魚的魚肚，體型較大，重量十足，深海魚本就較難捕捉，這麼大的魚肚必定來自體積較大的魚，市面上肯定少之又少。中醫認為花膠具備滋陰養顏、補腎和強壯機能等妙用，特別適合女士養顏、產後調理身體和手術後傷口復原食用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3447', 'MALAYSIAN FISH MAW', '馬來西亞 蜘蛛膠', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_545_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_545_2.jpg', '545', '80,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：馬來西亞<br />\n數量：2隻<br />\n重量：共重約125克(約3兩3)<br />\n<br />\n由於蜘蛛膠（小鱗波曼石首魚）在市面上相當的稀少，因此價格不菲。此拍品產自馬來西亞，為香港海味店珍藏之物。蜘蛛膠在香港名氣非常高，價格一直呈上升趨勢。蜘蛛膠有公母之分，香港人在選擇蜘蛛膠時特別喜歡肚子中間有條「筋」的蜘蛛膠公膠，口感頗豐富。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3448', 'PAKISTAN MALE CODFISH MAW', '巴基斯坦 紅雞鰵魚公肚', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_546_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_546_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_546_3.jpg', '546', '68,000 - 100,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：巴基斯坦<br />\n數量：2隻<br />\n重量：各淨重約180克(約4両8)，180克(約4両8)<br />\n共重約9両6<br />\n<br />\n紅雞鰵魚膠，系屬於赤嘴鰵魚膠中的一種。嘴鰵肚是繼金錢鰵肚、蜘蛛肚、白花膠之後最名貴的花膠品種，是一種深海魚類，屬於鰵魚類，分幾個品種，按產地分為台山赤嘴、湛江赤嘴、紅雞赤嘴、大耳赤嘴等。<br />\n紅雞赤嘴是四大赤嘴中最廣為人所知的品種，其補血，美容，產後滋補效果都非常有效。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3449', 'DRIED AFRICA SEAHORSES', '非洲 野生海馬', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_547_1.jpg', '547', '', '15,340', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地： 非洲<br />\n數量：75隻<br />\n重量：共重約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為野生海馬，產自非洲。海馬分大海馬，中海馬，小海馬。產自非洲南岸的，多屬大海馬，也稱管海馬。正宗的非洲海馬，體側扁，較高，腹部突出，尾彎曲。頭呈馬頭形，頭冠較低，液浸標本體灰黑或黃褐色，頭部和體側具有小白斑。藥用價值高，補腎作用在海馬裡面屬於最強。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3450', 'ENORMOUS DEER’S TAILS FROM HUNCHUN', '琿春大鹿尾巴', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_548_1.jpg', '548', '8,000 - 12,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：中國吉林省琿春市<br />\n數量：3條<br />\n重量：各淨重約97克(約2.5両)、97克(約2.5両)、101克(約2.7両)<br />\n<br />\n野生梅花鹿屬於國家一級重點保護野生動物，已禁捕獵。目前市面上供應的鹿茸、鹿尾巴和鹿筋，均來自養鹿。市面上以中國琿春和新西蘭為主要飼養地，而中國琿春養鹿的品種體積較大，所以價格也比其他地方的高許多倍。<br />\n此拍品產自琿春，重量較足，具有壮腰脊、添精髓、强筋骨之功效。常人久服可添精養腎，健腦益智，祛病強身，益壽延年。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3451', 'PREMIUM AUSTRALIAN DRIED SEA DRAGONS', '超級海龍', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_549_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_549_2.jpg', '549', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：澳洲<br />\n數量：27隻<br />\n重量：約1200克(約2斤)<br />\n<br />\n《現代實用中草》中對海龍的記載：“為強壯藥，有興奮作用，用於老人及衰弱者之神經衰憊。治血氣通。”<br />\n此拍品產自澳洲，為頂級海龍，每隻約重45克，體型較大。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3452', 'PREMIUM PIECES OF ANTLER', '特級 鹿茸蠟片', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_550_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_550_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_550_3.jpg', '550', '10,000 - 15,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：新西蘭<br />\n數量：2盒<br />\n重量：各淨重約77克、74克<br />\n<br />\n鹿茸，即為還沒有長成硬骨的鹿角，帶有茸毛，其性溫而不燥，是上好的壯陽和提高免疫力的補品。對於鹿茸，《本草綱目》中記載：鹿茸具有「生精補髓、養血益陽、強健筋骨」的作用。 <br />\n按鹿茸部位的不同，從上到下依次分為蠟片、粉片、紗片、骨片四個等級，越往上越貴。此拍品為特級鹿茸蠟片，蠟片為鹿茸最頂端最嫩部分。蠟片蠟質多，粉質少或無粉質。一整條的鹿茸只能切出2～3片全蠟片，瑰寶奇珍。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3453', 'PREMIUM THAILAND DRIED SEAHORSES', '極品海馬', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_552_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_552_2.jpg', '552', '45,000 - 60,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：泰國<br />\n數量：32隻<br />\n重量：共重約600克<br />\n<br />\n此拍品產自泰國，體型較大，每隻約有19克。形狀完整，外表保存良好的質素，體色較黑，說明為深海海馬，比較少見，乃出品人珍藏多年之物。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3454', 'IMMENSE DEER’S TAILS FROM HUNCHUN', '琿春特大鹿尾巴', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_553_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_553_2.jpg', '553', '8,000 - 12,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：中國吉林省琿春市<br />\n數量：2條<br />\n重量：各淨重約105克(約3両)、103克(約3両)<br />\n<br />\n鹿尾巴是蓋在鹿脊近臀部之上，鹿運動量多，尾巴含油量少，又有多種胺基酸、蛋白膠原、鈣、磷、鋅等是鹿的精華所在。<br />\n吉林省琿春市出產的鹿尾巴名氣很大，約6000元/両，其他地方培植的約600元/両。此拍品是產自琿春市的特大鹿尾巴，體積肥厚、圓渾，一隻近3両，鹿尾巴體積大表示鹿強壯，補益功效也就更相得益彰。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3455', 'PREMIUM AUSTRALIAN DRIED SEA DRAGONS', '頂級澳洲海龍', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_554_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_554_2.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_554_3.jpg', '554', '', '18,880', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：澳洲<br />\n數量：19隻 <br />\n重量：約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品產自澳洲，為頂級海龍，每隻約重32克，每年挑選出這種重量級數的只有一百多斤，十分罕見珍貴，在市面上非常少見，多數落入藏家手中。<br />\n<br />\n海龍是一個很有名的藥材，也叫水雁或是錢串子，這種藥材在生活中被廣泛的運用，因為它所含的物質成分，有著非常好的功效，其提取物對人體有抗癌、提高機體免疫力、性激素作用及抗衰老等。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3456', 'PREMIUM THAILAND DRIED SEAHORSES', '極品海馬', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_555_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_555_2.jpg', '555', '', '44,840', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：泰國<br />\n數量：40隻<br />\n重量：約600克(約1斤)<br />\n<br />\n在《本草拾遺》中，海馬又名水馬、蝦姑、馬頭魚、龍落子魚，為海龍科動物。<br />\n中醫學認為海馬味甘、鹹，性溫。歸腎經、肝經，功效則包括補腎壯陽，散結消腫。<br />\n此拍品產自泰國，近年由於環境污染問題，泰國出口海馬數量逐年減少，當地政府更於2015年頒布命令暫停發放海馬出口許可證，所以海馬在市面上越來越少。而擁有如此拍品這樣體型較大、形狀完整、外表保存良好的質素，更是屈指可數，乃出品人珍藏多年之物。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3457', 'JAPANESE KANTA SEA CUCUMBER', '日本關東遼參', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_556_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_556_2.jpg', '556', '', '53,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：日本關東<br />\n數量：6盒<br />\n重量：共淨重約3600克(每盒約600克/32條)<br />\n<br />\n此拍品為6盒關東遼參，每盒約有32條參，海參具有補腎養血、潤膚養顏等功效與作用。<br />\n日本遼參一直以關東所產的為首選，價錢也最貴。關東遼參，主產於日本東北及關東地區，因氣候、水質等地理因素，所出產的遼參質素較佳。關東遼參體型不大，參體渾圓，偏肥厚，肉質細糯，口感脆爽，外皮多呈黯黑色，色澤光亮鮮明，長滿密集尖銳肉刺，通常約有6排，排列整齊帶序，長3-5寸。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3458', 'JAPANESE HOKKAIDO SEA CUCUMBER', '日本 北海道刺參', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_557_1.jpg,/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_557_2.jpg', '557', '', '47,200', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：日本北海道<br />\n數量：4盒<br />\n重量：共凈重約2400克(每盒約600克)<br />\n<br />\n海參的功效與作用極高，屬於一種具有高營養價值的海產，雖生於海，其性溫補，足敵人蔘，所以取名為“海參”，但非熱性之品，而是性質很溫和的食物。日本為海參盛產之地，有北海道遼參、關東遼參、關西刺參等多個種類。<br />\n此拍品產於日本北海道，屬關東以北地區，因當地地理氣候及水質的關係，海參的生長較緩慢，質素上乘。雖然體型不大，但參壁肥厚，肉質細糯，口感爽滑，體面皮薄，多呈灰褐色，佈滿大小不等的圓錐肉刺(約有6排)，故又名“刺參”。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3459', 'PARADIS COGNAC HENNESSY	 1990S', '九十年代 軒尼詩 杯莫停 \n干邑 白蘭地', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_558_1.jpg', '558', '', '56,640', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：法國<br />\n年份：1990年代<br />\n數量：5瓶<br />\n容量：750毫升 (ABV 40%)<br />\n<br />\n軒尼詩杯莫停為干邑白蘭地中的極品，其基酒內含陳年近二百年的原酒，由軒尼斯品牌成立一直陳釀至今，其罕貴酒質，至香至醇，非筆墨能描寫。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3460', 'THE FIRST GENERATION RICHARD HENNESSY COGNAC', '軒尼詩 李察\n幹邑 白蘭地 初代', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_559_1.jpg', '559', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：法國<br />\n年份：90年代<br />\n數量：4瓶<br />\n容量：700毫升(ABV 40%)<br />\n<br />\n軒尼詩李察干邑被譽為軒尼詩家族的靈魂，由超過一百種非凡的生命之水「eaux-de-vie」調製而成，主要原料大多數源自大香檳區的最佳葡萄園，擁有世界最長久耐嘗幹邑的美譽。<br />\n軒尼詩李察一共有3個版本，1996年問世的軒尼詩初代李察，瓶蓋頂部為黑色，也稱黑木頭李察，具有豐厚如絲的口感，意蘊深邃，令人回味無窮。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3461', 'THE SECOND GENERATION RICHARD HENNESSY COGNAC', '軒尼詩 李察\n幹邑 白蘭地 二代', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_560_1.jpg', '560', '', '76,700', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：法國<br />\n年份：90年代<br />\n數量：4瓶<br />\n容量：700毫升(ABV 40%)<br />\n<br />\n為了襯托軒尼詩李察的獨特不凡，軒尼詩特別與法國頂級水晶品牌Baccarat合作，選用純熟工匠需耗費40個小時以上工時，才能完成的雕花精品水晶瓶身，讓顧客從視覺上，就能感受這瓶頂級干邑白蘭地的尊貴。<br />\n軒尼詩李察一共有3個版本，此拍品為二代李察，瓶蓋為銀頭。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3462', 'R', '約六十年代 人頭馬 路易十三\n干邑 白蘭地', '40', '/public/pic_content/img/a29/LOTNO_561_1.jpg', '561', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '產地：法國<br />\n年份：約1960年代<br />\n數量：5瓶<br />\n容量：700毫升(ABV 40%)<br />\n<br />\n此5瓶路易十三乃60年代左右出品。瓶身、瓶塞及瓶底有人手雕刻之產品編號，瓶頸封口以純金雕刻而成。均配備原廠專屬收藏硬盒、巴卡拉水晶瓶塞及產品編號說明書。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3463', '1991年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '1991年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_601_1.jpg', '601', '', '330,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1986至1996年出產的茅臺酒，封蓋為鋁制金屬蓋，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3464', '1993年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '1993年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_602_1.jpg', '602', '180,000 - 250,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1986至1996年出產的茅臺酒，封蓋為鋁制金屬蓋，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3465', '1995年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '1995年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_603_1.jpg', '603', '180,000 - 260,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1986至1996年出產的茅臺酒，封蓋為鋁制金屬蓋，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3466', '80年代貴州茅臺酒(小飛天)', '80年代貴州茅臺酒(小飛天)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_604_1.jpg', '604', '60,000 - 80,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '茅臺酒獨產於中國的貴州省遵義市仁懷市茅臺鎮，是漢民族的特產酒，與蘇格蘭威士卡、法國科涅克白蘭地齊名的三大蒸餾酒之一。1915年至今，貴州茅臺酒共獲得15次國際金獎，連續五次蟬聯中國國家名酒稱號，與遵義董酒並稱貴州省僅有的兩大國家名酒，是大麯醬香型白酒的鼻祖，有“國酒”之稱，是中國最高端白酒之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3467', '1983年-1986年地方國營貴州茅臺酒', '1983年-1986年地方國營貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_605_1.jpg', '605', '280,000 - 380,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '酒標右下角寫“地方國營茅臺酒廠出品”，俗稱“地方國營茅臺”，該商標在1983至1986年間使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3468', '1983年-1986年地方國營貴州茅臺酒', '1983年-1986年地方國營貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_606_1.jpg', '606', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '酒標右下角寫“地方國營茅臺酒廠出品”，俗稱“地方國營茅臺”，該商標在1983至1986年間使用。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3469', '1989年 大M珍品貴州茅臺酒', '1989年 大M珍品貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_607_1.jpg', '607', '70,000 - 120,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '酒標正面寫“珍品貴州茅臺酒”，有紙盒、木盒兩種包裝，被稱為“珍品茅臺”，是八十年代中期開始生產的高檔茅臺酒，採用窖藏多年的陳酒勾兌而成，具有醬香濃郁，酒體醇厚，回味綿甜之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3470', '2001年貴州茅臺酒', '2001年貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_608_1.jpg', '608', '', '118,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '2001年出產的貴州茅臺酒，口味純正，酒體細膩柔順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3471', '2003年貴州茅臺酒', '2003年貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_609_1.jpg', '609', '', '112,100', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '2003年出產的貴州茅臺酒，口味純正，酒體細膩柔順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3472', '2005年貴州茅臺酒', '2005年貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_610_1.jpg', '610', '', '94,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '2005年出產的貴州茅臺酒，口味純正，酒體細膩柔順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3473', '1996年貴州茅臺酒', '1996年貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_611_1.jpg', '611', '', '177,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1996年出產的貴州茅臺酒，口味純正，酒體細膩柔順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3474', '1999年貴州茅臺酒', '1999年貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_612_1.jpg', '612', '', '153,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1999年出產的貴州茅臺酒，口味純正，酒體細膩柔順。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3475', '1996年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '1996年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_613_1.jpg', '613', '', '306,800', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1986至1996年出產的茅臺酒，封蓋為鋁制金屬蓋，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3476', '1987-1996年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋十年)', '1987-1996年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋十年)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_614_1.jpg', '614', '', '354,000', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1986至1996年出產的茅臺酒，封蓋為鋁制金屬蓋，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3477', '1987年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '1987年貴州茅臺酒(鐵蓋)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_615_1.jpg', '615', '120,000 - 180,000', '', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '1987年出產的，被稱為“鐵蓋茅臺”。因瓶身沒有標明度數，又稱“無度茅臺”，該商標在1987至1990年間使用。具有醬香突出，酒體醇厚豐滿，回味陳香悠長，空杯留香持久之特點。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3478', '80年代貴州茅臺酒(大飛天)', '80年代貴州茅臺酒(大飛天)', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_616_1.jpg', '616', '', '259,600', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '茅臺酒獨產於中國的貴州省遵義市仁懷市茅臺鎮，是漢民族的特產酒，與蘇格蘭威士卡、法國科涅克白蘭地齊名的三大蒸餾酒之一。1915年至今，貴州茅臺酒共獲得15次國際金獎，連續五次蟬聯中國國家名酒稱號，與遵義董酒並稱貴州省僅有的兩大國家名酒，是大麯醬香型白酒的鼻祖，有“國酒”之稱，是中國最高端白酒之一。', '100', null, null, null, null, null), ('3479', '1985-1986年特供黑醬貴州茅臺酒', '1985-1986年特供黑醬貴州茅臺酒', '41', '/public/pic_content/img/a30/LOTNO_617_1.jpg', '617', '', '448,400', null, null, null, null, 'For detailed information, please refer to Chinese site', '醬茅、黃茅當年均是人民大會堂、釣魚臺國賓